NK088(su)001:1: // sa rba bud+d+ha s+ya sa n+d+hi sam g+r+aa ha s+au
NK088(su)001:2: tra pa ny+tsi k+aa ta mo ba r+m+ma ku ny+tsi
NK088(su)001:3: k+aa b+h+aa sa yo ga ta ra bi n+aa ma
NK088(su)001:5: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dgongs pa 'dus pa mdo'i
NK088(su)001:6: dka' 'grel mun pa'i go cha lde mig gsal byed
NK088(su)001:7: rnal 'byor nyi ma zhes bya ba stod cha bzhugs
NK088(su)001:8: so // bcom ldan 'das gsang ba'i bdag po phyag na rdo rje la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK088(su)001:9: phyogs bcu byin brlabs 'byung ba'i gleng gzhi /
NK088(su)001:10: dus bzhi rgyal sku rigs bdag la //
NK088(su)001:11: sangs rgyas so lung bstan brgyud pa'i gleng gzhi /
NK088(su)001:12: so'i dgongs pa gsang sngags don //
NK088(su)001:14: bcu gnyis tshe na'ang thos shing bsdus //
NK088(su)001:15: de gtan tshigs phyir gsang bdag skyes bur grags //
NK088(su)001:16: bdag gsang ba mchog pos dbang bskur 'chad par gnyer gtad pa'i rtags //
NK088(su)001:17: lag na rgya gram 'khor lo bskor //
NK088(su)001:18: gnas lang+ka'i grong brdal rgya mtsho'i do //
NK088(su)001:19: drag shul can rtser sdud pa lang+ka sogs //
NK088(su)001:20: 'khor skal ldan 'dus la bstan pa gsang ston pas //
NK088(su)001:21: des na 'chad pa'i skyes bu de //
NK088(su)001:22: sngon gyi go chas bskor mdzad pa //
NK088(su)001:24: bka' yi me long kun 'dus rgyud //
NK088(su)001:25: bstan pa'i gzugs brnyan gzhi rtsa'i don //
NK088(su)001:26: phyogs gang ma 'ongs dman don du //
NK088(su)001:27: lus kyi mngon sum bdag gis 'grel //
NK088(su)001:28: de la sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dgongs pa 'dus pa'i mdo /
NK088(su)001:30: gsang ba bas ches gsang ba /
NK088(su)001:31: yang gsang rmad du byung ba'i bka' khyad par can 'di /
NK088(su)001:32: dbu zhabs su don rnam pa gsum du 'dus shing /
NK088(su)001:36: bya ba byed pa'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK088(su)001:37: bya ba med pa'i rnal 'byor ro //
NK088(su)001:41: bdag nyid las mi gzhan pas bsgrub pa'i 'brel pa dgod pa dang /
NK088(su)001:42: de lta bu'i don gnyer byar byed pa dang /
NK088(su)001:43: 'bad pa chud ma zos pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:44: de dag ni dpe sa bon dang /
NK088(su)001:45: so nam gyi bya ba dang /
NK088(su)001:46: 'bad pas barnga btsas byas pa'i 'bras kyi phung po lta bu'o //
NK088(su)001:47: de'ang le'u re dgu pa las gsungs te /
NK088(su)001:48: grogs po dag /de bas na bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i rnam pa gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:49: 'di ltar bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i chos thams cad kyi rnam pa ni /
NK088(su)001:50: rnal 'byor rnam pa gsum gyis yongs su 'grel ba ste /
NK088(su)001:53: bya ba byed pa'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK088(su)001:54: bya ba med pa'i rnal 'byor ro //
NK088(su)001:56: kun 'dus kyi le'u dang po las kyang /
NK088(su)001:59: 'bras bu'i rnal 'byor dang gsum du 'dus par bka' stsal to //
NK088(su)001:60: 'on kyang rtsa ba'i rgyud las gsungs pas /
NK088(su)001:61: bshad pa'i rgyud 'di yang lugs ma nor bar bzhed do //
NK088(su)001:62: de la ni shes par bya ba'i yul dang /
NK088(su)001:64: zin pa'i sgo nas mtshan nyid gsum du'ang brjod do //
NK088(su)001:65: de la bya ba'i rnal 'byor ni /
NK088(su)001:66: snying po byang chub kyi ngo bo /
NK088(su)001:67: tha snyad thams cad ma spangs bral ba'i ye ji bzhin pa nyid do //
NK088(su)001:68: tha snyad du gsang sngags dngos po rgyud du'ang grags pa ngo bo 'di 'drar brjod pa med pa /
NK088(su)001:69: tha snyad de nyid du'ang zhen pas bzung ba dang bral ba'o //
NK088(su)001:70: de lta bu ma bcos ma bslad ma bsgyur ba'i ngang du thams cad rgyas thebs pa la /
NK088(su)001:71: bla dwags kyi ming nges par 'grub bo //
NK088(su)001:72: bya ba byed pa'i rnal 'byor ni /
NK088(su)001:73: lam mam rgyu'i theg pa ste /
NK088(su)001:74: 'dir gsang ba'i rgyud gtso bor ston pa'i phyir 'chad par 'gyur ro //
NK088(su)001:75: bya ba med pa'i rnal 'byor ni /
NK088(su)001:76: gsang sngags 'bras bu'i theg pa'i lam dang 'bras bu ste /
NK088(su)001:77: rgyal ba yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas /
NK088(su)001:81: bdag gi don rjes su thob zin pa dang /
NK088(su)001:82: gzhan gyi bya ba thams cad ma btsal bar rdzogs par byed pa dang /
NK088(su)001:83: de nyid la'ang rgyun gyi dus bral ba /
NK088(su)001:84: gang bya ba thams cad zin pa'i ye shes chen po mtshan nyid gang du'ang mi phyed pas /
NK088(su)001:85: mtshan nges par ldan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:86: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lngar 'dus pa ste /
NK088(su)001:87: mtshan nyid ni 'di 'drar bstan dka' bar ston pa'o //
NK088(su)001:88: de dag gi le'u'i mtshams bsdu ba ni /
NK088(su)001:90: le'u bdun cu rtsa lnga dag rnal 'byor gsum du
NK088(su)001:91: 'dus par man ngag gis 'jal bar byos shig /khas
NK088(su)001:92: blangs pa'i bya ba med pa'i rnal 'byor rgyas par
NK088(su)001:93: bshad pa ji lta bu zhe na /
NK088(su)001:101: rab kyi dbang du rnal 'byor lnga dang /
NK088(su)001:103: tha ma'i dbang du bzhi bcu la sogs pa'i shes rab bo //
NK088(su)001:104: de ni dpe zhing sa lta bu'o //
NK088(su)001:105: des rtogs pa byed pa'i rkyen ni bka' rgyud 'di nyid de chu lung lta bu'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:106: de la mdo nyid rkyen de'i rjes su dpags nas /
NK088(su)001:107: rgyu shes rab de dag gis rtogs par byed pa'i thabs tshul yang ji lta bu zhe na /
NK088(su)001:108: mos pa'i dbang gis dbang po rab mdor bstan pas go ba dang /
NK088(su)001:109: 'bring rnam par dbye bas go ba dang /
NK088(su)001:110: tha ma 'dren pa'i tshig gi yan lag bcus yi
NK088(su)001:111: ge zhib tu bshad pa la mos pas go ba'o
NK088(su)001:112: // de la rab kyi dbang du mdor bstan pas go ba'i tshul ni /
NK088(su)001:113: rta dkyus kyis bstan pa lta bus mtshan nges par brjod pa'i sgo nas 'jal ba ste /
NK088(su)001:114: skabs su zhib tu ston par 'gyur ro //
NK088(su)001:115: rnam par dbye bas go ba'i dbang du ni /
NK088(su)001:120: de la rgyud yin pa'i bshad thabs ni le'u zhe bdun pa las /
NK088(su)001:121: dam pa rnams kyi gsang ba'i sgo //
NK088(su)001:122: yan lag mdo dang rtsa ba yi //
NK088(su)001:124: de nyid nges par mthong ba'o //
NK088(su)001:125: 'byed pa rgyu dang rtsa ba dang //
NK088(su)001:126: 'brel pa'i tshig dang nges pa dang //
NK088(su)001:127: sbyor bas yan lag rdzogs pa yin //
NK088(su)001:134: de la rgyud ni yan lag sgo 'byed pa drug ste /
NK088(su)001:136: rtsa ba gleng bslang ba dang /
NK088(su)001:138: rgyud kyi don phun sum tshogs pa dang /
NK088(su)001:141: bka' drin dran pas bstod pa'o //
NK088(su)001:143: rtsa ba gsum la sogs pa'i ngo bo ni lung dang man ngag tu 'chad do //
NK088(su)001:144: de la re zhig gleng gzhi skabs 'dir gnyis te /
NK088(su)001:146: rgyu gleng gzhi gang 'byung ched phyir ni //
NK088(su)001:147: rgyu yi ngo bo byin gyis kyi gleng gzhi /
NK088(su)001:149: lung bstan brgyud pa'i gleng gzhi nyid du nges par snang //
NK088(su)001:151: dngos po dang po gleng gzhi gcig las med na'ang /
NK088(su)001:152: ston pas gtan tshigs 'byung khungs rgyu'i gleng gzhi dang /
NK088(su)001:153: byin rlabs de nyid brgyud pa'i gleng gazhi'o //
NK088(su)001:154: de la rgyu'i gleng gzhi'i ngo bo ni /
NK088(su)001:155: ston pa yang rgyas 'bring bsdus gsum ste /
NK088(su)001:158: kun tu bzang po rdo rje 'dzin pa'o //
NK088(su)001:159: gnas kyang zhing khams tha dad pa dang /
NK088(su)001:161: 'og min chen po'i gzhal yas khang ngo //
NK088(su)001:162: 'khor yang bzhi'am lnga las snang ba'i byang chub sems dpa' dang /
NK088(su)001:165: gsum ka'i sdud pa po phyag na rdo rje nyid do //
NK088(su)001:167: sku bzhi las thos pa'i dus dang /
NK088(su)001:168: 'byung 'byung ba'i dus tshul bcu gnyis kyi'ang tshe'o //
NK088(su)001:170: sems kyi dkyil 'khor 'od gsal ba gsang sngags ji bzhin pa nyid do //
NK088(su)001:172: yi ge gsum gyi don du bka' stsal to //
NK088(su)001:174: lung bstan brgyud pa'i gleng gzhi ni bzhi ni /
NK088(su)001:182: sh+aakya thub pa mya ngan las 'das khar 'khor bsdus nas /
NK088(su)001:183: 'khor la gdams ngag gsum bzhag nas /
NK088(su)001:184: byung tshul bcu gnyis kyi tshul gyis /
NK088(su)001:185: gsang sngags phyis 'byung bar lung bstan pa'o //
NK088(su)001:186: rgyu ni ston pa sh+aakya thub pa 'das nas /
NK088(su)001:187: dam pa lnga rig 'dzin sems dpa' rnams kyis ma la ya'i rtse mor 'dus nas /
NK088(su)001:188: gdung ba nyi shu rtsa gsum bton pa'o //
NK088(su)001:190: rgyal ba rnams kyis gdung ba gsan nas /
NK088(su)001:191: lcang lo can gyi pho brang du 'dus te /
NK088(su)001:192: phyag na rdo rje la 'jig rten du chos kyi 'khor lo bskor cig par bskul bas /
NK088(su)001:193: phyag na rdo rjes kyang zhal gyis bzhes pa'o //
NK088(su)001:194: rang gi ngo bo la drug ste /
NK088(su)001:195: ston pa ni phyag na rdo rje nyid de /
NK088(su)001:196: ston pa gang yin 'khor gyis dris pa dang /
NK088(su)001:197: 'khor gyi nang du lo rgyus gsungs pa brjod pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:198: de la ni mtshan nam ngo bo phyag na rdo
NK088(su)001:199: rje gnod 'dul rgyal po mi 'khrugs rdo rje sems
NK088(su)001:200: dpa' zhes bya'o // gnas ngo bo ni /
NK088(su)001:203: ma nges pa ni zhing tha dad pa'o //
NK088(su)001:206: ri ma la ya'i rtse mo /
NK088(su)001:207: chos 'dzin rigs kyi grub gnas nyid do //
NK088(su)001:208: 'khor ni rig 'dzin dam pa'i rigs can dag go //
NK088(su)001:209: sdud pa lang+ka'i mnga' bdag srin po mgrin bcu'o //
NK088(su)001:211: sh+aakya thub pa 'das nas lo nyi shu rtsa brgyad lon pa na'o //
NK088(su)001:212: bstan pa ngo bo ni rgyud 'di nyid do //
NK088(su)001:213: gleng gzhi bcas pa'i sbyor ba ni /
NK088(su)001:214: thugs rjes la gshegs pas sa rnams g.yos pa'o //
NK088(su)001:215: de bas na phyag na rdo rjes 'khor gyi nang du ngas gnas gang du /
NK088(su)001:217: dus gang gi tshe rgyud 'di thos par brjod pas /
NK088(su)001:219: gtan tshigs byung khungs kyi gleng gzhi brjod do //
NK088(su)001:220: mi yul du gdul bya smin par bya ba'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:221: byin rlabs brgyud pa'i gleng gzhi bstan te /
NK088(su)001:222: lhan cig pa dang brgyud kyis pa'i 'khor gyi dbang du'o //
NK088(su)001:223: don la rmongs pa gang la la dag sh+aakya thub pa ston pa yin no zhes smra ba ni /
NK088(su)001:224: rgyud kyi mtha' yang ma mthong ba'i blo bem po ste /
NK088(su)001:226: phyis bstan pa 'di gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:227: byin rlabs gleng gzhi kha cig 'og tu zhe bdun par phyung ba ni /
NK088(su)001:229: lung bstan brgyud pa'i gleng gzhi dus 'dir brtson par
NK088(su)001:230: bya'i dbang stee gleng bslang ba'ang rjes su mthun no
NK088(su)001:231: // gleng bslang ba'ang le'u 'di nyid las /
NK088(su)001:232: rtsa ba yan lag gang dag gi //
NK088(su)001:233: mdun bsu gus dang dri ba dris //
NK088(su)001:234: skabs las gleng du bslang ba'o //
NK088(su)001:237: ston pa phyag na rdo rjes mdun bsu ba dang /
NK088(su)001:238: dam pa lnga 'khor gyis gus pas dri ba rnams dris pa dang /
NK088(su)001:239: ston pa dang 'khor gnyis ka'i skabs las gleng du bslang ba'o //
NK088(su)001:240: de dag ni lung bstan brgyud pa'i gleng bslang bar sbyar ro //
NK088(su)001:241: gleng gzhi dang po rgyud byung khungs kyi gleng gzhi'i rjes su bsnyeg na /
NK088(su)001:242: 'khor dbang bskur bar gleng bslang ba dang /
NK088(su)001:243: rgyud bshad par gleng bslang ba'o //
NK088(su)001:244: de la zhe brgyad pa 'khor dbang bskur bar gleng bslang ba la'ang drug ste /
NK088(su)001:245: yum gyis bskul ba'i sa la bzhengs pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:246: ston pa sku gsung thugs mnyam pa nyid la bzhugs pa dang /
NK088(su)001:247: yum gyis dgongs pa la bzhengs par bskul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:248: bskul bas bzhengs pa dpe dang bcas par bstan pa dang /
NK088(su)001:249: ston par bzhengs nas rol pa nyi shu rtsa bzhi'i sgo nas sbyor ba la zhugs pa dang /
NK088(su)001:250: yum gyis sbyor ba'i bde ba las bzhengs par bskul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:251: ston pas bzhengs pa'i 'khor rnams la gsang ba'i dbang bskur ba'o //
NK088(su)001:252: rgyud bshad par gleng bslang ba la'ang /
NK088(su)001:253: yum gyis rgyud bshad par bskul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:254: ston pas zhu ba bsgugs pa'i phyir cang mi gsung bar bzhugs pa dang /
NK088(su)001:255: 'khor gyis sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las nyi shu rtsa lnga'i sgo nas bstod de /
NK088(su)001:256: rgyud bshad par gsol ba btab pa dang /
NK088(su)001:257: gsol ba btab pas ston pas 'od zer bkye nas /
NK088(su)001:258: 'od las theg pa gzhan gyi gleng gzhi snang bar mdzad pa dang /
NK088(su)001:259: ston pa rdo rje rgyan gyi ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs nas /
NK088(su)001:260: snod min rnams mtshams gcad pa dang /
NK088(su)001:261: thun mong gi 'khor rnams kyis bdag cag byin gyis rlobs shig par gsol ba btab pa dang /
NK088(su)001:262: ston pas 'od bkye nas 'khor thun mong ba rnams byin gyis brlab pa'i brdar bstan pa'o //
NK088(su)001:265: 'brel ba yan lag rnam pa bzhi //
NK088(su)001:266: rjod dang brjod bya dgos 'brel las //
NK088(su)001:273: de la rjod par byed pa ni /
NK088(su)001:275: ston pa 'khor dang bcas pa la bstan to //
NK088(su)001:276: 'adi'ang 'chad pa'i skyes bu phyag na rdo rje ste /
NK088(su)001:277: zhe dgu pa las bstan to //
NK088(su)001:278: brjod bya ni rgyud kyi don to //
NK088(su)001:280: rgyu dang 'bras bu'i tshul du 'brel pa ni /
NK088(su)001:281: rdo rje sems dpa' ston pa'i thugs de bzhin nyid las skyes pa ste /
NK088(su)001:282: bcom ldan 'das kyi thugs dang 'brel cing thugs las skyes pa dang /
NK088(su)001:283: thabs dang thabs las byung ba'i tshul du 'brel ba ni /
NK088(su)001:284: ston pas dbang bskur nas phyag na rdo rjes dbang thob ste /
NK088(su)001:287: dgos pa pa dang dgos pa'i yang dgos pa'o //
NK088(su)001:289: rgyud kyi don la ma dang rkyen dang bcas pa'o //
NK088(su)001:290: dgos pa'i yang dgos pa ni rnal 'byor lnga dang gsum gyi 'bras bu tha ma mthar phyin pa'o //
NK088(su)001:291: rgyud kyi don 'dren pa bcu'i nges don gtan tshigs kyi yan lag dang /
NK088(su)001:292: nges par sbyor ba'i yan lag gis rgyud kyi don bstan pa ni gnyis te /
NK088(su)001:295: gang don du gnyer bar byed pas mthar 'byin pa'i nus pa can gyi rnal 'byor lnga rab dang /
NK088(su)001:297: tha ma bzhi bcu ste nges pa gnyis su'o //
NK088(su)001:299: bslab pa'i mtha' rnam pa bcu dang /
NK088(su)001:300: nges pa dang sbyor ba'i rtog pa rnam pa bzhi dang /
NK088(su)001:301: chos rtags kyi phyag rgya bzhi dang /
NK088(su)001:302: mtshan nyid rnam pa bzhi dang /
NK088(su)001:306: dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa'i yan lag bzhi dang /
NK088(su)001:307: bsnyen bsgrub bzhi spyir sum cu rtsa gnyis ste nges pa rnam gnyis dang /
NK088(su)001:308: gzhan don du 'byung ba nyer brgyad dang /
NK088(su)001:309: de las gzhan pa bsgrub pa dang /
NK088(su)001:312: phrin las la sogs pa rnams bsdu'o //
NK088(su)001:313: rkyen dang bcas pa'i lam gong ma de dag gi skabs su ni /
NK088(su)001:317: rang gi rkyen gang dang ldan pa dang /
NK088(su)001:321: so so'i ltas gang ldan pa la sogs pa'i don khong 'jal du bya ste /
NK088(su)001:323: rgyud bshad pa'i dgos pa ni /
NK088(su)001:324: lhan cig pa'i 'khor rnams la bshad pa dang /
NK088(su)001:325: ma 'ongs pa'i brgyud pa'i 'khor rnams la phyag na
NK088(su)001:326: rdo rjes gdul bya gsum gyi don du theg pa
NK088(su)001:328: snod bzhi la gsang sngags bstan lugs bzhi'i snod bzhi dang sbyar bstan par mdzad pa'o //
NK088(su)001:329: bka' drin dran pas bstod pa'ang ston pa la bstod pa dang /
NK088(su)001:330: gsang ba'i rgyud la bstod pa'o //
NK088(su)001:331: de la lung yin pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:332: lung gi mdo gcod bzhi'i bshad pa dang /
NK088(su)001:333: man ngag yin pa'i phyir rtsa ba gsum gyis bshad pa ni /
NK088(su)001:335: klad du brjod mi dgos pa'i phyir 'dir ma smos so //
NK088(su)001:336: de lta bas na don ni gzhi lam 'bras bu'am
NK088(su)001:337: rgyud lung man ngag tshig gsum du ston pa las
NK088(su)001:338: la la dag byung tshul bcu gnyis su rgyud kyi
NK088(su)001:339: don bsdus par 'dod pa dag ni /
NK088(su)001:340: lo rgyus dang dus su rgyud kyi don sdud pa ste don la rmongs so //
NK088(su)001:342: byung tshul bcu gnyis yod kyang /
NK088(su)001:343: de dag ril du byung ba'i bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:344: rgyud 'di las med pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:346: de la dbang po tha ma 'dren pa'i tshig gi
NK088(su)001:347: yan lag bcu'i yi ge dpe bcus mtshon te bshad
NK088(su)001:348: pa la mos pa'i dbang du 'bru tshig bshad pa
NK088(su)001:350: 'dren pa'i tshig /de yang seng ge'i mchongs pa lta bu'i bshad pa'i dbang du /
NK088(su)001:351: rnal 'byor bya ba med pa'i go lugs dang po bstan te /
NK088(su)001:354: bod kyi mtshan bstan pas go ba'i tshul ni ji ltar yin zhe na /
NK088(su)001:356: sarba ta th+aa ga ta tsit+ta dz+ny+aa na gu h+ya ar+tha gar+b+ha ha badz+ra ta na tra /
NK088(su)001:357: sid+d+hi yo ga +aa ga ma sa m+aa dza sarba
NK088(su)001:358: bi d+y+aa s+au tra ma h+aa y+aa na a b+hi
NK088(su)001:359: sa ma ya d+har+m+aa par+y+au ya bi bya ha n+aa
NK088(su)001:360: ma su tra / bru zha'i skad du /
NK088(su)001:372: lo ts+aa ba d+harma bo d+hi dang /
NK088(su)001:373: che btsan skyes kyis rgya gar las bru zha'i skad du bsgyur ba'o //
NK088(su)001:374: de dag shan sbyar zhing bsgyur ba ni /
NK088(su)001:375: khungs btsun pa'i phyir smos pas the tshom mi za ba dang /
NK088(su)001:376: rang skad kyi mjal bar bya ba'i phyir rim par bsgyur la /
NK088(su)001:377: tshim gcig gis thad log tu 'ang 'gyur te /
NK088(su)001:378: b+h+yi d+ha r+ya tha b+h+yi d+ha su zhes pa dang /
NK088(su)001:379: 'ub pi su ces pa'i 'dug sa bsnol dgos pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:380: de dag las bod kyi yul du skad mthun par
NK088(su)001:381: bsgyur ba ni lo ts+aa ba d+aa na rak+shi ta
NK088(su)001:382: dang / che btsan skyes kyi lo rgyus smos pas /
NK088(su)001:383: yid ches par bya ba'i phyir skad gsum ka smos pa'o //
NK088(su)001:384: de la bod skad du bsgyur ba'i don bshad pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:386: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs gsang ba'i ye shes /
NK088(su)001:391: theg pa chen po mngon par rtogs pa /
NK088(su)001:392: chos kyi rnam grangs rnam par bkod pa /
NK088(su)001:393: zhes bya ba'i mdo zhes pa /
NK088(su)001:396: sgra'i shan sbyar ba ni thad log tu bsgyur ba ste /
NK088(su)001:397: gzhan ni go rim bzhin kyang /
NK088(su)001:402: sid+d+hi yo gi zhes pa la /
NK088(su)001:409: kun 'dus rig pa'i mdo zhes shan sbyar ba thad log tu gyur pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:410: don bshad pas go ba'i tshul ni /
NK088(su)001:411: rta dkyus kyis bstan pa dang 'dra bar khas blangs pa'i don 'dir bsnyad de /
NK088(su)001:413: tshig nyung du klad du smos pas /
NK088(su)001:414: dbu zhabs kyi don go bar bston te /
NK088(su)001:415: de la mtshan gyi tshig bdun gyi don ni /
NK088(su)001:416: ji bzhin pa de kho na nyid kyi rnam grangs yin pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:417: 'di'i don dkyil 'khor gsum po h'u m+aum gyi don 'jal bas ril 'jal bar 'gyur ro //
NK088(su)001:418: de'i tshul ni don ji bzhin par rang thad du bstan pa dang /
NK088(su)001:419: che ba'i sgo nas bstan pa'o //
NK088(su)001:420: de la ji bzhin par bshad pa ni /
NK088(su)001:421: gtan tshigs kyis rgyas thebs shing lung las snang bar bshad pa le'u re drug pa las /
NK088(su)001:422: lang ka'i bdag po de la rnam grangs brgyad gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:423: sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa 'dus pa'i mdo zhes kyang bya'o //
NK088(su)001:424: don gyi nying po zhes kyang bya'o //
NK088(su)001:425: rdo rje bkod pa'i rgyud zhes kyang bya'o //
NK088(su)001:426: rnal 'byor grub pa'i lung zhes kyang bya'o //
NK088(su)001:427: kun 'dus rig pa'i mdo zhes kyang bya'o //
NK088(su)001:428: theg pa chen po'i mngon par rtogs pa zhes kyang bya'o //
NK088(su)001:429: chos kyi rnam grangs rnam par bkod pa zhes kyang bya'o //
NK088(su)001:430: theg pa chen po'i byung tshul bstan pa'i mdo zhes kyang bya'o //
NK088(su)001:432: lang+ka'i bdag po gang la dgongs pa de nyid las mi 'da' ba dang /
NK088(su)001:433: gang gi spyod yul ma yin zhing med las thams cad 'byung ba dang /
NK088(su)001:434: gang gi ye shes yongs su bkod pa dang /
NK088(su)001:435: 'di ltar gang nges pa rnal 'byor du lung ston pa dang /
NK088(su)001:437: dam pa rnams kyis mngon par chud pa dang /
NK088(su)001:438: gang la yang ma 'dres par bkod pa dang /
NK088(su)001:439: gnas skabs bcu gnyis su nges par 'byung zhing byung ba'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:441: 'og ma rnams gtan tshigs dang sbrags mar brjod pa'i
NK088(su)001:442: don gyis mtshan brgyad du bstan pa ste des yid
NK088(su)001:445: gzhi ji bzhin pa nyid du son pas gdul bya
NK088(su)001:446: la sku tha dad par snang ba ril gyi dgong
NK088(su)001:447: pa ni / sems kyi dkyil 'khor rang gi rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal /
NK088(su)001:448: de kho na nyid ji lta nyid bzhin pa brtags na med pa bsams na snang ste /
NK088(su)001:449: mtshan nyid yongs su ldan par ma zin pas lam
NK088(su)001:450: pa'i bsam pas reg dka' ba'i ye shes chen po
NK088(su)001:451: la / dus gsum du g.yo ba med pa 'di ni /
NK088(su)001:452: dgongs pa ji snyed pa dang /
NK088(su)001:453: ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo 'bum phrag lhun gyis rdzogs pas dgongs pa 'dus pa zhes kyang brjod de /
NK088(su)001:454: rgyal ba ril dgongs pa de las mi 'da' ba'i phyir mtshan dang po'i don to //
NK088(su)001:455: shes par bya ba ji snyed pa dang /
NK088(su)001:456: bsgrub par bya ba ji snyed pa'i bdag nyid yin pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:457: yul dang bral bzhin lta ba dang /
NK088(su)001:458: 'bras bu thams cad du yang rang shar bas don gyi rtsa ba'o //
NK088(su)001:459: gnyis su med pa'i ye shes chen po ni /
NK088(su)001:460: skad cig ma'i rgyun du skye ba'i yul bral bas
NK088(su)001:461: sgrib pa'i phung po ji snyed pa ka nas dag
NK088(su)001:462: par byed pa'i ngo bo la /
NK088(su)001:463: ji snyed pa'i ye shes thams cad lhun gyis rdzogs pas rdo rje bkod pa'ang yin no //
NK088(su)001:464: gang don chen po la gnas shing goms par byed
NK088(su)001:465: pa rnams kyis ji lta ba'i don rnyed cing grub
NK088(su)001:466: pa'i gdengs can rnams dam par lung ston par byed
NK088(su)001:467: de / skyes bu dam pa lnga lung bstan pa la sogs pa'i phyir mtshan bzhi pa'o //
NK088(su)001:468: lhun gyis rdzogs pa'i theg pa chen po ni /
NK088(su)001:469: phyi mo nyid pas ril gyi yum yin pa'i phyir rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa ril gyi don dang /
NK088(su)001:470: log pa'i lam yan chad ma bkol bas so so'i
NK088(su)001:471: shan ma 'dres par gsal ba'i phyir mdo don gyi
NK088(su)001:472: che ba 'dir gcig pas mtshan lnga pa 'grub bo
NK088(su)001:473: // gang yang spangs pa dang dor ba med pa'i ngo bo ni /
NK088(su)001:474: snang ba dang mi snang ba las kyang grol bas
NK088(su)001:475: gsang sngags ji bzhin pa nyid de dngos theg pa
NK088(su)001:476: chen po'o // de ltar bu'i don dam pa rnams kyis rang rig pa'i mngon sum du byas te /
NK088(su)001:477: mthong ba med pas mthong bar byed pa'i thabs dang don gnyis ka 'di nyid do //
NK088(su)001:479: cha mthun gyi log lta la sogs pa ril ma
NK088(su)001:480: 'dres par gsal bar ngo bo ji bzhin pa la
NK088(su)001:481: rdzogs pa'i phyir yi ge'ang chos rnam par bkod pa'o
NK088(su)001:482: // de dag ni mtshan gyi rnam grangs bdun te dbu'i don to //
NK088(su)001:483: byung tshul bstan pa'i mdo brgyad kyi dbang du gnas
NK088(su)001:484: skabs bcu gnyis su'ang thun mong ma yin pa'i don
NK088(su)001:485: 'di nyid snang bas bya ba rdzogs par byed pa'i
NK088(su)001:486: phyir byung tshul bstan pa zhes kyang bya'o //
NK088(su)001:487: de ni byung tshul bcu gnyis kyi tshul ston pa'i le'u bdun cu rtsa lnga ji skad bstan kyang /
NK088(su)001:488: rgyu'i rim gyis pa dang 'bras bu cig car bas go zhing 'jug par bya rgyu /
NK088(su)001:489: ni dngos po rnams kyi de kho na nyid las mi snang la /
NK088(su)001:490: de'i mtshan gyi khyad par brgyad po ni bdun du
NK088(su)001:491: bsdus nas bstan pa de'i don rig pa'i ril rig
NK088(su)001:492: par smra'o // che ba'i don dang sbyar ba ni /
NK088(su)001:493: bstan pa gzhan las 'phags pa'i che ba bdun yang de kho na nyid kyi khyad par te /
NK088(su)001:495: rgyud thams cad kyi rgyal po /
NK088(su)001:496: man ngag thams cad kyi rtsa ba /
NK088(su)001:498: don thams cad kyi mjug sdud /
NK088(su)001:499: chos thams cad kyi me long /
NK088(su)001:500: bstan pa thams cad kyi 'byung gnas yin te /
NK088(su)001:502: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs gsang ba'i
NK088(su)001:503: ye shes ni bud+d+ha'i dgongs pa'i zhe phugs kyi phyir
NK088(su)001:504: rim gyis bgrod pa yin pas theg pa'i yang rtse'o
NK088(su)001:505: // don gyi snying po de kho na nyid ni man ngag gi rtsa ba'o //
NK088(su)001:506: rdo rje bkod pa'i rgyud ni /
NK088(su)001:507: rig pa'i bye brag ril gyi bdag nyid pas rgyal po'o //
NK088(su)001:508: rnal 'byor grub pa'i lung 'dis ril gtan la 'bebs pa dang /
NK088(su)001:509: bstan pa ril gyi don 'di la 'dus pas 'dis gcod pa dang /
NK088(su)001:510: gsang sngags pa ji bzhin pa nyid ji lta ba ma mthong pa mthong bar 'dis byed pa dang /
NK088(su)001:511: bka' rgyud ril lhun gyis grub pas 'di las snang ba'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:512: yin pa'i don gsum gyi gong du che ba bdun
NK088(su)001:513: bshad pa'i tshul gyis mtshan dang po dang gnyis pa
NK088(su)001:514: ni man ngag gi mtshan no //
NK088(su)001:515: bzhi pa dang lnga pa ni lung gi mtshan no //
NK088(su)001:516: gsum pa dang drug pa theg pa chen po'i mngon par rtogs pa /
NK088(su)001:517: dang bdun pa chos kyi rnam grangs rnam par bkod rgyud kyi mtshan du bstan to //
NK088(su)001:518: khong gi don 'gros kyis 'gal ba yang ma yin no //
NK088(su)001:519: bam po dang po ste zhes pa ni /
NK088(su)001:520: don gyi bam po dang tshig gi bam po las
NK088(su)001:521: 'dir tshig gtso bor byas nas shwa lo ka sum
NK088(su)001:522: brgya ni bam po gcig go //
NK088(su)001:523: des grangs kyi dang por bstan to //
NK088(su)001:524: sdud pa po phyag na rdo rjes ston pa rigs kyi bdag po nyid la mchod pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:525: bcom ldan 'das dpal sgrol byed thugs rje'i rgyal po
NK088(su)001:526: shin tu rnam par grol ba nyid la phyag 'tshal
NK088(su)001:527: lo // zhes pa rnal 'byor lnga'i mthar son pa'i ye shes chen po ni /
NK088(su)001:528: bya ba thams cad byas zin te /
NK088(su)001:529: thams cad kyi dngos gzhir bzhugs pa la /
NK088(su)001:530: spyod yul ka nas dag pas /
NK088(su)001:531: nyon mongs pa'i bdud bcom sdug bsngal gyi sa bon med pa dang /
NK088(su)001:532: de'i phyir na phung po'i bdud lnga phung gi ngo bo mi snang zhing /
NK088(su)001:533: 'chi 'chi bdag gi bdud 'pho ba'i chos bral ba la /
NK088(su)001:534: bar lha'i bdud chad ril ma dmigs pa'i tha tshig
NK088(su)001:535: dang ldan pa'i thugs ni legs pa'i bdag nyid kyang
NK088(su)001:536: / mtha' grol bas dngos gzhi bstan dka' ba ni chos kyi sku chen po nyid do //
NK088(su)001:537: de kho na'i phyir bdag gi dpal la gdul bya
NK088(su)001:538: gsum mdzad pa'i theg pa gsum gyis chu bo bzhi
NK088(su)001:539: las mthar son par byed pas sgro la byed gzhan
NK088(su)001:540: gyi dpal te sprul pa'i sku'i yang bdag nyid do
NK088(su)001:541: // dgongs pa sgrol byed de bzhin nyid dus gsum du 'byung 'jug bral te /
NK088(su)001:542: lhan ne lham me lhang nge bar rnal bzhin mdzad
NK088(su)001:543: thugs rje pa'i rlabs rgyun mi 'chad pa'i ngo bo
NK088(su)001:544: rgyal po mnga' thang yongs su rdzogs pa'i sku bzhugs
NK088(su)001:545: pa ni longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku chen po'i bdag
NK088(su)001:546: nyid do // de lta bu'i shin tu rnam par
NK088(su)001:547: ngo bo ye nyid 'ching ba dang bral ba dang
NK088(su)001:548: thabs dam pa'i ngo bor bzhugs pas thogs pa med
NK088(su)001:549: pa ni ngo bo nyid dang gsang ba'i sku ste
NK088(su)001:550: sku lnga rdzogs pa'i ngo bo ni kun tu bzang
NK088(su)001:551: po sangs rgyas he ru ka chen po nyid do
NK088(su)001:552: nyid do // // phyogs yul phyogs gcig pa gzhan ni skabs 'dir rnam par bcad do //
NK088(su)001:553: de nyid gsang bdag skyes bu nyid dang gcig dang
NK088(su)001:554: du ma bral ba'i tshul du rig pa ni mchod
NK088(su)001:556: de dag 'og ma pa dman pas lus ngag gis
NK088(su)001:557: mos par smra ba ni theg pa chen po'i nang
NK088(su)001:558: du mi 'gyur bas de la yid rton par mi
NK088(su)001:559: bya'o // gzhan lung bstan brgyud du lang kas 'dul ba'i skyes bu la mchod pa'o //
NK088(su)001:560: de ltar ston pa mchod nas bgro ba la 'jug pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:561: 'di skad bgro ba bdag gis thos pa'i dus gcig na zhes pa /
NK088(su)001:562: 'di nye bar mtshon pa ni bstan pa ste rgyud 'di nyid do //
NK088(su)001:563: skad gsal bar bgro ba ni ston pa ste /
NK088(su)001:564: zhing khams dang gnas tha dad na ston pa rnams kyis bgro bar byed pa'o //
NK088(su)001:565: bdag gis dngos po nyid bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:566: byung khungs gleng gzhi'i sdud pa phyag na rdo rje nyid de /
NK088(su)001:567: des gsan pa ni sku tha dad gcig kun tu bzang po /
NK088(su)001:568: dang bcu la'ang phyogs bcu'i bud+d+ha thos la /
NK088(su)001:569: sku bzhi la'ang so sor thos pa thos lugs bzhi'i tshul du thos te /
NK088(su)001:570: ngo bo ste so so'i thos bya ste bstan pa'o //
NK088(su)001:571: dus ni byung tshul bcu gnyis kyi tshe dang sku
NK088(su)001:572: bzhis bstan pa'i dus bzhi ste tshe skabs kyi don
NK088(su)001:575: lung bstan brgyud pa'i dbang du na /
NK088(su)001:576: ston pa la yang mchod pa ni /
NK088(su)001:577: srin po'i byang chub sems dpa' blo gros thabs ldan dngos lang ka mgrin bcus /
NK088(su)001:578: mthu stobs chen po'i mnga' bdag gsang ba'i bdag po
NK088(su)001:579: 'chad pa'i skyes bu gnod 'dul la phyag 'tshal nas
NK088(su)001:580: / mi yul du yi ge bsdu ba mdzad pa'o //
NK088(su)001:581: lang ka'i bdag pos bstan pa 'di /
NK088(su)001:582: phyag na rdo rjes zhing tha dad pa na rang gi ston pa la nyan nas /
NK088(su)001:583: nye 'khor la bgro ba bdag gis lang kas thos
NK088(su)001:584: pa'i dus te sh+aakya thub pa 'das nas lo nyi
NK088(su)001:585: shu rtsa brgyad kyi tshe sdud pa lang kas skad
NK088(su)001:586: gsal bar thos zhes yi ger bris pa'o //
NK088(su)001:587: gleng gzhi rnam gnyis kyi ngo bo thun mong du bstan pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:588: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad zhes pa mang po bsdus pa'i sgras /
NK088(su)001:589: ril gyi bdag nyid rigs kyi gtso bo drug pa
NK088(su)001:590: ste mtshan rdo rje 'dzin pa chen po zhes kyang
NK088(su)001:591: bya'o // rnam pa gcig tu na /
NK088(su)001:592: lung bstan brgyud pa'i dbang du de bzhin gshegs pa
NK088(su)001:593: thams cad kyi bcom ldan 'das ni dngos gsang ba'i
NK088(su)001:594: bdag po phyag na rdo rje nyid de /
NK088(su)001:595: dbang thob pas rgya gram 'khor lo lag na bsnams pas mtshan rdo rje 'dzin pa zhes bya'o //
NK088(su)001:596: don ston pa las ji skad thos pa ltar dman
NK088(su)001:597: pa'i lus can la ston pa'i 'chad pa'i skyes bu
NK088(su)001:598: smra ba'i seng ge barla bkyal gyi spobs pa can
NK088(su)001:599: gyi byin rlabs thob pas 'khor gyi nang du 'gying
NK088(su)001:600: bag gis 'khor lo bskor ba dang /
NK088(su)001:601: seng ge rol pa'i ga zha mdzad pa'i phyir seng ger brjod pa nyid do //
NK088(su)001:603: 'di ltar sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams bsam gyis mi khyab pa na zhes pa la sogs pa /
NK088(su)001:604: byung khungs kyi don du na gnas ni zhing khams bsam gyis mi khyab pa /
NK088(su)001:605: ston pa ni phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba dang rigs lnga la sogs pa'o //
NK088(su)001:606: de na sems can gyi gnas tha dad na /
NK088(su)001:607: ji ltar 'dul ba'i sku bzhugs te mdzad pa'i phrin
NK088(su)001:608: las ni chos ston te gdul ba smin par mdzad
NK088(su)001:609: pa yang / bstan pa shin tu zab bsam gyis
NK088(su)001:610: mi khyab cing mtha' dang bsam du med pa mu
NK088(su)001:611: med pa'i dpag tu med pa'i rgyal ba'i kun gyis
NK088(su)001:612: pa yang / basngagasa pa / dgongs pa'i zhe phugs mthar thug pa /
NK088(su)001:614: de ril bsnums pas de kun thams cad ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs par rang gsal ba /
NK088(su)001:615: smrar med cing spyod yul du ma gyur la /
NK088(su)001:616: yon tan gyis bzhag pa'i mtshan nyid bstan du yod la ngo bo med pa ste /
NK088(su)001:617: bla dwags thams cad dang bral ba /
NK088(su)001:618: ji snyed pa'i chos so cog gi de kho na nyid ma bcos ji bzhin pa ma bslad pa /
NK088(su)001:619: dngos po gnyis kyi gzhi chos ril dang lam rnal
NK088(su)001:620: 'byor gsum ril gsal bar ston pa'i bka' 'di las
NK088(su)001:622: der sdud pa po phyag na rdo rjes zhing khams so so'i rgyal ba la gus pas nyan cing /
NK088(su)001:623: dman pa'i lus can dag la ma nor bar ston pas 'chad pa po yang yin te /
NK088(su)001:624: de rang gis 'khor la zhing khams tha dad na
NK088(su)001:625: 'chad pa'i tshul ni nye bar 'di lta ste bstan
NK088(su)001:626: pa'o // de ltar gleng gzhi byin rlabs lung bstan
NK088(su)001:627: gnyis thun mong du 'chad par 'gyur pa dag la'ang
NK088(su)001:628: pa'o // sbyar ro // zhing khams so so nas rgyas par bstan pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:629: sangs rgyas mi bskyod pa'i zhing khams mngon par dga' ba /
NK088(su)001:630: zhes pa la sogs pa mi bskyod pa ni ston pa nyid do //
NK088(su)001:631: zhing khams ni bzhugs sa dang 'dul ba gnyis te gnas dang gdul bya'o //
NK088(su)001:632: ci mngon par dga' ba kho nar bstan pa ci lta bu zhe na /
NK088(su)001:633: rgyal ba mi bskyod pa de dang po de bzhin
NK088(su)001:634: gshegs pa rdo rje 'chang chen po la byang chub
NK088(su)001:635: mchog tu sems bskyed pa'i dus su zhing khams 'dir
NK088(su)001:636: mtshan de skad ces bya bar 'gyur ba'i lung bstan
NK088(su)001:638: gnas de ni yangs shing mnyam pa la rin po che'i gcal bkram pa /
NK088(su)001:639: chu yan lag brgyad dang ldan pa /
NK088(su)001:640: shing yal ga phyogs bzhir gyes pa /
NK088(su)001:641: dus bzhi'i dgra las skyob pa /
NK088(su)001:643: der skye ba thams cad sems mngon par dga' bar byed pa dang ldan pa'i phyir mtshan nges pa'o //
NK088(su)001:644: ye shes lnga'i ngo bor gsal ba'i phyir rdo rje d+r+wa ba'i 'od zer dang ldan pa /
NK088(su)001:645: ri'i phyogs gang nas bltas kyang rdo rje'i rtse mo'i
NK088(su)001:646: dbyings su snang ba'i gnas de na skyes bu chen
NK088(su)001:647: po sems dpa' rdo rje de ni /
NK088(su)001:648: gleng gzhi gnyis kyi don gyis zhing khams 'dir mi
NK088(su)001:649: bskyod pa dang phyag na rdo rje gnyis ka'i mtshan
NK088(su)001:650: du sbyar ro // byang chub sems dpa' ni bye
NK088(su)001:651: ba phrag sa ya'i de snyed de 'khor phun sum
NK088(su)001:652: du sbyar ro // tshogs pa'o // bstan pa ni
NK088(su)001:653: byang chub sems lhun gyis rdzogs pa gang dang yang
NK088(su)001:654: lhan mi gcig pas sgrib byed ngang gis med pa
NK088(su)001:655: ngo bo 'od gsal yongs su gzung dka' ba ni
NK088(su)001:656: gsang sngags dngos rgyud 'di nyid do //
NK088(su)001:657: de sdud pa po phyag na rdo rjes rang gi
NK088(su)001:658: ston pa mi bskyod pa la nyan cing 'chad pa'i
NK088(su)001:659: skyes bur snang bas rang gi nye 'khor la yang
NK088(su)001:660: 'di ston te / de bzhin gshegs pa de sku
NK088(su)001:661: mya ngan las 'das kyang zhing de na chos thams
NK088(su)001:662: cad de bzhin nyid ji bzhin pa de kho na
NK088(su)001:663: nyid dman pa'i lus can gyi 'khor la bgro bar
NK088(su)001:664: 'di ston te / byed do // 'o na zhing
NK088(su)001:665: khams gcig tu ston pa gnyis ston pa ni mi
NK088(su)001:666: srid pas chos dang 'gal lo zhe na /
NK088(su)001:667: zhing de'i ston pa ni mi bskyod pa nyid yin la /
NK088(su)001:668: phyag na rdo rje de tsam na 'khor gyi gtso
NK088(su)001:669: bo byang chub sems dpa'i cha byad du snang ba'i
NK088(su)001:670: phyir rgyal ba nyid ma yin pas rgyal tshab rgyud
NK088(su)001:671: kyi ston pa yin pa mi 'gal lo //
NK088(su)001:672: gleng gzhir ngos gzung bar sbyar gzhan dag la'ang de ltar sbyor ro //
NK088(su)001:674: zhing khams dpal dang ldan pa zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK088(su)001:675: zhing khams de na gdul bya'i longs spyod ji ltar
NK088(su)001:676: 'dod pa 'byung ba dang tshe dang bsod nams mchog
NK088(su)001:678: de na rin po che sna tshogs kyi phung po
NK088(su)001:679: de la bkod pa rtse mo la nor bu bee
NK088(su)001:680: d+aur+ya'i ri shin tu mtho zhing 'od 'bar ba yod
NK088(su)001:681: pa'i phyir ro // zhing khams bde ba can pad+mo
NK088(su)001:682: mdzes pa zhes bya ba la sogs pa zhing de
NK088(su)001:683: na sems can chen po thams cad pad+mo las bardzusa
NK088(su)001:684: te skye zhing bde ba dang ldan zhing bar ma
NK088(su)001:685: dor 'chi ba dang 'thab rtsod dang zas skom dang
NK088(su)001:686: khur dang sdug bsngal du bya ba med pa'i phyir
NK088(su)001:687: pa'i phyir ro // ro // zhing de la pad+mo sna tshogs kyis mdzes pa /
NK088(su)001:688: ri'i dbyibs pad+ma brtsegs pa lta bur snang ba'i gnas so //
NK088(su)001:689: zhing khams rnam par dag pa /
NK088(su)001:691: zhing de na las dag pa'i sems can rnams skye
NK088(su)001:692: ste ngan pa'i las lam dag mi spyod pa sha
NK088(su)001:693: stag ste / shin tu dag pa'i las lam spyod pa la mos pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:694: de la rin po che in+d+ra n+ai la shin tu mdzes pas brgyan pa /
NK088(su)001:695: rin po che sna tshogs kyi 'phra bkod pa'i rin po che ni gnas so //
NK088(su)001:696: byang chub kyi snying po can zhes bya ba /
NK088(su)001:698: zhing de'i 'khor gyi byang chub sems dpa' thams cad byang chub kyis gnon pa /
NK088(su)001:699: lung stan pa thob pa sha stag gnas pa /
NK088(su)001:700: gdul bya'i bsam pa rnam par dag pa /
NK088(su)001:701: ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo mang po rdzogs pa'i gnas /
NK088(su)001:702: dgongs pa mi g.yo pa khyad par chen pos dpag pas gnas de 'og min zhes bya'o //
NK088(su)001:703: zhing khams mos pa can mi mjed /
NK088(su)001:705: lnga po rnams su'ang gsan la zhing khams 'di nyid du'ang thos pa'o //
NK088(su)001:706: zhing de na mos pa spyod pa'i byang chub sems
NK088(su)001:707: dpa' mang zhing 'khor rnams mos brtson dang ldan pa
NK088(su)001:709: 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug la sogs pa la sems mi mjed pa /
NK088(su)001:710: 'jig rten phyogs cha drug dang gnas drug rer la'ang phyogs bcu dang ldan pa /
NK088(su)001:711: rdo rje'i gdan dpag tshad brgyad cu gser las grub
NK088(su)001:712: cing srab ste 'og rdo rje'i brag tu snang ba
NK088(su)001:713: / bya rgod phung po'i ri bo zhes bya bar thub pa'i dbang po la yang nyan cing /
NK088(su)001:714: gnod sbyin gyi gnas byang phyogs lcang lo can gyi
NK088(su)001:715: pho brang na dman pa'i lus can rnams la ston
NK088(su)001:716: to // 'o na thub pa'i dbang po rgyud 'di'i ston par 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK088(su)001:717: de ni zhing khams sgron ma bkod pa ril gyi rgya ba la gsan pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:718: thub pa'i dbang po gcig pu'i ston par mi 'gyur ro //
NK088(su)001:719: 'o na thub pa'i dbang pos rgyu'i theg pa las
NK088(su)001:720: ma gsungs par gsang sngags nyan par ji lta bu
NK088(su)001:721: zhe na / thub pa'i dbang pos rgyu'i byang chub
NK088(su)001:722: sems dpa' dang lha mi skal ba can la sogs
NK088(su)001:723: pa la rgyu'i 'khor lo'i tshig tu bskor la /
NK088(su)001:724: 'bras bu'i byang chub sems dpa' la gsang sngags ji bzhin pa bstan nas /
NK088(su)001:725: gzhan la 'dul ba'i dus la ma bab pas phyis
NK088(su)001:726: 'byung bar bstan pa 'gal ba ma yin par bka'
NK088(su)001:727: lung du ma la gsungs so //
NK088(su)001:728: 'khor gnod sbyin rigs can ni gnod 'dul nyid dang
NK088(su)001:729: rigs mthun pas gsang sngags la mos pa rnams so
NK088(su)001:730: // de bzhin du sangs rgyas bsam gyis mi khyab pa /
NK088(su)001:731: zhes bya ba la sogs pa /
NK088(su)001:732: zhing khams thams cad kyi sprul sku ston pa thams
NK088(su)001:733: cad la'ang gsang ba'i bdag po mtshan grangs med par
NK088(su)001:734: so sor grags pa pos thos nas 'khor la ston
NK088(su)001:735: to // ston pa de dag 'das pa'i dus su
NK088(su)001:736: gsang sngags kyi 'khor lo bskor ba las sku bzhugs
NK088(su)001:737: pa'i dus su ni mi yul du gsang ba ston
NK088(su)001:739: de bzhin du chos kyi sku'i zhing khams /
NK088(su)001:741: snying po byang chub ni 'og min chen po chos thams cad kyi de bzhin nyid do //
NK088(su)001:742: 'khor rigs lnga la sogs pa rgyal ba rgya mtsho dang gsal ba bas lnga la thob pa'o //
NK088(su)001:743: de la gcig tu ma dang bral ba'i tshul gyis
NK088(su)001:744: bzugs nas sems nyid ye ji bzhin par tshig tu
NK088(su)001:745: ma phyung bar dgongs pa nges par 'grel to //
NK088(su)001:746: de lta bas na chos kyi sku las kyang thos so //
NK088(su)001:748: zhes pa la sogs pa smos pa'i sems can ji
NK088(su)001:749: snyed pa'i gnas ris tha dad pa na ston pa'i
NK088(su)001:750: sku ji ltar mos shing 'dul ba ltar snang bas
NK088(su)001:751: cha mthun pa'i 'khor la so so'i skad du chos
NK088(su)001:753: nye 'khor la ston pa de dag 'das nas ston
NK088(su)001:754: pa yang gsang ba po ste mtshan tha dad du
NK088(su)001:755: byung nas brda skad tha dad kyis ston to //
NK088(su)001:756: 'o na dmyal ba la sogs pa la rang rang
NK088(su)001:757: gi gnas ngan na rang rang skad du chos ston
NK088(su)001:759: yod de de yang ngan 'gro'i skal can dag la
NK088(su)001:760: so so'i thub pa snang bas sdug bsngal de dag
NK088(su)001:762: 'khor de dag skal ba dang sa mnyam pa nyi tshe'am snyam pa la /
NK088(su)001:763: de dag sa mtho dman dang skal ba che chung yod pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:764: de lta bu'i byang chub sems dpa' de dag kyang /
NK088(su)001:766: 'khor lnga phrag drug gnyis gcig gi don bstan te
NK088(su)001:767: 'di dag ni lam la gnas pa sha stag go
NK088(su)001:768: // de yang thun mong gi lam dang khyad par
NK088(su)001:769: gyi lam gnyis 'dir thun mong du bstan kyang don
NK088(su)001:770: gyis thun mong ma yin pa'i lam du 'jal bar
NK088(su)001:771: bya ste gsang sngags nyan pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:772: mi mthun pa ston pa ni skal bas mtho dman lngar 'gyur ro //
NK088(su)001:773: lnga phrag dang po la la ni byang chub kyi rigs can dag go //
NK088(su)001:775: dgar ba ni nang ris 'byed pa'o //
NK088(su)001:776: 'di lnga'ang 'dun pa byed pas brgyud nas 'khor ba
NK088(su)001:777: las nges par 'byung ba ba'i blo dang ldan pa'i
NK088(su)001:778: phyir tshogs dang / don khong du chud pas slob
NK088(su)001:779: pa bas don mthong la ma rag sbyor pa'i phyir
NK088(su)001:780: phyir tshogs dang / dang / sngar don ji lta
NK088(su)001:781: bar ma mthong bar mthong bas don dang shes rab
NK088(su)001:783: rtogs sgom pa las kyang ting nge 'dzin gyis yang
NK088(su)001:784: nas yang du gom par byed pas 'gro don gyis
NK088(su)001:785: sprul pa mang po yang mi 'gog pa'i phyir dang
NK088(su)001:786: / mthar goms pa mthar phyin nas ltos pa'i bya ba yongs su rdzogs pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:787: mtshan gyi khyad par ni gong 'og la ltos nas 'jog pa'o //
NK088(su)001:788: de bzhin du gzhi lam lnga lnga las btags pa tha dad du grags pa ni /
NK088(su)001:791: skal ba gong 'og rang rang thad du mnyam pa'i
NK088(su)001:792: gzhi lnga las mtshan gyi rnam pa tha dad du
NK088(su)001:793: grags pa rnams nye bar bstan pa ni gang zhe
NK088(su)001:794: na / gnyis pa 'dun pa'i rnal 'byor du gnas
NK088(su)001:795: pas rtogs pa'i mthu khyad par can du ma gyur
NK088(su)001:796: kyang thun mong ma yin pa'i don la rjes su
NK088(su)001:797: yi rang bas rtsol ba dag dang /
NK088(su)001:798: mnyam pa chen po'i ngo bo gang du'ang mi zin
NK088(su)001:799: pa'i don bstan pa la mi skrag mi sngangs ba
NK088(su)001:800: dag dang / ji bzhin pa mthong ba'i shes rab
NK088(su)001:801: kyi spyan dang ldan pas lta ngan dang sgrib pa
NK088(su)001:802: dang nyon mongs pa'i rdul dang dri ma dag pa
NK088(su)001:803: dag dang / dang / yang nas yang du goms
NK088(su)001:804: pas sgom pas mi g.yo ba mtshan ma la sogs
NK088(su)001:806: bslab pa mthar phyin pas sangs rgyas pa'i mtshan dang
NK088(su)001:807: zhing khams kyi lung bstan pa thob pa dag go
NK088(su)001:808: // gsum pa'i rnal 'byor lnga yang de nyid las /
NK088(su)001:809: gzhi tha dad du snang ba ni /
NK088(su)001:810: bla ma dang gsang ba la 'dun pa'i rgyus yang
NK088(su)001:811: dag pa'i don la phyogs pa'i rnal 'byor dang po
NK088(su)001:812: pa dang / theg pa chen po la zhugs mi
NK088(su)001:813: 'gyur bas nas dad pas de don rang gis mtshan
NK088(su)001:814: nyid du mos shing rtsal sbyong ba'i rnal 'byor gnyis
NK088(su)001:815: pa dang / pa dang / chos ji lta bu
NK088(su)001:816: mthong bas dbugs phyin pa ngal sos pas bsti gnas
NK088(su)001:818: skye ba phyi ma la mdzad pa mthar phyung nas 'tshang rgya ba byams pa lta bu dang /
NK088(su)001:819: skye ba 'di nyid kyis mdzad pa mthar dbyung nas 'tshang rgya ba rgyal bu don grub lta bu'o //
NK088(su)001:820: bzhi pa kun gzhi skabs lnga /
NK088(su)001:821: gzhi nyid rgyu'i kun gzhi'i stobs kyis sems rgyu rkyen drug gis lam dam pa la 'jug pa dang /
NK088(su)001:822: sbyor ba 'dun pa'i kun gzhi'i stobs kyis bslab pa
NK088(su)001:823: la zhugs nas gong ma la sbyor zhing skyed du
NK088(su)001:824: 'gro ba dang / snang ba don gyi kun gzhi'i
NK088(su)001:825: stobs kyis ji bzhin pa nyid du ngal sos te
NK088(su)001:826: 'dzin pa dang bral ba rig pa la mjal ba
NK088(su)001:827: 'gro ba dang / dang / 'gyur ba med pa'i
NK088(su)001:828: kun gzhi'i stobs yod pas 'gro dgongs pa las ma
NK088(su)001:829: g.yos par sprul pa'i lus kyis 'gro don byed don
NK088(su)001:830: la phyir skye ba tha dad rang dbang du bzhes
NK088(su)001:831: 'gro ba dang / dang / pa dang / btsal
NK088(su)001:832: med gnas pa'i kun gzhi'i stobs kyis bya ba med
NK088(su)001:833: par gnas pa'i phyir 'jug rim mo //
NK088(su)001:834: lnga pas sems lnga byang chub 'dod pa shes pa'i
NK088(su)001:835: phyir bla ma la dad gsang sngags kyi don rtogs
NK088(su)001:837: pa'i sems chos kyi rnam pa shes pa'i phyir de
NK088(su)001:838: la mi gnas par dad pa dang rtsol bas langs
NK088(su)001:839: te sbyor ba'i sems pa ba dang /
NK088(su)001:840: lta ba don thams cad shes pa'i phyi don la
NK088(su)001:841: rig pa gnyis med du 'jug pa 'i sems dang
NK088(su)001:842: / lam yongs su shes pa'i phyir ting nge 'dzin la gnyis med kyis gnas pa 'i sems dang /
NK088(su)001:843: shes pa chen po mnga' ba'i phyir bslab pa rdzogs
NK088(su)001:844: pa 'i sems ste sems mthar thug pa'i ye shes
NK088(su)001:846: drug pa bsti gnas lnga las sbyong ba'i bsti gnas
NK088(su)001:847: pa'i phyir tshogs la sgo gsum gyis rtsol ba dang
NK088(su)001:848: / bslab pa sbyong ba'i bsti gnas pa'i phyir mtha' bcu la slob pa mi 'bral ba dang /
NK088(su)001:849: mtshan ma'i rgyud spyong ba'i bsti gnas bden pa mthong
NK088(su)001:850: bas zag bcas la mi slob pa'i ba'i phyir dang
NK088(su)001:851: / sgyu mas sbyong ba'i bsti gnas bslab pa med
NK088(su)001:852: pa'i don ting nge 'dzin yang nas yang bsgom pa'i
NK088(su)001:853: / phyir dang / ye shes rtsal gyi bsti gnas
NK088(su)001:854: pa'i phyir rdo rje lta bu'i gnyis med kyi don
NK088(su)001:855: nam rgyan gyi 'khor lo rang rig mngon du gyur
NK088(su)001:857: bdun pas byang chub lnga sems bskyed pa'i rigs can yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:858: byang chub pa'i rigs su nges pa yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:859: don mthong bas byang chub sems dpa' yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:860: byang chub rnam gnyis la gnas te bsgom pas sems dpa' chen po yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:861: byang chub chen po yin te nye 'khor la chos ston nus pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:862: 'gyur dbang brgyad pas sa lnga ma nges pa'i sa
NK088(su)001:863: pa sa bon nam ras bal dang 'dra bas gang
NK088(su)001:864: du'ang 'gyur du btub pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:865: nges par zhugs pas mi 'chor ba'i phyir myu gu'am snam bu dang 'dra ba dang /
NK088(su)001:866: 'dab ma bkru btsag lta bur sbyangs pas don mthong ba 'khor bar mi ldog pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:867: me tog gam 'jen tshur ltar gom pas 'bras bur byed pa'i don mthong dka' ba'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:868: 'bras bu dang chos kyi kha dog tu 'gyur ba
NK088(su)001:869: dang 'dra ste yon tan mang po dang ldan pa'i
NK088(su)001:870: phyir ro // dgu pas mthar phyin lnga lam mthar phyin par byed pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:871: bslab pa mthar phyin par byed pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:872: mthong ba mthar phyin pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:873: ting nge 'dzin mthar phyin pa dang /
NK088(su)001:874: grub pa mthar phyin pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:875: bcu pas ting nge 'dzin lnga yid la byed pa'i
NK088(su)001:876: ting nge 'dzin thob pa'i phyir bdun pa'i rnal 'byor
NK088(su)001:877: pa dang / 'phro 'du gcig pa'i ting nge 'dzin
NK088(su)001:878: thob pas yang dag pa'i rigs su 'gro ba'i phyir
NK088(su)001:879: pa dang / dang / yongs su mi ldog pa'i
NK088(su)001:880: ting nge 'dzin thob pas dbugs dang po phyin pa
NK088(su)001:881: pa dang / dang / dang / de bzhin nyid
NK088(su)001:882: kyi ting nge 'dzin thob pas rgyal ba'i bka' lung
NK088(su)001:883: pa dang / dang / dang / thob pa dang
NK088(su)001:884: / kun tu snang gi ting nge 'dzin thob pas
NK088(su)001:885: bdag gzhan bya ba rdzogs pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:886: bcu gcig pas tshogs pa lnga tshig dang sgra la slob pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:887: yi ge 'phro 'du la gnas pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:888: thams cad ming tsam las ngo bo med par shes pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:889: brda dang ting nge 'dzin gyis grol ba'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:890: dbyings dang ye shes kyi tha snyad du shes shing
NK088(su)001:891: byang chub sems kyi don du 'jal ba'i phyir ro
NK088(su)001:892: // de dag las gzhi gsum pa ni /
NK088(su)001:894: spyod yul gyi gsum pa bden pa mthong ba'i skabs
NK088(su)001:895: las btags te dbugs mtha' ma phyin pa ni ma
NK088(su)001:896: yin no // bcu gnyis pa tshogs la gnas pas
NK088(su)001:897: lus ngag gi spyod pa gtso bor byed pa'i phyir
NK088(su)001:898: yin no // dang / mos pas shes rab dang ting nge 'dzin la gnas pa dang /
NK088(su)001:899: des don rang rig pa'i mngon sum du thob pa dang /
NK088(su)001:900: gzhan don du byang chub phyir sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:902: bcu gsum pa rig 'dzin lnga mtshan ma tshig gi
NK088(su)001:903: rnal 'byor pa don yid la byed pa tsam ste
NK088(su)001:905: rigs su nges pas rnal 'byor gnyis la rtsol zhing gnas pas sa la gnas pa'i rig 'dzin dang /
NK088(su)001:906: don rtogs pas 'jig pa lnga spang ba'i phyir tshe la dbang thob pas tshe'i rig 'dzin dang /
NK088(su)001:907: lung nges par thob ste rnal 'byor la gnas pas
NK088(su)001:908: mtshan dang dpe byad kyi sku mchog mngon du snang
NK088(su)001:909: ba'i phyir dang / bslab pa mthar phyin te skad
NK088(su)001:910: cig snga phyi rag lus pa tsam las rtsol ba
NK088(su)001:912: klag 'dir gzhi lnga las nang ris de dag tu
NK088(su)001:913: phye zhing bstan pa ci dgos lnga phrag gcig gis
NK088(su)001:915: de ni mdo sngags kyi grags lugs dang sangs rgyas
NK088(su)001:916: kyi zhing tha dad pa'i phyir dang don gcig la
NK088(su)001:917: sgra tha dad shes par bya ba'i phyir bkod do
NK088(su)001:918: // 'on kyang 'di ni rgyud 'di nyid kyi lam
NK088(su)001:919: la gnas pa'i mtshan tha dad par 'jal te lam
NK088(su)001:920: la de dag la gsang sngags de kho na nyid
NK088(su)001:921: kyi chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bas sa nas sar
NK088(su)001:923: de dag dus nam gyi tshe zhe na /
NK088(su)001:924: 'khor ba thog ma dang tha ma med par gdung 'tshob 'khor mor snang ba'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:925: de ltar na 'jig rten gyi khams tha dad pa na /
NK088(su)001:927: gnas ji snyed kyi 'dzam gling de snyed du ston
NK088(su)001:928: pa de dag snyed byung nas chos kyi sgron mas
NK088(su)001:929: gdul bya'i ma rig pa'i ling tog bsal te bya
NK088(su)001:931: sprul pa de dag nyi zla nub pa ltar sku
NK088(su)001:932: mya ngan las 'ada'o zhes dus snga phyir zhing de
NK088(su)001:933: dag tu grags shing gdul bya la snang ngo //
NK088(su)001:934: de lta bas na zhing 'dir thub pa'i dbang po
NK088(su)001:935: mya ngan las 'da' ba'i sgra ngang 'das pa ltar
NK088(su)001:936: snang ba yang dus 'khor mo'i skabs cig bzung ba'i
NK088(su)001:937: phyir ro // thun mong bcas gzhi'i le'u ste dang
NK088(su)001:938: po'o ////zhes pa 'dir gtan tshigs byung khungs dang byin
NK088(su)001:939: rlabs brgyud pa'i gleng gzhi gnyis thun mong du bstan
NK088(su)001:940: phyir ro // pa'i phyir ro // de bas na gos dang 'dra ste /
NK088(su)001:941: don gyi tshoms ma 'dres par ston pa'i phyir le'u ste thog mar bshad pa'o //
NK088(su)001:942: de nas gleng gzhi gnyis pa lung bstan brgyud pa'i gleng gzhi'i rgyu'i rgyu shes par bya ba'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:943: de nas ji ltar de ltar 'di ltar mi mjed ces bya ba'i /
NK088(su)001:944: zhes pa la sogs pa stag gi tshul gyis bshad de /
NK088(su)001:945: snyegs pa ni thun mong phyogs gcig gi gleng gzhi
NK088(su)001:946: la snyegs pas rgyu'i rgyu dang 'brel par mtshams sbyar
NK088(su)001:947: ba'o // de yang byung ba'i tshul dang /
NK088(su)001:949: nye bar ston pa 'byung ba ste dug gsum pa
NK088(su)001:950: sems mi 'phro ba'i zhing 'di na ston pa'i sku
NK088(su)001:951: shin tu sra zhing bdud kyi dpung bcom pa'i sh+aakya
NK088(su)001:952: thub pa de sku snang ba'i dus skye dgu mi'i
NK088(su)001:953: tshe lo brgya pa la byung ste /
NK088(su)001:954: yun lo brgyad cu rtsa gnyis bzhugs nas rtag tu
NK088(su)001:955: re ba sun dbyung ba'i phyir sku rdo rje lta
NK088(su)001:956: bu mi snang zhing 'da' bar dgongs nas rgya gar
NK088(su)001:957: gyi yul yangs pa can du 'khor rnam bzhi la
NK088(su)001:958: sogs pa ji snyed pa dang thabs gcig tu bzhugs
NK088(su)001:959: te / dbyar zla ba gsum 'das nas ston zla
NK088(su)001:960: ra ba'i nya la 'da' bas 'khor la zhal chems
NK088(su)001:961: gsum bzhag pa'i dgos ched du 'khor gyi nang nas
NK088(su)001:962: rdzu 'phrul gyi mchog moong+gala gyi bu chen po la
NK088(su)001:964: 'jig rten sems can nga'i bka' la mos pa rnams
NK088(su)001:965: bsdus shig /spyan sngar 'dus pa'i blo la nges par
NK088(su)001:966: gzhag rgyu yod do zhes zhal chems por bar bka'
NK088(su)001:968: chos kyi skad cig gis go bar bsgrags nas /
NK088(su)001:969: zhes pa la sogs pa ngag gi rdzu 'phrul yod
NK088(su)001:970: pa'i phyir yungs kar bskor ba'i yun gyis tshig bzhi
NK088(su)001:971: bsgrags pas kun gyis rgyal ba 'da' ba'i zhal chems
NK088(su)001:972: byung bar go nas spyan sngar 'dus pa gang zhe
NK088(su)001:973: na / dam pa'i rigs can lnga ma gtogs pa ni /
NK088(su)001:974: zhes pa la sogs pa theg pa chen por rigs
NK088(su)001:975: nges pa lang ka'i bdag po blo gros thabs ldan
NK088(su)001:976: dang / klu'i rgyal po gtsug na rin chen yod pa'i 'jog po ste blo gros rgya mtsho dang /
NK088(su)001:977: tshangs pa dung gi gtsug phud can blo gros mtha' yas dang /
NK088(su)001:978: gnod sbyin skar mda' gdong blo gros dad sel dang /
NK088(su)001:979: dge bsnyen dri ma med par grags pa blo gros
NK088(su)001:980: rab zhi lnga ni ston pa la skye 'jig mi
NK088(su)001:981: mnga' bar mkhyen sngags kyi bsam gtan la zhugs pas
NK088(su)001:984: de nas 'dus pa de dag la bka' stsal pa /
NK088(su)001:985: zhes pa la sogs pa chos thams cad mi rtag
NK088(su)001:986: pa'i phyir rtag tu re ba sun 'byin pa'i phyir
NK088(su)001:987: / nang yang mi rtag pa 'da' bas rang rang
NK088(su)001:988: gi the tshom dris shig pa bskul zhing gdams pa'o
NK088(su)001:989: / // 'khor de 'dus par gyur pa'i rig 'dzin gyi rgyal po kuny+dzara zhes bya ba /
NK088(su)001:990: zhes pa la sogs pa 'khor gyis zhu ba lnga
NK088(su)001:991: zhu ba'i phyir drang srong kuny+dza ras dga' bo sgra
NK088(su)001:992: ji bzhin du 'di skad zhus so //
NK088(su)001:993: khyod ni nam mkha'i rang bzhin te //
NK088(su)001:994: zhes pa la sogs pa ngo bo la ni 'pho
NK088(su)001:995: 'gyur mi mnga' ba rdo rje'i skur bzhugs kyang 'dul
NK088(su)001:996: thabs kyis don bya bar dgongs pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:997: des na ston pas rgyu'i theg pa gsum gyi bya ba rdzogs kyang /
NK088(su)001:998: nges pa'i gsang sngags lta spyod blang dor med cing
NK088(su)001:999: 'bras bu lhun gyis rdzogs pa'i thabs khyad pa can
NK088(su)001:1000: sngar ma gsungs pas gsung 'tshal bar zhu ba dang
NK088(su)001:1002: rgyal ba'i dgongs don zab mo tshig gsum blo nges par bzhag pa zhus pa dang /
NK088(su)001:1003: sde snod rin po che gsum don gyi ngo bo gang /
NK088(su)001:1007: byed pa po gang gis bsdu bar zhus pa dang /
NK088(su)001:1008: ston pa 'das nas 'jig rten du chos su yis ston zhus pa dang /
NK088(su)001:1009: bstan pa la rgol ba'i log sde pa tshar gang gis gcod dang lnga zhus so //
NK088(su)001:1010: de'i lan nges par gdab pa bstan pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:1011: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK088(su)001:1012: zhes pa la sogs pa ston pa la kuny+dza ras
NK088(su)001:1013: zhus pa las gnang ba don gyis bka' stsal pa'o
NK088(su)001:1014: // lan dang po'i the tshom gcad pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:1016: de kho na nyid nges pa'i theg pa chen po de /
NK088(su)001:1017: zhes pa la sogs pa gsang sngags theg pa chen
NK088(su)001:1018: po sngar ma bstan pa de ni gnas skabs bcu
NK088(su)001:1019: gnyis su 'byung ste de las gzhan du mi srid
NK088(su)001:1020: do // gang rmongs pa gdung ba sel ba na yang 'byung /
NK088(su)001:1021: zhes pa la sogs pa ni dus kyi ngo bo
NK088(su)001:1022: ste byung ba ni rgyud gcig po dgongs 'dus 'di
NK088(su)001:1024: gsang sngags kyi theg pa thams cad kyi bdag nyid do //
NK088(su)001:1025: de la dus 'di dag sh+aakya thub pas spyi'i lo rgyus brjod pas rgyun gyi 'khor mor 'byung ba'o //
NK088(su)001:1027: de'i phyir zhing 'dir yang phyis 'byung bar lung ston par smos te /
NK088(su)001:1028: ma la ya'i rtse la dman pa'i lung can rnams
NK088(su)001:1029: kyis gdung ba nyi shu rtsa gsum bton pa de
NK088(su)001:1030: dag gsang ba pas sel ba'i dus su'ang gsang sngags
NK088(su)001:1031: 'byung ngo // de'i don le'u dang po dang drug pa yan chad kyis ston to //
NK088(su)001:1032: rdo rje sems dpa'i sprul pa'i zhing khams so sor
NK088(su)001:1033: bkod de chos ston pa'i sgron ma rnams mya ngan
NK088(su)001:1034: las 'das pa'i rjes thogs su'ang 'byung ste /
NK088(su)001:1035: de'i don le'u bdun pa dang brgyad pas le'u gnyis kyis bstan to //
NK088(su)001:1036: dam pa'i khye'u lnga la sogs pas gsang sngags kyi
NK088(su)001:1037: nges don rnyed de tha ma'i dbugs phyin tsam na'ang
NK088(su)001:1038: 'byung ste bskal pa mngon dag'i dus te /
NK088(su)001:1039: de'i don le'u dgu pa nas bcu bzhi drug pa'i bar gyis bstan to //
NK088(su)001:1040: skyes bu dam pa thub dka' gzhon nu la sogs
NK088(su)001:1041: pa snying po byang chub nyid du son pa'i dus
NK088(su)001:1042: su'ang 'byung ngo // de ni le'u bco lnga pa
NK088(su)001:1043: nyid kyis ston te ru dra snang ba'i bskal pa
NK088(su)001:1044: su'ang 'byung ngo // dang gcig go // snying po
NK088(su)001:1045: byang chub kyi don skye ba bzhis 'grel ba'i dus
NK088(su)001:1046: te le'u bcu drug pa nas bcu dgu pa'i bzhi'i
NK088(su)001:1048: dge slong thar pa nag po ru drar gyur pa
NK088(su)001:1049: gdul ba'i dus la bab pa'i tshe yang gsang sngags
NK088(su)001:1050: 'byung ste le'u nyi shu pa nas so gcig gi
NK088(su)001:1051: bar bcu gnyis kyis ston to //
NK088(su)001:1052: sku gsung thugs dang spyod pa'i byin rlabs snang ba'i
NK088(su)001:1053: tshe'ang 'byung ste so gcig pa nas so lnga pa'i
NK088(su)001:1055: gsang ba pas dgongs pa dang tshig gis brgyud nas
NK088(su)001:1056: lha mi la grags pa'i dus su'ang 'byung ste le'u
NK088(su)001:1057: so drug pa nas so brgyad pa'i bar gsum gyis
NK088(su)001:1059: grong khyer gsum gyi ched du mdzad pa bzhi snang
NK088(su)001:1060: zhing don mdzad pa'i tshe na'ang 'byung ste so dgu
NK088(su)001:1061: pa nas zhe gnyis bar gyis bzhis bstan to //
NK088(su)001:1062: rgyal ba rnams kyis nyid kyi bstan pa re la
NK088(su)001:1063: gsang sngags phyis 'byung bar lung bstan pa'i tshe na'ang
NK088(su)001:1064: 'byung ste zhe gsum pa las gsal bar ston to
NK088(su)001:1065: // theg pa gsum gyis las gsum gyi rgyud gcod
NK088(su)001:1066: pa'i tshe na'ang 'byung ste le'u zhe bzhi pas gsal
NK088(su)001:1067: // bar ston to // ma la yar gsang ba'ibadaga
NK088(su)001:1068: pos dgongs pa'i mdo bgro zhing gsungs pa'i tshe'ang 'byung
NK088(su)001:1069: ste le'u zhe lnga pa nas don lnga 'i bar
NK088(su)001:1070: le'u so gcig pas gsal bar ston to //
NK088(su)001:1071: de dag ni sngar thams cad kyi da ltar thams cad nas ma 'ongs thams cad du /
NK088(su)001:1072: zhes pa la sogs pa bcu gnyis pa'i don de
NK088(su)001:1073: dag gdul bya ril gyi ngo la snga ma nas
NK088(su)001:1074: phyi dus su 'jig rten ma lus par bstan pa
NK088(su)001:1075: de'i tshe snga ma dang da ltar dang phyis snang
NK088(su)001:1076: ngo snang bar gyur to snang bar 'gyur ro //
NK088(su)001:1077: de lta bas na dus gsum kar byung tshul bcu
NK088(su)001:1078: gnyis tshang ba'i dbang gis 'byung ba'i phyir da ltar
NK088(su)001:1079: gyi dus 'adi'ang byung tshul bcu gnyis kyi tshul mdzes
NK088(su)001:1080: pa las bstan pa snang bar 'jal to //
NK088(su)001:1082: byung tshul dang po'ang bskal pa 'di nyid la ma la ya'i rtser gdung ba bsal lo //
NK088(su)001:1083: gnyis pa'i sgron ma'ang zhing 'dir thub pa'i dbang pos bkod do //
NK088(su)001:1084: gsum pa khye'u lnga sangs rgyas te nges pa chen po rnyed pa'ang bskal pa 'adi'o //
NK088(su)001:1085: bzhi pa'ang khye'u lngas snying po byang chub tu nges pas 'gro ba'i gnyen por gyu pa'ang dus 'adi'o //
NK088(su)001:1086: lnga pa khye'u dgongs pa 'grel ba'ang dus 'di la
NK088(su)001:1087: gong dang mtshungs par bcu drug pa'i stod nas gsal
NK088(su)001:1088: lo // drug pa ru dra ma la ya'i rtse la dus 'di nyid la'ang babs so //
NK088(su)001:1089: bdun pa byin rlabs kyang ru dra la sogs pa
NK088(su)001:1090: 'bras bu thob pa'i phyir thub dkas byin rlabs snang
NK088(su)001:1091: bar bstan pa yang bskal pa 'di nyid do //
NK088(su)001:1092: brgyad pa'ang snying po byang chub nas dgongs pas brgyud
NK088(su)001:1093: pa'i rgyal tshab skyes bus 'jig rten du grags pa'ang
NK088(su)001:1095: dgu pa grong khyer gsum gyi ched du mdzad pa bzhi bskal pa 'di la'ang mdzad do //
NK088(su)001:1096: bcu pa rgyal ba thub pa'i dbang po'i lung bstan pa'ang 'di nyid las gsungs so //
NK088(su)001:1097: bcu gcig pa mdzad pa gsum gyis las rgyud bskal pa 'di la'ang bcad pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:1098: bcu gnyis pa tha ma so so'i dgongs pa zhing
NK088(su)001:1099: so so nas bgro ba yang rim la ya'i rtse
NK088(su)001:1101: lang kas bskul bas gsang ba pas sku bzhi las
NK088(su)001:1102: thos pa'i bgros pa yang bskal pa 'di nyid kyi
NK088(su)001:1103: phyir ro // de lta bas na bskal pa gcig la'ang byung tshul bcu gnyis tshang ngo //
NK088(su)001:1104: 'on bskal pa gcig la byung tshul bcu gnyis smos ci dgos gcig gis chog mod ces dris na /
NK088(su)001:1105: dgos pa so so'i phyir bstan pa gcig pa de ltar 'byung ngo //
NK088(su)001:1106: de dag gi gtan tshigs so so'i le'u tshom bsdus pa las gsal te 'chad par 'gyur ro //
NK088(su)001:1107: des na gsang sngags phyis bskal ba 'di nyid la
NK088(su)001:1108: ston pa'i rjes thogs su 'byung bar le'u bdun pa
NK088(su)001:1109: las byung tshul lung bstan du gsal bas the tshom
NK088(su)001:1111: ston pa gcig mya ngan las 'das ma thag par
NK088(su)001:1112: 'byung ba las byung tshul bcu gnyis ril smos pas
NK088(su)001:1113: kyang / dus gsum kar 'byung ba 'di la yang tshang bar mngon no //
NK088(su)001:1114: de nas ston pas dri ba gnyis pa bka' stsal pa /
NK088(su)001:1115: zhes pa la sogs pa dri ba gnyis pa'i lan bka' stsal ba'i phyir bos pa'o //
NK088(su)001:1116: 'khor la spyi'i gdams ngag gsum bstan pa'i don gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:1117: dang por bslab par bya ba rnams la sbyong bas zhi gnas dang shes rab dang ldan par bya'o //
NK088(su)001:1118: shes rab 'byongs pas skye ba med pa'i don rno
NK088(su)001:1119: myur zab yang zhib par gyur pas ji bzhin pa'i
NK088(su)001:1120: don mthong ba'i gdeng rnyed cing lhag mthong gi gros
NK088(su)001:1122: de ltar thag chod pa la blo mi g.yo bar
NK088(su)001:1123: 'dug pa'i sems bzhag bcas kyis zung du 'brel ba'i
NK088(su)001:1124: spyod lam thabs kyis zin par bya'o //
NK088(su)001:1125: rnam pa gzhan du na shes rab kyi gdams ngag tu'ang mi 'thad pa ma yin no //
NK088(su)001:1126: sdom pa spyod pa'i gdams ngag gsum gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:1127: thun mong dang thun mong ma yin par sbyar te sems kyis sgo gsum g.yo sgyu med pa dang /
NK088(su)001:1128: ngag gi sgro skur med pas bsam pa ji bzhin par smra ba dang /
NK088(su)001:1129: lus kyi bdag gzhan gyi don du 'gyur ba ma yin pa gnod pa'o //
NK088(su)001:1130: sems yang dran rtog don dam par de bzhin nyid
NK088(su)001:1131: rang byung gi ye shes su shar bas log par
NK088(su)001:1133: ngag don dam par mi brjod rgyal ba'i gsung la skyon bzhi ma spangs bral bar rtogs pa dang /
NK088(su)001:1134: lus don dam par ril rgyal ba'i mdzad pa la legs nyes bral ba ste /
NK088(su)001:1135: de dag la ni spyod pa mi 'gog 'ching spyad med pa'o //
NK088(su)001:1136: shes rab lta ba'i gdams ngag gsum ni /
NK088(su)001:1137: thos pa'i shes rab ji bzhin pa de kho na
NK088(su)001:1138: nyid thabs khyad par can gyi gtan tshigs kyis btsal
NK088(su)001:1140: bsam pa'i shes rab de la dgos pa ci yod pa shes par bya ba dang /
NK088(su)001:1141: bsgom pa'i de ltar btsal bas lta ba'i gnad tshud de gdeng rnyed pas don mthong bar bya'o //
NK088(su)001:1142: don rjes tshig gis 'tshob pa ngag gi gdams ngag gsum ni spyod par 'gyur te /
NK088(su)001:1143: brjod pa ci'ang brdzun pa spang ba dang /
NK088(su)001:1144: tshig rjes tshig gis ngag brjod pa las phyis rjes su snyog pa dang /
NK088(su)001:1145: tshig rjes don gyis ngag dang mthun par sgo gsum spyod pa'o //
NK088(su)001:1146: bya ba byed pa'i bslab pa'i gdams ngag gsum ni /
NK088(su)001:1147: dka' thub sdom pa'i sgo spyod pa dang /
NK088(su)001:1148: rtogs pa shes rab kyi sgo dang /
NK088(su)001:1149: goms pa ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo'o //
NK088(su)001:1150: gol sa shes par bya ba'i phyir rtsol bas 'jug pa'i sgo dang /
NK088(su)001:1151: grub pa thabs kyi sgo dang /
NK088(su)001:1153: spyir shes par bya ba'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:1154: stong pa nyid kyi rnam par thar pa'i sgo dang /
NK088(su)001:1155: mtshan ma med pa'i sgo dang /
NK088(su)001:1156: smon pa med pa'i sgo mo'o //
NK088(su)001:1157: phyis 'byung ba'i gsang sngags de kho na nyid ji bzhin pa'i ming gi rnam grangs te /
NK088(su)001:1158: yi ge +amo m+aum h'u gi don rang bzhin lhun
NK088(su)001:1159: gyis grub pa bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po +amo
NK088(su)001:1160: nyid dang / ye m+aum ji bzhin pa ril dang ngo bo mi phyed pa dang /
NK088(su)001:1161: rtsa h'u ba byang chub kyi sems spyod yul dang bral ba blos reg dka' ba de nyid de /
NK088(su)001:1162: de dag ni sngags gsum ste /
NK088(su)001:1163: de la cir yang mi bsam mi dpyad g.yo ba med de /
NK088(su)001:1164: mi bsgom pa'i bsgom pa la bslab pa med pa'i bslab par bya'o //
NK088(su)001:1165: de yang rigs sngags gsang sngags gzungs sngags su mdo las grags pa nyid la bslab par bya'o //
NK088(su)001:1166: de ltar bsgom pas gol sa sgrib pa ni grong khyer gsum ste /
NK088(su)001:1167: sgo gsum dang khams gsum dang shes pa gsum gyi rtog pa bshig par bya'o //
NK088(su)001:1168: 'o na 'dir gsum tsho lnga la gdams ngag gsum zhes pa btub bam zhe na /
NK088(su)001:1169: de ni bco lngar snang yang rtsa ba'i dbang gis gsum zhes pa mi 'gal te /
NK088(su)001:1170: dper na rim nyin bzhi pa'am sbrul gom pa bdun pa dang shing 'dab bdun pa lta bu'o //
NK088(su)001:1171: de dag ni blo chung ba'i blos bzhag pa'i lan yin pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:1172: rgyu'i theg pa'i nges par bzhag pa gsum ste gnyis pa'i lan no //
NK088(su)001:1173: dri ba gsum pa'i lan bstan pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:1174: de nas yang ston pas dri ba gsum pa bka' stsal pa /
NK088(su)001:1176: nga yis sgron ma gang bzhag pa //
NK088(su)001:1177: zhes pa la sogs pa ston pas yi ge'i sgron ma bstan pa phun sum tshogs pa gsum ni /
NK088(su)001:1178: snod kyi rim rab 'bring tha ma pa gsum du
NK088(su)001:1179: snang ba'i phyir sde snod rin po che gsum du
NK088(su)001:1180: bsdu'o // de'i don bsdu lugs ni zhi gnas lhag mthong las mtha' gsum du'o //
NK088(su)001:1181: de las 'dul dbang gis shes pa'i rgyud gsum la bsdu'o //
NK088(su)001:1182: rnam pa gzhan du gang zag gcig gis kun gzhi yid nyon yid shes pa gsum la'ang bsdu'o //
NK088(su)001:1183: 'jug pa'i skal ba chung bas yi ge la ma
NK088(su)001:1184: brten par mi go ba'i phyir yi ge'i tshogs te
NK088(su)001:1185: sde snod glegs bam du bsdu'o //
NK088(su)001:1186: gang gis bsdu na gang zag blo mtho dman gyi
NK088(su)001:1187: ched du theg pa la mtho dman yod pas nyan
NK088(su)001:1188: thos kyi lugs su bsdu 'od srung gis ba dang
NK088(su)001:1189: / theg pa chen po dbu ma'i lugs su so so'i sdud pa kun dga' bos pos bsdu'o //
NK088(su)001:1190: theg pa che chung gi blo yis yul chos kyang
NK088(su)001:1191: lta spyod mtho dman gdul bya'i mos phyogs su bka'
NK088(su)001:1192: stsal to // de nas ston pas dri ba bzhi pa dang /
NK088(su)001:1193: lnga pa tshig le'u gcig pa bka' stsal pa /
NK088(su)001:1194: zhes pa la sogs pa dri ba tha ma gnyis
NK088(su)001:1195: lan gcig gis chod par bya ba'i phyir bka' stsal
NK088(su)001:1196: pa ni / kuny+dza la bos nas gdams te /
NK088(su)001:1197: ston pa sku mya ngan las 'das pa'i 'og tu
NK088(su)001:1198: sngags gsung ba yang sku ma 'das pa'i gong du
NK088(su)001:1199: phyis gsang sngags 'byung bar lung dzahl bstan pas gsang
NK088(su)001:1201: phyag na rdo rjes dman pa'i lung can gyi sems
NK088(su)001:1202: dpa' dam pa'i rigs can lnga rgyal po dzahl sogs
NK088(su)001:1203: pa dag kyang byung nas de dag la ston cing
NK088(su)001:1204: de dag gis kyang so sor rang rang gi mthun
NK088(su)001:1205: pa'i gnas ris su ston par mdzad cing spros nas
NK088(su)001:1206: bstan pa gsal bar byed pa dang /
NK088(su)001:1207: lnga pa'i lan log pa'i sde pa sun 'byin cing tshar gcod do //
NK088(su)001:1208: de skad brjod pas dri ba tha ma gnyis chod do //
NK088(su)001:1209: gdams ngag nges par gzhag pa ni //
NK088(su)001:1210: zhes pa ni gsungs pa'i lan lnga dang /
NK088(su)001:1212: de ni gdung ba nyi shu rtsa gsum 'byung ba'i yang rgyu yin pa'i phyir rgyu'i rgyu kho na'o //
NK088(su)001:1213: gnyis pa bkrol ba'o ////bshad tshul rjes su mthun par lung bstan pa'i gleng gzhi'i rgyu bstan pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:1214: de'i tshe de'i dus na gang dag mi chen po rnams ni /
NK088(su)001:1215: zhes pa la sogs pa de'i dus na don la
NK088(su)001:1216: shed bye ba'i dam pa'i rigs can lnga po la
NK088(su)001:1217: sogs pa sems dpa' chen po rnams rig 'dzin ni
NK088(su)001:1218: sku la 'da' ba dang mi 'da' ba med par
NK088(su)001:1219: shes pa'i dbang gis nang du bsam gtan mi g.yo
NK088(su)001:1220: ba la zhugs te 'das pa la gdung ba'i mya
NK088(su)001:1221: ngan med do // don chen po la shed ma
NK088(su)001:1222: bye ba'i nyan thos lo ka ba la sogs pa
NK088(su)001:1223: gzugs sku skye 'jig tu mthong ba'i lta ba can
NK088(su)001:1224: dag ni ston pa sku 'da' bar mthong nas mya
NK088(su)001:1225: ngan gyis sems myong te smre sngags 'don to //
NK088(su)001:1226: 'jig rten gyi lha mi phal pa dag kyang sgra ji bzhin du gyur to //
NK088(su)001:1227: lha'i gnas ris man chad rtsi shing skams pa dang /
NK088(su)001:1228: rlung dang kha char la sogs pa yid du mi
NK088(su)001:1229: 'ong ba snang bar gyur te mos pa can gyi
NK088(su)001:1230: sems can ril sems kyi dran pa nyams so //
NK088(su)001:1232: gzhan don du de nas lo brgyad dang bcu gnyis 'das pa na /
NK088(su)001:1233: zhes pa la sogs pa ston pa sku myang las
NK088(su)001:1234: 'das nas lo nyi shu rtsa brgyad lon pa na
NK088(su)001:1235: / dam pa'i rigs can lang ka'i bdag po la
NK088(su)001:1236: sogs pa dgongs pa'i ting nge 'dzin las bzhengs pa
NK088(su)001:1237: / dang / ston pa 'das par mthong nas mya ngan gyi smre sngags 'don to //
NK088(su)001:1238: de nas rig pa 'dzin pa kun bgro ba dang
NK088(su)001:1239: gdung ba 'don pa'i phyir ma la yar 'dus te
NK088(su)001:1240: gdung ba'i smre sngags nyi shu rtsa gsum bton pa
NK088(su)001:1242: ston pa sgron ma'i 'od du nub na //
NK088(su)001:1243: zhes pa la sogs pa 'di dag rgyu dang rkyen
NK088(su)001:1244: thun mong du'ang 'gyur te byang chub sems dpa' de
NK088(su)001:1245: dag la mngon shes yod pas snying po byang chub
NK088(su)001:1246: kyi rgyal ba la don gyis bskul bar yang 'gyur
NK088(su)001:1247: ba'i phyir ro // de dngos kyi 'di lta ste /
NK088(su)001:1248: ston pa 'das nas phyis ma rig pa'i mun pa
NK088(su)001:1249: bstan pa dang ston pa gang gis sel bar zhus
NK088(su)001:1250: pa dang / ston pa mi bzhugs na bstan la
NK088(su)001:1251: 'jug par 'dod pa'i lta ba log par mi 'gyur
NK088(su)001:1253: ston pa med na gang zag rtogs pa dang ldan
NK088(su)001:1254: pas mi shes pa'i slob bu la bshad pas gtan
NK088(su)001:1255: la phebs mi phebs dris pa dang /
NK088(su)001:1256: ston pa ye shes kyi spyan can mi bzhugs pas
NK088(su)001:1257: log stobs 'phel bar mi 'gyur ram dris pa dang
NK088(su)001:1258: / tshad ma'i zhal mi bzhugs pas bka' tshad ma'ang
NK088(su)001:1259: nub nas lam pa dag ma rig pas non par
NK088(su)001:1260: mi 'gyur ram zhes dris pa la sogs pa sgra
NK088(su)001:1262: ngag sems kyi hud kyi sgra sgrogs shing blang bas gdung ba de dag bton no //
NK088(su)001:1263: thog mar dam pas gdung ba bton pa'i le'u /
NK088(su)001:1264: zhes pas gdung ba 'di dag byis pa rnams kyis
NK088(su)001:1265: mi spobs te dam pa'i rigs can lnga la sogs
NK088(su)001:1267: gsum pa bkrol ba'o ////de ltar gdung ba gsan pas gdung ba sel bar bgro ba mdzad nas /
NK088(su)001:1268: phyag na rdo rje la bskul ba'i rkyen du 'gyur ba'i don bstan pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:1269: de skad smras te gdung ba las //
NK088(su)001:1270: srid gsum 'gro ba'i gnyen gcig pu //
NK088(su)001:1271: zhes pa la sogs pa gdung ba rtsa gsum bton
NK088(su)001:1272: pa de thugs rje'i dbang gis snying po byang chub
NK088(su)001:1273: kyi rgyal ba ji snyed pas gsan nas gsang sngags
NK088(su)001:1274: kyi bdag po la 'gro don du bskul ba'i phyir
NK088(su)001:1277: gsang ba'i bdag po khyod kyis dang po byang chub
NK088(su)001:1278: mchog tu sems bskyed pa'i dus na 'gro ba'i sdug
NK088(su)001:1279: bsngal sel bar dam bcas nas /
NK088(su)001:1280: brtson pa dang dam bcas kyi go cha gyon pa
NK088(su)001:1281: khyed kyis mi shes sam zhes gnad du bskul te
NK088(su)001:1282: / thugs rjes mi yul du gshegs nas gdung ba de dag bsam pa dang /
NK088(su)001:1283: bdud dang mu stegs log pa'i tshogs btul la /
NK088(su)001:1284: thabs 'dzud bsre ba dang cha mthun sbyor bas 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:1285: 'dod pa rang rkyen dang dkri drang brgyud pa'i mthun 'jug gis 'du shes bsgyur la /
NK088(su)001:1286: gsang sngags bshad de yang dag pa'i sa la 'khod cig par bskul lo //
NK088(su)001:1287: der gsang ba'i bdag pos gsan nas mi g.yo ba
NK088(su)001:1288: las bzhengs te zhal gyis bzhes pa bstan pa'i phyir
NK088(su)001:1289: / dpa' bo rdo rje 'dzin rgyal po //
NK088(su)001:1290: zhes pa la sogs pa bdud dang log pa'i dpung bcom pa'i mthu mnga' ba dang /
NK088(su)001:1291: thabs thams cad las mchog tu gyur pa dang /
NK088(su)001:1292: 'khor ba'i dgra dpung bsnyil ba'i phyir mtshan gnod 'dul lo //
NK088(su)001:1293: gsang ba'i dbang thob pa'i rtags 'chang bas rdo rje
NK088(su)001:1294: 'dzin pa zhes bya ba de gdul bya'i ngo la
NK088(su)001:1295: snang bas / cho 'phrul gyi mdzad pa mang po'i
NK088(su)001:1296: byin rlabs snang bar mdzad nas lang ka'i bdag po
NK088(su)001:1297: la sogs pa gsang sngags kyi skal ba can du
NK088(su)001:1298: snang bas / / thub pa'i dbang pos skal ba
NK088(su)001:1299: can la gsang sngags 'byung bar lung bstan pa ltar
NK088(su)001:1300: da ltar gsang sngags bstan pa'i dus la bab bas
NK088(su)001:1301: snang bas / / / 'khor ba nyid snying po
NK088(su)001:1302: byang chub yin par bstan pa'i ched du sngar gyi
NK088(su)001:1303: rgyal ba mang po'i mdzad pa'i byin rlabs kyis theg
NK088(su)001:1304: pa chen po bshad pa dang /
NK088(su)001:1305: sprul pa'i sku rnams kyis phyin 'byung bar lung bstan pa bzhin ngas bshad par zhal gyis bzhes so //
NK088(su)001:1306: de'i gnas nges pa gang du snyam pa la /
NK088(su)001:1307: drag shul can zhes bya ba'i ri //
NK088(su)001:1308: zhes pa la sogs pa ri'i mtshan ni re zhig rten can gyi mtshan rten la btags pa dang /
NK088(su)001:1309: shin tu dben pa de ni bde bar gshegs pa
NK088(su)001:1310: rnams kyi dgongs pa gsang sngags theg pa chen po
NK088(su)001:1311: 'byung ba'i gnas yin te yon tan de lta bu
NK088(su)001:1312: yod pa'o // dus snga phyi ril gyi gsang sngags
NK088(su)001:1313: kyang de lta bu'i gnas su 'byung bas rgyal ba
NK088(su)001:1314: ril gyis ri de la mchog tu basngagasa pa brjod
NK088(su)001:1315: yod pa'o // pa'o // ston pa po yang thog mtha' ril du rgyal ba snyed pas /
NK088(su)001:1316: so so'i zhing gnas su gsang sngags bstan pa'i rjes su bdag gnod 'dul gyis kyang /
NK088(su)001:1317: sprul pa de dag 'das ma thag par bskul pa
NK088(su)001:1318: 'byung ba'i dus ril du bdag gi cho 'phrul gyis
NK088(su)001:1319: gsang sngags bstan pa yin pa'i phyir 'dir yang bstan
NK088(su)001:1320: to zhes bka' zhal gyis 'ches so //
NK088(su)001:1321: gang gi gdung ba sel bar bgros pa'i le'u /
NK088(su)001:1322: zhes pa dman pa'i gdung ba de dag rgyal ba
NK088(su)001:1323: ril dang gsang ba pos sel bar bka' bgros dang
NK088(su)001:1324: / bskul bas zhal gyis 'ches pa'i le'u bzhi pa
NK088(su)001:1325: mdor bkrol ba'o ////lung bstan brgyud pa'i gleng gzhi'i ngo
NK088(su)001:1326: bo dang gleng bslang ba bstan pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:1327: de nas de tshe de nyid du //
NK088(su)001:1328: zhes pa la sogs pa snyegs pa dang 'dren pa'i
NK088(su)001:1329: zhal gyis 'ches pa dang ngo bo'i 'phrad sbyor ba'o
NK088(su)001:1330: // de yang dus ni bskul ba'i dus de'o //
NK088(su)001:1331: gnas ni ma la ya nyid do //
NK088(su)001:1332: ston pa ni gnod 'dul te zhal gyis 'ches pa'i tshig gis de bka' stsal nas /
NK088(su)001:1333: gnas kyi ngo bo ni mi yul gling bzhi ji snyed pa las gling 'di'i ri ma la ya'o //
NK088(su)001:1334: gleng gzhi bcas pa'i sbyor ba ji snyam pa la /
NK088(su)001:1335: thugs rje'i sa la mngon sprul gshegs //
NK088(su)001:1336: zhes pa la sogs pa thugs rje chen po'i shugs
NK088(su)001:1337: kyis 'khor ba'i gnas su sku gdul bya'i ngo la
NK088(su)001:1340: phyi'i sa dngos g.yos pa dang nang gi sa rnams
NK088(su)001:1341: 'og nas gong du g.yos po la sogs pa'i mdzad
NK088(su)001:1342: pas gdul bya'i rtog sgrib bsal te bde ba la
NK088(su)001:1343: bkod do // de lta bu'i ltas de dang po su la shar zhe na /
NK088(su)001:1344: sngon du snang ba'i skal ldan can //
NK088(su)001:1345: zhes pa la sogs pa thub pa'i dbang po nyid bzhugs tsam na /
NK088(su)001:1346: rgyal po la 'byung bar lung bstan thob pa'i skal
NK088(su)001:1347: can mi lus dman pa'i d+r+wa ma rgyal po dzah'i
NK088(su)001:1348: ltas rmis ltas su byung ngo //
NK088(su)001:1349: 'khor gyis ston pa gang yin ngo shes par bya ba'i phyir dris pa gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:1350: de tshe dam pa'i rigs can rnams //
NK088(su)001:1351: zhes pa la sogs pa rgyal po'i gnas su 'byung ba'i dus der /
NK088(su)001:1352: lang ka la sogs pas gsang sngags 'byung ba dang
NK088(su)001:1353: ston pa gshegs pa la dga' zhing the tshom skyes
NK088(su)001:1354: te gang yin dris pa ni drug ste sgra bzhin
NK088(su)001:1355: no // de la ston pas don bcu bdun gyi lo rgyus zhib tu brjod pa ni /
NK088(su)001:1357: zhes pa la sogs pa cho 'phrul gyi bdag nyid
NK088(su)001:1358: gsang bdag gis lan brjod pa nye bar bstan pa
NK088(su)001:1359: ni / mtshan ci yin pa gsungs pa dang /
NK088(su)001:1360: thugs rje skyabs kyi bdag po yin pa dang /
NK088(su)001:1363: yab dang yum bstan pa dang /
NK088(su)001:1364: don ma rig pa'i lo rgyus dang /
NK088(su)001:1365: sems kyi don ma rtog par mkhyen nas sdug bsngal brgyud pa dang /
NK088(su)001:1366: lam btsal bas ma rnyed pa'i lo rgyus gsungs pa dang /
NK088(su)001:1367: dus der ston pa rdo rje sems dpas bstan pa'i
NK088(su)001:1368: tshig gis sems kyi nor bu rang la yod par
NK088(su)001:1369: mi shes na yal bar ma 'dug cig par bskul
NK088(su)001:1370: ba'i lo rgyus bka' stsal pa dang /
NK088(su)001:1371: gsang ba po nyid kyis sems ji bzhin par rtogs pa'i thabs zhus pa dang /
NK088(su)001:1372: ston pas rang nyid las tshol cig par gsungs pa'i lo rgyus brjod pa dang /
NK088(su)001:1373: bka' gsang bdag nyid kyis thos nas ston pa nyid
NK088(su)001:1374: la zhus te theg pa chen po'i sgor zhugs te
NK088(su)001:1375: bgrod pas 'khor ba'i skye rga na 'chi bsgral te
NK088(su)001:1376: / sgo kun nas bsdur te theg pa chen po'i
NK088(su)001:1377: yang chen por zhugs te sa bgrod nas btsal bas
NK088(su)001:1378: byang chub rang rig pa nyid las ma rnyed par
NK088(su)001:1379: / rnyed de / ji lta ba'i 'bras bu thob
NK088(su)001:1380: pa med par thob nas ji bzhin pa lhun gyis
NK088(su)001:1382: thub pa'i dbang po sprul pa snang ba'i dus 'dir /
NK088(su)001:1383: dge sdig spyod pa'i gnas 'dir 'gro 'ongs med par 'ongs /
NK088(su)001:1385: nga ni thabs kyi mnyan pa mkhan //
NK088(su)001:1386: zhes pa la sogs pa 'gro ba bsgral ba'i ched
NK088(su)001:1387: du yon tan bcu gcig gi mdzad thabs bcu gcig
NK088(su)001:1388: gis gdul bya thar bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:1389: 'khor gyis ma zhus par ston pas sbran nas gleng
NK088(su)001:1390: bslang ba'i don gnyis las ston pas mdun bsu bar
NK088(su)001:1391: sbyar te sgra ji bzhin du'o //
NK088(su)001:1393: rnam dag lam chen kun sgrol 'dir //
NK088(su)001:1394: zhes pa la sogs pa theg pa chen po 'dir
NK088(su)001:1395: su zhugs pa 'bras bu rang la 'char te brtson
NK088(su)001:1396: pas rtogs pa nyid sangs rgyas yin pas 'bad cig
