NK088(su)001:1397: par gsungs so // rdo rje gsang chen gsang ba yi //
NK088(su)001:1398: zhes pa la sogs pa ngo bo ji bzhin pa
NK088(su)001:1399: dngos po rnams kyi de kho na nyid ni mi
NK088(su)001:1400: byed mi 'gyur rgyu rkyen bral ba'i don nyid mthong
NK088(su)001:1401: dka' ba ni rdo rje gsang sngags te /
NK088(su)001:1402: rgyud lung man ngag gi mdzod rgyal ba ril gyi
NK088(su)001:1403: yum du gyur pa'i theg pa dag 'dir bshad pas
NK088(su)001:1404: tshangs pa gtsug phud dang dri ma med par grags
NK088(su)001:1405: pa la sogs pa rnams las snga phyir brgyud de
NK088(su)001:1406: lha mi'i yul du rgyas shing snang bar gsungs pa
NK088(su)001:1407: dang / lha mi 'jig rten thams cad kyi //
NK088(su)001:1408: zhes pa la sogs pa gdul bya de dag gi ma rig pa gnyis dang /
NK088(su)001:1409: gdung ba rtsa gsum la sogs pa bsal nas rang
NK088(su)001:1410: rig pa rang gi rang bzhin gyi 'od gsal la
NK088(su)001:1411: rtogs par 'gyur bar gsungs pa dang /
NK088(su)001:1412: ci phyir gdung ba'i mun par zhugs //
NK088(su)001:1413: zhes pa la sogs pa dam pa'i rigs can khyod
NK088(su)001:1414: dgos pa gang gi ched du gdung ba nyi shu
NK088(su)001:1415: rtsa gsum gyis gzhan du tshol ba'i mya ngan gyi
NK088(su)001:1416: mun par zhugs pa yin zhes dris nas ston pa
NK088(su)001:1417: 'das pa la mya ngan bya bar rig pa min
NK088(su)001:1418: te / de ni chos kyi sku'i bdag nyid sku
NK088(su)001:1419: lnga lhun gyis rdzogs pa rdo rje'i sku brnyes pas
NK088(su)001:1420: 'das ma 'das med pas ma gdung cig pa'i lan
NK088(su)001:1421: te / bka' stsal to // de dag dri ba drug gi lan du sbyar ba ni /
NK088(su)001:1422: drug pa yan chad dang po'i lan btab pa'o //
NK088(su)001:1423: bcu gnyis pa'i lan gsum ni /
NK088(su)001:1424: gnyis pa dang bzhi pa dang lnga pa'i lan no //
NK088(su)001:1425: bdun pa nas bcu gcig ni gsum pa'i lan no //
NK088(su)001:1426: bcu gsum pa ni dri ba drug pa'i lan no //
NK088(su)001:1427: bcu bzhi pa tha ma'i lan no //
NK088(su)001:1428: bco lnga pa gsum pa dang lnga pa'i lan no //
NK088(su)001:1429: bcu drug pa dang bcu bdun pa'ang tha ma'i lan
NK088(su)001:1430: te khri'ura du 'byung bas don gyi gting brtags te
NK088(su)001:1431: mjal bar bya'o // gleng bslang ba'i don gus pas dri ba dris pa bstan pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:1432: sngon du byung ba'i rigs can rnams //
NK088(su)001:1433: zhes pa la sogs pa ston pa yin par ngo
NK088(su)001:1434: shes nas dga' ba'i sems kyis sgo gsum gus pas
NK088(su)001:1435: zhu ba spobs pa'i tshul lo //
NK088(su)001:1436: mtshan mo mun nag sprin rum nas //
NK088(su)001:1437: glog 'gyus bar snang ston lta bus //
NK088(su)001:1438: zhes pa la sogs pa zhu ba'i phyir ston pa
NK088(su)001:1439: skyes bu'i mtshan gyi rnam grangs las bstod pa brgyad
NK088(su)001:1440: byas pa ste / dang po khyod gsang ba'i don
NK088(su)001:1441: gyi bdag po sku shin tu bkod pa'ang rgyal ba
NK088(su)001:1442: ril gyi dgongs pa'i mnga' bdag yin no bar bstod
NK088(su)001:1443: pa ni thabs bcu bzhi pa'i yon tan gyi sgo
NK088(su)001:1444: byas pa ste / nas bstod pa'o // bka' rnams bgro bar khyod basngagasa pas //
NK088(su)001:1445: zhes pa dag bka' thams cad kyi dgongs pa 'grel
NK088(su)001:1446: lo bar bstod pa ni thabs bcu pa dang bcu
NK088(su)001:1447: gcig pa'i yon tan gyi sgo nas bstod pa'o //
NK088(su)001:1448: sems kyi dkyil 'khor thams cad las //
NK088(su)001:1449: zhes pa dag ni gdul bya'i bsam pa ril la
NK088(su)001:1450: gsang ba gsum gyi don shar bar mdzad nas sgrib
NK088(su)001:1451: pa'i mun pa sel ba'i nyi ma yin no bar
NK088(su)001:1452: bstod pa ni / thabs brgyad pa'i yon tan gyi sgo nas bstod pa'o //
NK088(su)001:1453: gdul dka' ma lus kun 'dul zhing //
NK088(su)001:1454: zhes pa la sogs pa log lta dang log lta
NK088(su)001:1455: can ril gyis mi tshugs shing 'joms pas bdud kyi
NK088(su)001:1456: yang bdud khyod yin no bar bstod pa ni thabs
NK088(su)001:1457: drug pa'i yon tan la bstod pa'o //
NK088(su)001:1458: de bzhin nyid kyi ngo bo nyid //
NK088(su)001:1459: zhes pa dag ni chos ril ma 'dres la yongs
NK088(su)001:1460: su rdzogs par gsal bar mdzad pas chos kyi me
NK088(su)001:1461: long khyod yin no bar bstod pa ni /
NK088(su)001:1462: thabs gnyis pa'i yon tan gyis bstod pa'o //
NK088(su)001:1464: zhes pa dag gdul bya'i nang gi gcong rnying 'byin
NK088(su)001:1465: pa'i sman pa'i rgyal po khyod yin no bar bstod
NK088(su)001:1466: pa ni thabs gsum pa'i sgo nas bstod pa'o //
NK088(su)001:1467: dga' mgu rangs par mdzad pas na //
NK088(su)001:1468: zhes pa dag gdul bya ril bsam pa dang mthun
NK088(su)001:1469: par don mdzad pas sgo gsum gyi gdung ba sel
NK088(su)001:1470: ba la bshes gnyen mgon yin no bar bstod pa
NK088(su)001:1471: ni / mdzad pa dang po dang bzhi pa dang lnga pa'i sgo nas bstod pa'o //
NK088(su)001:1472: 'dod pa yid bzhin skong bas na //
NK088(su)001:1473: zhes pa dag gdul bya'i bsam pa'i re 'dod ril
NK088(su)001:1474: skong bas nor bu rin po che khyod yin no
NK088(su)001:1476: thabs bdun pa dang dgu pa'i yon tan gyi sgo nas bstod pa'o //
NK088(su)001:1477: de ltar mnyes pa'i rgyus zhu ba dngos bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:1478: dam pa rnams dang mthun mdzod la //
NK088(su)001:1479: zhes pa la sogs pa sngar gyi ston pa rnams
NK088(su)001:1480: dang mdzad pa mthun pas bdag cag dman pa'i lus
NK088(su)001:1481: can gyi 'khor rnams la sprul sku mya ngan las
NK088(su)001:1483: zhing khams so sor sgron ma ji ltar bkod pa dang /
NK088(su)001:1484: gsang sngags theg pa chen po ji ltar byung ba
NK088(su)001:1485: gsum zhus nas gsang sngags kyi rgyud bdag cag la
NK088(su)001:1487: nges don dgongs pa'i dris tshig gsum po dang ye
NK088(su)001:1488: ji bzhin pa'i don ston cig par bskul zhing gsol
NK088(su)001:1489: ba gdab pa gsum brjod do //
NK088(su)001:1490: lung dam pa bgro bar gsol ba gdab pa ni bshad ma thag pa nyid do //
NK088(su)001:1491: le'u lnga pa bkrol ba'o ////le'u gsum pa'i gdung ba sel ba dang /
NK088(su)001:1492: bstan pa'i don nyid gsungs pas gnas skabs la gleng
NK088(su)001:1493: bslang ba'i don khyung lta bus shes par bya ba'i
NK088(su)001:1494: phyir / de skad ces gsol ba btab pa las /
NK088(su)001:1495: zhes pa la sogs pa gsol ba btab pa la
NK088(su)001:1496: snyegs pas gsang ba pas lan dang 'brel pa ste
NK088(su)001:1498: rgyud bshad pa gang snyam pa la /
NK088(su)001:1499: sems kyi dkyil 'khor de bzhin nyid //
NK088(su)001:1500: zhes pa dag ni dri ba nyi shu rtsa gsum gyi dang po'i lan btab pas sel ba ste /
NK088(su)001:1501: sems kyi dkyil 'khor rang gi rang bzhin gyi 'od gsal ba'i ngo bo ni /
NK088(su)001:1502: ston pa nyid las rdo rje'i sku mnga' ba de
NK088(su)001:1503: ni gsang sngags ji bzhin pa'i don du shar nas
NK088(su)001:1504: 'gro ba'i mun pa ma spangs sel bar lan btab
NK088(su)001:1505: pas dri ma dang po'i gdung ba sangs so //
NK088(su)001:1506: lan ni sgra ji bzhin par 'byung ba dag kyang sbyar ro //
NK088(su)001:1507: tshad ma gnyis kyis gang gzhal ba //
NK088(su)001:1508: zhes pa dag thub pa'i dbang po dang gsang sngags
NK088(su)001:1509: ni gcig du ma las grol ba'i ngo bos phyis
NK088(su)001:1510: gsang sngags thun mong ma yin pa'i mngon sum pa
NK088(su)001:1511: dang rjes dpag gnyis su byung zhing /
NK088(su)001:1512: gnyis po la'ang lung dang man ngag gi tshad mar shar nas /
NK088(su)001:1513: de rtogs pa'i gang zag gis kyang don gtan la
NK088(su)001:1514: phebs pas log par mi 'gyur bas gdung ba sangs
NK088(su)001:1515: so // legs nyes rtsa ba'ang de nyid pas //
NK088(su)001:1516: zhes pa dag ston pa 'das kyang nor ba dang
NK088(su)001:1517: ma nor ba gtan la 'bebs pa'i gzhi tshad ma
NK088(su)001:1518: gnyis kyis bstan pa la zhugs pas rgol ba tshar
NK088(su)001:1520: sems kyi rang bzhin 'od gsal bas //
NK088(su)001:1521: zhes pa dag gsang sngags de kho na nyid kyi
NK088(su)001:1522: lugs kyis kun gzhi dgu pa nyid ye nas bden
NK088(su)001:1523: pa gnyis su med par rang shar ba la mthas
NK088(su)001:1524: ma bsgribs pa / 'phral du lam pas tha dad
NK088(su)001:1525: dang gcig par sel ba'i gnyen po bral ba la
NK088(su)001:1526: gol sa mi dmigs pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:1527: sangs rgyas mya ngan yongs mi 'da' //zhes pa la
NK088(su)001:1528: sogs pa bshad pa bzhin 'pho 'gyur mi mnga' bas
NK088(su)001:1529: lhun gyis grub pa'i bstan pa la shar nub med
NK088(su)001:1530: do // de lta bas na gdul bya la sgra bzhin snang ba ni /
NK088(su)001:1532: ngo bo nyid nam mkha' dang 'dra bas gnyis med don gyis log pa tshar gcod par byed do //
NK088(su)001:1533: rang bzhin 'od gsal spros bral ba'i //
NK088(su)001:1534: zhes pa la sogs pa rgyu rkyen med pa'i ye
NK088(su)001:1535: shes ni spros pa gsum ma spangs bral ba'i mi
NK088(su)001:1536: g.yo ba chen po nyid gsung lnga'i ngo bo bas
NK088(su)001:1537: / de'i don ji lta bar son pa'i 'gying bag gis chos ston pa'i gsang bdag nyid dang /
NK088(su)001:1538: lang ka la sogs pas bstan pa khyad par can rgyas shing 'phel bar mdzad pa'o //
NK088(su)001:1539: bslab pa lhag pa'i sems nyid dang //
NK088(su)001:1540: zhes pa la sogs pa lhag pa'i bslab pa ni
NK088(su)001:1541: theg pa chen po rang rig nyid yin pas don
NK088(su)001:1542: du gnyer ba'i mchog ste gsang sngags so //
NK088(su)001:1543: de ni 'gro ba'i lus can lang ka la sogs pas 'dzin to //
NK088(su)001:1544: mthar thug med pa'i sems can rnams //
NK088(su)001:1545: zhes pa la sogs pa 'khor ba thog ma med
NK088(su)001:1546: pa'i 'gro ba rnams ye snying po byang chub la
NK088(su)001:1547: gnas pas rigs mi 'gyur ba'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:1548: rmad du byung ba'i theg pa 'dis bya ba med pa'i sangs rgyas su lung ston to //
NK088(su)001:1549: sems nyid yod dang med do zhes //
NK088(su)001:1550: zhes pa la sogs pa gang thun mong ma yin
NK088(su)001:1551: pa la shed ma bye ba'i dbu ma la sogs
NK088(su)001:1552: pa ni mtha' yod med la rtsod kyang /
NK088(su)001:1553: shed bye ba'i 'bras bu pa dag ni ye mtha'
NK088(su)001:1554: bral ba la de nyid du'ang 'dzin cing rtogs pa
NK088(su)001:1556: nga yi gsang sngags gsang ba 'di //
NK088(su)001:1557: zhes pa dag ni dngos po rnams kyi de kho na nyid lhun gyis grub pa ni /
NK088(su)001:1558: rgyal ba ril gyi dgongs pa'i zhe phugs shin tu brtag dka' bas /
NK088(su)001:1559: gang blos mthong ba'i skal pa med pa dag gis /
NK088(su)001:1560: thun mong gi tshad ma gnyis kyis tshol ba dang /
NK088(su)001:1561: de ltar brtags pas mthong ba tha dad kyi phyir /
NK088(su)001:1562: sgra gcig la don tha dad du 'phel zhing ris 'dzin par 'byung ngo //
NK088(su)001:1563: dam pa rnams kyis gsang lung 'di //
NK088(su)001:1564: zhes pa la sogs pa rmad du byung ba'i bka'
NK088(su)001:1565: sgro skur dang bral ba'i don ma rnyed pa'i gang
NK088(su)001:1566: zag don chen po mdongs shing sems pa 'phyon ma'i
NK088(su)001:1567: sems lta bus / khyad par lhag pa'i bka' dang
NK088(su)001:1568: snyan ngag gi chos dang zang zing barje ba 'byung
NK088(su)001:1569: ste de ni gtsub shing lta bur 'gyur ro //
NK088(su)001:1570: kun gsal me long 'od po che //
NK088(su)001:1571: zhes pa la sogs pa bde ba chen po'i klong
NK088(su)001:1572: nyid ni bde ba chen po ril ma bkol bar
NK088(su)001:1573: dngos po gnyis par ril ma bkrol bas rang gsal
NK088(su)001:1574: ba nyid / gcig dang tha dad pa las grol
NK088(su)001:1575: ba'i phyir thub pa'i dbang po'ang dpe nam mkha' ltar
NK088(su)001:1576: ba nyid / bzhugs pa'o // de bas na ma
NK088(su)001:1577: rungs pa'i rang bzhin yang snang la mi dmigs pas
NK088(su)001:1578: ngo bo mi zin pa nyid do //
NK088(su)001:1579: byang chub snying po yod kyi bar //
NK088(su)001:1580: zhes pa dag byang chub snying po de kho na
NK088(su)001:1581: nyid ji tsam gnas par bstan pa gnas te tha
NK088(su)001:1583: thog ma tha ma med pas na //
NK088(su)001:1584: zhes pa dag bstan pa dus ril du shar te byung ngo 'byung ngo 'byung bar 'gyur ro //
NK088(su)001:1585: don du na ye thog ma med pa nas rang
NK088(su)001:1586: shar bas dus gsum rgyud las grol te ngo bo
NK088(su)001:1587: ji bzhin pa la dgongs pa'o //
NK088(su)001:1588: dang po med las byung brjod pas //
NK088(su)001:1589: zhes pa dag gzhi ji bzhin pa nyid las bstan
NK088(su)001:1590: pa 'gro 'ong med par snang ba'i phyir mtha' yang
NK088(su)001:1591: gzhi ji bzhin pa las gzhan du ma yin pa'i
NK088(su)001:1592: phyir ro // gdung 'dzin thog ma'ang de bzhin nyid //
NK088(su)001:1593: zhes pa dag bstan pa 'dzin pa'i rigs can dag
NK088(su)001:1594: kyang de kho na nyid kyi ngo bo'i phyir tha
NK088(su)001:1597: zhes pa la sogs pa ril de bzhin nyid la
NK088(su)001:1598: 'gro 'ong ma dmigs kyang gdul bya'i ngo tsam du
NK088(su)001:1599: btags te / ye ma bcos pa nyid la sku snang ba med pa dang /
NK088(su)001:1600: rig pa'i klong nyid du bzhugs pa dang /
NK088(su)001:1601: rang byung gi ye shes kyi ngo bo nyid du gsal ba'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:1602: de 'das nas don brda ma go ba'i phyir skus 'dul ba sgra bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:1603: 'o na de kho na ltar 'byung 'jug snang ba yod dam zhe na /
NK088(su)001:1604: snang stong gi mtha' las grol bar bstan to //
NK088(su)001:1605: thub pa'i dbang po'i tshul de ltar zhing tha dad kyi sprul pa ji snyed byung ba yang /
NK088(su)001:1606: sgyu ma mkhan gyi rdzas ltar sku 'das nas snga
NK088(su)001:1607: ma'i mtshan dang sku ma yin pa gzhan ji ltar
NK088(su)001:1608: 'dul ba ltar snang nas don mdzad do //
NK088(su)001:1609: de bas na ston pa rdo rje sems dpa' de
NK088(su)001:1610: kho na nyid kyi sprul pa 'jig rten ji snyed
NK088(su)001:1611: du rang snang ba yang 'das shing snang ba lta
NK088(su)001:1612: bu la sogs pa de gcig dang du ma la
NK088(su)001:1613: sprul pa ril grol ba'i phyir te /
NK088(su)001:1614: ston pa'i rgyud gcig 'byung 'jug can gyi chos ni ma dmigs pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:1615: skye med ye shes nyid kyi dbyings //
NK088(su)001:1616: zhes pa la sogs pa ngo bo gang du mi
NK088(su)001:1617: zin la bsgrib pa ni byang chub kyi snying po
NK088(su)001:1618: ste / ril de'i bdag nyid la bshad pa ltar
NK088(su)001:1619: mig gis mig ma mthong ba bzhin yang mgon skyabs
NK088(su)001:1620: dam pa rang gi de kho na nyid de las
NK088(su)001:1622: rgyal ba'i dgongs pa tshig gsum po //
NK088(su)001:1623: zhes pa la sogs pa dkyil 'khor gsum dang sngags
NK088(su)001:1624: gsum gyi don te ngo bo nyid sgra bzhin blo
NK088(su)001:1625: dang gros yun gyi don gsum ste /
NK088(su)001:1626: lam pa'i ngor shes rab dang ting nge 'dzin dang de gnyis su med pa ste /
NK088(su)001:1627: de ni rnal 'byor mchog gi spyod yul yin pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:1628: rang las btsal na rnyed par 'gyur ro //
NK088(su)001:1629: rgyal ba kun gyi thugs 'jug pa //
NK088(su)001:1630: zhes pa dag ni dngos po thams cad kyi chos
NK088(su)001:1631: lugs kyi chos nyid la ni 'byung 'jug gi dus
NK088(su)001:1632: bral ba'i phyir don de nyid la cir yang ma
NK088(su)001:1633: bsams pa nyid blo bzhag pa yin pa'i phyir ro
NK088(su)001:1634: // chos kun nam mkha'i mtshan nyid de //
NK088(su)001:1635: zhes pa la sogs pa chos so cog snang la
NK088(su)001:1636: ma grub pa med la zad mi shes pa stong
NK088(su)001:1637: la thams cad 'byung ba'i mtshan dang mthun pas ji
NK088(su)001:1639: mtha' bral ba'i ye shes mnga' ba'i rgyal ba'i sku
NK088(su)001:1640: snang med gnyis bral bas sku gdung 'byung mi 'byung
NK088(su)001:1641: mi mnga' na sku gdung la mos pa dag la
NK088(su)001:1642: gang yang rdzogs pa'i byin rlabs sku gdung tshad nyungs
NK088(su)001:1643: 'bru tsam la sogs pa 'dul thabs byung ngo //
NK088(su)001:1645: 'o na de btsal bas 'byung zhing rnyed dam zhe na /
NK088(su)001:1646: 'dod pa med pa'i byin rlabs 'dod pa tha dad
NK088(su)001:1647: kyis tshol bas mi rnyed pa ni yi ge'i sgra
NK088(su)001:1648: bzhin no // gzugs snang zab sgrogs snying po can //
NK088(su)001:1649: zhes pa la sogs pa 'gro ba'i cha lugs su
NK088(su)001:1650: snang bas theg pa chen po'i don ston pa'i man
NK088(su)001:1651: ngag dang ldan pa ni rdo rje gsum gyi bdag
NK088(su)001:1652: nyid bla ma slob dpon te /
NK088(su)001:1653: rgyal ba ril gyi yang ston pa dang /
NK088(su)001:1654: yab dang yum yin pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:1655: mchod gnas dam pa yin par ston pa rdo rje sems dpas bka' stsal to //
NK088(su)001:1656: dpag tu med pa'i rgyal ba rnams //
NK088(su)001:1657: zhes pa dag ni sprul pa dang longs spyod ji
NK088(su)001:1658: snyed pa'ang 'gro ba'i rgyud dag pa las byung ba'i
NK088(su)001:1659: phyir / gdung ni 'gro ba skal can gyis 'dzin te brgyud mar 'byung ngo //
NK088(su)001:1660: de lta bas na 'khor ba med na /
NK088(su)001:1661: rgyal ba'ang mi 'byung na de yod pas de 'byung ba'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:1662: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sprul pa mya ngan las 'das
NK088(su)001:1663: pa ngo bo med pa'i dpe don sgra bzhin no
NK088(su)001:1664: // de lta bu'i don la 'khor rnams gdung ba
NK088(su)001:1665: byed de 'da' bar mthong bas gdung ba ni ji
NK088(su)001:1666: bzhin pa ma rig pa'i 'khrul pa'o //
NK088(su)001:1667: mya ngan byar med pa la byed pa ni ngo mtshar te /
NK088(su)001:1668: 'di ji nyes blo ji ltar nor ces skyes bu
NK088(su)001:1669: sku 'gying bag seng ge'i lta stangs kyis gzigs te
NK088(su)001:1670: bzhad mo mdzad pas 'khor rnams mya ngan dang bral
NK088(su)001:1671: te mi bzhin pa'i don mtha' mthong bas mdangs gsal
NK088(su)001:1672: bar gyur to // le'u lnga pa'i dri ba gsum
NK088(su)001:1673: pa dang gsol ba gdab par tshig drug smos pa'i
NK088(su)001:1674: lan ni gdung ba'i dri ba lan dus gcig tu
NK088(su)001:1675: smos pa go sla ste ngo sbyar ro //
NK088(su)001:1676: de nas lang ka'i bdag po /
NK088(su)001:1677: zhes pa la sogs pa 'jig rten ngang dus ril
NK088(su)001:1678: dang zhing 'di'i de ltar gdung ba gang sel dris
NK088(su)001:1679: pa'o // gsang ba'i bdag pos smras pa /
NK088(su)001:1680: zhes pa la sogs pa lan te zhing ril dang
NK088(su)001:1681: dus gsum gyi gdung ba ngas sel bas 'dir yang
NK088(su)001:1683: gdung ba gang la yod ce na /
NK088(su)001:1684: don dang blo ma rig cing shed ma bye ba'o //
NK088(su)001:1685: don blo shes shing shed bye ba ni blo ma
NK088(su)001:1686: bcos pas gdung ba med do zhes lang ka la
NK088(su)001:1687: sogs pa thos nas mya ngan las grol to //
NK088(su)001:1688: gang rmongs pa gdung ba sel ba'i le'u /
NK088(su)001:1689: zhes pa bshad zin pa dag ni mtshan no //
NK088(su)001:1690: drug pa bkrol ba ste de dag byung tshul dang
NK088(su)001:1691: po'i don brjod po'o ////de nas lang ka'i bdag pos
NK088(su)001:1692: sngon du gnang ba'i tshig bcu gnyis pa'i gnyis pa
NK088(su)001:1693: / zhes pa la sogs pa thub pa'i dbang pos
NK088(su)001:1694: lung bstan pa gnang ba'i tshig drug gnyis kyi gnyis
NK088(su)001:1695: pa dri ba'i dgos ched du ston pa 'das na
NK088(su)001:1696: gsang sngags ji ltar 'byung ba dris pa yi ge
NK088(su)001:1699: gsang ba'i bdag pos smras pa zhes pa la sogs pa /
NK088(su)001:1700: gsang bdag gis lang ka ci khyod kyis sngon thub
NK088(su)001:1701: pa'i dbang po nyid kyis kho bo cag gi chos
NK088(su)001:1702: kyi spun du gyur pa'i kuny+dza ras zhus pas lung
NK088(su)001:1703: bstan bcu gnyis gsungs pa de nye bar bstan pa
NK088(su)001:1704: ste khyod kyi dris lan du'ang nye bar bstan te
NK088(su)001:1705: / sgra ji bzhin du bcu gnyis bka' stsal nas
NK088(su)001:1706: de ni dus gsum du snang ngo snang bar gyur
NK088(su)001:1707: / to 'gyur ro // zhes sh+aakya thub pas lung
NK088(su)001:1708: bstan pas zhing 'dir grags pa khyod kyis mi shes
NK088(su)001:1710: de'i don lang ka nang du yang dag 'jog pas
NK088(su)001:1711: thub pa'i dbang po las tshul bcu gnyis ma thos
NK088(su)001:1713: tshig 'dis ni phyis kyi lung bstan tsam las dngos
NK088(su)001:1714: su bka' stsal pa ma yin pa'i phyir yang thub
NK088(su)001:1715: pa'i dbang po ni rgyud 'di'i ston pa ma yin
NK088(su)001:1717: lang ka'i bdag pos smras pa /
NK088(su)001:1718: e ma'o gsang ba'i bdag po zhes pa la sogs pa /
NK088(su)001:1719: thub pa'i dbang po las ma thos kyang gsang bdag
NK088(su)001:1720: nyid las thos pas tshul dang po'i the tshom sangs
NK088(su)001:1721: nas gnyis pa'i tshul zhus pa sgra ji bzhin no
NK088(su)001:1722: // gsang bdag gi lan sprul pa nyag gcig gi cha bzung ba'ang yi ge'i sgra bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:1723: yang thub pa'i dbang po nyid gang gis sprul pa
NK088(su)001:1724: yin par dris pa lan rdo rje sems dpa'i sprul
NK088(su)001:1725: par gsungs so // de'i gtan tshigs bstan pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:1726: lang ka'i bdag po de ci'i phyir zhe na zhes pa la sogs pa /
NK088(su)001:1727: sangs rgyas rdo rje sems dpa'i sprul pa ji snyed
NK088(su)001:1728: pas bdag gzhan gyi 'khor ba'i dpung bsnyil ba'i phyir
NK088(su)001:1730: de'ang 'dul dbang gis gnas drug gi 'jig rten re
NK088(su)001:1731: re la phyogs bcur mtshan mthun par grags pa ni
NK088(su)001:1733: kye lang ka'i bdag po'i der yang ma zad de zhes pa la sogs pa /
NK088(su)001:1734: zhing 'di'i 'jig rten drug gi thub pa drug po
NK088(su)001:1735: ma yin pa gzhan mang po bzhugs pa ston pa'o
NK088(su)001:1736: // de'ang mi mjed 'di na snang ba'i tshul dang /
NK088(su)001:1737: dpe de lta de ltar zhing bsam gyis mi khyab pa na bzhugs pa nye bar bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:1738: shar phyogs kyi 'jig rten gyi khams gling bzhi pa stong phrag bcu gnyis 'das pa na /
NK088(su)001:1739: zhes pa la sogs pa mi mjed kyi 'jig rten
NK088(su)001:1740: stong gsum po 'jig rten stong gsum po 'di las
NK088(su)001:1741: phar brtsis pa 'di'i pha mtha' nas gling bzhi ri
NK088(su)001:1742: rab dang bcas pa 'di lta bu'i grangs stong phrag
NK088(su)001:1744: 'jig rten der skyes pa'i sems can rnams rang bzhin
NK088(su)001:1745: gyis nyon mongs pa dang nag po'i las mi spyod
NK088(su)001:1746: pa'i phyir mtshan dri ma med pa /
NK088(su)001:1747: rgyu rin po che las byas pa /
NK088(su)001:1748: tshe dang longs spyod dang skye ba'i phyogs dang spyod tshul dang /
NK088(su)001:1749: bsam smon dang ston pa'i mtshan dang /
NK088(su)001:1751: de nyid kyi sprul pa drug gis gdul bya dang mthun par ston pa'i don to //
NK088(su)001:1752: 'di dag gi dgongs pa ni le'u tha ma'i dgongs
NK088(su)001:1753: mdo gsungs pa dag kyang rim pa bzhin rig pas
NK088(su)001:1754: 'thad do // slob dpon bde ba gsal mdzad kyi ti ka bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:1755: 'o na dri med sgra nyid thub pa drug gi cha'am bdun du 'gyur zhe na /
NK088(su)001:1756: mi las grags pa gtsor byas pa'i dbang yin pas bdun du mi 'gyur te /
NK088(su)001:1757: 'chad pa ril de bzhin sbyar te go sla bas sgra ji bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:1758: yang stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i mi mjed ces bya ba 'di na /
NK088(su)001:1759: zhes pa la sogs pa sh+aakya thub pa de ltar gyi ston pa nyid do //
NK088(su)001:1760: de bzhin du 'jig rten gyi khams bye ba sa yar zhes pa la sogs pa /
NK088(su)001:1761: de dag tu ma zad de grangs med par sku
NK088(su)001:1762: snang ba yang 'gro 'ong med par rdo rje sems
NK088(su)001:1763: dpa' nyid 'dul bzhin snang ba'ang chu dang zla ba
NK088(su)001:1764: lta bu'o // de dag las dus gcig tu chos ston pa ni ma yin te /
NK088(su)001:1765: 'khor mor rgyun ma chad pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:1766: la lar mngon par rdzogs pa sangs rgyas pa /
NK088(su)001:1767: zhes pa la sogs pa yi ge bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:1768: sprul pa ngos gzung bar 'thad pa min te tshul brtsi bar mi 'gal lo //
NK088(su)001:1769: 'dir yang sprul pa tha dad sems can bzang ngan
NK088(su)001:1770: gyi cha lugs kyis kyang chos ston te yi ge
NK088(su)001:1771: ji bzhin no // de las sha ri ram dang
NK088(su)001:1772: rus pa'i sku ni rim pa bzhin sku gdung ring
NK088(su)001:1773: ji bzhin no // bsrel lo // skye ba tha dad pa'i gzugs su snang ba go 'jal sla'o //
NK088(su)001:1775: ji ltar nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor zhes pa dag ste /
NK088(su)001:1776: don dang rjes thogs su sbyar ro //
NK088(su)001:1777: mtshan gyi mtha' mi rdzogs pa dang /
NK088(su)001:1778: dgos ched dang chos ston lugs sgra ji bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:1779: zhing de dag gi sprul pa'i dbang du phan tshun
NK088(su)001:1780: smos pa las yan man gsal bar ma bstan kyang
NK088(su)001:1781: / 'dir phyogs bcu kar 'jal bar byas te bye ba sa yar snang ba'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:1782: chos ston lugs gnyis kho nar smos pa ji zhe na /
NK088(su)001:1785: rdo rje sems dpa'i zhing khams na 'khod pa'i sems
NK088(su)001:1786: can chen po de dag ni zhes pa la sogs
NK088(su)001:1787: pa / zhing de'i 'gro ba rnams ni gsang sngags
NK088(su)001:1788: kyi skal ba dang ldan pa'i phyir khyad par gyi
NK088(su)001:1789: pa / sgrar brjod do // de nyid la shes rab ji bzhin pa mthong ba'i mthu can dang /
NK088(su)001:1790: gang yang mi skrag theg pa dang /
NK088(su)001:1792: don ji lta bar thag chod pa dang /
NK088(su)001:1793: lam mang du thebs shing yul de ma thag par 'jug pa lnga ni shes rab kyi mchog go //
NK088(su)001:1794: de kho na nyid kyi mthu mtha' tshol ba dang /
NK088(su)001:1795: don zab mo mi shong ba dang /
NK088(su)001:1797: don thag mi chod pa dang /
NK088(su)001:1798: lan don thogs pa dang bcas pa ste dman pa'o //
NK088(su)001:1799: de ltar cha gnyis las gzhan pa bkag pa'o //
NK088(su)001:1800: de lta bu'i blo dman pa dang mchog gis rim
NK088(su)001:1801: pa bzhin gsang sngags 'jug lugs gnyis su thos kyang
NK088(su)001:1802: rigs can du gyur pas chos la bzod pa thob
NK088(su)001:1804: de na gnas pa'i tshe tshad kyang zhes pa /
NK088(su)001:1805: rdo rje sems dpa'i zhing na 'khod pa'i 'gro ba
NK088(su)001:1806: rnams las dang bsod nams tha dad pas tshe tshad
NK088(su)001:1808: zhing 'dir brgya pa ste sprul pa nyag gcig gi dbang ngo //
NK088(su)001:1809: rgyu des na longs spyod kyang sgra bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:1810: ril la gsang sngags spyod par lung bstan par thob pa sha stag go //
NK088(su)001:1812: ril snying po byang chub kyi ngo bo nyid kyis bsnums pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:1814: 'bu cor sde la sogs pa la skal ba med pa ci zhe na /
NK088(su)001:1815: ngo bo nyid gsang sngags su ma gyur pa med
NK088(su)001:1816: pa la mdongs pa dang phal che ba'i phyir ro
NK088(su)001:1817: // sangs rgyas rdo rje sems dpa'i mtshan thos pa'i yon tan ni /
NK088(su)001:1818: rgyal ba thams cad kyis dngos gzhi yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:1819: lam pa'i dbang du na don gzhan la dgongs pa dang /
NK088(su)001:1820: snying po byang chub las mi 'gyur ba nges pa'i
NK088(su)001:1821: phyis snang ba'i skal ba nges pa can yin pa
NK088(su)001:1822: dang / bder gshegs mang pos sngar byin gyis brlabs
NK088(su)001:1823: te bdag nyid byin rlabs kyi bdag po'i phyir dang
NK088(su)001:1824: dang / / dman pa'i dbang du yang ril theg
NK088(su)001:1825: pa chen por nges par 'byung bas dus gzhan la
NK088(su)001:1826: dang / / dgongs pa ste / gnyis pa bzhi pa nas mar lnga ka'i don to //
NK088(su)001:1827: kye lang ka'i bdag po de'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:1828: zhes pa la sogs pa rgyas par brjod pa gtan
NK088(su)001:1829: tshigs su gyur pa'i sgo nas 'dir sprul pa nyag
NK088(su)001:1831: de bas na de snyed la mya ngan 'das pa
NK088(su)001:1832: ji snyed 'di ma yin pa'ang bzhugs pas the tshom
NK088(su)001:1833: chod de yid mgu bar gyur to //
NK088(su)001:1834: rdo rje sems dpa'i cho 'phrul yongs su bkod pa'i le'u zhes pa /
NK088(su)001:1835: rgyas par bkod pa rnams kyi don te bdun pa
NK088(su)001:1836: bkrol ba'o ////de nas yang lang ka'i bdag pos dris
NK088(su)001:1838: zhes pa la sogs pa le'u 'di ni rnal 'byor
NK088(su)001:1839: dang po'i rgyu'i don te sprul pa'i sgron ma 'byung
NK088(su)001:1840: ba'i gzhi'i ngo bo nges par dris pa'o //
NK088(su)001:1841: lan gsang ba pas brjod pa ni /
NK088(su)001:1842: gsang ba'i bdag pos smras pa /
NK088(su)001:1843: lang ka'i bdag po rdo rje sems dpa' ni //
NK088(su)001:1844: zhes pa dag rang gi sems ril len cing sdud
NK088(su)001:1845: pas snying por gyur pa la sgrib byed ngang gis
NK088(su)001:1846: bral ba thun mong ma yin pa'i don ma bcos
NK088(su)001:1847: ma bslad pas ma nor ba'i don las gzhan phyogs
NK088(su)001:1848: bcad pa nyid du bka' stsal to //
NK088(su)001:1850: ces pa la sogs pa nges par chud par bya
NK088(su)001:1851: ba'i phyir dri ba bzhi re re nas dris pa'o
NK088(su)001:1852: // gsang ba'i bdag pos smras pa /
NK088(su)001:1853: lang ka'i bdag po sems zhes bya ba ni /
NK088(su)001:1854: zhes pa la sogs pa lan rgyas pa ste /
NK088(su)001:1855: gang rgyu rkyen 'dus pa las 'phral du ma grub
NK088(su)001:1856: pa'i ye shes la 'phral du rnam rtog gis byed
NK088(su)001:1857: pa po ka nas dag pas rgyu rkyen la rag
NK088(su)001:1858: ma las par ji mtshan nyid de snyed pa'i chos
NK088(su)001:1859: su ma rol pa 'gags par rang shar ba snang
NK088(su)001:1862: brtags na med la bzhag na sna tshogs 'byung ba'i legs pa che //
NK088(su)001:1863: dngos po med par chags pa'i cha lugs kun la ston //
NK088(su)001:1866: bde ba chen po ji bzhin pa'i klong chen po ni /
NK088(su)001:1867: ril gyi dngos gzhi pas tha snyad gzhan theg dgu
NK088(su)001:1868: 'dus la ma dmigs pa'i phyir 'bras kyi phung po
NK088(su)001:1869: bzhin no // rtsa ba bzhi'i dang po'i lan no de dag rim pa bzhin du sbyar te /
NK088(su)001:1870: de kho na nyid ni gang du'ang snang ma myong
NK088(su)001:1871: yang ngo bo dang dri ma bral ba'i don te
NK088(su)001:1872: phyogs med pa ye shes kyi snang ba'o //
NK088(su)001:1873: mi shes pa las ma rig pa pa tsam ma
NK088(su)001:1874: yin pa'i gzhan gang gis sgrib byed gzhan med pa
NK088(su)001:1875: ste / ngo bos ma rig de nyid kyang ye shes chen po'i don dang /
NK088(su)001:1878: brjod pa mthar gyur pas bstan du mi btub pa nyid yul las grol ba'i brtag dka' ba dang /
NK088(su)001:1879: sngags byin rlabs kyi gzhir gyur pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:1880: ngo bo yongs su mi zin pas gza' gtad med
NK088(su)001:1881: pa bzhin dngos po gnyis pa'i chos rnams kyi rtsa
NK088(su)001:1883: rtsa ba'i gsum pa min pa yin par 'phral du
NK088(su)001:1884: lam pas gtan tshigs ma bsgyur rtsol ba dang bsam
NK088(su)001:1885: dpyod kyis sel ma zhugs pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:1886: yul du ma gyur pas ye shes bshad pa bzhin
NK088(su)001:1887: glo bur du gzhan gyi ngo bo bsgrub pa min
NK088(su)001:1888: te / ming gi tha snyad ma bkol bar rang bral ba'i don dang /
NK088(su)001:1889: de nyid pas gol sa med cing gnyen pos bya ba med pa /
NK088(su)001:1890: 'gro ldog spyi'u tshugs gar 'gros kyang snying po byang
NK088(su)001:1891: chub nyid pa'i phyir ngo bo nges par 'grub pa'o
NK088(su)001:1892: // yang lang ka'i bdag pos dris pa /
NK088(su)001:1893: zhes pa la sogs pa dri ba gnyis dris pa
NK088(su)001:1894: sgra ji bzhin te snga ma'i dri ba yang yin
NK088(su)001:1895: pa'i phyir ro // gsang ba'i bdag pos smras pa /
NK088(su)001:1896: lang ka'i bdag po byed pa po med /
NK088(su)001:1897: ces pa la sogs pa ma lus pa'i chos thig
NK088(su)001:1898: le chen por rgyas thebs pa la mkhan byed pa
NK088(su)001:1899: po po dang las gnyis kar yang ma dmigs pas
NK088(su)001:1900: / des ngo bo zhig bya bas btsal du med
NK088(su)001:1901: bsgrub tu'ang mi btub pa'i phyir ma byas pa'o dang
NK088(su)001:1902: / / phyi mo'i chos nyid gang du'ang ma g.yos pa'i phyi ma bcos pa'o dang /
NK088(su)001:1903: gang med pa las rang gis ngo bo bstan du
NK088(su)001:1904: med par rgyun tu 'byung zhing rang bzhin thams cad
NK088(su)001:1905: pa'i phyir dus gsum ril du tha dad mtshan ma
NK088(su)001:1906: thams cad la zhen pa ma bsgom par khyab pas
NK088(su)001:1907: / las kyis dngos po ste dge sdig lung ma
NK088(su)001:1908: bstan gzhi gsum gyi nang sna tshogs ril tha dad
NK088(su)001:1909: du rang snang ba'i phyir rnam shes dgu pa de
NK088(su)001:1910: nyid dpe nam mkha' lta bu'o //
NK088(su)001:1911: de'i rgyun ni de nyid dus tshogs brgyad kyis rgyun
NK088(su)001:1912: du snang ba ni nam mkha'i cho 'phrul sprin sogs
NK088(su)001:1913: lta bu ste glo bur ba'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:1914: kho thag chod pas ngo bo'i don rig go //
NK088(su)001:1915: nges tshig dri ba'i phyir yang dris pa /
NK088(su)001:1916: gsang ba'i bdag po de la ci'i phyir rdo rje sems dpa' zhes bgyi /
NK088(su)001:1917: zhes pa la sogs pa dri ba dngos dang lan ni gtan tshigs bdun gyis 'grub ste /
NK088(su)001:1918: rdo rje sems dpa' ma bslad pa'i de bzhin nyid
NK088(su)001:1919: chen po ni dus snga phyi ril du de bshig
NK088(su)001:1921: bdag gzhan med pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:1922: rgyu rkyen med pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:1923: mi nor mi 'gyur ba'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:1924: mi g.yo ma bsgribs par gsal ba dang /
NK088(su)001:1925: don chen po ji lta bar ye mngon du byas pa'i ngo bo dang /
NK088(su)001:1926: mtshan gzhi cir yang snang ba ril mnyam pa chen
NK088(su)001:1927: por ma bkag ma dmigs par gtan nas sbyangs pa'i
NK088(su)001:1928: phyir mtshan nges par bstan pa ste /
NK088(su)001:1929: dang po nas gnyis pa gsum pa ni mtshan dang po'i rdo rje bsad pa'o //
NK088(su)001:1930: bzhi pa nas drug pa ni bar sems pa'i don to //
NK088(su)001:1931: tha ma ni tha ma'i dpal don to //
NK088(su)001:1932: rdo rje sems dpa'i mtshan sgra du mar snang ba'i rtsa ba bcu gcig bstan pa gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:1933: lang ka'i bdag po de la ni bla na med pa'i byang chub kyi sems zhes kyang bya'o //
NK088(su)001:1934: zhes pa la sogs pa rdo rje sems dpa'i de
NK088(su)001:1935: kho na nyid che ba bla na med pa ril
NK088(su)001:1936: gyi bdag nyid pas zla med cing dri ma ma
NK088(su)001:1937: spangs dag pa la yon chub tan gyis gzhag pas
NK088(su)001:1938: ngo bo gsal sems la mi g.yo ba'i phyir dang
NK088(su)001:1939: / bshad pa'i chos bzhis bsdus pa ril gyi ngo
NK088(su)001:1940: bo phyogs ris bral ba'i chos rnams kyi chos nyid
NK088(su)001:1941: ma bcos pa chen po'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:1942: ngo bo sems kyi stong pa ma spangs ma grub pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:1943: mtha' las 'das tshig gis brjod du mi btub pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:1944: de nyid du dbu ma 'dzin pa bral ba'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:1945: rgyal ba sangs rgyas kun ril gyi ngo bor bzhugs
NK088(su)001:1946: pas nor bu rin po che lta bu'i phyir dang
NK088(su)001:1947: / gdul bya ji lta ba de ltar rang snang ba'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:1948: bud+d+ha ril 'dis grol bar byed pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:1949: sprul pa thams cad pa yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:1950: byin rlabs mi 'gogs rang snang ye shes chen pos zin pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:1951: ril ma 'dres pa yongs su rdzogs pa'i phyir te /
NK088(su)001:1953: sems ni gzugs bral gzugs kyang rdzogs //
NK088(su)001:1955: lang ka la bos nas mtshan bstan pa'i dgos pa ni /
NK088(su)001:1956: rig tha dad nas bya ba'i sgor bstan kyang ngo
NK088(su)001:1957: bo la med pa'i phyir bla dwags su rtogs par
NK088(su)001:1959: lang ka'i bdag po de'i phyir na sangs rgyas ni bla dwags so //
NK088(su)001:1960: zhes pa la sogs pa snga ma'i don gyis brjod
NK088(su)001:1961: pa thams cad bla dwags su rig bya ba'i don
NK088(su)001:1962: to // bla dwags kyi mtshan nyid bstan pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:1963: lang ka'i bdag po bla dwags gang yin pa /
NK088(su)001:1964: zhes pa la sogs pa de bzhin nyid la rtog
NK088(su)001:1965: kyang dngos po gnyis thog ma can ni ma yin
NK088(su)001:1966: no // bla dwags nyid mtshan nyid de las gzhan ldan pa' skyon ni /
NK088(su)001:1967: lang ka'i bdag po gal te ye nas ldan na /
NK088(su)001:1968: zhes pa dag de bzhin nyid dang mtshungs te glo
NK088(su)001:1969: bur ma yin na skyon dngos po gnyis pa'i chos
NK088(su)001:1971: gal te na sgrib pa sbyangs kyang dag par mi 'gyur ba'i skyon yod do //
NK088(su)001:1972: glo bur gyi mtshan nyid dpe yis brjod pa sgra ji bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:1973: lang ka'i bdag po de'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:1976: zhes pa dag glo bur gyi ngo bo ste btags pa'i chos rnams dang /
NK088(su)001:1977: zhen blos phyi rol du snang ba'i mthu can dag dang /
NK088(su)001:1978: ming tsam pa de sgra'i spyi dang don gyi spyi dang /
NK088(su)001:1979: sgra rang gi mtshan nyid dang /
NK088(su)001:1981: bsod nams ma yin pa dang /
NK088(su)001:1983: khams gsum la sogs pa'i ngo bo'o //
NK088(su)001:1984: de'i mtshan nyid zhen pa po la snang ba dang /
NK088(su)001:1986: don mthong du mi ster ba dang /
NK088(su)001:1987: de mtshan ma 'byongs pa'i phyir glo bur gyi gtan tshigs bzhir 'gyur ro //
NK088(su)001:1988: 'o na gong gi dkon mchog gsum la sogs pa
NK088(su)001:1989: ni bsgrub bya nyid las glo bur du mi 'gyur
NK088(su)001:1990: ro zhe na / de dag ni ngo bo nyid ma spangs bral ba'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:1991: lam pas der 'dod na ched du byas pa'i zhen pa ste /
NK088(su)001:1992: chu bo brgal ba'i gru bzhin de dag tu 'dzin pa nyid kyang 'dor bar rig pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:1993: glo bur min pa'i skyon gsum bshad pa de'i ngo bo bstan pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:1995: gal te las dang las kyi rnam par smin pa
NK088(su)001:1996: zhes pa dag rgyu 'bras kyi chos rnams glo bur
NK088(su)001:1997: ma yin na de kho na nyid kyang dri ma
NK088(su)001:1998: can pas mtshan nyid bshad pa ltar mi 'gyur na
NK088(su)001:1999: de bas de bzhin nyid du brjod pa'ang phyi mo'i
NK088(su)001:2000: chos nyid mi 'gyur ba'i bla dwags so //
NK088(su)001:2001: lang ka'i bdag po de'i phyir chos thams cad zhes
NK088(su)001:2002: pa dag gtan tshigs bshad pa bzhin pas chos kun
NK088(su)001:2003: ji bzhin pa'i ngang nyid la rnam pa'i brtags pa
NK088(su)001:2004: med / sgra nyid ma dmigs pas mtshon par byed pa med /
NK088(su)001:2005: bshad pa bzhin ngo bo gang du'ang ldan pa med
NK088(su)001:2006: pa'i phyir bstan du med pas ngo bo nyid mtshon
NK088(su)001:2007: pa bral ba'o // lang kas ji bzhin pa nyid
NK088(su)001:2008: du blos gzung du yod med dris pa bstan pa'i
NK088(su)001:2009: pa bral ba'o // phyir / smras pa gsang ba'i bdag po gang ming du btags pa'i gzhi la /
NK088(su)001:2010: zhes pa gzhi ci bzhin pa btags pa bral ba nyid du'ang brtag tu med dam zhes dris pa'o //
NK088(su)001:2011: smras pa lang ka'i bdag po /
NK088(su)001:2012: zhes pa la sogs pa lan te gal te gzhi
NK088(su)001:2013: ci bzhin pa'i ngang la rtogs bya rtog byed ma
NK088(su)001:2014: dmigs pa dang / de nyid du rtog na'ang nad yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:2015: de las gzhan pa'i gtan tshigs kyis de'i ngo ldan par mi rnyed pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:2016: bshad pa'i don gyis glo bur gyi rtog pa bzang
NK088(su)001:2017: ngan gnyis la sangs rgyas dang sems can du btags
NK088(su)001:2018: pas zhen pa gnyis kyis de ltar mthong gi ngo
NK088(su)001:2019: bo la gnyis pa med par bka' stsal to //
NK088(su)001:2021: zhes pa la sogs pa de bas don chen po
NK088(su)001:2022: ma rig pa'i byis pa rgyu'i theg pa ba dag
NK088(su)001:2023: /bshad pa'i rtog pas don mthong du mi ster ba'i
NK088(su)001:2024: phyir de dag la slar don du gnyer zhing rgyu
NK088(su)001:2025: 'bra la sogs par 'dzin pa ni 'khrul to //
NK088(su)001:2026: de'i rang bzhin rtogs par bya ba'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:2029: 'o na sems can dang sangs rgyas 'di gnyis /
NK088(su)001:2030: zhes pa la sogs pa dris pa rnams ni sgra bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:2031: lan ni rim par bstan te /
NK088(su)001:2033: lang ka'i bdag po stong pa nyid du shes par bya'o //
NK088(su)001:2034: zhes pa dag /rang rig pa 'od gsal ba'i ngo
NK088(su)001:2035: bo la ni sangs rgyas sems can gyi ngo bo
NK088(su)001:2037: lam rim par de lta bu'i chos so cog gi mtshan nyid pas ril la khyab bo //
NK088(su)001:2038: de ni spyod yul rten dang brten can grol bas gang la'ang rten mi 'acha'o //
NK088(su)001:2039: stong pa nyid la gnas pa ci la gnas pa lags /
NK088(su)001:2040: zhes pa de ltar stong pa chen po la 'byed pa med pas bya ba rdzogs te /
NK088(su)001:2041: don byed pa'i lhag pa po de las med de gzhan nas mi rnyed par bstan pa'o //
NK088(su)001:2044: zhes pa la sogs pa sgra ji bzhin dri ba gnyis kyi lan brjod par bya ste /
NK088(su)001:2045: dngos po gnyis pa ril mtha' bral ba'i stong chen
NK088(su)001:2046: gyi ngo bor ma bgrod par rgyas btags pas de'i
NK088(su)001:2047: don ci'ang ma mthong ma rig par mthong rig na
NK088(su)001:2048: / 'gro don ma byas rdzogs te bsgral ba chen po'i phyir snying rje chen po nyid do //
NK088(su)001:2049: de lta bu'i nges don ma rnyed pa'i theg pa
NK088(su)001:2050: dman pa dag dmigs pas stong gsum gyi 'gro ba'i
NK088(su)001:2052: mya ngan las 'das pa la bkod pa ni snying
NK088(su)001:2053: rje chung ngu ste de ni dmigs pas bya ba'i
NK088(su)001:2055: 'jig rten mtha' med la ltos nas ba spu'i cha'i don tsam yang med pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2056: slar yang 'chi ba yod pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:2057: de dag gi rtsa ba yang chen po yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:2058: de bas na thugs rje chen po la dmigs pas
NK088(su)001:2059: gnas par mi 'dod pa ni gnas pa ste de
NK088(su)001:2060: lta bar bya'o // snying rje chen po la gnas
NK088(su)001:2061: pa'i rnal 'byor chen po dag gi mdzad pa ni
NK088(su)001:2062: lta bar bya'o // / sems can ji snyed pa dag gi 'ching ba gcig par yang mi byed /
NK088(su)001:2063: de nyid sdom pa yang mi byed do //
NK088(su)001:2064: de ltar ye 'ching grol ma dmigs pa la /
NK088(su)001:2065: don de'i rjes su shes pa 'brang ba'ang med pa ni /
NK088(su)001:2066: bya ba dang stsol ba'i theg pa ril bcad pas mtshon cha chen po ste /
NK088(su)001:2067: gdul bya snang ba ma 'gags la mi dmigs par bsgral to //
NK088(su)001:2068: de gtan tshigs kyis grub pa ni /
NK088(su)001:2069: gzhi la 'gro ba rang rgyud pa med pas zhen
NK088(su)001:2070: rtog snang ba'i phyir btags pa'i yod pa tsam pas
NK088(su)001:2071: so // snying rje chen po de ni de bzhin nyid dang /
NK088(su)001:2072: glo bur gnyis kyi khyad par gyi /
NK088(su)001:2073: zhes pa lan gnyis pas ston te /
NK088(su)001:2074: thugs rje chen po de'i ming nges par gang las grub zhe na /
NK088(su)001:2075: gnyis ka las btags te ye gnyis su med pas zin pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2076: tha snyad de nyid du dag pa tsam las btags pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:2077: lang ka'i bdag po de lta bas na 'di lta ste /
NK088(su)001:2078: mtha' yas ming du btags pa'i gzhi //
NK088(su)001:2079: zhes pa la sogs pa tshig shad kyi tshul gyis sngags kyi mdo zhes pa ming 'grub ste /
NK088(su)001:2080: don lhag pa min kyang lhug pa dang tshig shad
NK088(su)001:2081: gnyis mdo rgyas su 'byung ba'i phyir te cha mthun
NK088(su)001:2083: sdud pa po la bos nas /
NK088(su)001:2084: sngar rgyas par de lta bas na bstan pa'i tshul
NK088(su)001:2085: des na mdor yang 'di lta ste de nyid nye
NK088(su)001:2087: dngos po bsam yas pa'i ming du btags pa grags pa'i chos //
NK088(su)001:2088: zhes pa gnyis med kyi ngo bo la dngos po
NK088(su)001:2089: bzang ngan gyi yul drug mthong snang grags la sogs
NK088(su)001:2090: pa ril bla dwags ci'ang ma yin pa las cir
NK088(su)001:2091: yang btags par zad snang ba'i phyir ngo bo rang
NK088(su)001:2092: rgyud pa de la dngos gzhi med do //
NK088(su)001:2093: 'o na gang med pa las snang na ri bong
NK088(su)001:2094: rwa dang nam mkha'i me tog kyang 'byung bar rigs
NK088(su)001:2095: so zhe na / gang las ming du btags pa'i gzhi //
NK088(su)001:2096: med rgyu btags chags bsgrub 'grub cing //
NK088(su)001:2097: zhes pa de kho nyid kyi dngos po gang la
NK088(su)001:2098: snang ba tha dad pa la ming du btags pa
NK088(su)001:2099: ril gyi gzhi ni ji lta ba du zhe na
NK088(su)001:2100: / mtshan nyid thams cad pa mtshan nyid med pa /
NK088(su)001:2101: rnam pa kun ldan rnam pa bral ba /
NK088(su)001:2102: brjod pa kun 'byung brjod pa med pa ni /
NK088(su)001:2103: gang yang ma bkol bas rnam pa'i phyogs bral ba'i
NK088(su)001:2104: phyir ngo bo med pa lhun gyis grub pa'i rgyul
NK088(su)001:2105: ji ltar btags bsnyad pa ltar chags grub bsams pa
NK088(su)001:2107: de lta bas na ri bong rwa dang mi mtshungs so //
NK088(su)001:2109: rang bzhin gcig tu ma nges pas //
NK088(su)001:2110: ji ltar bltas pa de ltar snang //
NK088(su)001:2113: mdor na ji ltar btags bsams bzhin //
NK088(su)001:2114: 'gyur bas thams cad ngo bor snang //
NK088(su)001:2116: des na bya med byas pa zin //
NK088(su)001:2117: zhes pa gtan tshigs la snyegs te bya med mdzad
NK088(su)001:2118: pa med pa'i phrin las kyis don byas pa zin
NK088(su)001:2119: ril 'grub bo // mi snang ba las kun snang ba //
NK088(su)001:2120: zhes pa dag ni byang chub sems ni mtha' gang
NK088(su)001:2121: du snang ma myong ba mi snang ba las thams
NK088(su)001:2122: cad kyi dngos gzhi bas zhen pas ji ltar bsam
NK088(su)001:2123: pa ltar kun snang ba ni thams cad thams cad
NK088(su)001:2124: bzang ngan ril bshad pa ltar ltos pa'i glo bur
NK088(su)001:2125: ba'o // snang bzhi nyid med pa'i snying po ste //
NK088(su)001:2126: zhes pa dag btags chags par byung ba'i ril de
NK088(su)001:2127: kho na nyid las gzhan pa med pa'i phyir mtha'
NK088(su)001:2129: 'o na bla dwags smos pa ci dgos zhe na /
NK088(su)001:2130: sangs rgyas med las sangs rgyas dang //
NK088(su)001:2131: zhes pa la sogs pa gzhi nyid gang yang lhun
NK088(su)001:2132: gyis grub pa'i phyir rnam pa'i sangs rgyas chos gang
NK088(su)001:2133: du'ang med pa las bla dwags sangs rgyas dang byang
NK088(su)001:2134: chub sogs bzang phyogs su btags pa ni don shed
NK088(su)001:2135: ma bye ba rnams brgyud pas drang ba'i dgos pa
NK088(su)001:2137: de lta bas na gsang sngags de kho na nyid
NK088(su)001:2138: la ni ye rnam pa mi dmigs pa la smos
NK088(su)001:2139: pa 'di dag gi ming gi tha snyad tsam yang
NK088(su)001:2140: med pas der snang yang med do //
NK088(su)001:2141: chos nyid nam mkha'i dkyil yangs nas //
NK088(su)001:2142: zhes pa la sogs pa gang de bzhin nyid stong la zad mi shes pa /
NK088(su)001:2143: med la thams cad 'byung zhing khyab pa snang la mi 'gag pa nam mkha' lta bu ste /
NK088(su)001:2144: de la mtha' mi dmigs pa'i bla dwags tsam la
NK088(su)001:2145: ma chud pa med pas de nyid rang byung gi
NK088(su)001:2146: ye shes ril gyi dngos gzhi 'byung gnas su rang
NK088(su)001:2147: shar ba ni snying rje chen po'i bdag nyid do
NK088(su)001:2148: // de ni dpe me dang 'dra ste ma rig
NK088(su)001:2149: pa gnyis ka nas sbyangs pas ril spyod yul dag
NK088(su)001:2150: pa nyid du gsal lo zhes gsang bdag gis bka'
NK088(su)001:2151: // stsal to // lang ka'i bdag po la sogs pa //
NK088(su)001:2152: zhes pa dag 'khor rnams don de thos pas lam
NK088(su)001:2153: dang 'bras bu gzhan na med par rtogs pas tha
NK088(su)001:2154: ma'i dbugs phyin te gsang sngags gnyis med kyi don
NK088(su)001:2156: gsang sngags rang gi ngo bo bstan pa'i le'u zhes pa /
NK088(su)001:2157: ji bzhin pa nyid kyi mtshan nyid bstan pa ste bdag nyid chen po'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK088(su)001:2158: lhun gyis grub pa'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK088(su)001:2159: klong yangs chub pa'i rnal 'byor gyi spyod yul lo //
NK088(su)001:2160: le'u brgyad pa bkrol ba'o ////de nas yang lang ka'i bdag pos /
NK088(su)001:2161: yang gsang ba'i bdag po la zhes pa la sogs pa /
NK088(su)001:2162: byung tshul gsum pa gang gis nges pa ci zhig dus nam rnyed zhus pa sgra bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:2164: lang ka'i bdag po gang gis zhes pa la sogs pa /
NK088(su)001:2165: su gang yang rung bas rnyed par bya ba ni
NK088(su)001:2166: rdo rje sems dpa' de bzhin nyid nges par go
NK088(su)001:2167: ba ni gsang sngags thob pa ste bshad zin to
NK088(su)001:2169: gsang ba'i bdag po zhes pa dag dri ba bzhi dris te /
NK088(su)001:2171: de kho na rnyed par byung ba de'i rgyu dang gnas dang yul dang byung tshul dris pa'o //
NK088(su)001:2172: gsang ba'i bdag pos smras pa zhes pa la sogs pa /
NK088(su)001:2173: nges don dris pa'i lan te /
NK088(su)001:2174: de ni gzhan na med pa'i phyir dngos po 'khor
NK088(su)001:2175: 'das gnyis de kho na nyid du rang snang ba
NK088(su)001:2176: dang / ye nyid nas dgongs pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2177: bsam pa lhun gyis grub cing son pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2178: 'jig rten tha dad par sku bstan pa'i gzugs brnyan
NK088(su)001:2179: gyis mtshon nas byin rlabs sgron ma rang snang ba
NK088(su)001:2180: dang / ye ngo bo nyid rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2181: zhen pa'i bsam rgyud dag pa gnyis lta bur byung ngo zhes gsungs so //
NK088(su)001:2182: yang lang ka'i bdag pos dris pa /
NK088(su)001:2183: zhes pa dag ni dris lan tha ma'i nges pa dris pa ste sgra bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:2184: gsang ba'i bdag pos smras pa /
NK088(su)001:2185: zhes pa la sogs pa de'i nges pa gnyis kyi dang po ni /
NK088(su)001:2186: zhing khams tha dad pa'i sgron ma yang sprul pa
NK088(su)001:2187: dang bcas pa la sogs par snang ba'i ngo bo
NK088(su)001:2188: so so ba med pa'i phyir bla dwags tsam du
NK088(su)001:2189: mtha'i 'ching ba ye bral ba ji bzhin pa lam
NK088(su)001:2190: pa dang / ma bcos pa rtsol bas bsgyur bslad
NK088(su)001:2191: med de ye ril gyi 'bras bu'i rtsa bar gnas
NK088(su)001:2192: pa ni ngo bo 'di 'drar yod la med pa
NK088(su)001:2193: ste ngo bo gcig ye ji bzhin grub bo //
NK088(su)001:2194: gnyis pa rgyud dag pa ni de kho na 'gro
NK088(su)001:2195: ba'i sems kyi chos nyid de de ma mthong ba
NK088(su)001:2196: dang mi 'dra ba'i mthong ba dang mi 'dra ba'i
NK088(su)001:2197: mthong bar 'gyur bas zhen pa dang rang gi ngo
NK088(su)001:2198: bo gnyis ka dang bral ba la nges par bzhag
NK088(su)001:2199: go // ril ye ji bzhin gyi mes chen po
NK088(su)001:2200: de lta bas na de ltar sras kyi rgyal ba
NK088(su)001:2201: ril yang bsam dbang gis gnyis su gsal te /
NK088(su)001:2202: des na de rtogs ma rtogs gnyis kyi snang bas
NK088(su)001:2203: phye ba las ngo bo ma tha dad med pas
NK088(su)001:2204: gsang sngags ji bzhin par nges par gzhag go //
NK088(su)001:2205: yang lang ka'i bdag po dris pa /
NK088(su)001:2206: zhes pa la sogs pa rgyud dag pa'i rdo rje
NK088(su)001:2207: sems dpa' la dri ba'i phyir zhal gyis 'ches pa'i
NK088(su)001:2208: sems kyi chos nyid kyi ngo bo dang /
NK088(su)001:2209: de rtogs na ngo bo 'di'i don gang rtogs par 'jogs pas dris pa'o //
NK088(su)001:2210: gsang ba'i bdag pos smras pa /
NK088(su)001:2211: zhes pa la sogs pa 'gro ba ril gyi sems
NK088(su)001:2212: kyi chos nyid ji lta ba de ci yang ma
NK088(su)001:2213: rnyed par rnyed pas chos ril rtogs te don de
NK088(su)001:2214: las gzhan med pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:2215: de kho na chos sku chen po nyid yin te /
NK088(su)001:2216: de rtog dpyod tshol ba'i chos rnams kyis rnyed pa ma yin te /
NK088(su)001:2218: dpe yis mtshon pas de la yul dang yul can bsgrub bya dang sgrub byed med pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:2219: de'i mtha' gang du'ang ma byung ste /
NK088(su)001:2220: ye nyid 'bras bu la de nyid kyi tha snyad
NK088(su)001:2221: tsam yang med pas sems can 'gro ba'i ngo bo
NK088(su)001:2222: dang ming btags pa dang dngos po chos can rnams
NK088(su)001:2223: kyi ngo bo dang ming btags rgyal bas btsal kyang
NK088(su)001:2225: de'i gtan tshigs brjod pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:2227: chos thams cad ni byang chub kyi mtshan nyid yin la zhes pa la sogs pa /
NK088(su)001:2228: 'gro ba dang chos can gsal ba min te /
NK088(su)001:2229: chos so cog sems kyi rang bzhin ye shes 'od gsal ba'i ngo bo nyid yin te /
NK088(su)001:2230: de ni rang rig pa'i nam mkha'o //
NK088(su)001:2232: mtshan nyid thams cad pa yin pa'i phyir rnam pa'i mtshan nyid gang yang ma yin pa'o //
NK088(su)001:2233: don des na gzhan nas 'bras bu med pas bdag
NK088(su)001:2234: nyid las mi btsal ba'i btsal ba chen po nyid
NK088(su)001:2235: btsal ba'o // de ni bdag nyid kyi ngo bo
NK088(su)001:2236: dang tshol ba dag la dgongs pa dang dgag pa'i
NK088(su)001:2237: btsal ba'o // phyir ro // 'o na 'bras bu
NK088(su)001:2238: de rang rig pa la tshul ji ltar gnas zhe
NK088(su)001:2239: btsal ba'o // phyir ro // na / sems de
NK088(su)001:2240: ni rang bzhin gyis yongs su dag pa'i phyir zhes
NK088(su)001:2241: btsal ba'o // phyir ro // na / pa dag
NK088(su)001:2242: ni / rang bzhin dang tshig gi gtan tshigs las
NK088(su)001:2244: des na sems 'bras bu'i mtshan nyid de /
NK088(su)001:2245: dngos po gsum kar yang snang la ma grub pas phyi nang bar na yang med do //
NK088(su)001:2246: 'o na ngo bo gang zhig gtan nas mi rnyed dam zhe na /
NK088(su)001:2247: rgyal ba nyid kyis kyang dus gsum du ma mthong ma gzigs so //
NK088(su)001:2249: de ji ltar ma gzigs na /
NK088(su)001:2250: kha dog tu ma gzigs so //
NK088(su)001:2253: zhes pa la sogs pa dbyibs kha dog bcu dang nyi shu rtsa lnga dang /
NK088(su)001:2255: pho mo ma ning drug dang /
NK088(su)001:2256: khams gsum thams cad kyi bdag nyid de /
NK088(su)001:2257: khams gsum de las gzhan ma yin pa chos so cog gi ngo bo gzhi rtsa yin pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:2258: des na rnam pa'i phyogs cha rnams dang bral bas /
NK088(su)001:2259: phyogs cha smros pa rnams su nam du'ang ma gzigs
NK088(su)001:2260: pas ngo bos snang ma myong ba nyid dus 'dzin
NK088(su)001:2262: 'chad par 'gyur pa'ang rjes su mthun no //
NK088(su)001:2263: 'o na rnam par nges na ci skyon nam zhe na /
NK088(su)001:2264: de ni rnam pa gcig tu nges na rnam pa
NK088(su)001:2265: ji snyed pa 'gags pa dang gzhan dang ma 'brel
NK088(su)001:2266: ba bkol ba'i skyon du 'gyur te /
NK088(su)001:2268: lha'i sems su ma gzigs so //
NK088(su)001:2269: klu'i sems su ma gzigs so //
NK088(su)001:2270: zhes pa dag ni rgyud zhi bar gyur pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2271: gti mug che zhing longs spyod la 'chel ba dang /
NK088(su)001:2274: rtsod pa la dga' ba dang /
NK088(su)001:2279: tshul de dang 'dra ba'ang yin pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2283: de dag la sogs pa 'chad par 'gyur te sems
NK088(su)001:2284: can gyi rigs sna tshogs pa'i rgyud kyi rnam par
NK088(su)001:2285: ma gzigs so // ngo bo nyid gzung ba dang 'dzin pa ril bral ba'i ngo bor bzhugs pa'o //
NK088(su)001:2286: de gtan tshigs yid ches pas 'grub pa'i don bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:2288: sems kyi rang bzhin gang yin pa de ni /
NK088(su)001:2289: rdo rje sems dpa'i rang byung gi ye shes yin la zhes pa la sogs pa /
NK088(su)001:2290: gang 'gro ba ril gyi sems nyid ji bzhin pa ni rgyu rkyen la rag ma las pa /
NK088(su)001:2291: mtshan nyid thams cad ma spangs gsal ba'i phyir gcig dang dum ma yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:2293: yang lang ka'i bdag pos dris pa /
NK088(su)001:2295: sems can gyi sems de'i ci'i phyir zhes pa la sogs pa dri ba dngos sgra bzhin te /
NK088(su)001:2296: lan kyang rang byung gi ye shes dang sems kyi
NK088(su)001:2297: tha snyad rnams ngo bos gnyis su med par lan
NK088(su)001:2298: btab ste / mdo rgyas su bstan pa yi ge'i sgra bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:2299: sems kyi tha snyad grags pa brgya dang brgyad cu
NK088(su)001:2300: po dag kyang sems kyi ngo bo dang dpe brjod
NK088(su)001:2301: pa thun mong du mjal bar bya'o //
NK088(su)001:2302: de dag gi ngo bo so sor re zhig bstan pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:2303: de bzhin du spro ba'i sems kyi de kho na nyid dang /
NK088(su)001:2304: 'byed pa'i sems kyi de kho na nyid dang /
NK088(su)001:2305: zhes pa la sogs pa gang gcig la'ang mang por 'byeed pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2307: gang gcig la gcig 'khrug pa'i sems dang /
NK088(su)001:2308: gang rgyud 'jam pas pha rol la lhan pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2310: gzhan dang mthun pa'i sems dang /
NK088(su)001:2311: rtsod cing 'thab pa la dga' ba dang /
NK088(su)001:2312: mnyam pas mtshungs par lta ste 'jar ba dang /
NK088(su)001:2313: tshig tu brjod shes pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2314: brjod mi shes pa'i sems dang /
NK088(su)001:2315: bdag nyid la bzang bar rlom sems byed pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2316: longs spyod 'ba' zhig gi phyir sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2317: pha rol gyi bar du gcod par dga' ba dang /
NK088(su)001:2318: gang du shor la dog cing smod pas phrag dog pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2319: gzhan dag la gnod par sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2320: gang cir yang las kyi don du sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2321: shin tu gdug pa'i sems dang /
NK088(su)001:2322: gzhan la gnod 'gal btsal bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2323: phyogs 'dzin pas gzhan bsten pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2324: gang chags pas gnod pa'i sems dang /
NK088(su)001:2325: bdag dang mi 'dra ba'i sems dang /
NK088(su)001:2326: bdag btsan zhing bzang bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2327: gang 'dod pa 'khrig pa'i phyir chos bsten pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2328: gzhan las rigs kyi dman par sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2329: bdag yod pa'i dbang gis ngar 'dzin pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2330: gang bdag las phyi rol na snang bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2331: gang bsrel zhing phan par sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2332: gang sems can la byams shing gso bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2333: pha mas phan par bya bar sems shing lan glan par dga' ba dang /
NK088(su)001:2334: gcig la gcig bstun te srid btsa' bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2335: ngan pa'i lan pha rol la glan par sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2336: thams cad bdag gir bya'o sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2337: thams cad bdag gis bskyed do bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2338: thams cad kyi khong du 'gro bar dga' ba dang /
NK088(su)001:2339: thams cad bdag gis gtang ngo bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2340: ril bdag gis bsdus so bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2341: yul kun tu 'gro bar sems pas bsam pa ma nges pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2342: gang bsdus pa spel ba'i phyir kun tu bgrod par sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2343: gang thob pa du ma tshol ba'i phyir skyed do bas las sten pa'i sems dang /
NK088(su)001:2344: gang mtha' gnyis la ltas shing rten pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2345: gang sred pa chung ngur sten pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2346: gang gdon mi za bar zab po bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2347: gang rang gi ched du mi sems par kun la phan gdags par sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2348: gang yang nas yang du gcig kho nar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2349: gang sems pa de las sbyar bskyang zhing khyad par sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2350: gang sems pa de dang de nyid du gdung bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2351: gang sems pa der pha rol gyi sems bsgyur bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2352: gang 'di nyid la 'tshe bas mi tshugs par bya'o zhes sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2353: gang lhag par chags pas gzhan la mi ster ba dang /
NK088(su)001:2354: kun tshim par dga' bas ma chags te khyab pa bya bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2355: rang gi rtsal la ltos pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2356: gang bcing ba thams cad gcad par sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2357: gang chung ngu na bag tsam byin pas kyang mgu zhing chung ngus khro ba dang /
NK088(su)001:2358: gang kun dga' zhing sten pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2359: gang dran pa sna tshogs ma nges pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2360: gang mthun pas tshims par bya bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2361: gang bdag la sems shing bdag la dmigs pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2362: gang sgra'i phyir sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2363: de dag gi de kho na nyid ni chos can
NK088(su)001:2364: gyi sgo nas ma 'dres la ngo bos ji bzhin
NK088(su)001:2365: pa nyid du gcig pa'i phyir gcig du ma las
NK088(su)001:2366: kyang grol bar de nyid kyis gsal lo //
NK088(su)001:2367: de lta bas na 'chad pa rnams kyang de kho na nyid rjes su sbyar ro //
NK088(su)001:2368: lce 'bebs pa lta bu'i sems dang /
NK088(su)001:2371: dus kyi 'brug lta bu'i sems dang /
NK088(su)001:2372: zhes pa la sogs pa gang gzhan thogs pa med par gzhom par sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2373: yud tsam du gzhan gsal bar bya bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2374: gang mi rtag pas bsgribs par sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2375: gang spro ba bskyed par sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2376: thams cad zil gyis gnon par sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2377: gang bdag gir bya bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2378: gang chung bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2379: gang zin pa mi gtang bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2380: gang du gnas pas brtan par sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2381: gang cir yang snang bar bya bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2382: gang mi g.yo bar sems pas khengs pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2383: gang yul la bye brag tu sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2384: gang pha rol la gcam par sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2385: thams cad la skrag pas rang bag zon bya bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2386: gang bgrod par myur bar phyin par bya bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2387: gang bcud 'byung bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2388: gang skrag par bya ba sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2389: gzhan bza' bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2390: gang la 'dzem dogs pa pas 'jigs par sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2391: gang stobs dang ldan par sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2393: gang gze bas bzung ba'i sems dang /
NK088(su)001:2394: bdag 'ba' zhig gi ched du bya bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2395: bdag gis ched du mi sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2396: btson ra las brgal bas bde ba'i sems dang /
NK088(su)001:2397: btson ra las ma thar bas sdug bsngal bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2398: gang chags sdang gis bsad cing bza' bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2400: gzhan la mdzes pas 'dod pa sten pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2401: thams cad dbang bya bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2402: gang chags pas 'dod pa btsal bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2403: gang ma nges par sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2404: gang gtsang bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2405: gang bsad pas 'tsho bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2406: gang yid gdung bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2407: gang nyam thag pa'i sems dang /
NK088(su)001:2408: gang thams cad la gzugs par sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2409: thams cad du ya nga ba'i sems dang /
NK088(su)001:2410: thams cad du dman par sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2411: gang nyam nga ba med par sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2412: gang 'dus shing gsal bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2413: gang gtum par sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2414: gzhan bcing bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2415: thams cad ri li ga ri'i du bskyang bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2416: gzhan dag gzung bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2418: thams cad blang bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2419: gang bsags par sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2422: brlag par bya bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2423: thams cad du gsal bar bya bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2424: thams cad du khyab pas dro bar bya bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2425: thams cad du bsil bas gdung ba bsal bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2426: thams cad du mnyen par sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2429: thams cad du 'byung bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2430: thams cad brlan par sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2431: drang por bya bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2432: gzhib mor bya bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2433: gzhan bsdam zhing mthun par 'jug par sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2434: gzhan bskyab cing sems phyogs gnyis ka dang ldan par sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2435: gang gdung bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2436: thams cad brdegs shing bskrad par sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2437: bdag gi nyes pa gzhan la basku'o bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2438: pha rol gyi nyes pa 'dzin cing sems rtog skyed pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2439: sems gar 'jug pa'i yul la chags par bya ba nyid du ston par sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2440: log pa la ma log par sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2441: gnod pa ched du bya bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2442: phan pa nyi tshe bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2443: gang brtas par bya bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2444: rgya chung ngus rlan par sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2445: gang mi 'gyur bar gcig tu phigs par bya bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2446: gang gnyis ka gcad par sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2447: gang kun gyi bya ba de bskyar bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2448: gang gyong ba la phyogs gcig tu rgyud mnyen par sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2449: gang dag bsdam par sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2450: gang gyong zhing bsgyur dka' bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2451: gang gis gang zhig sems pa de la yang sems
NK088(su)001:2452: de thams cad nor du rung bar kun la phan
NK088(su)001:2453: par bya ba sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2454: gang bsam pa las yul gzhan du mi 'jug par bzhar ba sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2455: gang dran zhing mi 'gyur bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2456: gang mi 'gyur bar gzhom par sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2457: gang brtan par sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2458: gang mi g.yo bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2459: gang yang mi bya bar 'dug pa'i sems dang /
NK088(su)001:2460: gang rang skyong ba'i sems dang /
NK088(su)001:2461: gang sngar sems pa de la phyis de la gtad par sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2462: gcig tu mi gnas par 'du byed dang 'grogs te 'gro ba dang /
NK088(su)001:2463: gang gi sems dang ba bskyed pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2464: gang don yod pas mthar thug par sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2465: gang sems mang po gcig tu chud par sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2466: gcig las mang por sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2467: yan lag kun gcig tu bsrung bar sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2468: gang zhim pas mi gnod par sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2469: gang mi mthun par sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2471: yang nas yang du sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2472: gang yang mi sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2473: gang gzhan gyis ma bslad par sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2474: don mi 'gyur ba de gzhan gyis mi 'grub /
NK088(su)001:2475: yi ge ni mi 'gyur te a'i don a nyid
NK088(su)001:2476: las gzhan gyis mtshon du mi btub pa bzhin no
NK088(su)001:2478: zhes pa dag cir yang 'phro ba dang /
NK088(su)001:2479: bya ba kun sgo dbye bar 'byed pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2480: nus pa chung bas mi 'jug pa'i sems dang /
NK088(su)001:2481: kun spro ba bskyed pas kun sdud pa'i sems dang /
NK088(su)001:2482: gang yang mi phyed par byed pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2483: gong go gsal bar byed pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2484: gang khyab pas phan gdags par sems pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2485: gang gcig gi mthun pa gnyis la mthun te tsha grang gnyis ka dang mthun pa bzhin /
NK088(su)001:2486: gang gzhan zhig mi mthun pa'i gzhi gang du'ang mthun pa bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:2487: dngos po gzhan bsdu ba ni dngos po sna tshogs
NK088(su)001:2488: kyi sems te g.yo 'gul dngos po ma 'dres pa
NK088(su)001:2489: thams cad ril bu'i sems so //
NK088(su)001:2490: de rnams kyi de bzhin nyid ye ma bcos ma
NK088(su)001:2491: bslad pa kho na rdo rje sems dpa' nyid yin
NK088(su)001:2492: te tha dad pa gzhi nas med do //
NK088(su)001:2497: rdo rje sems dpa'i de kho na ye ji bzhin
NK088(su)001:2498: pa'i ngo bo ni byed pa po med pa'i phyir
NK088(su)001:2499: dang / ye nyid gsal ba chen po sel med pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:2500: rgyu rkyen la rag ma lus shing mkhan po med pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2501: bla dwags bral ba'i chos bzhi dang ldan pa de
NK088(su)001:2502: ltar 'gro ba'i sems kyi chos nyid kyang de bzhin
NK088(su)001:2503: pa'i phyir ro // de gnyis so sor ni dus
NK088(su)001:2504: gsum du'ang thams cad mkhyen pa dang rgyal tshab skyes
NK088(su)001:2505: bu rigs lnga la sogs pa'i so sor rtogs pa'i
NK088(su)001:2506: shes rab kyis ma gzigs mi phyed de /
NK088(su)001:2507: gzhan dang gzhan pa btsal gyis mi rnyed pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:2509: gsang sngags kyi nges pa rnyed par 'dod pa rnams kyis sems kyi de kho na nyid /
NK088(su)001:2510: ces pa dag nges don dam pa de rtogs par gdams pa'o //
NK088(su)001:2513: sems tha dad par snang ba rnams /
NK088(su)001:2514: zhes pa gtan tshigs ji lta bu zhe na /
NK088(su)001:2515: rnal 'byor gnyis po 'di ni bya ba byed pa'i rnal 'byor gyi khyad par te /
NK088(su)001:2516: bshad pa'i gzhi dang 'bras bu la thal bar mi 'gyur ro //
NK088(su)001:2517: gang gzhan don du rtsol ba ched du byed pa
NK088(su)001:2518: ni dbu ma man chad bden pa so so'i rnam
NK088(su)001:2519: pas tha dad du mthong yang /
NK088(su)001:2520: gsang sngags 'dir 'bras bu nyid du shes pas bya
NK088(su)001:2521: ba med pa'i rnal 'byor mchog a ti yo ga'i
NK088(su)001:2522: gzhung ltar gnyis med kyi don chen por shar te
NK088(su)001:2523: / de'i ngo bo ni gsang sngags ji lta ba
NK088(su)001:2524: ma bslad pa nyid yin pa'i gtan tshigs des na
NK088(su)001:2525: rdo rje sems dpa' nyid kyang don 'di rtogs pas
NK088(su)001:2526: sangs rgyas te mthar thug gi lam dam pa brnyes
NK088(su)001:2527: / so // de ji ltar zhe na /
NK088(su)001:2528: sems kyi de kho na nyid ni rnam par dag pa'i sgo yin no //
NK088(su)001:2529: chos snang ba'i sgo yin no //
NK088(su)001:2530: zhes pa la sogs pa'i log lta ka nas bral ba'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:2531: bstan pa ril 'di'i byin rlabs las snang ba'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:2532: mu mtha' bral ba'i ngo bo 'bras bu'i bdag nyid pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2533: sde snod rgyud dag gal po rdzogs pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:2534: dus gsum yeng bral med pa'i phyir na ston pa nyid kyang 'dis mthar son pa brnyes pa'o //
NK088(su)001:2535: rtogs pa'i yon tan dang ltas bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:2538: gang gi sems kyi de kho na //
NK088(su)001:2539: zhes pa la sogs pa lam pa su zhig gis
NK088(su)001:2540: gsang sngags ye ji bzhin pa mthong thabs kyis nges
NK088(su)001:2541: pa rnyed na / ril der gsal ba'i phyir brjod
NK088(su)001:2542: pa ril don ma nor ba nyi tshe bas sgra
NK088(su)001:2543: tshad sogs tshig thos pa'i rgyu la 'phral du ma
NK088(su)001:2544: ma bstan ltos kyang tshig theg pa kun la mkhas
NK088(su)001:2545: don bden pa ji snyed pa 'byung gzhan don zhing
NK088(su)001:2547: ji bzhin pa'i gtan tshigs zab mo pha rol skal
NK088(su)001:2548: ldan la ston nus na thob pa'i ltas de la
NK088(su)001:2549: yeng bral dang yal bar 'dug pa don ston la
NK088(su)001:2550: sogs med do // kye lang ka'i bdag po de ltar na /
NK088(su)001:2551: sems kyi de kho na nyid ni /
NK088(su)001:2553: brgya brgyad cu rnams ston pa rdo rje sems rtogs
NK088(su)001:2554: pa'i klung chen ma yengs dpa' dang blan med pa'i
NK088(su)001:2555: chos sku chen por gcig par bstan to //
NK088(su)001:2556: de sangs rgyas kun gyi bdud rtsir gyur pa ni /
NK088(su)001:2557: zhes pa dag ni don byang chub sems kyi chu
NK088(su)001:2558: med na 'di ma rtogs na lam gzhan gyis 'tshang
NK088(su)001:2559: mi rgya bas lhun gyis grub pa ni rtsol ba'i
NK088(su)001:2560: nad gso ba'i sman dang khrus chen po'o //
NK088(su)001:2561: byang chub sems kyi chu bo 'dis //
NK088(su)001:2563: bya ba med pa mdzad pa'i mtshan nyid kyi ngo bo nye bar bstan pa ste /
NK088(su)001:2564: des gang zhig bkrus nas thog ma med pa nas
NK088(su)001:2565: las kyis brtags pa'i rtog pa gnyis dang lam dang
NK088(su)001:2566: 'bras bu gzhan du tshol bas don gyi sel med
NK088(su)001:2568: sems kyi rang bzhin stong nyid pas //
NK088(su)001:2569: de las byung ba thams cad stong //
NK088(su)001:2570: zhes pa dag rang rig pa ni mtha' thams cad
NK088(su)001:2571: dag pa'i phyir na rnam pa'i mchog thams cad dang
NK088(su)001:2572: ldan pa'i stong pa nyid yin pas na /
NK088(su)001:2573: mtshal dang khu ba ltar sems snang ba'i dngos po'i chos rnams kyang de nyid do //
NK088(su)001:2574: de bas na byang chub chen po'i mtshan nyid kyang
NK088(su)001:2575: stong pa chen po ril gyi rtsa ba bcud du
NK088(su)001:2576: gyur pa nyid nges par gzung ba'o //
NK088(su)001:2577: rang byung ye shes chu chen po //
NK088(su)001:2578: rmad byung rgya rtogs pa ting nge 'dzin ye shes
NK088(su)001:2579: spyod lam 'brel ba bar ma chad pa mtsho'i klong
NK088(su)001:2580: dkyil nas // zhes pa la sogs pa rag gang
NK088(su)001:2581: du'ang ma lus par kun gyi thog mar shar ba'i
NK088(su)001:2582: dkyil nas // ye shes ni / bshad pa bzhin
NK088(su)001:2583: pas ril rig pa'i rgya mtshor chud cing brlan pa'i
NK088(su)001:2584: dkyil nas // ye shes ni / phyir / log
NK088(su)001:2585: rtog dang ma 'dres pa'i phyir ye shes 'ba' zhig
NK088(su)001:2586: las phyi rol gyi chos ma spangs ma dmigs pa'i
NK088(su)001:2587: ngang las de ji lta bar rig pa la shar
NK088(su)001:2589: rigs kyi char gtogs pa yan chad kyi rtags su
NK088(su)001:2590: gnang ba'i rgyal ba ril gyi lta ba tshol bas
NK088(su)001:2591: gdung ba'i mtha' thams cad des dag par mdzad do
NK088(su)001:2592: // 'di ni gsang ba'i snying po ste //
NK088(su)001:2593: zhes pa dag gsang sngags kyi gzhi rtsa nyid ston
NK088(su)001:2594: pa rdo rje sems dpa'i ngo bo yin pas rgyal
NK088(su)001:2595: ba ma lus pa'i lam dang 'bras bu'i mchog tu
NK088(su)001:2597: de bas de'i phyir lang ka'i bdag po /
NK088(su)001:2598: sems kyi de kho na nyid ni /
NK088(su)001:2599: ces pa don chen po mthong bar bya ba ni
NK088(su)001:2600: mtha'i phug chen po yin pas don de rtogs par
NK088(su)001:2602: phyag na rdo rjes bka' stsal pas 'khor rnams kyis
NK088(su)001:2603: gsang sngags ji bzhin pa'i don rtogs par gyur to
NK088(su)001:2604: // rdo rje sems dpa'i de kho na nyid bstan pa'i le'u zhes pa ni 'grel zin te /
NK088(su)001:2605: rnal 'byor dang po'i don te lam pa'i bya ba med pa dag gi yul lo //
NK088(su)001:2606: le'u dgu pa bkrol ba'o ////de nas lang ka'i bdag pos /
NK088(su)001:2607: gsang ba'i bdag po la dris pa /
NK088(su)001:2608: zhes pa la sogs pa gsang sngags gang gi spyod yul dris pa ste /
NK088(su)001:2609: spyod yul bzhi las rang rig pa'i mngon sum gtsor byas pa'o //
NK088(su)001:2611: rgyal ba nyid kyi mngon sum pa'i yul yin gyi /
NK088(su)001:2612: gsang bar na'ang gang sems skyes pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2613: gzhi rten pas khyad par 'gro ba la gnas pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2614: rgyud nas pas kyang bgrod pa'i sa bcu pa'i sems
NK088(su)001:2615: dpa' chen po man chad kun gyi yul ma yin
NK088(su)001:2617: de'i gtan tshigs gsang sngags ji bzhin pa de rnam
NK088(su)001:2618: pa thams cad pa yin pa sa blos brtag par
NK088(su)001:2620: mtshan nyid ma nges pa sa gzhan la bstan dka' dang /
NK088(su)001:2621: brjod pa thams cad kyis tha snyad bral bas thog tu mi phebs pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:2624: brjod pa'i tha snyad dang yang bral ba'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:2625: yang lang ka'i bdag pos dris pa /
NK088(su)001:2627: sems kyi de kho na nyid /
NK088(su)001:2629: lang kas rgyal ba nyid kyi spyod yul las /
NK088(su)001:2630: gsang sngags de gzhan gyi spyod yul ma yin par
NK088(su)001:2631: na gang stsol ba ched du byed pa'i mdo bya
NK088(su)001:2632: ba'i rnal 'byor sde pa'ang sems kyi de kho na
NK088(su)001:2633: nyid le'u dgu pa'i don la dmigs shing dpyod de
NK088(su)001:2634: des so sor rtogs pa'i shes rab kyis sems btsal
NK088(su)001:2635: te bltas na sems phyi nang 'byung ba yul lus
NK088(su)001:2636: rnam shes bar gang la'ang 'di 'drar ma mthong ste
NK088(su)001:2637: / don dam par ma skyes pa'i ngo bo nyid yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:2639: rab 'byor 'das pa'i sems kyang dmigs su med /
NK088(su)001:2640: ma 'ongs pa'i sems kyang dmigs su med /
NK088(su)001:2641: da ltar byung ba'i sems kyang dmigs su med do //
NK088(su)001:2642: zhes pa'i phyir ma mthong ngo //
NK088(su)001:2643: sems 'di gang las 'byung zhes bltas na /
NK088(su)001:2645: gang dmigs pa yod pas na /
NK088(su)001:2646: zhes pa la sogs pa ngo bo ma mthong bas
NK088(su)001:2647: de'i rang bzhin mthong bar 'dod pa'i phyir bltas na
NK088(su)001:2648: / 'di bzhin yid la byed de dmigs pa'i yul
NK088(su)001:2649: yod pas rkyen bzhi 'dzom nas shes pa skye ba
NK088(su)001:2650: yang rgan po mkhar ba la brten pa ltar mnyam
NK088(su)001:2651: du ldang zhing skye bar mthong ngo //
NK088(su)001:2652: yul dang shes pa de gnyis gcig gam tha dad
NK088(su)001:2653: pa brtags pas yul nyid shes pa la shes pa
NK088(su)001:2655: gcig na ni mdzub mo'i rtse mo dang ral gri ltar rang la rang dmigs par mi rung ngo //
NK088(su)001:2656: gal te tha dad na chos ji bzhin par ma
NK088(su)001:2657: 'dus pas tha dad par 'gyur ba'i skyon yod do
NK088(su)001:2658: zhes brtags pa'i rgyus don dam pa'i rang bzhin mthong
NK088(su)001:2659: tshul nye bar bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:2666: don dam pa 'ba' zhig gi tha snyad bcu bdun las grol bar bstan te /
NK088(su)001:2667: mi 'gyur ba yongs su grub pa ma skyes pa de rgyu rkyen las ma bskyed pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2668: de la gzhi rten bral ba dang /
NK088(su)001:2669: rtsa ba med pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:2670: dran pa sna tshogs kyi sgyu ma'i snang ba'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:2671: ther zug pa dang gang zag gi bdag med pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:2673: de ma yin par rgya chad pa min pas gzhan na med pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:2674: dngos po de las gzhan las skyed pa ma yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:2675: rgyu rkyen gyi ngo bo de kho na lta ba yang ma yin pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2676: de la rnam pa'i rgyud 'dzin pa med pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:2677: rjes su long btags nas rjes su 'byung ba nges pa ma yin pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2678: mtha' gar yang mi snang ba'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:2679: ngo bo gang du'ang mi gzigs pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:2680: de gang yang min pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:2681: gzhi ma bcos ma bslad de ltar lam pa'i blos mthong ngo //
NK088(su)001:2682: chos 'byung ba med pa'i mdo las /
NK088(su)001:2683: 'jam dpal chos gang gi chos thams cad skye ba
NK088(su)001:2684: dang 'jig pa bral zhing shes pa dang mi shes
NK088(su)001:2685: pa dang bral te rang bzhin gyis stong par mthong
NK088(su)001:2686: na de ni shes rab kyi dbang pa'o zhes gsungs
NK088(su)001:2687: so // yang dag pa mi g.yo ba dang /
NK088(su)001:2690: zhes pa la sogs pa mnyam par bzhag pa'i sems la gnas pa'i dus na'ang /
NK088(su)001:2691: tha snyad bcu gnyis grol bar bstan te /
NK088(su)001:2692: ji lta ba de kho na nyid stong pa de ni /
NK088(su)001:2693: mi bslu ba ma nor ba'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:2694: ril ma skyes pa 'ba' zhig pa'i phyir ci'ang mi 'byung ba dang /
NK088(su)001:2695: spros pa brgyad dang gsum las ring du gyur pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2696: rang gi ngo bo mi rnyed pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2697: phyogs char mi zin pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2698: ci'ang mi dmigs shing de nyid du'ang mi 'dzin pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:2699: ri dang 'dra bar log chos kyis mi bsgul zhing gang yang yid la mi byed pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2700: ngo bo tha dad du mi 'byung ba'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:2701: shes pa dbyibs kha dog gi rnam pa med pas
NK088(su)001:2702: de snang ba'i chos rnams stong pa dang yul sems
NK088(su)001:2703: kyi rnam pa gnyis ka yang stong pa ma skyes
NK088(su)001:2704: pa ste / de lta bas na chos kyi sku
NK088(su)001:2705: yang ma skyes pa de kho na nyid de gzugs
NK088(su)001:2706: pa ste / med do // de bas na rdo rje gcod pa las /
NK088(su)001:2707: gang gis nga la gzugs su mthong //
NK088(su)001:2708: gang gis nga la sgrar shes pa //
NK088(su)001:2709: log par spros la zhugs pa ste //
NK088(su)001:2710: skye bo de yis nga mi mthong //
NK088(su)001:2711: 'dren pa rnams ni chos kyi sku //
NK088(su)001:2712: chos nyid du ni sangs rgyas blta //
NK088(su)001:2714: de gzhan ma yin rang gi sems nyid do //
NK088(su)001:2715: sems dang chos ni thams cad mi phyed pas ma skyes pa de kho na nyid du rtogs so //
NK088(su)001:2719: zhes pa la sogs pa sems kyi mtshan nyid nyer
NK088(su)001:2720: lnga las grol ba las gzhan ma yin par yang
NK088(su)001:2721: mthong ste / sems de ltar rtogs pa nyid kyang
NK088(su)001:2722: skad cig la thogs pa med par 'byung ba glog
NK088(su)001:2723: mthong ste / dang 'dra ba / ches shin tu yang thogs pa med pa /
NK088(su)001:2724: mtshan nyid gcig tu mi dmigs pa yul la sna tshogs su 'gro ba'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:2725: sgo kun tu 'byung ba'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:2726: 'du byed lnga bcus g.yengs pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:2727: kun tu 'gro bar snang ba'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:2728: snga phyi rgyun mi chad cing ngos 'byar ba'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:2729: rgyu rkyen las byung zhing gsal ba'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:2730: gdos pa ma zin pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2731: rgyang ring por rgyu ba dang /
NK088(su)001:2732: rang bzhin 'byung 'jug bral ba'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:2733: brtags pa'i dngos po yul las slar 'ongs pa dang /
NK088(su)001:2734: sgra don spyi'i yul dang mi phyed pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:2735: tshogs drug gi yul du snang ba ril gsal bar rig pa /
NK088(su)001:2736: zhi bar gnas pas mi 'phro ba'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:2737: ngo bo gang du'ang mi snang ba rtogs ma rtogs
NK088(su)001:2738: las cir yang snang ba rang bzhin ji bzhin pa'i
NK088(su)001:2739: phyir dang / las kyi khyad par gyi ngo bo mi gcig pa /
NK088(su)001:2740: shes shing rig pa'i rigs su 'dus pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:2741: rang bzhin 'du byed dang bral ba /
NK088(su)001:2742: thun mong dang thun mong ma yin pa'i 'khor dang mtshungs pas 'du byed pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:2743: snga phyi dang da ltar du'ang rang bzhin ma skyes te /
NK088(su)001:2744: rnam pa med pa snying po med pas bzang ngan bral ba /
NK088(su)001:2745: rang rig pa nyid chos nyid skye ba med pa'i
NK088(su)001:2746: ngo bo ma nor ba mi 'gyur ba'i rang bzhin
NK088(su)001:2747: du rtogs rig mthong ba sems la dbang thob pa
NK088(su)001:2748: de ltar 'gro ba gzhan gyi sems kyang shes so
NK088(su)001:2750: bdag gi sems ji ltar stong ba de ltar /
NK088(su)001:2751: zhes pa dag sgra bzhin te /
NK088(su)001:2752: ngo bos tha mi dad pa'i phyir bdag rtogs pas gzhan shes su rung ba'o //
NK088(su)001:2753: bdag gzhan shes bya chos thams cad kyang de ltar shes te /
NK088(su)001:2754: gcig dang du ma las grol ba'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:2755: de lta bu ma skyes pa chos kyi dbyings de
NK088(su)001:2756: ni gang dman pa gang gi yul ma yin par
NK088(su)001:2757: rtogs so // zhes sems la gnas pa /
NK088(su)001:2760: zhes pa la sogs pa sems ma skyes pa'i ting nge 'dzin la 'dug pa /
NK088(su)001:2763: de la shes rab kyis dmigs pa /
NK088(su)001:2764: rang bzhin rtogs pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:2765: sems kyi don brda mjal ba yin na de dag
NK088(su)001:2766: gis ma rtogs par rgyal ba nyid kho na'i spyod
