NK088(su)001:4094: dang / thams cad gnas pa'i rten gyi phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:4095: thams cad bskyed pas yum nyid do //
NK088(su)001:4096: de las byung bas yab nyid do //
NK088(su)001:4097: gdung rgyud 'dzin pas srang nyid do //
NK088(su)001:4098: zhes pa la sogs pa ji bzhin pa'i de kho
NK088(su)001:4099: na nyid las 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das
NK088(su)001:4100: pa'i chos thams cad shar bas ma yin no //
NK088(su)001:4101: gzhi de las snang ba'i phyir pha yin no //
NK088(su)001:4102: rgyal ba'i gdung rgyud yin pas sras so //
NK088(su)001:4103: gzhan la rag ma las par ye byung ba'i phyir dbang ril yi sdong po'o //
NK088(su)001:4104: dus gsum du mi 'gyur ma chad pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:4105: dal por mchongs kyang khang thog ste mgyogs pas bros
NK088(su)001:4106: kyang de las gzhan du mi phyin pa'i phyir ro
NK088(su)001:4107: // rgyal ba dang lam la gnas pa ril zhe'am /
NK088(su)001:4108: dngos po la des bzung ba'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:4109: rgyal ba'i yon tan dang 'khor ba'i longs spyod ril zad pa med par shar ba'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:4110: ril gyi re bskongs ba'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:4111: dus gsum du thugs rjes don mdzad pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:4112: de kho na nyid ril gyi rten gzhi mi 'gyur ba'i lhun du zhugs pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:4113: brjod med barjooda pa kun 'byung ba'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:4114: ril ma 'dres rdzogs pa ngang gsal ba la mi rtogs pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:4115: dngos grub dang 'bras bu'i gzhir gyur pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:4116: thams cad mdzad pa chen pos don rgyun chad med par mdzad pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:4117: yul ril la son pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:4118: longs spyod gnyis la yul dang bral bar rol pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:4119: ril gyi rgyu spyad bya nyid du snang ba'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:4120: 'dod pa'i rkyen ril rdzogs pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:4121: bya ba ma spang bya ba med de snying po nyid kyi phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:4122: dngos po cir yang shar ba'i mtshan nyid ma nges pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:4123: sku phyag rgya la sogs par rkyen la rag ma lus par shar ba'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:4124: go 'phang logs nas mi gnyer bas gzhi'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:4125: de las thob bya rang rig pa nyid yin pa'i don gzhan nas ma byung ba'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:4126: 'bras bu nyid lam yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:4127: grub mtha' chen por rang nyid ye grub zin pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:4128: de lta bas na gzhi lam mtha' ril du snying
NK088(su)001:4129: po byang chub 'gro 'ong med par snang ba la
NK088(su)001:4131: zhes pa dag dris lan sgra bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:4133: zhes pa dag /ye grub zin pa'i gtan tshigs bzhi ste bshad pa'i khong gis khrol lo //
NK088(su)001:4134: zhes de lta de ltar stong pa nyid las /
NK088(su)001:4135: zhes pa dag snying po byang chub stong pa chen po'i byin rlabs so //
NK088(su)001:4136: de kho na nyid de kho na nyid du nges par /
NK088(su)001:4137: zhes pa dag don gyi snying po'ang ngo bo las gzhan pa med par bstan pa'o //
NK088(su)001:4139: de ltar skyes bu dam pas /
NK088(su)001:4140: zhes pa dag chos nyid kyi don ye shes la rang gsal ba /
NK088(su)001:4141: dpe nam mkha' dang nyi ma lta bur ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs par bstan to //
NK088(su)001:4142: de'i tshe de'i dus na gsang sngags 'byung ba'i rgyu /
NK088(su)001:4143: zhes pa dag snying po byang chub la snyegs pa ni nges pa rnyed pa ste /
NK088(su)001:4144: thub dka' gzhon nu dang skyes bu lnga dag ji bzhin par son pa'i dus te /
NK088(su)001:4145: dngos su na ru dra snang ba'i bskal pa'i dus nyid de /
NK088(su)001:4146: snying po byang chub ni dus gsum ma 'gags bral ba la /
NK088(su)001:4147: tshe skabs med gdul bya'i ngo btsan no //
NK088(su)001:4148: gdul bya sngon gyi gleng gzhi smos pa'ang 'di'i phyir te /
NK088(su)001:4149: 'di byung bas 'di byung ba'i phyir gnyen po ste sgra ji bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:4150: snying po byang chub tu 'dus pa ni gdul bya'i ngo ste /
NK088(su)001:4151: ngo bo nyid der ma 'dres rdzogs pa'o //
NK088(su)001:4152: gdul bya'i ngor 'og min na bzhugs pa de dag gis /
NK088(su)001:4153: skyes bu dam pa dag /la la ni byang chub chen por rnam par bskul /
NK088(su)001:4154: la la ni cho 'phrul chen por rnam par bskul /
NK088(su)001:4155: zhes pa la sogs pa ru dra 'dul ba'i phyir
NK088(su)001:4156: thub dka' gzhon nu byang chub snying po na bzhugs
NK088(su)001:4157: pa sku lnga'i sgo nas bskul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:4158: skyes bu tha dad la so so nas bskul ba
NK088(su)001:4159: ni spyi dang khyad par gyi dbang ste gnyis ka
NK088(su)001:4161: bla na med pa'i byang chub mchog ngo bo nyid
NK088(su)001:4162: kyi skur 'tshang rgya ba las bzhengs par bskul ba
NK088(su)001:4163: dang / bkar ba ni skyes bu dang bskul byed thun mong du sbyar ro //
NK088(su)001:4164: yang gsang ba'i sku rol pa nyi shu rtsa lnga
NK088(su)001:4165: lta bu la sogs pa'i cho 'phrul mdzod cig par
NK088(su)001:4166: bskul ba dang / sprul pa'i sku rdzu 'phul gyi
NK088(su)001:4167: bya ba rdzogs par gyis shig par bskul ba dang
NK088(su)001:4168: bskul ba dang / / longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku'i
NK088(su)001:4169: sgo nas dgongs pa dang sku'i mdzad pas don mdzod
NK088(su)001:4170: bskul ba dang / / cig pa dang / chos
NK088(su)001:4171: kyi sku mtha' dang bral ba'i ye shes chen po'i
NK088(su)001:4172: sgo nas bskul bas gdul bya la snang ba ni
NK088(su)001:4173: bskul ba dang / / cig pa dang / /
NK088(su)001:4174: gzugs sku gnyis su byung nas gdul bya so so'i
NK088(su)001:4175: gnas su bkod de chos ston pas byung tshul gyi
NK088(su)001:4177: de dag gi don mdzad lugs ci zhe na /
NK088(su)001:4179: btags pa'i sangs rgyas brjod pa las 'das pa /
NK088(su)001:4180: tha dad pa dag /zhes pa la sogs pa ngo
NK088(su)001:4181: bo nyid chos kyi skur bzhugs pas gdul bya med
NK088(su)001:4182: na yang / lhun gyis grub pa de nyid gdul
NK088(su)001:4183: bya la mtshan tha dad par grags shing sku snang
NK088(su)001:4184: ba ril rgyal ba'i zhing bshad pa bzhin mtshan tha
NK088(su)001:4185: dad kyi 'jig rten gyi 'dzam bu gling rnams na
NK088(su)001:4186: na yang / / rgyal ba'i cha byad kyis theg pa de nyid kyi don bcu ston pa dang /
NK088(su)001:4187: sum cu rtsa gsum dang dga' ldan dang gtsang ma'i 'og min na longs spyod rdzogs pa dang /
NK088(su)001:4188: sprul pa'i rgyal tshab dam pa tog dkar po /
NK088(su)001:4189: brgya byin gsum chos so sor ston pa'o //
NK088(su)001:4190: srid pa tha mar mi yul la sogs pa la
NK088(su)001:4191: las rgyun gcod pa'i mdzad pa lngar snang ba dang
NK088(su)001:4192: / gsang ba'i sku yum gyi b+ha ga dang gsang
NK088(su)001:4193: ba'i rdo rje gnyis 'phrad pa'i dbu zhabs bde ba
NK088(su)001:4195: yan man du dbang bsgyur nas snang ba'i gnas tha dad pa na /
NK088(su)001:4196: gsang ba'i sku thig le gnyis su med pa'i bde
NK088(su)001:4197: ba chen po 'dus pa'i sku las mdzad pa cir
NK088(su)001:4199: mi'i gnas zhing tha dad pa na /
NK088(su)001:4200: sprul pa'i mtshan sgron ma bkod pa lta bus don mdzad pa dang /
NK088(su)001:4201: don thams cad grub pa lta bu'i thugs 'og min
NK088(su)001:4202: du sangs rgyas pas dgongs pa byang chub chen por
NK088(su)001:4203: bzhugs pa dang / de'i sku tha dad pa'i 'dzam
NK088(su)001:4204: bu'i gling na nee rany+dza nar dka' thub khog par
NK088(su)001:4205: bzhugs nas bsam gtan mdzad pa lta bu dang /
NK088(su)001:4207: bcu gnyis rdzogs pa lta bu dang /
NK088(su)001:4208: so so'i rdo rje gdan la gshegs te 'tshang rgya ba dang /
NK088(su)001:4209: r+ts+wa mchog grong khyer dang wa r+aa na s+air bdud btul chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba dang /
NK088(su)001:4210: gdan nyid la sangs rgyas pa lta bu 'ba' zhig tu snang ngo zhes bka' stsal pas /
NK088(su)001:4211: lang ka la sogs pa 'gro ba'i lus can gyi 'khor snying po byang chub mngon du gyur te /
NK088(su)001:4212: de nges pa'i byin rlabs las gsang ba snang bar shes so //
NK088(su)001:4213: gsang ba dam pa de kho na nyid du nges pa'i le'u /
NK088(su)001:4214: zhes pa lnga dang bzhi dang /
NK088(su)001:4216: skyes bu bcu la sogs pa de bzhin nyid du ngo bo nges pa'i don bstan pa ste /
NK088(su)001:4217: le'u bco lnga pa bkrol ba'o //
NK088(su)001:4218: byung tshul bzhi pa'i don khong gis khrol to ////bam mo gsum par zug pa /
NK088(su)001:4219: de nas lang ka'i bdag pos /
NK088(su)001:4221: zhes pa la sogs pa byung tshul lnga pa'i dris pa sgra bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:4222: dgongs pa 'grel pa de'i dus nges pa ni byung tshul bzhi pa dang gcig go //
NK088(su)001:4223: ngo bo ni so sor ma 'dres pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:4226: gang skyes bu dam pa nyid du nges pa de
NK088(su)001:4227: dag /ces pa la sogs pa lang kas ngo bos
NK088(su)001:4228: gang gi tshig mtshan ci las btags pa dris pa
NK088(su)001:4231: snying po ni rtsa ba la bya'o //
NK088(su)001:4233: dang po snying po dngos po gnyis kyi gzhir gyur pa'o //
NK088(su)001:4234: gnyis byang chub pa ni gnyis med ji bzhin pa'o //
NK088(su)001:4235: gsum pa dgongs pa ni rang gi rig pa'i ngo bo ngang gis ma g.yos pa'o //
NK088(su)001:4236: bzhi pa nges pa ni 'khrul pa med pa'i thog tu phebs pa'o //
NK088(su)001:4237: lnga pa 'grel pa ni ji lta bar mngon du byas pa'i don rang gsal ba'o //
NK088(su)001:4238: de ni ji bzhin ma bcos de bzhin ma bslad pa'i glo bur gyi tha snyad do //
NK088(su)001:4241: des de ji ltar 'grel pa lags /
NK088(su)001:4242: zhes pa la sogs pa dris lan sgra bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:4243: yang de nyid la dris pa dang /
NK088(su)001:4247: zhes pa la sogs pa ngo bo bstan pa ni gnyis te /
NK088(su)001:4250: de la'ang lam gyi dang mthar thug pa 'dir thun mong du sbyar ro //
NK088(su)001:4251: slob dpon bde ba gsal mdzad kyis ni /
NK088(su)001:4252: cho 'phrul rtsa ba bzhi'i bzhi dang /
NK088(su)001:4253: ngo bo dang snang ba gnyis la sbyar na mi 'thad pa ma yin no //
NK088(su)001:4254: gang gzhi skyes bu lnga'i dgongs pa rtsa las 'grel
NK088(su)001:4255: pa'i ngo bo snang ba'i phyir skye ba ste ngo
NK088(su)001:4256: bo bzhir shar ba ma 'dres pa'i 'grel pa ste
NK088(su)001:4257: / de ni rgyal ba rnams kyi mdzad pa ci'ang dgongs pa can pas /
NK088(su)001:4258: 'dir 'khor 'das dngos po gnyis pa ril snang ba cho 'phrul bzhir 'dus la /
NK088(su)001:4259: de nyid snying po byang chub la ma 'dres pa
NK088(su)001:4260: la yongs su rdzogs par gsal ba'i phyir de bstan
NK088(su)001:4261: pa'o // las kyi rdzu 'phrul las skye ba'i cho 'phrul dang /
NK088(su)001:4262: zhes pa gang las gsum gyi bya ba byed nus pa ni /
NK088(su)001:4263: khams gsum gyi 'gro ba tha dad cir yang snang bas dngos po gnyis ma 'dres pa'o //
NK088(su)001:4264: de dngos skye ba ni mi dang grog sbur dang
NK088(su)001:4265: 'dab chags dang bar ma do dang dmyal ba la
NK088(su)001:4266: sogs pa ste / bzhi'i cha 'dzin smos pa ste
NK088(su)001:4267: dngos po gnyis kyi khams gsum pa thams cad do
NK088(su)001:4268: de ni cho 'phrul bzhi'i yang tha ma nyid do
NK088(su)001:4269: sogs pa ste / // bsam gtan gyi rdzu 'phrul las skye ba'i cho 'phrul gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:4270: zhes pa gang yang dag pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK088(su)001:4271: nus pa'i rtsal cir yang 'byung ba'i rgyu las lam
NK088(su)001:4273: gzhan du na snang ba ma nges pa bzhi ni /
NK088(su)001:4274: brtags pas shes rab skye ba dang /
NK088(su)001:4275: btsal bas goms pa skye ba dang /
NK088(su)001:4276: bsgrub pas 'bras bu skye ba dang /
NK088(su)001:4277: bsgom pas drod dang rtags rnams skye ba'o //
NK088(su)001:4278: chos nyid kyi rdzu 'phrul las skyes pa'i cho 'phrul gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:4279: zhes pa dag gang ji bzhin pa thams cad kyi bdag nyid pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:4280: de nyid cir yang snang du btub pa'i gzhi las gzhi nges pa tha dad par snang ba ni /
NK088(su)001:4281: rang zhin gyi cho 'phrul bzhi ste /
NK088(su)001:4282: nam mkha'i ngang las 'byung ba'i cho 'phrul tha dad snang ba dang /
NK088(su)001:4283: sems kyi ngang las sems las byung ba'i cho 'phrul skye ba dang /
NK088(su)001:4284: chos nyid kyi ngang las chos can gyi cho 'phrul skye ba dang /
NK088(su)001:4285: zhi gnas ji bzhin pa'i ngang las lhag mthong shes rab rang 'char ba'o //
NK088(su)001:4286: snying rje'i rdzu 'phrul las skye ba'i cho 'phrul gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:4287: zhes pa gang rang byung gi ye shes thugs rje
NK088(su)001:4288: chen po'i thabs kyis mdzad pa lhun gyis grub pa'i
NK088(su)001:4289: gzhi las gdul bya la cir yang 'dul ba bzhin
NK088(su)001:4290: snang ba bzhi ni sgra bzhin te /
NK088(su)001:4291: de re re'ang rtag pa rgyun gyis skye ba dang /
NK088(su)001:4292: rang bzhin shugs kyis skye ba dang /
NK088(su)001:4293: bskul zhing gsol bas skye ba dang /
NK088(su)001:4294: yul dang 'phrad pas skye ba ste skye ba'i dus dang ngo bo'i rgyur sbyar ro //
NK088(su)001:4295: 'di dag kun 'dus le'u gsum pa las gsungs pa 'dir le'u re res rgyas par ston pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:4296: bshad pa'i rgyud du yang khas len to //
NK088(su)001:4297: de dang rjes su mthun par 'chad pa dag la'ang sbyar ro //
NK088(su)001:4298: rgyas par bstan pa'i dang po gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:4300: de la rdzu 'phrul gyi cho 'phrul ni 'di lta ste /
NK088(su)001:4301: zhes pa la sogs pa ci bzhin pas 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:4302: gzhi de las gdul bya la mi mthun par snang ba'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:4304: gang snang bar mdzad pa'i cho 'phrul ni /
NK088(su)001:4305: zhes pa dag de la dang po la lngar snang ba ni /
NK088(su)001:4306: dngos po gang yang rung ba 'byung ba dag ni brda'i don du 'chad de /
NK088(su)001:4314: yan lag mtshon pa'i don dang /
NK088(su)001:4315: gnyis kyis 'dul ba dag gdul bya la dgongs pa dang /
NK088(su)001:4316: thabs tshul tha dad pas 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:4317: de nyid kyi las dang yon tan gyis 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:4318: yid tshims shing dga' bar byed pas 'dul ba la
NK088(su)001:4319: dgongs pa'i phyir ming gi gtan tshigs su 'gyur ro
NK088(su)001:4321: de la gang mtshon pas 'dul ba la dgongs pa'i cho 'phrul ni /
NK088(su)001:4322: zhes pa gnyis ni rang bzhin dang /
NK088(su)001:4323: gdul bya la snang ba'i rigs tha dad gang la'ang mos par 'dul ba'o //
NK088(su)001:4325: de la ma bcos pas 'dul ba la dgongs pa ni /
NK088(su)001:4327: bzhi ni lha gcig la'ang ldan te /
NK088(su)001:4328: ye rang bzhin mjal la dag pa'i phyir dri ma med pa dang /
NK088(su)001:4329: gzi mdangs dang ldan pa'i phyir snums la 'dril ba dang /
NK088(su)001:4330: kun la snang zhing rnyogs pa med pa'i ba'i rtags dwangs shing gsal la 'tsher ba dang /
NK088(su)001:4331: rang bzhin gyi 'od gsal ba'i rtags shin tu gsal zhing 'tsher ba nyid de dpe sgra bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:4332: ye nas lha kun la khyab pa'i phyir ma bcos pas 'dul ba'i ming grub bo //
NK088(su)001:4333: lang ka'i bdag po rigs so sor rang bsgyur bas 'dul ba la dgongs pa ni /
NK088(su)001:4335: zhes pa dag rigs gang la mos pa ltar snang ba'i phyir bsgyur ba te /
NK088(su)001:4340: ljang gu ste rin po che'i rigs dang /
NK088(su)001:4344: las kyi rigs te dpe sgra bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:4345: rigs lnga ye shes lnga kha dog lnga k+aa w+aa
NK088(su)001:4346: tsi lnga sbyar ba ni rgyud kun gsal lnga'i don
NK088(su)001:4347: dang po sku la yan lag dgu bshad pa'o //
NK088(su)001:4349: gang gis mtshon pas 'dul ba la dgongs pa ni /
NK088(su)001:4353: phyag rgya ste rang gi ngo bos ming grub bo //
NK088(su)001:4355: de la gang byung ba ni /
NK088(su)001:4356: zhes pa dag phyag gi don te /
NK088(su)001:4359: ye shes drug mtshon pa la dgongs te phyag gi grangs kyang de bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:4360: phyag mtshan ye shes drug gi rol pas 'gro ba
NK088(su)001:4361: sgrol ba'i phyir rdo rje la sogs pa drug yang
NK088(su)001:4368: dam tshig gi phyag rgya dang /
NK088(su)001:4369: chos dang las te gzhi ci bzhin pa ma g.yos par bzhugs pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:4370: gang don las mi 'da' ba dang /
NK088(su)001:4371: 'dul dbang gis tha dad du ston pa dang /
NK088(su)001:4372: bya ba gang 'brel pa yod pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:4374: ma bcos pa ni 'di lta ste /
NK088(su)001:4376: rgyu rkyen dang bral bas ma skyes pa chos kyi sku dang /
NK088(su)001:4377: de'i tshul mi 'gags pa gzugs kyi sku ste /
NK088(su)001:4378: gdul bya la snang ba'o sku phyag rgya chen po rnam pa ste /
NK088(su)001:4379: rang gi mtshan nyid kyis ming 'grub bo //
NK088(su)001:4380: de la ma 'gags pa gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:4382: zhes pa dag ni gzugs sku la phye ba bzhi ste /
NK088(su)001:4383: yul la ma 'gags pa ye shes rang bzhin /
NK088(su)001:4384: gzugs kyi sku 'og min na bzhugs pa nyid dang /
NK088(su)001:4385: mtshon pa ma 'gas pa mthar phyin gyi k+aa w+aa tsi gzugs brnyan du byung ba dang /
NK088(su)001:4386: mtshan ma ma 'gags pa gzugs brnyan gyi dal rnams dang ring bsrel gyi sku dang /
NK088(su)001:4387: sku gsung thugs brtags pa ma 'gag pa bsgom pa ting nge 'dzin gyi sku'o //
NK088(su)001:4389: yon tan rdzogs pa'i gzhir gyur pa dang /
NK088(su)001:4390: de rmongs pa la bstan pa'i phyir byas pa dang /
NK088(su)001:4391: grub pa'i rtags su gyur pa dang /
NK088(su)001:4392: rang gi bsam pas byas pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:4395: zhes pa dag dam tshig gi phyag rgya'i rnam grangs te /
NK088(su)001:4396: zin pa ni thugs kyi rtags te 'dzin pa dam tshig gi phyag rgya dang /
NK088(su)001:4397: thugs rje las mi 'da' ba 'gro don mdzad pa bca' ba dam tshig gi phyag rgya dang /
NK088(su)001:4398: rtse gcig tu bsam pa dam tshig gi dgongs pa phyag rgya'o //
NK088(su)001:4402: gang bsams pa las gzhan du mi 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:4404: ma nges pa gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:4405: zhes pa dag chos kyi phyag rgya ste 'gro ba'i
NK088(su)001:4406: bsam pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang mthun pa'i
NK088(su)001:4407: sgo bsam gyis mi khyab pa tha dad pa'i phyir
NK088(su)001:4408: bstan te / de la'ang rang bzhin dang /
NK088(su)001:4410: bzlas pa'i 'phro 'du las 'dir yi ge tha dad tha ma'i dbang du byas pa'o //
NK088(su)001:4414: zhes pa dag las kyi phyag rgya ste bca' ba
NK088(su)001:4415: las dang dam tshig thun chos thams cad zad med
NK088(su)001:4416: dbyings su 'brel pa ste bde ba chos kyi rgya
NK088(su)001:4417: dga' ba'i khyad par can no //
NK088(su)001:4419: chos bskyod par byed pa'i thabs khyad par can te
NK088(su)001:4420: thabs shes rab rgya bzhis rol pa'i phrin las chos
NK088(su)001:4421: rgya'o // dang las 'brel ba nyid du bstan pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:4422: gnyis pa phyag rgya nying lag bcu bzhir bstan pa'o //
NK088(su)001:4424: gang gi gyur pas 'dul ba la dgongs pa'i cho 'phrul gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:4425: zhes pa dag bzhugs thabs dang gzhal yas khang dang bzhugs tshul lo //
NK088(su)001:4426: lang ka'i bdag po thabs gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:4428: gral gyi thabs dang sku'i thabs gnyis te /
NK088(su)001:4429: 'dir sku'i thabs dgongs pa mnyam pa nyid las mi
NK088(su)001:4430: g.yo ba gzhi dang mthun pa'i phyir 'greng bu dang
NK088(su)001:4431: / khyad par gang dag bar snang bas skyil krung dang /
NK088(su)001:4436: zhes pa don gzung 'dzin dang bral ba'i ye shes yul dang yul can grol ba'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:4437: gdul bya la snang ba'i gnas sgra bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:4441: zhes pa so so'i gtan tshigs kyis /
NK088(su)001:4442: bla phab nas mi g.yo ba'i tshul dang /
NK088(su)001:4444: bzhud la ma rag pa dang /
NK088(su)001:4446: sku gyong ba dang bral ba lta bu dang /
NK088(su)001:4447: sku cir yang drang du rung ba lta bu dang /
NK088(su)001:4449: rked skabs phyed par phra ba lta bu dang /
NK088(su)001:4452: sku mdog rigs lnga ye shes lnga thabs shes rab /
NK088(su)001:4455: shin tu byin che ba dang /
NK088(su)001:4456: phyag zhabs gang du'ang thogs pa med pa lta bu dang /
NK088(su)001:4457: spyan phye tsam du zhugs pa dang /
NK088(su)001:4460: gdan la rten pa'i tshul dang /
NK088(su)001:4461: dbu g.yas g.yon du 'byo ba dang /
NK088(su)001:4462: gcig la gcig dbu btud pa lta bu dang /
NK088(su)001:4463: yab yum dang mnga' thang rkyen longs spyod rdzogs pa lta bu dang /
NK088(su)001:4467: rtsa gsum ste gsum pa'i nying lag rtsa ba'i rtsa
NK088(su)001:4468: thabs kyi gnyis dang gnas dang tshul la nyer gsum
NK088(su)001:4472: gang theg pas 'dul bar dgongs pa'i cho 'phrul ni /
NK088(su)001:4473: zhes pa dag gdan khri'i don te /
NK088(su)001:4474: chos kyi tsakra bskor ba'i phyir 'og gang 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi'i don dang /
NK088(su)001:4475: sa'i khyad par bzhin bgrod zin pa'i phyir them skas kyi don dang /
NK088(su)001:4476: che ba'i gu na dus gcig la rdzogs pas nyi zla pad+ma rin chen dang /
NK088(su)001:4477: sems can gyi gdan rnams snang ba'i don to //
NK088(su)001:4479: gang ltar mdzes pas 'dul bar dgongs pa ni /
NK088(su)001:4480: zhes pa la sogs pa rgyan gyi don te /
NK088(su)001:4481: thun mong ma yin pa'i byang chub kyi yan lag bdun rdzogs pa'i rtags su /
NK088(su)001:4482: chos rnam par 'byed pa dbu rgyan dang /
NK088(su)001:4483: chos nyan las dga' ba snyan cha dang /
NK088(su)001:4484: bsam pa shin tu sbyangs pa do shal dang /
NK088(su)001:4485: zag med kyi sa ste ting nge 'dzin mgur chu dang /
NK088(su)001:4486: de nyid mi brjed pa dran pa phreng ba dang /
NK088(su)001:4487: gang yang dang du mi len pa'i btang snyoms se mo do dang /
NK088(su)001:4488: bar mi chad pa'i brtson 'grus phyag gdub ste /
NK088(su)001:4489: so so'i rgyan gyi las dang /
NK088(su)001:4490: dbyibs kyi don dang chos mthun zhing mtshon du btub pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:4491: thugs ye shes snang ba'i rgyan mchog go //
NK088(su)001:4495: zhes pa dag k+aa w+aa tsi lnga 'bras bu lnga
NK088(su)001:4496: nyid rang snang ba'i rgyan gsal ba brjid pa'i sku
NK088(su)001:4498: thugs rje chags pa'i smad dkris gsung /
NK088(su)001:4504: mdzad pa gar gyi gsang gos sku reg dang phu dung /
NK088(su)001:4505: gsang gos nye der nges pa ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK088(su)001:4506: gdul bya phyogs gcig gi dbang las /
NK088(su)001:4507: mtha' grol bas ther zug pa ni ma yin te /
NK088(su)001:4510: thugs shin tu brjid pa dang /
NK088(su)001:4511: gu na mngon par mtho ba'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:4512: las bya ba dang bcas pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:4514: gzhan yang mtshan gyi me tog gis rgyas par mdzes shing /
NK088(su)001:4515: zhes pa dag thun mong ma yin pa'i mtshan sems dpa' bcu tshan gsum dang gnyis so //
NK088(su)001:4516: sems dpa' re re la'ang dbu rgyan rigs lnga lnga ste lnga bcu drug ste brgyad cu'o //
NK088(su)001:4517: sems ma ni grangs las 'das pa'i don te ma brjod te //
NK088(su)001:4520: zhes pa la sogs pa thun mong ma yin pa'i 'phags pa'i lam yan lag brgyad rdzogs pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:4521: yang dag pa'i sa ma d+hi la goms dpal be'u dang /
NK088(su)001:4522: bslab pa mtha' bcu yi don la rtsol ba mthar phyin pas 'khor lo dang /
NK088(su)001:4523: bden pa dang chos dang bzlas pa'i gsung gi yang dag pa'i ngag pad+ma dang /
NK088(su)001:4524: dam pa rnams kyi de kho na la rtogs shing dpyod pa la rgyal mtshan dang /
NK088(su)001:4525: sgo gsum gyi spyod pa las mtha' las nges par
NK088(su)001:4526: 'byung zhing nyi ma'i tshad pa sel ba gdugs dang
NK088(su)001:4527: / ma nor ba'i lta ba'i mgul bum pa dang /
NK088(su)001:4528: dam pa'i chos sgra nyan cing 'chad pa dang dung dang /
NK088(su)001:4529: dam pa'i yo byad lnga la yun ring 'tsho ba nya ste bkra shis brgyad por byung ste /
NK088(su)001:4530: las dang dbyibs kyi chos mthun par sbyar ro //
NK088(su)001:4531: bzhi pa dang lnga pa la nyi shu rtsa gsum du phye bas bshad pa'o //
NK088(su)001:4532: spyir nying lag bdun cu rtsa gnyis zhi ba'i rtog pa bshad pa ni /
NK088(su)001:4533: dngos po gang gdul bya la snang na de dag
NK088(su)001:4534: snang bas snying po byang chub kyi ngang du mtshan
NK088(su)001:4535: nyid ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:4537: gcig dang du ma las grol bar bstan pas khro bo yang rjes su mthun no //
NK088(su)001:4538: 'khor la snang ba ni sgra bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:4539: de nas yang gsang ba'i bdag pos smras pa /
NK088(su)001:4541: gang du rnam par bsgyur ba'i cho 'phrul ni /
NK088(su)001:4542: zhes pa dag gang de nyid kyis mi 'dul ba'i
NK088(su)001:4543: gdul bya'i ngo la snang ba'i las snga phyir gyur
NK088(su)001:4544: pa'i phyir te / lam pa'i dbang du 'dzin pa
NK088(su)001:4545: gzhil dka' la tshan che zhing 'thug pa'i phyir te
NK088(su)001:4546: pa'i phyir te / / grangs ni rtsa ba'i dbang ngo //
NK088(su)001:4547: de la grangs byang btab pa dag ni sgra bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:4548: de yang gsum pa yan chad la gsum gsum /
NK088(su)001:4551: drug pa drug /bdun pa la gsum /
NK088(su)001:4552: brgyad pa la bcu drug /dgu pa la nyi shu /
NK088(su)001:4554: 'di la nying lag brgyad cu rtsa gcig yod pa'i dbang du'o //
NK088(su)001:4555: de dag ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK088(su)001:4556: yang dag pa'i sa la sbyor ba'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:4557: ngo bo mi phyed pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:4558: phyi ma'i ngo bo tha mi dad par nges par zin pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:4559: sku phyag rgyar snang ba'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:4560: bar du gcod pa bdud 'joms pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:4561: gang rkyen du 'tshams pas 'dul ba'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:4562: yon tan mtshon par 'byung ba'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:4563: gdul bya mngon du snang ba'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:4564: mdzad pa mi 'gog par mdzad pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:4565: nang gi don phyi ru snang ba'i phyir te /
NK088(su)001:4567: de las gyur pa grangs phrag gnyis po la nges par 'dzin pa ni /
NK088(su)001:4568: lam lnga la gnas pa'i rnal 'byor gnyis pa man chad la bsgrib pas /
NK088(su)001:4569: de ngo shes pas bsal ba'i phyir bstan te gdams pa'ang mdzad do //
NK088(su)001:4570: de la grangs dang po'i dbang du dgu gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:4574: zhes pa dag bcu brgyad cu dang dgu bcu'o //
NK088(su)001:4576: dgu po re re la'ang snga ma'i bcu po tshang bar yod pas grangs nges so //
NK088(su)001:4577: dgu'i ngo bo ni mtshan ma bsdus pa dgu yul du byed pa'i zhen rtog nges par 'dzin dagu'o //
NK088(su)001:4578: bco brgyad pa dang gcig pa gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:4579: bcu phrag brgyad dang gcig gi grangs nges pa ste /
NK088(su)001:4580: bshad pa'i sum phrag gsum re rer brtsis pa gsum ste /
NK088(su)001:4581: sbyor zhen dngos gzhi yan lag dgu dang bcas pa /
NK088(su)001:4582: rtsa ba'i dbang du byas pas yan lag mtshon pa'o //
NK088(su)001:4583: bskyed pa'i rtog pa bco lnga la gcig tu brtsis pas bzhi /
NK088(su)001:4584: yan lag nyi shu rtsa bzhi'o //
NK088(su)001:4585: rkyen gyi bzhi gcig tu brtsis pa lnga ste yan lag nyi shu rtsa brgyad do //
NK088(su)001:4586: las kyi rtog pa drug bsdom pa dang drug ste yan lag sum cu rtsa bzhi'o //
NK088(su)001:4587: mtshan ma'i rtog pa gsum gcig tu byas pas /
NK088(su)001:4588: bdun te yan lag sum cu rtsa bdun no //
NK088(su)001:4589: mngon pa'i rtog pa lnga gnyis drug ste bcu drug bsdom pas brgyad de /
NK088(su)001:4590: yan lag lnga bcu rtsa gsum mo //
NK088(su)001:4591: spyod pa'i rtog pa bcu phrag gnyis gcig tu brtsis
NK088(su)001:4592: pa dang dgu ste yan lag bdun cu rtsa gsum
NK088(su)001:4593: mo // rtags kyi bdun bsdom pa rtsa ba bcu la yan lag brgyad cu'o //
NK088(su)001:4594: de ril la yang nges par rtog pa yod pas
NK088(su)001:4595: brtags pa'i zhen pa gcig ste brgyad cu rtsa gcig
NK088(su)001:4596: go // 'o na grangs gnyis bstan pa ci dgos zhe na /
NK088(su)001:4597: rtog pa rtsa ba las phye ba dang /
NK088(su)001:4598: yan lag las phye ba ngo shes par bya ba'i phyir bkod de /
NK088(su)001:4599: spyir bsdom pa nyis brgya drug cu'o //
NK088(su)001:4600: de dag brgyad cu las nying lag gis brgya nyi shu rtsa drug ngo shes par bya ba'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:4602: de la sbyor ba'i rtog pa gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:4604: chos dbyings de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK088(su)001:4605: kun tu snang ye shes ba'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK088(su)001:4606: rgyu'i zung ting nge 'dzin gyis las dang mtshan nyid
NK088(su)001:4607: de 'bras bu mthar phyin pa la lhun gyis grub
NK088(su)001:4609: spyi'i dbang du zhi gnas chen po dang /
NK088(su)001:4611: zung du 'brel ba la rtog pa'o //
NK088(su)001:4613: zhen pa'i rtog pa gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:4614: zhes pa dag /sems stong pa bdag med khro bo
NK088(su)001:4615: dag gdul bya'i ngo bo nyid spyod yul med pa
NK088(su)001:4616: / sems las ma gtogs pa'i chos med ngo bo gang du'ang sa ma zin pa /
NK088(su)001:4617: bdag la rtog pa'i 'du shes bral dngos gzhi ma rnyed pa'i /
NK088(su)001:4618: don mtshan ma med pa don la rtogs pa'o //
NK088(su)001:4620: dngos gzhi rtog pa gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:4621: zhes pa dag /kun chos dbyings las ma g.yos khro
NK088(su)001:4622: bo ril snying po byang chub lhun gyis grub pa
NK088(su)001:4624: kun mdzad pa drag po'i phrin las mdzad pa dang /
NK088(su)001:4625: ril shin tu khros par shes rab dang thugs rje zhugs pa la rtog pa'o //
NK088(su)001:4627: bskyed pa'i rtog pa gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:4628: zhes pa dag gzhi ni rtsa ba ste /
NK088(su)001:4629: rang rig pa'i ye shes nyid khro bor gyur pa dang /
NK088(su)001:4630: gzhan dur khrod las gyur pa dang /
NK088(su)001:4631: gdug pa 'dul phyir gyur pa dang /
NK088(su)001:4632: drag po 'dul thabs kyis khro bor gyur pa'o //
NK088(su)001:4634: gang gyur pa ni 'di lta ste /
NK088(su)001:4635: zhes pa dag /de la dang po la bzhi ni /
NK088(su)001:4636: ye nyid rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i phyir khro bo chos dbyings /
NK088(su)001:4637: dang khro bor mtshan ma ngang gis bcom pas /
NK088(su)001:4639: gdul bya 'dul ba'i thugs rje dang smon lam gyis /
NK088(su)001:4640: shugs kyis khro bor snang ba ste /
NK088(su)001:4641: de yang de bzhin nyid kyi khro bo /
NK088(su)001:4645: bya ba snang ba ni ru dra lta bu'i /
NK088(su)001:4646: ched du byas pa'i phyir te /
NK088(su)001:4647: ye shes kyi khro bo dang /
NK088(su)001:4650: lang ka'i bdag po gang la gyur pa ni /
NK088(su)001:4652: khro bo de yang yul dur khrod ru dra gsum lta bu dregs pa can dang /
NK088(su)001:4653: dur khrod kyis bam ril thod pa mkhar gnas las snang ste /
NK088(su)001:4654: drag po'i las kyis dug gsum ste sha khrag rus pa gsum /
NK088(su)001:4656: phung po dur khrod kyi gnas su byas pa'o //
NK088(su)001:4657: shes 'bras bu ni pa byang chub bkod pa mi 'khor ba dang dam las btags pa'o //
NK088(su)001:4659: rtsa ba ni sgra gnyis pa'i don to //
NK088(su)001:4661: gang gis phyir gyur pa ni /
NK088(su)001:4663: gdul bya drag po de lta ngan spyod cing nyon
NK088(su)001:4664: mongs la zhe na mtshams med pa byed pa dang
NK088(su)001:4665: / ru dra 'bras bu shin tu drag par skyes pas /
NK088(su)001:4666: bdag gzhan gyis sdug bsngal gyis sa bon 'debs par smin zin pa 'dul ba'i dgos ched du ste /
NK088(su)001:4667: gang gzhi'i don gyis rtsa ba 'grub bo //
NK088(su)001:4671: ye shes chen pos bskyed pa'i snying po h'u ha he phata ces pa'o //
NK088(su)001:4672: rtog mtshan ril sgrol ba'i thugs rje mnga' ba'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:4673: dur khrod brub khang las gzhal yas rgyan dang ldan pa'i dbang gis so //
NK088(su)001:4674: kyi gzhal yas khang las gyur te /
NK088(su)001:4675: dper na me dang lho phyogs rtsub 'gyur tshal lta bu'o //
NK088(su)001:4676: thabs ni bdag nyid yab yum cho ga gsum gsal nas 'khor yan chad gsal /
NK088(su)001:4677: thugs rje'i thabs kyis bsgral la ma thogs pa dang /
NK088(su)001:4678: phrin las drag po cir yang snang ba mnga' ba dang /
NK088(su)001:4680: gnas spar bas sdug bsngal tshar bcad nas bde ba
NK088(su)001:4681: ye shes su gyur pa la sbyor ba'i byed pa
NK088(su)001:4682: ste / gsum pas nges tshig grub bo //
NK088(su)001:4684: de la rkyen gyi rtog pa gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:4685: zhes pa dag lha'i bu'i bdud ni drag po dang lha brgyad btul nas gdan du mdzad pa dang /
NK088(su)001:4686: phung po'i bdud de ma dmigs pas /
NK088(su)001:4687: rgas rgud med par mdzad pas shes rab kyi mtshon
NK088(su)001:4688: gyis gdug pa can gyi gdos bcas kyi lus bral
NK088(su)001:4689: ba dang / nyon mongs pa bdud ma dmigs par bcom pas sa bon med pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:4690: dug gsum zad pas sha rus khrag zos 'chos 'thung ba dang /
NK088(su)001:4691: skye shi mi mnga' bas na 'chi bdag bcom pas
NK088(su)001:4692: shes pa zag med sa la bkod pa la rtog
NK088(su)001:4693: pa'o // las kyi rtog pa gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:4694: zhes pa dag dbang phyug dug lnga dbang sdud sbrul thod chen po'i yon tan brnyes pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:4695: bdag gzhan gyi dpal mnga' ba'i phyir dpa' bas 'jigs shing nyam nga ba med pa'i rtags la /
NK088(su)001:4697: mtshan sku mtha' yas dang dpe byad kyi sku mchog mnga' ba'i rtags 'khor lo dang /
NK088(su)001:4698: ril du grags chos kyi phung po grags pa mtha' yas pa'i rtags /
NK088(su)001:4699: pa phun sum tshogs pa mnga' ba dang /
NK088(su)001:4700: cis kyang las nyon gyi d+r+wa ba gcod pa la thogs pa med pa ral gri /
NK088(su)001:4701: ma gos pa'i ye shes mnga' ba dang /
NK088(su)001:4702: dug gsum rgyun ma chad pa'i gdul bya chud ma gson pa'i /
NK088(su)001:4703: brtson 'grus chen po'i go cha mnga' ba'i las dus gcig grub pa'i rgya gram phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:4705: mtshan ma'i rtog pa gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:4706: zhes pa dag rtsa ba gsum ni /
NK088(su)001:4707: na bza' rgyan gyi lung rnams don gyi ngo bo las mi 'da' ba dang /
NK088(su)001:4709: 'gro ba'i don gyi mdzad pa dang /
NK088(su)001:4710: che ba yon tan gyi lung /
NK088(su)001:4713: de la mi 'da' ba gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:4715: gdul bya las mi 'da' ba dang /
NK088(su)001:4716: zhes pa dag dang po bcu gcig 'chad de /
NK088(su)001:4717: thugs rje chen po lhun gyis grub pas dus gsum du gdul bya mi dor ba'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:4719: khro bo'i rang bzhin du dpa' ba dang /
NK088(su)001:4720: thugs kyis gnyis med du mkhyen pas mtha' ril 'joms pa'i phyir stag gi sham thabs dang /
NK088(su)001:4721: lung bstan las zab mo yum gyi rtags sbrul bzhi
NK088(su)001:4722: sbrul gyi rtogs pas nyon mongs pa la spyod pa'i
NK088(su)001:4723: rtags / chun po'i chas brgyad do //
NK088(su)001:4724: dug gsum sku gsum du thabs kyi dbang bsgyur bas
NK088(su)001:4725: thod phreng thabs mchog dpag gis mi langs pas 'khor
NK088(su)001:4727: sngon gyi go chas gdul bya mi dor ba'i phyir
NK088(su)001:4728: na thod pa tshar gsum dang zhing gi g.yang 'khor
NK088(su)001:4729: ba sgrol bar dam bcas pa'i rtags zhing lpags gzhi
NK088(su)001:4730: mnabs pa'o // thugs rje dang shes rab kyis chen po'i 'khor 'das la /
NK088(su)001:4731: chags pa mi phyed pa rak+ta dang /
NK088(su)001:4732: chos mnyam pa'i dri ma zug de kho na'i bcud
NK088(su)001:4733: rlan pa rngu bral bar mkhyen pa'i phyir rak+ta'i thig
NK088(su)001:4734: le dang / zhag gi zo ris smin mtshams dang skra mtshams su brgyan te /
NK088(su)001:4735: sku gsum gyis dug gsum 'joms pa'i las mnga' bas
NK088(su)001:4736: thal ba mdzad pas 'gro ba sgrol bas thal chen
NK088(su)001:4737: mtshan ma / de dag ni thun mong ye shes rang snang gi rgyan brgyad do //
NK088(su)001:4738: ye shes las mi 'da' ba dang /
NK088(su)001:4739: zhes pa dag ye shes kyi mtha' bral ba'i mtshan ma bsregs pas me klong na bzhugs pa dang /
NK088(su)001:4740: dgongs pa'i chos nyid kun tu ma 'dres pa'i sprul pa 'phro bas ral pa khyab pa dang /
NK088(su)001:4741: dgongs pa'i don shin tu de kho na nyid 'gyur ba med par sku mdog gsal ba'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:4743: ral pa gtibs pa dang sku mdog go //
NK088(su)001:4747: ces pa rang gi don gyi ngo bo yongs su lhun gyis grub pa dang /
NK088(su)001:4748: de dag gzhan don so so'i phrin las bstan pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:4754: dug gsum ma skyes par gsal ba'i dbu gsum dngos
NK088(su)001:4755: gzhi yongs su ma zin pa'i ye shes ril gyi
NK088(su)001:4756: bla gyur pa'i phyir dbur grub dang /
NK088(su)001:4757: mtho dman theg pa'i bye brag dgu ma 'dres par
NK088(su)001:4758: gzigs pa'i spyan dgu gzugs snang yul med par ma
NK088(su)001:4759: 'dres gsal ba chu dang gza' skar lta bu spyan
NK088(su)001:4760: dang / thugs ting 'dzin gsum las mi yengs pa shangs /
NK088(su)001:4761: 'gro 'ong 'byung 'jug dus gsum bral ba'i phyir shangs /
NK088(su)001:4762: dbu dang spyan dang shangs te /
NK088(su)001:4763: gral dang las dang dbyibs kyis bzhag pa'o //
NK088(su)001:4764: ngo bo ma bsgribs thams cad mi gsan pa mi
NK088(su)001:4765: mnga' ba par brjod pa ril ma gsan par gsal
NK088(su)001:4766: ba'i ngo bor bzhugs pa snyan dang /
NK088(su)001:4767: rnam thar gsum gyis ci la rol pa zhen chags mi mnga' ba zhal dang /
NK088(su)001:4768: ye shes theg pa kun la pas mi shes mdud pas ma bsdams pa ste brjod pa ljags dang /
NK088(su)001:4769: las bzhi dus gcig grub pa tshigs ched du ma mi sbyor bar mdzad pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:4770: snyan dang zhal dang ljags dang mche bar byung ba'o //
NK088(su)001:4771: phrin las gang la'ang thogs pa med pa'i ye shes
NK088(su)001:4772: chen po la skad cig tsam la mdzad pa dang
NK088(su)001:4773: / yon tan mang po 'dus pa rigs drug gi don rdzogs par mdzad pa dang /
NK088(su)001:4774: bgrod pa thams cad chos dbyings su gsal bas med par sa non pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:4781: gdul bya gzigs par mdzad pa dang /
NK088(su)001:4782: zhes pa la sogs pa gdul bya ched du ma bltas gzigs pa spyan dang /
NK088(su)001:4783: sprul pa'i 'byung gnas su gyur pas 'phro ba shangs dang /
NK088(su)001:4784: thugs dam bskul zhing gsol ba ril dngos grub snang bar mdzad pa snyan dang /
NK088(su)001:4785: 'gro ba'i mgon skyabs mdzad pa ni /
NK088(su)001:4786: dbu spyan shangs snyan dbu'i phrin las so //
NK088(su)001:4787: dug gsum zad par mdzad pas sha rus khrag la rol pa zhal dang /
NK088(su)001:4788: gsang sngags ston par mdzad pa ljags dang /
NK088(su)001:4789: mnga' dang drod gsher sgo nga bardzusa nas skye ba'i sa bon 'joms pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:4790: mche ba zhal dang ljags dang mche ba bzhi'i phrin las so //
NK088(su)001:4791: 'gro drug gnas nas sgrol ba phyag dang /
NK088(su)001:4792: mtha' drug 'bras bus ye shes drug dang 'bras bu
NK088(su)001:4793: drug lhun gyis rdzogs par mdzad pa phyag mtshan dang
NK088(su)001:4794: / phrin las bzhis 'gro ba sgrol bar mdzad pa ni /
NK088(su)001:4795: zhabs tha ma phyag dang phyag mtshan zhabs gsum gyi phrin las so //
NK088(su)001:4799: gnyen po med pa'i che ba dang /
NK088(su)001:4800: 'gran zla med pa'i che ba dang /
NK088(su)001:4801: zhes pa la sogs pa thun mong ma yin pa'i
NK088(su)001:4802: pha rol tu phyin pa bcu mnga' ba'i phyir te
NK088(su)001:4803: / gnyis med kyi ye shes chen po mnga' ba'i gnyen pa dang bral ba rdo rje phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:4804: mnyam pa'i ngang la sdug bsngal ma spangs bral ba'i
NK088(su)001:4805: bzod pa chen po mnga' bas don byed pa'i phyir
NK088(su)001:4806: thugs rje ye shes kyis 'phags pa dung khrag dang
NK088(su)001:4807: / stong gsum dug gsum yongs sgrol gyi stobs mchog
NK088(su)001:4808: che ba mnga' ba'i phyir dug gsum lha bdud 'joms
NK088(su)001:4810: yon tan bdag la rdzogs pas smin gnas mthar phyin
NK088(su)001:4811: pa'i phyir gang la'ang rag ma lus pa dregs pa
NK088(su)001:4812: can bran du 'khol ba'i zhing gi g.yab mo dang
NK088(su)001:4813: / thabs mchog dpag gi mi lang ba'i mdzad pa'i
NK088(su)001:4814: byin rlabs kyis thong gshol gyis gdug pa 'dul ba
NK088(su)001:4815: nyon mongs pa'i tha ba 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:4816: gsang sngags ji bzhin pa de kho na nyid du 'dzin pa dang yang bral bas /
NK088(su)001:4817: mi dmigs pa'i shes rab chen pos rmad du byung
NK088(su)001:4818: ba'i theg pa gzhan la'ang sgrogs pa pha rol shes
NK088(su)001:4820: dus gsum du 'da' nyams bral bas pham ltung gis
NK088(su)001:4821: mi gos tshul khrims chen po mnga' ba 'khor ba'i
NK088(su)001:4822: dpung gis mi 'jigs pa'i pad+ma dang /
NK088(su)001:4823: snying po byang chub lhun gyis rdzogs pa'i ngang las
NK088(su)001:4824: dus gsum du mi g.yo ba chen po'i bsam gtan
NK088(su)001:4825: mnga' ba dang / dbang bcu thob pas tsakra bya
NK088(su)001:4826: byed bral bas yengs pa med pa'i brtson 'grus kyi
NK088(su)001:4827: mnga' ba dang / go mtshon gyis / 'khor ba'i
NK088(su)001:4828: le lo'i skyon gyi dgra dpung gtan nas 'joms pa
NK088(su)001:4829: ye shes thugs rjes mtha' gnyis gcod pa'i ral gri
NK088(su)001:4830: mnga' ba dang / go mtshon gyis / dang /
NK088(su)001:4831: nub cing zad pa med pa gang la'ang ma chags
NK088(su)001:4832: thams cad khyab pa'i sbyin pa'i yon tan chen po
NK088(su)001:4833: 'phel 'grib dang bral ba mnga' ba'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:4834: mi zad pa ldan rin po che /
NK088(su)001:4837: g.yon bar kha t+w+aam ga dang /
NK088(su)001:4844: rat+na rin po che rnams rim pa bzhin bsnams pa'o //
NK088(su)001:4846: mngon par rtog pa gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:4848: zhes pa'ang sgra bzhin te rtsa ba'i nges tshig yan lag gis 'grub /
NK088(su)001:4849: de bzhi la'ang bcu drug tu 'gyur te /
NK088(su)001:4852: cir yang snang ba ri bo lta bu'i tshul dang /
NK088(su)001:4853: zhes pa la sogs pa rgyal ba'i sku gdul bya'i bsam pa bzhin snang ba ni /
NK088(su)001:4854: ri rab phyogs bzhi kha dog so sor snang ba bzhin du bstan pa dang /
NK088(su)001:4855: mtshan nyid ma nges pas gcig du ma bral ba'i
NK088(su)001:4856: tshu la gyis snang ba'i dpe gar mkhan lta bu
NK088(su)001:4857: dang / thams cad las che btsan gcig pur byung bas lha chen gtso bo dag mnan pa dang /
NK088(su)001:4858: bdud dpung gis mi bardzi zhing de nyid 'joms pas zhabs 'gying ba'o //
NK088(su)001:4859: de ni sku'i rngam du 'gyur ro //
NK088(su)001:4860: gang du rdub pa zhal gyi tshul dang /
NK088(su)001:4861: zhes pa hom lnga 'brel ba'i zhal du ril gsol ba dang /
NK088(su)001:4862: gsung sgras cir yang 'gyur ba'i ljags dang /
NK088(su)001:4863: skye shi rtsa ba gcod pa'i tshems dang /
NK088(su)001:4864: gdul bya'i blo la gsal bar ston pa'i gsung ste gsung gi rngam bzhi'o //
NK088(su)001:4865: dgongs pa nam mkha'i skar tshogs lta bu'i tshul dang /
NK088(su)001:4866: zhes pa dag ni ril ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs par gsal ba dang /
NK088(su)001:4867: dgongs pa mi g.yo ba'i gang las 'gro don mdzad
NK088(su)001:4868: pa mi 'gag pa rgya mtsho'i rlabs lta bu dang
NK088(su)001:4869: / sku dang ye shes kyi yon tan ril gyi
NK088(su)001:4870: 'byung gnas su snang bas rdzogs pa dpe sa gzhi
NK088(su)001:4872: thugs rje chen pos ril zin pas rgyun med pa
NK088(su)001:4873: gar gyi phreng ba lta bu ste thugs kyi rngom
NK088(su)001:4874: mo // mthu'i rngam bstan pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:4875: gnas kyi khyad par 'byung zhing sdud pa dur khrod lta bu'i tshul dang /
NK088(su)001:4876: zhes pa rnams ru dra dregs pa bcom pa'i gnas sprul pa dang /
NK088(su)001:4877: yon tan 'dus shing 'byung ba dur khrod lta bu dang /
NK088(su)001:4878: dregs pa lha chen gdan du mdzad pas rgyal po
NK088(su)001:4879: btson du bzung ba lta bur gzhan spa bkong ba
NK088(su)001:4880: dang / khams gsum bsgral ba'i zhing du sangs rgyas kyi sa la bkod pa dang /
NK088(su)001:4881: mdzad spyod ci la'ang chig chod du grub pas slar gnon bya mi dgos pa'o //
NK088(su)001:4883: spyod pa'i rtog pa gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:4884: zhes pa la sogs pa brjid nyi shu rtsa lnga dpe 'dis mtshon pa sgra bzhan no //
NK088(su)001:4887: sku che yan lag rags pa'i gzi brjid dang /
NK088(su)001:4888: grangs mang rkyen dang 'tshams pa'i gzi brjid dang /
NK088(su)001:4889: zhes pa la sogs pa chos sku mnyam pas che
NK088(su)001:4890: chung thugs rje mnyam pas rags tshad med pa dang
NK088(su)001:4891: / sku ji snyed du snang ba'i yon tan mnga'
NK088(su)001:4892: bas gdul bya gang la gang 'tshams pas 'dul ba
NK088(su)001:4893: / dang / 'jig rten pa dang sa pas gtso mchog tshogs kyi bdag por lta ba dang /
NK088(su)001:4894: zla med pas gdul bya'i bsam pa dang mthun pa'o //
NK088(su)001:4895: gsung gi brjid gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:4896: gdul bya'i gnas ril du skad cig la khyab pa dang /
NK088(su)001:4897: 'khor gyi bsam pa'i gegs ji snyed re mos pa med par sel ba dang /
NK088(su)001:4898: 'khor rnams gcig kyang nga kho na dgongs shing chos ston snyam pa dang /
NK088(su)001:4899: yon tan gyi phung por snang ba'o //
NK088(su)001:4900: thugs kyi brjid gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:4901: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa gnyis ka ma spangs par re dogs bral ba dang /
NK088(su)001:4902: gnyis med la gang gis kyang ma bsgribs pas mtha' rnams ngang gis dag pa dang /
NK088(su)001:4903: mi g.yo mi 'gog pas 'gro ba bsgral ba'i thugs dam chen po'i bdag nyid dang /
NK088(su)001:4904: thabs smin dper thams cad yang d+r+wa ba /
NK088(su)001:4906: yon tan gyi brjid gang snyam pa la /
NK088(su)001:4907: med pa zad mi shes pa'i gzi brjid dang /
NK088(su)001:4908: zhes pa la sogs pa ngo bo 'di 'drar ma
NK088(su)001:4909: grub pas dngos grub 'grib pa med par 'byung ba
NK088(su)001:4910: dang / ngo bo gcig la lhun gyis grub pa'i
NK088(su)001:4911: byin rlabs rin po che lta bur 'byung ba dang
NK088(su)001:4912: dang / / bsgral gnas la sogs pa'i mdzad pa yang sman chen po nyid du 'gyur ba dang /
NK088(su)001:4913: mdzad spyod gang la'ang sa bon du gyur pa med pa pad+ma bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:4914: phrin las kyi brjid ji lta bu zhe na /
NK088(su)001:4915: bdud dpung gi bag tsha ba med pa'i gdeng mnga' bas mdzad pa dang /
NK088(su)001:4916: 'khor ba thog mtha' med par don mdzad pa la ngal dub mi mnga' ba dang /
NK088(su)001:4917: 'gro mgon dus rgyun chad med par mdzad pa dang /
NK088(su)001:4918: 'gro ba bsgral bar dgongs pa mthar phyin pa'o //
NK088(su)001:4919: des kun 'dus kyi le'u dang po bshad cing 'grel ba ni /
NK088(su)001:4920: rtogs pa'i ri bo dang mtshungs so //
NK088(su)001:4922: rtags kyi rtog pa gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:4924: zhes pa rtsa ba bdun no //
NK088(su)001:4925: chos kyi mnga' bdag chen po dbang bcu brnyes pas chos kyi 'khor lo bcu bskor ba la /
NK088(su)001:4926: the tshom gyi bsnyengs pa mi mnga' ba'i yon tan
NK088(su)001:4927: snang zhing mtshon pa'i phyir ming 'grub 'khor lo bo
NK088(su)001:4928: // thabs dang shes rab kyi bde ba nyams bag
NK088(su)001:4929: phyag rgya bzhi la rol pa'i rgyun med pa'i yon
NK088(su)001:4930: tan snang zhing mtshon pa'i phyir btsun mo dang /
NK088(su)001:4931: gar dgus bdud bzhi'i dpung gis mi thub pa'i phyir dmag dpon dang /
NK088(su)001:4932: 'khor ba'i dus thog mtha' med par tshad med bzhis don 'grub pa khyim bdag dang /
NK088(su)001:4933: thun mong ma yin pa'i stobs mchog bcu mnga' bas
NK088(su)001:4934: mi mthun pa'i phyogs mi ldang bar mdzad pa glang
NK088(su)001:4935: po dang / skad cig ma la'ang thabs khyad par
NK088(su)001:4936: can gyi rdzu 'phrul bzhis sa non pa'i rtags rta
NK088(su)001:4937: po dang / mchog dang / yon tan 'phel 'grib
NK088(su)001:4938: mi mnga' bar snang zhing mtshon pa'i phyir nor bu
NK088(su)001:4939: po dang / mchog dang / dang / 'khor lo rin po che dang /
NK088(su)001:4945: nor bu rin po che mnga' ba'o //
NK088(su)001:4946: de dag yan lag gis dbang du rgyas par bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:4949: de la mnga' dbang chen po brnyes pa'i rtags ni /
NK088(su)001:4951: gang dbang bcu yongs su rdzogs pa'i /
NK088(su)001:4952: zhes pa la sogs pa gang rmad du byung ba'i dbang bcu ni /
NK088(su)001:4953: lhun gyis rdzogs pa'i yon tan snang ba ste /
NK088(su)001:4954: de la man ngag gi tshigs su na /
NK088(su)001:4955: skye bzhi skur ston skye bzhi sgrol mdzad pa //
NK088(su)001:4956: lha mi sdig sprul skye ba bzhi ru bstan //
NK088(su)001:4957: yo byad 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga dang ni //
NK088(su)001:4958: rtog pa gzhom phyir sman lnga dang len rol //
NK088(su)001:4959: ji ltar mos bzhin tshul dgu'i gzugs ston pa //
NK088(su)001:4960: gar dbang thabs kyi tshul dgus 'joms par mdzad //
NK088(su)001:4961: rdzu 'phrul ba spu'i dbyings nas phra men 'phro //
NK088(su)001:4962: lus ni cir bardzu sems ni cho 'phrul ston //
NK088(su)001:4963: gad rgyangs gdangs ngar sna tshogs phyogs bcur sgrogs //
NK088(su)001:4964: mche bas zil gnon chos rnams tha dad ston //
NK088(su)001:4965: shes rab thabs ldan spyan gyis dbu ma'i ngang //
NK088(su)001:4966: dbyings las mi g.yo cir yang sa ler mkhyen //
NK088(su)001:4967: sems kyi bye brag ting 'dzin sa ya 'phrog /bsam gyis mi khyab bzhi la rol pa mdzad //
NK088(su)001:4968: rdo rje sder mo pags pa spu phreng brgyan //
NK088(su)001:4969: 'khor ba ji srid bzhugs pa'i tshe la dbang //
NK088(su)001:4970: lta ba rnam bzhi spyan zur gyis bskul bas //
NK088(su)001:4971: phra men bzhi 'phro phyogs bzhi las bzhi mdzad //
NK088(su)001:4972: smon lam dbang gis drag po'i skur ston cing //
NK088(su)001:4973: dus mtha'i bskal pa bzhin du bshol du med //
NK088(su)001:4976: nyams bag chen por rol pa'i zhes pa dag /ma chags rdo rje'i gzungs kyi yum gyis 'khyud //
NK088(su)001:4977: zhi gnas ting 'dzin mi g.yo yum gyis sbyor //
NK088(su)001:4978: lhag mthong ye shes yum gyis gnyis med 'bebs //
NK088(su)001:4979: thogs med shugs 'chang dngos grub yum gyis bskyod //
NK088(su)001:4982: gang gi dpung gis mi bsnyengs pa'i rtags ni /
NK088(su)001:4983: zhes pa la sogs pa tshul dgu ste /
NK088(su)001:4984: dur khrod rgyan dang cha lugs ldan pas sgeg /bdud
NK088(su)001:4985: bzhi dpung bcom bag tsha med pas dpa' //zhal dbus
NK088(su)001:4987: zhal g.yon dmar gdangs gdug pa gshe //
NK088(su)001:4988: zhal g.yas dkar bzhad theg chen sgrogs //
NK088(su)001:4989: 'gro drug thugs rjes mi gtong snying rjer ldan //
NK088(su)001:4990: dug gsum zhal du gsol bas bdud la rngam //
NK088(su)001:4991: sku gsung las lnga rdzogs pas ya mtshan che //
NK088(su)001:4992: dgongs pa chos nyid klong chen shin tu zhi //
NK088(su)001:4995: yun gyi don srid brnyes pa'i rtags ni /
NK088(su)001:4997: khro gtum tshad med byams par snang //
NK088(su)001:4998: gsod chen snying rje'i mtshan nyid de //
NK088(su)001:4999: bsgral zhing bstab pas dga' ba'i mchog /yal bar mi 'dor btang snyoms so //
NK088(su)001:5002: stobs kyis gzhan gang gnon pa'i rtags ni /
NK088(su)001:5004: snying rje chen po'i stobs kyis dregs pa sgrol //
NK088(su)001:5005: chos nyid stobs kyis cir yang snang ba'i mdog /spangs len med par barlanga po'i rdzas la rol //
NK088(su)001:5006: grub pa'i stobs kyis bdud rtsi dngos grub rgyu //
NK088(su)001:5007: ma spangs stobs kyis gdos bcas sku la brgyan //
NK088(su)001:5008: ma g.yos stobs ni don mthun grol ba'i rgyan //
NK088(su)001:5009: smon lam chen pos bskal pa yongs sgrol mdzad //
NK088(su)001:5010: sprul pa'i mgo brnyan 'grong 'ong med par 'gro //
NK088(su)001:5011: thams cad zin pas log lta spong mi byed //
NK088(su)001:5012: chags pa'i stobs ni yun chags spyan dmar bzlog /zhes bya'o //
NK088(su)001:5014: rdzu 'phrul gyis mi gnas par bskyod pa'i rtags ni /
NK088(su)001:5017: chos nyid rdzu 'phrul mi spongs yongs rdzogs pas //
NK088(su)001:5018: mkha' la 'ja' tshon bzhin du rnam par bkra //
NK088(su)001:5019: ye shes mtshan nyid ma bsgribs dag pa'i phyir //
NK088(su)001:5020: mkha' la nyi shar 'dra ste gsal la stong //
NK088(su)001:5021: thugs rje mi g.yo kun la khyab pas na //
NK088(su)001:5022: mkha' la mnyam pa'i sprin phung bzhin du bdal //
NK088(su)001:5024: ro gcig char bab snod kyi bye brag phye //
NK088(su)001:5025: cir yang snang zhing ma nges snang la med //
NK088(su)001:5026: des na ming gi don bzhi rdzogs par bshad //
NK088(su)001:5029: mi zad pa'i mdzod la mnga' ba'i rtags gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:5030: zhes pa la sogs pa lhun gyis rdzogs pa'i khro
NK088(su)001:5031: bo'i thugs ye shes ni rin po che nyid de
NK088(su)001:5032: / dpe nor bu mchog lta bu bas /
NK088(su)001:5033: 'gro rnams ji ltar 'dul zhing re 'dod tshim par byed //
NK088(su)001:5034: mi zad rgyun med gter chen nam mkha'i mdog /srid gsum ling thog sel ba'i ye shes sgron //
NK088(su)001:5035: dus gsum rgyun med rin chen phreng bar snang //
NK088(su)001:5037: de lta bu'i yon tan rtsa ba dang /
NK088(su)001:5039: zhe lnga'i bdag nyid du bzhugs pa ni khro bo gnyis te /
NK088(su)001:5040: de la 'dzin pa ni ched du byas pa'i rtog pa ste spang bya nyid do //
NK088(su)001:5041: de dag gi don ci zhe na /
NK088(su)001:5043: rdzu 'phrul gyi cho 'phrul gyis bsdus pa ni gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:5044: zhes dag cho 'phrul dang po'i don bstan pas /
NK088(su)001:5045: de dag ril ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs par 'khor gyi rig pa la gsal bar mdzad do //
NK088(su)001:5046: rdzu 'phrul gyi cho 'phrul bstan pa'i le'u ste bcu
NK088(su)001:5047: drug pa bkrol ba'o ////de nas yang gsang ba'i bdag
NK088(su)001:5048: pos / lang ka'i bdag po la bos te smras pa /
NK088(su)001:5049: zhes pa la sogs pa cho 'phrul gnyis pa bstan par dgongs nas bos te bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:5050: ston pa bos gnas tha dad pa ru /
NK088(su)001:5051: gdul bya chos snang ba'i ngo bo 'chad pa dag sbyar bas /
NK088(su)001:5052: gnas dang 'jig rten de dag tu /
NK088(su)001:5053: de'i byin brlabs dang mthu yis /
NK088(su)001:5054: dngos su mtha' mtho na dbus dma' ba la sogs pa'i tshabs che ba dang khyab par g.yos te /
NK088(su)001:5055: rjes su 'chad pa gsum gsum yang mthun no //
NK088(su)001:5057: phyi nang gi mun pa thams cad sbyangs nas /
NK088(su)001:5058: zhes pa 'dis 'das pa dag brda ru 'gyur te /
NK088(su)001:5059: 'gro ba'i rgyud la chos snang ba'i cho 'phrul snang bas /
NK088(su)001:5060: byang chub sems g.yos tshabs che chung gsum lam pa man chad la 'byung ba dang /
NK088(su)001:5061: des rang rang sa la mi gnas par don gong ma la 'jug pa dang /
NK088(su)001:5062: zhugs pas rang rang gis zhen pa mi brtan par gyur ba dang /
NK088(su)001:5063: chos ci bzhin pa rig pa la mjal ba ni brjod pa dang 'dra bar grags pa'o //
NK088(su)001:5064: des sa'i sgrib pa shin tu 'joms pa tshabs che chung dang /
NK088(su)001:5065: des snying po byang chub mtshan nyid cir yang snang
NK088(su)001:5066: la ma nges pa nyid du son par mdzad pa
NK088(su)001:5067: ste / dngos gzung 'dzin rnam gnyis rang rgyud dang /
NK088(su)001:5068: ched du byas pa phra rags sbyangs te /
NK088(su)001:5069: de'i rim pa yid ches pas ni /
NK088(su)001:5070: 'gro ba mtha' thug med pa dag /zhes pa dag /
NK088(su)001:5071: 'jig rten pa'i sa na sems skyes pa nas dga' ba bskyed /
NK088(su)001:5072: de bzhin du sems dang po pa rnams rig pa
NK088(su)001:5073: gsal bar byas te rmad du byung ba la 'jug
NK088(su)001:5074: cing zhugs / theg pa chen por sbyor lam la rten pas bden pa mthong ste /
NK088(su)001:5075: sa nas sar 'phar bas rtsal chen rdzogs pa snying po byang chub tu gyur to //
NK088(su)001:5076: thams cad re zhing ngam pa'i chos nyid /
NK088(su)001:5077: ces pa dag /de ltar snang bas 'gro ba dang
NK088(su)001:5078: sa pa ril 'bras bu gong ma la 'dod pa
NK088(su)001:5079: skye zhing don snang ba la /
NK088(su)001:5080: shin tu ya mtshan par snang bar byed pa'i chos dngos gzhi par bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:5081: 'jig rten mtha' yas rdul snyed du //
NK088(su)001:5082: zhes pa gnas der don mdzad pa po grangs las
NK088(su)001:5083: 'das pa snang bas yi ge'i sgra'i chos dag bstan
NK088(su)001:5084: pas / yon tan ni bshad pa ltar sgrib pa'i phung po sbyangs te /
NK088(su)001:5085: ril snying po byang chub la rim par bkod do //
NK088(su)001:5086: sprul pa'i don ni rdul snyed las //
NK088(su)001:5087: chos nyid nges par snang ba'i sgo //
NK088(su)001:5088: zhes pa la sogs pa gdul bya sprul pa dang mnyam pa snyed /
NK088(su)001:5089: chos snang ba'i ngo bo ni rtsa ba a h'u rgyu'i ngo bo bas /
NK088(su)001:5090: yi ge bzhi bcur snang ba ni sngags kyi yig 'bru rnams so //
NK088(su)001:5091: de re re nas bstan pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:5092: lang ka'i bdag po 'di lta ste /
NK088(su)001:5093: a chos kyi dbyings rnam par dag pa'i snang ba'i sgo /
NK088(su)001:5094: zhes pa la sogs pa lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis
NK088(su)001:5095: kyi ngo bo nyid yi ge sngags kyi sgra las
NK088(su)001:5097: a a b+ha dra sa man+ta ces pa'i sngags su gyur pas /
NK088(su)001:5098: chos nyid kyi ngo bo ril gyi 'byung gnas yum kun tu bzang mor gsal bar byung ngo //
NK088(su)001:5099: h'u h'u badz+ra tsit+ta'i sngags kyis rang byung ye shes
NK088(su)001:5100: ngo bo ma bcos pa kun tu bzang po'i skur
NK088(su)001:5101: byung ba rang rig pa'i chos nyid gsal bar byed
NK088(su)001:5102: do // h'u h'u badz+ra d+h+rika gi sngags las rdo
NK088(su)001:5103: rje 'dzin pa mi bskyod pa nyid sems kyi chos
NK088(su)001:5106: +amo dzi na dzika ces pa'i don rang rig cir
NK088(su)001:5107: yang shar ba'i don de nyid rnam par snang mdzad
NK088(su)001:5110: s+w+aa rat+na d+h+rika ces pas yon tan ji snyed 'byung
NK088(su)001:5111: ba'i rin chen 'byung ldan te sems yon tan lhun
NK088(su)001:5112: gyis rdzogs pa'i chos nyid snang bar byed do //
NK088(su)001:5114: +aam a ro lika ces pa'i don snang ba mtha'
NK088(su)001:5115: yas kyi chos nyid gsal la ma g.yos pa ste
NK088(su)001:5116: / 'khor ba'i 'gro ba dang sa'i rig pa la
NK088(su)001:5117: ye grub pa nyid gsal bar byed pa'i phyir ro
NK088(su)001:5119: h+aa pradz+ny+aa d+h+rika gi don gyis shes rab kyi don
NK088(su)001:5120: ma bral bas bdag gzhan gyi bya ba rdzogs pa
NK088(su)001:5121: don yod grub pa'i chos nyid de gsal bar byed
NK088(su)001:5122: pa'o // de la sngags ni lam pas bskyed pa dang /
NK088(su)001:5123: sgra don dang ldan pas mtshon pa'i dbang ste 'chad par 'gyur ba yang sbyar ro //
NK088(su)001:5124: m+aum l+aam m+aam p+aam t+aam zhes pa lnga ni /
NK088(su)001:5125: sngags kyi don gyis chos kyi dbyings ma skyes pa
NK088(su)001:5126: tshig las grol bas gang yang mi 'gog par khyab
NK088(su)001:5127: pa ni rdo rje dbyings kyi dbyings phyug ma'i chos
NK088(su)001:5128: nyid dang / sa nyid rang rig ma byung ma
NK088(su)001:5129: brlag ngo bo mi 'gyur bar gsal ba sangs spyan
NK088(su)001:5131: 'byung ba chu'i ngo bo de bzhin nyid yon tan
NK088(su)001:5132: 'phel 'grib med par 'byung ba m+aa ma k+aa'i chos
NK088(su)001:5133: nyid / 'byung ba me rang rig pa mtha' ma
NK088(su)001:5134: sgrib dag pa ste gos dkar mo'i chos nyid do
NK088(su)001:5135: nyid / // 'byung ba rlung gi de bzhin nyid
NK088(su)001:5136: kyi ngo bo mtshan nyid gang du'ang mi zin par
NK088(su)001:5137: skad cig la'ang 'gro don mi 'gog par mdzad pa
NK088(su)001:5138: dam tshig sgrol ma'i chos nyid dag pa lhun gyis
NK088(su)001:5140: h+r+aiht+r+aam k+sh+aim dz+aim zhes pa dag ni sems dpa' bzhi'i chos nyid do //
NK088(su)001:5141: spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung gi rigs 'dzin pa'i chos nyid do //
NK088(su)001:5142: nam mkha'i snying po nam mkha' dngos po go 'byed
NK088(su)001:5143: pa ltar yon tan ci'ang mi 'gog pa'i chos nyid
NK088(su)001:5144: do // sa'i snying po 'gro ba'i mig dag pa ste /
NK088(su)001:5145: me long lta bu'i ye shes kyi ngo bo ci'ang
NK088(su)001:5146: ma 'dres mi rtog par gsal ba'i chos nyid do
NK088(su)001:5147: // phyag na rdo rje gsang ba'i mthu stobs kyi
NK088(su)001:5148: bdag nyid pas gnod byed 'dul ba'i chos nyid do
NK088(su)001:5149: // // de dag ngo bo mi mthun pa bzhi'i
NK088(su)001:5150: char snang ba'i chos nyid yi ger snang bar byed
NK088(su)001:5151: // // pa'o // h'u t+r+aam h+r+aih+aamhzhesa pa dag rang
NK088(su)001:5152: rig pa ni ril lhun gyis rdzogs pa ma 'gag
NK088(su)001:5154: l+aa skye ste sgeg mo me long can gyi chos nyid do //
NK088(su)001:5155: rgyal ba'i yon tan sna tshogs rgyun med par snang ba m+aa l+ye phreng ba'i chos nyid do //
NK088(su)001:5156: chos kyi sgra dbyangs ji ltar 'dul bar ston pa g+airti glu dbyangs ma'i chos nyid do //
NK088(su)001:5157: phrin las sna tshogs kyis don mdzad pa n+airti gar bsgyur ma'i chos nyid do //
NK088(su)001:5158: me th+l+him h'u m+aum zhes pa /
NK088(su)001:5159: sngags kyi sgra don gyis tshad med bzhi dang sbyar te /
NK088(su)001:5160: thams cad gnyis su med par mkhyen pas 'byed pa'i
NK088(su)001:5161: phyogs ris med pas phan 'dogs pa byams pa'i chos
NK088(su)001:5162: nyid do // thugs rje chen pos zin pas skyob pa ni sgrib pa sel ba'i chos nyid do //
NK088(su)001:5163: thugs rje chen pos spyod yul dag pas don mdzad
NK088(su)001:5164: pa la 'gyod pa bral ba kun tu bzang po'i
NK088(su)001:5165: chos nyid do // ye shes chen po zug rngu
NK088(su)001:5166: bral bas mnyam pas 'dul ba 'jam dpal gyi chos
NK088(su)001:5167: chos nyid do // nyid do // d+h+au pu bam hohzhesa pa la sogs pa /
NK088(su)001:5168: d+h+au pe'i chos tshim par byed pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi cho 'phrul lo //
NK088(su)001:5169: push+pe'i chos nyid go bar byed pas dbang po'i cho 'phrul lo //
NK088(su)001:5170: +aa lo ke'i chos nyid gzhan la snang bar byed pas byin rlabs kyi cho 'phrul lo //
NK088(su)001:5171: gan+d+he'i chos nyid mnyes par byed pas mchod pa'i cho 'phrul lo //
NK088(su)001:5172: ya th+aa h+r+aihmh'u zhes pa la sogs pa sgo ba'i 'chad de /
NK088(su)001:5173: khro bo ya m+aan+ta krita gshed po ste //
NK088(su)001:5174: mtha' yi gshin rje 'joms pas stong nyid sgo la gnas //
NK088(su)001:5175: khro bo stobs chen stong 'dzin mtshan ma 'joms //
NK088(su)001:5176: de phyir mtshan med rnam thar sgo la gnas //
NK088(su)001:5177: rta mgrin re smon rtog pas tshol ba bcom //
NK088(su)001:5178: de phyir bdag rdzogs smon med sgo la gnas //
NK088(su)001:5179: bdud rtsi 'khyil ba yang dag zhen bgegs 'joms //
NK088(su)001:5180: de phyir bya med thabs chen rang bzhin 'od gsal sgo //
NK088(su)001:5181: ye nas dag la lhun rdzogs khro bo'i chos //
NK088(su)001:5182: yi ge chos nyid mdzad pas rig la snang bar byed //
NK088(su)001:5183: dzahmh'u bam hohzhesa pa la sogs pa /
NK088(su)001:5184: lcags kyu'i chos nyid sbyin pas 'gro ba 'dren pa'i sgo /
NK088(su)001:5185: zhags pa'i chos nyid snyan pa'i don brjod sgo mas las ngan 'ching //
NK088(su)001:5186: lcags sgrog chos nyid 'gro ba'i don spyod lag sdom sgo //
NK088(su)001:5187: dril bu'i chos nyid 'gro don mthun pas dga' byed sgo //
NK088(su)001:5188: bsdu ba rnam thar sgo bzhir yab yum brgyad rnams bzhugs //
NK088(su)001:5189: log skyon tshogs brgyad ye bcom bsrung ba'i ngo bor gnas //
NK088(su)001:5190: krem drum srum pram k+sham ye zhes pa la sogs pa /
NK088(su)001:5191: lha'i thub pa chos nyid thun mong ma yin pa'i
NK088(su)001:5192: byang chub kyi yan lag bdun gyi ngo bo ste
NK088(su)001:5193: rang bzhin zhi ba chen po'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:5194: lha min thub pa'i chos nyid stobs lnga ste rtsod pa lhur byed pa 'dul ba'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:5195: mi'i thub pa 'dod pa rang dga' sgom pas 'dul te dbang po lnga'i chos nyid do //
NK088(su)001:5196: byol song gi thub pa ma rig pa las chos
NK088(su)001:5197: nyid kyis bskyod par 'dul bas rdzu 'phrul rkang pa
NK088(su)001:5199: yi dwags thub pa 'dod pa spong bas 'bras bu
NK088(su)001:5200: mi 'byu bar 'dul bas yang dag par spong ba
NK088(su)001:5202: dmyal ba'i thub pa log lta 'thibs po dang sdug bsngal gyis myos pa sgrol bar 'dul ba ste /
NK088(su)001:5203: dran pa nye bar bzhag pa bzhi'i chos nyid do //
NK088(su)001:5204: b+h+aum ni stong pa chen po lhun gyis rdzogs pa'i gzhal yas khang gi chos nyid do //
NK088(su)001:5205: e wam ma ya zhes pa /
NK088(su)001:5206: e ni drag po'i las te /
NK088(su)001:5208: ma ni rgyas pa'i phrin las /
NK088(su)001:5210: yi ge bzhi dbyibs so sos las bzhi bstan /
NK088(su)001:5211: de nyid ye nas gnas pa yi ger snang /
NK088(su)001:5212: shwa ni shwa sa ni'i sgras gnas phyi nang du snang ba'i chos nyid do //
NK088(su)001:5213: d+ha ni d+harma d+h+aa tu ste chos kyi 'byung gnas b+ha ga'o //
NK088(su)001:5214: ma ni ma nu ste dran zhing rig pa'i ting nge 'dzin to //
NK088(su)001:5215: h+aa ni h+ya hi kye ste spyan drangs pa'i chos so //
NK088(su)001:5216: pra ni phra ba ste 'od zer spro ba'i chos so //
NK088(su)001:5217: k+sha ni k+sha ya ta na mtha' zad pa ste dkyil 'khor bsdu ba'i las zin to //
NK088(su)001:5218: dz+ny+aa ni dz+ny+aa na ste shes pa brgyad do //
NK088(su)001:5219: he ni he tu na rgyu'o //
NK088(su)001:5220: s+w+aam ni swa b+h+aa ba na 'bras bu'o //
NK088(su)001:5221: tham ni tham ka na rkyen bzhi'o //
NK088(su)001:5222: ska ni skan+d+ha na phung po lnga'o //
NK088(su)001:5223: kra ni karma na las so //
NK088(su)001:5224: pam ni pam ka la na nag po'o //
NK088(su)001:5225: tra ni tra ni ye na dkar po'o //
NK088(su)001:5226: de dag ni lha'i sku mdog gi chos kyi zur 'dren pa'o //
NK088(su)001:5227: +amo ni rang grub pa'i chos nyid rnam pa snang ba'i sgo'o //
NK088(su)001:5228: zhes pa dag yon tan rdzogs pa'i phyir rang bzhin grub pa'i yi ge'i chos nyid do //
NK088(su)001:5229: h'u ni chos ril gyi 'byung gnas rang gi byang chub sems so //
NK088(su)001:5230: m+aum ni chos nyid kyi phyi mo ma bslad pa ma bcos te /
NK088(su)001:5231: sngags gsum dkyil 'khor gsum gyi don to //
NK088(su)001:5233: de dag ni yi ge'i cho 'phrul /
NK088(su)001:5234: zhes pa dag don bshad pa dag yi ger snang bar byas pa'o //
NK088(su)001:5238: zhes pa la sogs pa de'i gtan tshigs ni yi ge sgras drangs pa dang /
NK088(su)001:5240: bsgyur bas mtshon nas ji bzhin pa mthong ba'o //
NK088(su)001:5241: de mi brjed pa thob pa dang /
NK088(su)001:5246: dgongs pa'i ting nge 'dzin gsal ba dang /
NK088(su)001:5248: der ma zad 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i don brda ril gsal bar gyur /
NK088(su)001:5249: des mtshon nas ji lta ba nyid mthong shes par byed do //
NK088(su)001:5250: de dag gi 'chad pa la ltos nas bcos pa'i cho 'phrul lo //
NK088(su)001:5252: gang ma bcos par snang ba'i cho 'phrul gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:5254: zhes pa la sogs pa gang gzhi ji bzhin pa
NK088(su)001:5255: las cir snang yang cir srid mtshan nyid ma nges
NK088(su)001:5256: par de kho na nyid kyi rang bzhin bstan pa'o
NK088(su)001:5257: // de yang rgyas pa gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:5258: chos can mtshan mar snang ba'i rang bzhin rnams //
NK088(su)001:5259: zhes pa la sogs pa chos dang ldan pa'i chos
NK088(su)001:5260: ji snyed pa zhen blo ngo la snang ba dag
NK088(su)001:5261: /rang bzhin rgyal po phru gu las nor ba 'dra
NK088(su)001:5262: ba tsam gyi phyir chos nyid kyi ngang nyid do
NK088(su)001:5263: // sems gsum dang ldan pa'i 'gro ba nyid ni /
NK088(su)001:5264: snang ba nyid na nyi ma'i zer bzhin pas /
NK088(su)001:5265: rang rig pa mtha' bral ba nyid brda dang tha
NK088(su)001:5266: snyad mang po brtags pa la snang ba dag cir
NK088(su)001:5268: snang ba med de ye ma bcos pa'i ngang nyid do //
NK088(su)001:5269: 'gro ba rigs lnga'i sdug bsngal gyi rgyu 'du byed
NK088(su)001:5270: lnga 'khrul pa la snang ba dag spu ma barjesa
NK088(su)001:5271: mdog ma bsgyur bzos ma byas par ye shes lnga
NK088(su)001:5272: nyid do // khams gsum gyi gzhi nyon mongs pa
NK088(su)001:5273: gsum nyid ye nas ngo bo snang la med pas
NK088(su)001:5274: nyid do // sku gsum mo // 'gro ba'i lus
NK088(su)001:5275: smin dper yul zhes gsungs sems la rtog pa gnyis
NK088(su)001:5276: su snang ba nyid ye dbyings ye shes kyi bdag
NK088(su)001:5278: 'gro ba'i yul dang shes pa ci snang ba nyid
NK088(su)001:5279: ther zug rgyun med pas thabs shes kyi bdag nyid
NK088(su)001:5280: dbyer med pa'o // mtshan nyid mi rtag pa'i lnga
NK088(su)001:5281: phung nyid ma spangs par rnam par grol ba zag
NK088(su)001:5282: pa med pa'i phung po lngar sangs rgyas so //
NK088(su)001:5283: 'khor ba rang rgyud ka nas bral bas de nyid mya ngan las 'das pa'o //
NK088(su)001:5284: snod bcud ril rang rig rang snang bas rgyal ba'i
NK088(su)001:5285: dkyil 'khor gcig du ma las grol ba nyid do
NK088(su)001:5286: // dngos po gnyis pa ril ye lhun gyis grub pa ma bslad ji bzhin pa nyid do //
NK088(su)001:5287: de dag ni byed pa med par rang snang la
NK088(su)001:5288: ma nges pas ji bzhin pa nyid kyis phyir ming
NK088(su)001:5290: snang ba'ang snang ba yod pa'i phyogs las btags pa'i
NK088(su)001:5291: tha snyad de ngo bo ni snang mi snang las
NK088(su)001:5292: grol to // de 'khor gyi rig pa la brjod pa dang 'dra bar mjal ba'ang zhing ril du'o //
NK088(su)001:5293: des kyang byung tshul gyi don gsal bar 'grel to //
NK088(su)001:5294: chos snang ba'i cho 'phrul bstan pa'i le'u ste /
NK088(su)001:5295: zhes pa le'u mtshan gyi don rgyas par bsdus pa'o //
NK088(su)001:5296: bcu bdun pa 'grel ba'o ////lang ka'i bdag po /
NK088(su)001:5297: kun brjod pa'i cho 'phrul gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:5298: zhes pa la sogs pa nges tshig nye bar brjod de /
NK088(su)001:5299: chos ril gyi spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid gnyis
NK088(su)001:5300: byang chub sems su ma 'dres rdzogs pa nyid de
NK088(su)001:5301: / de kho na nyid ji bzhin pa yin pa'i
NK088(su)001:5302: don gzhi ji ltar bar sgro skur med par tshig
NK088(su)001:5303: tu phyung bas nges tshig 'grub ste /
NK088(su)001:5304: de ni lam ma nor ba yang dag pa nyid du nges par gzhag go //
NK088(su)001:5305: sku dang gsung thugs rang bzhin yang //
NK088(su)001:5306: zhes pa dag don de las mya ngan las 'das pa'i 'bras bu gzhan na med par bstan pa'o //
NK088(su)001:5307: dngos po 'khrul pa dang lam dang 'bras bu ji
NK088(su)001:5308: snyed brjod pa'i dang po bstan pa gang snyam pa
NK088(su)001:5309: la / gti mug ma 'dres kun nas rmongs //
NK088(su)001:5310: zhes pa ma rig pa rang gi mtshan nyid chos
NK088(su)001:5311: gzhan dang ma 'dres par gsal ba ni dus dang
NK088(su)001:5312: skabs ril du don mi shes te /
NK088(su)001:5314: yongs su rdzogs pas stong bdag med //
NK088(su)001:5315: zhes pa de nyid ye rig pa byang chub sems
NK088(su)001:5316: nyid pas ye shes gsal ba'i ngo bo la ma
NK088(su)001:5317: rig pa ma spangs ma grub pas brtags pa'i bdag
NK088(su)001:5318: bral ba ni spyi'i mtshan nyid do //
NK088(su)001:5319: de nyid ma 'dres yongs rdzogs na //
NK088(su)001:5320: zhes pa dag spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid la snyegs pas nges par gzung ba ni /
NK088(su)001:5321: de gnyis so sor snang ba ma 'gag bzhin du
NK088(su)001:5322: ngo bo bstan du yang med pas mtha' gnyis las
NK088(su)001:5323: grol ba'i phyir / de min pa la yin par
NK088(su)001:5324: ma byas par gti mug chos thams cad kyi ji
NK088(su)001:5325: bzhin yin par sangs rgyas pas na /
NK088(su)001:5326: ma bcos de bzhin nyid kho na //
NK088(su)001:5327: zhes gsungs te 'chad pa dag rjes su mthun par sbyar ro //
NK088(su)001:5328: de bas na dug lnga ye shes lnga las rigs lngar 'char ba'o //
NK088(su)001:5329: zhe sdang ma 'dres mnar sems pas //
NK088(su)001:5330: zhes pa la sogs pa nas 'khor ba'i mtshan nyid bcu bzhi brdar 'jal sla'o //
NK088(su)001:5331: ma chags ma 'dres gtong bas nyid //
NK088(su)001:5332: zhes pa la sogs pa lam gyi chos rnams te /
NK088(su)001:5338: shes rab ste pha rol tu phyin pa drug dang /
NK088(su)001:5339: gzugs khams kyi bsam gtan bzhi dang /
NK088(su)001:5341: gzugs med pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa bzhi dang /
NK088(su)001:5342: 'di rtsa bar med khams gnyis kyi nyon mongs pa kun dang /
NK088(su)001:5343: rnam par thar pa gsum dang /
NK088(su)001:5348: gzungs kyi sgo lnga brgya dang /
NK088(su)001:5349: ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo 'bum phrag dang /
NK088(su)001:5350: sangs rgyas kyi chos ma 'dres pa bco brgyad dang /
NK088(su)001:5351: mngon par shes pa chen po drug dang /
NK088(su)001:5352: chos ji snyed pa rnams kyi spyi dang rang gi
NK088(su)001:5353: mtshan nyid dang sbyar te lam du phal che ba
NK088(su)001:5355: ye shes kun mkhyen skye 'gag med //
NK088(su)001:5356: zhes pa la sogs pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes dang /
NK088(su)001:5359: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku dang /
NK088(su)001:5361: rgyal ba'i yon tan thams cad dang //
NK088(su)001:5362: drug gi rang spyi bshad pa'o //
NK088(su)001:5363: chos kun brjod pa'i cho 'phrul las //
NK088(su)001:5364: zhes pa la sogs pa skabs 'dir ril ma bcos pa de kho na nyid du gsal ba ni /
NK088(su)001:5366: rgyal ba dang rgyal tshab kyi yul du gyur pa 'di rdo rje theg pa chen po'i don te /
NK088(su)001:5367: theg pa dang rgyal ba dbyer med pa'i don to //
NK088(su)001:5368: des na 'di la spyod pa dag kyang bya ba
NK088(su)001:5369: med pa'i thabs kyis ched du ma bsgrod par non
NK088(su)001:5370: to // rdo rje rnal 'byor mi ldan na //
NK088(su)001:5371: zhes pa dag don 'di ma rig pa'i skyon no //
NK088(su)001:5372: de bas rnal 'byor chen po yis //
NK088(su)001:5373: zhes pa la sogs pa 'di'i lugs spyod pa pas cho 'phrul bzhi'i don bshad pa dang /
NK088(su)001:5374: 'chad pa'ang 'da' bar mi bya bar bka' stsal pa
NK088(su)001:5375: ni lta ba ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa
NK088(su)001:5376: las gzhan gol bar mi lta ba'o //
NK088(su)001:5377: de gsungs pas spyod yul dag ste don gdeng du gyur to //
NK088(su)001:5378: kun brjod pa'i cho 'phrul gyi le'u ste bco brgyad pa bkrol ba'o ////lang ka'i bdag po /
NK088(su)001:5379: de la rjes su bstan pa'i cho 'phrul gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:5380: zhes pa la sogs pa rjes su mthun par 'chad de /
NK088(su)001:5381: de kho na nyid mi g.yo ba'i rjes su tha
NK088(su)001:5382: snyad ril gsang bar 'grel ba'i phyir de nye bar
NK088(su)001:5383: bstan pa ni / ji snyed pa thams cad ji bzhin nyid du yongs su /
NK088(su)001:5384: zhes pa dag 'chad pa'i tha snyad ril rang rig
NK088(su)001:5385: pa ma bcos pa nyid du ma btsal bar byung
NK088(su)001:5386: thebs pa la sel med par bstan pa'o //
NK088(su)001:5387: de'i tshul nye bar bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:5388: de nyid mi g.yo nam mkha' la //
NK088(su)001:5389: g.yo rdul tha snyad ji snyed pa //
NK088(su)001:5390: zhes pa dag de bzhin nyid kyi ngo bo rang gi sems nyid kyi nam mkha' la /
NK088(su)001:5391: snod bcud kyi dngos po cir snang yang ngo bo
NK088(su)001:5392: med par gtod 'dzin bral ba'i ye shes mi g.yo
NK088(su)001:5393: ba gting dpag dka' ba chen po las tha snyad
NK088(su)001:5394: gzhan pa rang bzhin gyi gtan tshigs kyis smin dper
NK088(su)001:5395: ming 'grub par rnam pa mi 'gyur bar bstan pa
NK088(su)001:5396: nyid yid bzhin gyi nor bu la ril rdzogs pa'o
NK088(su)001:5397: // de na dman dang sems dpa' dag /ces pa
NK088(su)001:5398: la sogs pas rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor la snyegs
NK088(su)001:5400: de'i ngang rgyu nyan rang sogs la gang zag rgyud
NK088(su)001:5401: tha dad gsang don rtogs pa'i skal ba med pas
NK088(su)001:5403: gsang sngags la sangs rgyas sems can lam gyi tha
NK088(su)001:5404: snyad so so ba med de byang chub snying po'i
NK088(su)001:5405: ngang nyid do // nges pa'i dgongs pa'i nyams rnyed nas //
NK088(su)001:5406: zhes pa dag de la rtogs par byar yang med
NK088(su)001:5407: pa'i don cir yang ma rnyed par rig pas gdeng
NK088(su)001:5408: rnyed nas gzhan don du gsang sngags sems kyi dkyil
NK088(su)001:5409: 'khor 'od gsal ba ma bslad ma byas ma nor
NK088(su)001:5410: gting dpag dka' ba'i don sku dang ye shes lnga
NK088(su)001:5411: lnga la sogs pa'i ya mtshan rdzogs pa'i shugs kyis
NK088(su)001:5412: byang chub snying por lhun gyis mnyam pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:5413: ston pa dang 'khor snang la mi phyed pa nyid
NK088(su)001:5414: la nyid kyis bka' stsal ba'i don nye bar gsal
NK088(su)001:5415: bar ston pa'i tshig gsang ba pas bka' stsal to
NK088(su)001:5416: // 'grel lugs khas blangs pa gang snyam pa la /
NK088(su)001:5417: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK088(su)001:5418: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK088(su)001:5419: zhes pa skyes pa dang ma skyes pa gnyis su
NK088(su)001:5420: med pa'i ngo bo ni shin tu ngam e ma'o
NK088(su)001:5421: zhing ya mtshan ngo mtshar pa ste /
NK088(su)001:5422: rmad kyi chos gnyis med kyi don de ni lhun gyis rdzogs pa nyid yin pas /
NK088(su)001:5423: theg pa gzhan las khyad par du 'phags pa /
NK088(su)001:5424: kun gyi spyod yul ma yin zhing /
NK088(su)001:5425: rgyal ba ma lus pa tshogs gnyis kyi mnga' bdag
NK088(su)001:5426: rnams kyi yang thugs gsang kyi brnag par bya ba
NK088(su)001:5427: shin tu blos reg cing ngo bo gzung dka' ba
NK088(su)001:5428: ste / 'chad pa ril yang rang rang skabs kyi
NK088(su)001:5429: don dang sbyar zhing rjes su mthun par 'grel to
NK088(su)001:5430: ste / // ngo bo gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:5431: skye ba med las thams cad skyes //
NK088(su)001:5432: skyes pa nyid na'ang skye ba med //
NK088(su)001:5433: ces pa byang chub sems kyi ngo bo ni /
NK088(su)001:5434: ye gang du'ang snang ba skye ba med las /
NK088(su)001:5435: med pa nyid ril thams cad skyes gyi 'byung gnas pas /
NK088(su)001:5436: skyes pa nyid na'ang cir yang snang zhing 'byung ba ste 'gog rgyu yang med la /
NK088(su)001:5437: de tsam na ngo bo nyid rnam pa thams cad pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:5438: 'di skye ba med 'drar mi zin pas mtha' grol ba ni gsang sngags nyid do //
NK088(su)001:5439: de bas 'chad pa'i shwa lo ka sum cu rtsa
NK088(su)001:5440: bdun gnyis yang gsang sngags 'og ma gnyis kyi don
NK088(su)001:5441: skabs skabs su phyed mar 'grel to //
NK088(su)001:5442: 'gag pa med pa thams cad 'gag /ces pa dag
NK088(su)001:5443: ni ye ji bzhin pa ni skad cig ma med
NK088(su)001:5444: pas skye shi'i rgyun grol ba'i bdag nyid de lhun
NK088(su)001:5445: gyis gong ma rdzogs pas rim gyi gzhi yin pa'i
NK088(su)001:5447: zhen blo la 'gag pa'i chos su yang snang la /
NK088(su)001:5448: de tsam na ngo bo cir yang ma zin pas
NK088(su)001:5449: 'gag bdo ba la 'gag pa ma grub pa ni
NK088(su)001:5450: nam mkha'i ri bong can lta bu'o //
NK088(su)001:5451: dmigs pa med las thams cad dmigs //
NK088(su)001:5452: zhes pa snying po byang chub yul dang bral ba la /
NK088(su)001:5453: zhen pa gnyis pa gnas pa'i sa pa dang 'gro ba ni yul du 'dzin par snang ba ste /
NK088(su)001:5454: dmigs bdo tsam na ngo bo spyod pa dang yul
NK088(su)001:5455: dbyer med pas gtod 'dzin dang ngang gis bral ba'o
NK088(su)001:5456: // mi gnas pa las thams cad gnas //
NK088(su)001:5457: zhes pa ngag de kho na nyid snang ba dam
NK088(su)001:5458: pa ni rten dang rten can gyi ngo bo ma
NK088(su)001:5459: grub pa'o // 'byung khungs lta bu'i don ni rjes su mthun te 'chad pa la'ang sbyar ro //
NK088(su)001:5460: zhen pa dag la yod pa ltar snang ste /
NK088(su)001:5461: de nyid kyi dus na ngo bo 'di 'dra bar med pa'o //
NK088(su)001:5462: de ni rma bya'i mdongs rtse lta bu'o //
NK088(su)001:5464: zhes pa dag gsang sngags kyis ngo bo ni ril
NK088(su)001:5465: la bsnums pas phan tshun yan man med pa las
NK088(su)001:5466: / brtags pa'i rtog pa can dag la 'gro 'ong du snang la /
NK088(su)001:5467: de nyid na 'gro 'ong ma 'gags 'gro 'ong med pa'o //
NK088(su)001:5468: ma bcos ma bslad byas pa med //
NK088(su)001:5469: ces pa dag ni ye ji bzhin pa'i sems nyid
NK088(su)001:5470: sangs rgyas nyid ye gang du'ang ma g.yos pa la
NK088(su)001:5471: cir snang cing srid kyang mtha' ma spangs bral ba'i
NK088(su)001:5472: phyir dri ma dang rdul ye med pa'o //
NK088(su)001:5473: rang bzhin med pa'i rang bzhin las //
NK088(su)001:5474: zhes pa dag brtags pa'i rang bzhin ye ngang gis
NK088(su)001:5475: bral ba'i ngo bo nyid la sdug bsngal ka nas
NK088(su)001:5476: dag pa'i ngo bor bzhugs pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:5477: gzhi rtsa med pa'i sems nyid ni //
NK088(su)001:5478: zhes pa dag rang rig pa la skyed pa dang
NK088(su)001:5479: rten gnas bral ba nyid las ril mi 'gog par
NK088(su)001:5480: ji ltar bsams pa ltar 'char ba'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:5481: stong pa ma yin mi stong min //
NK088(su)001:5482: zhes pa dag de kho na nyid ni 'bras bu
NK088(su)001:5483: bzhag kyang ngo bo mi rnyed pas mtha' grol ba
NK088(su)001:5484: la dbu ma'i tha snyad gdags gzhi dang yang bral
NK088(su)001:5485: ba'o // nges par brtags na rtag pa nyid //
NK088(su)001:5486: ces pa dag ye shes chen po rgyud du mi
NK088(su)001:5487: skye bas don de la dpyad pas dpyad na ngo
NK088(su)001:5489: de la zil gyis gnon pa dang 'joms pa po med pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:5490: nges par chad na chad pa med //
NK088(su)001:5491: ces pa dag don mi 'gyur ba'i ngo bo gang
NK088(su)001:5492: du'ang ma grub pa la chad pa bkol ba med
NK088(su)001:5493: pas log lta'i chad pa ngang gis dag go //
NK088(su)001:5494: chos so cog gi rang bzhin ni //
NK088(su)001:5495: zhes pa dag phyi nang du grags pa ril ye
NK088(su)001:5496: shes sems 'od gsal ba'i ngo bo yin pa'i phyir
NK088(su)001:5497: na rgyal ba'i go 'phang nyid do //
NK088(su)001:5499: sangs rgyas nyid las gzhan pa'i chos //
NK088(su)001:5500: zhes pa dag dper na rin po che gser gling dang 'dra ba'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:5501: dngos po gzhan pa zhig rgyal bas kyang mi rnyed de /
NK088(su)001:5502: ngo bo btsal du med par la bcad do //
NK088(su)001:5504: rab 'byams mtha' yas gang nas kyang //
NK088(su)001:5505: ces pa dag 'jig rten gyi khams mthar thug pa
NK088(su)001:5506: med pa gang nas kyang go 'phang mi gnyer te
NK088(su)001:5509: sems nyid rtogs pas sangs rgyas te //
NK088(su)001:5510: zhes pa dag sems kyi chos nyid bshad pa lta
NK088(su)001:5511: bu'i mtshan nyid go ba nyid go 'phang chen po
NK088(su)001:5512: yin pa'i phyir / srid gsum ye nas snying po nyid //
NK088(su)001:5513: ces pa dag 'di phyi bar ma do dang 'dod pa dang /
NK088(su)001:5515: gzugs med pa'i ngo bo phyi mo nas byang chub
NK088(su)001:5516: snying po yin pa la 'khrul pa'i log skyon ngang
NK088(su)001:5517: gis ma dmigs te rdzogs pa chen po nyid do
NK088(su)001:5518: // rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dbyings //
NK088(su)001:5519: zhes pa dag mnyam pa'i dbyings yon tan gyis bzhag
NK088(su)001:5520: pa las 'phral du 'bad rtsol med pa tshogs gnyis
NK088(su)001:5521: rdzogs pa'i ngo bor bzhugs pa'o //
NK088(su)001:5522: kun nas kun tu ngang bzang po //
NK088(su)001:5523: zhes pa la sogs pa snga phyir rig pa'i klong nyid kyi ma khyab pa med de /
NK088(su)001:5524: ngo bo med pa la skyon gyis rnam pa bral bas /
NK088(su)001:5525: ril gsang sngags ji bzhin pa ma yin pa med pa'o //
NK088(su)001:5526: snying po byang chub de nyid las //
NK088(su)001:5527: zhes pa dag ril byang chub snying por sangs rgyas pa la mtha'i skyon dag pa ni /
