NK088(su)001:5528: gser sa le sbram lta bu'o //
NK088(su)001:5529: 'o na 'khrul pa'i sems can 'byung ba'i snyad ci yod ce na /
NK088(su)001:5530: thams cad sangs rgyas yin pa la //
NK088(su)001:5531: zhes pa dag bshad pa'i gar yang sbas pa ma
NK088(su)001:5532: mthong ba'i don gyis yul du ma gyur bas brtag
NK088(su)001:5533: tu mi btub pas lhan ci skyes pa'i ma rig
NK088(su)001:5534: pa ste / dper mtshon rnon po rang gis rang mi chod pa lta bu'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:5535: 'o na de dag snying po byang chub la 'das sam zhe na /
NK088(su)001:5536: rtog pa nyid na rtog med phyir //
NK088(su)001:5537: zhes pa dag de ltar 'khrul cing 'dzin pa'i ngo bo nyid snang la med pa ni /
NK088(su)001:5538: bshad pa bzhin glo bur gyi mtshan nyid pas theg zug med de /
NK088(su)001:5539: dpe gser las byas pa'i rdzas bzhin snying po byang chub nyid do //
NK088(su)001:5540: kun gyi snying po byang chub la /
NK088(su)001:5541: zhes pa dag dngos po grags so cog gi rtsa ba chos kyi sku chen po ni /
NK088(su)001:5542: gdod nas rgyal ba'i dgongs pa 'bras bu'i bdag nyid la rgyu 'bras gnyis med do //
NK088(su)001:5544: rdo rje gsang ba'i snying po las //
NK088(su)001:5545: zhes pa dag btsal ba med pa ngang 'dus ma byas pa dang /
NK088(su)001:5548: 'joms pa'i ngo bo ni ye shes chen po'i ngo
NK088(su)001:5549: bo phra zhing zab pa ril gyi 'bras bu nyid
NK088(su)001:5550: de / de la ni don du gnyer ba dang /
NK088(su)001:5552: ye gnyis su med pa la de nyid kyis tha snyad bral ba'o //
NK088(su)001:5554: ye nyid 'bras bu dam pa la //
NK088(su)001:5555: zhes pa dag snying po byang chub ni tshogs las byas pa ma yin te /
NK088(su)001:5556: thog ma nas de nyid kyi ngo bor bzhugs pas
NK088(su)001:5557: ming gi bla dwags tsam yang bral ba la rnyed
NK088(su)001:5558: par bya ba'i chos ma dmigs so //
NK088(su)001:5559: gsang sngags gsang ba'i snying po 'di //
NK088(su)001:5560: zhes pa dag de kho na nyid shin tu mthong dka' ba 'bras bu'i ngo bo de nyid ni /
NK088(su)001:5561: rgyal ba dang 'gro ba gnyis ka'i ngo bo der gcig pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:5562: de'i phyir lam gyi bstan pa ril gyi ngo bo yang /
NK088(su)001:5563: 'di'i mtshan gyi rnam grangs snang bas yon tan cha re mtshon pa las btags te /
NK088(su)001:5565: 'dus pa gsang ba rmad byung ba //
NK088(su)001:5566: zhes pa dag gnyis su med pa'i byang chub sems su bshad pa ltar /
NK088(su)001:5567: ril ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa ngo bo phra zhing zab pa ni don gyi mchog ste /
NK088(su)001:5568: de kho na nyid rdo rje rnam gsum grub mtha'i bcud nyid de /
NK088(su)001:5569: gsang ba 'dus pa yang yin te /
NK088(su)001:5571: gsang ba zhes su bstan pa ni //
NK088(su)001:5572: sku gsung thugs ni rnam pa gsum //
NK088(su)001:5575: gsang ba dam pa'i snying po 'di //
NK088(su)001:5576: zhes pa dag shin tu dpag par dka' ba ni /
NK088(su)001:5577: mi bstan par bya'o cog gi mchog yin te /
NK088(su)001:5578: chos thams cad kyi srog yin pas shin tu ma
NK088(su)001:5579: nor ba'i don ni rgyal ba kun gyi dgongs pa'i
NK088(su)001:5580: zhe phugs yin pas gsang ba'i snying po de kho
NK088(su)001:5581: na nyid nges pa zhes kyang bya'o //
NK088(su)001:5582: zla ba gsang ba las byung ba //
NK088(su)001:5583: zhes pa dag rang rig pa ni mtha' dri ma dwangs pa la /
NK088(su)001:5584: ngo bo ma bsgrib pa nyid bsam dka' ste /
NK088(su)001:5585: de nyid ma 'gags ma 'dres par rang shar ba
NK088(su)001:5586: la spros mtha' grol bas mu mtha' mi rnyed pa'i
NK088(su)001:5587: ngo bo bas zla gsang thig le'o //
NK088(su)001:5588: sangs rgyas kun dang mnyam sbyor bas //
NK088(su)001:5589: zhes pa dag ye ji bzhin pa dang /
NK088(su)001:5590: rgyud dag pa'i rgyal ba ril dang ngo bo mi phyed pas /
NK088(su)001:5591: rgyal ba'i gzugs sku ril dpe ji lta bar ma
NK088(su)001:5592: 'dres la rdzogs pas gcig dang du ma med pa'i
NK088(su)001:5593: phyir sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor ro //
NK088(su)001:5594: snang srid sgyu ma'i ye shes las //
NK088(su)001:5595: zhes pa dag snod bcud sgyu ma ltar snang la
NK088(su)001:5596: med pa ye shes chen po'i ngo bor lhun grub
NK088(su)001:5597: las 'gro 'ong med par ji snyed pa'i chos su
NK088(su)001:5598: 'phrul te / byung ba nyid dbyer med pa'i phyir sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'o //
NK088(su)001:5599: sprul pa thabs kyi d+r+wa ba las //
NK088(su)001:5600: zhes pa dag rang rig pa cir yang snang ba ni thabs chen po ste /
NK088(su)001:5601: de yod med la sogs pa ril ma spangs par
NK088(su)001:5602: de nyid du mdzad pa'i phyir thabs kyi zhags pa'o
NK088(su)001:5603: // bya bral rnam grol mthun 'jug spyod //
NK088(su)001:5604: zhes pa dag lhun gyis grub pas bya rtsol bral ba'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:5605: dbyings dang ye shes kyi ngo bo 'ching ba dang bral ba'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:5606: chags sdang can la spyod pa mthun 'jug tu snang
NK088(su)001:5607: ba'i phyir rgyud gsum ste bskyed rdzogs gsum yin no
NK088(su)001:5609: ngo bo nyid la bya byed ma dmigs par sku
NK088(su)001:5610: phyag rgya mtshan ma dang mtshan ma med pa'i rnal
NK088(su)001:5611: 'byor rnam gnyis su shar bas cha mthun 'tshams par
NK088(su)001:5614: sbyor thabs bya ba las rgyud 'byung //
NK088(su)001:5615: zhes pa ngang gis mi g.yo zhi ba'i ting nge 'dzin du zhugs pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:5617: bya ba'i las su shar bas rgyud gsum ste /
NK088(su)001:5622: sgo gsum sa la 'god pa'i thabs kyi bya ba'i
NK088(su)001:5623: las gtsor byed pa'i ngo bo yang shar bas kri
NK088(su)001:5624: ya'o // khyad par gyi dbang du tshig snga phyi gnyis ka kri yar sbyar ro //
NK088(su)001:5626: lhag par mthong dang zhi bar gnas //
NK088(su)001:5627: zhes pa dag kun rdzob sgyu ma dang /
NK088(su)001:5628: don dam pa'i ngo bo gnyis ma 'gags par shar ba dang /
NK088(su)001:5629: de nyid ji lta ba la bying rgod la sogs pa med de mi bsgul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:5630: mtha' bzhi dang spros mtha' brgyad ye bral bas /
NK088(su)001:5631: don dam pa ma skyes pa dbu ma'i mtha' las
NK088(su)001:5632: nges par 'byung ba'i theg pa'ang yin te der yang
NK088(su)001:5633: shar ro // sde mdzod dam pa'i bka' lung rnams //
NK088(su)001:5634: zhes pa dag sde snod gsum dang /
NK088(su)001:5636: mdo sngags kyi bka' lung ji snyed pa'i ngo bor bzhugs pas /
NK088(su)001:5637: de dag gis don rdzogs pa dang /
NK088(su)001:5638: phyogs cha mtshon pa'i bka' tshigs dang /
NK088(su)001:5639: yi ger yang byin gyis brlabs shar nas /
NK088(su)001:5640: de nyid mngon sum dang rjes dpag dang /
NK088(su)001:5641: rim gyis dang cig car dang /
NK088(su)001:5645: mdor bstan pa kun 'dis nor du rung bar byed pa'o //
NK088(su)001:5646: des bka' thams cad kyang snying po byang chub nyid do //
NK088(su)001:5648: gdul bya'i yul ni ji snyed pa'i //
NK088(su)001:5649: zhes pa dag gdul bya'i bsam pa rab 'bring tha
NK088(su)001:5650: ma ji snyed pa'i don du rgyud dang 'tshams pa'i
NK088(su)001:5651: bstan pa de snyed kyi sgo /
NK088(su)001:5652: de ltar lhun gyis grub pa'i phyir snang du btub pa'o //
NK088(su)001:5653: de bas na rgyud 'di lta bu nyid kyang ji ltar snang yang /
NK088(su)001:5654: ngo bo'i dbang du ston pa nyag gcig gi byin rlabs snang ba'o //
NK088(su)001:5656: bka' yi rab brgyud dam pa nyid //
NK088(su)001:5657: zhes pa dag che ba bdun dang ldan pa'i rgyud
NK088(su)001:5658: don dang tshig khyad par can du gdul bya la
NK088(su)001:5659: snang ba'i dgongs pa 'dus pa chos kyi me long
NK088(su)001:5660: du nye bar bzung ba ni /
NK088(su)001:5661: mdo sngags kyi bka' de snyed bsgrags pa'i mchog ste /
NK088(su)001:5662: snying po byang chub nyid ji lta ba'i sgro skur med par tshig tu snang ba 'di nyid do //
NK088(su)001:5663: dam par brjod pa'i gtan tshigs gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:5664: ji bzhin pa yi de kho na //
NK088(su)001:5665: zhes pa dag snying po byang chub kyi ngo bo
NK088(su)001:5666: rgyud 'di las bka' de snyed 'byung ba'i rgyu yi
NK088(su)001:5667: snying po ste / bstan pa thams cad kyi 'byung
NK088(su)001:5668: gnas yin pa'i che ba dang ldan pa'i phyir ro
NK088(su)001:5669: snying po ste / // zab mo 'dus pa'i gtan tshigs 'di //
NK088(su)001:5670: zhes pa dag don tshigs gting dpag dka' ba 'dir
NK088(su)001:5671: ril 'dus pa'i rgyud 'di rtogs pa las rgyal ba
NK088(su)001:5672: ril 'byung bas / bde bar gshegs pa thams cad kyi yum yin no //
NK088(su)001:5673: rnam pa sna tshogs snang bar mdzad //
NK088(su)001:5674: ces pa dag rgyal ba'i sku yon tan ji snyed
NK088(su)001:5675: pa mi 'gog par mdzad pas rnam par snang mdzad
NK088(su)001:5676: do // ngo bo gnyen po bral ba'i thugs la g.yo ba med pas rdo rje sems dapa'o //
NK088(su)001:5677: rgyal ba'i gsung grags mtha' ji snyed gsal bar shar bas snang ba mtha' yas so //
NK088(su)001:5678: mtshan dang dpe byad dang dngos grub ji snyed pa'i
NK088(su)001:5679: yon tan gyi 'byung gnas dpe ji lta bar 'byung
NK088(su)001:5681: gdul bya ril gyi don ma btsal rdzogs pas don yod grub pa'am gdon mi za ba'o //
NK088(su)001:5682: rang byung gi ye shes las dang ngo bos rdo
NK088(su)001:5683: rje ste ye shes ril gyi rtsa ba de nyid
NK088(su)001:5684: las / de nyid kyi byin rlabs ye shes lnga'i ngo bor shar bas /
NK088(su)001:5685: rang byung nyid dang drug gi phyir rigs kyang rjes su mthun te /
NK088(su)001:5686: de bas na rgyal ba'i yum smin dper yul yang du'ang mngon no //
NK088(su)001:5687: bsam med bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i //
NK088(su)001:5688: dpag med brgyad khri bzhi stong sgo //
NK088(su)001:5689: zhes pa la sogs pa chos kyi sgo mo grangs las 'das pa yang /
NK088(su)001:5690: mdor nyon mongs pa 'dul dbang gis stong phrag brgyad cur bstan cing grags pa yin yang /
NK088(su)001:5691: don ma nor bar nges pa'i chos rgyud 'di ste dngos gsang ba mchog gi theg pa'o //
NK088(su)001:5692: 'dir rigs ma nges ma rtogs pa sha thang bas rtsol ba'i bar du 'jug sgo yang mang la /
NK088(su)001:5693: 'di dang 'phrad na mdo 'jug sgo gcig po 'di
NK088(su)001:5694: las lhag pa med pa'i phyir sgo kun nas bsdur
NK088(su)001:5696: brjod dang bstan pa'i rnam grangs kun //
NK088(su)001:5699: brda mtshon brgyud nas don chen po rtogs par byed pa'i sgron me dang 'dra'o //
NK088(su)001:5700: des na dngos po ril rang rig pa kho na bas gsang sngags nyid yin pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:5701: ril der lung bstan pas shes bya de kho na nyid do //
NK088(su)001:5702: de dag de nyid ngang grol na //
NK088(su)001:5703: zhes pa la sogs pa snyegs pas sdud pa ni dngos po ril lo //
NK088(su)001:5704: de rnams de bzhin nyid kyi ngang du byas pa med par grol te /
NK088(su)001:5705: ngo bo ma dmigs pa nyid dngos po de kho na nyid gsang ba'i don no //
NK088(su)001:5706: de ji lta ba de ltar rig pa nyid sangs rgyas yin pas /
NK088(su)001:5707: de la spyod yul ril bde ba chen po'i klong du gsal bas /
NK088(su)001:5708: snying po de kho na nyid du 'dzin pa'am ched du byas pa nyid kyang med do //
NK088(su)001:5709: de lta bas na rang rig pa bde ba chen po la /
NK088(su)001:5710: rang bzhin bde ba chen po ma bsdus par rdzogs pa'i ye shes dus phyed par gsal lo //
NK088(su)001:5711: ma lus mtha' dag thig le rgya //
NK088(su)001:5712: zhes pa la sogs pa 'khor ba dang mya ngan
NK088(su)001:5713: las 'das pa kun byang chub sems kyi rgyas thebs
NK088(su)001:5714: pa'i phyir / ma grub pa grub par byar yang med pas 'bad pa dang bral te /
NK088(su)001:5715: rgyu dang 'bras bu la snga phyi dang bral lo //
NK088(su)001:5716: de bas rang gi blo ji bzhin pa'i rjes su'ang mi 'brang nges par mi 'dzin te /
NK088(su)001:5717: de kho na nyid bdag nyid pas dmigs byar med pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:5719: zhes pa la sogs pa ji bzhin pa las gol
NK088(su)001:5720: ba'i mun sprul gyi blo can rnams kyis rgyu yis
NK088(su)001:5721: grub par rtog cing 'bras bu la nges par 'dzin
NK088(su)001:5722: pas / lam de dag rang gi rtog pa med
NK088(su)001:5723: bzhin snang ba'i sgyu ma'i dbang gis rgyu 'bras dbyer
NK088(su)001:5724: med pa la so sor mthong bas /
NK088(su)001:5725: nor ba'i rtog pas ma grol bar gyur to //
NK088(su)001:5726: de bas na gang la'ang rag ma lus pa'i ye
NK088(su)001:5727: shes chen po dus gsum du bdal khyab chen por
NK088(su)001:5729: ye ma byas ma bslad pa'i ngo bo'am bdag nyid las gol ba ma dmigs par la bazla'o //
NK088(su)001:5730: thams cad byang chub snying po bas //
NK088(su)001:5731: zhes pa dag ril chos nyid la bya rgyu med
NK088(su)001:5732: pas de nyid mngon du byed pa'i 'du byed pa'i
NK088(su)001:5733: 'du shes kyang med pa ni gnas pa chen po
NK088(su)001:5735: snang srid 'khor ba'i kha brgyud kyang //
NK088(su)001:5738: ji ga 'khor bar ji snyed du btsal kyang don
NK088(su)001:5739: de nyid las gzhan du ma 'ongs pa'i phyir dang
NK088(su)001:5740: / rgyal ba'i zhing bgrod kyang snying po'i don las ma 'phags so //
NK088(su)001:5741: dpag med rgyal ba'i sku bskrun yang /
NK088(su)001:5742: zhes pa dag rgyal ba ril gyi sku bskrun te
NK088(su)001:5743: grub kyang de khon na nyid las mang zhing rags
NK088(su)001:5744: pa med la / sdug bsngal can gyi 'gro ba
NK088(su)001:5745: ji snyed du shar yang nyung ba dang phra ba
NK088(su)001:5746: pa med la / med do // de'i don rnams ji lta bu zhe na /
NK088(su)001:5747: skye bzhi rgyud lngar gang snang ba //
NK088(su)001:5748: sangs rgyas nyid de ye shes sku //
NK088(su)001:5749: zhes pa la sogs pa rgyud lnga skye bzhi nyid ye chos sku chen por grub pa la /
NK088(su)001:5750: dngos po gnyis pa'i rnam pa med de /
NK088(su)001:5751: bde ba chen po'i lhun la bzhugs pa la skye
NK088(su)001:5752: shi 'pho 'gyur mi mnga' ba'i phyir 'phel 'grib bral
NK088(su)001:5753: lo // bya ba med pa'i dkyil 'khor gsum //
NK088(su)001:5754: zhes pa dag h'u m+aum +amo gyi don gsum dkyil 'khor gsum du shar ba de /
NK088(su)001:5755: 'phral du lam pas ma byas pas thob zin pa'i phyir yang de bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:5756: bsgrub pa 'di la gang gnas pa //
NK088(su)001:5757: zhes pa dag gang gis bsgrub tu med par shes
NK088(su)001:5758: pa nyid gang yang don du mi gnyer ba ni
NK088(su)001:5759: / bsgrub pa chen po la gnas pa ste /
NK088(su)001:5760: de ni thabs chen po zhes bya ste lam gyi mchog yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:5761: de ni las khyad par can yin te /
NK088(su)001:5762: de ltar thag chod pa la rtsol ba'i mtha' las kyang mi 'gog ste /
NK088(su)001:5763: byas pa la byas 'dzin med pas don chen po las nyams pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:5764: rgyal ba kun gyi snying po nyid //
NK088(su)001:5765: ces pa la sogs pa gang bdud kyi dpung las
NK088(su)001:5766: che bar gyur ba ril gyi 'bras bu lhun gyis
NK088(su)001:5767: grub par mnga' ba rang snang ba ni /
NK088(su)001:5768: mdo sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga ste /
NK088(su)001:5769: ya mtshan chen po de dag ji bzhin pa las byung ba med par 'char ro //
NK088(su)001:5770: rgyal ba rgya mtsho rnams kyi yum //
NK088(su)001:5771: zhes pa la sogs pa de'i phyir rgyal ba ril bskyed par byed do //
NK088(su)001:5772: de bas longs spyod sprul pa ril ngang chen po las snang ba'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:5773: rtsa ba chen po de bzhin nyid kyi ye shes
NK088(su)001:5774: ye mtha' thams cad bral ba'i ngo bor bzhugs pa
NK088(su)001:5775: las / rgyal ba'i gdung 'tshob pa'i 'gro ba chen po rnams kyi don ched du /
NK088(su)001:5776: don de nyid kyi dbang gis ston pa nyid la nyid 'chad ces bya'o //
NK088(su)001:5777: zhi gnas mi rtog mkha' khyab la //
NK088(su)001:5778: zhes pa dag ji bzhin pa'i nam mkha' gang du'ang
NK088(su)001:5779: mi g.yo mi 'dzin pa ni rang bzhin gyi zhi
NK088(su)001:5780: gnas so // rang rig pa'i mngon sum ye gsal
NK088(su)001:5781: ba chen po bshad pa bzhin ma 'dres la rdzogs
NK088(su)001:5782: par gsal ba ni ngo bo nyid kyi lhag mthong
NK088(su)001:5783: gnas so // ste / de ltar so sor ma
NK088(su)001:5784: 'dres rdzogs pa'i ngo bo gcig dang du ma yod
NK088(su)001:5785: med rtag chad ma spangs grol ba'i don du gsal
NK088(su)001:5786: ba las nges par 'grel zhes bsnyad do //
NK088(su)001:5789: zhes pa la sogs pa tshig gis don 'grub pa'i ngo bo bstan pa'o //
NK088(su)001:5790: lang ka'i bdag po de ltar na /
NK088(su)001:5791: dgongs pa nges par 'grel de dag kyang /
NK088(su)001:5792: zhes pa la sogs pa bshad pa la snyegs pa'i don gyis rjes su mthun par ston pa ni /
NK088(su)001:5793: rang bzhin ji bzhin pa dang /
NK088(su)001:5796: nges don sel med pa ste cho 'phrul bzhi'i don bstan pa ste /
NK088(su)001:5797: gzhi lhun gyis grub pa las snang ba rdzu 'phrul gyi cho 'phrul dang /
NK088(su)001:5798: gdul bya don la 'jug pa'i phyir chos snang ba dang /
NK088(su)001:5799: don sbyor bas kun brjod pa'i dang /
NK088(su)001:5800: ji bzhin pa rtsa ba'i rjes su bstan pa dang bzhir shes par bya'o //
NK088(su)001:5801: zhes gdams ngag gi mdo bka' stsal pas 'khor rnams
NK088(su)001:5802: kyis de'i don rtogs te tha ma'i dbugs phyin par
NK088(su)001:5803: gyur to // gang yongs su rdzogs par 'grel ba'i
NK088(su)001:5804: le'u ste bcu dgu pa bkrol ba'o ////gtam rgyud brjod
NK088(su)001:5806: zhes pa dag snying po byang chub kyi ngo bo kun tu bzang pos /
NK088(su)001:5807: nyid la nyid 'grel pa 'dir gsang ba pas gtam rgyud du thos pa barjooda pa'i phyir lnga pa'o //
NK088(su)001:5809: lang ka'i mnga' bdag byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po des /
NK088(su)001:5811: zhes pa la sogs pa sdud pa pos ston pa
NK088(su)001:5812: la byung tshul drug pa dris pas sgra bzhin no
NK088(su)001:5813: // smras pa lang ka'i bdag po /
NK088(su)001:5814: gsang sngags 'byung 'byung ba'i rgyu gdul bya khyad par can /
NK088(su)001:5815: zhes pa la sogs pa lan du gdul bya las dang rtsal shin tu drag pas /
NK088(su)001:5816: khams gsum byang chub sems kyi sa bon rlag par byed pa /
NK088(su)001:5817: khro bo chen po dang cha lugs tshul mthun pa ni /
NK088(su)001:5818: las kyi khro bo'i ngo bo dang las dang cha lugs te /
NK088(su)001:5819: gdul bya la thugs rje 'byung ba'i dus su phyin te smin pa'o //
NK088(su)001:5820: de 'dul ba'i phyir rgyal ba rnams gnas chen po nyid du 'dus te /
NK088(su)001:5821: thub dka' dang dan phag 'chad pa bzhin gyur pa la bskul ba ni /
NK088(su)001:5822: spyir cha 'dra bas gcig dang du ma las grol gyis kyang /
NK088(su)001:5823: dang po 'dul ba'i dpon du gyur pa dang /
NK088(su)001:5824: g.yog yin pas khyad par gyi thugs rje 'byung ba'i yul dang gnyen por gyur pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:5825: de yang zhi ba'i zhing khams bkod pa'i sprul pa
NK088(su)001:5826: dang mnyam pa snyed rdul dang mnyam pas btul ba'i
NK088(su)001:5827: dus su / theg pa chen po 'di yang 'byung zhing grags so //
NK088(su)001:5830: gdul bya de gang las byung zhes pa dag lang kas ru dra'i rgyu rkyen dang /
NK088(su)001:5832: gsang ba'i rgyu ru ji ltar byung ba dang gsum dris pa'o //
NK088(su)001:5833: gsang ba'i bdag pos smras pa /
NK088(su)001:5834: zhes pa la sogs pa rgyu dris pa'i lan te /
NK088(su)001:5835: de yang rgyu sogs pa'i dus dang /
NK088(su)001:5837: de la lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu drag po la sogs pa'i dus gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:5839: dran pa bskal pa dpag tu med pa'i bskal pa
NK088(su)001:5840: dang bstan pa'i sgo nas slob dpon gyi yon tan
NK088(su)001:5842: zhes pa la sogs pa sgra ji bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:5844: dngos po bzhi kho nar spyad de /
NK088(su)001:5845: zhes pa la sogs pa de la rgyu nye bar bzung ba 'dir lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu dang /
NK088(su)001:5846: rkyen thun mong du gyur pa ste sbyor sgrol dang /
NK088(su)001:5849: tshig rtsub mo ste spyad par bya ba lnga dang /
NK088(su)001:5853: 'dod yon lnga ste lnga phrag bzhi dang dngos po
NK088(su)001:5854: la zhen te don ma go bar tshig gi rjes
NK088(su)001:5855: 'brangs pa ni ru dra thar pa nag po'o //
NK088(su)001:5856: de dag sgra ji bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:5857: de la rtsod pa chen por gyur to //
NK088(su)001:5858: zhes pa la sogs pa g.yog dang rtsod pa ni mtshams med sogs pa'i rgyu'o //
NK088(su)001:5859: de ltar ltangs bcad pas slob dpon la khros te song ba ni /
NK088(su)001:5860: mtshams med pa dang rtsa ba nyams pa ste de yang lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu dang rkyen no //
NK088(su)001:5861: de nas thar pa de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung gi sgo grangs mang zhing /
NK088(su)001:5862: zhes pa la sogs pa mtshungs par ldan pa'i rgyu
NK088(su)001:5863: lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pas bsgribs pas gsang
NK088(su)001:5864: ba'i don ma go ba ste gab pa'i gsang ba
NK088(su)001:5865: ma rtogs pa'o // gtan tshigs lung man ngag zab
NK088(su)001:5866: mos ma gzhal bar rang gi 'thad phyogs su drangs
NK088(su)001:5867: pas spyod pa log pa byed pa ni rkyen te
NK088(su)001:5869: de nas skye ba de 'phos par gyur te /
NK088(su)001:5870: skye ba de'i phyi ma la /
NK088(su)001:5871: zhes pa la sogs pa 'phos pa'i skye ba dang po ste thar pa tshe 'phos ma thag pa'o //
NK088(su)001:5873: skye bzhi rnam grangs ni skye ba brgyad pa yan
NK088(su)001:5874: chad la skye ba bzhi stong du don gyis brtsis
NK088(su)001:5875: pa'o // de ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK088(su)001:5878: bdun pa brgyad pa la grangs nges pa ma smos kyang /
NK088(su)001:5879: tha dad pa'i lus blangs ces pa dang /
NK088(su)001:5880: gong 'og gis sgra nges pas bartsi'o //
NK088(su)001:5881: skye ba dgu pa nas yang sos man chad skye ba dgu brgyud pa ni /
NK088(su)001:5882: 'gyod pa'i rgyus gyen du 'byung ba ste /
NK088(su)001:5883: skye ba 'bum phrag brgyad du brgyud pa'o //
NK088(su)001:5884: 'di dag ni las ma rdzogs pa rdzogs par byed pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:5885: skye ba brgyad yan chad du gyur te yongs su
NK088(su)001:5886: rdzogs par byed pa'i rkyen dang 'phen pa'i las zhes
NK088(su)001:5887: bya ste rgyu dang thun mong ngo //
NK088(su)001:5888: dmyal ba rnams ni 'bras bu gsum las rnam par smin pa'i 'bras bu'o //
NK088(su)001:5890: gang 'jig pa'i bskal pa mu ge dang /
NK088(su)001:5891: zhes pa la sogs pa bskal pa'i snyigs ma gsum
NK088(su)001:5892: du sdug bsngal myong ba ni myong ba rgyu mthun
NK088(su)001:5893: gyi 'bras bu'o // de dag las thar nas kyang /
NK088(su)001:5894: sha dang rus pa'i ched du gsod pa'i /
NK088(su)001:5895: zhes pa la sogs pa spyod pa rgyu mthun du rtogs te las ngan der yang sog go //
NK088(su)001:5896: de nas skye ba 'chad pa gsum sgra bzhin te dbang gi 'bras bur yang 'gyur ro //
NK088(su)001:5897: mdor skye lnga brgya bzhi stong brgyad dang lnga brgya
NK088(su)001:5898: dang gsum skye ba dmyal bar brgyud pa'i skye ba
NK088(su)001:5899: bcu rdo rje dmyal nas sha dang rus pa'i ched
NK088(su)001:5900: du gsod pa'i bar gcig la /
NK088(su)001:5901: tshe tshad bskal pa 'bum phrag dgu dang drug khri
NK088(su)001:5902: snyed du brgyud nas lang ka'i yul du skyes so
NK088(su)001:5903: // skye ba de'i phyi ma la yul skye ba'i lan btab pa'o //
NK088(su)001:5904: lang ka pur zhes bya ba /
NK088(su)001:5905: zhes pa la sogs pa 'dir rgyu mthun spyod pa'i
NK088(su)001:5906: 'bras bu rdzogs pa'i ru dra nyid de sgra ji
NK088(su)001:5907: bzhin no // dang por khro bor bsgom pa shes rab kyis ma yin pa dang /
NK088(su)001:5908: bka' log pa'i rgyu dngos su snang ba'i phyir te /
NK088(su)001:5909: 'jig rten gyi bdag po dbang can gdul dka' bar byung ngo //
NK088(su)001:5910: le'u nyi shu pa bkrol ba'o ////der skyes pa'i ngo
NK088(su)001:5911: bo dang rang skal gyi las kyi nus mthu gang
NK088(su)001:5912: zhe na / de nas yi dwags drag po de nga rgyal gyis gtum skad 'byin te /
NK088(su)001:5913: zhes pa la sogs pa ngo bo srin por gyur
NK088(su)001:5914: pas che ba'i nga rgyal sgrogs pa sgra bzhin no
NK088(su)001:5915: // de yi las dang nus mthu log lta can du gyur pa ni /
NK088(su)001:5916: de yi tshe 'gro ba rnams kyi /
NK088(su)001:5917: ces pa la sogs pa log lta brgyad la gnas shing /
NK088(su)001:5918: des dbang byas pas ltung ba'i 'bras bu dang bcas pa sgra ji bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:5919: de rgyas par bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:5920: 'das pa'i dus na sngon byung ba //
NK088(su)001:5921: bdag nyid chen po rtag pa yi //
NK088(su)001:5922: zhes pa la sogs pa bskal pa grangs med 'das
NK088(su)001:5923: pa'i sngon du bskal pa mngon dga' zhes bya bar
NK088(su)001:5924: / zhing khams kun dga' zhes bya ba la /
NK088(su)001:5925: sangs rgyas mi bskyod pa'i bstan pa la thar pa nag po byung ba des /
NK088(su)001:5926: rigs kyi bdag po chen po ngo bo mi 'gyur
NK088(su)001:5927: ba'i bka' gsang ji lta ba'i don ma go ba
NK088(su)001:5928: las byung ba'i 'gro ba srin po'i tshul ma tram
NK088(su)001:5929: ka dregs pa chen por byung ba ni /
NK088(su)001:5930: spyir 'khor ba thog ma dang tha ma med par byung na /
NK088(su)001:5931: skabs kyi cha gcig tu brtsi na gsang ba'i theg
NK088(su)001:5932: pa ma byung gi gong du bskal pa 'di nyid
NK088(su)001:5934: 'on kyang le'u rtsa bzhi pa las /
NK088(su)001:5935: 'das pa'i dus na sngon byung ltar //
NK088(su)001:5936: da lta dus 'di nyid du byung //
NK088(su)001:5937: ces 'byung bas 'di ni sngon gyi lo rgyus brjod pa'i dbang du na'o //
NK088(su)001:5938: ru dra byung ba'i dus de'i skabs na 'gro ba
NK088(su)001:5939: rnams kyi blo dregs pas brlabs nas stong pa nyi
NK088(su)001:5940: tshe bar lta'o // rgyu des rigs chad pa'i rdo rje'i dmyal bar skye'o //
NK088(su)001:5941: de las thar nas kyang thar pa'i skabs med de
NK088(su)001:5942: lta ba de nyid la dga' ste lung 'dogs so
NK088(su)001:5943: // mdor na dang po gol ba'i dus dang /
NK088(su)001:5945: dngos po byung ba'i dus dang /
NK088(su)001:5946: de'i rtsal gyis dge ba'i myu gu chad de ril
NK088(su)001:5947: log pa'i lam du drangs pas ltung ba dang bcas
NK088(su)001:5948: par 'chad pa rnams kyang sbyar te sgra ji bzhin
NK088(su)001:5949: no // skabs su bskal pa gsum gyis bskal bar gyur /
NK088(su)001:5950: ces pa rgyu le lo dman pa la sbyor ba dang /
NK088(su)001:5951: snyoms las dang gnyis kyis mi khom pa brgyad las thon nas kyang /
NK088(su)001:5952: bskal pa grangs med pa gsum gyis kyang yang dag pa'i lam las 'gyang bar gyur to //
NK088(su)001:5953: zhes thams cad du grags so //
NK088(su)001:5954: zhes pa zhing khams kun tu de ltar gyur bar grags so //
NK088(su)001:5955: mdor ru dra ni bcas pa'i ltung bar gyur pas 'gro ba rang bzhin gyis ltung bar gyur to //
NK088(su)001:5956: le'u nyi shu rtsa gcig pa bkrol ba'o ////de nas gsang ba'i bdag pos smras pa /
NK088(su)001:5957: zhes pa la sogs pa mi yi 'jig rten dbang
NK088(su)001:5958: du gyur pas nga rgyal gyis che ba'i rlom sems
NK088(su)001:5959: byed cing / che ba gzhan 'jig rten na su
NK088(su)001:5960: yod pa nyan cing phrag dog gang che ba dbang
NK088(su)001:5961: du bsdus la bdag gir bya'o snyam pas /
NK088(su)001:5962: skabs su lang ka'i bdag po dbang du sdud pas
NK088(su)001:5963: srin po'i gnas su babs pa ni sgra bzhin te
NK088(su)001:5964: / dngos dri ba gsum gyi tha ma gsang sngags
NK088(su)001:5965: 'byung ba'i rgyur ji ltar 'gyur ba'i lan du'ang 'gyur
NK088(su)001:5966: / te / kho yi las dang rtsal dang spyod
NK088(su)001:5967: drag pas 'dul byed gnyen po 'byung nges pa'i phyir
NK088(su)001:5968: / te / ro // ma tram ka ru ni'i gnas su babs te /
NK088(su)001:5969: yongs sad par dbang du bya ba brtsam nas dzams na /
NK088(su)001:5971: zha mar sod pa mi 'dra thub pa na /
NK088(su)001:5972: ru dras lha yi ded dpon dbang du bsdu bar
NK088(su)001:5973: nyams sad pas rnal mar thub pa mi 'dra nas
NK088(su)001:5974: / ru dra'i dbugs tsha grang 'thab pa las byung
NK088(su)001:5975: ba'i dbugs des btab pas nad kyi mtshon cha spros
NK088(su)001:5976: / nas / lha ma tri ka ru na'i lus la khyab ste /
NK088(su)001:5977: 'brum bus bsad pa'i ro dzam bu'i gling du bor ba la /
NK088(su)001:5978: dge gnas kyi yul o rgyan /
NK088(su)001:5980: bal po'i yul la sogs par mchod rten brgyad dngos
NK088(su)001:5981: grub brgyad dang ldan pa ma mo brgyad kyis srung
NK088(su)001:5984: zhes pa dang bru sha'i skad de /
NK088(su)001:5985: de dang byas so 'dus so song ngo zhes pa dang /
NK088(su)001:5987: skabs kyi don dang sbyar la sgra bshad do //
NK088(su)001:5988: dbang gi snying po h+r+aihzhesa dbang brgyud du nyan na /
NK088(su)001:5989: nyon cig /ru tra kho na nyid kyis tha'i kha brdab pa byas /
NK088(su)001:5990: zhes pa dag sngon rta mgrin h+r+aih'i sgra sgrogs shing nga dbang gis 'dul du 'ongs pa la /
NK088(su)001:5991: nga yis khyod kyis mi thul ba'i ngag smras zhes bya'o //
NK088(su)001:5992: jen no pa ni song ngo pa dang /
NK088(su)001:5993: rang gi gnas su log go zhes pa'o //
NK088(su)001:5994: gnam rim pa bcu bzhi na /
NK088(su)001:5995: zhes pa lung gis nyi shu rtsa gcig gi bcu bzhi pa na bzhugs pa'o //
NK088(su)001:5997: zhes pa rdo rje sems dpa' man chad nga yi dbang du bsdus la 'khor du bya'o //
NK088(su)001:6000: zhes pa dang po bskal pa kun dag'i dus kyi slob dpon no //
NK088(su)001:6002: zhes pa de yi tshe g.yog ste de gnyis snying po byang chub nyid dang /
NK088(su)001:6003: rgyal tshab skyes bu rdo rje sems dpa' zhes kyang bya /
NK088(su)001:6004: 'dzin pa'i bshad pa bskul ba dag khyad par 'di gnyis su brjod pa'ang don 'di'i dbang ngo //
NK088(su)001:6007: / 'dul ba'i gnyen po 'byung ba'i rgyu rkyen gyis snang bar byed pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:6008: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad snying po byang chub gang na bar 'dus nas /
NK088(su)001:6010: zhes pa rgyal ba ril de nyid ngo bo gcig pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:6012: thub dka' gzhon nu snying po byang chub na bzhugs pa la cha mthun gyis bskul ba'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:6013: sku mi snang bar mdzad de /
NK088(su)001:6014: de nyid thub dka' la snang bar byas zhes bsnyad do //
NK088(su)001:6015: de nyid kyi sgra de nyid la grags pa /
NK088(su)001:6016: ces pa rgyal ba ril dang thub dka' gzhon nu
NK088(su)001:6017: ngo bo tha mi dad pas nyid la nyid bskul
NK088(su)001:6018: ba'o // dngos zhing khams kyi 'gro ba'i rgyud du dag par ma byas pa dang /
NK088(su)001:6019: rgyal ba'i phrin las drag po'i las yan lag kun ma rdzogs pa dang /
NK088(su)001:6020: khro bo'i sku la sogs pa mang po da dung skyes bu thub dkas snang bar ma byas par /
NK088(su)001:6021: mngon par sangs rgya ba'i dus ma yin pas de gsum gyis shig pa'i phyir bskul ba'o //
NK088(su)001:6022: stong pa nyid de las 'di skad du grags so //
NK088(su)001:6023: zhes pa bskul ba gsan nas thub dkas rgyal ba
NK088(su)001:6024: ril la de dag gi dgongs pa dang dgos pa
NK088(su)001:6025: dris pa lta bu ste sgra ji bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:6026: yang thams cad kyis de kho na nyid las bskul ba /
NK088(su)001:6027: zhes pa rgyal ba ril snying por bzhugs pa las bskul ba'i thabs tshul gsum brjod pa'i thog ma /
NK088(su)001:6028: de bzhin nyid kyi sgo nas bskul ba la sogs pa lnga brjod pa'i yang /
NK088(su)001:6029: dang po de bzhin nyid du bzhugs pa las bzhengs par bskul te /
NK088(su)001:6030: stong nyid mi g.yo nam mkha' la //
NK088(su)001:6031: ces pa la sogs pa stong pa chen po 'byung
NK088(su)001:6032: 'jug dang bral bar gsal ba'i ngo bo yongs su
NK088(su)001:6033: mi g.yo ba'i chos sku chen po brnyes pa'i ngo
NK088(su)001:6034: bo la ni / cir yang gtod 'dzin med de
NK088(su)001:6035: ma bcos pa chen po'i ngang las thugs rje chen
NK088(su)001:6036: po'i dbang gis yang dag pa'i rtog pa brgyad cu
NK088(su)001:6037: rtsa gcig la sogs par snang bar mdzod ces bzhengs
NK088(su)001:6038: par bskul ba'i sgra byung ngo //
NK088(su)001:6040: de la yang skyes bu dam pa de nyid las 'di skad ces grag go //
NK088(su)001:6041: zhes pa la sogs pa skyes bu thub dka' chos
NK088(su)001:6042: nyid las snang ste bsgom pa dmigs su med pa'i
NK088(su)001:6043: ngang las snang bar bya'o bar don gyis bzhes pa'o
NK088(su)001:6044: // de ltar bskul ba rgyal ba ril gyi chos nyid las byung ba dang /
NK088(su)001:6045: lan skyes bu'i chos nyid las byung nas zhal gyis
NK088(su)001:6046: bzhes par 'chad pa'i ril yang rjes su sbyar ro
NK088(su)001:6047: // mi rtog ngang las brtag nyid du //
NK088(su)001:6048: zhes pa dag mi rtog pa nyid bla dwags dang
NK088(su)001:6049: yang bral ba chen po'i ngang las dus thams cad
NK088(su)001:6050: du zhen pas bzung bas stong par snang ba ni
NK088(su)001:6051: / ther zug pa'i rtog pa gzhi la dka' ba yin pas de bzhin nyid ma yin no //
NK088(su)001:6052: de bas na 'dir mi rtog pa chen po lhun
NK088(su)001:6053: gyis grub pa'i ngang ni brgyad cu rtsa gcig la
NK088(su)001:6054: sogs ril ma 'dres pa yongs su rdzogs pas rtog
NK088(su)001:6055: pa bskyed ci dgos par lan btab bo //
NK088(su)001:6056: rgyal ba'i ril las yang byung ba //
NK088(su)001:6057: nam mkha'i dbyings kyi snying po las //
NK088(su)001:6058: zhes pa la sogs pa ye shes chen po ma
NK088(su)001:6059: bsgrib ye gsal gyi ngo bor brdal ba ni ril
NK088(su)001:6060: gyi rtsa ba yin pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:6061: nga yi rang bzhin gyis ril zin pas thugs rje chen po ste /
NK088(su)001:6062: thams cad kyi don mdzad cing 'byung ba'i yum yin
NK088(su)001:6063: pas 'gro ba ji snyed rgyal ba'i rigs 'dzin pa
NK088(su)001:6064: dag thugs rjes smin par mdzod cig par kun tu
NK088(su)001:6065: snang gi ting nge 'dzin gyis bskul lo //
NK088(su)001:6066: kun 'byung kun gzhi chos nyid dbyings //
NK088(su)001:6067: zhes pa la sogs pa dngos po bzang ngan ril
NK088(su)001:6068: snang zhing rten pa'i chos thams cad kyi de bzhin
NK088(su)001:6069: nyid ngo bo ldan pa med pa ni /
NK088(su)001:6070: ye shes chen po nyid de thams cad la snums shing gsal ba la /
NK088(su)001:6071: 'di 'drar brjod pa dang bral te sangs rgyas sems
NK088(su)001:6072: can ril thugs rje chen po de las 'char ba'i
NK088(su)001:6073: yum ye nas yin pa la ched du bskyed ci
NK088(su)001:6075: tha dad rnam par snang mdzad na //
NK088(su)001:6076: zhes pa la sogs pa la rgyal ba'i sku mi
NK088(su)001:6077: mthun pa mang po 'gro ba la snang ba'i gzhi
NK088(su)001:6079: rgyal ba ril gsung yi ge'i ngo bo dang tha
NK088(su)001:6080: mi dad pa'i rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin yi ge dang
NK088(su)001:6081: gsung gi cho ga'i ngo bor gsal bar mdzod cig
NK088(su)001:6083: de nyid yi ge'i rang bzhin te //
NK088(su)001:6085: zhes pa dag chos rnams kyi de bzhin nyid ni yi ge lhun gyis grub pa'i ngo bo'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:6086: chos rnams kyi rang bzhin ma skyes pa nyid m+aum gyi ngo bor ye nas shar ro //
NK088(su)001:6087: rang rig pa nyid bshad pa bzhin pas ye shes
NK088(su)001:6088: ji snyed pa'i ngo bo yi ge h'u du gsal
NK088(su)001:6089: lo // bde bar gshegs pa'i ngo bo nyid yon
NK088(su)001:6090: tan ril gyi bdag nyid kyang yi ge'i rang bzhin
NK088(su)001:6091: pas +amo la sogs pa bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis ye
NK088(su)001:6092: lo // gsal lo // chos so cog yi ge'i
NK088(su)001:6093: ngo bo dang tha mi dad pas ril ma skyes
NK088(su)001:6094: pa'i phyir ye nas a'i ngo bor shar ba la
NK088(su)001:6095: 'phral du rgyu'i yi ge bskyed mi dgos pas lan
NK088(su)001:6096: lo // gsal lo // btab bo // rgyu dang gsung gi cho ga thun mong du 'grel to //
NK088(su)001:6097: ye shes pha rol phyin rdzogs pas //
NK088(su)001:6098: zhes pa la sogs pa rgyal ba'i thugs snying po
NK088(su)001:6099: byang chub la ye shes ril ma 'dres 'dus pas
NK088(su)001:6100: / de'i don lam pas rig cing rtogs par bya ba'i mtshon pa'i thabs su /
NK088(su)001:6101: thugs ye shes lnga la sogs pa'i rang rtags rdo
NK088(su)001:6102: rje 'khor lo la sogs par gsal bar rgyal ba
NK088(su)001:6104: skyes bus kyang thugs mtshon pa'i thugs mtshan dam tshig
NK088(su)001:6105: gi phyag rgya bskyed par mdzod cig ces thugs kyi
NK088(su)001:6108: sangs rgyas kun gyi ye shes ni //
NK088(su)001:6109: zhes pa la sogs pa zhen pa gnyis mthar spangs
NK088(su)001:6110: pas thams cad ma bkol ba'i ngo bor bzhugs pa
NK088(su)001:6112: dus gsum mi 'gyur bar mtshan ma'i rtog pa grol ba brnyes pa las 'byung ba'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:6113: ngo bo mi rtog pa'i ye shes 'dzin rtog gi mdud pa zhig pa chen po'o //
NK088(su)001:6114: de bas na rtog pa can la phyag rgya'i mtshan
NK088(su)001:6115: ma snang yang thugs ye grol ba la mtshon pa'i
NK088(su)001:6116: phyag rgya bskyed mi dgos par lan btab bo //
NK088(su)001:6117: stong nyid mi rtog me long las //
NK088(su)001:6118: zhes pa la sogs pa ji bzhin par rang gsal
NK088(su)001:6119: ba las longs spyod dang sprul pa 'char ba'ang dpe
NK088(su)001:6120: nam mkha'i 'ja' tshon dang 'dra ba'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:6121: mi g.yo ba'i chos sku chen po las khro bo'i
NK088(su)001:6122: phyag rgyar bzhengs su gsol zhes sku yongs su rdzogs
NK088(su)001:6123: pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis bskul lo //
NK088(su)001:6125: de bzhin nyid du mi dmigs kyang //
NK088(su)001:6126: zhes pa la sogs pa ye ma bcos pa'i ngang la gzugs sku'i rnam pa grol ba'o //
NK088(su)001:6127: mi dmigs pa'i mthun pa'i sku snang ba yang mi 'gog ste /
NK088(su)001:6128: de la mu mtha' med do //
NK088(su)001:6129: de bas na ngang chen po la gcig du ma
NK088(su)001:6130: bral tshul gyis lhun gyis grub pa'i gtan tshigs de'i
NK088(su)001:6131: phyir / zhi khro'i sku ma 'dres par gsal ba la skur bzhengs ci dgos zhes lan btab bo //
NK088(su)001:6132: de ltar bskul ba dang po des yongs su rdzogs par bskul bas /
NK088(su)001:6133: zhes pa dag dang po'i lngas sku rdzogs par gyis shig par bskul bas /
NK088(su)001:6134: don gyis zhal gyis bzhes nas bskul ba gsan pa'i
NK088(su)001:6135: phyir 'byung 'jug med par sku snang ba dpe dang
NK088(su)001:6137: sku de snang yang bskul ba'i sa la bzhes pa'i
NK088(su)001:6138: phyir rigs gang du'ang ma nges pas cir yang 'gyur
NK088(su)001:6140: de ltar sku snang bas zhing khams kyi gdul bya sbyong ba'i phyir lan dang po bstan to //
NK088(su)001:6141: lan gnyis pa bstan pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:6142: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bskul ba gnyis pa 'dis /
NK088(su)001:6143: zhes pa la sogs pa rgyal ba kun gyis yang
NK088(su)001:6144: skyes bu la bskul tshig nye bar bstan pa ni
NK088(su)001:6145: / rang bzhin rang byung ma bcos de bzhin nyid //
NK088(su)001:6146: ces pa dag chos rnams kyi de bzhin nyid ji
NK088(su)001:6147: bzhin pa'i mtha' gang du'ang snang ba med pa'i ngo
NK088(su)001:6148: bo nyid kyi sku la rtsol ba 'gro 'ong ma
NK088(su)001:6149: dmigs pa'o // de bas na dbyings dang ye shes
NK088(su)001:6150: gnyis su med pa'i chos kyi sku la de nyid
NK088(su)001:6151: kyis btags pa'ang med bzhin du ril gyi 'byung gnas
NK088(su)001:6152: ji ltar bsam pa bzhin snang ngo //
NK088(su)001:6153: de nyid la skye 'jig bral bas gnyen po bral
NK088(su)001:6154: ba'i rdo rje yang sku ste rtag pa chen por
NK088(su)001:6155: bzhugs so // de kho na nyid gdod ma nas
NK088(su)001:6156: ma bslad pas dgyes pa chen po'i thugs kyi ngo
NK088(su)001:6157: bo dus gsum du mi g.yo ma 'gags pa'i bcud
NK088(su)001:6158: chen por bzhugs pa ni gsang ba'i sku yang yin
NK088(su)001:6159: bzhugs so // no // de nyid chos kyi rgyal
NK088(su)001:6160: po rgyal ba ril gyi bshes gnyen ston pa por
NK088(su)001:6161: byung ba longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku'o //
NK088(su)001:6162: rgyal ba ril gyi btsan po nyid thams cad du 'dul bzhin snang bas sprul pa'i sku'o //
NK088(su)001:6163: de lta bu sku lnga po ma lus pa'i ngo
NK088(su)001:6164: bor bzhugs la mi rtog ma 'gags pa chen po
NK088(su)001:6165: khyod khro bo ji snyed 'byung ba'i khro bo chen
NK088(su)001:6166: po yab yum du mdzod cig pa ni thub dka'
NK088(su)001:6167: gong du bzhengs nas sku ma nges pa la nges
NK088(su)001:6168: par bskul ba'o // rigs drug la so sor bskul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:6169: skyes bu nyid la rigs drug don mdzad pa'i tshul
NK088(su)001:6170: gyis bskul ba ni spyi dang khyad par gyi dbang
NK088(su)001:6171: ste / de thun mong du bstan pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:6172: gang dag byang chub snying po mtshungs pa yi //
NK088(su)001:6173: rang dag dbyings zhes pa la sogs pa rigs kyi
NK088(su)001:6174: bdag po la bskul ba dang de'i tshul nas skyes
NK088(su)001:6176: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams snying po byang chub tu
NK088(su)001:6177: gcig pas rang bzhin rnam par dag pa'i ngang las
NK088(su)001:6178: bskyed pa med pa'i sems nyid du bzhugs kyang gnas
NK088(su)001:6179: tha dad par dus thog mar rgyal ba ril gyis
NK088(su)001:6180: grong khyer gsum ma spangs bral nas 'bras bu chen
NK088(su)001:6181: po brnyes pa'i tshe skye 'jig mi mnga' ba'i sku
NK088(su)001:6182: mchog las 'gro ba mang po'i don du gsung yi
NK088(su)001:6183: ge tha dad par snang bar mdzad nas don mdzad
NK088(su)001:6184: cing yi ge de las kyang sku'i dkyil 'khor byung
NK088(su)001:6185: ste thugs ye shes rang snang ba'i sras sprul pa
NK088(su)001:6186: ji snyed pa'i dbus na gtso bo khro bo'i sku
NK088(su)001:6187: phyag rgyar bstan nas dpyang thag chad pa'i gdung ba'i
NK088(su)001:6188: sa bon dag par mdzod cig ces bskul te spyi
NK088(su)001:6189: dbang du rgyal ba ril la bskul bar yang 'chad
NK088(su)001:6190: do // khyad par gyi dbang du lam 'debs pa'i
NK088(su)001:6191: tshul gyis rigs kyi bdag po dang rgyal ba ji
NK088(su)001:6192: snyed pas de ltar mdzad pa ltar skyes bu khyod
NK088(su)001:6193: khro bo'i sprul pa'i 'khor tshogs dang bcas par byung
NK088(su)001:6194: nas gdug pa can gyi las sbyang du gsol ces
NK088(su)001:6195: bskul bar sbyar te 'chad pa dag kyang rjes su
NK088(su)001:6196: do // bsnyad do // gang du dang po rdo rje snying po ni //
NK088(su)001:6197: khams gsum nas byung bde chen lhun gyis grub //
NK088(su)001:6198: gtum thung gdug pa thabs kyis grol mdzad phyir //
NK088(su)001:6199: zhes pa la sogs pa rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs pa rigs lnga bskul ba ste /
NK088(su)001:6200: gnas dus gang du thog mar rdo rje sems dpa'
NK088(su)001:6201: dang snang mdzad dang 'byung ldan dang 'od dpag med
NK088(su)001:6202: dang gdod mi za ba dang lngas khams gsum gyi
NK088(su)001:6203: sa bon zad par bton nas mngon par rdzogs par
NK088(su)001:6204: sangs rgyas pa'i 'bras bu lnga brnyes nas nyon mongs
NK088(su)001:6205: dug lngas 'ching ba'i gdul bya so sor btul ba'i
NK088(su)001:6206: phyir dgongs pa lngas so sor yi ger snang ba
NK088(su)001:6207: las khro bo'i skur byung ste so so'i 'khor dang
NK088(su)001:6208: sprul pa'i gtso bor mdzad nas bzhugs pa khyod dang
NK088(su)001:6209: po byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed pa'i smon lam
NK088(su)001:6210: dang da lta'i thugs dam gyi dbang rigs lnga he
NK088(su)001:6211: ru ka lnga ru bzhengs su gsol zhes bskul lo
NK088(su)001:6212: // gang du dang po'i tshig ni skyes bu ma bskul ba'i gtan tshigs su 'gyur ro //
NK088(su)001:6213: sngon gyi thugs dam smon lam ni rang rang la bskul ba'i gnyer te /
NK088(su)001:6214: de'i phyir thun mong du bstan to //
NK088(su)001:6215: bskul ba'i yon tan ni gsan nas skur snang ba ste /
NK088(su)001:6216: zhes bskul ba gnyis pa dang ces pa sgra bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:6217: de ltar ye shes kyi sku snang bas rgyal ba'i
NK088(su)001:6218: mdzad pa phrin las mdzad par gyur pas lan gcig
NK088(su)001:6220: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis bskul ba gsum pa 'dis /
NK088(su)001:6221: zhes pa lan tha ma'i phyir te /
NK088(su)001:6222: khro bo'i lha'i sku phyag rgya chen po rigs nges pa'i longs spyod chen por bskul lo //
NK088(su)001:6223: de bzhin nyid du gshegs pa khyod //
NK088(su)001:6224: 'jig rten mngon rdzogs rgyas mdzod la //
NK088(su)001:6225: zhes pa la sogs pa snying po byang chub nyid
NK088(su)001:6226: du son pa'i skyes bu khyod ces nges par gzung
NK088(su)001:6227: ba'i phyir thub dka' rdo rje snying por bskul bas
NK088(su)001:6228: 'thad do // de ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK088(su)001:6229: 'chad pa'i kye ma la sogs pa dang rtsa lnga
NK088(su)001:6230: pa las thub dka' rdo rje snying po las sprul
NK088(su)001:6232: 'on kyang skabs mthun pa nges pa gzung ba las
NK088(su)001:6233: rgyal ba gzhan dang tha dad par mi lta ste
NK088(su)001:6234: gdul bya'i snang ba tsam mo //
NK088(su)001:6235: de lta bu khyod zhing khams su dbang po mngon
NK088(su)001:6236: du 'tshang rgya ba'i bya ba byos la de las
NK088(su)001:6237: 'gro ba'i don du sku shar bar bskul lo //
NK088(su)001:6238: 'jig rten khams ni dpag med du //
NK088(su)001:6239: zhes pa zhing khams mang pa ra rgyal ba mang
NK088(su)001:6240: po'i sprul pas 'gro don mdzad pa ltar don gyis
NK088(su)001:6242: khams gsum 'khor ba'i nad pa la //
NK088(su)001:6243: zhes pa la sogs pa la sgra ji bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:6244: rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i skyes bu nyid //
NK088(su)001:6245: ces pa dag 'bras bu lhun gyis grub pa khyod
NK088(su)001:6246: snying po byang chub kyi ngang las mi g.yo bar
NK088(su)001:6247: sprul pa'i 'od kyis ma rig pa sol cig par
NK088(su)001:6248: bskul to // kye ma skyes bu don grub pa //
NK088(su)001:6249: bya ba byas shing byed pa byas //
NK088(su)001:6250: zhes pa 'bras bu chen po brnyes pa la ngo mtshar ba dang ldan pas /
NK088(su)001:6251: rdo rje snying po bsgrub bya ril chub pa bdag
NK088(su)001:6252: gzhan gyi bya byed zin pa srid lam gyi rtsol
NK088(su)001:6253: ba'i gdung ba dang phral ba snga ma'i rgyal ba'i
NK088(su)001:6254: rjes su don srid chen po brnyes la khyod dus
NK088(su)001:6255: 'dir dregs pa gdul ba'i dus la bab bo zhes
NK088(su)001:6256: pa'o // gtsang ma'i gnas mchog 'og min gyi //
NK088(su)001:6257: zhes pa khyad par gyi sgras 'jig rten gyi 'og
NK088(su)001:6258: min las khyad par du gyur par 'og min chen
NK088(su)001:6259: por rigs kyi bdag po longs spyod chen por gshegs
NK088(su)001:6260: te rgyal ba'i snying po byang chub na bzhugs pa
NK088(su)001:6261: ril bskul ba khyod kyis mdzod cig ces bskul lo
NK088(su)001:6262: // 'dis sku tha dad 'dul bzhin snang bar byas
NK088(su)001:6263: nas lam zhing khams sbyor ba rdzogs par 'gyur bas
NK088(su)001:6264: // lan tha ma'o // rnam pa bskul bas /
NK088(su)001:6265: ji lta ji ltar sprin mthong nas //
NK088(su)001:6266: zhes pa la sogs pa bskul bas bzhengs pa'i tshul
NK088(su)001:6267: dpe dang bcas pa sgra bzhin te 'gro 'ong dang
NK088(su)001:6269: rdo rje snying po skyes bu de longs spyod chen
NK088(su)001:6270: por smon lam dang thugs dam gyi dbang gis bzhengs
NK088(su)001:6271: so // gang gi cho 'phrul bskul ba'i le'u ni
NK088(su)001:6272: skyes bu rdo rje snying po'i cho 'phrul gyis shig
NK088(su)001:6273: so // par bskul ba'o // le'u nyi shu gsum
NK088(su)001:6274: pa bkrol ba'o ////de nas chos kyi rgyal po rdzogs
NK088(su)001:6275: longs spyod pa de rdo rje gong byed yongs su
NK088(su)001:6276: bsdu ba'i mtshan ma mdzad pas rmad du byung bas
NK088(su)001:6277: ston pa mchog ril gyi bdag po tshogs gnyis dang
NK088(su)001:6278: dngos po gnyis la dmigs par btang ba chen po
NK088(su)001:6279: so // par bskul ba'o // des / brda ni bka' bgros la spyan drangs pa'i phyir te /
NK088(su)001:6280: sa ma dzah'i sgras thugs dam bskul zhing phyag g.yas g.yon bkyed pa dang /
NK088(su)001:6281: bsnol ba'i se gol ni 'gyed sdud kyi mtshan ma ste /
NK088(su)001:6282: phyag rgya de mdzad pas stug po bkod pa nas rgyal ba ril byon te /
NK088(su)001:6283: gdul ba'i bka' bgros mdzad do //
NK088(su)001:6285: zhes pa spyan drangs pa dang byon pa'i skabs su'o //
NK088(su)001:6286: zhing khams so so'i rgyal bas bka' bgros gsungs pa so sor bstan pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:6287: sangs rgyas snying rjes yongs su rol pa'i tshogs kyis /
NK088(su)001:6288: zhes pa 'jig rten khams gdung ba sel ba bzhugs
NK088(su)001:6289: pa'i rgyal ba rnams gsung mtshungs par bgros pa ni
NK088(su)001:6290: / kye kye sangs rgyas rnam pa mang po'i tshogs //
NK088(su)001:6291: zhes pa la sogs pa rgyal ba rnams 'bod pa dang /
NK088(su)001:6292: gdul bya'i ngo bo dang mtshan nyid ci 'dra ba'i rgyu 'bras bstan pa dang /
NK088(su)001:6293: de'i spyod yul gzhan la gnod pa dang /
NK088(su)001:6295: bka' bgros kyis gdul bar 'grel to //
NK088(su)001:6296: de bzhin du nyon mongs pa lnga'i 'chad pa rnams kyang rjes su mthun no //
NK088(su)001:6297: dngos po bzhi'i bstan pa mdzod //
NK088(su)001:6298: zhes pa 'khor ba'i dngos po bzhi bshad pa dag
NK088(su)001:6299: 'dir spang du med de spyad pas 'dul bar mdzod
NK088(su)001:6300: ces bka' 'dun thag chod de gdul bar mthun no
NK088(su)001:6301: // 'dus pa chen po rnam pa bgros pa'i /
NK088(su)001:6302: zhes pa chos kyi mthong ba'i gnas su byon pa
NK088(su)001:6303: ril gyis bka' bgros pa'i don bstan pa'i le'u nyi
NK088(su)001:6304: shu bzhi pa bkrol ba'o ////de ltar 'dus pa chen
NK088(su)001:6305: po bka' bgros yongs su chad nas las rnam bzhi
NK088(su)001:6306: gang gis 'dul ba'i skabs la bab par /
NK088(su)001:6307: zhes pa bka' bgros chod pas gdul ba'i phrin las
NK088(su)001:6308: la 'jug pa'i phyir rtog pa ni dgos ched do
NK088(su)001:6309: // thub dka' gzhon nu rdo rje snying por /
NK088(su)001:6310: zhes pa dag dge slong des snying po byang chub
NK088(su)001:6311: tu son pa'i mtshan te 'dir thugs dam gyi dbang
NK088(su)001:6312: gis khyad par gyi gnyen por gyur pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:6313: de'i byin rlabs las sh+aakya thub pa snang ba la
NK088(su)001:6314: rgyal bas bskul te ru dra'i 'khor ba'i dngos po
NK088(su)001:6315: bzhis shes rgyud sreg pa de bden tshig gis zlog
NK088(su)001:6318: zhes pa sh+aakya thub pas dregs pa'i 'khor du snang
NK088(su)001:6319: bar byas nas bden tshig 'jam pas khos mi thul
NK088(su)001:6320: ba'i gtam byas pa sgra bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:6321: bdud kyi dngos po bzhis yongs su nyams pas gtsang ma'i rigs /
NK088(su)001:6322: zhes pa spyi'i dbang du bdud kyi mda' dang mtshon cha dang /
NK088(su)001:6323: ngag rtsub mo dang bu mos bslu ba'o //
NK088(su)001:6324: 'dir dngos po bzhi po kun gyis spang bya nyid do //
NK088(su)001:6325: de dag gi spyod pa sh+aakya thub pa la btang
NK088(su)001:6326: bas rgyal ba dri ma med pa rnams dngos po
NK088(su)001:6327: ngan pa de la thugs rtogs nas slar bzhud pa
NK088(su)001:6328: ltar ru dra'i ngo la snang ngo //
NK088(su)001:6329: don des kyang zhi rgyas kyis mi 'dul bar mkhyen te 'chad do //
NK088(su)001:6330: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis /
NK088(su)001:6331: zhes pa la sogs pa rgyal ba rnams kyi thugs
NK088(su)001:6332: rje mnga' ba spyan gzigs la bskul te rgyal ba'i
NK088(su)001:6333: gsung pad+ma'i rigs 'tshob cing 'dzin pa chos kyi rgyal
NK088(su)001:6334: po gsung gi don ji snyed pa mnga' ba'i rdo
NK088(su)001:6335: rje chos gdul bya ril spyan gyis bya ra dang
NK088(su)001:6336: so mdzad cing gzigs pa khyod kyis /
NK088(su)001:6337: sa bon h+r+aihls ngag gi dbang phyug dbang gi khro bo rta mgrin shin tu rngam par byung bas /
NK088(su)001:6338: dregs pa thul gnon zhes bskul ba ni don gyis gsan te /
NK088(su)001:6339: rta mgrin gyi sku mi bzad pas rta skad ha ha sogs bsgrags pas /
NK088(su)001:6340: 'khor phru ma spa zhum zhing bag 'khums pa la sogs pa sgra ji bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:6344: zhes pa ngo bo ste bshad pa'ang zhi rgyas kyi mi 'dul ba 'dis yid ches so //
NK088(su)001:6345: yongs su zhams pa sgra ji bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:6346: ru dras snga ma bzhin mi gtsang rta mgrin bas
NK088(su)001:6347: log snyam kyang khro bos gdul phyir thim du han
NK088(su)001:6348: ces pa / kho'i khong du mid nas kha zas su mdzad de byon no //
NK088(su)001:6349: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa des dbu kho na'i gtsug tu phyungs /
NK088(su)001:6350: zhes pa dag de nas lus brgyangs te btul ba sgra bzhin te /
NK088(su)001:6351: las gang gis 'dul brtags pa la /
NK088(su)001:6352: dngos su btul ba ni ma yin no //
NK088(su)001:6353: de la ma bzod pas dbang drag gis 'dul bar mkhyen no //
NK088(su)001:6354: dbang drag gis 'dul bar bka' bgros nges par bcad pa'i mdo /
NK088(su)001:6355: zhes pa bka' le'u gong ma dang 'di gnyis bgros lnga ba pa ni /
NK088(su)001:6356: gong ma ni spyir 'dul ba tsam dang /
NK088(su)001:6357: 'di ni khyad par gyi las gang gis 'dul ba'i phyir mi 'gal lo //
NK088(su)001:6358: de so so gsungs pa nye bar bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:6359: de bzhin gshegs pa rnam grol spyod pa'i tshogs //
NK088(su)001:6360: zhes pa mtshan de nyid du nges pa ji snyed pa'o //
NK088(su)001:6361: shin tu 'gog pas zhi ba la //
NK088(su)001:6362: zhes pa la sogs pa zhing khams 'dir dregs pa dang 'gro ba'i tshul 'di ltar 'gyur te /
NK088(su)001:6364: rab tu yang dag pa'i sems 'gog pas mun pa'i zhi bar gdul bya chud pa la /
NK088(su)001:6365: khro bos btul yang chad la de las mi snang ste /
NK088(su)001:6366: mnyam pa'i ngang las zhi ba chen por mdzod cig pa'o //
NK088(su)001:6368: nyan thos 'gog pa zhi ba phyogs gcig pas srid
NK088(su)001:6369: pa'i rtse mo man chad kyi sa bon spongs nus
NK088(su)001:6370: na / mtha' gnyis pos zhi ba'i rnal 'byor chen pos kyang smos kyang ci dgos te /
NK088(su)001:6371: byang chub kyi chu bo skams pa dag thugs rjes spang ba dang /
NK088(su)001:6372: shin tu 'gog pa bslang ba'i dgos ched du /
NK088(su)001:6373: chos nyid kyi ngang las cir yang snang ba'i mdzad
NK088(su)001:6374: pas don byos shig par rgyal ba rnams la bka'
NK088(su)001:6375: bgros pa'o // 'di dag gdul bya dang /
NK088(su)001:6377: cha mthun du mdzod cig par bskul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:6378: mdzad pas don grub par the tshom mi za ba dang /
NK088(su)001:6379: dgos ched dang mthun pa'i yon tan snang bas mdzod
NK088(su)001:6380: cig par bskul bar 'chad par dag kyang rjes su
NK088(su)001:6381: 'grel to // stong nyid tshul can stong pas kyang //
NK088(su)001:6382: zhes pa mdo sde stong pas sngags kyis stong pa
NK088(su)001:6383: chen po ni ma mthong yang cha 'dra ba'i nus
NK088(su)001:6384: pa'o // ngo bo mi 'gyur ba'i tshogs /
NK088(su)001:6385: zhes pa mtshan dang rigs de nyid du nges pa'i rgyal ba rnams kyis bka' bgros pa'o //
NK088(su)001:6386: mi 'gyur tshul can rtag pas kyang //
NK088(su)001:6387: zhes pa 'gro ba rnams kyi zhen pa rdzas can du lta ba mthu brtas pas snang ba'o //
NK088(su)001:6388: gzhan ni bshad pa'i rjes su bsnyad do //
NK088(su)001:6389: khro ba'i tshul can khros pas kyang //
NK088(su)001:6390: zhes pa las kyi khro bo ru dra ni /
NK088(su)001:6391: ye shes chen pos snang ba dang /
NK088(su)001:6392: thugs rje chen po dang cha 'dra bar snang ba ni /
NK088(su)001:6393: mthus kyang srid gsum gyi 'gro ba skrag pa'o //
NK088(su)001:6394: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa rdo rje snying po de kho na nyid nges pa /
NK088(su)001:6395: zhes pa mtshan dang rigs de nyid kyi bdag po rdo rje sems dpa' nyid do //
NK088(su)001:6396: gsang chen sbyor ba'i ldem dgongs las //
NK088(su)001:6397: zhes pa la sogs pa de kho na nyid kyis
NK088(su)001:6398: theg pa shin tu bstan cing brtag dka' ba de
NK088(su)001:6399: brda dang dgongs pa dang ldem pa'i thabs mang po
NK088(su)001:6400: las 'dir mthun thabs kyis 'dul bar bskul ba dang
NK088(su)001:6401: / theg pa chen po'i phrin las dang mtshungs pa ni dngos po bzhi rang 'thad spyod pas /
NK088(su)001:6402: 'gro ba bka'i don las log par bsgyur ba'i ru dra'i spyod pa'o //
NK088(su)001:6404: ces pa dper chang gis chang nad bsal ba ltar ro //
NK088(su)001:6405: de nyid kyis de nyid 'joms pa ni thabs rmad du byung ba ste dgongs pa gnyis so //
NK088(su)001:6406: dka' thub tshul can 'gags pas kyang //
NK088(su)001:6407: zhes pa ser sna mchog tu che ba nor rdzas sdom pa ni sdom pa'i cha dang mtshungs te /
NK088(su)001:6408: de'i stobs kyis tshe 'di nyid 'tsho bar nus pa'o //
NK088(su)001:6409: mi g.yo tshul can gnas pas kyang //
NK088(su)001:6410: zhes pa snyoms las gyur pa'i le lo ni bya
NK088(su)001:6411: btsal dang bral ba'i don dang mtshungs pa de dang
NK088(su)001:6412: ldan pas thar pa'i lam brlagsa par nus pa'o //
NK088(su)001:6413: gti mug tshul can rmongs pas kyang //
NK088(su)001:6414: zhes pa ma rig pas non pa ni yang dag
NK088(su)001:6415: pa'i gti mug dang mtshungs pa de dang ldan pas
NK088(su)001:6416: / dus gsum du ma rig pa chen pos don mi mthong ba'i stobs can du gyur to //
NK088(su)001:6417: chags pa'i tshul can spyod pas kyang //
NK088(su)001:6418: zhes pa log pa'i 'dod chags ni yang dag pa'i
NK088(su)001:6419: sbyor ba dang cha 'dra ba de su la yod
NK088(su)001:6420: pas spyad pa'i stobs kyis grong khyer gsum la shin
NK088(su)001:6421: tu zhen pas mi 'bral bar nus so //
NK088(su)001:6422: mthun 'jug tshul gyis cha mthun pas //
NK088(su)001:6423: zhes pa dregs pa'i spyod pa rang kha ma log 'tshos dga' dgar spyod pa ni /
NK088(su)001:6424: thabs kyi spyod pa dang 'dra ba des grong khyer gsum gyi 'gro ba lam log par byed pa'o //
NK088(su)001:6425: de la sogs pa mtha' yas snyed //
NK088(su)001:6426: ces pa la sogs pa snyegs pas dngos po gzhan bsdu ba ni /
NK088(su)001:6427: thabs kyi spyod pa snga ma dang phyi ma ril gyis thul cig pa ste sgra ji bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:6428: de la sogs pa mtha' yas snyed //
NK088(su)001:6429: kun gzhi mnyam dang mi mnyam pa'i //
NK088(su)001:6430: zhes pa la sogs pa thabs 'das pa la snyegs pas bsdu ba ni /
NK088(su)001:6431: thabs mu mtha' yas par 'dren pa'o //
NK088(su)001:6432: snying po byang chub kyi dbyings bder gshegs dang 'khor ba ril la khyab pas /
NK088(su)001:6433: mu mtha' med pa'i ngang gis gang nas gang du
NK088(su)001:6434: bsnums par khyad par 'dod zhen pa dang ma bral
NK088(su)001:6436: yid dang lus can 'byung ba'i phung po dang ldan pa'i 'gro ba rnams kyis /
NK088(su)001:6437: rang rig pa dpal rnam gsum gyi ngo bo rdo
NK088(su)001:6438: rje snying po rab tu gnas snying po byang chub
NK088(su)001:6439: thabs dang mdzad pa ril lhun gyis ye grub pa'o
NK088(su)001:6440: // de'i phyir sems can ril sangs rgyas te /
NK088(su)001:6441: snying po rdo rje sems dpa' de bzhin nyid ye
NK088(su)001:6442: nas yin byang chub ye ma bcos par nges so
NK088(su)001:6443: // de bas na bsgrang ba las 'das mtha' thug
NK088(su)001:6444: med pa'i sems can rnams bsam pa ji ltar mos
NK088(su)001:6445: pa ltar thabs kyi mdzad pa ji ltar yang snang
NK088(su)001:6446: bas ma bkag ma bcos ji bzhin pa de bzhin
NK088(su)001:6448: de nges pa nyid du 'gyur ba yin nyid du
NK088(su)001:6449: son pa'i rgyal ba'i thabs khyad par can dpag gis
NK088(su)001:6450: mi lang ba ji snyed pa grangs las 'das pa
NK088(su)001:6451: ni / gcig las mdzad spyod gar thabs sprin dpung
NK088(su)001:6452: gis ma g.yos cir yang snang ba sprin snyed kyis
NK088(su)001:6453: ni / / ji ltar spyad kyang de nyid las //
NK088(su)001:6454: ma g.yos ma gos dbyings na dpal //
NK088(su)001:6455: zhes pa la sogs pa gdul bya'i bsam pa dang mthun par mdzad pa ji ltar spyad kyang /
NK088(su)001:6457: de nyid mnyam pa'i dbyings las ma g.yos ma gos ma bskyod pas /
NK088(su)001:6458: ji ltar spyad kyang 'khrul nor med pas legs pa dpal ste /
NK088(su)001:6459: lhun gyis rdzogs pa'i mdzad par nyid du nges pa'i ngo bo rang bzhin las /
NK088(su)001:6460: mdzad spyod mu mtha' yas las 'das pa /
NK088(su)001:6461: blo dpag tu med mi 'khyud pa'i sgo gang yang ma bsdam par phye bas /
NK088(su)001:6462: ji ltar 'tshams pas btul drang ste /
NK088(su)001:6463: ril kyang yang dag pa'i dam pa rnams kyis spyod par 'gyur bas bskul te /
NK088(su)001:6464: yal bar ma bzhag cig pa'o //
NK088(su)001:6465: 'dir ni nan tan drag shul gyis //
NK088(su)001:6466: zhes pa la sogs gnas skabs nye bar 'dir ni
NK088(su)001:6467: bzung ba'i gdul bya shin tu drag pas bshad pa
NK088(su)001:6468: ltar / zhi rgyas kyis mi 'dul ba'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:6469: dbang drag gi mdzad pa rdo rje 'dzin pa nyid
NK088(su)001:6470: kyis de dag gi ngo bo ye nyid rang bzhin
NK088(su)001:6471: gyi dkyil 'khor mi bzad pa'i ye shes kyi me
NK088(su)001:6473: las kyi khro bo 'jig rten gyi dur khrod bdag po 'dul ba'i gnyen po /
NK088(su)001:6474: che mchog he ru ka'i sku snang bar mdzod cig ces bskul nas bka' gros thag chad do //
NK088(su)001:6475: 'o na rgyal ba'i longs sku la sogs pa /
NK088(su)001:6476: tshogs re la rtags stong gdul bya mi mthun par snang ba dang /
NK088(su)001:6477: rgyal ba khro la byams sogs ril gyi bgros pa
NK088(su)001:6478: la thabs yas par bstan pa ji lta bu zhe
NK088(su)001:6479: na / bde bar gshegs pa la ngo bo tha
NK088(su)001:6480: dad mi bzhugs kyis kyang rigs dang mthun pa'i thabs
NK088(su)001:6482: de dag gi tshigs re re'i phyir thabs kyi grangs kyang rjes su mthun la /
NK088(su)001:6483: rgyal ba ji snyed pa'i thabs kyang de snyed kyi phyir smos so //
NK088(su)001:6484: bka' gros dam pa bcad pa'i le'u zhes pa drag pos 'dul bar bcad pa'o //
NK088(su)001:6485: le'u nyi shu lnga pa bkrol to ////lang ka'i bdag po de'i tshe de yi dus na /
NK088(su)001:6486: kho bo 'khor de nyid du 'dus par gyur pa zhig gis /
NK088(su)001:6487: zhes pa ru dra 'byung ba'i dus dang /
NK088(su)001:6488: bka' bgros bcad pa'i dus gnyis ngo bor gcig pa'i dus der /
NK088(su)001:6489: gsang ba'i bdag po phyag na rdo rje nga nyid
NK088(su)001:6490: rgyal ba de dag gi 'khor gsang ba 'dzin pa'i
NK088(su)001:6491: sdud pa po byed pa zhig gis /
NK088(su)001:6492: ru dra'i mtshan nyid la thugs mnga' bzhin du /
NK088(su)001:6493: dus de tsam gyi byang chub sems dpa' lang ka mgrin bcu blo gros thabs ldan gyis /
NK088(su)001:6494: shes sam mi shes nyams su blang ba'i dgos shed du dri ba bdun sgra bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:6495: bskul ba'i go cha chen po des smras pa /
NK088(su)001:6496: zhes pa la sogs pa gsang bdag gis bskul nas /
NK088(su)001:6497: brtson 'grus kyi go cha dang ldan pa'i lang kas ni /
NK088(su)001:6498: dus der gsang bdag gis sdud pa la bos te lan du smras pa sgra ji bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:6499: kho bos de la 'di skad ces smras so //
NK088(su)001:6500: e ma'o sems dpa' chen po /
NK088(su)001:6501: 'o na dus 'di ni dus la bab pa'o //
NK088(su)001:6502: zhes pa la sogs pa ru dra'i rgyu 'bras la
NK088(su)001:6503: sogs pa la ngam nas lang ka la bos te
NK088(su)001:6504: / de ltar yin na dregs pa can 'dul ba'i dus la tshad mar phyin pas /
NK088(su)001:6505: de la drag po'i phrin las rmad du byung ba mdzod la thul cig pa'o //
NK088(su)001:6506: de'i dus su byung ba'i gsang sngags kyi don 'di
NK088(su)001:6507: rgyal ba'i dgongs pa'i yang zhe phugs te sgra ji
NK088(su)001:6508: bzhin du'o // gong ma sems dpa' chen po blo gros thabs ldan dang /
NK088(su)001:6509: chos kyis mtho ba'i gnas na sngar 'dus pa'i rgyal ba ma lus pa la bskul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:6510: drag po las kyi stong gsum ma lus bsod nams kyi tshad dang bcas pas bskul ba ni /
NK088(su)001:6511: don gyis der 'dus pa'i 'khor gyis shes par bya ba dang /
NK088(su)001:6512: gsang ba sngags 'byung ba'i sgo dbye ba dang /
NK088(su)001:6513: dpyad thag chad pa ru dra yal bar mi 'dod pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:6514: don 'dis na 'khor ba thog ma tha ma med
NK088(su)001:6515: par gsang ba 'byung ba'i skabs su gsang bdag nyid
NK088(su)001:6516: dang / bskul ba'i go cha blo gros thabs ldan
NK088(su)001:6517: zhes pa'i mtshan 'ba' zhig tu grags pa la 'gal
NK088(su)001:6519: 'dir gsang bdag gis 'das pa'i dus kyi lo rgyus brjod par zad do //
NK088(su)001:6520: de bas na phyis kyang gsang bdag dang lang kas gsang sngags 'byung ba la the tshom med do //
NK088(su)001:6521: de lta yin na gsang bdag gis gsang sngags bstan
NK088(su)001:6522: pa ma la ya'i rtser 'dus pa'i 'khor la bshad
NK088(su)001:6523: pa dang / srin po ma la yar babs pa gnyis gal te dus gcig na ni /
NK088(su)001:6525: bstan pa gcig la dus gnyis smos pa la'ang gos pa med par 'gyur ro //
NK088(su)001:6527: tha dad na dus gcig la gsang sngags lan gnyis 'byung bar 'gyur ro //
NK088(su)001:6528: de ma yin na gnyis ka bskal pa 'di la ma la yar byung ba'ang 'gal lo zhe na /
NK088(su)001:6529: de dag ni thog ma dang tha ma med par
NK088(su)001:6530: smos pa las 'dir 'das pa'i dus btul ba dang
NK088(su)001:6531: / gsang ba 'byung ba dang gsungs pa'i lo rgyus smos pa dus 'dir yang 'byung ste /
NK088(su)001:6532: de dag dus gcig par 'og nas 'chad par 'gyur te /
NK088(su)001:6533: dgos pa re re'i phyir byung tshul tha dad kyang
NK088(su)001:6534: bstan pa ni bskyar zhing ma gsungs te 'gal ba
NK088(su)001:6536: le'u nyi shu bdun pa las /
NK088(su)001:6537: sprul pa rdo rje 'dzin rgyal po //
NK088(su)001:6538: sngar byung rgyal tshab skyes bu yis //
NK088(su)001:6539: zhes pa la sogs pas the tshom gyi kho thag chod do //
NK088(su)001:6540: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis /
NK088(su)001:6541: dan phag gnas gyur pa skyes bu dam pa rdo rje 'dzin du snang ba nyid la /
NK088(su)001:6542: zhes pa la sogs pa thar pa'i g.yog dan phag dus 'dzin du bcug pa nges pa rnyed do //
NK088(su)001:6543: rgyal tshab skyes bu gsang ba'i bdag po phyag na rdo rje nyid du gyur pa la /
NK088(su)001:6544: rgyal ba rnams kyis ru dra thul cig par bka'i las gnyer gtad pa ni /
NK088(su)001:6545: don 'di nyid kyis gsang bdag tu mngon no //
NK088(su)001:6547: rgyal ba kun gyi gsang 'dzin pa //
NK088(su)001:6548: zhes pa la sogs pa sgra bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:6549: skyes bu rdo rje 'dzin pa de //
NK088(su)001:6550: zhes pa la sogs pa bskul ba gsan nas /
NK088(su)001:6551: sngon gyi go cha'i dbang gis zhal gyis bzhes pa sgra ji bzhin du sbyar ro //
NK088(su)001:6553: dregs pa'i mthus phyi nang gi skye ba log cing /
NK088(su)001:6554: lo nyes pa la sogs 'byung ba'o //
NK088(su)001:6555: mkhyen te thugs rjes gdung ba ni //
NK088(su)001:6556: zhes pa la sogs pa dregs pa'i mthus 'gro ba
NK088(su)001:6557: rnams shin tu lam stor zhing nyam thag par thugs
NK088(su)001:6558: su chud nas / mi g.yo ba'i ngang las mi 'gog pa'i khyad par /
NK088(su)001:6559: shin tu 'brel pa'ii brtse ba ste drag po'i gnas
NK088(su)001:6560: skabs pas shin tu khros pa'i tshul gyis rta mgrin
NK088(su)001:6561: la sogs pa la gdug pa gzhom pa'i bka' lung
NK088(su)001:6563: ngag gi dbang phyug rdo rje'i gdong //
NK088(su)001:6564: zhes pa la sogs pa khro bo rta mgrin ni rgyal ba rnams kyi gsung gi bdag nyid pas /
NK088(su)001:6565: khyod kyis mdur glu dang bcas pas dregs pa 'joms pa'i zhal te rdo rje gdong zhes bos pa'o //
NK088(su)001:6566: lang ka'i yul la sogs pa sgra bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:6567: mi ngas skyams ling chen po la //
NK088(su)001:6568: khams gsum rdo rje bya sbron thongs //
NK088(su)001:6569: zhes pa la sogs pa dregs pa 'khor bcas rang
NK088(su)001:6570: gi gnas nas srog chags kyi skyams ling la song
NK088(su)001:6571: ba'i dus su / rta mgrin khyod kyis rgyal ba
NK088(su)001:6572: thugs rje chen po grong khyer gsum gyi mgon po
NK088(su)001:6573: gdug pa 'joms pa rnams bya btang ba dang sbron
NK088(su)001:6575: cis kyang mi bskyod mi 'khrugs pa'i //
NK088(su)001:6576: zhes pa la sogs pa rdo rje sems dpa' nyid la bskul ba ste sgra ji bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:6577: med la kun 'byung stong nyid las //
NK088(su)001:6578: zhes pa la sogs pa rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i sangs rgyas dang /
NK088(su)001:6579: stug po bkod pa'i rgyud dag pa'i rgyal ba rnams la bos pa'o //
NK088(su)001:6580: bdag ni bka' yi las mkhan te //
NK088(su)001:6581: zhes pa la sogs pa nga ni gsang ba ston
NK088(su)001:6582: pa la sogs pa rgyal ba'i phrin las bdag ni
NK088(su)001:6583: bka' las mkhan te ril gyi byed pa po yin
NK088(su)001:6584: sogs pa pas / bdag gis kyang bgyi zhes zhal
NK088(su)001:6585: gyis 'chis pa'i don gyis sangs rgyas chos sku dang
NK088(su)001:6586: gzugs sku rnam gnyis la bskul ba'o //
NK088(su)001:6587: dgongs pa gsang ba kun 'dus la //
NK088(su)001:6588: zhes pa la sogs pa gsang sngags kyi rgyud 'dis
NK088(su)001:6589: 'gro ba rnams byang chub kyi sa las 'khod cig
NK088(su)001:6590: par bskul te gsang ba ston cig pa'o //
NK088(su)001:6591: chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang nas //
NK088(su)001:6592: zhes pa dag sgra bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:6593: bde bar gshegs pa rnams 'gro 'ong med par khro
NK088(su)001:6594: bo'i 'bar ba'i gar dgu tshul dgus snang bar mdzad
NK088(su)001:6595: de / rta yi tshogs la bka' bsgo ba ni /
NK088(su)001:6596: song kun tu rab tu song /
NK088(su)001:6597: zhes pa la sogs pa song mtha' la song shig pa'ang /
NK088(su)001:6598: 'jig rten ril du shin tu nges par song shig pa'o //
NK088(su)001:6599: de'i tshul ni rta'i stabs dgu sgeg pa dpa' ba
NK088(su)001:6600: la sogs pa ste le'u nyi shu rtsa bdun pa
NK088(su)001:6602: gdul bya'i shes rab rab 'bring dgu la theg pa
NK088(su)001:6603: dgu'i chos ston cig pa ste sgra bzhin sbyar ro
NK088(su)001:6604: // snying rje chen po rtog 'jug gis //
NK088(su)001:6605: zhes pa thugs rje chen po'i rgyus 'gro ba rnams
NK088(su)001:6606: bya ras rgyu 'bras gang ltar spyod cing 'gro ba
NK088(su)001:6607: bde bar gyis shig pa ste /
NK088(su)001:6608: skabs kyis dregs pa ci byed pa'i so thag chod par gyis shig par bsgo ba'o //
NK088(su)001:6609: rdo rje chos rab bka' 'khor lo //
NK088(su)001:6610: zhes pa la sogs pa bskul bas spyan ras gzigs rta'i gdong de shin tu dgyes nas /
NK088(su)001:6611: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bar dgongs shing gdul bya
NK088(su)001:6612: la spyan ras 'tsho ba ni dbang gi rigs te
NK088(su)001:6614: rdo rje gsum gyis sgo nas pad+mo'i 'khor lo bskor
NK088(su)001:6615: bar dgongs pas sku mngon du snang bar mdzad de
NK088(su)001:6616: / de lta bu mang pos skabs dang mthun pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:6617: byang chub snying por skad cig gis non cing bgrod
NK088(su)001:6618: pa'i rdzu 'phrul dang ldan pas shes bya gang la'ang
NK088(su)001:6619: ma rmongs pa byol song gi gtso bo rta'i stabs
NK088(su)001:6621: rta mgrin gyi tshogs kyis nam mkha' gang bar mdzad pa ni dregs pa'i snang ba'o //
NK088(su)001:6622: ma la ya yi rtse la lhags //
NK088(su)001:6623: zhes pa dag sprul pa de rnams kyis srin po'i gnas su byon te /
NK088(su)001:6624: yun 'khor ba ma stong gi bar du thugs rje
NK088(su)001:6625: chen pos mi rtog bzhin du bya ra mdzad do
NK088(su)001:6627: stug po bkod pa'i rgyal ba yang //
NK088(su)001:6628: zhes pa la sogs pa rdul gcig steng na rdul snyed kyi rgyal ba rnams kyang /
NK088(su)001:6629: rta'i tshogs dang dgongs pa mi gnyis gcig pas grong
NK088(su)001:6630: khyer gsum ril gnyis med du bsgral cing dgod pa'i
NK088(su)001:6632: 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug gi sa bon rtsa
NK088(su)001:6633: ba nas zad par byin gyis brlabs par mdzad nas
NK088(su)001:6634: / gnas gcig tu yang yang sbyor ba'i sdug bsngal
NK088(su)001:6635: ril mnyam pa chen po'i ngang du mi rtog pa'i
NK088(su)001:6637: gang sgo gsum gdung ba'i ngo bo nyid nam mkha'i 'ja' rlan dang 'dra zhing /
NK088(su)001:6638: lam gzhan du ma dmigs pa de nyid kyi gdeng chud pas mthar phyin pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:6639: sdug bsngal byang chub lam du mdzad //
NK088(su)001:6640: las nyid rang byung ye shes 'grel //
NK088(su)001:6641: zhes pa la sogs pa smad pa'i bya ba nyid
NK088(su)001:6642: ril byang chub sems kyi mdzad pa las thal ba
NK088(su)001:6643: med pas / rang byung ba'i ye shes chen por gsal ba'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:6644: des bskyed pa'i rnam par smin pa'i 'bras bu log
NK088(su)001:6645: pa'i sgo gsum rdo rje gsum gyi ngo bor gsal
NK088(su)001:6646: ba ni / glo bur du lam pas byas pa min te /
NK088(su)001:6647: ye ma bcos ma byas te rgyu rkyen dang bral
NK088(su)001:6648: ba'i ngo bo lhun gyis rdzogs pa chen po'i ngang
NK088(su)001:6650: de lta bu'i don ni ngo bo gnyis med la dgongs pas /
NK088(su)001:6651: gdul bya'i snang ba rta'i tshogs la rgyal ba rnams kyis mthu btang ba dang /
NK088(su)001:6652: de nyid kyi mdzad pa mi dor ba'o //
NK088(su)001:6653: gsang bdag rdo rje 'dzin pa yang //
NK088(su)001:6654: zhes pa la sogs pa rta'i tshogs ma la ya'i rtser so mdzad pa'i tshe /
NK088(su)001:6655: dan phag phyag na rdo rjer gyur pa yang thugs
NK088(su)001:6656: dam gyi dbang gis rdo rje gsum mi phyed pa
NK088(su)001:6657: las / sprul tshogs rdo rje gzhon nu byis pa'i
NK088(su)001:6658: gzugs can grangs las 'das pa snyed du snang bas
NK088(su)001:6659: nam mkha' gang bar mdzad pa yang /
NK088(su)001:6660: gnas der byon te srin po'i spyod pa dang mthun
NK088(su)001:6661: 'jug gis cir yang mdzad pa'i phyir byis pa'i spyod
NK088(su)001:6662: par bstan pa'o // las bzhi rdo rje sgos kyi le'u zhes pa spyi dbang du dgongs pa ste /
NK088(su)001:6663: 'dir ni las gnyis kho na mdzad pa'i phyir gcig la gcig bsgo ba dang /
NK088(su)001:6665: stug po bkod pa'i sangs rgyas dang /
NK088(su)001:6666: rdo rje 'dzin pa la sogs pa nyid nyid kyi las so sor bsgos pa'i don ston pa'o //
NK088(su)001:6667: le'u nyi shu drug pa mdor bkrol ba'o ////de nas mthun 'jug skyes bu des //
NK088(su)001:6668: mthun pa'i spyan gyis gang gzigs nas //
NK088(su)001:6669: zhes pa la sogs pa ma la ya'i rtser byon pa la snyegs pa dang /
NK088(su)001:6670: 'dren pa ni skabs kyi 'brel tshig go //
NK088(su)001:6671: rdo rje 'dzin pa rgyal tshab skyes bu mthun 'jug shin tu khros pas he ru ka byung ste /
NK088(su)001:6672: sprul pa gzhon nu'i 'byung gnas des /
NK088(su)001:6673: mthun 'jugs byis pa'i spyod pa mdzad pa'i spyan gyis
NK088(su)001:6674: dur khrod bdag po'i dngos po rnams tshul ji ltar
NK088(su)001:6676: las kyi yi dwags drag po de //
NK088(su)001:6678: zhes pa la sogs pa sgra bzhin du 'grel te /
NK088(su)001:6680: zhes pa smos pa'i 'dom gyis grong rdal la 'obs
NK088(su)001:6681: su bskor ba de ru dra'i spyod yul yi ge
NK088(su)001:6682: ji bzhin pa'o // dpal chen rdo rje 'dzin pa des //
NK088(su)001:6683: de nyid yang dag dngos min pa'i //
NK088(su)001:6684: zhes pa la sogs pa dregs pa 'khor bcas kyi
NK088(su)001:6685: pho rnams skyams ling la song ba skyes bus gzigs
NK088(su)001:6686: te rang gi gnas nas dong ba'i skabs su /
NK088(su)001:6687: mo la sbyor bas sras kyis 'dul ba'i ched du
NK088(su)001:6688: dpal he ru ka de nyid kyi sku ma yin
NK088(su)001:6689: pa bshad pa ltar de las sprul pa'i sras gzhon
NK088(su)001:6690: nu ni yum med pa'i phyir snam nas bton pa'o
NK088(su)001:6691: // de dngos kyi cha lugs ci 'dra zhe na /
NK088(su)001:6692: mi gtsang ba'i tshogs zhal du gsol bas mtshan sme
NK088(su)001:6693: brtsegs zhes bya ste cha byad sgra ji bzhan no
NK088(su)001:6694: // des dregs pa ci 'dra bar mdzad pa ni srin mo la snang bar bya ba'i ched du /
NK088(su)001:6695: bshung ba lnga ni bdud rtsir bsgyur //
NK088(su)001:6696: zhes pa ru dra'i mi gtsang bas 'obs bkang ba'i dam rdzas lnga'o //
NK088(su)001:6697: de nyid bdud rtsir mdzad de gsol nas /
NK088(su)001:6698: 'obs la sogs pa rgyu rkyen dang bral ba'i chos nyid stong par mdzad de /
NK088(su)001:6699: nye gnas la sogs 'khor mo rnams //
NK088(su)001:6700: zhes pa la sogs pa la las kyi koo ri
NK088(su)001:6701: ma brgyad la sogs pa 'khor gyi bud med rnams
NK088(su)001:6702: la ma chags pa'i sbyor ba cha mthun du mdzad
NK088(su)001:6703: nas / de dag dbang du mdzad de nyon mongs sbyangs nas /
NK088(su)001:6704: de dag gi lhums su thugs ye shes snang ba'i sems dpa' brgyad la sogs pa bzhag pas /
NK088(su)001:6705: de las sras su 'thon pa ye shes kyi ko'u sing la sogs par snang ste /
NK088(su)001:6706: mthun pas mthun pa 'dul ba'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:6707: de bas na lam pas zhi ba las khro bor bsgom pa yang tshul 'di dag gi phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:6709: de nas sme ba brtsegs pa des //
NK088(su)001:6710: zhes pa la sogs pa khro bo des sprul pa
NK088(su)001:6711: gdul bya'i bsam pa gang ltar 'tshams par 'byung ba'i
NK088(su)001:6712: yon tan mnga' ba'i phyir sngags 'chad pa'i che ba'i
NK088(su)001:6713: mtshan dang / dus myur bar 'byung ba'i snying po
NK088(su)001:6714: brjod pas gdug pa 'dul ba'i bya ba thams cad
NK088(su)001:6715: byed pa'i mchog phrin las ril mdzad pa yin pa'i
NK088(su)001:6716: mthu can gyi phyir sngags bka' stsal pa sgra bzhin
NK088(su)001:6717: mtshan dang / te / +amo 'bur bsnyen bsgrub bzhis bsdus pa'o //
NK088(su)001:6720: zhes pa la sogs pa he ru ka la chags
NK088(su)001:6721: pa mi mnga' bas srin mo'i chags pa la chags
NK088(su)001:6722: thabs kyi sbyor ba mdzad pas sel ba'i dus su
NK088(su)001:6723: / khro bo he ru ka nyid min pa'i sprul pa sme ba brtsegs pa ste /
NK088(su)001:6724: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs kyi gsung gi cho 'phrul sku la bsdus te /
NK088(su)001:6725: dang po rnam par snang mdzad nyid las sprul pa ltar /
NK088(su)001:6726: 'dir yang sa bon thams cad pa'i phyir lhag pa'i khu ba nyid +amo gyi gzugs su phabs te /
NK088(su)001:6727: +amo ni sku ji snyed pa mngon du snang bar
NK088(su)001:6728: byed pa'i nus mthu can yin pas +amo kho na
NK088(su)001:6729: bzhag pa las / srin po ci 'dra bar yi ge +amo yang skur bsgyur te /
NK088(su)001:6730: srin mo kro ti ma'i mngal du bzhag go //
NK088(su)001:6731: rdo rje ljags kyi 'od zer las /
NK088(su)001:6732: rak+sha sh+r+ai he ru ka /zhes pa de nas sa bon de brtan pa'i sngags brjod de /
NK088(su)001:6733: sku mngon du rdzogs shing bskyed pas gdug pa 'joms
NK088(su)001:6734: par byed pa'i yi ge phata brjod pa'i mthu yis
NK088(su)001:6735: shin tu drag po mthu dang ldan pa rab tu
NK088(su)001:6737: dngos med rig pa'i skyes bu de //
NK088(su)001:6738: zhes pa ngo bo mi zin par thams cad mkhyen
NK088(su)001:6739: pa'i ye shes kyi ngo bor bzhugs pa ni khro
NK088(su)001:6741: yab rdo rje 'dzin he ru ka chen po la bsdus te mi dmigs so //
NK088(su)001:6742: drag shul stobs ldan skyes bu de //
NK088(su)001:6743: zhes pa la sogs pa shin tu drag cing gtum rngam chen po ni /
NK088(su)001:6744: rdo rje 'dzin pa he ru kar byung ba'i ngo
NK088(su)001:6745: bo rdo rje gzhon nu gzhon nu rnams kyi yab
NK088(su)001:6746: nyid de / de dpe sgyu ma ltar ye shes
NK088(su)001:6747: rdo rje'i sprul pa gzhon nu bye bas ya mang
NK088(su)001:6749: bdud dang srin po log pa'i sde pa 'dul ba'i mdzad spyod byis pa'i spyod pa bor te /
NK088(su)001:6750: tsha bo srin mo'i lhums su bzhag cing phyogs bcu'i gdug pa btul bas thugs khral bskyungs pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:6751: dgongs pa'i snying po byang chub kyi ngang du ma
NK088(su)001:6752: 'dres rdzogs par gsal ba nyid du bzhugs pa de
NK088(su)001:6753: nyid gdul bya'i snang ba la sprul pa gsang ba'i
NK088(su)001:6754: bdag po phyag na rdo rje sngar gyi ston pa'i
NK088(su)001:6755: rgyal tshabs skyes bu mdzad pa des /
NK088(su)001:6756: sum cu rtsa gsum dang dga' ldan dang 'og min
NK088(su)001:6757: du grags pa'i gsang sngags chen po 'di 'dzin cing
NK088(su)001:6759: de bas na he ru ka nyid gsang bdag drag
NK088(su)001:6760: shul can dan phag tu gyur pa la the tshom
NK088(su)001:6761: med do // 'on kyang de nyid gcig dang du
NK088(su)001:6762: ma las grol bas gsang bdag gnyis su thal ba'ang
NK088(su)001:6763: med do // med de / bskal pa gcig gi cha bzung ba'o //
NK088(su)001:6764: de nas yi dwags drag po de //
NK088(su)001:6765: rang gi gnas su 'ong ba dang //
NK088(su)001:6766: zhes pa la sogs pa srin po skyams ling las rang gi gnas su 'ong ba dang /
NK088(su)001:6767: yul khams dang 'khor snga ma dang ma 'dra bas ma rangs pa sgra bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:6768: deng lags la h+aun han de ring phan chad bdag gi bsgrubs phan nyo ba ti //
NK088(su)001:6769: kho bdag gi na 'am lhums ni tsa smra mi bde ste /
NK088(su)001:6771: dpa' bo khyed kyi gdung brgyud 'tshob pa /
NK088(su)001:6773: khyed kyi ku lan tra lags na tsa bu ci zhig 'khrul th+ra tha //
NK088(su)001:6774: zhes srin po ma rangs pa'i sems rtog skyes pa las /
NK088(su)001:6775: srin mos dpa' bo khyod kyi thugs kyi dgongs pa bdag gis bsgrubs te /
NK088(su)001:6776: bdag gis mngal mi bde bas khyed kyi gdung 'tshob
NK088(su)001:6777: kyi sras nges par bdag la 'byung na thugs ji
NK088(su)001:6778: ltar 'khrug ces tshigs smras te srin po'i rtog pa
NK088(su)001:6779: chad do // mdangs la chags pas 'dug pa dang //
NK088(su)001:6780: zhes pa la sogs pa sgra bzhin du sbyar ro //
NK088(su)001:6781: 'jigs pa'i gzugs kyis sa gzhi khebs //
NK088(su)001:6783: zhes pa la sogs pa sprul pa mi zad pa dang phyag mtshan bcu drug gi grags so //
NK088(su)001:6784: rdo rje dril bu bsnams pa dang bco brgyad du 'gyur ro //
NK088(su)001:6786: rdo rje srin po khro bo che //
NK088(su)001:6787: dbu dgu sum brtsegs ral pa 'bar //
NK088(su)001:6788: rdo rje'i gdengs gshog bar snang khebs //
NK088(su)001:6789: nyi shu rtsa bdun spyan ras gzigs //
NK088(su)001:6790: zhabs brgyad lha chen brgyad la gnon //
NK088(su)001:6791: bco brgyad dang po g.yas g.yon gyis //
NK088(su)001:6792: rdo rje thod khrag dkrug cing gsol //
NK088(su)001:6793: de 'og ste ra ril mid mdzad //
NK088(su)001:6794: de 'og gnyis ni rgyu zhags ldog /bzhi pa g.yas g.yon nyi zla 'dzin //
NK088(su)001:6795: lnga pa gnyis na 'ug pa khra //
NK088(su)001:6796: drug pa rdo rje mdung rtse gsum //
NK088(su)001:6797: bdun pa za ma tog rdul yab //
NK088(su)001:6798: brgyad pa rnga dang ri rab bskor //
NK088(su)001:6799: dgu pa stong gsum rgyang mar 'phen //
NK088(su)001:6800: klu dbang 'bum gyis sku la brgyan //
NK088(su)001:6801: dur khrod rgyan rtags bco brgyad 'bar //
NK088(su)001:6802: dus mtha'i me ltar sku la 'bar //
NK088(su)001:6803: sdom sdig smrigs sbrul sku las 'phro //
NK088(su)001:6805: rdo rje srin po'i cha lugs bshad pa'o //
NK088(su)001:6807: bdud kyi sgyu 'phrul gyi d+r+wa ba bkram ste /
NK088(su)001:6808: bswo dang cha'i sgra bsgrags te /
NK088(su)001:6810: zhes pa bdud rnams kyi cho 'phrul yod tshad bstan te /
NK088(su)001:6811: grong brdal nas ma la ya'i rtse mo'i 'khra sar rgod par dpags te phyin pa'o //
NK088(su)001:6812: rdo rje'i rta'i tshogs kyis rdo rje s+t+wam b+ha na'i stobs kyis /
NK088(su)001:6813: zhes pa la sogs pa srin po rnams spa bkong
NK088(su)001:6814: ba'i phyir gong du ma la yar so mdzad pa'i
NK088(su)001:6816: gom stabs kyis rdzu 'phrul shin tu mgyogs shing drag
NK088(su)001:6817: pas khro bo gzhan gyi bzhon pa rnams kyang rang
NK088(su)001:6818: dbang med par bdud kyi ngo la mdur thag gcod
NK088(su)001:6824: gar gyi phyag rgya 'bar bas dbang phyug non //
NK088(su)001:6825: zhes pa la sogs pa gar dgu dang ldan pa'i
NK088(su)001:6826: sku chen po me dpung 'bar bas ma h+aa de
NK088(su)001:6828: yi ge rtsa ba ni snying po ste dbang du
NK088(su)001:6829: bsdu ba'i phyir mi gtong bas brjod pas mgo 'dren
NK088(su)001:6830: no // 'dod chags kyis dran pa nyams par myos
NK088(su)001:6831: byed byed pa ma h+aa de wa brgya phrag bcu
NK088(su)001:6832: bas lhag pa'i skur ston mdzod la /
