NK088(su)001:9532: dpe na rgod ma shi ba'i rte'u rlon ra yar gyi 'o mas mi 'tsho ba bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:9533: 'on kyang theg pa chen po nyid la thabs med pa ni ma yin no //
NK088(su)001:9534: gang zhig rdo rje snying po gsang 'dzin pa //
NK088(su)001:9535: shing rta la sogs rta la 'dug spyod pa //
NK088(su)001:9536: zhes pa la sogs pa rmad du byung ba'i theg pa don 'dzin pa'i rnal 'byor pa de ni /
NK088(su)001:9537: dper shing rta dang glang po che la sogs pa'i bzhon pa rnams zhon pa'i dus na /
NK088(su)001:9538: bzhon pa de dag la gang zhon pa 'degs pa dang /
NK088(su)001:9539: gnas su bskyal ba las bya ba'i las gzhan med pa ltar /
NK088(su)001:9540: theg pa chen pos rnal 'byor mthar phyin pa'i phrin las mnga' ba'o //
NK088(su)001:9541: de bas na theg pa chen po'i bzhon pa'i rnal 'byor ni /
NK088(su)001:9542: rgyal ba nyid kyi dbu yi thog tu bkur bas mdzad do //
NK088(su)001:9543: mdo sde las stong pa dang mtshan ma med pa
NK088(su)001:9544: dang smon pa med pa la bskal pa'i yun du
NK088(su)001:9545: btsal kyang rgyal bas bkur bar mi mdzad do //
NK088(su)001:9546: de dag gis dgongs pa dam pa la zhugs ma
NK088(su)001:9547: zhugs kyi bye brag gis sar nges par 'byung ba
NK088(su)001:9548: myur bul yod pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:9549: de bas na theg pa chen po mchog ni rgyal
NK088(su)001:9550: ba nyid kyi'ang yab yum ston pa mchod gnas dam
NK088(su)001:9551: pa yin pas / de la gnas pa'ang rjes su mtshungs so //
NK088(su)001:9552: de lta ba'i phyir gsang don skad cig mthong ba dang /
NK088(su)001:9553: sems skyes pa'i yon tan stong gsum gyi kha lces
NK088(su)001:9554: so sor brjod kyang mi zin pa'i yon tan dang
NK088(su)001:9555: ldan no // dkar po mthar thug bsod nams kun //
NK088(su)001:9556: zhes pa chos spyod bcu dang bsdu ba bzhi la sogs pa'i bsod nams ni /
NK088(su)001:9557: sen mo'i steng gi rdul gyi grangs tsam mo //
NK088(su)001:9558: theg pa 'dir sems skad cig tsam skyed pa ni sa gzhi chen po'i rdul snyed yod de /
NK088(su)001:9559: mdo sngags kyi dge ba'i rtsa ba bskrun du mi btub bo //
NK088(su)001:9560: dkar po phyogs kyi mtha' thug pa //
NK088(su)001:9561: zhes pa dag ni mdo sde'i tshogs rnam gnyis bsags pas rdzogs pa ni /
NK088(su)001:9562: mun khang gi sgron me dang 'dra ste ye shes chen po mu mtha' med pa ma mthong ste /
NK088(su)001:9563: sgrib pa srab pa tsam mo //
NK088(su)001:9564: theg pa chen po 'dir tshogs ma bsags par rdzogs te /
NK088(su)001:9565: ril theg pa chen po nyid du rtogs na /
NK088(su)001:9566: dus mthar 'jig rten 'jig pa'i me chen dang 'dra ste /
NK088(su)001:9567: gang sbyar bya ril ka nas ma bsal dag pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:9568: dbu mar snang ba'i nam mkha' ni //
NK088(su)001:9569: zhes pa lta ba'i khyad par 'chad de /
NK088(su)001:9570: mdo sde bas dngos po rten 'brel la sogs pas
NK088(su)001:9571: gzhal ba'i mtha' don dam pa ma skyes pa'i don
NK088(su)001:9572: gsal la mi g.yo bar 'dod pa ni /
NK088(su)001:9573: gnas khyim gyi skar khung gi nam mkha' lta bu'o //
NK088(su)001:9574: theg pa chen po ril gnyis med pa las gzhal
NK088(su)001:9575: bya 'jal byed du'ang med pas ston pa'i chos nyid
NK088(su)001:9576: bden pa gnyis grol ba'i don ma bsgribs mi 'gog
NK088(su)001:9577: ma phyin kun la khyab pa'i don ni /
NK088(su)001:9578: ril rdzogs par gsal ba 'byung chen gyi nam mkha' lta bu'o //
NK088(su)001:9579: des na rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa ni ji sa
NK088(su)001:9580: nas bskrun du med de 'chad par yang 'gyur ro
NK088(su)001:9581: // de lta bu'i gdeng ni ma rnyed /
NK088(su)001:9582: gsang sngags la gnad ma chud /
NK088(su)001:9583: dus deng sang gi gang zag mdo sde la lce sbyangs nas theg pa chen por zhugs pa dang /
NK088(su)001:9584: gsang sngags la ldongs pa kha cig /rgyu 'bras kyi
NK088(su)001:9585: theg pa ni don dam pa'i lta ba la yang
NK088(su)001:9586: khyad med / grub thag nye ring gi thabs tsam
NK088(su)001:9587: las 'bras bu la yang khyad med do zhes smra
NK088(su)001:9588: khyad med / ba ni / nong bus blon gral mi zin pa dang 'dra ste /
NK088(su)001:9589: rmongs pa des theg pa chen po'i sa mi non te /
NK088(su)001:9591: 'on kyang theg pa chen po ni yon tan gyi
NK088(su)001:9592: khyad par de lta bu dang ldan pas mos pa
NK088(su)001:9593: tsam yang mi gtong bar rigs so //
NK088(su)001:9594: phrin las kyi don ji lta bu snyam pa la /
NK088(su)001:9595: mdzad pa rlabs kyis zhi ba ni //
NK088(su)001:9596: stong pa'i bskal pa lta bur snang //
NK088(su)001:9597: zhes pa la sogs pa thabs chen po'i byin rlabs kyis mnyam pa chen po'i gnad chud pas /
NK088(su)001:9598: rtog mtshan gyi zug rngu bral ba la mtha' gang
NK088(su)001:9599: yang ma dmigs pas 'jig rten stong pa lta bu'o
NK088(su)001:9600: // de lta bu'i spyod yul du ril 'bras bu'i
NK088(su)001:9601: ngo bos gang bar snang ba ni 'jig rten chags
NK088(su)001:9603: ril yang snying rje chen pos zin pa'i don 'jal
NK088(su)001:9604: ba ni gcig tu bsdus pa'i phyir chags pa lta
NK088(su)001:9605: bu'o // rtogs pa'i thabs thugs rje chen pos dngos
NK088(su)001:9606: po yul ril skye med du bsgral ba ni 'jig
NK088(su)001:9607: bu'o // pa lta bu'o // lang ka'i bdag po /
NK088(su)001:9608: de dag ni yon tan mi zad /
NK088(su)001:9611: ces pa yon tan dang las thun mong gi mtshan no //
NK088(su)001:9612: le'u sum cu lnga pa 'grel pa'o //
NK088(su)001:9613: byin rlabs snang ba na yang 'byung /
NK088(su)001:9614: zhes pa bshad pa ltar gsang ba dam pa las
NK088(su)001:9615: sngon byung skyes bus sa non pa'i 'bras bu lnga'i
NK088(su)001:9616: byin rlabs ril du shar ba'o //
NK088(su)001:9617: byung tshul bdun pa bshad pa'o ////de nas lang ka'i mnga' bdag byang chub sems dpa' /
NK088(su)001:9618: zhes pa la sogs pa byung tshul brgyad pa'i dris lan no //
NK088(su)001:9619: lang ka'i bdag po de gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:9621: gang gis gang la gang brgyud pa /
NK088(su)001:9622: zhes pa dag byung tshul gyis don nye bar bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:9623: ston pa yang dag par rdzogs pa nyid kyi dgongs pa'i don /
NK088(su)001:9624: chos kyi rgyal tshabs rgyud dag pa la chu dang zla ba ltar brgyud nas /
NK088(su)001:9625: rgyal tshabs skyes bus 'khor gang dag la chos gsang ba ji bzhin pa'i ngo bo /
NK088(su)001:9626: de kho na nyid kyi don lha mi'i gnas su tshig tu bka' stsal pa ni /
NK088(su)001:9627: sngon du dngos su lung bstan pa thob pa'i 'gro
NK088(su)001:9628: ba'i lus can gyi byang chub sems dpa' so so
NK088(su)001:9629: la snang ba'o // de ltar snga bar grags pa'i lo rgyus kyi yid ches par bya ba'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:9630: grags pa de yang ji ga gang //
NK088(su)001:9631: 'das pa'i dus na sngon byung ba //
NK088(su)001:9632: zhe pa de ltar 'jig rten du snang ba'i tshul gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:9633: sngon bskal pa grangs med pa las kyang grangs med
NK088(su)001:9634: pa 'das pa'i sngon rol bskal pa kun dga' la
NK088(su)001:9635: byung ba'i ston pa 'gro ba rnams kyi skabs dam
NK088(su)001:9636: pa thub dka' gzhon nu rdo rje snying por gyur
NK088(su)001:9637: pas / dus der byung ba'i thar pa nag po
NK088(su)001:9638: 'khor bar zlos bur brgyud pa'i sdug bsngal can ru
NK088(su)001:9640: byang chub zhing la dgod pa'i dus su /
NK088(su)001:9641: yongs su sa non pa dang ma non pa tshogs pa'i 'khor la /
NK088(su)001:9642: gsang ba'i theg pa 'di dus der yang rgyal tshab skyes bus bshad pas da lta'ang 'chad pa ste /
NK088(su)001:9643: de bas na byung tshul ni skabs gcig gi dbang
NK088(su)001:9644: du dus gcig par 'dus kyang som nyi med do
NK088(su)001:9645: // lang ka'i bdag po de'i tshe de'i dus na /
NK088(su)001:9646: zhes pa dregs pa btul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:9647: gsang sngags byung ba'i dus gnyis gcig gi skabs so //
NK088(su)001:9648: yongs su rdzogs par ngos ma zin pa'i sras de dag yongs su /
NK088(su)001:9649: zhes pa dag ni ston pas ru dra btul ba'i 'dir lo rgyus su bsnyad pa ni /
NK088(su)001:9650: dgos ched dang ldan pas ston pas 'khor de dag
NK088(su)001:9651: la bskul ba dam tshig longs shig pa sgra bzhin
NK088(su)001:9652: no // der 'khor gyi de nyid shes par bya ba'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:9653: dri ba ma bcos pa'i dam dang ji ltar gzung
NK088(su)001:9654: ba gnyis dris pa'i lam nye bar ston pas bka'
NK088(su)001:9655: stsal pa ni / ma nor ma bcos dam tshig ni //
NK088(su)001:9656: de bzhin nyid kyi chos nyid la //
NK088(su)001:9657: zhes pa la sogs pa ngo bo ma nor ma
NK088(su)001:9658: 'khrul pas byas bslad med ma bcos pa'i bsrung bya
NK088(su)001:9659: gang zhe na / chos rnams kyi de bzhin nyid
NK088(su)001:9660: kho na rang rig gi sems kyi chos nyid pas
NK088(su)001:9661: gang zhe na / / de nyid du'ang 'dzin pa'i 'du shes ma zhugs pa ni /
NK088(su)001:9662: gang du'ang ma g.yos pa'i phyir na ming du bzhag pa'ang yin te /
NK088(su)001:9663: de mi 'da' ba las gang du'ang gyur pa med
NK088(su)001:9664: pa ni bde bar gshegs pa rnams kyi thugs dam
NK088(su)001:9665: mchog yin no // zhes gsungs so //
NK088(su)001:9666: 'dus pa'i tshogs rnams shin tu skrag cing sngangs nas /
NK088(su)001:9667: zhes pa bshad pa ltar ngos ma zin pas chos la bzod pa ma thob ste /
NK088(su)001:9668: 'jigs sngangs nas yid ma mgu nas ngag tu yang stong pa chen po'i don ma mthong bas /
NK088(su)001:9669: ma rangs pa'i sgra e ma'o zhes pa sgra bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:9671: zhes pa dam tshig mchog la so so'i spyod pa mi spong bas /
NK088(su)001:9672: rang rang gis dam tshig dang spyod pa ci dgar
NK088(su)001:9673: spyod par gnang bas dam tshig phul cig bar bskul
NK088(su)001:9674: te / der yid rangs nas smras pa sgra bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:9675: nag po ded dpon 'khor dang bcas pa rnams kyis /
NK088(su)001:9676: ces pa dag ru dra gtso 'khor gyi dam tshig phul ba nye bar bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:9677: dregs pa rang dag gi dam pas rang gi chos lugs la gnas pas /
NK088(su)001:9678: zhe sdang gis pha rol dpung 'joms pa'i dam tshig phul lo //
NK088(su)001:9689: rdzun dang smra ba'i sho par pa dang /
NK088(su)001:9692: 'jig rten gyi sngags rten pa'i rgyang 'phen pa dang /
NK088(su)001:9695: bargya'am stong du gon nas ni //
NK088(su)001:9697: zhes pa gos de dag gon te sngags grangs bcu phrag bcu'am brgya phrag bcu bzlas te /
NK088(su)001:9698: las byas te ling ga gtubs na tshad rgyal ba'ang 'jig par 'dod pa'o //
NK088(su)001:9699: ldem dgongs su mthun pas drang phyir rigs rgyud can la gsungs pa dang /
NK088(su)001:9701: log sred can gyi ched du /
NK088(su)001:9702: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis gang ma 'dres yongs su mi 'gog pa'i /
NK088(su)001:9703: zhes pa ma rungs pa dag gis dam pa so
NK088(su)001:9704: sor btsal la spyod du gnang bar gsungs pa ni
NK088(su)001:9705: / gang 'dir 'dus pa'i skal ldan kun so so
NK088(su)001:9706: la bos nas rang rang gi dam tshig longs shig
NK088(su)001:9707: par bka' stsal nas gdams pa'o //
NK088(su)001:9708: dregs pa 'khor bcas la bka' stsal pa /
NK088(su)001:9709: gzhan gyi sde pa 'joms byed cing //
NK088(su)001:9710: zhes pa rang gi spyod pa de ma spangs bzhin
NK088(su)001:9711: du ji bzhin pa'i ngang du rtogs pa'i nga rgyal
NK088(su)001:9713: theg pa'i snod yin no bar bka' stsal pa'o //
NK088(su)001:9714: gral ni bshad pa dang rim pa bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:9716: zhes pa thabs kyis 'dod chags spyod la ma zin na snod yin pa'o //
NK088(su)001:9717: srog gi dbang po rgyun bcad nas //
NK088(su)001:9718: zhes pa shes rab dang ting nge 'dzin gyi dngos
NK088(su)001:9719: su bsgral zhing lnga drug gi rgyun dang sgo bkag
NK088(su)001:9720: cing bcad pa ni dam tshig go //
NK088(su)001:9721: blangs nas 'dod pa'i longs spyod pa //
NK088(su)001:9722: zhes pa 'phrul dag'i ting nge 'dzin gyis blangs na dam pa ma nor ba'o //
NK088(su)001:9723: dur khrod snod la chos shes pa //
NK088(su)001:9724: zhes pa ma rig pa ka nas dag par rtogs pas mgo bcad de /
NK088(su)001:9725: rtsa ba'i rgyud las gsungs pa ltar thod pa brtags
NK088(su)001:9726: te bzang zhing shis pa snod du 'chang ba ni
NK088(su)001:9728: rnal 'byor chen po'i zas yin pas //
NK088(su)001:9729: zhes pa sha dngos su spyod pa la mi chags pas spangs len bral ba'i longs spyod do //
NK088(su)001:9730: de bzhin du 'chad par 'gyur ba'i spyod pa ril
NK088(su)001:9731: yang dag pa'i lta bas zin pas ma spangs spyad
NK088(su)001:9732: na theg pa chen po'i snod yin par 'grel te
NK088(su)001:9735: ces pa dregs pa btul bar bshad zin to //
NK088(su)001:9736: bye brag thams cad gcig pas na //
NK088(su)001:9737: zhes pa dag ni log sred dag gis dam tshig
NK088(su)001:9738: so sor ma 'dres pa de dag sems kyi chos
NK088(su)001:9739: nyid du dbyer med pas byas la ma gsog pas
NK088(su)001:9740: rnam smin sogs pa'i las dkar nag gi kha thabs
NK088(su)001:9741: su mi 'gyur ba'i don ni thog tu phebs pa
NK088(su)001:9742: ma bslad pa'i dam tshig ste /
NK088(su)001:9743: de la ni las kyi rnam par smin pa'i 'bras bu med pas dam tshig mchog go //
NK088(su)001:9744: yang dag pa'i dam tshig nyid rjes su bstan pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:9745: mi g.yo mi 'gyur mi bskyod pa //
NK088(su)001:9747: yang dag pa'i gdeng dang ldan pa'i rig pa ni
NK088(su)001:9748: 'du shes gang du'ang mi bskyod mi 'jigs mi bsgul
NK088(su)001:9750: blos cir yang mi bsam pa nyid rnal 'byor te mtha' med kyang /
NK088(su)001:9751: yon tan chen po'i bcud rlag pa dang bral ba
NK088(su)001:9752: med pas 'byung 'jug gi bya ba dang bral ba
NK088(su)001:9754: de nyid chen por kun gcig pas //
NK088(su)001:9756: dngos po rnams de kho na nyid kyi ngang du bdal ba la ris med pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:9757: spong len bral ba'i gnyis pa'i chos ril ma dmigs
NK088(su)001:9758: pa'i don gyi bla dwags gnyis su snang ba'i chos
NK088(su)001:9759: rnams kun ni grangs kyi gzhir brjod de rnam pa
NK088(su)001:9760: med do // dkar po nag po gang 'di la //
NK088(su)001:9761: zhes pa la sogs pa las dge sdig gi 'bras bu 'khrul pa la ma 'dres par snang yang /
NK088(su)001:9762: mnyam pa'i ngang la las su 'du shes pa med pas rnam smin med pa ni /
NK088(su)001:9763: spyod la ma chags mkha' dang mtshungs pa la ris med pas mnyam pa'i dam tshig ces bsnyad de /
NK088(su)001:9764: mnyam nyid rig pa'i rgyal po las //
NK088(su)001:9765: zhes pa la sogs pa ji lta ba'i don rtogs
NK088(su)001:9766: pa'i ye shes ni ril gyi bdag po bas las
NK088(su)001:9767: so sor dbye ba'i ris ngo bos ma grub pa
NK088(su)001:9769: spyad bya spyod byed ril rig pas rgyas btab pas
NK088(su)001:9770: de nyid du gsal ba ni ye shes chen po'i
NK088(su)001:9771: dam tshig ste / yang dag pa'i thugs dam chen po lnga'i don to //
NK088(su)001:9772: gsang tshig bsten pa'i dam tshig ni /
NK088(su)001:9773: ling ga skye ba'i rgyun bcad na //
NK088(su)001:9775: zhes pa gos kyi brda yi don ni 'gro ba'i
NK088(su)001:9776: lus te skye ba'i sa bon ling ga srog rgyun
NK088(su)001:9777: gcod pa'ang mi dmigs pa rtogs pa'i mdzad pa skye
NK088(su)001:9778: ba rnam grangs brgya bcu phrag bcu snyed du bskyar
NK088(su)001:9779: zhing btang bar sngags bzlas pa de ting nge 'dzin
NK088(su)001:9780: de nyid gyis byang chub de nyid zhing la bkod
NK088(su)001:9781: nas / de lta bus ni sangs rgyas gzugs yang
NK088(su)001:9782: dag pa ched du byas pa'i rgyal ba nyid du
NK088(su)001:9783: zhen pa nyid kyang bral bar gyur pa ni dam
NK088(su)001:9784: nas / pa mchog go // phra men ma'i ni /
NK088(su)001:9785: 'dod pas spyad pa'i longs spyod lnga //
NK088(su)001:9786: zhes pa dag gzugs dang sgra la sogs pa'i longs
NK088(su)001:9787: spyod ni chos nyid kyi ngang la mi ldan ma
NK088(su)001:9788: bral bar bzhag pas ril mi zhen pa dam pa
NK088(su)001:9789: mchog go // 'dus pa chen po'i tshogs rnams rab tu mgu /
NK088(su)001:9790: zhes pa yi rang bas bstod de gsol ba btab bo //
NK088(su)001:9795: zhes pa rang rang gi dam tshig don la ma
NK088(su)001:9796: nor ba'i dam par gsol ba btab pa la dgyes
NK088(su)001:9797: nas / dam tshig dang spyod pa ma nor ba dang /
NK088(su)001:9799: de nyid dam par gsol ba la gnang ba byin pa'o //
NK088(su)001:9800: dam tshig dam pa de nye bar zungs shig /tish+tha badz+ra sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK088(su)001:9801: zhes pa gdams nas dam tshig brtan par phog ste dam pa mi 'da' bar bzung ngo //
NK088(su)001:9803: lang ka'i bdag po de nas 'dus pa'i tshogs kyis //
NK088(su)001:9804: zhes pa rang rang gi rigs dam tshig 'bras bu go 'phang gnyis dris pa'o //
NK088(su)001:9805: lang ka'i bdag po bcom ldan 'das /
NK088(su)001:9806: zhes pa la sogs pa nyon cig par gdams pa'o //
NK088(su)001:9807: e ma'o thod pa can gyi tshogs //
NK088(su)001:9808: zhes pa log pa'i spyod pa dang dam tshig gis
NK088(su)001:9809: thar du re ba la ngam pa dang ngo mtshar
NK088(su)001:9810: ba ste / mi ma yin pa la mi'i mgo can du snang ba kun /
NK088(su)001:9812: khyod kyis rang rang gi dam pa smras pa'i tshig ni /
NK088(su)001:9813: so sor rtog pa grol dka' bas mi thar pa'i tshig yin pas /
NK088(su)001:9814: de dus kun tu thar bar mi 'gyur ro zhes gsungs so //
NK088(su)001:9816: yang dag pa'i zhen pa la'ang mi gnas par bya ba'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:9817: yang dag yang dag ces smra ba //
NK088(su)001:9818: zhes pa dag de skad brjod pa ni brjod du
NK088(su)001:9819: med pa dang bsam du med pa la brjod bsam
NK088(su)001:9821: de las thar cing grol bar ma byas na shes
NK088(su)001:9822: rab kyi sgo lcags phye bar mi 'gyur bar bka'
NK088(su)001:9823: stsal pa'o // de ltar mi grol ba so so'i dam tshig dang sbyar nas bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:9824: rtsa ba'i rgyud las ltung ba'i sgo dgu 'di nyid
NK088(su)001:9825: du bcu gsum bstan pa de 'dir gang snyam pa
NK088(su)001:9826: la / mtshams med pa dag /ces pa rgyu des bdud chen por ltung ba'i sgo'o //
NK088(su)001:9827: yi dwags dang chags pa'i las rnams sbyor ba dag
NK088(su)001:9828: /ces pa ni spyir dmyal ba khyad par mngal gyi
NK088(su)001:9830: gang du sdang bas gsod pa'i las //
NK088(su)001:9831: zhes pa shan spyir dmyal ba pa'i rgyu mthun pa
NK088(su)001:9832: ste chags sdang gnyis ni shan par ltung ba'i sgo'o
NK088(su)001:9833: // rgyal ba rnams kyi rnam dag pas //
NK088(su)001:9834: zhes pa ngan skyugs kyi skye bor gyur pa'o //
NK088(su)001:9835: sha dang khrag la sogs pa'i zas //
NK088(su)001:9836: zhes pa de dag spyod pa'i lus la dri za
NK088(su)001:9837: dang srin bu mang po 'dus nas srog gcod pa
NK088(su)001:9838: dang mdangs 'phrogs te yi dwags su skye'o //
NK088(su)001:9839: de nyid rin chen yodabazhina du //
NK088(su)001:9840: zhes pa ma byin par len pas yi dwags su ltung ba'o //
NK088(su)001:9842: zhes pa dkar nag 'dren ma mu stegs su ltung ba'i sgo'o //
NK088(su)001:9844: zhes pa dran pa nyams par 'gyur ro //
NK088(su)001:9846: zhes pa srin por ltung ba'i sgo'o //
NK088(su)001:9848: zhes pa don gyis lha chen por ltung ba'i sgo ste rgyu mthun gyi dbang ngo //
NK088(su)001:9849: bram ze'i lus la sogs pa ni rnam par smin pa'o //
NK088(su)001:9851: zhes pa lha dang gzhal yas khang la sogs pa'i
NK088(su)001:9852: bsgom pa mi dmigs pas ma zin pa ru drar
NK088(su)001:9853: ltung ba'i sgo'o // a dang h'u la sogs pa yi //
NK088(su)001:9854: zhes pa ma skyes pa dang thugs kyi yi ge gnyis rang rgyud du song na /
NK088(su)001:9855: mchod rten hrul po'i sems can dang /
NK088(su)001:9856: tsan+dana gyi sbrul du skye ste /
NK088(su)001:9857: rjes su 'jug pa'i rnal 'byor gyi gzhung ting nge 'dzin mchog gi rgyud las rgyas par 'byung ngo //
NK088(su)001:9859: zhes pa bgegs chen por ltung ba'i sgo'o //
NK088(su)001:9861: zhes pa srin mo brgyad du skye ba'o //
NK088(su)001:9863: zhes pa phra men ma rang rgyud du bsgoms pas sho gam gcan chen can du ltung ba'i sgo'o //
NK088(su)001:9864: las kyi dbang btsan bran mo'i tshogs //
NK088(su)001:9865: zhes pa gnod sbyin mo nyi shu rtsa brgyad du ltung ba'o sgo'o //
NK088(su)001:9866: des na mdud pa dam po 'di //
NK088(su)001:9867: zhes pa la sogs pa skyon de ltar che bas
NK088(su)001:9868: rang rang gi dam tshig la 'dzin pa dgrol dka'
NK088(su)001:9870: de lta bu'i phyin ci log gi ling tog gis shes rab kyi spyan mdongs pas /
NK088(su)001:9871: rang rig pa'i yid bzhin gyi nor bu lta ngan gnyis su rlag pa'o //
NK088(su)001:9872: de dag gang gis dam tshig nor ba yin pa
NK088(su)001:9873: ni bshad pa'i thod pa can dag dang ngo sprod
NK088(su)001:9874: pa'o // 'dus pa'i tshogs de dag rtogs pa'i nad kyis /
NK088(su)001:9875: zhes pa la sogs pa don de thos pas rang gi lta spyod dam pa nor bar shes nas /
NK088(su)001:9876: sngar mthun 'jug tu bka' stsal pa bslus so zhes smras nas /
NK088(su)001:9877: nor ba spyad pa la 'gyod de mchi ma blags so //
NK088(su)001:9879: zhes pa dus gnyis kyis ni /
NK088(su)001:9880: bka' stsal pa dang ngus pa dus gcig gi skabs su gsungs pa ni /
NK088(su)001:9881: rang rang gi las kyi rgyud ltos shig par gdams nas /
NK088(su)001:9882: de dag gi las brtags pas rig pa la snang bas /
NK088(su)001:9883: dpe'i sgo nas dri ma lta bu'i sgrib pa yin par shes so //
NK088(su)001:9886: zhes pa de'i rgyus ma nor ba'i don la 'dod pa skyes nas gsol ba btab pa'o //
NK088(su)001:9887: de'i dgos pa ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK088(su)001:9888: bdag cag ni rang rang gi dka' thub la zhen /
NK088(su)001:9889: zhes pa la sogs pa nor ba'i dam tshig la chags pa ni grol bar bya ste /
NK088(su)001:9890: de ni chos thams cad ni sgyu ma lta bu
NK088(su)001:9891: ste sogs pa chos rnams kyi mtshan nyid ma nges
NK088(su)001:9892: pas bsgyur zhing dgrol du btub bo //
NK088(su)001:9893: theg pa chen po'i sgo ni /
NK088(su)001:9894: zhes pa dag gsang sngags mchog 'dis log pa mi sbyong ba'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:9895: nam mkha' go skabs yangs pa dang /
NK088(su)001:9896: sa spong len med pa dang /
NK088(su)001:9897: rlung cir yang snang ba'i thabs mchog dang ldan pas /
NK088(su)001:9898: rnam rtog log pa'i tshogs de dag shong zhing yang dag par skye ba dang /
NK088(su)001:9900: der ma zad de ston pa nyid thabs mang po'i phung por gyur nas /
NK088(su)001:9901: bdag cag gi bsam pa dang mthun par bstan du gsol zhes gsol ba btab bo //
NK088(su)001:9903: bcom ldan 'das des dgyes pa chen po'i zhal bzhad pa mdzad /
NK088(su)001:9904: ces pa la sogs pa bos pa ni lo rgyus gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:9905: ma nor ba'i don la mos pas dgyes pa mdzad
NK088(su)001:9906: nas gnang ste bos nas bka' stsal pa sgra bzhin
NK088(su)001:9907: no // skye ba 'di las gzhan pa dpag tu med pa blangs /
NK088(su)001:9908: zhes pa la sogs pa da lta'i skye ba ma yin pa khyed kyis snga phyir blangs pa dang /
NK088(su)001:9909: len pa'i skabs su skye ba ji snyed du dngos po bcu gcig smos pa'ang /
NK088(su)001:9910: re re nas tha dad pas gcig tu bzung du
NK088(su)001:9911: mi btub pa ni gtan tshigs te don ma nges
NK088(su)001:9913: gsol ba btab pa sgra ji bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:9914: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal ba /
NK088(su)001:9915: bos nas nyon cig par gsungs nas /
NK088(su)001:9916: yang dag pa'i dam tshig nye bar bstan pa /
NK088(su)001:9917: mtshams med lnga yi dam tshig ni //
NK088(su)001:9918: zhes pa gang gi dam tshig yang dag par bsgyur ba ni log pa dang rim par sprad do //
NK088(su)001:9919: dang po 'dir rtsa ba dang yan lag ma nyams par bsrung ba dang /
NK088(su)001:9921: don ji lta ba rtogs pa'i lta ba dang /
NK088(su)001:9922: don dam pa dang kun rdzob gnyis su med pa'i byang chub kyi sems dang /
NK088(su)001:9923: snying rje chen po ste lnga dus gsum par mtshams med par byed pa'o //
NK088(su)001:9924: chags pa chen po'i dam tshig ni //
NK088(su)001:9925: zhes pa 'khor ba thugs rjes mi gtong ba dang /
NK088(su)001:9926: chos nyid lta bas mi gtong bas mi phyed pa dang /
NK088(su)001:9928: ma dang bu mo sring mo ni //
NK088(su)001:9929: zhes pa dag chos nyid dang ye shes lnga dang mnyam pa'i dbyings shar ba'i rang rig pa ni /
NK088(su)001:9932: rang las byung ba'i phyir ma sring bu mo'o //
NK088(su)001:9933: de dang dus gsum du zhen pa mi 'bral ba'o //
NK088(su)001:9934: gang la skye ba med bstan na //
NK088(su)001:9935: zhes pa dag rnal 'byor pa su zhig la ji
NK088(su)001:9936: bzhin pa'i don bstan pa go mjal bas sa bon
NK088(su)001:9937: thams cad zad par bton pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:9938: dus phyi bar skye ba'i rgyun bral ba dang /
NK088(su)001:9939: ril ma dmigs par gshegs pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:9940: dngos po med la dngos por ston //
NK088(su)001:9941: zhes pa dag yang dag pa'i rdzun ni chos rnams
NK088(su)001:9942: ye ngo bo bral ba las sna tshogs snang ba'i
NK088(su)001:9943: phyir dang / chos so cog tu snang la ma grub pa'i don du ston pa'i mtshon byed ni /
NK088(su)001:9944: rgyal ba rnams kyi bka' lung ste /
NK088(su)001:9945: yang dag pa'i rdzun chen po'o //
NK088(su)001:9946: gzhan gyi yid bzhin nor bu la //
NK088(su)001:9947: zhes pa dag pha rol gyi longs spyod la rgyal
NK088(su)001:9948: ba'i dgongs pa'i rjes su rjes su zhes pa ni
NK088(su)001:9949: dad pa shes par brtson 'grus blang ba ni dam
NK088(su)001:9950: pa'i gdams ngag rtogs pa'i ngang la ma yengs pa
NK088(su)001:9952: lcags kyu ni dran pa ma yengs pa'o //
NK088(su)001:9953: sus kyang ma byin pa blangs pa'o //
NK088(su)001:9954: bsgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi 'od zer gyis blangs nas /
NK088(su)001:9955: bdag gzhan gnyis ka byang chub chen po'i don du 'god pa dang /
NK088(su)001:9956: mngon du thabs dang de nyid kyis 'gugs pa ni dam pa'o //
NK088(su)001:9957: de lta bas na byang chub chen po'i don nyid rig pa'i lcags kyus len pa ni /
NK088(su)001:9958: yang na 'bras bu lnga zad pa med pas ma byin par len pa'o //
NK088(su)001:9959: de nyid chen po de 'dod pas //
NK088(su)001:9960: zhes pa dag lhun gyis grub pa'i de bzhin nyid rtogs par 'dod pas /
NK088(su)001:9961: rtog zhen las slar log ste yang dag pa gnyis med du spyod pa ni /
NK088(su)001:9962: ril chos nyid kyi bya ba de ngang du thim pas ltos pa'i phyir mi 'grub ste /
NK088(su)001:9964: dam tshig ting 'dzin shes rab dang //
NK088(su)001:9965: zhes pa dag ngo bo ni bshad zin te /
NK088(su)001:9966: dam tshig sha dang ting 'dzin gshad //
NK088(su)001:9967: shes rab gci ba sems khu ste //
NK088(su)001:9968: snying rje khrag rnams don gzhi dang //
NK088(su)001:9969: rtog sbyong log dang don bcu dang //
NK088(su)001:9970: 'gro la chags phyir dam pa'i mchog /
NK088(su)001:9971: 'bras bu'i don phyir rgyu yi phul //
NK088(su)001:9973: log par 'tsho ba'i yo byad kyang //
NK088(su)001:9974: zhes pa dag 'khor ba'i 'bras bu 'byin pa'i rgyu ni /
NK088(su)001:9975: 'jigs tshogs dang mthar 'dzin la sogs pa lnga dang /
NK088(su)001:9976: 'dod chags la sogs pa lnga dang /
NK088(su)001:9977: rnam par dkar nag mi g.yo ba'i las dang /
NK088(su)001:9978: nye ba'i nyon mongs pa rnams dang /
NK088(su)001:9979: gzugs sgra la sogs pa lnga la spyod cing 'dun pa dang /
NK088(su)001:9980: pho mo gnyis la chags pa dang bdun te /
NK088(su)001:9981: tshan pa lnga 'dres mar spyod pas log pa la de skad grags pas /
NK088(su)001:9982: 'khor ba bskyed pa'i rgyu chen po'i phyir log pa'i yo byad do //
NK088(su)001:9983: log par spyod pa'i lta ba lnga //
NK088(su)001:9985: bshad pa'i lta ba lnga dang sde lnga phye ste khyad par spyi dbang ngo //
NK088(su)001:9986: de ni ltos pa'i sme zas so //
NK088(su)001:9987: bcom ldan 'das kyis de skad ces bka' stsal pa /
NK088(su)001:9989: de ltar 'khor gyis don mthong nas zhus pa dang /
NK088(su)001:9990: theg pa chen po la gang yang dog pa med par shong ba dang /
NK088(su)001:9991: de'i gtan tshigs zhus pas 'grel to //
NK088(su)001:9992: ji ltar nam mkha'i rang bzhin la //
NK088(su)001:9994: don ni gsang sngags rgya mtsho'i sgor lta ba ril dang spyod pa ril shong ba dang /
NK088(su)001:9995: spang bya med pa'i gtan tshigs des na /
NK088(su)001:9996: gsang sngags ma yin pa med par lan btab bo //
NK088(su)001:9998: zhes pa dag sgra bzhin te /
NK088(su)001:9999: don rang la yod pa sngar ma shes pa la mchi ma blags so //
NK088(su)001:10001: zhes pa ston pas dris pa dang 'khor gyis lan sgra bzhin te /
NK088(su)001:10003: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK088(su)001:10004: zhes pa dag ston pas 'khor khyed cag gi sems
NK088(su)001:10005: nyid ye ma bsgribs par sangs rgyas pa nyid bshad
NK088(su)001:10006: pa bzhin ma rig pas ma mthong ba tsam ste
NK088(su)001:10007: / ngo bo nyid ril de nyid kyi ngang la bshad nyan yang med la /
NK088(su)001:10008: bdag nyid yin pa'i phyir bshad ci dgos par bka'
NK088(su)001:10009: stsal pas 'khor gyi rig pa la don de snang
NK088(su)001:10010: ba gtang rag phul ba sgra bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:10011: rmongs pa sel ba spyod mthun dgrol ba'i le'u zhes
NK088(su)001:10012: pa 'khor don ma mthong ba'i sgrib pa sel ba'i
NK088(su)001:10013: phyir / khong dag rang rang gi bsam spyod dang
NK088(su)001:10014: mthun 'jug sbyor ba'i lung du bka' stsal ba lo
NK088(su)001:10015: rgyus su brjod pa gsang ba'i 'khor 'dus pa de
NK088(su)001:10016: dag rgyud dgrol bar gyur to //
NK088(su)001:10017: le'u sum cu drug pa mdor 'grel pa'o //
NK088(su)001:10018: de yan chad du bam po lnga'o ///
NK088(su)001:10021: de nas lang ka'i mnga' bdag byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po des /
NK088(su)001:10022: zhes pa dag sgra ji lta bar 'grel te dris lan no //
NK088(su)001:10024: gsang ba dam pa ni shin tu me dang 'dra ste /
NK088(su)001:10026: zhes pa la sogs pa gsang ba spyad legs nyes kyi dper bstan pa ste /
NK088(su)001:10027: rtsa ba'i rgyud las 'das pa sngon byung gi le'u las ston te /
NK088(su)001:10028: de dag gis 'dir 'grel te sgra ji bzhin du sbyar to //
NK088(su)001:10029: 'o na rtsa bas bshad rgyud 'grel ba ni de
NK088(su)001:10030: nyid mi nges par 'gyur ro bar dogs pa la
NK088(su)001:10031: / de ni skabs su sgo gsal ba dang rgyas pa'ang yod kyi /
NK088(su)001:10032: spyir rtsa ba las yan lag rgyas par phye ba'i
NK088(su)001:10033: grangs shin tu rgyas par bshad rgyud las ston pa'i
NK088(su)001:10034: phyir na / the tshom gyi dog pa sel bar 'gyur ro //
NK088(su)001:10037: zhes pa gsang bas sdud pa la bos nas /
NK088(su)001:10038: lo rgyus su brjod pa'i ston pa po des 'khor
NK088(su)001:10039: la gsungs pa zhu ba nye bar bstan pa ni
NK088(su)001:10040: / brgyud de grags pas gang spyod pa //
NK088(su)001:10041: zhes pa la sogs pa bshad pa ltar rgyal ba
NK088(su)001:10042: las rim par brgyud de lha mi la grags pa'i
NK088(su)001:10043: gsang sngags gzhung du byed pa'i rnal 'byor pas gsang
NK088(su)001:10044: don 'di spyad legs ji lta ba sngar gsungs pa
NK088(su)001:10045: ltar 'dir yang lung rigs man ngag gsum gyis gtan
NK088(su)001:10047: de lta bu'i gsang ba ni spyad legs na lam ma nor ba'o //
NK088(su)001:10048: gang du log pa'i chos rnams dang //
NK088(su)001:10049: zhes pa la sogs pa gsang ba nyid las log
NK088(su)001:10050: mu stegs yin pa pa dang ma nor bar spyod
NK088(su)001:10051: pa dag /gsang sngags spyod par ming mthun pas brtag
NK088(su)001:10052: dka' ba'i phyir / blos dpyad de nges par brtags te zin par bya /
NK088(su)001:10053: don ma nor bar mthong bar bya'o //
NK088(su)001:10054: theg pa chen po'i gsang sngags 'di //
NK088(su)001:10055: zhes pa dag gsang ba'i thabs ni gang yang mi spang ba'i tshul ni /
NK088(su)001:10056: gdul bya ji ltar dga' ba ltar mos phyogs su ston pa la /
NK088(su)001:10057: don ma rnyed par sgra bzhin du go nas thar
NK088(su)001:10058: pa bzhin du 'byung phyi rol gzhan du 'gyur srid
NK088(su)001:10060: mtshon pa tshig dang sgra tsam la nges pa'i gdeng du mi bya'o //
NK088(su)001:10062: dam pa rnams kyi dgongs pa 'di //
NK088(su)001:10063: zhes pa la sogs pa rgyal ba rnams kyi dgongs pa'i zhe phugs gsang sngags ji bzhin pa ni /
NK088(su)001:10064: brjod pas thog tu mi 'bab pa dang /
NK088(su)001:10065: thun mong du ma gyur pas thun mong bdag gis mthun pa'i dpe dang /
NK088(su)001:10068: gzhi yang gnyis su 'dus pa'i mngon sum la'ang dbang po dang /
NK088(su)001:10072: de'ang mngon sum yin la rigs pa ma yin pa dang /
NK088(su)001:10073: rigs pa yin la mngon sum ma yin pa dang /
NK088(su)001:10075: gnyis ka ma yin pa dag rjes su dpag pa
NK088(su)001:10076: la yang bshad pa dag gi lkog tu gyur pa
NK088(su)001:10077: gnyis la dmigs pa dag dang /
NK088(su)001:10079: gtan tshigs 'ba' zhig gis sbyor ba dang /
NK088(su)001:10080: mthun pa'i phyogs nyid can gyis sbyor ba dang /
NK088(su)001:10081: mi mthun pa'i phyogs nyid can gyi sbyor ba dag gis gtan la 'bebs pa dang /
NK088(su)001:10082: rig pa bzhi dang bcas pas dpog pa'i so sor
NK088(su)001:10083: rtog pa'i shes rab kyi gsang sngags go bar mi
NK088(su)001:10084: nus so // 'on kyang gzhung 'di nyid kyi dpe
NK088(su)001:10085: dang tshad ma la sogs pa mi 'dod pa ni
NK088(su)001:10086: nus so // ma yin no // dgongs don gsang ba'i snying po la //
NK088(su)001:10087: zhes pa dag /ma rtogs par 'chad pa dag ma
NK088(su)001:10088: bshad ma rtogs par bshad pa long bas long ba
NK088(su)001:10089: khrid pa lta bu bas na khyod nges par 'achi'am
NK088(su)001:10091: de bzhin spyod dang lta ba dang //
NK088(su)001:10092: zhes pa gsang sngags la dmigs pa lta ba dang /
NK088(su)001:10093: byed pa bsgrub dang ched du gnyer ba dang /
NK088(su)001:10094: rtog dpyod byed pa'i gang zag don shed ma bye
NK088(su)001:10095: bar byed pa dag /gsang ba ma spyad na khyod
NK088(su)001:10096: la nyes pa ci byung stee /
NK088(su)001:10097: gdod nas ma thos na shin tu dge ba yin pas log par ma spyod cig pa'o //
NK088(su)001:10098: ci phyir gsang sngags rgya mtsho 'di //
NK088(su)001:10099: zhes pa la sogs pa gsang ba'i don gting dpag dka' ba ni /
NK088(su)001:10100: dper rgyal ba sh+aakya thub pas sprid pa bsangs pa la /
NK088(su)001:10101: nad pa dang sman pa dang khyo mo gsum gyi rna bar /
NK088(su)001:10102: rin chen srog dang ma bral na //
NK088(su)001:10103: sgyu ma'i nor ni btsal gyis rnyed //
NK088(su)001:10104: nor gyi mchog ni snying rje yin //
NK088(su)001:10105: phyi ma cir 'gyur cha med kyis //
NK088(su)001:10106: snga ma de la nan tan skyed //
NK088(su)001:10107: ces so sor thos pa ltar bka' lung gcig kyang
NK088(su)001:10108: brda dang dgongs pa'i skabs kyis don du mar 'gyur
NK088(su)001:10109: bas shin tu brda mjal bar daka'o //
NK088(su)001:10110: des na gsang ba dam pa'i don //
NK088(su)001:10111: zhes pa dag ni ma rtogs par bshad pa'i sdig
NK088(su)001:10112: pa'i tshad de lam log par bkod pa'i phyir ro
NK088(su)001:10113: // gsang ba nyid las gol ba yi //
NK088(su)001:10114: zhes pa phyogs dang zla dang rang rgyud du gol
NK088(su)001:10115: ba'i gang zag shed ma bye bar gzhan la smra
NK088(su)001:10116: ba'i log pa la zhen chags dang ldan pa dag
NK088(su)001:10118: gsang sngags kyi thabs kyis bya bas zin na 'gro
NK088(su)001:10119: ba bsad kyang sdig pa mi 'ong bas sod cig
NK088(su)001:10120: ces log pa'i lam du kha lo bsgyur ba dus
NK088(su)001:10121: phyis kyang dran pa thog ma'i dus na /
NK088(su)001:10122: bram ze'i rigs log lta can bshad pa ltar gzhan
NK088(su)001:10123: la chos log par ston cing rang yang spyod pas
NK088(su)001:10124: gzhan log pa'i lam du bsgyur ba byung ngo //
NK088(su)001:10125: 'di dag rtsa ba'i rgyud las kyang gsal po 'byung ba'i rjes su bsnyad do //
NK088(su)001:10126: gang 'dir log par spyod rgyas pa //
NK088(su)001:10127: zhes pa bshad pa ltar log par spyod pa'ang 'phel te /
NK088(su)001:10128: rigs kyang log pa la zhugs te /
NK088(su)001:10129: de la ming du gsang sngags spyod par btags nas mngon du byed pa 'byung ngo //
NK088(su)001:10131: dran pa thog ma'i dus de nyid na /
NK088(su)001:10132: gang du gzhan 'byung log sred can //
NK088(su)001:10133: zhes pa dag dus kyi dngos po der bram ze
NK088(su)001:10134: de nyid ma yin pa'i 'gro ba log lta can
NK088(su)001:10136: gsang ba dam pa'i nyid ma yin par tshul mtshungs
NK088(su)001:10137: par spyod pas yang dag pa las nor ba 'byung
NK088(su)001:10138: ngo // gang du 'di ltar log pa'i chos //
NK088(su)001:10139: zhes pa dus gang yang rung bar sngags nor ba'i chos spyod pa ni /
NK088(su)001:10140: theg pa chen po gsang sngags kyi bka' lung ni
NK088(su)001:10141: gcig kyang bshad pa ltar don du ma 'byung ba'i
NK088(su)001:10142: gzhi mdongs pas ma rig par spyad pa ni /
NK088(su)001:10143: rnal 'byor de bdud kyi spyod pa la gnas pa ste /
NK088(su)001:10144: rnam par smin pa dmyal ba chen po brgyad kyi steng du skye'o //
NK088(su)001:10145: ci phyir lta bas ma zin phyir //
NK088(su)001:10146: zhes pa dag lta ba bas ma zin pa kho na gtan tshigs te /
NK088(su)001:10147: bdud dang rak+sha'i spyod pa rang dgas bag chags brtas
NK088(su)001:10148: pas tsha grang brgyad kyi 'og /tshe tshad las 'das
NK088(su)001:10149: pas sdug bsngal mchog tu che ba rdo rje'i gtan
NK088(su)001:10150: gtun gyis sbyor bas mkhun par yang mi nus pa'i
NK088(su)001:10152: de yang ji lta bu zhe na //
NK088(su)001:10153: zhes pa lo rgyus brjod pa ste thar pa nag po nyid lta bu'o //
NK088(su)001:10154: e ma'o 'gro ba rnams mi grol //
NK088(su)001:10155: zhes pa la sogs pa log pas log par bsgyur bas ltung ba'i ngo mtshar ba ni /
NK088(su)001:10156: log pas bcings pa'i sems can 'jig rten du 'byung ba'i dus dag tu /
NK088(su)001:10157: des log g.yo dang ldan pas don nor bar bsgyur
NK088(su)001:10158: nas gsang sngags yin zhes ston pas sgro skur med
NK088(su)001:10159: pa'i gsang ba'i chos rnams gzhung dkrugs shing log pas
NK088(su)001:10160: bka' bslad sel byas nas ma nor ba'i lugs gzhung
NK088(su)001:10161: bor bzhag ste / nor ba'i don med log par chos 'phel ba'i rgyu yang gzhan ma yin te /
NK088(su)001:10162: gsang sngags rtsa ba nyid las gyur bar zad nyid gnad khong du ma chud pa las gyur to //
NK088(su)001:10163: de yang ji lta bu zhe na //
NK088(su)001:10165: sngon bskal pa grangs med pa'i sngon du gsang sngags
NK088(su)001:10166: ma nor ba'i phyogs ma 'di bar ma gyur yin
NK088(su)001:10167: pa / log pa'i bslad pa can sel dang ldan
NK088(su)001:10168: pa'i shes rgyud smad pas rang gis rang bslad de
NK088(su)001:10169: rgyud ngan pas de nyid bslad pa'o //
NK088(su)001:10170: nga yi yid bzhin nor bu 'di //
NK088(su)001:10171: zhes pa dag ston pa'i bka' yon tan gyi 'byung
NK088(su)001:10172: gnas gsang sngags zab mo thabs kyi sgo ji lta
NK088(su)001:10173: bur yang 'grel ba'i don zab mo blos rtogs dpag
NK088(su)001:10174: dka' ba'i gtan tshigs des na /
NK088(su)001:10175: phyis kyang ma 'ongs dus kyi log spyod kyis /
NK088(su)001:10176: nor bar zhen pas de'i gzhung 'dzin pa mang po sder langs pa 'byung ste /
NK088(su)001:10177: dus de tsam gyi phyi dus yin no //
NK088(su)001:10178: de kho na so so'i sde ma 'dres par bstan pa gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:10179: 'das pa'i dus na sngon byung ba //
NK088(su)001:10180: zhes pa dag dus der gsang ba dam pa'i lam rlag pa gol ba /
NK088(su)001:10181: shin tu log pa mu stegs kyi rigs can phyin
NK088(su)001:10182: ci log la chags pa'i sde pa phyogs mthun pa
NK088(su)001:10183: tshan pa gcig la'ang drug ste /
NK088(su)001:10184: rgya byed tsha la gnas sde dang /
NK088(su)001:10186: gtsug lag khang chen sde dang /
NK088(su)001:10187: mthar sgrogs rig byed sde dang /
NK088(su)001:10189: gnas ma bu'i sde dang drug go //
NK088(su)001:10190: phyogs log par gyur pa la drug ste /
NK088(su)001:10191: so so tha dad rgyur lta la spyad pas /
NK088(su)001:10192: dag par lta ba la sogs pa'i sde drug ste log sde phrag gcig go //
NK088(su)001:10193: gang la log zhen log dbang gis //
NK088(su)001:10194: zhen pa la sogs pa log pa'i shes bya gang
NK088(su)001:10195: rung la mngon par chags pa'i dbang gis rgyun log
NK088(su)001:10196: pa'i shes rab kyis de nyid lta ba'i log mthong
NK088(su)001:10197: mchog tu gtsor bzung nas byed pas ma nor ba'i
NK088(su)001:10198: sgo rnams la 'jug pa'i sems bral te /
NK088(su)001:10199: ma rig pa'i lta ba las mi 'gyur ba'o //
NK088(su)001:10200: de yang ci lta bu zhe na //
NK088(su)001:10201: zhes pa la sogs pa de'i tshul 'dzin pa'i dus
NK088(su)001:10202: der phyin ci log la mngon par zhen pa dang
NK088(su)001:10203: ldan pa'i thar pa nag po'o //
NK088(su)001:10204: des na bshad pa'i dus dang 'chad pa rnams bskal pa kun dga' lta bur rigs so //
NK088(su)001:10205: gang 'dir bcing pa lngas bcings nas //
NK088(su)001:10206: zhes pa dag nag po de nyon mongs lnga'i zhags
NK088(su)001:10207: pas bsdams pas che ba'i nga rgyal gyi sa la
NK088(su)001:10208: gnas te / bsam pa'i shes rab tsam yang mi
NK088(su)001:10209: bsten pas ma rig pas non pa ni glang po
NK088(su)001:10211: de'i tshul ni bskal pa de la log pa'i sde nag po rang gcig pu ste /
NK088(su)001:10212: nga las btsan pa dang che ba med par nga rgyal bas gzhan la log chos ston pa'o //
NK088(su)001:10213: gang du dmus long lam zhugs pa //
NK088(su)001:10215: dper ma lto nas long ba zhig lam du song
NK088(su)001:10216: na yid kyis dpags nas gom pa 'dor yang g.yang
NK088(su)001:10218: gsang ba'i don ma rtogs par ngan dpyod kyis spyod pa mchog tu byed pa 'byung ba'i tshul ni /
NK088(su)001:10219: dus gang du de nyid du ma rig pas mun
NK088(su)001:10220: bsdams pa'i zin pa'i lta ba pa dge 'dun phal
NK088(su)001:10221: chen sde'o // de las kyang nub kyi ri bo'i sde dang /
NK088(su)001:10222: shar gyi ri bo'i sde dang /
NK088(su)001:10223: gangs rir gnas pa'i sde dang /
NK088(su)001:10224: rtag par smra ba'i sde dang /
NK088(su)001:10225: 'jig rten 'das pa'i sde dang lnga ste /
NK088(su)001:10226: phyogs ltos dpyod pa gsang ba chen po'i zhar las byung ba barlanga po'i brtul zhugs spyod pa ste /
NK088(su)001:10227: gzhi tshul khrims dang brtul zhugs mchog tu 'dzin pa las gyes pa'i sde lnga'o //
NK088(su)001:10228: lung med rnal 'byor bsgom pa dang //
NK088(su)001:10229: zhes pa dag nges pa'i lung med par ting nge 'dzin byed pa dang /
NK088(su)001:10230: shed ma bye bar gzhan la sgrogs pa'i log spyod
NK088(su)001:10231: rtsa hral can log pa'i brtul zhugs gtsor byed pa
NK088(su)001:10233: dus der yang lung dang rig par ma brtags par
NK088(su)001:10234: byung rgyal du smra ba ni nang ris thams cad
NK088(su)001:10235: yod par smra ba'i sde dang /
NK088(su)001:10236: dge 'dun phal che ba'i sde dang /
NK088(su)001:10238: legs dpogs pa'i sde dag go //
NK088(su)001:10240: gang du shes pa yod smra ltar //
NK088(su)001:10241: de bzhin med par lta ba dang //
NK088(su)001:10243: gang du yod min med min lta //
NK088(su)001:10246: don med 'dug la brtson pa dang //
NK088(su)001:10247: zhes pa la sogs pa rtag tu dgon pa gdeng
NK088(su)001:10248: med par yal bar 'dug pa la grims pa dang
NK088(su)001:10249: / gser dngul dang 'jim pa la sogs pa'i brnyan ma la de nyid du zhen pas /
NK088(su)001:10250: thabs kyis ma zin pa'i mtshan ma can bsgyur dka' ba dag byung ba'i tshul ni /
NK088(su)001:10252: tshogs lnga'i sgo bkag nas nang du bsdus te /
NK088(su)001:10253: log pa'i ting nge 'dzin la 'jug pa'i ris bdun ni /
NK088(su)001:10254: yod par smra ba las gyes pa /
NK088(su)001:10255: gzhi thams cad yod par smra ba'i sde dang /
NK088(su)001:10259: mang du thos pa'i sde dang /
NK088(su)001:10261: rnam par phye ste smra ba'i sde byung ngo //
NK088(su)001:10262: de yang gzhan las gyur pa sde lnga dang /
NK088(su)001:10263: 'di las gyur pa sde gnyis te /
NK088(su)001:10264: kun nas rnam par mi g.yeng lta //
NK088(su)001:10265: zhes pa re brgyad pa las /
NK088(su)001:10266: zhar byung las gsal bar gang du rags pa'i ri bo 'byung ston to //
NK088(su)001:10267: sbas pa'i don rnams sgra bsgyur nas //
NK088(su)001:10268: zhes pa la sogs pa spyod gsang bar byas pa
NK088(su)001:10269: rnams brda dang zur gyis ston pa dag /rang thad
NK088(su)001:10270: kyi sgrar dpyad nas smras pas gtan la mi phebs
NK088(su)001:10271: te / rgyal ba'i rdo rje gsum mi 'thob par byed pa'i steng du mi 'bab gol sar 'gro /
NK088(su)001:10273: sdud pa po la bos nas /
NK088(su)001:10274: sngon yang de nas gsang ba pos bka' stsal te zhes bsnyad do //
NK088(su)001:10275: gzhan yang thabs ldan 'di lta ste //
NK088(su)001:10276: zhes pa la sogs pa gol ba mi mthun pa 'chad pa ni /
NK088(su)001:10277: blo gros thabs ldan lang ka la bos nas nye bar bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:10278: skabs kyi tshig gi 'brel pa'ang dus der ston pas
NK088(su)001:10279: gsungs ma thag par 'khor gyi rnal 'byor gnyis kyis
NK088(su)001:10280: rtsod pa ston pa'i phyir snyegs pa dang 'dren pa'o
NK088(su)001:10281: // ston pa de nyid kyi 'khor du gtogs pa
NK088(su)001:10282: theg pa mchog la zhugs pa'i tshangs pa'i 'od la
NK088(su)001:10283: // / mos pa chung ngu na gnas pa'i grags
NK088(su)001:10284: ldan gyis the tshom gyi gal po dri ba bcu
NK088(su)001:10285: // / gcig dris pa'o // dam par spyod pa tshangs pa'i 'od //
NK088(su)001:10286: ces pa la sogs pa dri ba dang po la'ang gsum gyi thog ma ni /
NK088(su)001:10287: bos nas khyed theg pa chen por spyod do zhes zer nas /
NK088(su)001:10288: 'khor ba'i spyod pa smad pa dag byed pa ni
NK088(su)001:10289: 'bras bu rnam pa mang po yod pa'i gtan tshigs
NK088(su)001:10290: nges na / de yang dag pa'i spyod par mi
NK088(su)001:10291: 'gyur ba ni dper mun pa snang bar mi 'gyur
NK088(su)001:10293: spyod pa ngan pa de yang dag pa'i spyod par
NK088(su)001:10294: mi 'gyur ro zhes gsang ba'i thabs kyis spyod pa
NK088(su)001:10295: gang yang mi spang ba la dris so //
NK088(su)001:10297: zhes pa la sogs pa dag tshig dang po gnyis dper 'gyur te /
NK088(su)001:10298: de ltar byang chub mchog thob par 'dod pas spyod
NK088(su)001:10299: pa de dag spyad na mi khom pa brgyad du
NK088(su)001:10300: skye bar des na der mi ltung ba'i thabs ci
NK088(su)001:10302: yang tshig gnyis ni dper 'gyur ro //
NK088(su)001:10303: de bzhin du sa pa dag sangs rgyas pa nyid du 'grub par bsam pa zhig yod na /
NK088(su)001:10304: mnyam pa nyid spyod pa la dman pa'i spyod pa
NK088(su)001:10305: rnams byas nas thob par rigs pa ma yin na
NK088(su)001:10306: / des ji ltar thob cing bshad pa'i spyod pa
NK088(su)001:10307: la dris pa'i bye brag gis gsum gyi tha mar
NK088(su)001:10308: / te / 'chad pa'ang rjes su mthun par 'gyur ro //
NK088(su)001:10310: zhes pa dper sbrul gyi sgo nga khyung du mi 'gyur ba ltar /
NK088(su)001:10311: 'gro ba'i spyod pa smad pa rnams yang dag pa'i
NK088(su)001:10312: rgyal ba'i spyod par mi 'gyur bas don gyi yang
NK088(su)001:10313: dag pa'i spyod pa grub par btub bam dris pa'i
NK088(su)001:10314: spyi gnyis pa'o // gang gis gsang ba las log pa //
NK088(su)001:10315: zhes pa la sogs pa rnal 'byor pa su zhig
NK088(su)001:10316: gi spyod pa theg pa chen po las 'khrul pa
NK088(su)001:10317: phyin ci log tu spyad pa gang dag kyang /
NK088(su)001:10318: dngos po thams cad ma grub pas mnyam pa nyid
NK088(su)001:10319: yin pas don ma rig pa dang chos sku yang
NK088(su)001:10320: ngo bos ma grub par mnyam mo zhes tshig tu
NK088(su)001:10321: smra ste / des don thog tu bab bam zhes dri ba gsum pa'o //
NK088(su)001:10322: 'tsho ba'i sman dang 'chi ba'i dug /ces pa dape'o //
NK088(su)001:10323: de bzhin dam pa dman pa'i las //
NK088(su)001:10324: zhes pa dag de ltar na theg dam pa pa
NK088(su)001:10325: chen po pas dug dman pa dang 'dra ba'i spyod
NK088(su)001:10326: pa kun gyis spang byar bzhag pa'i spyad par bya
NK088(su)001:10327: ba bzhi la sogs pa spyod pa bzang ngan dag
NK088(su)001:10328: ji bzhin par dbyer med na yang /
NK088(su)001:10329: 'dra mnyam par ba la spyod pa rnam par dkar
NK088(su)001:10330: ba bor nas sbyor sgrol la sogs pa ched du
NK088(su)001:10331: byed pa zhig min nam 'di'i don ji lta bu
NK088(su)001:10332: yin / tshul de lta bas na spyod pa dkar
NK088(su)001:10333: nag dang gtsang sme la sogs pa gnyis pa rnams
NK088(su)001:10334: mnyam mo zhes smra ba ni /
NK088(su)001:10335: dper dper na mchod gnas dam pa zhig bsti gnas sprul sku lta bu dang /
NK088(su)001:10336: 'jig rten gyi spyad tsam sman pa lta bu gyi las byed pa gnyis snyoms pa dang 'dra ste /
NK088(su)001:10337: spyod pa ci'ang mi 'gog pa de mnyam par sbyor
NK088(su)001:10338: pa'i don gyis mtshon pa'i rtags sam thabs su spyod
NK088(su)001:10339: do zhe na / des dug sman dang 'dra ste /
NK088(su)001:10340: bzang ngan mi mnyam pa can kun rdzob tu mi
NK088(su)001:10341: mnyam ste de mnyam par ga la 'gyur te mi
NK088(su)001:10342: 'gyur ro // ma bcos mnyam pa'i chos nyid la //
NK088(su)001:10343: zhes pa dag ye nas chos nyid che chung dang
NK088(su)001:10344: bral ba'i don las ma 'das kyang rang gi glo
NK088(su)001:10345: bur gyi las dang rtog pas che chung la sogs
NK088(su)001:10346: par snang ngo // tshig lhag ma ni khyod spyod pa mnyam pa nyid du 'dod pa ni /
NK088(su)001:10347: mi mthun pa'i dpe nam mkha' 'khrul bar 'dod pa dang 'dra'o //
NK088(su)001:10348: zhes khyod kyis mnyam par mi 'gyur bar smras te thag bcad pa'o //
NK088(su)001:10351: zhes pa dpe de ltar 'jig gong ltar rten pa
NK088(su)001:10352: drang thabs su gsang sngags pa ngan par spyod do
NK088(su)001:10353: zhe na'ang / khyed 'gro don du gsang sngags kyi
NK088(su)001:10354: rnam par dkar ba spyad na nyes pa zhig 'byung
NK088(su)001:10355: zhe na'ang / ngam / de mi spyod des don
NK088(su)001:10356: mi byed pa ji lta bu zhes dris te bzhi
NK088(su)001:10357: zhe na'ang / ngam / pa'o // mthun 'jug spyod pa drang ba'i thabs //
NK088(su)001:10358: zhes pa la sogs pa 'gro ba dang mthun pas
NK088(su)001:10359: 'dren pa'ang gdul bya'i bsam dbang du don spyod pa
NK088(su)001:10360: ni / dper na gang dpa' bo mdzangs pa shes rig can gyis /
NK088(su)001:10361: pha rol dang mi mthun pa dag thabs kyis 'og
NK088(su)001:10362: tu bcug pas dga' bas mthun par byed pa ltar
NK088(su)001:10363: / gdul bya dang ngag smra bar mtshungs par mos par byed pa'i don can gyis /
NK088(su)001:10364: don bya bar ni ji lta rig pa de ltar nges bden tshad mar bya'i /
NK088(su)001:10365: rang dbang med pa'i sgrol ba la sogs pa'i bya ba ni mi rigs so zhes dri ba lnga'o //
NK088(su)001:10366: ji ltar zhum pas khe brkam gyis //
NK088(su)001:10367: zhes pa la sogs pa dper na sdar ma dpa'
NK088(su)001:10368: zhum zhig gis khe dang grags pa 'dod pa'i ched
NK088(su)001:10369: du / rtsal stobs kyi nyams bag med par g.yul du zhugs te /
NK088(su)001:10370: pha rol gyi dpung dang stobs bkye nas rtsod na /
NK088(su)001:10371: gzhan gyi dpung gis rang nges par rlag ste kho'i dbang du 'gyur ba bzhin /
NK088(su)001:10372: de bzhin dam par bcos pa yis //
NK088(su)001:10373: zhes pa de ltar gsang sngags bar bcos pa'i mis /
NK088(su)001:10374: khe grags dang nga'i rlom sems 'dod pa'i ched du /
NK088(su)001:10375: gdul bya log pa rnams 'dren pa'i cha mthun gyi
NK088(su)001:10376: spyod pa la yang dag dam par nges bzung nas
NK088(su)001:10377: gdeng med par spyod pa gtsor byas te sgra ji
NK088(su)001:10378: bzhin par tshig gi lam nyid sgrar spyad na bdag
NK088(su)001:10379: gzhan gnyis ka ltung nges so zhes dri ba drug
NK088(su)001:10380: pa'o // thams cad gang gi theg tshad dang //
NK088(su)001:10381: zhes pa gang zag ril rang rang gi blos dngos po la 'tshams tshad dang /
NK088(su)001:10383: blo rtsal gyi nus tshad kyis nyams 'og tu chud gang du 'du tshad las ma gtogs pa /
NK088(su)001:10384: mi 'tshams pa la sogs par kun bzlog pa ni
NK088(su)001:10385: tshad las yul med de gdul bya dang ma 'phrod
NK088(su)001:10386: pas 'das na 'das pa nyid brgal te /
NK088(su)001:10387: shin tu'ang sdug bsngal gyi rgyu'am zhes dri ba bdun pa'i don to //
NK088(su)001:10388: gang yang tshad las 'das pa ni //
NK088(su)001:10389: zhes pa dpe bzhin du lta ba'i tshig gi khyad khams la brten nas /
NK088(su)001:10390: log pa'i dug chen po khong du chud par byed
NK088(su)001:10391: pa'i gang zag de'i spyod pa de dag rnal 'byor
NK088(su)001:10392: mchog gis spyad par mi rigs te /
NK088(su)001:10393: rgyal po la gdol ba'i spyod pa gnyer med pa
NK088(su)001:10394: dang mi 'dra 'am zhes dri ba brgyad pa'i tshig
NK088(su)001:10395: go // gang dag gang gis bcings pa las //
NK088(su)001:10396: zhes pa dag ni rnal 'byor pa su yang rung
NK088(su)001:10397: ba zhig gis rang mi shes pa'i d+r+wa ba'i rgyar
NK088(su)001:10398: chud bzhin pha rol sgrol bar rtsom pa ni /
NK088(su)001:10399: rkyal ma sbyangs par gzhan chu bo las sgrol ba dang 'dra ste /
NK088(su)001:10400: gnyis ka rlag pa'i phyir bslu ba'i spyod pa ste /
NK088(su)001:10401: de lta bu gsang sngags kyi spyod pas ci zhig bya ste /
NK088(su)001:10402: spyod pa bslab pa dang dngos ci lta bu zhes dri ba dgu pa'i tshig go //
NK088(su)001:10403: de nyid ma rig ma grol zhing //
NK088(su)001:10404: zhes pa dag theg pa chen por khas 'che ba'i
NK088(su)001:10405: gang zag de dngos kyi don ma rig ma mthong
NK088(su)001:10406: rgyud ma sbyangs ma grol te /
NK088(su)001:10407: de'i theg pa chen po'i don rig rtogs pa'i pa'i blo ma skyes na /
NK088(su)001:10408: rgyal ba'i zhing du bzhag kyang spang nges rang gi rtog pas dmyal ba'i yul du mthong ngo //
NK088(su)001:10409: rtogs de rig pa dang de'i don ldan na ma
NK088(su)001:10410: bsgral yang rgyal ba'i zhing dag par du dmyal yul
NK088(su)001:10412: sngags kyis sgrol ba'i kha na yod dam zhes dri ba bcu pa'i tshig go //
NK088(su)001:10413: gsang ba'i snying pos kun khyab kyang //
NK088(su)001:10414: zhes pa la sogs pa chos nyid ji bzhin pa
NK088(su)001:10415: phra zhing zab pa'i mchog des bdal ba la tshabs
NK088(su)001:10417: rtogs pa med na spyod pa spyad kyang mi grol
NK088(su)001:10418: bas don mthong ba ni dpe ji lta ba bzhin
NK088(su)001:10419: te dri ba bcu gcig pa'i don te //
NK088(su)001:10420: de dag lan nges par bstan pa gang snyam pa la /
NK088(su)001:10421: tshangs pa'i 'od ces bya ba ni sgra bzhin te smra ba'i lan ldon pa'o //
NK088(su)001:10422: 'dir rgyun dkrug pa ras chod can gyi ched du
NK088(su)001:10423: mdzad pa'i dbang du na thog mar dri ba drug
NK088(su)001:10426: zhes pa dag rgol ba po la bos nas /
NK088(su)001:10427: theg pa chen po gsang sngags kyi don ni spyod yul bzhi las /
NK088(su)001:10428: 'dir rang rig pa'i mngon sum gyi yul rgyal ba
NK088(su)001:10429: nyid las gzhan bkag pa gang gi spyod yul ma
NK088(su)001:10430: yin pas ni / mngon sum du ma mthong ba'i
NK088(su)001:10431: phyir sgra ji bzhin par spyad na rlag par byed
NK088(su)001:10432: pas tshul bcos kyis mi 'grub par lan btab ste
NK088(su)001:10433: yin pas ni / / 'on kyang mos pa dang
NK088(su)001:10434: slob pa dang brgyud pa'i spyod yul ni 'dir bsal
NK088(su)001:10435: yin pas ni / / ba med do // lan bdun pa gang snyam pa la /
NK088(su)001:10438: gang rnal 'byor pa su zhig gis 'dir theg pa chen po'i sgor shin tu dad pa dang /
NK088(su)001:10440: rtogs par 'dod pas bsam dpyod nus nas /
NK088(su)001:10441: de nyid rnal 'byor de theg pa chen po de la rtse gcig tu der bstan na dmigs na /
NK088(su)001:10442: yang dag pa de la ji bzhin pa'i don la
NK088(su)001:10443: gang zag de sbyor de 'gro zhing de nyid du
NK088(su)001:10444: de rigs nges pas de bzhin du rim pas 'bad
NK088(su)001:10445: de dag tsam pa ni 'tshams pa ste theg tshad
NK088(su)001:10446: ltung ba med par lan btab bo //
NK088(su)001:10447: lan smin dper brgyad pa'ang snang lnga pa gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:10448: gang 'dir theg pa mang bshad pa //
NK088(su)001:10449: zhes pa la sogs pa ston pa gang zhig gis theg pa chen po'i sgor /
NK088(su)001:10450: theg pa mang thabs kyi bye brag ji snyed du
NK088(su)001:10451: gsungs pa ngo bos ris su tha dad yod pa
NK088(su)001:10452: ma yin te ma chad de /
NK088(su)001:10453: 'on kyang gang zag mos pa tha dad pa'i ched
NK088(su)001:10454: du thabs kyi spyod sgo mang po bka' stsal pas
NK088(su)001:10455: rnal 'byor dam pa'i spyod pa'ang ma nges te /
NK088(su)001:10456: ji spyad kyang 'ching ba'i dug tu mi 'gyur bas bden pa ma nor bar lan btab bo //
NK088(su)001:10457: lan dgu pa ji lta bu zhe na /
NK088(su)001:10458: de kun mos pa ma bkags pa'i //
NK088(su)001:10459: zhes pa la sogs pa spyod pa'i thabs ji snyed
NK088(su)001:10460: pa kun kyang gdul bya'i bsam pa'i mos pa da
NK088(su)001:10461: dung theg pa chen por ma bkag pa'i ma 'dus
NK088(su)001:10462: pa dag gdon pa'i drang ba'i thabs su ched du
NK088(su)001:10463: sbyor mdzad pas gdul bya'i ngor ma nges pa'i phyir
NK088(su)001:10464: / spyod pa'i rnam grangs ril kun la 'di kho
NK088(su)001:10465: na'o nges pa zhes dam par blo mi gzhag mi
NK088(su)001:10466: / bya ste / gang du nges pa gcig nyid
NK088(su)001:10467: la'o de kho na nyid ji bzhin pa'i ngang du
NK088(su)001:10468: mi 'gyur ba'i don la blo gros dam par bzhag
NK088(su)001:10469: / bya ste / ste / spyod pa ril nor
NK088(su)001:10470: bu byed pa'i bslab pa chen po gcig de yin
NK088(su)001:10474: zhes pa la sogs pa bcu gcig pa'i lan /
NK088(su)001:10475: thabs chen po de kho na nyid nges pa'i sgo
NK088(su)001:10476: 'dir kun shong gang yang ma bkol kun 'jug bar
NK088(su)001:10477: 'dus te / yang dag pa'i lam 'dis bde ba
NK088(su)001:10478: thob par byed pas ming nges theg pa chen por
NK088(su)001:10480: 'on kyang ming theg pa mchog tu brjod pas thabs
NK088(su)001:10481: kyi sgo yang 'phags pa che dang grangs thabs las
NK088(su)001:10482: 'das pa mang bas gang gi thams cad gang yang
NK088(su)001:10484: spyod pa nyid kyi gang mi 'gog pas 'jug lam sbyor bas gdung ba dang bral lo //
NK088(su)001:10485: de lta bu la bde ba nyid la spyod par
NK088(su)001:10486: sla mi 'dzin ma chags pas bya bar dka' ba
NK088(su)001:10487: yang med do // lan bcu pa gang snyam pa la /
NK088(su)001:10488: thabs dang theg pa'i bye brag rnams //
NK088(su)001:10489: zhes pa la sogs pa don gnyis po ji snyed
NK088(su)001:10490: so sor mi mthun pa tha dad yod kyang thabs
NK088(su)001:10491: nges pa ma nor ba spyod la mi 'ching bas
NK088(su)001:10492: sbyor bas na bdag gzhan mthar phyin par byed pas
NK088(su)001:10493: na / nges pa'i gding rnyed na gnas mtho dman khyad par med la bzang ngan med de /
NK088(su)001:10494: 'khor ba nyid bde gnas su lan btab bo //
NK088(su)001:10495: smin dper bcu gcig pa'ang brgyad pa'i lan ji lta bu zhe na /
NK088(su)001:10496: dam tshig bsgrub dang spyod pa la //
NK088(su)001:10497: zhes pa la sogs pas rnam grangs de dag la
NK088(su)001:10498: sogs pa lta ba sna tshogs tha dad kun rnams
NK088(su)001:10499: / gdul bya byol song la sogs pa smos pa'i
NK088(su)001:10500: phyin ci log tu ltas pas spyod rnams 'dul te
NK088(su)001:10501: dam pa'i don la gzud ba'i ched du gsungs pas
NK088(su)001:10502: / / bstan pa sna tshogs ji snyed pa'i thabs dam tshig la sogs pa so so yang /
NK088(su)001:10503: ye ngo bo gdod nas rang rig pa rgyu rkyen
NK088(su)001:10504: dang bral bas rdo rje ngo bo skye 'jig med
NK088(su)001:10505: pa'i ngang du dbyer med pa'i don la gcig pa
NK088(su)001:10506: dgongs nas thabs kyis bsam pa tha dad pa'i gdul
NK088(su)001:10507: bya dang mthun pas 'jug nas drang ba'i ched du
NK088(su)001:10508: mdzad nas / de dag don la sbyong ba'ang mthun par sten 'jug cing pa dang /
NK088(su)001:10509: brid cing bton pas gnas chen po rang khrid cing bskyang ba'i thabs su gsungs pas zad de /
NK088(su)001:10510: ngo bo nyid la bstan du med kyang thabs chen
NK088(su)001:10511: pos ldongs pa 'dren pa'i spyod pa la long ba
NK088(su)001:10512: ltar ma rig pas non pas spyad par mi rigs
NK088(su)001:10514: lan dang po gnyis gang rnam pa la /
NK088(su)001:10515: dris pa gsum yang lan gcig gis mchod par bya ba'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:10516: 'jig rten kun gyi dman pa rnams //
NK088(su)001:10517: zhes pa la sogs pa gang 'gro ba rnams kyis
NK088(su)001:10518: smad pa'i spyod pa 'khor ba'i dngos po bzhi la
NK088(su)001:10519: sogs pa spyod pa'ang sna tshogs pa'ang gdul bya tha
NK088(su)001:10520: dad theg pa dam par chen por dkri ba'i drangs
NK088(su)001:10521: pa'i phyir ched du dman spyod ngan ji snyed 'jog
NK088(su)001:10522: par mthun pa'i spyod pa la yongs su rdzogs zin
NK088(su)001:10523: chags med pas rnam smin myong bar mi 'gyur bas
NK088(su)001:10525: thabs chen po'i mdzad pa la dman pa'i las su dor ba med par lan btab bo //
NK088(su)001:10526: dri ba gnyis pa'i lan ci zhe na /
NK088(su)001:10527: sbrul sgong khyung du mi 'gyur yang //
NK088(su)001:10529: dper sbrul sgong brnongs pa khyung du mi 'gyur ba khyod ltar yin yang /
NK088(su)001:10530: 'dir dper na gser 'gyur gyi rtsi dang dug 'gyur gyi rtsi'i las ltar /
NK088(su)001:10531: spyod ngan ril lam yang na sems can gyi de
NK088(su)001:10532: kho na nyid ma nor ma bslad par mthong shes
NK088(su)001:10533: bya na / de spyad pa nyid kyis dam par
NK088(su)001:10534: tshogs gnyis su 'gyur bas yang dag pa'i spyod par
NK088(su)001:10535: bya na / lan btab bo // lan gsum pa gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:10537: zhes pa de kho na nyid mu mtha' med pa'i ngang dbyings las mtho ris ngan pa'o //
NK088(su)001:10538: ngan song sangs rgyas go 'phang sems can gnyis med pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:10539: zhen blo can dag la bzang ngan tha dad snang
NK088(su)001:10540: yang spyod pa bzang ngan stong pa chen po'i rtogs
NK088(su)001:10541: pa la ma bkag dmigs pas de skad bstan pa
NK088(su)001:10542: la yang nyes pa ma dmigs par lan btab bo
NK088(su)001:10543: // lan bzhi pa gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:10544: dug dang sman gnyis so so yang //
NK088(su)001:10545: zhes pa la sogs pa dang po gnyis dape'o //
NK088(su)001:10546: 'khor 'das de ltar spyod pa la log ma log
NK088(su)001:10547: ma 'dres pa sna tshogs tha dad bsam yas snang
NK088(su)001:10548: yang / de dag nyid kun gyis rang bzhin de
NK088(su)001:10549: kho na nyid du rgyas rdzogs thabs pas de'i don
NK088(su)001:10550: gdeng chud pas rigs gang 'dir dam par 'gyur nges
NK088(su)001:10551: phyin chad gzhan don ched du spyod pa smod pa
NK088(su)001:10552: dman pa'i las rnams dag don du'ang spyod pa nyid
NK088(su)001:10553: spyod pa ma nor ba yin par lan btab bo
NK088(su)001:10554: yang / // lan lnga pa gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:10555: de nyid ma mthong gang dag gis //
NK088(su)001:10557: bden pa de nyid gnad ma chud ma mthong pa'i
NK088(su)001:10558: rnal 'byor gang dag gis pas tshig gi brda lam
NK088(su)001:10559: gyi rjes su blo song bas sgra rang thad du
NK088(su)001:10560: bzungs pas lam ma nor ba yang dag lam las
NK088(su)001:10561: 'khrul cing gol rgyab kyis log pa'i lam pa phyogs
NK088(su)001:10562: pa'ang shin tu'ang mang bar 'byung ngo //
NK088(su)001:10563: de bas na thabs chung ngus tshig mthun pas don
NK088(su)001:10564: spyod pa nyid rig pa dang nges pa ma yin
NK088(su)001:10566: de ltar theg pa chen po'i rnal 'byor des /
NK088(su)001:10567: rnal 'byor chung ngu'i nges pa ma rnyed pa'i dogs pa bsal to //
NK088(su)001:10568: zhes ston pa des sdud pa po la smras pas /
NK088(su)001:10569: skal ba dman pa dag theg pa mchog tu nges pa rnyed par gyur to //
NK088(su)001:10570: le'u sum cu bdun pa'i mdor 'grel pa'o ////de nas yang gsang ba'i bdag po des /
NK088(su)001:10571: lang ka'i bdag po byang chub sems dpa' /
NK088(su)001:10572: zhes pa la sogs pa dus der snga ma'i rjes
NK088(su)001:10573: su'ang ston pas sdud pa la bka' stsal pa sgra
NK088(su)001:10574: bzhin te / 'dir lo rgyus su brjod pa'o //
NK088(su)001:10575: brgyud pa'i grags pa zhes pa /
NK088(su)001:10576: dus de nyid kyi'ang snga ma'i gtam rgyud barjooda pa nye bar bstan pa ste /
NK088(su)001:10577: gsang ba spyad nyes pa ni sgra bzhin du sbyar ro //
NK088(su)001:10578: gsang ba'i bdag po 'di lta ste //
NK088(su)001:10579: zhes pa la sogs pa dag de yang rnam grangs bcu gcig tu 'grel te /
NK088(su)001:10580: gsang sngags log par spyod pa'i skyon rnams rnal 'byor bzang ldan lta bu dang /
NK088(su)001:10581: bdag bstod gzhan la smod de gzhung nor bas chos
NK088(su)001:10582: log spyad pas ltung ba rnal 'byor dpal sbyin lta
NK088(su)001:10583: bu dang / mi shes par ras chod kyi tshul
NK088(su)001:10584: bcos spyad pas ltung ba rnal 'byor dri med spyod
NK088(su)001:10586: gsang sngags la rigs dang sder phyes nas nyon mongs
NK088(su)001:10587: pas 'dul zhing dang ris bcad pas ltung ba rnal
NK088(su)001:10588: 'byor na zhi na lta bu dang /
NK088(su)001:10589: tshogs kyi yo byad la gsog 'jog byas pas khyi'i
NK088(su)001:10590: lus su ltung ba bud med bzang rgyan lta bu
NK088(su)001:10591: dang / bka' la the tshom dang rkun bu byas
NK088(su)001:10592: pas ltung ba rgyal po pra ma ta lta bu
NK088(su)001:10593: dang / dang / don ma go zhing rtsa ba
NK088(su)001:10594: nyams pas nga rgyal dregs pas gsang sngags tshul 'ches
NK088(su)001:10595: su spyad pas ltung ba rnal 'byor pe na ya
NK088(su)001:10596: dang / dang / lta bu dang / gsang sngags
NK088(su)001:10597: tshig tsam las khung phyungs nas chags sdang spyad pas
NK088(su)001:10598: ltung ba rnal 'byor bde sbyin lta bu dang /
NK088(su)001:10599: gsang sngags zab mo'i don la byol nas ltung ba rnal 'byor lha sbyin lta bu dang /
NK088(su)001:10600: rnal 'byor nang la skur pa btab pa dang /
NK088(su)001:10601: kha na ma tho ba brjod pas ltung ba rnal 'byor mi 'jigs lta bu dang /
NK088(su)001:10602: gsang sngags kyi gdeng med par spyi yud tsam la
NK088(su)001:10603: ltos pas ltung ba rgyal po rab gsal 'dzin lta
NK088(su)001:10604: bu'o // des na thabs la mkhas pa dang //
NK088(su)001:10605: blo gros ldan pa shin tu gces //
NK088(su)001:10606: zhes pa skyon gyi tshul de lta bas na gsang sngags spyad pa'i thabs mchog dang /
NK088(su)001:10607: mi dmigs pa'i shes rab mchog tu dgos so //
NK088(su)001:10608: de la gsang sngags spyad legs pa'i yon tan gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:10609: thabs mkhas blo gros ldan pa yi //
NK088(su)001:10610: zhes pa la sogs pa sgra bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:10612: yon tan sgra bsgrags sus bos pa //
NK088(su)001:10613: zhes pa dag gsang sngags kyi mtshan thos pas dman
NK088(su)001:10614: pa'i lus len pa las thon pa lha'i bu 'od
NK088(su)001:10616: chos la skur pas ngu 'bod du ltung nges pa las /
NK088(su)001:10617: theg pa chen por rigs nges pas dar gyi pho
NK088(su)001:10618: longs brdabs pa ltar slar 'bar ba ltar thon pa
NK088(su)001:10619: dang / gsang sngags la 'dun pa skyes pas bar
NK088(su)001:10620: chad med par thob pa bram ze byams ldan lta
NK088(su)001:10621: dang / bu dang / gsang sngags tshul bzhin du
NK088(su)001:10622: spyod pa la mos pas yon phul bas cho 'phrul
NK088(su)001:10623: bzhi thob pa lha'i bu dge ba'i rgyal po lta
NK088(su)001:10624: dang / bu dang / bu dang / gsang sngags
NK088(su)001:10625: spyod pa la dad pas rjes su 'brangs pas rig
NK088(su)001:10626: 'dzin gyi sa thob pa bram ze ke ran ta
NK088(su)001:10627: dang / bu dang / bu dang / lta bu
NK088(su)001:10628: dang / gsang sngags gzhung du spyod pa la mos
NK088(su)001:10629: pa ma bral ba tsam gyis 'bras bu mnyam por
NK088(su)001:10630: 'thob pa rgyal po dbang phyug 'od ldan dang /
NK088(su)001:10631: bram ze dge slong lta bu dang /
NK088(su)001:10632: gsang sngags gzhung bzhin bslab nas go ba'i yon tan bram ze gsal sbyin lta bu dang /
NK088(su)001:10633: tshogs kyi mchod pa byas nas tshe 'di nyid la
NK088(su)001:10634: 'bras bu thob pa dge slong gsal ldan lta bu
NK088(su)001:10635: dang / gsang sngags kyi chos rtag par bcangs pa
NK088(su)001:10636: tsam gyis 'bras bu thob pa khyim bdag mes sbyin
NK088(su)001:10637: dang / lta bu dang / gsang sngags go nas
NK088(su)001:10638: gzhan la bshad pa'i yon tan ni drang srong rnal
NK088(su)001:10639: 'byor ka la ya na lta bu'o //
NK088(su)001:10640: des na theg pa chen po gsang ba 'di //
NK088(su)001:10641: zhes pa bshad pa'i yon tan dang gtan tshigs so //
NK088(su)001:10642: rnal 'byor gang zhig /ces pa bsgom pa'i yon tan no //
NK088(su)001:10643: gzhan ni sgra ji bzhin du 'grel to //
NK088(su)001:10644: sum cu rtsa brgyad pa mdor bkrol ba'o //
NK088(su)001:10645: byung tshul brgyad pa'i don rdzogs so ////de nas yang
NK088(su)001:10646: lang ka'i mnga' bdag /ces pa la sogs pa byung
NK088(su)001:10647: tshul dgu pa dris pa sgra bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:10651: zhes pa ji bzhin pa ye 'phral du ma byas
NK088(su)001:10652: pa'i don ji lta bar mdzad pa yang de'ang mthun
NK088(su)001:10653: pa'o // smras pa ni de nyid dris pa'o //
NK088(su)001:10655: lang ka zhes pa grong khyer gsum la 'das pa
NK088(su)001:10656: sogs pa'i chos ji snyed pa'i rang snang ba nyid
NK088(su)001:10657: lugs kyi chos nyid de nyid kyi ma 'dres yongs
NK088(su)001:10660: chos thams cad kyi chos nyid de kho na nyid la ni /
NK088(su)001:10661: zhes pa la sogs pa sdud pa pos gsang bdag la /
NK088(su)001:10662: de kho na nyid kyis ched gdul bya'i du mdzad pa'i don byar yod med dris pa'i don ni /
NK088(su)001:10663: ji bzhin pa'i ngang la ltos pa'i tha snyad grol ba'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:10664: ye sangs rgyas zin pa la 'phral du sangs rgyas brtags pa'i tha snyad med pa /
NK088(su)001:10665: khams gsum sangs rgyas kyi sa la 'gro ba ming med pa /
NK088(su)001:10666: ji bzhin pa ni rnam pa thams cad pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:10668: dbyibs kha dog gi rnam pa dang bral ba /
NK088(su)001:10669: gzhan na ngo bo bstan pa dang bral bas dpe dang tshig gis mtshon par byar med pa /
NK088(su)001:10670: ril de nyid bas mtshon byed nyid kyang med pa /
NK088(su)001:10671: de la sems can don gyi bya ba bral ba /
NK088(su)001:10672: blos mi pho mo la sogs gsum 'khyud pa /
NK088(su)001:10673: sus kyang bstan du med sogs bzhi go bar bya med cing mthong bar dpag par dka' ba'o //
NK088(su)001:10676: gang ci yang med pa las /
NK088(su)001:10677: zhes pa la sogs pa de kho na nyid ngo bo med pa las /
NK088(su)001:10678: lan gyi tshul nas dri ba'i rnam grangs su 'gyur te /
NK088(su)001:10679: de lta bu'i ngang las cho 'phrul du sangs rgyas su snang ba ni dri ba dang po'o //
NK088(su)001:10680: de bzhin du grangs bcu ni dri ba bcu ste /
NK088(su)001:10681: med pa las yod par snang ba gang gi dgos pa yin dris pa'o //
NK088(su)001:10682: gsang ba'i bdag pos smras pa /
NK088(su)001:10683: kye lang ka'i bdag po yongs su dri ba /
NK088(su)001:10684: zhes pa la sogs pa ston pas bos nas zhus
NK088(su)001:10685: pa la legs par gnang ste don bka' stsal pa
NK088(su)001:10686: / gang ci'ang med pa las cir yang snang /
NK088(su)001:10687: zhes pa dri ba dgu pa'i lan du 'gyur te /
NK088(su)001:10688: mdzad pa thams cad lhun gyis grub pa'i de kho na nyid ni /
NK088(su)001:10689: gang ci'ang med pa las rnam pa'i mtshan nyid du ma grub pa las /
NK088(su)001:10690: 'chad pa'i mdzad pa cir yang snang ba mi 'gog
NK088(su)001:10691: pa dag gi de'i rang bzhin yang de kho na
NK088(su)001:10692: nyid yin pa las gzhan du ma thal ba'i phyir
NK088(su)001:10694: khams gsum gyi ched du grol bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:10695: mdzad pa phrin las tha dad ji snyed mi 'dra
NK088(su)001:10696: bar snang ba'i mdzad spyod la sel med 'ba' zhig
NK088(su)001:10697: pa'o // grong khyer gsum gang zhe na //
NK088(su)001:10698: zhes pa la sogs pa gdul bya la nye bar bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:10699: rgyud gcig pa dang tha dad pa gnyis kar sbyar te /
NK088(su)001:10700: rgyud gcig la nyon mongs zhen pa'i brtags pa nyid
NK088(su)001:10701: phyir pa'i yid phyi nang las nang phyed snang du
NK088(su)001:10703: tshogs drug phyi nang gnyis kun snang kar gsal ba'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:10704: kun gzhi mi snang shin tu cha phra ba rgyu ba'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:10705: de bas na khams gsum gyi sa bon rgyud la yod pa'ang mi 'dod pa ma yin no //
NK088(su)001:10709: gzugs med pa ste ngo bo ni zhen pa'i brtags pa snang ba yin la /
NK088(su)001:10710: de nyid ni nyin mtshan cha phyed snang gnyis su snang ba'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:10711: lus dang gnas kyi 'od kyis nyin mtshan med par kun snang gsal ba'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:10712: lus gnas mi snang gzhan gyis mi mngon pa'i phyir shin tu grangs las 'das pa'o //
NK088(su)001:10713: lang ka'i bdag po grong khyer gsum nyid /
NK088(su)001:10714: ces pa la sogs pa gdul bya dang byin rlabs
NK088(su)001:10715: kyi mdzod pa ngo bos tha dad par 'dzin pa'i
NK088(su)001:10716: dogs pa bsal ba'i phyir te /
NK088(su)001:10717: khams gsum ngo bos de kho na bas de la
NK088(su)001:10718: dngos gzhi med par bdal ba'i phyir chos kyi dbyings
NK088(su)001:10719: su brjod pa'i gtan tshigs ni /
NK088(su)001:10720: de gnyis khams gsum du chos dbyings ngo bo gcig
NK088(su)001:10721: mtshungs pas khams gsum las gzhan pa'i chos nyid ma
NK088(su)001:10722: dmigs so // gtan tshigs de bas na gnyis med
NK088(su)001:10723: pa'i don nyid ni dngos po gnyis pa 'khor 'das
NK088(su)001:10724: ril 'char ba'i sgo dang mdzad pa ji snyed pa'i
NK088(su)001:10725: dmigs so // gzhir gyur pa'o // lang ka'i bdag
NK088(su)001:10726: po grong khyer gsum gyi ched du sgo gsum snang
NK088(su)001:10727: dmigs so // gzhir gyur pa'o // ba ni / zhes pa /
NK088(su)001:10728: 'dod khams ye gnyis su med pa'i ngang las gzungs mi 'bral ba dang /
NK088(su)001:10729: gzugs de'i don ji ltar rig gnas pa mthong ba
NK088(su)001:10730: dang gzugs med de nyid mngon du gsang byas pa'i
NK088(su)001:10732: rnal 'byor gsum gyi don du'ang 'gyur te /
NK088(su)001:10733: khams gsum la snang ba ni rim pa bzhin du 'gyur ro //
NK088(su)001:10734: gzungs kyi sgo yang grong khyer gsum gyi ched du snang bar mdzad pa ni /
NK088(su)001:10736: rgyud gcig gi dbang du shes pa gsum de nyid tha dad par mi snang ba dang /
NK088(su)001:10737: der 'dzin nang gi bsam gtan la sogs pa'i 'du shes dang /
NK088(su)001:10738: de 'jug 'dod lnga'i yul la spyod pa'o //
NK088(su)001:10739: de dag grol bar bya ba'i rkyen gyis dgos pa ni /
NK088(su)001:10740: dang po'i rkyen du chos ji bzhin pa ye mi zhi gnas g.yo dang /
NK088(su)001:10741: bar ma'i rkyen chos nyid cis kyang ma bsgribs par rang gsal ba'i lhag mthong ye shes dang /
NK088(su)001:10742: tha ma'i rkyen du gnyis su med pa'i las mtha' 'bras bu ste /
NK088(su)001:10743: shes bya dam pa bas shes pa'i mtshan nyid du 'gyur ro //
NK088(su)001:10744: cha mthun gyi tshul nas ni gzugs med pa la
NK088(su)001:10745: chos nyid zhi gnas rang chas su yod pa dang
NK088(su)001:10746: / gzugs la ye shes lhag mthong rang chas su yod pa dang /
NK088(su)001:10747: 'dod pa la 'bras bu las mtha' rang chas su yod pa'i phyir te /
NK088(su)001:10748: 'on kyang gtan nas ris su chad pa ni ma yin no //
NK088(su)001:10749: lang ka'i bdag po rig pa'i sgo'ang /
NK088(su)001:10751: gzugs med pa'i ched du ji lta bar rtogs nas blo bying rgod dang bral bar bsgom pa dang /
NK088(su)001:10752: gzugs kyi ched du de kho na nyid ji lta ba'i bden pa mthong ba'i lta ba dang /
NK088(su)001:10753: 'dod pa la phung po khams la sogs pa ril
NK088(su)001:10754: 'bras bu sku dang ye shes gnyis su med pa'i
NK088(su)001:10757: gsang ba'i sgo zhes pa gsum ni /
NK088(su)001:10758: gzugs med pa la de bzhin nyid mngon du gyur pas 'byung 'jug med pa dang /
NK088(su)001:10759: gzugs la ye shes chen po mngon du byas pas rig pa ma 'gag pa dang /
NK088(su)001:10760: 'dod pa la de gnyis gnyis su med pas rtog
NK088(su)001:10761: tshogs 'bras bur shar ba ste rgyud kyi dbang du
NK088(su)001:10762: 'grel pa'o // theg pa'i dbang du 'grel pa ni /
NK088(su)001:10763: sgo gsum ni mdo sde pa dang /
NK088(su)001:10766: kun 'byung 'dren pas mi 'chor ba'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:10767: dka' thub rig byed kyis theg pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:10768: dbang bsgyur thabs kyi theg pa dang dpag dka' ba'i phyir sgo gsum gyi ming nges par 'grub bo //
NK088(su)001:10769: de bas zhi gnas lhag mthong lam mtha' gsum yang theg pa'i gzhung so so bar bsnyad do //
NK088(su)001:10770: lan dang pos dri ba dang po bcad pa ni gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:10772: grong khyer gsum gyi ched du /
NK088(su)001:10773: zhes pa la sogs pa sangs rgyas gsum nye bar bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:10774: ngo bo nyid kyi sku rgyu rkyen dang bral ba dang /
NK088(su)001:10775: chos kyi sku tshogs las grub pa dang /
NK088(su)001:10776: longs spyod dang sprul pa dang /
NK088(su)001:10777: gsang ba'i sku gdul bya la snang bas khams gsum 'dul lo //
NK088(su)001:10778: lan gnyis pas dri ba gnyis pa nges par bcad pa ni gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:10781: zhes pa grong khyer gsum gyi gnas na /
NK088(su)001:10782: lta ba ji bzhin pa gol bas shes pa gsum dang ldan pa'i 'gro ba dang /
NK088(su)001:10783: ye shes kyi don gol bas shes pa drug dang ldan pa'i 'gro ba dang /
NK088(su)001:10784: spyod pa gol bas shes pa tshogs brgyad char dang ldan pa'i 'gro ba rnams su snang ngo //
NK088(su)001:10787: grong khyer gsum gyi rkyen gyis lus gsum bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:10789: ting nge 'dzin gyi lus la gnas pas dngos po bral ba dang /
NK088(su)001:10790: shin tu gzugs byad dang ldan pa ste /
NK088(su)001:10791: khams de gnyis ni bardzusa nas skye ba'i cha'o //
NK088(su)001:10792: pho mo dang ma ning 'gyur bag can dang /
NK088(su)001:10794: rlugs pa dag tu snang ba ni 'dod khams so //
NK088(su)001:10797: gang 'dod pa'i rkyen gyis gang gi yab yum dang /
NK088(su)001:10799: 'dod pa la chags pa'i khams de'i rkyen gyis rgyal
NK088(su)001:10800: ba man chad la yab dang yum dang sras dang
NK088(su)001:10801: longs spyod lnga lta bur snang ngo //
NK088(su)001:10802: lan lnga pa ni 'di lta ste /
NK088(su)001:10803: de yang de bzhin gshegs pa'i yum du /
NK088(su)001:10804: zhes pa snyegs pas rjes su mthun par ston pa ni /
NK088(su)001:10805: rigs kyi bdag po he ru ka'i thugs ka nas
NK088(su)001:10806: kro d+h+ai shwa ri bton nas hi hi zhes yum
NK088(su)001:10807: du mdzad pa lta bu dang /
NK088(su)001:10808: bshad pa'i khro bo sme brtsegs lta bu la sogs pa dang /
NK088(su)001:10809: gsang ba'i sku b+ha ga la bzhugs pa dang /
NK088(su)001:10810: gsang ba'i sku'i mdzad pa yang thabs shes rab rol pa'i de na'ang byin rlabs las /
NK088(su)001:10811: gsang ba dam pa sngags de kho na nyid kyi nges pa rnyed par byed pa dang /
NK088(su)001:10812: the tshom chod nas de la rten pa med de slar log pa dang /
NK088(su)001:10813: gsang ba'i sku'i the tshom zhu ba ni /
NK088(su)001:10814: thabs la gnas pa dngos dang /
NK088(su)001:10815: de dag tu rtsom pa dang /
NK088(su)001:10816: des gsung sngags kyi rigs snang ba dang nges par byin gyis rlob pa bye ba dang /
NK088(su)001:10817: b+ha ga'i gnas bye ba snyed du 'jug pa'o //
NK088(su)001:10818: sprul pa dang longs spyod kyi mdzad par yang mi 'dod pa ma yin no //
NK088(su)001:10819: lan drug pa gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:10821: zhes pa dag ni gsang sngags ji bzhin nyid dang /
NK088(su)001:10822: theg pa'i sgo ma nges pa brda tha dad pa sna tshogs dang /
NK088(su)001:10824: de dag ni de kho na nyid mi g.yo ba rtogs pas chog pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:10825: ye shes kyi thabs sgo mang po dang /
NK088(su)001:10826: spyod pa la rten pa'i phyir te cha mthun gyi tshul lo //
NK088(su)001:10827: rgyud gcig pa ni rkyen gsum the tshom mi za na'ang /
NK088(su)001:10828: rgyud tha dad pa'i dbang du ni /
NK088(su)001:10829: gzugs med pa rang gi ting nge 'dzin gyi lus
NK088(su)001:10830: la rten pa la gsang sngags kyi skal ba med
NK088(su)001:10831: pa dang / 'dod khams zhen chags can la gsang sngags thabs kyi sgo gsungs na /
NK088(su)001:10832: 'dir theg pa chung ngur bstan pa ni 'gal ba du ma 'adu'o zhe na /
NK088(su)001:10833: sngon du dogs pa bsal zin te ris su chad pas bstan pa ma yin no //
NK088(su)001:10834: lan drug pa gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:10835: lang ka'i bdag po grong khyer gsum gyi ched du ting nge 'dzin /
NK088(su)001:10836: zhes pa shes pa gsum ting nge 'dzin gsum yin pa'i don ni 'chad par 'gyur ro //
NK088(su)001:10837: tha dad pa'i don du cha mthun du bstan pa ste brda mjal sla'o //
NK088(su)001:10838: lan bdun pa ni gang snyam pa la /
NK088(su)001:10839: lang ka'i bdag po grong khyer gsum gyi ched du mchod rten /
NK088(su)001:10840: zhes pa mchod rten nye bar mtshon pa ni /
NK088(su)001:10841: thugs ye shes snang ba bral ba'i rtags dang /
NK088(su)001:10842: sku phyag rgyar snang ba dang /
NK088(su)001:10843: gsung bstan pa dag ste khams gsum la mthun phyogs su snang ngo //
NK088(su)001:10844: dkyil 'khor gsum ni rang bzhin ye nas lhun gyis grub pa dang /
NK088(su)001:10845: rang rig pa lha'i dkyil 'khor du gsal ba dang /
NK088(su)001:10846: dngos su 'dra bar byas pa ste rim bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:10848: gdams ngag gi skabs su bshad zin te /
NK088(su)001:10849: 'dir yi ge gsum rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po +amo dang /
NK088(su)001:10850: ye ji bzhin pa ril dang mi phyed pa'i ngo bo m+aum dang /
NK088(su)001:10851: rtsa ba byang chub sems spyod yul dang bral ba blos reg dka' ba nyid h'u ngo /
NK088(su)001:10853: grags pa'i dbang du na spyi gzhung nyid do //
NK088(su)001:10855: grong khyer gsum gyi ched du 'bras bu dang /
NK088(su)001:10856: zhes pa grangs mthun pa'i sgo ste /
NK088(su)001:10857: gcig la'ang gsum ka thun mong du 'gyur ro //
NK088(su)001:10858: lang ka zhes pa sgra ji bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:10859: sum cu dgu pa'i 'grel pa'o ////de nas yang gsang ba'i bdag po des /
NK088(su)001:10860: lang ka'i bdag po la smras pa /
NK088(su)001:10861: zhes pa ston pas sdud pa po la bos nas /
NK088(su)001:10862: dri ba tha ma rjes su dpag pa'i don bstan pa'i phyir smras pa ni bka' stsal pa'o //
NK088(su)001:10863: lta ba mthun pa drang ba'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:10864: lang ka'i bdag po gzhan yang sangs rgyas kyi ched du /
NK088(su)001:10865: zhes pa bos nas dkri thabs snga ma las mi
NK088(su)001:10866: mthun pa 'dogs yang dag po'i gsung ba su gnang
NK088(su)001:10867: pa'i sgo nas gsang sngags spyod sangs rgyas pa'i rnal
NK088(su)001:10868: 'byor dam pa rnams kyis dgongs pas gsungs pa /
NK088(su)001:10869: sangs rgyas rnams kyi dam pa ni //
NK088(su)001:10870: zhes pa rgyal ba'i dgongs pa'i zhe phugs gsang sngags theg pa chen po dam pa nyid ni /
NK088(su)001:10871: dngos po thams cad kun kyang de nyid du byung
NK088(su)001:10872: nyid las thebs pa'i mi gzhan phyir gtan tshigs des
NK088(su)001:10873: na / gang la'ang spong len ci la'ang blang dor
