NK088(su)001:10874: byar med par mnyam pa nyid du rtogs pas na
NK088(su)001:10875: chos rdo rje nam mkha' kyi sku chen po thob
NK088(su)001:10876: pa la gdon mi za the tshom med par lta
NK088(su)001:10877: spyod de bzhin du gyis shigs pa'o //
NK088(su)001:10879: rang sangs rgyas kyi ched du snang ba rdo rje /
NK088(su)001:10880: zhes pa la sogs pa 'chad pa dag ni /
NK088(su)001:10881: gong dang mthun pas gsang sngags la zhugs pa'i don te /
NK088(su)001:10882: rgyun du zhugs pa la rigs phyed nas 'dod khams su skyes pas rtog dpyod dang ldan pas /
NK088(su)001:10883: bla ma la ma brten par byang chub thob pa
NK088(su)001:10884: ba rang sangs rgyas rnams theg pa chen por ched
NK088(su)001:10885: du drang ba'i phyir snang ba lus kyi rdzu 'phrul
NK088(su)001:10887: rdo rje mi 'jigs pa'i don ma mthun 'dzin pas
NK088(su)001:10888: theg pa chen por mdzad pa 'di bka' stsal pa
NK088(su)001:10889: / ngag nyid rang rig rdo rje 'dus ma byas pa'i ngo bo yi ge bstan pa ni med /
NK088(su)001:10890: lus nyid rang rig pa'i rdo rje yi ge rang
NK088(su)001:10891: snang ba ston pa rdzu 'phrul cir yang snang ba
NK088(su)001:10893: rang rgyal ba'i gang zag gi yid theg pa chen
NK088(su)001:10894: po'i 'dir sgor bcug drangs te gsang sngags pa nyid
NK088(su)001:10895: du su rigs nges pa mdzad do //
NK088(su)001:10896: nyan thos kyi ched du bslab pa rdo rje mdzad pa 'di /
NK088(su)001:10897: zhes pa la sogs pa ston pas nyan thos drang
NK088(su)001:10898: ba'i phyir sgo gsum gyi bslab pa bsrung bya rdo
NK088(su)001:10899: rje theg pa chen por mdzad pa'i thabs 'di gsung
NK088(su)001:10900: bka' stsal pa / lus ngag yid kyi bsrung bya
NK088(su)001:10901: gsum gsum bzhi ste dge ba bcu po nyid ni
NK088(su)001:10902: sgo gsum ye shes rdo rje yin pas de'i las
NK088(su)001:10903: bya ba bcu yang bsrung ba yongs su rnam par
NK088(su)001:10904: dag pa yin pa'i mtha' phyir /
NK088(su)001:10905: kho nyid kyi spyod pa ma dor bar gsang sngags
NK088(su)001:10906: su mdzad pas nyan thos mya ngan las 'das pa
NK088(su)001:10907: zhi ba phyogs yid gcig pu'i mtha' la gnas pa'ang
NK088(su)001:10908: theg pa chen por dam nyid du rigs nges pa'o
NK088(su)001:10910: zhes pa rnam rig dang rnal 'byor dbu ma pa drang ba'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:10911: ched du kho'i lta ba nyid rdo rje theg pa chen por gsung ba mdzad pa bka' stsal pa /
NK088(su)001:10912: thams cad dngos por ril rnam rig dper mig rdzi
NK088(su)001:10913: 'khor langs pas skra'i 'khor lo mthong ba ltar shes
NK088(su)001:10914: pa 'khrul pa snang ba nyid dngos yul tha dad
NK088(su)001:10915: par snang ba kun rdzob bo //
NK088(su)001:10916: de lta bas yul gyi rnam pa rang rgyud pa gzhan med de /
NK088(su)001:10917: shes pa de nyid ye shes skad mi rtag cig
NK088(su)001:10918: ma rgyun gyi rtag par don dam par yang yod
NK088(su)001:10919: par 'dod pa nyid rnam shes gang yin 'dir yang
NK088(su)001:10920: thams cad rig pa snang ba'i cha mthun gyi de
NK088(su)001:10921: dag gi yid mos bcug pas theg pa chen po'i
NK088(su)001:10922: gsang ba dam pa sgor zhugs te rigs nges par
NK088(su)001:10923: mdzad do // lang ka'i bdag po yang skyes bu
NK088(su)001:10924: des gang gi mtha' yongs su sel ba dag gi
NK088(su)001:10925: mdzad do // ched du / zhes pa la sogs
NK088(su)001:10926: pa ston pas dbu ma pa gzud pa'i phyir gsungs
NK088(su)001:10927: mdzad do // ched du / pa ni / dbu
NK088(su)001:10928: ma'i don dam par nam mkha' rdo rje ma skyes
NK088(su)001:10929: par gsal ba'i lta ba nyid rdo rje theg par
NK088(su)001:10930: mdzad pa'i don bka' stsal to //
NK088(su)001:10931: gang su zhig gis dbu ma'i skabs su 'dir rten 'brel gyi gtan tshigs kyis /
NK088(su)001:10932: rten 'brel 'dus mdo tsam na de nyid la rnam
NK088(su)001:10933: pa med pa ngo bo med pas yod mtha' grol
NK088(su)001:10934: la sgyu ma tsam du snang bas med pa grol
NK088(su)001:10935: ba nyid la / 'di 'drar med pa'i mtha' gnyis
NK088(su)001:10936: nges par rab bsal te bla dwags dbu ma ste
NK088(su)001:10937: ba nyid la / / sems nyid gang yin de
NK088(su)001:10938: nyid 'dir gnyis med mtha' las grol bar dbu mar
NK088(su)001:10939: mi dmigs mdzad pas dbu ma'ang theg pa chen por
NK088(su)001:10940: ba nyid la / / mdzad do // 'khor ba'i
NK088(su)001:10941: lam pa dag kyang yang dag pa'i lam du mdzad
NK088(su)001:10943: lang ka'i bdag po yang skyes bu dam pa des /
NK088(su)001:10944: tshangs pa la sogs pa gti mug can gyi /
NK088(su)001:10945: zhes pa la sogs pa sdud pa po la bos nas lo rgyus su bka' stsal pa ni /
NK088(su)001:10946: ston pa des gti mug can rnams gti mug de nyid kyis grol bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:10947: gti mug ma rig nyid rdo rje theg pa'i don
NK088(su)001:10948: du rdo rje mdzad pa'i thabs mdzad do bka' stsal
NK088(su)001:10949: pa / 'jig rten kun phyi nang na gnas pa'i
NK088(su)001:10950: 'gro ba'i rgyud kyi gti mug gi ngo bo nyid
NK088(su)001:10951: las nor ba tsam yang ngo bo byang chub sems
NK088(su)001:10952: kyi rdo rje 'byung ye shes chen po'i klong du
NK088(su)001:10953: pa / gsal ba'i phyir / gnyis su med pa
NK088(su)001:10954: byang chub chen po'i don du de nyid shar te
NK088(su)001:10955: pa / gsal ba'i phyir / / gti mug rdo
NK088(su)001:10956: rje 'byed pa med pa'i don gzhan nas btsal bas
NK088(su)001:10957: 'byung ba ma yin pas spang du med par bka'
NK088(su)001:10958: pa / gsal ba'i phyir / / stsal pas /
NK088(su)001:10959: gti mug can dag gsang chen theg par gnyis med
NK088(su)001:10960: don la btsud de rigs nges pa'o //
NK088(su)001:10961: lang ka'i bdag po yang skyes bu dam pa des /
NK088(su)001:10963: zhes pa ston pas skyes bu dam pa des 'dod
NK088(su)001:10964: chags can gu lang sogs grol bar bya ba'i ched
NK088(su)001:10965: du phyir / 'dod chags ye shes rdo rje mdzad pa'i thabs 'di bka' stsal to //
NK088(su)001:10966: 'jig rten 'gro ba pho mo bcud mang po ji
NK088(su)001:10967: snyed gang yang rung ba chags pas zhen po dag
NK088(su)001:10968: /khyad par du lo ka'i khams na gu lang dang
NK088(su)001:10969: u ma de ba gnyis 'khrigs pa chags pa la
NK088(su)001:10970: zhen pa yang bshad mthun pas 'dul ba pa'i g.yem
NK088(su)001:10971: la g.yem dang / mi mthun pas 'dul ba g.yem pa 'dul ba'i thabs khyad par can dang /
NK088(su)001:10972: chags pa nyid rdo rje chags med kyi ye shes
NK088(su)001:10973: pas mi 'gog yid bcugs nas mi thogs par bka'
NK088(su)001:10974: stsal pa / chags zhen can rnams gsang chen gnyis med don la btsud de /
NK088(su)001:10975: theg pa chen po'i rab rigs su nges pa yang dag par mdzad do //
NK088(su)001:10977: yang skyes bu dam pa des byish+nu la la sogs
NK088(su)001:10978: pa zhe sdang can gyi ched du gsod pa rdo
NK088(su)001:10979: rje 'di / zhes pa dag ston pa des zhe
NK088(su)001:10980: sdang can rnams kyi ched du spyod pa de nyid
NK088(su)001:10981: kyis grol bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:10982: gsod gcod yang dag pa'i mdzad par bstan pa'i thabs 'di gsung bar mdzad do bka' stsal pa /
NK088(su)001:10983: gsad bya'i ji snyed sems can g.yo rdul snyed rnams
NK088(su)001:10984: gnyis med rdo rje du rtogs pa'i mtshon chen shes
NK088(su)001:10985: rab ni las kyi rdo rje'i mtshon cha ste ril
NK088(su)001:10986: ma skyes pa'i ngang du bsad srog bcad pas /
NK088(su)001:10987: spyod pa zhe sdang nyid kyang ma bkag byas pa
NK088(su)001:10988: med na rdo rje yang dag pa'i yid bcugs nas
NK088(su)001:10990: de dag mos pa rdo rje theg par btsud de grol bar rab nges pa'o mdzad do //
NK088(su)001:10991: lang ka'i bdag po yang skyes bu dam pa des /
NK088(su)001:10992: gnod sbyin la sogs pa phrag dog can gyi /
NK088(su)001:10993: zhes pa la sogs pa ston pas phrag dog can gyi 'gro ba sgrol ba'i ched du phyir /
NK088(su)001:10994: 'khrugs pa sems kyi khong khro nyid rdo rje gnyis
NK088(su)001:10995: med kyi ye shes su mdzad pa'i thabs bka' stsal
NK088(su)001:10997: gzhan gyi sha khrag dag tu nying shas 'tsho ba dang /
NK088(su)001:10998: gzhan gyi longs spyod kyi 'dod pa yod par mi
NK088(su)001:10999: dga' kun sdom pas dus kun tu sdom pa phra
NK088(su)001:11000: dog ste / de ltar dogs pa nyid ye shes
NK088(su)001:11001: rdo rje chen po'i ngang la mtshan rtog mi chud
NK088(su)001:11002: pa'i don rtogs pa'i shes rab kyi /
NK088(su)001:11003: bdud dpung gis mi bardzi ba'i go mtshon bgos dang
NK088(su)001:11004: ldan pa de yin pas phrag dog spang kun 'khrug
NK088(su)001:11005: du med pas / spang du med par yid bcugs
NK088(su)001:11006: nas bka' stsal pas phrag dog can gyis don rtogs
NK088(su)001:11007: nas gsang chen snying por rigs nges so //
NK088(su)001:11008: lang ka'i bdag po yang skyes bu dam pa des /
NK088(su)001:11009: gang klu la sogs pa phra ma can gyi ched du /
NK088(su)001:11010: zhes pa la sogs pa ston pas phra ma sgrol
NK088(su)001:11011: ched du phyir de nyid ye shes chen por mdzad
NK088(su)001:11013: gnyis su med pa'i rdo rje dam pa ye shes
NK088(su)001:11014: theg pa 'dzin pa can ni gzhan dang 'byed pa'i
NK088(su)001:11015: phra ma'i ngo bo mchog nyid yin par rtogs pas
NK088(su)001:11016: phyin ci log gi lta ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11017: yang dag pa'i lta ba shan ma 'dres par byas te /
NK088(su)001:11018: log par mi gnas pa'i phra ma chen po de
NK088(su)001:11019: dag gis rtogs pa bcug pa ste gsang sngags dam
NK088(su)001:11021: lang ka'i bdag po yang skyes bu dam pa des /
NK088(su)001:11022: lha ma yin la sogs pa /
NK088(su)001:11023: zhes pa ston pas nga rgyal can rnams dgrol ba'i ched du phyir /
NK088(su)001:11024: gdul dka' dregs pas khengs pa'i ngo bo nyid rdo
NK088(su)001:11025: rje ye shes chen po'i yon tan rdzogs pa'i che
NK088(su)001:11026: btsan du mdzad pa gsungs pa /
NK088(su)001:11027: nga rgyal ma nor ba ni rdo rje gsum gyi
NK088(su)001:11028: sku mchog khro bor byung bas log pa'i gdul dka'
NK088(su)001:11029: ma lus pa / dregs pa can ril btul tshar
NK088(su)001:11030: bcad mnan te gdan du brtsegs pas nga rgyal gyi
NK088(su)001:11031: ri bo chen po spyod pa la byas 'dzin med
NK088(su)001:11032: pas rnam smin med par bka' stsal pas de dag
NK088(su)001:11033: gis rtogs nas rigs su rdo rje theg par nges
NK088(su)001:11034: ma lus pa / pa'o nges so // lang ka'i bdag po /
NK088(su)001:11035: yang skyes bu dam pa des srin po la sogs pa /
NK088(su)001:11036: zhes pa dag ston pas srin po la sogs sha za dgrol bar bya ba'i ched du phyir /
NK088(su)001:11037: chags rngam gyis 'tsho ba nyid 'dir rdo rje ye
NK088(su)001:11038: shes chen pos log pa la rngam pa nga rgyal
NK088(su)001:11039: rdo rje yid bcugs nas mdzad pa'i thabs gsungs pa
NK088(su)001:11040: / don mi phyed rdo rje mi 'jigs btsal ba
NK088(su)001:11041: med par rtogs pas ngo bo thams cad ma lus
NK088(su)001:11042: pa ye shes chen po'i klong du zad par gsal
NK088(su)001:11043: ba nyid la sha za ba'ang mi 'gogs pas za
NK088(su)001:11044: ba chen por rngam pa rdo rjer yid bcugs nas
NK088(su)001:11045: / gsungs pas / de dag gis don de mthong nas theg pa chen por rab nges pa'o //
NK088(su)001:11048: yang skyes bu dam pa des mkha' 'gro la sogs pa gang phra men ma dag gi ched du /
NK088(su)001:11049: zhes pa la sogs pa ston pas phra men rdo rje yid bcugs nas /
NK088(su)001:11051: smad pa lnga nyid yang dag pa'i don dam par bka' stsal pa ni /
NK088(su)001:11052: gshang gci la sogs pa smad pa'i rdzas nyid kyang
NK088(su)001:11053: rang rig pa la 'di btung mi btung med pa'i
NK088(su)001:11055: rgyal ba man chad kun gyi spyod pa bzung ba
NK088(su)001:11056: dam pa la dngos gzhi phyogs gcig gi spyod par
NK088(su)001:11057: chos nyid la gtsang sme med pa dang nyon mongs
NK088(su)001:11058: pa'i dug bdung rtsir bsgyur ba dang 'khor ba zad
NK088(su)001:11059: par byed pa'i thabs kyi phyir ma nges pas /
NK088(su)001:11060: de ltar rtogs pa ni ril mnyam pa'i ngang du
NK088(su)001:11061: 'thungs pa la spyad bkag med par spyad par bka'
NK088(su)001:11062: stsal pas / de dag gis rtogs nas sras rdo
NK088(su)001:11063: rje gsang bar rab nges pa'o dam par mdzad do
NK088(su)001:11064: stsal pas / // lang ka'i bdag po /
NK088(su)001:11065: yang skyes bu dam pa des /
NK088(su)001:11066: mtha' yas rdo rje mdzad pa 'di gsungs pa mdzad do //
NK088(su)001:11067: zhes la sogs pa ston pas 'gro ba mtha' yas ril sgrol ba'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:11068: spyod pa mtha' yas so so ji snyed pa'ang yang
NK088(su)001:11069: dag rdo rje pa'i mdzad pa'i thabs yin par bka'
NK088(su)001:11070: stsal pa / 'gro ba'i gnas rdul snyed na phyin
NK088(su)001:11071: ci log gi rtog pa nang ris mi mthun pa
NK088(su)001:11072: la gnyen po rdul snyed kyis spong ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11074: thag bsring ba la sogs rdul snyed kyi thabs kyis
NK088(su)001:11075: cha mthun 'dul bar mdzad pas de dag ril rdo
NK088(su)001:11076: rje theg pa'i dbyings su sbyor bas yang dag pa
NK088(su)001:11077: la 'god do // 'gro ba'i spyod pa bsam yas
NK088(su)001:11078: pa'ang rang rig pa'i ye shes rgyu rkyen dang bral
NK088(su)001:11080: don de rtogs na spyad pa tha dad gang la
NK088(su)001:11081: dga' spyod de nyid gnang bas cha mthun par bstan
NK088(su)001:11082: pa des 'gro ba ril yang mos shing rtogs pas
NK088(su)001:11083: sras su mi 'gyur bar mdzad do //
NK088(su)001:11084: de dag gi don yang ril gsang sngags mtshon pa'i sgor ma gyur pa med pa dang /
NK088(su)001:11085: de nyid kyis rgyas btab pas spyod pa dor bya ma dmigs pa dang /
NK088(su)001:11086: don gzhan nas mi 'byung ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11087: rig na rang las 'char ba'i phyir rtogs pa dang /
NK088(su)001:11090: sras dam par gyur pa la the tshom med do //
NK088(su)001:11091: tshig de las rjes su dpag pa dpyad brtags na go bas lan tha mar yang nges so //
NK088(su)001:11092: le'u bzhi bcu pa bkrol zhing 'grel pa'o ///
NK088(su)001:11094: / 'dir yang dri ba dgu pa'i lan nges par bstan pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:11095: de nas gsang ba'i bdag po des /
NK088(su)001:11096: lang ka'i bdag po la smras pa /
NK088(su)001:11097: zhes pa ston pas sdud pa la thabs kyi phrin las nye bar bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:11099: ces pa gdul bya'i bsam pa mi mthun pa'i dgos
NK088(su)001:11100: ched du thabs kyi sgo ji snyed pas mthar phyin
NK088(su)001:11101: par mdzad pa'o // yul la la ni /
NK088(su)001:11102: zhes pa la sogs pa rnams ni /
NK088(su)001:11103: don bya ba'i yul gdul bya bsam pa mi mthun pas la la dgar ba ni /
NK088(su)001:11104: thar pa'i spyod pas 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11105: 'jig rten pa'i spyod pas 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11106: dge ba dkar ba'i las spang bas 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11108: de bzhin du 'chal ba'i spyod pas 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11109: ngag 'jam po'i spyod pas 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11110: shin tu rtsub pas 'dul ba lha dang lha ma yin lta bu'o //
NK088(su)001:11111: de gnyis ka byas pas 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11113: rgyal po'i cha lugs kyis 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11114: nyon mongs pa spyad pas 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11115: sems bying rmugs pa ste gti mug gis 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11116: rtsod pas 'dul ba ste zhe sdang gis 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11117: nga rgyal gyi ri bos gnon pas 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11118: 'dod chags kyi mes sreg pas 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11120: de ma yin pas 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11121: gnod bgegs lta bus 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11122: phan pas 'dul ba lha lta bus byed par mos pa dang /
NK088(su)001:11123: lus dang longs spyod la 'tshe ba byas pas 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11124: ma gtses par gzhag pas 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11125: sgo gsum la smad par byas pa'i ngag gis 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11127: sngar gyi bya ba la 'gyod pas 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11129: ku re dang bre mos 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11131: tan du byas pas 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11135: nor zas dngos po gang la'ang chog shes pas 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11136: ming la sogs pa sgra bzhin du sbyar ro //
NK088(su)001:11137: de bas na byang chub sems skye ba'i rkyen ma
NK088(su)001:11138: nges pas gsang sngags kyi mdzad pa la'ang ris med
NK088(su)001:11139: par spyod pa'o // sems skye ba'i tshul ni rang gi rig pas skabs su sbyar ro //
NK088(su)001:11140: gang la la ni thub pas so //
NK088(su)001:11141: gang la la ni rgyun mi chad par smra bas so //
NK088(su)001:11142: zhes pa la sogs pa gang dag la sprul pa'i sku lta bus 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11143: dus gsum du chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bas 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11144: se gol yul du chos bstan pas 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11145: longs spyod kyi sku lta bu ma gsungs pas 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11147: chos kyi gsung dbyangs kyis 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11148: gang dag rdo rje sems dpa' sangs rgyas kun gyi
NK088(su)001:11149: dge ba'i bshes gnyen gyi gsung gis 'dul ba dang
NK088(su)001:11150: / rnam par mi rtog pa bstan pas 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11151: rtog pa sha stag gis 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11152: sdug bsngal du bcugs pas 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11153: bde ba la bkod pas 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11154: chos dang gang zag med pas 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11155: yod par bstan pa lta bus 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11156: phrin las rnam bzhis 'dul ba dngos dang /
NK088(su)001:11157: lhun gyis grub pa'i phrin las kyis 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11158: sdug bsngal myong bar lung bstan pas 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11159: bde ba'i go 'phang thob par bstan pas 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11160: nyan thos kyi dka' thub lta bus 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11161: gsang sngags nang pa'i spyod pa lta bus 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11162: rig sngags kri ya'i spyod pa lta bus 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11163: bdag nyid la longs spyod tshangs bas 'khor los sgyur ba'i longs spyod lta bus 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11164: gang bya ba ril dus gcig tu rdzogs pa'i thabs a ti yo ga lta bus 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11165: sbyin pa dang snyan par smra ba dang don mthun
NK088(su)001:11166: pa dang don spyod pa'i bsdu ba'i dngos po bzhis
NK088(su)001:11167: 'dul ba dang / lus sbyin pas 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11168: longs spyod sbyin pas 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11169: gnyis ka gtang bas 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11170: de ril la zhen pas 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11175: thabs kyi sgo brgyad cu rtsa bdun smos pa la sogs pas 'dul ba'o //
NK088(su)001:11177: gang de ltar mos pa tha dad pa /
NK088(su)001:11183: zhes pa bsam pa tha dad pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:11184: dngos po bdun po'ang tha dad par ston pa'ang snga ma'i lus mdor bstan pa ste /
NK088(su)001:11185: yar bkab la bshad dgos pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:11186: 'di dag thams cad du rang thad ma yin te /
NK088(su)001:11187: gang la'ang 'chad pa'i ldem dgongs brgyad kyi cha dang
NK088(su)001:11188: mi ldan pa ni ma yin te kun la'ang ldan
NK088(su)001:11189: no // le'u bzhi bcu gcig pa 'grel pa'o ////dpe ngang sku'i mdzad pa gnyis bstan pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:11190: de nas yang gsang ba'i bdag po des /
NK088(su)001:11191: lang ka'i bdag po la smras pa /
NK088(su)001:11192: zhes pa lan brgyad pa dpe'i le'u 'di la mtshon pa dpe'i tshig med pas /
NK088(su)001:11193: dpe'i lan du ji ltar 'gyur zhe na /
NK088(su)001:11194: 'dra ba dang mi 'dra ba dang phyogs tsam mthun pa'i dpe bcad nas don dper blangs yin te /
NK088(su)001:11196: sdud pa po la bos nas dpe sgron ma dang
NK088(su)001:11197: 'dra ba'i tshul nas sku'i mdzad pa nye bar bstan
NK088(su)001:11198: pa ni / ji ltar rdo rje sems dpa'i sprul pa /
NK088(su)001:11199: zhes pa la sogs pa klad du le'u bdun par
NK088(su)001:11200: smos pa dag gi sprul pas gdul bya smin par
NK088(su)001:11202: de ltar na gang gi ched du /
NK088(su)001:11204: gdul bya'i phyir thugs dang gsung dang sku'i las dang
NK088(su)001:11205: sprul pa dang thabs shin tu mang la 'brel pa
NK088(su)001:11206: ni / gcig tu nges pa med pas gcig dang
NK088(su)001:11207: du ma las grol bas ngo bo ma de ni
NK088(su)001:11208: 'gro ba rnams blo dang mos pa bzhin nges te
NK088(su)001:11213: 'gro ba bsam pa tha dad pa thabs sgo mang po'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:11214: lang ka'i bdag po gang dam pa /
NK088(su)001:11215: zhes pa dag rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis /
NK088(su)001:11216: mtsho dwangs pa'i gza' skar ltar rnam grangs ji snyed
NK088(su)001:11217: pa spyod yul dang bral bas mi rtog bzhin du
NK088(su)001:11218: mkhyen pa'o // thams cad nas thams cad du dus
NK088(su)001:11219: dang skabs ril du rgyal ba'i thugs ji bzhin pa'i
NK088(su)001:11220: ngang du mtshan nyid ma 'dres par yongs su rdzogs
NK088(su)001:11221: byung thebs pas gcig dang tha dad las 'das pa'i
NK088(su)001:11223: gang gi snying po byang chub na mi g.yo ba la ma rtog pa nyid dang /
NK088(su)001:11225: rgyal ba gang zhig gi dgongs pa ye nas gnas pa'i chos ji bzhin pa la /
NK088(su)001:11226: 'byung 'jug gi yul med par mi g.yo ba la gsal ba la /
NK088(su)001:11227: 'du shes thams cad dang bral ba mi rtog pa nyid dang /
NK088(su)001:11228: khams gsum gyi 'gro ba gnas til 'bru'i nang 'dug pa yan chad la /
NK088(su)001:11229: lam pa la ldog pas byas pa'i tha dad du
NK088(su)001:11230: yod kyang ngo bo dbyer med pas nye ring dang
NK088(su)001:11231: bral ba'o // 'khrul pa la so sor snang yang
NK088(su)001:11232: don gcig pas gcig dang tha dad med pa dang
NK088(su)001:11233: bral ba'o // / de kho na nyid la snums
NK088(su)001:11234: tshab che chung med par gsal ba'i gtan tshigs kyis
NK088(su)001:11235: bral ba'o // / / mnyam pa'i dbyings su dbyer
NK088(su)001:11236: med par gnas pas tha dad pa med pa'i phyir
NK088(su)001:11238: ma 'dres gsal ba'i bla dwags mkhyen pa'o //
NK088(su)001:11239: de dag sku'i phrin las so //
NK088(su)001:11240: le'u bzhi bcu gnyis pa bkrol ba'o ////byung tshul dgu pa'i don bshad pa'o //
NK088(su)001:11241: de nas lang ka'i mnga' bdag byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po des /
NK088(su)001:11242: zhes pa dag byung tshul dris pa'o //
NK088(su)001:11243: gsang ba'i bdag pos smras pa /
NK088(su)001:11244: lang ka'i bdag po gang dri ba ni legs so //
NK088(su)001:11245: zhes pa la sogs pa ston pas sdud pa pos dris pa la legs par gnang ste /
NK088(su)001:11247: legs so sngon gyi rgyal bas lung bstan pa yod pa dang /
NK088(su)001:11248: shin tu da ltar thub pa'i dbang pos lung bstan pa yod pas rab tu grangs smos pa ste /
NK088(su)001:11249: dus gsum gyi dbang du'ang 'gyur ro //
NK088(su)001:11250: de'i don gyi mtshan nyid nye bar bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:11251: zhing khams 'khor ba thog mtha' med par /
NK088(su)001:11252: dus bskal pa thog mtha' bral ba'i skabs su /
NK088(su)001:11253: ston pa'i grangs sprul pa thog mtha' med pas gdul
NK088(su)001:11254: bya gang gi ston par snang ba dag gis kyang
NK088(su)001:11255: / sku mya ngan las ma 'das kyi bar du
NK088(su)001:11256: drangs pa'i thabs rgyu'i theg pa 'ba' zhig gi mdzad
NK088(su)001:11257: pas gdul bya gang la'ang so so'i spyod pa spong
NK088(su)001:11258: ba'i phyogs gcig gis phan gdags pa dang /
NK088(su)001:11259: sa'i rim pa bskrun zhing nod par byas kyang /
NK088(su)001:11260: yang dag par rdzogs pa nyid du 'tshang rgya ba'i
NK088(su)001:11261: thabs med pas gsang sngags kyi thabs mchog d+r+wa ba
NK088(su)001:11262: sprin dpung gis bshad pa ltar so so ji ltar
NK088(su)001:11263: mos pa ltar 'dul bas nyon mongs pa spyod spong
NK088(su)001:11264: gang ltar dga' ba ltar byung ba'i thabs ris dang
NK088(su)001:11265: bral bas yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sa nyid la
NK088(su)001:11266: dgod pa'i mdzad pa rnams sprul pa'i sgron ma gang
NK088(su)001:11267: gis kyang dngos su ma gsungs ma mdzad pas /
NK088(su)001:11268: thabs kyi theg pas 'dul ba gang zhig bsam phyogs
NK088(su)001:11269: su mthun par gsang sngags theg pa chen pos 'dul
NK088(su)001:11270: ba thugs dam du bzhes pas /
NK088(su)001:11271: gsang sngags phyis sku mya ngan las 'das nas 'jig
NK088(su)001:11272: rten du 'byung zhing mdzad pa tha dad snang bar
NK088(su)001:11273: lung bstan pa de zhing khams kun tu yongs su
NK088(su)001:11275: sprul pa'i sku gang gis kyang de nyid kyi dgongs
NK088(su)001:11276: pa'i spyod yul du snang ba'i rgyu'i theg pa las
NK088(su)001:11277: ma gtogs pa gsang sngags kyi thabs kyi sgo ji
NK088(su)001:11278: snyed pa thams cad snang ba ni ma yin pa'i
NK088(su)001:11279: gtan tshigs des na sprul pa'i skus gsang ba bshad
NK088(su)001:11280: par smra ba ni long ba lam du zhugs pa
NK088(su)001:11281: dang 'dra'o // de ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK088(su)001:11282: sprul pa ni bka' du ma las kyang 'dod chags spang ba'i cha lugs su bzhugs pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:11283: sku dang bstan pa mthun pas gdul bya'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:11284: ril gyis lung bstan gsungs pa'ang sngon du bka' stsal
NK088(su)001:11285: na 'byung bar mi rigs pas skyon du mar 'gyur
NK088(su)001:11286: ro // yang lang ka'i bdag po /
NK088(su)001:11287: lung bstan pa de'ang ji lta ji ltar 'di lta ste /
NK088(su)001:11288: zhes pa dag snga ma dang da ltar lung bstan pa nye bar bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:11289: 'di lta ste 'khor ba dang bskal pa thog mtha'
NK088(su)001:11290: bral ba'i sprul pa'i lung bstan pa rnams bshad kyis
NK088(su)001:11291: mi lang bas / phyogs gcig tu sprul pas lung
NK088(su)001:11292: bstan pa dag bshad kyis dam bcas go cha bgos
NK088(su)001:11293: khyod nyon cig par gdams pa mdzad do //
NK088(su)001:11294: bskal pa kun bkod bya ba la //
NK088(su)001:11295: zhes pa dag sgra ji bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:11297: zhes pa rgyal ba de 'das nas de snyed na 'byung bar bstan pa'o //
NK088(su)001:11298: gzhan yang bskul ba chen po nyon //
NK088(su)001:11300: brgya phrag gcig na don snang 'gyur //
NK088(su)001:11301: zhes pa 'dir ston pa'i dus rjes su mthun par snang ngo //
NK088(su)001:11305: dus der yang gsang ba'i bdag po phyag na rdo rje nyid kyis ston to //
NK088(su)001:11306: bskul ba'i go cha gzhan yang nyon //
NK088(su)001:11308: brgya phrag bco lngar gyur pa na //
NK088(su)001:11309: zhes pa ston pa de 'das nas lo stong lnga brgya na 'byung ste /
NK088(su)001:11310: skye rgu'i tshe lo'ang de nyid do //
NK088(su)001:11311: gnod 'dul zhes pa der yang phyag na rdo rjes ston to //
NK088(su)001:11312: de lta bas na thog ma tha ma med par
NK088(su)001:11313: phyag na rdo rje dang lang ka kho nas bka'
NK088(su)001:11314: stsal zhing gsang sngags bsdus pa la the tshom med
NK088(su)001:11315: do // de bas na sangs rgyas bzang rgyan dpal
NK088(su)001:11316: sku mya ngan las 'das nas lo lnga bcu na
NK088(su)001:11318: sangs rgyas dkon dpal 'das nas lo brgyad cu rtsa gnyis na byung ngo //
NK088(su)001:11319: thub pa'i dbang po 'das nas lo brgyad bcu gnyis na byung nyi shu dang brgyad ngo //
NK088(su)001:11320: lha gnas gsum ni dbang bsgyur khang bzang dang /
NK088(su)001:11323: drag shul can zhes bya ba'i ri //
NK088(su)001:11325: ston pa ni sprul sku ma yin te phyag na rdo rje kho na'o //
NK088(su)001:11326: le'u bzhi bcu gsum pa mdor 'grel pa'o ////lung chen nges par bstan pa na yang 'byung /
NK088(su)001:11327: zhes pa de ltar rgyal ba re res lung bstan pa'i dus der byung bas /
NK088(su)001:11328: 'dir yang thub pa'i dbang pos lung bstan pa'i tshe byung ngo //
NK088(su)001:11329: de bas na byung tshul ni 'dir smos pa kho
NK088(su)001:11330: nas mi chog pa med na'ang bshad pa bzhin dgos
NK088(su)001:11331: pa'i dbang gis bcu gnyis smos te /
NK088(su)001:11332: bskal pa thog ma med pa'i skabs re rer gsang
NK088(su)001:11333: sngags byung ngo cog la byung tshul gyi dgos pa
NK088(su)001:11334: yang tshang bar byung ste bcu pa'o ////de nas lang
NK088(su)001:11335: ka'i bdag po byang chub sems dpa' chen po des
NK088(su)001:11336: / zhes pa byung tshul bcu gcig pa dris pa'o //
NK088(su)001:11338: zhes pa lan bka' stsal pa /
NK088(su)001:11339: las rgyud gcad pa'i gdul bya la'ang gsum ste /
NK088(su)001:11340: 'dod pa lngas gdung shing 'jol nyogs su spyod pa 'dod pa la zhen pa'i gdul bya dang /
NK088(su)001:11341: dbang po rab 'bring gi bye brag gis 'khor ba
NK088(su)001:11342: las 'das par nges par 'byung ba'i gdul bya dang
NK088(su)001:11343: / gong ma gnyis kyis ma 'dul ba la rnam
NK088(su)001:11344: smin drag pos gdul dka' drag po'i gdul bya dang
NK088(su)001:11345: / gsum mo // las rgyud gcod byed 'gro ba
NK088(su)001:11346: de dag gang gis 'degs 'dren pa'i rtsal thabs kyang
NK088(su)001:11348: 'khor lo ltar rgyun du 'byung bas rgyun gyi theg pa dang /
NK088(su)001:11349: 'dod pa'i 'bras bu don dam lam du nges pa'i theg pa dang /
NK088(su)001:11350: skye ba med pa las 'phrul pa cho 'phrul bud+d+ha nyid drag shul du mngon 'byung gi theg pa'o //
NK088(su)001:11351: de dag ni ril rang bzhin ye nas rgyal ba'i thugs gsang sngags dam pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:11352: theg pa gsum yang byin gyis rlabs kyis rgyal ba'i mdzad par shar ba'o //
NK088(su)001:11353: ji ltar 'degs pa'i thabs rnams ni //
NK088(su)001:11355: bsam gyis mi khyab don byed pa'i tshul ji snyed pa bsdu na gsum ste /
NK088(su)001:11356: nyid du snang ba gang yin pa ni theg pa
NK088(su)001:11357: dang por rang bzhin nam 'tsho ba'i shugs kyis 'dul
NK088(su)001:11358: ba dang / nyon mongs 'dul ba'i bar mas gnyen po thabs kyis 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11359: log par zhen pa tha mas las rgyud gcod pas 'dul ba'o //
NK088(su)001:11360: de la de dag so so nas bstan pa'i phyir dang po gang snyam pa la /
NK088(su)001:11361: 'khor lo rgyun du snang ba yang //
NK088(su)001:11362: zhes pa dag bskal pa'i 'khor lor bar mi chad par rgyun du snang ba la lnga ste /
NK088(su)001:11363: ye gdod nas che ba sangs rgyas lnga'i rgyal bar
NK088(su)001:11364: grags pa lnga des gdul bya'i don 'dul byed pa'i
NK088(su)001:11365: phyir / 'byung ba nyid chen po lngar byung nas
NK088(su)001:11366: gdul bya la lngar snang nas 'gro ba 'dul sgrol
NK088(su)001:11367: te tshul ji ltar zhe na /
NK088(su)001:11368: skyed dang 'tsho dang rten pa yi //
NK088(su)001:11369: rgyu dang rkyen dang gnas pa ni //
NK088(su)001:11370: zhes pa la sogs pa 'gro ba thams cad skyed pa'i rgyu dang /
NK088(su)001:11371: 'tsho ba'i longs spyod kyi rkyen dang /
NK088(su)001:11372: rten pa'i gnas byed pas 'dul ba'ang ye shes chen
NK088(su)001:11373: po la don bya ba'i rtog 'dzin mi mnga' bar
NK088(su)001:11374: ye ngang gi lhun gyis grub pa'i shugs kyis 'byung
NK088(su)001:11375: 'dod yon lnga ril du snang nas thabs rgyu rkyen
NK088(su)001:11376: sogs gsum gyis rang las byung ba'i 'gro ba'i don
NK088(su)001:11377: byed pa'ang / de dag gi rgyu ther zug med
NK088(su)001:11378: bzhin du dus mi zad gsum du 'phel 'grib med
NK088(su)001:11379: par 'byung zhing don rnam pa gsum ste rgyu rkyen
NK088(su)001:11380: byed pa'ang / rten mdzad do // mdzad pa gsum mdzad pa gang snyam pa la /
NK088(su)001:11381: 'khor lo rgyun gyi theg pa'ang snang ba ni gang gi dbyings dang mngon sum pa /
NK088(su)001:11382: bdag nyid chen po de nyid ni //
NK088(su)001:11383: zhes pa la sogs pa chos kyi dbyings su sangs rgyas pa'i che ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11384: mngon sum du sangs rgyas pa'i che ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11385: bdag nyid chen po'i sangs rgyas pa'i che ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11386: de yin pa'i sangs rgyas pa'i che ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11387: thams cad nas thams cad du sangs rgyas pa med pa'i che ba'o //
NK088(su)001:11388: de dag kyang re re nas 'chad pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:11389: lang ka'i bdag po 'di lta ste /
NK088(su)001:11390: gang dag dbyings su sangs rgyas pa //
NK088(su)001:11391: zhes pa la sogs pa sdud pa la bos nas /
NK088(su)001:11392: sangs rgyas dang po nye bar bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:11393: dngos po lnga ril ye phyi mo nas chos kyi
NK088(su)001:11394: dbyings kyi ngang du sangs mi dmigs par bdal rgyas
NK088(su)001:11396: gnas pa tha gru che chen po bar gyur pas
NK088(su)001:11397: sa chu me rlung nam mkha' lngar snang dag /gang
NK088(su)001:11398: 'di 'gro ba dang rtsi 'khrungs la sogs pa ril
NK088(su)001:11399: gyi rgyur gyur pa 'byung ba la /
NK088(su)001:11400: snang ba bar mtshams med pa rgyun gyi nyid ye nas ril bcom 'dus shing rdzogs ldan pa la /
NK088(su)001:11401: 'das ngo bo mtha' las grol bas mtshan nges pa'o //
NK088(su)001:11402: thugs rje rtag pa'i sangs rgyas te //
NK088(su)001:11403: zhes pa mi g.yo ba'i ngang las mdzad pa gsum
NK088(su)001:11404: snang ba ni rgyun gyi rtag pa'i ngo bo dang
NK088(su)001:11406: rang bzhin kun la khyab par gnas //
NK088(su)001:11407: zhes pa ngo bo'i bdag la mi gzhan pas snod bcud ril dang gnyis su med pa'o //
NK088(su)001:11409: ces pa bzang ngan ji ltar 'dod dang gang la
NK088(su)001:11410: mos pa'i ngo bo gsum las mi 'gyur 'dod par
NK088(su)001:11413: ces pa snod bcud gnyis ka bskyed pa dang /
NK088(su)001:11415: don byed pa'i phyir ming nges so //
NK088(su)001:11417: de ltar snang la rgyun ma chad pa'i ngo bo
NK088(su)001:11418: rtag pa de nyid kyi rang bzhin ye nas sems
NK088(su)001:11419: kyi dkyil 'khor stong pas 'od gsal ba'i ngo bo
NK088(su)001:11420: yin pas snang la ma grub pa ni chos kyi
NK088(su)001:11421: dbyings te / de bas na mdzad pa gang yang mi 'gog pa'o //
NK088(su)001:11422: lang ka'i bdag po gzhan yang gang //
NK088(su)001:11423: mngon sum pa yi sangs rgyas ni //
NK088(su)001:11425: sdud pa la de las sangs rgyas gnyis pa bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:11426: 'byung ba lnga dbang po'i mngon don rdzogs par mdzad pa'o sum du gnas pa nyid /
NK088(su)001:11427: ye nas mnyam pa'i ngang du dri ma med pas sangs khyab pa'i rgyas ngo bo ni /
NK088(su)001:11428: 'byung ba nam mkha'i mtshan nyid kun tu mu mtha'
NK088(su)001:11429: med thug pa med pa'i dbyings ngang du 'dod pa
NK088(su)001:11431: gzugs med par snang ba dngos med ril dang /
NK088(su)001:11432: mtshams phyogs bcu'i 'gro ba'i kun gyi lus dang gnas
NK088(su)001:11433: la sogs pa kun go skabs nam mkhas gsal bar
NK088(su)001:11435: 'dus pa'i yod bde ba gnas dang ldan pas don mngon du mdzad do //
NK088(su)001:11437: zhes pa la sogs pa 'gro ba dang mi 'gro
NK088(su)001:11438: rtsi shing la sogs pa'i rten gzhi sa sra ba'i
NK088(su)001:11439: ngo bo ni / dngos po thams cad lus dang nags tshal rtsi thog skyed pa dang /
NK088(su)001:11442: 'gro ba kun la rnams kyi bsam pa dga' bar
NK088(su)001:11443: 'dod pa bzhin sbyor ba ni tshim par byed pa
NK088(su)001:11445: bskal phran brgyad cu'i yun gyi gzhi cig char gnas pas ming 'grub bo //
NK088(su)001:11446: 'o na nam mkha' la ni 'jig chags med pas
NK088(su)001:11447: nges par theg pa de ma yin no zhe na
NK088(su)001:11448: / gzhi la 'jig chags stong gnas yod pas phal che'i dbang dang /
NK088(su)001:11449: gzhi la bzhi 'byung ba'i yang gzhir 'gyur te /
NK088(su)001:11450: nam mkha' med na snang bar mi 'gyur ba'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:11451: theg pa de nam mkha'i mdzad spyod kyis go 'byed pa'o //
NK088(su)001:11452: mnyen lcugs gzhan bskyed rang bzhin gsal //
NK088(su)001:11453: zhes pa la sogs pa chu'i mtshan nyid gsher bas
NK088(su)001:11454: yul mnyen zhing gang du'ang lcug drang du btub pas
NK088(su)001:11455: phyi nang gzhan bskyed pa'i las byed pa dang /
NK088(su)001:11456: rang bzhin mdangs la sogs pa gsal bar byed pa dang /
NK088(su)001:11458: mi ldog rgyun du 'bab cing rgyun du 'gro ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11459: dgon pa'i sa gzhi skam po dang skom pas gdung ba kun rlan zhing tshim par byed pa dang /
NK088(su)001:11460: dus gsum du rnam par g.yo rlabs 'byung bas skye
NK088(su)001:11461: 'tsho rten las gsum byed pa'ang yun bskal phran nyi
NK088(su)001:11463: kun smin mun sel kun ston snyoms //
NK088(su)001:11464: zhes pa la sogs pa mes drod snyoms nas phyi nang smin par byed pa dang /
NK088(su)001:11465: 'od kyis mun pa sel ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11466: mthong bya'i rdzas rnams gsal bar ston pa dang /
NK088(su)001:11467: phyi nang snyoms par khyab pa dang /
NK088(su)001:11468: dngos po sreg tshig par byed pa dang /
NK088(su)001:11470: rang gi kha dog shin tu gsal bar 'byung ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11471: phyi nang gi bcud mi gtong ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11472: yongs su brtas snang ba de dag brtas par byed pa'i las dang dgu /
NK088(su)001:11473: rtsa ba gsum gyis don mdzad pa dang yun yang rjes su bsnyad do //
NK088(su)001:11474: mi gnas thogs med shugs kyis 'byung //
NK088(su)001:11475: zhes pa la sogs pa rlung gi mtshan nyid g.yo
NK088(su)001:11476: bas gcig tu gnas mi zin pas gang du'ang thogs
NK088(su)001:11477: pa med par shugs kyis 'byung ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11478: rlung nyid la dbyibs kha dog med par gzugs su snang ba bas kyang drag par 'byung ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11479: yang ljid med par kun tu g.yo 'byung ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11480: phyi nang thams cad du khyab par 'jug pa dang /
NK088(su)001:11481: snod bcud kyi gzhi rten du 'gyur ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11482: rgyu rkyen lnga yis gsum du don spyod pa ni yun 'dra'o //
NK088(su)001:11483: de dag ni gnas pa cha gcig bzung ba ste spyir 'khor mor 'byung ba'o //
NK088(su)001:11484: lang ka'i bdag po 'di lta ste /
NK088(su)001:11485: bdag nyid chen po'i sangs rgyas ni //
NK088(su)001:11486: zhes pa la sogs pa bdag nyid chen por las sangs rgyas pa rang bzhin bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:11487: 'byung ba lnga nyid ril gyi bdag nyid rang sems
NK088(su)001:11488: nyid du ye nas rdul sangs med par gsal rgyas
NK088(su)001:11489: bas bdal ba ni gong ma med pa'i mchog ste
NK088(su)001:11490: / ye shes chen po'i klong nyid nam mkha' shar ba ni /
NK088(su)001:11491: dngos po phyi nang kun 'dus shing yel 'phyo yangs
NK088(su)001:11492: pa la kun tu bzang dwangs snyigs spyad pa'i mtshan
NK088(su)001:11493: nyid med par sangs rgyas pa ni ye shes nyid
NK088(su)001:11495: sa nyid rang rig pa rang snang ba ni ril
NK088(su)001:11496: 'degs shing brjid pa lhun stug ste ye shes thugs
NK088(su)001:11497: rje kyi sku'o // chu'i las sdud pa ni gsang
NK088(su)001:11498: sngags ji bzhin pa'i mnyam sbyor ngo bo'i dgongs pa
NK088(su)001:11499: ting nge 'dzin dus gsum gang zag 'byung 'jug dang
NK088(su)001:11500: bral ba nyid 'bras bu nyid do //
NK088(su)001:11501: me las mun pa sel ba nyid ye shes lhag
NK088(su)001:11502: mthong chen po rang bzhin ji lta bar mngon du
NK088(su)001:11503: byas pa'i shes rab 'bar rang rig pa'i mngon sum
NK088(su)001:11505: rlung las gang du'ang thogs pa med pa nyid ma
NK088(su)001:11506: rmongs ye shes chen po rang bzhin ril ma 'dres
NK088(su)001:11507: rdzogs par gsal ba'i shes bya rdzogs bdag nyid de
NK088(su)001:11508: / gang la'ang thogs pa dang nyam nga ba med
NK088(su)001:11509: pa'i phyir las 'phral du byas pa lta bu ma
NK088(su)001:11510: / yin no // thams cad 'byung ba'i bdag nyid las byung ba'i ye shes chen por nges pa'o //
NK088(su)001:11511: lang ka'i bdag po gzhan yang ni //
NK088(su)001:11512: de nyid yin pa'i sangs rgyas ni //
NK088(su)001:11513: zhes pa la sogs pa ni /
NK088(su)001:11514: bos nas 'byung ba lnga rigs lnga ye shes lnga'i
NK088(su)001:11515: rang bzhin yin pa de nye bar bstan pa ni
NK088(su)001:11516: / nam mkha' thams cad du khyab cing go 'byed pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:11517: sa sra zhing mi 'gyur ba'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:11518: mes kun tu gsal zhing mnyen pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:11519: chus thams cad khyab cing drang du rung ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11520: rlung gang du'ang thogs pa med pa'i phyir sangs rgyas
NK088(su)001:11521: lngar bstan kyang ngo bo gtan nas tha dad pa
NK088(su)001:11523: 'byung ba lnga rigs lnga'i ngo bo yin pa'o //
NK088(su)001:11524: lang ka'i bdag po 'di lta ste //
NK088(su)001:11525: gang 'dir don gong ma dag ngo bo la brjod
NK088(su)001:11526: pa'i yul las 'das shing gzhan du sangs rgya ba
NK088(su)001:11527: med pa dang de nyid tsam du'ang mtshon pa dang
NK088(su)001:11528: bral ba'o // sangs rgyas med pas zhes sangs rgyas gzhan nas zhes so //
NK088(su)001:11530: zhes pa la sogs pa de nyid nye bar bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:11531: dngos po ril skabs 'dir ye nas stong pa chen
NK088(su)001:11532: po byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor du sangs pa
NK088(su)001:11533: la de nyid kyi bla dwags ma bcos dang /
NK088(su)001:11535: dngos po lngar snang yang des bsdus pa rnams ye
NK088(su)001:11536: nas snang ma myong ba la mtha'i dri ma dang
NK088(su)001:11537: bral ba bcom thams cad la ldan bdal ba ni
NK088(su)001:11538: / rnam grangs gcig tu nan gyis 'das bcom pa
NK088(su)001:11539: ma yin par gsal bas nges tshig tu 'gyur ro
NK088(su)001:11540: / // de dag min pa las yin par ma bsgyur te /
NK088(su)001:11541: gdod nas de lta bu lngar snang ba nyid sus
NK088(su)001:11542: kyang ma byas par rgyal ba'i ngo bor shar bas
NK088(su)001:11543: da 'phral du gdags pa dang bral ba'o //
NK088(su)001:11544: de dag ni rang bzhin gyi snang ba 'ba' zhig gi ngo bor 'gyur ro //
NK088(su)001:11545: lang ka'i bdag po de dag ni //
NK088(su)001:11546: 'khor lo rgyun gyi theg pa ste //
NK088(su)001:11548: zhes pa'ang theg pa'i ngo bos bstan te /
NK088(su)001:11549: sus kyang ma byas par ngang gis dus kyi rgyun du bar mi chad par byung ste /
NK088(su)001:11550: snod bcud gnyis ka la khyab par gnas te /
NK088(su)001:11551: des na snang ba 'byung lnga che ba lnga 'khor
NK088(su)001:11552: lo rgyun bshad pa'ang nges te phan pa 'ba' zhig
NK088(su)001:11554: 'di dag ni rgyal ba rdo rje sems dpa' ji
NK088(su)001:11555: bzhin pa gsang ba dam pa'i byin rlabs dang mdzad
NK088(su)001:11556: pa la / rmongs pa dag sems can gyi las su smra ba basngagasa pa ni /
NK088(su)001:11557: sngags kyi don zab mo ma mthong ba ste /
NK088(su)001:11558: dper khre'u yig 'bru thu ba yis sa gzhi chen po ma mthong ba dang 'dra ste /
NK088(su)001:11559: gsang sngags theg pa chen po la mdongs so //
NK088(su)001:11560: de bas las rgyud gcod pa'ang rjes su sbyar ro //
NK088(su)001:11561: lang ka'i bdag po gzhan yang gang //
NK088(su)001:11562: don dam nges pa'i theg pa ni //
NK088(su)001:11563: zhes pa dag gdul thabs dang po las mi mthun
NK088(su)001:11564: pa nges par 'byung ba'i gdul bya'i ched du don
NK088(su)001:11565: dam nges pa'i theg pa bstan pa'ang las dang skal
NK088(su)001:11567: 'jig rten kun 'byung tu sprul pa'i sku snang bas
NK088(su)001:11568: drang 'dren ba'i don gyis 'dul ba rgyu'i theg pa
NK088(su)001:11569: dang dka' thub dam tshig gtsor byas pas don rig
NK088(su)001:11570: par byed pa'i phyi rgyud dang /
NK088(su)001:11571: rig pa rang dbang du gyur pas thabs gang yang
NK088(su)001:11572: spong len med pas dug 'gyur rtsi ltar 'dul ba
NK088(su)001:11573: nang pa'o // gang 'dir 'dren pa 'di lta ste //
NK088(su)001:11574: yul gsum nges par snang ba ni //
NK088(su)001:11575: zhes pa la sogs pa theg pa dang pos 'dul
NK088(su)001:11576: ba'i yul la shes rab rab 'bring tha gsum yod
NK088(su)001:11577: pa'i phyir / theg pa yang rjes su mthun par snang ba ni gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:11578: dang po nyan thos bstan pa'i phyir //
NK088(su)001:11579: tha ma'i yul du gyur pa ni //
NK088(su)001:11580: shin tu ya nga'i las spangs te //
NK088(su)001:11582: tha ma la gsum gyi tha ma'i yang tha ma 'phags pa nyan thos kyi spyod yul ni /
NK088(su)001:11583: mi dge ba'i las so cog bkag ste /
NK088(su)001:11584: gzhan gyi bsam pa dang mthu na zhing mos pa'i
NK088(su)001:11585: cha lugs sgo gsum nyis brgya lnga bcu bsdoms nas
NK088(su)001:11587: rang gi 'bras bu dgra bcom pa'i gnas thob par
NK088(su)001:11588: gnyer ba'i lta spyod gzhung bsrangs nas spyod pas gang
NK088(su)001:11589: zag so sor sdug bsngal thar pa'i lam zung bzhi
NK088(su)001:11590: snang ba'o // des ni rgyal chen dang 'dra ste rang don 'ba' zhig go //
NK088(su)001:11591: 'bring gi yul du gyur pa ni //
NK088(su)001:11593: zhes pa la sogs pa tha ma'i 'bring rang rgyal ba'i spyod yul ni /
NK088(su)001:11594: dngos po phyi nang rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba bcu gnyis las snang la /
NK088(su)001:11595: de dag dgag tu rung mi rung rtsad bcad de
NK088(su)001:11596: lugs nas 'byung bas ngos zin pas lugs las bzlog
NK088(su)001:11597: pas bkag ste / gang zag la bdag med pa'i
NK088(su)001:11598: steng du gzugs kyi phung po chos ril la bdag
NK088(su)001:11601: dngos po gzugs la thogs med rab tu 'jug /ces 'byung ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11603: gzugs kyi phung po chos kyi phyogs gcig khams gcig la bdag med par rtogs so //
NK088(su)001:11604: de ltar rtogs nas 'gog pa dang /
NK088(su)001:11605: mi lcogs pa med pa la sogs pa'i ting nge
NK088(su)001:11606: 'dzin bcu gcig rim par bsgoms pas yid bzhin bde
NK088(su)001:11607: ba mchog gi sa thob ste /
NK088(su)001:11608: brjod med ngag gis mi ston par lus kyi sprul pa'i rdzu 'phrul gyis /
NK088(su)001:11609: rgyal ba'i bstan pa nub pa dang /
NK088(su)001:11610: ma byung ba'i skabs su 'dul zhing lus kyi rdzu 'phrul gyis chos ston te /
NK088(su)001:11611: de yang rang rgyal bar gyur tsam na /
NK088(su)001:11612: slob dpon la ma brten par rang gi shes rab
NK088(su)001:11613: kyi rtsal gyis rtogs bsgoms pas sa de thob ste
NK088(su)001:11615: rab kyi yul du gyur pa ni //
NK088(su)001:11616: bdag med byams snyoms rtogs las 'das //
NK088(su)001:11618: tha ma'i rab mdo sde'i lugs ni /
NK088(su)001:11619: chos dang gang zag gi dngos po gnyis yang na
NK088(su)001:11620: don dam ma dmigs pa'i lta bas spyod pa kun
NK088(su)001:11621: rdzob byams pa dang snying rje dang dga' ba dang
NK088(su)001:11622: btang snyoms gtod pa med par kun la mnyam pas
NK088(su)001:11623: 'dul lo // ting nge 'dzin ni rnam par mi rtog pa bsgom pas 'dzin pa med do //
NK088(su)001:11624: chos la bdag med pas phyi rol yang med la /
NK088(su)001:11625: nang gang zag med pas 'dzin pa dang bral te /
NK088(su)001:11626: bshad pa'i rten 'brel gyi gtan tshigs kyis mthong bas phyi nang gnyis kar ma zin te /
NK088(su)001:11627: phyogs dang bral don dam pa'i bden pa yul sems kyi ris med pa sa dang por mthong /
NK088(su)001:11628: gnyis pa na yar bsgoms pa sa rim pa bzhin sa bcu dang /
NK088(su)001:11629: de yang rnam par thar pa'i sgo gsum la rim
NK088(su)001:11630: par brten nas bsgrub pas sa bcu pa thob pa
NK088(su)001:11631: la shes bya'i sgrib pa dge ba zag bcas kyi
NK088(su)001:11632: dngos po gtan du bar cha phra ba'ang dag par
NK088(su)001:11633: byas te / lam dang chos nyid dang gnas ngan len dang /
NK088(su)001:11634: gnas 'gyur gsum gyi tshul gyis dngos med mtha' gnyis
NK088(su)001:11635: bral ba'i kun tu ngo bo nyid 'od kyi chos
NK088(su)001:11637: 'on kyang gsang sngags kyi ngo bo nyid kyi sku la ni ma reg go //
NK088(su)001:11638: lang ka'i bdag po gzhan yang gang //
NK088(su)001:11639: dka' thub rig byed theg pa ni //
NK088(su)001:11640: zhes pa lang ka la bos nas /
NK088(su)001:11641: theg pa bar ma sngags phyi pa la mos pa'i
NK088(su)001:11642: shes rab 'bring la'ang rab 'bring tha ma gsum ste
NK088(su)001:11643: / de la 'bring gi tha ma dag las snang ba kri ya'i gzhung ni /
NK088(su)001:11644: dka' thub sdom dang brtul zhugs dang //
NK088(su)001:11645: zhes pa sgo gsum gyi dka' thub dang /
NK088(su)001:11646: sdom dang rtsa ba lnga dang /
NK088(su)001:11648: brtul zhugs khrus dang gtsang sbra'i spyod pa la gtsor
NK088(su)001:11649: byas te don dam par chos thams cad mnyam nyid
NK088(su)001:11650: ma skyes pa'i ngang du mnyam par rtogs nas skye
NK088(su)001:11651: med las mi g.yos la zhen pas kun rdzob tu
NK088(su)001:11652: dam tshig sems dpa' cho ga yan lag bcu gcig
NK088(su)001:11653: gis bskyed nas / ye shes sems dpa' bkur 'os rje bor blta ste /
NK088(su)001:11654: spyi bor rdul gsum gyis mchod pa tsam du bzhugs te /
NK088(su)001:11655: 'dun pa bdag bran gyi tshul du byas nas bsgom pa dang /
NK088(su)001:11656: lha drug dang ldan pas bsgom zhing bzlas pa byas
NK088(su)001:11657: nas mchod pa dang bshags pa dang gsol ba gdab
NK088(su)001:11659: de ltar bsgrub pas rigs gsum gyi rig 'dzin non
NK088(su)001:11660: nas mjug de nyid kyis rigs kyi rdo rje 'dzin
NK088(su)001:11662: 'bring la rnam par snang ba ni //
NK088(su)001:11664: 'bring gi 'bring u pa ya'i spyod yul rnam par snang ba ni ni /
NK088(su)001:11665: spyod pa las dang bya ba gtsor kri ya ltar
NK088(su)001:11666: byas nas khyad par du rigs bzhi'i lha bsgom pa'ang
NK088(su)001:11667: de kho na nyid bzhi dang ldan pas yum dang
NK088(su)001:11669: mchod bzlas gsol ba byas nas /
NK088(su)001:11670: rdo rje mi bskyod pa'i rig 'dzin grub nas /
NK088(su)001:11671: mjug rigs bzhi rgyal ba nyid du 'gyur ro //
NK088(su)001:11672: rab la nges par snang ba ni //
NK088(su)001:11674: 'bring gi rab yo ga'i bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:11675: bsgom bya'i yul lnga mngon par byang chub pa bsgoms te /
NK088(su)001:11676: dang por rang rig pa gdan zla ba bsgom pa dang /
NK088(su)001:11680: yongs su rdzogs pa la sbyangs te mjug las su rung ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11681: bsgom bya mngon byang lnga nyid rang rig pas rnal 'byor gyi mngon sum du gsal te /
NK088(su)001:11682: bsgom pa'i yul de nyid mtshan ma nyid der ni mtshan ma med par mngon byang gsal te /
NK088(su)001:11683: gnyis su med par chud nas rig 'dzin gyi go
NK088(su)001:11684: 'phang brgyud nas 'bras bu rigs lnga'i rdo rje gsum
NK088(su)001:11685: dang tha mi dad par 'gyur ro //
NK088(su)001:11686: lang ka'i bdag po gzhan yang gang //
NK088(su)001:11687: zhes pa phyi pa las mi mthun par 'dul ba'i
NK088(su)001:11688: theg pa la'ang gdul bya rab kyi rab 'bring tha
NK088(su)001:11689: ma gsum gyis lha rim par bsgom pa la rtsal
NK088(su)001:11691: skad cig mas rdzogs dang bsgom pa bdal ba chos nyid kyi sa pa dang /
NK088(su)001:11692: bskyed rdzogs dang bral ba yongs su rdzogs pa spyi chibs kyi sa pa'o //
NK088(su)001:11693: tha ma bskyed par gang snang ba //
NK088(su)001:11694: thabs dang shes rab rnam dag pas //
NK088(su)001:11695: zhes pa la sogs pa rab kyi tha ma ma
NK088(su)001:11696: h+aa yo ga ste bskyed pa'i tshul gyi lugs ni
NK088(su)001:11697: / lta spyod kyi thabs shes rab gnyis ji lta
NK088(su)001:11698: bar snang stong dang bral bar rtogs pa'i lhan cig
NK088(su)001:11699: pa'i ye shes nyams rnam dag pas rnyed nas dri
NK088(su)001:11700: chen dri chu zil pa lhag pa'i byang chub sems
NK088(su)001:11702: dngos po gzhan bsdu ba ni /
NK088(su)001:11704: spyad par bya ba lnga dang /
NK088(su)001:11706: de dag gi rang bzhin ye phyi mo nas de
NK088(su)001:11707: bzhin nyid mtha' las grol ba'i ngo bos rigs lnga
NK088(su)001:11708: dang tha dad med par rtogs shing bsgom par sangs
NK088(su)001:11709: rgyas so // de bas na blang dor med pa'i
NK088(su)001:11710: rnal 'byor spyod pa de dag ched du byas te
NK088(su)001:11711: rgyas so // spyod cing / de bzhin nyid kyi
NK088(su)001:11712: ngang las lha'i dkyil 'khor rim par bskyed de bsgom
NK088(su)001:11713: pas dngos po rtogs tshogs nyid 'bras bu dkyil 'khor
NK088(su)001:11714: du sangs rgyas par gyur pa ni rtsal chen rdzogs
NK088(su)001:11716: 'bring la rdzogs par gang snang ba //
NK088(su)001:11717: mnyam pas mnyam pa'i don mthong na //
NK088(su)001:11718: zhes pa rab kyi 'bring a nu yo ga rdzogs
NK088(su)001:11719: pa'i tshul du spyod pa'i lugs gang snang ba ni
NK088(su)001:11720: / 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos
NK088(su)001:11721: rnams mnyam pas sras byang chub kyi sems bde ba
NK088(su)001:11722: chen por che chung med par gsal ba'i don ji
NK088(su)001:11723: lta ba bzhin du mnyam pa'i don mthong rtogs pa'i
NK088(su)001:11724: / dus na / chos kyi dbyings bya ba tsam la'ang dmigs pa'i rten mi 'cha' mnyam rdzogs ste /
NK088(su)001:11725: rig pa nyid ngo bo yul shes ma grub bzhin
NK088(su)001:11726: gsal bas gnyis med pa'i ngo bor dbyings ye shes
NK088(su)001:11727: ril rtogs pas chos so cog kun rig de nyid
NK088(su)001:11728: du ma 'dres can rdzogs par mkhyen cing /
NK088(su)001:11729: rgyu 'bras kyi chos thams cad kyi bdag nyid yin par kun tu snang dus gsum du gsal lo //
NK088(su)001:11730: de lta bu la dkyil 'khor rim par bskyed pa dang /
NK088(su)001:11731: spyod pa ched du bsten pa'ang med de /
NK088(su)001:11732: chos nyid mi 'gyur ril gnyis med du gsal bas bdal ba chos kyi sa 'thob bo //
NK088(su)001:11733: rab la yongs su rdzogs pa ni //
NK088(su)001:11734: ye shes dbyings zhes bya ba'i don //
NK088(su)001:11735: zhes pa rab kyi rab shin tu rnal 'byor a
NK088(su)001:11736: ti yo ga'i lugs kyis gang snang ba ril bdag
NK088(su)001:11737: nyid chen por rdzogs pa'i lugs ni /
NK088(su)001:11738: kun nas nyon mongs pa dang rnam par byang ba
NK088(su)001:11739: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gnyis kyi chos rnams
NK088(su)001:11740: gdod nas ma bsal ma bkod par rang bzhin lhun
NK088(su)001:11741: gyis grub pa'i ngang du gsal ba la /
NK088(su)001:11742: dngos po gzhal ba'i grub mtha' khong du chud par byar yang med de /
NK088(su)001:11743: 'du shes gang du'ang ma zhugs btsal med ma bsams
NK088(su)001:11744: ma dpyad pa nyid kyis ji bzhin pa'i don mthong
NK088(su)001:11745: ba med par mthong bar 'gyur te /
NK088(su)001:11746: rdo rje sems dpa' nam mkha' che las kyang /
NK088(su)001:11747: bya ba med pas grol bas grol //
NK088(su)001:11748: rang byung ye shes btsal med pas //
NK088(su)001:11749: grol nas grol ba'i lam yang ston //
NK088(su)001:11751: dngos po gzhal zhing don tshol ba'i bya byed med
NK088(su)001:11752: pa nyid kyis tha snyad tsam du grol zhes kyang
NK088(su)001:11753: bya ste / de la bcings pa'i chos ma dmigs pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:11754: de bas na ngo bos yul bral ba la dbyings
NK088(su)001:11755: ye shes gnyis su med pa la'ang yid mi rten
NK088(su)001:11756: pas / sems thag pa nas gud nas go bar byar med do //
NK088(su)001:11757: 'on kyang gtan nas go ba byar med na chos
NK088(su)001:11758: ji bzhin pa nyid du ji ltar 'gyur zhe na
NK088(su)001:11759: / ci la'ang rig par byar med par rig na ma rtogs par rtogs /
NK088(su)001:11760: ma mthong bar mthong ba'i bla dwags tshig gi tha snyad du rtogs zhes bya ste /
NK088(su)001:11761: bslab pa med pa'i bslab pa'o //
NK088(su)001:11762: de lta bu'i gdeng chud pa la 'chad pa'i zin
NK088(su)001:11763: pa'i don dang ldan pas sgo gsum sha thang bas
NK088(su)001:11764: btsal med bsgrub pa med do //
NK088(su)001:11765: dus gsum gyi rgyal ba ril gyi spyi mes 'bras bu'i sdong po ni /
NK088(su)001:11766: rang gi sems ji bzhin par rdzogs gsal ba nyid pas de lta bu'i bsgom pa'i dus na'ang /
NK088(su)001:11767: rig pa ji bzhin pa'i rjes su 'brang ba med /
NK088(su)001:11769: bsam pa dang dpyod pa med /
NK088(su)001:11775: de ltar cir yang bsam du med pa nyid phyi mo'i chos nyid kyi thog tu bab pas /
NK088(su)001:11776: de dag nyid du 'dod pa'ang med pa'i bla dwags
NK088(su)001:11777: su rnam par mi rtog pa zhes kyang bya ste
NK088(su)001:11778: / de lta bu la ni yengs pa'ang med bsgom rgyu'ang med do //
NK088(su)001:11779: de ltar rtogs na bsgom pa mi 'gog bsgom pa'ang med de /
NK088(su)001:11780: thun mtshams med pa'i bsgom pa chen po'o //
NK088(su)001:11781: dus deng sang gi gang zag rab gcig de ni chos kyi gzhi yin no //
NK088(su)001:11782: gang zag gi bsam pas a ti yo ga la dmigs dgos pas /
NK088(su)001:11783: thabs dmigs pa can gyi man ngag gis 'grol zhes smra ba ni /
NK088(su)001:11784: de nyid kyi don gyi gdeng ma rnyed par gsal te /
NK088(su)001:11785: mdongs pa de ni dper na dong rwa'i lde'u mig
NK088(su)001:11786: gis bang mdzod tha ram 'byed par 'dod pa dang
NK088(su)001:11787: 'dra'o // de lta bu'i don chen po ni /
NK088(su)001:11788: ril ma btsal lhun gyis rdzogs pas rdzogs pa spyir chibs kyi sa'o //
NK088(su)001:11789: lang ka'i bdag po gzhan yang gang //
NK088(su)001:11791: zhes pa dag sdud pa po la bos nas /
NK088(su)001:11792: theg pa tha mas 'dul ba'ang gsum ste /
NK088(su)001:11795: 'khrugs zhe sdang mchog tu che ba'i 'gro ba smad pa'i las ngan sha stag spyod pas /
NK088(su)001:11796: 'du shes bsam ngan rnams chad pa'i las kyis 'phro bcad la /
NK088(su)001:11797: 'du shes snga ma las bsgyur ba'i phrin las mdzad pa'i bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:11798: 'di phyi ma srid gsum bar ma dor d+r+wa ba thar dka' zhing /
NK088(su)001:11799: gnas gcig tu'ang 'khor lo skyor bur 'byung ba rnams
NK088(su)001:11800: kyi zhe sdang 'dod chags gti mug gi spyod pa'i
NK088(su)001:11801: las rgyud gcod pa ni dgos ched phyir du phyir
NK088(su)001:11803: zhes pa rgyal ba'i thugs rje chen po'i 'khor lo
NK088(su)001:11804: bskor bas byas nas las ngan tshar gcad pa ni
NK088(su)001:11805: / dngos bskal pa'i 'khor lo nyid kyis gcad do //
NK088(su)001:11806: ci phyir sems can kha cig ni //
NK088(su)001:11807: zhes pa dag bskal pa kho nas tshar gcad pa'i dgos pa ni /
NK088(su)001:11808: 'gro ba ji snyed pa las la la ni shin tu chags pa che ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11809: la la ni shin tu ma rig pas non pa dang /
NK088(su)001:11810: la la shin tu zhe sdang ba ste dus ni
NK088(su)001:11811: 'chad de sgron ma'i bya ba rnams rdzogs te nub
NK088(su)001:11812: pa'i dus te / de lta bu dug gsum bdo
NK088(su)001:11813: ba las thabs gzhan gang gis kyang mi 'dul bas
NK088(su)001:11814: pa'i dus te / / 'tsho ba'i srog dang bral
NK088(su)001:11815: bas 'chi ba'i sdug bsngal bstan pas las ngan chad
NK088(su)001:11816: pa'i dus te / / pa dang / sdug bsngal
NK088(su)001:11817: nyid kyis sems skyo ba'i rgyur 'gyur bas de dag
NK088(su)001:11818: bstan pa'i ched du 'dul byed ni /
NK088(su)001:11821: zhes pa rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa sems kyi
NK088(su)001:11822: dkyil 'khor 'od gsal ba'i ye shes kyi cho 'phrul
NK088(su)001:11823: dbang po'i mngon du snang ba ni gang zhe na
NK088(su)001:11824: / rang bzhin gyi khro bo 'gro ba zhal du gsol bar mdzad pa'i dngos po ni /
NK088(su)001:11825: 'chad pa 'byung ba lnga dag gis 'joms par byed do //
NK088(su)001:11826: ci yang ma yin pa'i ngang las rang snang bas mdzad pa ma nges pa ni cho 'phrul te /
NK088(su)001:11827: bskal pa lnga ni rang bzhin gyi khro bo'o //
NK088(su)001:11828: des phyi nang gi dngos po ma lus ril bsgral
NK088(su)001:11829: nas ma grub par byed pa'i stong par mdzad gtan
NK088(su)001:11830: tshigs kyis khro bor ming grub bo //
NK088(su)001:11831: de dag kyang las kyi dbang gis rang thad du snang ba tsam ma yin pas /
NK088(su)001:11832: ril ye shes chen po'i phyir stong pa chen po'i
NK088(su)001:11833: nam mkha' ni ye shes chen po'i khro bo ste
NK088(su)001:11834: thams cad der thim mi gnas par rngub par mdzad
NK088(su)001:11835: do // de lta bas na dngos po ril de
NK088(su)001:11836: kho na nyid du bsgral ba'i skyas thebs pas thugs
NK088(su)001:11838: sred zhi 'tsho bral bskal pa yis //
NK088(su)001:11839: zhes pa dag 'thad pa'i bza' btung bral ba ni
NK088(su)001:11840: mu ge'i bskal pa ste lo gsum 'byung ye shes
NK088(su)001:11841: las bdun bdun bas zas skom la sogs pa 'dod
NK088(su)001:11842: pa la lhag par zhen pa'i las 'joms so //
NK088(su)001:11844: zhes pa bzod ldan mi bzod pa'i sdug bsngal can
NK088(su)001:11845: dran pa nyams par byed pa nad kyi bskal pa
NK088(su)001:11846: sprin dmar mched pa 'dra ba zla gsum bdun gyis
NK088(su)001:11847: yid kyi las 'du byed mang po dang khyad par
NK088(su)001:11848: du gti mug gi las lam 'joms par byed do
NK088(su)001:11849: // thabs 'dzin mtshon cha'i bskal pa yis //
NK088(su)001:11850: zhes pa zhe sdang 'joms pa'i thabs can ni /
NK088(su)001:11851: mtshon cha'i bskal pa zhag gsum 'byung ste /
NK088(su)001:11852: des bdag gzhan gyi dngos po gnyis ka 'joms so //
NK088(su)001:11853: lhag mthong me yi bskal pa yis //
NK088(su)001:11854: zhes pa me'i las rang bzhin gyi lhag mthong ste /
NK088(su)001:11855: des bshad pa'i dug gsum la sogs pa'i ngo bo dngos ril bsreg go //
NK088(su)001:11856: zhi gnas chu yi bskal pa yis //
NK088(su)001:11857: zhes pa rang bzhin gyi zhi gnas chu'i bskal pas
NK088(su)001:11858: nyon mongs pa dang las lam gyi dri ma dag
NK088(su)001:11859: par byed do // thogs med rlung gi bskal pa yis //
NK088(su)001:11860: zhes pa mtshan nyid gang du'ang ma zin pas skad
NK088(su)001:11861: cig la'ang bya ba byed pa'i rlung gis yul dngos
NK088(su)001:11862: po thams cad phyogs ril du gtor te med par
NK088(su)001:11863: byas so // shes rab nam mkha'i bskal pa yis //
NK088(su)001:11864: zhes pa mi dmigs pa'i ngo bo rang bzhin gyis
NK088(su)001:11865: shes rab stong pa nam mkhas dngos po skye 'gro'i
NK088(su)001:11866: rgas rgud ril med par mdzad pas khro bo lnga
NK088(su)001:11867: yis mdzad pa'i grub mtha' lta bu bas spyir sbyar
NK088(su)001:11868: ro // de'i dgos pa ci yod zhe na /
NK088(su)001:11869: las ngan myur du rgyun bcad nas //
NK088(su)001:11871: thabs dang theg pa zhes pa /
NK088(su)001:11872: dus dang 'dul thabs gnyis ka'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:11874: snyigs mar gyur pa'i skabs rnams su //
NK088(su)001:11875: zhes pa la sogs pa zas dang /
NK088(su)001:11879: las kyi snyigs ma la bab pa'i tshe mdo sngags
NK088(su)001:11880: kyi bstan pa 'dul ba rnam gnyis nub pa dang
NK088(su)001:11881: dung phyis pa ltar gyur ba'i dus su /
NK088(su)001:11882: chags sdang la sogs pa dngos su che ba 'byung ba'i tshe /
NK088(su)001:11883: theg pa chung ngu ba thams cad mdzad par ma
NK088(su)001:11884: shes pas phyogs gcig pa'i mdzad pa la zhen pa
NK088(su)001:11885: dag na re / ston pa ni 'das /
NK088(su)001:11887: 'gro ba 'dul ba'i thabs ci yang med do zhes smra ba dag ni /
NK088(su)001:11888: dus de dag la gsang sngags kyi thugs rje 'char
NK088(su)001:11889: nub med pas mdzad pa ma nus kho nas ston
NK088(su)001:11890: pa ma 'das bstan pa ma nub pa ni de
NK088(su)001:11891: dag nyid yin pa'i phyir shugs kyis 'dul ba yin
NK088(su)001:11892: snyigs ma'i dus der thugs rje chen po'i byin rlabs
NK088(su)001:11894: sangs rgyas mya ngan yongs mi 'da' //chos kyang nub par mi 'gyur te //
NK088(su)001:11895: zhes gsungs pa'i don kho na'o //
NK088(su)001:11896: lang ka'i bdag po de ltar na //
NK088(su)001:11897: 'di kun gsang ba dam pa yi //
NK088(su)001:11898: zhes pa la sogs pa bshad pa'i tshul des ni /
NK088(su)001:11899: bskal pa ji ltar byung yang de kho na nyid brtags dka' ba'i ngang las 'gyur ba med de /
NK088(su)001:11900: de nyid gsang sngags yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:11901: de bas na snang tshul yang mnyam pa'i dbyings mtha' gang yang ma bkol ba las /
NK088(su)001:11902: ngo bo de nyid las stong pa'i chos rnams 'byung
NK088(su)001:11903: bar zad mi gzhan pa'i bskal pa 'gro 'ong med
NK088(su)001:11905: de dag gi ngo bo stong nyid gsang ba de kho na stong pa chen por bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:11906: chos kyi me long theg pa chen po 'di nyid yin te gnyis pa med pa'o //
NK088(su)001:11907: gsang ba'i bdag pos de skad ces brjod pas /
NK088(su)001:11908: zhes pa 'khor gyis gsang ba'i gdeng rnyed pa'o //
NK088(su)001:11909: le'u bzhi bcu bzhi pa 'grel pa'o ////las rgyun gcod pa na yang 'byung /
NK088(su)001:11910: zhes pa gnyen pos gcod pa na'ang 'byung ba'i nges
NK088(su)001:11911: tshig dang yi ger snang ba'i dbang du bstan te
NK088(su)001:11912: / don du gsum ka tha dad par 'gyur ba med de /
NK088(su)001:11913: byung tshul bcu gcig pa'i don bshad pa'o //
NK088(su)001:11914: bam po drug pa'o ////bdun pa 'chad pa ni /
NK088(su)001:11916: lang ka'i mnga' bdag byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po des /
NK088(su)001:11917: zhes pa la sogs pa sdud pa pos byung tshul tha ma dris pa sgra bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:11920: zhes pa gsang bdag gis gsang sngags che ba 'byung ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11921: bskul ba'i sa la bzhengs pa'i phyir bstan par bka' stsal pa'o //
NK088(su)001:11923: zhes pa sdud pa pos nges par bskul ba gnad
NK088(su)001:11924: la phab nas 'gro ba'i ched du zhu ba'i phyir
NK088(su)001:11925: ston pa la kye skyes bu bos nas /
NK088(su)001:11926: gdul bya nyon mongs rnams la snying brtse thugs rje chen pos phan par bya ba'i dgos ched du /
NK088(su)001:11927: mi chen po theg pa chen po'i rnam 'byor d+r+wa ma dag gi yul /
NK088(su)001:11928: chos thams cad ngo bo nyid ril sangs rgyas kyi
NK088(su)001:11929: sar ston pa de'i phyir spyod pa gang du ma
NK088(su)001:11930: bkag pa'i sogs la yang ris med de /
NK088(su)001:11931: mnyam pa nyid du mdzad pa thabs kyi theg pa
NK088(su)001:11932: chen po 'ching ba'i las nyid kyis thar bar byed
NK088(su)001:11933: pa'i don ni / rgyal ba'i dgongs pa dam pa
NK088(su)001:11934: sogs dgongs pa'i zhe phug brnag pa ma nor ba'i
NK088(su)001:11935: gsang sngags kyi theg pa 'di ni /
NK088(su)001:11936: chos rnam par bgro zhing sogs ston pa'i 'gying bag tu bzhugs pa'i ston pa khyod kyis /
NK088(su)001:11937: don ji lta ba nyid kho na ltar bstan du gsol zhes skabs la bab bo ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11938: shin tu'ang 'dis 'dul bas skabs la bab po ba dang /
NK088(su)001:11939: nges don bka' stsal ba'i dus la bab bo zhes brnag cing zhus so //
NK088(su)001:11940: gnad la dbab par zhu ba'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:11941: de ci'i slad du zhe na /
NK088(su)001:11942: skyes bu chen po khyod ni /
NK088(su)001:11944: zhes pa khyed kyis bstan par dka' bar gsungs kyang /
NK088(su)001:11945: rtog dpyod pa'i gtan tshigs dang dgos pa ni /
NK088(su)001:11946: skyes bu sogs ston pa khyod la rgyal ba thams
NK088(su)001:11947: cad kyi rigs kyi bdag po nyid kyis 'chad pa
NK088(su)001:11948: ltar / rdo rje rgya gram gyi 'khor lo lag tu gtad de /
NK088(su)001:11949: rnam par bla brkyal gyi spobs pa can du byin
NK088(su)001:11950: gyis brlabs nas gsang sngags 'chad pa'i skyes bur dbang
NK088(su)001:11951: bskur nas / gang rmongs pa dman pa gsang don
NK088(su)001:11952: la mdongs pa'i ye shes grol bar bya ba dang
NK088(su)001:11953: bskur nas / / gang 'thoms pa shes rab kyi spyan mdongs pa dag gi ling thog bsal te /
NK088(su)001:11954: sprin dpung thabs mang po zad pa med pas gdul
NK088(su)001:11955: bya rnams thams cad gdung ba med par bde blag
NK088(su)001:11956: tu thar pa mchog drang ba'i thob pa'i bya ba'i
NK088(su)001:11957: phyir / dbang bskur ba lags pas 'dir yang dgos pa de nyid kyi phyir /
NK088(su)001:11958: dgongs pa dam pas gsang sngags theg pa chen po
NK088(su)001:11959: bshad du gsol zhes gsol ba gdab cing gzhan bskul
NK088(su)001:11960: mdzad pa'o // gsang ba pa'i bdag po des 'di skad du /
NK088(su)001:11961: zhes pa sdud pa po khyod kyis gsang sngags zhu
NK088(su)001:11962: bar bskul ba'i dam bcas pa'i go cha brtson 'grus
NK088(su)001:11963: dang ldan pas gdul bya kun la rab tu la
NK088(su)001:11964: thugs rje'i ched du don zab mo dngos gzhi gang
NK088(su)001:11965: la ston pa la zhu ba la brtson pas gsang
NK088(su)001:11966: sngags shod cig par gleng bslang ba la legs pa
NK088(su)001:11967: gnang bas skabs las gleng du bslang ba 'di las
NK088(su)001:11969: thos pa'i lo rgyus bka' stsal pa /
NK088(su)001:11970: 'di ltar ston pa bzhis 'khor bzhi la bstan pa
NK088(su)001:11971: bzhi gsungs pa bdag gis ma brgyud par mngon sum
NK088(su)001:11972: du skad cig la thos zhe'o //
NK088(su)001:11974: zhes pa la sogs pa thos pa'i tshul 'di ltar
NK088(su)001:11975: nye bar bstan pa bzhin don 'di skad ston pa
NK088(su)001:11976: nga nyid kyis gsang sngags ma nor ba'i don ji
NK088(su)001:11977: bzhin pa byang chub nges pa nyid chos du ma
NK088(su)001:11978: la dgongs pas thos pas don snang ba'i rig pa
NK088(su)001:11979: la dus gcig na shar ba'i tshe /
NK088(su)001:11980: thams cad ni ji snyed pa'i chos kun de las 'phrul pa'o //
NK088(su)001:11981: dpe nam mkha' lta bu chos kyi sku las ni tshig tu ma brjod par /
NK088(su)001:11982: rang byung nga'i shes rab dang ba la byin rlabs khong nas shar te /
NK088(su)001:11983: rang snang ril ji bzhin par blo la shar ba ni thos pa'o //
NK088(su)001:11984: sku bzhi las thos par 'chad pas yid ches par bya ba'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:11985: gsang ba'i tshig ni 'di skad du //
NK088(su)001:11987: gsang sngags kyi don 'di nye bar bstan pa skad
NK088(su)001:11988: sku yi bstan pa longs spyod sku las thos pa'i
NK088(su)001:11989: dus gcig tshe / gdul bya rnams dang mnyam pa
NK088(su)001:11990: la 'jog pa'i byang sems la lta spyod mthun pas
NK088(su)001:11991: drangs pa'i thabs su dgongs pas brgyud de longs spyod
NK088(su)001:11992: rdzogs pa'i sku las thos pa'o //
NK088(su)001:11993: lung gi gtan tshigs 'di skad du //
NK088(su)001:11994: zhes pa gsang sngags kyi lung gcus nas tshig tu
NK088(su)001:11995: bstan pas 'di skad du nye bar bzung ba ni
NK088(su)001:11996: / bdag gis sprul pa'i sku las tshig tu thos
NK088(su)001:11997: pa'i tshe 'chad pa'i ldem po bzhi dang dgongs pa
NK088(su)001:11998: bzhis gzhan don la dgongs nas /
NK088(su)001:11999: gzhan gyi tshig tu smra ba la sogs pa'i tshig gsungs pas drang ba'i don du thos pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12001: zhes pa gdul bya'i 'dod chags la sogs pa nyon
NK088(su)001:12002: mongs pa re re'i cha rkyen du de dang 'tshams
NK088(su)001:12003: pa de nyid du spyod pa'i tshig 'di nye bar
NK088(su)001:12005: gsang ba'i sku'i byin rlabs kyi rtogs pa kho na thos pa yin pa'i tshe /
NK088(su)001:12006: shin tu 'dod chags che ba'i las spangs pas mi spongs te /
NK088(su)001:12007: dper mes tshig pa la mes gdung na phan pa bzhin /
NK088(su)001:12008: 'dod pa spyod pas mi ltung grol ba'i thabs kyis
NK088(su)001:12009: 'dren pa'i tshig tu thos te brjod pa dang 'dra
NK088(su)001:12010: ba'i phyir ro // gsang sngags rdo rje nam mkha' che //
NK088(su)001:12011: tshig gi spyod yul ma yin zhes pa /
NK088(su)001:12012: lhag pa'i rnal 'byor chen po'i don gsang sngags shin
NK088(su)001:12013: tu zab pas rdo rje dbyer med cing btsal ba
NK088(su)001:12014: dang bral ba nam mkha' thams cad la bdal che
NK088(su)001:12015: ba'i don ni / ngo bo ma nges pas ma
NK088(su)001:12016: rtogs pa la gzhan du bstan pa'i yul med de
NK088(su)001:12017: ba'i don ni / / tshig gis mi phebs spyod yul min pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:12018: te tshig lhag ma'i don ni /
NK088(su)001:12019: mtshan nyid de lta bas na ngas khyod la bdag
NK088(su)001:12020: gis go bar rab tu dka' bstan du mi btub
NK088(su)001:12023: dape'am tshad ma'am gtan tshigs sam //
NK088(su)001:12024: zhes pa la sogs pa thun mong gi gtan tshigs kyis mi phebs pa bshad zin te /
NK088(su)001:12025: de ni dper dmus long nam mkha' la mthos 'jal ba dang 'dra'o //
NK088(su)001:12026: 'on kyang bka' yi gnyer gtad cing //
NK088(su)001:12027: log gzhan thabs kyis drang ba dang //
NK088(su)001:12028: zhes pa de ltar bstan dka' na'ang /
NK088(su)001:12029: rgyal ba ril gyis gsang ba'i bdag por dbang bskur gnyer gtad pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:12030: thabs chen pos log sred drang ba'i phyir lang ka
NK088(su)001:12031: khyed kyis gsang sngags 'chad par bskul ba'i brtson 'grus
NK088(su)001:12032: kyi go cha dang ldan pas bskul ba dang gsum
NK088(su)001:12033: gyi dbang gis tshig gis ji lta bar phebs dka'
NK088(su)001:12034: yang / gsang sngags ma mthong ba'i mun pa'i blo
NK088(su)001:12035: can rnams thun mong ma yin pa'i tshig gi don
NK088(su)001:12036: gsal bar byas nas rgyud dgrol bas yang dag pa'i
NK088(su)001:12038: dper khye'usa khye'u 'byin pa'i tshul du rtogs nas sa
NK088(su)001:12039: non pa'i thabs ji ltar 'tshams par bshad par zhal
NK088(su)001:12040: gyis 'ches pa'o // rang bzhin ye nas sangs rgyas pa //
NK088(su)001:12041: zhes pa la sogs pa gsang sngags rang bzhin ye nas ji bzhin pa'i don ni /
NK088(su)001:12042: spyir rtogs pa mthong dang ma rtogs pa ma mthong gnyis las /
NK088(su)001:12043: dman pa'i 'gro ba rnams kyis ma rtogs /
NK088(su)001:12044: sangs rgyas dang rig pa 'dzin pa chen po rnams kyis ni rtogs so //
NK088(su)001:12045: de'i phyir yang bstan dgos pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12046: mthong ba mngon thos rnam gnyis las //
NK088(su)001:12047: zhes pa la sogs pa gsang sngags kyi don ji lta bar mthong ba dang /
NK088(su)001:12048: dbang po mngon sum du ma nor ba thos pa rnam gnyis las /
NK088(su)001:12049: thos pas mthong ba goms pas skyed du bya ba
NK088(su)001:12050: mthong ba med par gyur pa mthar phyin dam pa
NK088(su)001:12051: rgyal ba'i dgongs pa mngon sum ma yin te /
NK088(su)001:12052: de ni blo gros shes rab dang rnal 'byor ting nge 'dzin dang spyod par yon tan ldan pas /
NK088(su)001:12053: gsang ba'i che ba mdo bzhi lta bus thos pas
NK088(su)001:12054: mtshon nas rtogs par 'gyur ba'i ched du'ang tshig tu
NK088(su)001:12055: bstan no // stug po bkod pa'i rgyal ba yang //
NK088(su)001:12056: zhes pa la sogs pas stug po bkod pa 'di
NK088(su)001:12057: la gnas pa'i rgyal ba ji snyed pa dag byang
NK088(su)001:12058: chub chen po chos sku snying po lhun gyis grub
NK088(su)001:12059: pa'i tshe na'ang / byang chub chen por bzhugs pas gdul bya mi smin pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:12060: rgyal ba de dag gi mdzad pas gdul bya bskyang
NK088(su)001:12061: ba'i ched du sprul pa dang longs spyod du snang
NK088(su)001:12062: bar mdzad nas / theg pa chen po'i chos kyi
NK088(su)001:12063: longs skus 'khor lo dngos su ston pa dang tshig
NK088(su)001:12064: gis lung bstan pa mdzad do //
NK088(su)001:12066: zhes pa dag dus gsum gyis rgyal ba rnams kyis kyang /
NK088(su)001:12067: dus thams cad du nyid kyi dgongs don theg pa chen po 'khor la bka' stsal te /
NK088(su)001:12068: ngas 'dus pa'i 'khor khyed rnams la bgros pas nyon cig par gdams so //
NK088(su)001:12069: bstan pa dngos ji lta bu zhig snyam pa la /
NK088(su)001:12070: lang ka'i bdag po 'di lta ste /
NK088(su)001:12071: dam pa rnams kyi dgongs pa la 'jug par 'dod na mdzod du 'jug par bya'o //
NK088(su)001:12072: zhes pa la sogs pa sdud pa po la bos nas bgros pa'i don nye bar bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:12073: rgyal ba'i brnag par bya ba'i gsang sngags la khyed
NK088(su)001:12074: slob pa la 'jug par 'dod mos pa zhig na
NK088(su)001:12075: / 'jug pa'i de'i thabs chos kyi rnam grangs bcu yod de /
NK088(su)001:12076: rnam grangs dang po ni le'u zhe lnga nas nga drug gi bar bcu gnyis gyis 'grel to //
NK088(su)001:12077: gnyis pa ni nga bdun pas 'grel to //
NK088(su)001:12078: gsum pa ni nga brgyad pas 'grel to //
NK088(su)001:12079: bzhi pa ni nga dgu pas 'grel to //
NK088(su)001:12080: lnga pa ni drug cu pas 'grel to //
NK088(su)001:12081: drug pa ni re gcig pas 'grel to //
NK088(su)001:12082: bdun pa ni re gnyis pas 'grel to //
NK088(su)001:12083: brgyad pa ni re gsum pas 'grel to //
NK088(su)001:12084: dgu pa ni re bzhi pas 'grel to //
NK088(su)001:12085: bcu pa ni re lnga pa nas tha ma'i bar gyis 'grel to //
NK088(su)001:12088: zhes pa de dag nyid rtogs pa'i thabs dris pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12091: zhes pa ston pas dri ba bcu las dang po'i
NK088(su)001:12092: don bstan pa 'chad pa'i sgo gsum nas brgyud pa
NK088(su)001:12093: zhugs nas mngon sum pas gang med la sogs lhun
NK088(su)001:12094: gyis grub pa'i gsang sngags dam pa /
NK088(su)001:12095: yon tan gyi 'byung gnas nyid thob par bya'o zhes gsungs pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12098: lan du sgo gsum bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:12099: rnam par dka' ba'i spyod pas bdag gzhan mthar phyin par byed pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12100: thabs kyis sgo mang pos sbyong ba dang /
NK088(su)001:12101: ji lta ba'i don ma bslad par bstan pas sbyor ba'i phyir rgyu'i theg pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12103: nang pa'i theg pa bstan pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12106: zhes pa la sogs pa rtogs pa'i thabs dri lan sgra bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:12107: de dag so so nas rtogs par bya ba'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:12108: lang ka'i bdag po de la spyod pa'i 'dren sgo /
NK088(su)001:12109: zhes pa rnam grangs kyi mdor bstan pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12110: de la yan lag drug gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:12111: grangs la snyegs pas yan lag bkar ba la'ang drug ste /
NK088(su)001:12112: bstan pa dang 'bras bu'i gzhir gyur pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:12113: lta spyod kyi yul sbyor ba'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:12114: las mthar phyin pa'i don bstan pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:12115: chos rnams kyi rang gi ngo bo bstan pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:12116: sdom pa gzung bar bya ba'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:12117: chos rnams kyis mtshan nyid ci 'dra ba bstan pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:12118: de la rgyu'i yan lag gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:12119: zhes pa drug la snyegs pas rgyu bkar nas bstan pa ni gnyis te /
NK088(su)001:12120: bstan pa phun sum tshogs pa 'byung ba'i gzhi dang mthar phyin pa'i 'bras bu 'byung ba'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:12121: la nga ka'i bdag po de la 'byung ba'i yan lag gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:12122: zhes pa gnyis pa las bkar nas 'di nyid ston pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12123: gang yongs su tshogs na brjod pa 'byung ba nyid la bya ste /
NK088(su)001:12124: zhes pa 'di nyid dngos po grub par byed pa'i gtan tshigs te /
NK088(su)001:12125: phun sum tshogs pa drug tshang na bstan pa'i sgra 'byung ba'i phyir rgyur nges so //
NK088(su)001:12126: de kho na ston pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12132: sgro skur dang rdzun spangs pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:12133: rgyud grol bar byed pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:12134: thos pa'i don mi gtong ba'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:12135: mchod gnas dam pa dag gi gzhi rten du gyur pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:12136: mang po tshogs pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:12137: de nyid las gzhan du ma yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:12139: gang dam par smin pa'i rgyu ste /
NK088(su)001:12140: zhes pa dag 'di nyid bstan pa'i dngos po gang
NK088(su)001:12141: zhig chos sku nyid 'grub par byed pa'i rgyu la
NK088(su)001:12142: bya ste / ngo bo dang nges tshig 'grub par 'gyur ro //
NK088(su)001:12143: de nye bar bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:12144: mdor byang chub kyi yan lag ste dngos bdun gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:12145: chos rnam par 'byed pa yang dag byang chub kyi yan lag dang /
NK088(su)001:12146: dran pa yang dag byang chub kyi yan lag dang /
NK088(su)001:12147: brtson 'grub yang dag byang chub kyi yan lag dang /
NK088(su)001:12148: dga' ba yang dag byang chub kyi yan lag dang /
NK088(su)001:12149: shin tu sbyangs pa yang dag byang chub kyi yan lag dang /
NK088(su)001:12150: ting nge 'dzin yang dag byang chub kyi yan lag dang /
NK088(su)001:12151: btang snyoms yang dag byang chub kyi yan lag go //
NK088(su)001:12152: lam gyi yan lag /ces pa 'phags pa'i lam yan lag brgyad de /
NK088(su)001:12153: yang dag pa'i lta ba dang /
NK088(su)001:12154: yang dag pa'i rtogs pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12156: yang dag pa'i las kyi mtha' dang /
NK088(su)001:12158: yang dag pa'i rtsol ba dang /
NK088(su)001:12159: yang dag pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK088(su)001:12163: zhes pa dag de nyid bstan pa la gnyis te /
NK088(su)001:12164: shes rab gsum gyi don rnyed nas phar bcus sa
NK088(su)001:12165: bcu la sbyor shes rab kyis shes bya la sbyor
NK088(su)001:12166: ba dang / thugs rje'i spyod pas 'gro don la sbyor ba'o //
NK088(su)001:12168: de la blo'i yul la sbyor ba ni /
NK088(su)001:12169: zhes pa de nyid la'ang bzhi ste /
NK088(su)001:12170: don gyi rtogs pa 'byung ba'i rgyu gsung rab ston
NK088(su)001:12171: pas gnang ba dang 'khor gyis gus pas zhu ba
NK088(su)001:12172: gnyis sde yan lan bcu gnyis pa sogs pa'i thos
NK088(su)001:12174: des don ji lta ba mthong bas sa dang po la sbyor ba dang /
NK088(su)001:12175: de nyid thos bsam goms nas rnam thar sgo gsum nges pa'i lta bas mthong ba'o //
NK088(su)001:12176: goms pa mi 'gyur bas chos kyi sku la sbyor ba dang /
NK088(su)001:12177: bden pa don la zhi lhag gis bsgoms te goms
NK088(su)001:12178: pa mthong nas blo bzhag ste chos nyid ma skyes
NK088(su)001:12182: zhes pa snying rje bsgom pa'ang gang 'gro ba rnams
NK088(su)001:12183: las dang nyon mongs pas khams gsum du smin par
NK088(su)001:12184: byed pa dang / de bsgrub pas sdug bsngal spyod
NK088(su)001:12185: dang khyad par gsum dang brgyad la sogs pas gdung
NK088(su)001:12187: 'gro ba rnams kyis ma skyes pa'i don mthong bas rang bzhin 'khrul pa la snying rje 'byung ba'o //
NK088(su)001:12191: gang dang grub pa'i mtha' 'brel ba'i ni rgyu rkyen
NK088(su)001:12192: 'bras bu rim par 'brel ba bsgoms pas sa bcu
NK088(su)001:12193: rdo rje lta bu'i sa tis bdud btul nas kun
NK088(su)001:12194: 'od gyi dngos pos bya ba dgos ched mthar phyin
NK088(su)001:12195: pa'i don dam par chos kyi sku nyid du byung
NK088(su)001:12196: ba ste / thob pa dam pa de kho na dngos kun tu 'od kyi sa'o //
NK088(su)001:12198: de la dngos gzhi'i yan lag ni //
NK088(su)001:12199: zhes pa dag ni de nyid bstan pa ni bde
NK088(su)001:12200: bar gshegs pa'i dgongs pa chos nyid ma skyes pa
NK088(su)001:12201: gtan 'bebs par byed pa'i ngo bo yan lag 'byung
NK088(su)001:12202: ba'i gzhi yin pas nges tshig 'grub bo //
NK088(su)001:12204: don nyid lam dang bsgrub pa'i rang bzhin dang /
NK088(su)001:12205: gzhal bya'i rtsa ba 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos dang /
NK088(su)001:12206: 'khor ba dang lam pa dang 'bras bu ril gyi gzhi bden pa gnyis so //
NK088(su)001:12208: de la rang bzhin gyi dngos gzhi gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:12210: zhes pa la sogs pa bzhi ste /
NK088(su)001:12211: rang bzhin ma skyes pa'i don de lam pas thun mong gi gzhung ma nor bar thos pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12212: de'i don la chos dang bla ma la skyabs su
NK088(su)001:12213: dong rjes su yi rang bas bsam dpyod byed pa
NK088(su)001:12214: dang / de sdom pa dang bslab pa ma mthong bar du mi gtong ba dang /
NK088(su)001:12215: blo sdom pa dang bslab pa mthar phyin gros yongs su chub pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12217: rtsa ba'i dngos gzhi gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:12218: zhes pa la sogs pa de nyid ni nye bar bstan pa ni bcu gcig ste /
NK088(su)001:12220: dngos po gnyis pa'i yo byad kyi ming dang tha snyad dang /
NK088(su)001:12221: spyod pa dang gnyis ka'i cha las btag pa'i sgo
NK088(su)001:12222: gsum gyi spyod pa ming gi tha snyad ji snyed
NK088(su)001:12223: pa dang / skye ba dang sems kyi gang zag
NK088(su)001:12224: de'i las bzang ngan tha dad par rgyu rkyen las
NK088(su)001:12225: pa dang / byung ba dang / skyes nas de
NK088(su)001:12226: dag lus ther zug pa med de skad cig ma'i
