NK088(su)001:12228: bde ba gnas pa'i mtshan nyid la 'tsho bas tshims pa longs spyod pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12229: lus dang de la brten pa'i brtag pa'i chos rnams kyis gdung ba ste 'khor ba'i rten no dang /
NK088(su)001:12230: yongs su byang ba brtags pa'i zhen pa thog ma
NK088(su)001:12231: nas bsags pa'i dang 'di la bsags pa'i bag chags
NK088(su)001:12233: rgyu rkyen gyis rnam pa brda tha snyad kyi dngos
NK088(su)001:12234: po tha dad par sems snang ba bshad pa rnams
NK088(su)001:12236: lus brten gyi dus bcas pa'i sgo nas dbang ba'i bdag nyid dang /
NK088(su)001:12237: dmigs pa'i sgo nas shes bya'am bstan bya'i yul dang /
NK088(su)001:12238: de dag gi 'du gcig la gcig 'phrod kyi sgo
NK088(su)001:12239: nas rten 'brel gyis gsal bar ldan pa'i phyir 'bras
NK088(su)001:12240: bu 'dzin pa'o rnam par shes pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12242: thams cad kyi dngos gzhi gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:12244: dang po ci tsam du srid pa'i sa bon ma
NK088(su)001:12245: zad kyi bar du gnas pa'i ngo bo la snang
NK088(su)001:12246: ba'i kun rdzob ni bzhi ste /
NK088(su)001:12248: zhes pa dag ni dbang du bya ba'i phyir yul
NK088(su)001:12249: dang las dang skye ba dang rgyu rkyen 'brel ba
NK088(su)001:12250: du ma 'dus te gnas 'du ba dang dang /
NK088(su)001:12251: bsam pa dang sbyor bas bya ba gang la rtsom 'jug pa'i shes pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12252: brtags pas gang zag gis bdag dang srog dang /
NK088(su)001:12253: shed can dang shed bdag tu snang ba dang /
NK088(su)001:12254: yul dang snod dang dngos po ste phung khams skye mched rnams su bzung ba'o //
NK088(su)001:12255: yongs su dag pa la snang ba ni /
NK088(su)001:12256: zhes pa nyi shu rtsa bdun te /
NK088(su)001:12262: zhes pa dran pa nye bar bzhag pa bzhi dang /
NK088(su)001:12263: yang dag par spong ba bzhi dang /
NK088(su)001:12265: tshad med pa bzhi ste rgyud du 'dogs pas mi 'bral ba dang /
NK088(su)001:12266: skyon gyi bya ba 'dor ba'i las byed pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12267: bsam pa mi g.yo ba dang /
NK088(su)001:12268: bdag gzhan sdug bsngal bral bar byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:12277: zhes pa pha rol tu phyin pa bcu dang /
NK088(su)001:12278: so so yang dag pa rig pa bzhi dang /
NK088(su)001:12280: bsdu ba'i dngos po bzhi dang /
NK088(su)001:12284: ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo 'bum phrag go //
NK088(su)001:12285: de yang mi dmigs zin pas bdag gzhan gyi don
NK088(su)001:12286: spyod pa la ma chags pa'i thabs spyod yin pa'i
NK088(su)001:12287: phyir dang / shes bya so so rig pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:12288: don rtogs pa'i gzhir gyur pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:12289: bdag gzhan don chud mi gson pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:12290: yul sems 'dzin pa bral bas ngar 'dzin med pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:12291: yang dag pa'i don mthu can byed pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:12293: mi rtog pa'i lhag mthong rnam gnyis mthong bar byed pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:12294: ting nge 'dzin mi g.yo bar gnas pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:12301: mngon par shes pa drug dang /
NK088(su)001:12303: zhes 'bras bu mchog mi 'gyur ba'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:12304: so so'i cha ma 'dres pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12306: byang chub kyi spyod par 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:12318: zhes pa spong ba'i 'du byed brgyad dad pa 'dun
NK088(su)001:12319: pa brtson 'grus btang snyoms shes rab rtog pa dran
NK088(su)001:12321: rnam thar gsum bsgom pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12323: gzungs kyi sgo lnga brgya dang /
NK088(su)001:12325: 'phags pa dang byang chub kyi lam bco lnga dang /
NK088(su)001:12326: byang chub phyogs kyi chos sum cu rtsa bdun dang /
NK088(su)001:12331: de yang skyon bdun dmigs brjed na dran pa bsten /
NK088(su)001:12332: blos ma zin na rtog pa /
NK088(su)001:12333: rgod na 'khor ba la skyo ba bskyed dran pa'i thag pas gdags /
NK088(su)001:12336: le lo na dad pa 'dun pa brtson 'grus /
NK088(su)001:12340: bsam pa don las mi g.yeng ba dang /
NK088(su)001:12341: don du gnyer nas sa la bskyod par byed pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12342: ltung ba med pa'i yon tan dang /
NK088(su)001:12343: bdud dang mu stegs la sogs pas mi tshugs mi shigs pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12344: lam gyis khong du chud de gnyer bas 'bras bu chub par byed pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12345: gzhan du ma 'dres pa'i cho dag khong du chud par bya ba yin pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12346: ji lta ba'i don mthong ba dang /
NK088(su)001:12348: sa'i rtse mo nyid du gyur pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12349: sgrib pa bsrabs pas thob la ma rags pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:12350: de'i ngo bo bstan pa ni ngo shes par bya ba'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:12352: de la gzung ba'i yan lag gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:12353: zhes pa la sogs pa 'dir sgo gsum gyi sdom pa bzung ba'i don bstan pa ni bdun te /
NK088(su)001:12354: gang dang po mkhan po dang /
NK088(su)001:12362: dge slong gi tshul khrims rnams legs par nod pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12363: de yang rtsa ba ni phas pham bzhi dang /
NK088(su)001:12364: ltung byed dgu bcu rtsa gci dang /
NK088(su)001:12365: bslab pa mang po'i chos brgya dang /
NK088(su)001:12366: dge 'dun gyi lhag ma'i chos bcu gsum dang /
NK088(su)001:12367: rtsod pa nye bar zhi ba'i chos bdun la sogs
NK088(su)001:12368: pa dag theg pa che chung gnang bkag gi chos
NK088(su)001:12369: bsrung ba dang / sgo gsum sdom pa'i rang bzhin can du bya ba dang /
NK088(su)001:12370: 'chal ba'i dri ma med par bya ba dang /
NK088(su)001:12371: nyes pa'i rang bzhin rtogs nas khyim nas khyim med
NK088(su)001:12372: par don dam rtogs nas 'khor ba las rab tu
NK088(su)001:12373: byung ba dang / rgyal srid dang longs spyod rab
NK088(su)001:12374: tu byung bas btang ba dang zhar la byang sems
NK088(su)001:12375: des ma chags par gtang ba dang /
NK088(su)001:12377: khyo mo la sogs pa la yongs su ma chags pa kho na ste /
NK088(su)001:12378: de ni sdom pa bzung ba'o //
NK088(su)001:12380: de la mtshan nyid kyi yan lag nang rigs dang sna tshogs gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:12381: zhes pa de la'ang bcu gcig ste /
NK088(su)001:12384: de la kun rdzob gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:12386: bcu gcig la snyegs pas kun rdzob bkar nas bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:12388: kun gzhi shes pa skad cig ma las dang nyon
NK088(su)001:12389: mongs pas rgyas par ltung ba'i sa bon dang bcas
NK088(su)001:12390: pa dang / sgra don spyi la nan gyis zhen
NK088(su)001:12391: pa'i ngo bo med pa la yod par bzung ba
NK088(su)001:12392: yul thams cad du brtags pa'i 'khrul dang /
NK088(su)001:12394: ngo bo sgyu ma tsam du snang ba'ang /
NK088(su)001:12395: bsdu na ngo bo gnyis te /
NK088(su)001:12396: yang dag pa dang ma dag pa'i dbye bas lung ma bstan shes par bya'o //
NK088(su)001:12397: lang ka'i bdag po de la dam pa gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:12398: zhes pa don dam pa yang tshan gsum ste /
NK088(su)001:12399: mtha' rgyu rkyen bral bas ril gyis ma bsgos pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12400: rgyu rkyen las ma byas pas des na mi 'jig pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12401: chos thams cad kyang skye ba med pa'i ngang du 'dus so //
NK088(su)001:12404: nges tshig dang bcas par 'jal bar bya'o //
NK088(su)001:12405: dmigs pa ni thams cad du bstan pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12406: zhes pa dmigs byed ni dus kun tu shes pa kho na yin par bsnyad do //
NK088(su)001:12407: rnam pa ni thams cad du yang brtags pa ste /
NK088(su)001:12408: zhes pa ngo bo nyid dus ril du rang gi blos bzung bas ma 'dres par snang ba'o //
NK088(su)001:12409: de la'ang rnam pa dgu ste /
NK088(su)001:12411: de la ni bden pa ni gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:12412: de kho na nyid gang yin pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12413: zhes pa chos rnams kyis chos nyid mi 'gyur ba yongs su grub pa la /
NK088(su)001:12414: ma nor mi 'gyur ba yin no bar zhen pa gang yin pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12416: zhes pa brjod mi brjod nges par gzhag pa yang shugs kyis bcur 'gyur ba gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:12417: thog ma med pa nas las lung bstan mar /
NK088(su)001:12418: phung po lnga yi rgyun blos ma phye ba'i gang
NK088(su)001:12419: zag dang kyi bag chags kyi rgyun gyi dbang du
NK088(su)001:12420: gyur pa can du mthong ba dang /
NK088(su)001:12421: 'khrul pa'i chos rnams su zhen pas 'i dbang gis tha dad du bsams pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12422: chos rnams don yang na rang bzhin med par phyogs gcig tu bstan pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12423: so sor yang na gang zag gi bsam pa dang
NK088(su)001:12424: kun rdzob kyi brjod pa ji ltar mos pa ltar
NK088(su)001:12426: phyir rgol ba pa la bde bar gtan la phab
NK088(su)001:12427: kyang log pa'i gal du smra ba la bdag gis
NK088(su)001:12428: ma nges na khyod kyis ji ltar rtogs zhes pa'o
NK088(su)001:12429: // dris te lan brjod pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12430: ci'ang mi brjod par bzhag pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12431: sngar grub zin pa la rjes mi gcad par gzhag
NK088(su)001:12432: pa des kyang ma 'dul na de der bzhag pa
NK088(su)001:12435: thams cad la der yang 'ong zhing drin mi smra'o //
NK088(su)001:12436: bstan pa ma yin par brjod pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12437: ji skad bshad pa rnams 'khor la don zhib tu brjod par bya ba dang /
NK088(su)001:12438: mkhan po gzhan gyi bla ma dang bud+d+ha la gzhan dag tu lung bstan pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12441: zhes pa sdug bsngal myong ba'i rgyur gyur pa'i phyir te /
NK088(su)001:12442: ma rig pa'i las rnams su brtags pa kun nas nyon mongs pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12444: zhes pa 'bad pas bde ba thob pa'i phyir te /
NK088(su)001:12445: rnam par byang ba'i yon tan brjod pa rnams su brtags pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12446: lang ka'i bdag po tshul gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:12447: zhes pa 'bras bu la sbyor ba'i lugs brjod pa ste /
NK088(su)001:12448: bsgrub bya'i don dam pa lta bu'i don la 'jug pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12449: thos pas 'bras bu ste kun mkhyen dang /
NK088(su)001:12450: bstan pa'i tshig don bdag gi rtogs gzhan la mtshon pa brjod pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12451: des mtha' yi lta ba sel ba'i tshul ni gang la ltos pa mtha' ste mi gnas pa'o dang /
NK088(su)001:12452: ji snyed pa'i don shes pa'i ngang la mi 'da' ba zhi ba lhag mthong dang /
NK088(su)001:12453: dgongs pa la mi g.yo mi 'gyur ba zhi gnas so //
NK088(su)001:12454: de dag ni yang dag pa ched du byas pa'i brtags pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12455: lang ka'i bdag po 'jug pa gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:12457: zhes pa shes pa yul la 'jug pa'i don ni gsum ste /
NK088(su)001:12458: shes pa 'jug pa'i rtsom pa med pa nas kyang
NK088(su)001:12459: yin la legs nyes gang la 'jug pa'i tshe'o dus
NK088(su)001:12460: skabs dang / gsum tshogs pa'i reg pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12461: rkyen bzhi 'dzom pas ji lta ba nges par byed pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12462: de lta bus yul shes par brtags pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12463: lang ka'i bdag po rig pa gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:12464: zhes pa bden pa dang bcas pa blo la grub par byed pas the tshom chad pa ste /
NK088(su)001:12465: de la bzhi ni rnam grangs bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:12466: lang ka'i bdag po de la ltos pa gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:12467: zhes pa ltos pa'i rig pa ni /
NK088(su)001:12468: gang rgyu rkyen la ltos nas 'bras bu 'byung bar gzhag pa da nga /
NK088(su)001:12469: brjod pa dang dngos po gang grags pa'i stobs kyis
NK088(su)001:12470: yod pa la ltos nas med pa la tha snyad
NK088(su)001:12473: skye ba grub pa dang tha snyad gdags pa'i grub pa'i bye brag gis gnyis so //
NK088(su)001:12474: bya ba byed pa gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:12475: zhes pa byed pa'i rig pa'ang bye brag gis gsum ste /
NK088(su)001:12476: dngos po zhig 'bras bur gyur par bya ba la
NK088(su)001:12477: rgyu rkyen des byed pa lta bu ste thob pa'o
NK088(su)001:12478: // rnam rtog mthun snang gang gi dbang gis yul
NK088(su)001:12479: gang la grags pa'i bya ba byed pa ste dper
NK088(su)001:12480: na ri bong can la zla ba'i sgras brjod pa'i
NK088(su)001:12481: bya ba byed pa lta bu dang gnyis /
NK088(su)001:12482: skye ba'i dngos po rgyu rkyen so sor rang rang gis las kyi bya ba byed pa ste /
NK088(su)001:12483: rgyu rkyen las yod pa'i las bsgrub pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12485: de la gang go cha bgos pa ste /
NK088(su)001:12486: zhes pa 'thad pa bsgrub pa'i rig pa bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:12487: bsgrub bya gang bsgrub par gang gi dam bcas te mi 'gyur pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12489: zhes pa gzhan gyi mthun pa dang mi mthun brtsod pa'i bden pa dang brdzun pa smra ba'o //
NK088(su)001:12491: bdag nyid kyi bsgrub bya gang nges skyon dang bral
NK088(su)001:12492: ba par shes par bya ba'i phyir rgyu lung dang
NK088(su)001:12493: rig pa rkyen du gyur pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12494: zhes pa rang gi don du don bsgrub pa'i shes pa ste nges pa bskyed pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12495: lang ka'i bdag po de yang 'di ltar dag pa dang ma dag pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12496: zhes pa sdud pa po la bos nas de la dbye na skabs kyis gnyis te /
NK088(su)001:12497: yang dag pa'i shes pa ste bdag gi sde pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12498: yang dag pa ltar snang ba'i shes pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12505: zhes pa yang dag pa'i shes pa ni rnam pa lnga yis mthar phyin par 'gyur te /
NK088(su)001:12507: bsgrub bya rtsod gzhi chos can la 'brel zhing yod pa'i gtan tshigs dang /
NK088(su)001:12508: grags par mtshon par byed pa'i dpe dang /
NK088(su)001:12509: pha rol grags pa'i gtan tshigs dang /
NK088(su)001:12510: kun gyi stobs las byung ba'i nges pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12512: de la 'du byed thams cad mi rtag pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12513: 'khor ba thams cad sdug bsngal ba dang /
NK088(su)001:12514: chos thams cad stong pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12515: chos rnams bdag med pa ni bdag gis sde pa'i dmigs pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12516: zhes pa sdud pa po la bos nas /
NK088(su)001:12517: rjes su dpag par bya ba bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:12520: dmigs pa bstan de yang nang pa kun gyi spyi'i gzhi yin pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12521: nang pa kun la grags pas 'dir mtshon par byed pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12522: thams cad skad cig ma dang /
NK088(su)001:12523: skye zhing 'pho ba'i phyir pha rol gzhan yod pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12524: zhes pa 'dus byas ril kun gyis 'jig pas skad cig ma yin pas byas pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12525: thams cad brtags pa las snang bas 'khrul pa tsam gyi ngo la gzhan dbang yod pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12526: las rnams mi rtag pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12527: zhes pa dag sgo gsum gyi bya ba la yod
NK088(su)001:12528: pa'i byed pa ste nus par 'byin nas zad par
NK088(su)001:12530: bya ba sngar gyi las la ltos te rgyu la gnas pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12531: las de dang las la yod pa'i bde sdug rnams
NK088(su)001:12532: 'bras bu la gnas pa ste 'bras bu bzho ba
NK088(su)001:12534: de ni 'dus byas kyi gnas skabs las 'bras bu brtsis pa ste /
NK088(su)001:12535: bsgrub bya sgrub par byed pa'i gtan tshigs so //
NK088(su)001:12536: gnas skabs kyi stobs kyis chos grags pas bsgrub bya rang bzhin du bsgrub pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12537: thams cad la grags pa ni nye bar sbyar ba dang /
NK088(su)001:12538: zhes pa dag phyir rgol ba'i blo la grags pa sdud pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12539: mthun pa dang mi mthun pa dgu dang dgu ldan pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12540: rgol ba dang phyir rgol ba la grags pa'i dbang gis dper 'grub pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12542: zhes pa dpe de dag pha rol la bum pa
NK088(su)001:12543: la sogs pa gang gi lo ka la skye ba
NK088(su)001:12544: dang 'jig par chad cing grags pa ni grags pa'o
NK088(su)001:12545: grags pa dang / des gtan tshigs mthun snang grub grags pas chos can bsgrub pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12546: gang gi lung gis tshad mas tshad ma nyid du snang ba ni nges pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12547: zhes pa byed pa dang las bsgrub bya nyid nges
NK088(su)001:12548: par bdag gzhan gnyis ka'i blo la bden pa'i bya
NK088(su)001:12549: ba ste 'di blo la 'di snang ba'o //
NK088(su)001:12550: lang ka'i bdag po de yang 'di ltar /
NK088(su)001:12551: zhes pa dag sdud pa po la bos nas /
NK088(su)001:12552: gtan tshigs de yang mngon sum bzhir byung ba bas rtsod pa dang bral dang /
NK088(su)001:12553: rjes dpag la yod par nges pa rang bzhin dang /
NK088(su)001:12554: 'bras bu bsgrub pa'i mthun phyogs la yod pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12555: mi dmigs pa'i mi mthun pa'i phyogs la yod pa
NK088(su)001:12556: rtags te gtan tshigs ni 'bras bu rgyu yod par
NK088(su)001:12558: de rnams la gtan nas yang dag pa'i shes pas
NK088(su)001:12559: the tshom dang yid gnyis log pa'i phyogs gcod pa
NK088(su)001:12560: dang / gcod pa nye bar 'jug pa'i rkyen mi
NK088(su)001:12561: mthun pa'i mthun pa'i phyogs dang 'gal ba dang ma
NK088(su)001:12562: grub pa ma tshang ba bral ba ste /
NK088(su)001:12564: bden phyogs dang mthun par gzhan blo la snang ba lo na ni bsgyur bas phyir gyi don te /
NK088(su)001:12565: spyir gyis gnas las gtan tshigs kyi bzhi par bsgyur
NK088(su)001:12566: ba ste chos lnga dang ldan pa'i gtan tshigs kyis
NK088(su)001:12567: don nges na yang dag 'khrul pa mi 'byung nges
NK088(su)001:12568: par thag chod pa'i tshad ma'o //
NK088(su)001:12569: de ni las dang po'i mngon sum dang /
NK088(su)001:12570: zhes pa bsdu na tshad ma dpag pa 'di gnyis su 'dus pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12572: zhes pa de dag gi skyon rnams sel bas bral snang gi yang dag pa'i tshad ma'o //
NK088(su)001:12573: lang ka'i bdag po ma dag pa ni 'di ltar /
NK088(su)001:12574: zhes pa bos nas gtan tshigs ltar snang ba bstan pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12576: zhes pa dag grangs bstan pa ste gong gi lnga las rim pa bzhin log pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12577: lang ka'i bdag po de la yongs su dag pa'i mtshan nyid /
NK088(su)001:12578: ces pa la sogs pa sdud pa po la ma dag pa bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:12579: mtshan nyid mi mthun pas phan tshun mi mthun pa ni 'gal ba'o //
NK088(su)001:12580: lang ka'i bdag po thams cad yid kyi yul du bya ba dag go //
NK088(su)001:12581: zhes pa dag bsgrub bya log pa ni /
NK088(su)001:12582: thams cad yid kyi yul du bstan pa ni sgra
NK088(su)001:12583: chos can rtag ste shes bya yin phyir zhes pa
NK088(su)001:12584: lta bu phyogs gnyis kar yod pas thun mong gi
NK088(su)001:12585: ma nges pa ste rtags phyogs gnyis kar zhugs par
NK088(su)001:12587: rtags de bsgrub bya yang dag gi phyogs gcig la
NK088(su)001:12588: ma grub pas dngos po'i ril nam mkha' mthun pa
NK088(su)001:12589: dang / mi mthun pa bum pa la'ang zhugs pa'i
NK088(su)001:12590: stobs kyis bsgrub bya yang dag ma grub pa dang
NK088(su)001:12591: dang / / sgra chos can mi rtag ste byas pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:12592: rig byed kyi sgra bzhin zhes bkod tshe rig byed
NK088(su)001:12593: rtag par 'dod pas mthun phyogs la ma mthong ba
NK088(su)001:12594: lta bu mthun par sbyar ba la ma grags pa'i
NK088(su)001:12595: stobs kyis thun mong ma yin pa'i ma nges pa
NK088(su)001:12596: mi mthun phyogs la yod kyang ma mthong ba phyogs
NK088(su)001:12597: gnyis kar med nas ma mthong ba gnyis kar yod
NK088(su)001:12598: kyang ma mthong ba la sos par gyur pa dang
NK088(su)001:12599: / de'i stobs kyis bsgrub bya yang dag pa mi 'grub pas ma dag pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12600: phyogs thams cad kyi stobs kyis rang bzhin la mthun par snang ba ni /
NK088(su)001:12601: dngos po la ma grub pas ma grub pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12602: mtshan nyid mi mthun pa gcig la gcig snang ba'i dbang gis 'gal lo //
NK088(su)001:12603: lang ka'i bdag po gzhan yang mthun pa'i dpe /
NK088(su)001:12604: zhes pa la sogs pa mthun pa dpe sgra chos can /
NK088(su)001:12607: nam mkha' bzhin dang sbyar ba la /
NK088(su)001:12608: rtags de mi mthun phyogs blo la'ang zhugs pas mi
NK088(su)001:12609: mthun pa snang bas thun mong ma yin pa'i 'gal
NK088(su)001:12610: ba'o // sgra chos can rtag ste lus can min
NK088(su)001:12611: pa'i phyi dper na bum pa bzhin zhes mi mthun
NK088(su)001:12612: pa dpe dang sbyar ba la rtags de mthun pa
NK088(su)001:12614: mi mthun pa'i phyogs la med pa nyid du ma nges pas thun mong ma yin pa'i 'gal ba'o //
NK088(su)001:12615: de dag ma nges pa'i skyon yang yin no //
NK088(su)001:12616: rang bzhin las ma grub pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12617: rtog pa las ma grags pas ma dag pa'i rnam par snang ba ste /
NK088(su)001:12618: de'i ngang gi bya ba ma dag pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12619: byed pa'i shes pa ma dag par snang ba las nges pa las log pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12620: lang ka'i bdag po chos nyid /
NK088(su)001:12621: ces pa chos nyid kyi rig pa ni /
NK088(su)001:12622: dper na chu'i chos rang bzhin gyis gsher zhes bstan pa lta bu'o //
NK088(su)001:12623: lang ka'i bdag po gang du /
NK088(su)001:12624: zhes pa shes pa'i rigs gcig tu 'dod pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12625: du mar spros pa'i tshul gnyis ni /
NK088(su)001:12626: phyi rol gyi yul ril la'ang de bzhin du 'gyur te /
NK088(su)001:12627: 'dir shes pa'i rigs su gcig pa la las kyi
NK088(su)001:12628: khyad par gyis brgyad du phye ba lta bu ste
NK088(su)001:12629: / mdor gcig las du ma du ma las gcig
NK088(su)001:12630: de ltar phye bas don gyi dngos po gcig du
NK088(su)001:12631: ma dang bral bar gyur pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12632: mtshan nyid kyi yan lag la bcu gcig gi gsum man chad kyi don brjod pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:12633: lang ka'i bdag po dmigs pa ni 'dzin pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12635: zhes pa shes pa rgyu 'bras kyi chos kyi yul la gtod pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12636: de nyid kyi so sor bye brag ma 'dres pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12637: 'o na 'di gnyis bldabs par gyur pa ci dgos pa la /
NK088(su)001:12638: de ni mdo rgyas dang ngo bo brjod pa dang nges tshig lta bu'i phyiir ro //
NK088(su)001:12639: lnga pa byang chub ni rang bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:12640: zhes pa rgyu 'bras 'khor 'das chos rnams kyi ngo bo chos nyid do //
NK088(su)001:12641: drug pa gang spangs pas gang thob pa ni 'bras bu'o //
NK088(su)001:12642: zhes pa sgrib pa phra rags gnyen pos bral bas sku gsum ye shes bzhi mngon du snang ba'o //
NK088(su)001:12643: bdun pa gang byang chub cing gang la brjod pa ni bsnyad pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12644: zhes pa dag gis bdag don du shes bya don
NK088(su)001:12645: khong du legs par chud nas gzhan la ston pa'o
NK088(su)001:12646: // brgyad pa gang gi phyogs dang /
NK088(su)001:12647: zhes pa gang dag pa'i tshad ma mya ngan 'das
NK088(su)001:12648: pa ba dang mi mthun pa ma dag pa lta
NK088(su)001:12649: ba ngan pa bdag 'dzin le lo lta bu don
NK088(su)001:12651: dgu pa gang gi phyogs la nan tan /
NK088(su)001:12652: zhes pa mthun pas bden pa'i rnam par grol ba
NK088(su)001:12653: de kho na gtan tshigs la yang yang du dems
NK088(su)001:12654: su byed pas chud brtson 'grus mi gson pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12655: bcu pa gang dang mi mthun pa'i /
NK088(su)001:12656: zhes pa phyir rgol ba 'khor ba'i chos lta bu'am
NK088(su)001:12657: mu stegs lta bu ma dag pa'i rig pa can
NK088(su)001:12658: gyi phyogs su nyes pa son pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12659: bcu gcig pa gang dang mthun par /
NK088(su)001:12660: zhes pa sangs rgyas pa lta bu lam la zhugs
NK088(su)001:12661: pas 'bras bu mthar phyin nang rigs pa dag pa
NK088(su)001:12665: 'bras bu mthar phyin sdud pa po la bos nas bshad pa rnams kyis /
NK088(su)001:12666: chos rnams kyi mtshan nyid bstan pa'i phyir ngo bo bstan pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12667: de ltar yan lag drug gis rgyu'i theg pa tha ram dang 'dra bar /
NK088(su)001:12668: lde'u mig 'dis gsal bar 'chad cing ston pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12669: lang ka'i bdag po de la mdo bzhi gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:12671: zhes pa lde'u mig gnyis kyi grangs brjod pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12672: lang ka'i bdag po de la dgongs pa'i gzhan pa'i mdo ni /
NK088(su)001:12674: zhes pa gzhan la dgongs nas gzhan du smra ba'i dgongs pa la bzhi ste /
NK088(su)001:12675: mnyam nyid kyi rang bzhin la dgongs pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12676: dus gzhan la dgongs pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12677: don gzhan la dgongs pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12678: gang zag gi bsam pa la dgongs pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12680: zhes pa mnyam pa nyid la dgongs pa ni /
NK088(su)001:12681: gang zhig dus gsum rgyal ba so so sangs rgyas
NK088(su)001:12682: mar me mdzad bas sh+aakya thub pa la 'dul zhing
NK088(su)001:12683: chung snyam du rtog pa la /
NK088(su)001:12684: sangs rgyas bzang ngan dang gnyis su rtog pa'i zhen pa bsal ba'i ched du /
NK088(su)001:12685: rgyal ba gnyis po yang chos sku la dgongs gzhi mnyam pa dgongs te /
NK088(su)001:12686: sh+aakya thub pas de mar me mdzad gang yin pa
NK088(su)001:12687: ni 'di nyid do nga nyid yin no zhes gcig
NK088(su)001:12688: par bka' stsal pa lta bu'o //
NK088(su)001:12689: lang ka'i bdag po dus ni 'di ltar sgyid lug
NK088(su)001:12690: pa gang dag /ces pa la sogs pa dus gzhan
NK088(su)001:12692: gang zag sems rtsol ba dang mos pa dang shes
NK088(su)001:12693: rab la sems zhum pa dang le lo can dag
NK088(su)001:12694: /sangs rgyas kyi chos thabs dang brtson pa chen pos
NK088(su)001:12695: 'grub dgos zer ba de tsam mi 'grub mi lcogs
NK088(su)001:12696: zhes smra ba dag /sems dang ba bskyed pa'i ched
NK088(su)001:12697: du rgyu chung ngus kyang brgyud nas thob pas rgyu
NK088(su)001:12698: 'bras mi bslu ba'i don dus nam zhig 'grub pa
NK088(su)001:12699: la dgongs te / ar+ya pa lo zhes brjod pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12701: skad cig tsam mos pa sgo gsum gyi bya ba tsam gyis 'grub po bar bka' stsal pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12702: lang ka'i bdag po don ni 'di ltar /
NK088(su)001:12703: zhes pa don gzhan la dgongs pa ni /
NK088(su)001:12704: su zhig gis shes bya gang zab mo'i don ma
NK088(su)001:12705: mthong bar tshig tsam la ngas ji bzhin pa rtogs
NK088(su)001:12706: so mthong ngo zhes nga rgyal gyi che ba'i sems
NK088(su)001:12707: byed pa dag gi ma rig pa bsal te don
NK088(su)001:12708: rnal ma la gzhug pa'i ched du gang zhig gis
NK088(su)001:12709: sa dang po ma thob bar de bzhin nyid mi
NK088(su)001:12711: chos nyid kyi don mthong bar bya ba ni dpag
NK088(su)001:12712: tu med pa'i rgyal ba mang po la bsnyen bkur
NK088(su)001:12713: byas te / the tshom ma bcad par rtogs par mi 'gyur ro zhes bka' stsal pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12714: lang ka'i bdag po yul la dgongs pa ni 'di ltar /
NK088(su)001:12716: gang zag gi bsam pa la dgongs pa ni /
NK088(su)001:12717: su zhig sbyin pa'am 'don nam dge ba cha gcig tsam byas pas 'bras bu thob ste /
NK088(su)001:12718: gzhan mi byed pas chog par bsam pa dag dge ba rgya chen po la gzud pa'i ched du /
NK088(su)001:12719: pha rol phyin pa bcu la sogs pa dge ba
NK088(su)001:12720: ji snyed pa'i yon tan gyi basngagasa pa bshad de
NK088(su)001:12721: / phyogs cha gcig gi 'bras bu la sbyor mi nus pa la dgongs te /
NK088(su)001:12722: sbyin pa la dga' ba zhig na sbyin pa bas
NK088(su)001:12723: kyang tshul khrims la sogs pa gzhan dge ba stong
NK088(su)001:12724: 'gyur gyis che bar brjod par mdzad do //
NK088(su)001:12725: mdor kha cig dge ba gang spyod pa de las gzhan dge rtsa che bar brjod pa lta bu'o //
NK088(su)001:12726: lang ka'i bdag po de la ldem po ngag gi mdo ni /
NK088(su)001:12728: zhes pa don gzhan du ldem pas gzhug pa'i thabs la bzhi ste /
NK088(su)001:12729: gzhugs pa la ldem pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12730: mtshan nyid la ldem pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12731: gnyen po la ldem pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12733: lang ka'i bdag po de la sbyor ba ni gang 'di ltar /
NK088(su)001:12734: zhes pa'ang gzhugs pa la ldem pa ni /
NK088(su)001:12735: su zhig don zab mo stong pa nyid la sngangs
NK088(su)001:12736: nas 'bad pa sna tshogs kyi sha rgyu 'bras la
NK088(su)001:12737: zhen pas thang bar rtsol ba dang /
NK088(su)001:12738: su zhig dngos po la kha'i lta ba la mngon
NK088(su)001:12739: par zhen pas dge ba spyod pa dkar po ci'ang
NK088(su)001:12740: mi byed bdag don mthun pa la gzhug pa'i ched
NK088(su)001:12741: du las stong pa la gzhan pa la gang dang
NK088(su)001:12742: gang spyad pa la brgyud pa'i 'bras bu yod pa
NK088(su)001:12743: dang / chos so cog don dam par ma skyes pa la dgongs nas /
NK088(su)001:12744: sdangs bas rtsol ba la chos thams cad la ngo bo yod do zhes mthun par dgongs pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12745: dngos po la zhen pa bzlog pa'i phyir thams cad
NK088(su)001:12746: stong pa nyid do zhes brjod pas 'jug par 'gyur
NK088(su)001:12747: to // lang ka'i bdag po dbye ba ni 'di ltar /
NK088(su)001:12748: zhes pa mtshan nyid gsum du bstan pas gzhug pa'i don ni /
NK088(su)001:12749: su zhig chad par lta ba la mos pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12750: rtag par lta ba la mos pa dag drang ba'i ched du yongs su grub pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12751: gzhan dbang gnyis yod pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12752: kun brtags med la dgongs te rtag pa la gnyis bstan pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12753: chad pa la gcig bstan pa lta bu'o //
NK088(su)001:12754: lang ka'i bdag po zil gyis gnon pa ni /
NK088(su)001:12755: zhes pa gnyen po ldem pa ni /
NK088(su)001:12756: gang zhig 'jig rten na longs spyod dang gzugs byad
NK088(su)001:12757: khyad par du grags pa'i che bas dregs pa dag
NK088(su)001:12759: de bas kyang 'phags pa'i longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku'i
NK088(su)001:12760: mtshan dpe dang gnas dang zhing khams dang longs spyod
NK088(su)001:12762: zil gyis mnan la drang ba'i ched du de bas
NK088(su)001:12763: kyang nga 'phags pas nga rgyal che ba zhum pa'i
NK088(su)001:12764: gnyen por gyur pa la dgongs te /
NK088(su)001:12765: rgyal ba'i zhing dang longs spyod yon tan rgya chen
NK088(su)001:12766: por bshad pas de thob pa la 'jug pa lta
NK088(su)001:12767: bu'o // lang ka'i bdag po bslu ba ni /
NK088(su)001:12768: zhes pa bsgyur ba la ldem pa ni /
NK088(su)001:12769: gang mtshams med pa lta bu la sogs pa log sred kyi spyod pa la dga' brnams la /
NK088(su)001:12770: don zab mo sbas te de kho na nyid dang
NK088(su)001:12771: mthun par spyad pas grol lo zhes pa 'du shes
NK088(su)001:12772: bsgyur ba la zhugs pa'i don du don ril ma
NK088(su)001:12773: skyes pa'i ngang las mi 'gyur ba la chos nyid
NK088(su)001:12774: la dge sdig ma grub pa la dgongs te /
NK088(su)001:12775: byang chub bsgrub pa'i rgyu yang dag pa ma yin
NK088(su)001:12776: pa'i mtshams med pa lnga spyad pas kyang 'grub par
NK088(su)001:12778: de yang gsang ba pas log sred can gyi dam
NK088(su)001:12779: tshig dang mthun par bka' stsal pas bsgyur bas bshad
NK088(su)001:12781: lang ka'i bdag po de la mthun 'jug sbyor ba'i lung ni /
NK088(su)001:12782: zhes pa la sogs pa gang gdul bya dang mthun
NK088(su)001:12783: par yang dag pa'i don la bkod pa'i bka' sgro
NK088(su)001:12785: nang ris pa bzhi ste rnam grangs bstan pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12786: lang ka'i bdag po 'di la rang rkyen gnyer gyi lung ni /
NK088(su)001:12787: zhes pa gdul bya su zhig la de nyid kyi bsam pa gang la mos pa ltar /
NK088(su)001:12788: de dang 'tshams par de'i cha rkyen ston par byed pa'i bka'o //
NK088(su)001:12790: gdul bya pha rol gyi dngos po dbang du bya
NK088(su)001:12791: ba'i thabs kyis pha rol dang bdag gi spyod pa
NK088(su)001:12792: bsres te / gcig tu spyad pas 'du shes mthar
NK088(su)001:12793: las kyi skyon bgrangs pa la sogs kyis sems bsgyur
NK088(su)001:12794: bsres te / ba'o // cha mthun sbyor ba ni /
NK088(su)001:12795: zhes pa pha rol gyi spyod pa kho na ltar
NK088(su)001:12796: bdag kyang spyad nas yang dag pa theg pa la
NK088(su)001:12797: 'dren pa'o // gdams ngag nan tan gyi lung ni /
NK088(su)001:12798: zhes pa gdul bya gang zhig la gang bstan pa
NK088(su)001:12799: de nyid shin tu bzang la phangs pa bsgom pa
NK088(su)001:12800: la brnag par bya ba la gdams de bas su
NK088(su)001:12802: 'o na rgyu'i theg pa de ltar don spyod pas
NK088(su)001:12803: gsang sngags kyi thabs dang khyad par med do bar
NK088(su)001:12804: dogs pa la / de dag ni lus ngag gis ched du spyod pa la /
NK088(su)001:12805: gsang sngags dam pa ni thabs su ma gyur pa
NK088(su)001:12806: med pas ril mdzad spyod la ched du cha re
NK088(su)001:12807: nas bya ba bral ba'i phyir bskrun du med do
NK088(su)001:12808: // de bas na spyod pa la khyad par che'o //
NK088(su)001:12809: lang ka'i bdag po don dam nges pa'i lung ni 'di lta ste /
NK088(su)001:12810: zhes pa chos ji bzhin pa'i don sgro skur med
NK088(su)001:12811: par ston pa'i don nye bar bstan pa la skabs
NK088(su)001:12813: lang ka'i bdag po de la dgos pa gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:12815: dngos po gang snang ba 'di dag gi mtshan nyid
NK088(su)001:12816: rig par bya ba'i ched du so sor rtog pa'i
NK088(su)001:12817: shes rab kyis gzhal te dpyad bsam pas don rnyed
NK088(su)001:12819: 'dir yang gtan tshigs kyis gzhal ba byas pas go
NK088(su)001:12820: bar gyur pa'i gtan tshigs des na don ji lta
NK088(su)001:12821: bar mthong ba'o // nges pa ni 'di ltar gang la /
NK088(su)001:12822: zhes pa don ma nor ba nyid ni shes bya'i dngos gzhi bshad pa ltar brtags te /
NK088(su)001:12823: snod du rung bar byas pas blo la nges pa'i gdeng chud pa'i don mi 'gyur ba'o //
NK088(su)001:12825: zhes pa mtshon pa'i ming dang tshig ji snyed pas
NK088(su)001:12826: brjod par bya ba'i don gyi ngo bo nyid do
NK088(su)001:12828: zhes pa su zhig la dri ba'i don gyi dngos
NK088(su)001:12829: po zhig gang zag gang gis thabs te gang dang
NK088(su)001:12830: gang du 'gal ba'i tshig blo la blangs te brtags
NK088(su)001:12831: pa'o gal du gtan nas dri ba'o //
NK088(su)001:12832: lang ka'i bdag po zhes pa sgra bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:12833: lang ka'i bdag po de la rtsa ba gsum gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:12834: zhes pa la sogs pa shes bya de nyid kyi phyir ming 'grub ste rnam grangs gsum mo //
NK088(su)001:12835: lang ka'i bdag po de la blo'i rtsa ba ni /
NK088(su)001:12836: zhes pa 'di ltar ye ji bzhin pa ni ma skyes pa'i dbyings so //
NK088(su)001:12837: de bzhin nyid ni de la blo gnas pa'i tshul de mi rtog nyid spyi dang bye brag go //
NK088(su)001:12838: ma skyes pa bsgom pa'i ngang la /
NK088(su)001:12839: blo'i bying rtog la sogs pa'i dbang du mi 'gyur ba ni zhi gnas kyi mchog go //
NK088(su)001:12840: lang ka'i bdag po gros kyi rtsa ba ni /
NK088(su)001:12841: zhes pa shes bya mchog gi dngos gzhi dus dang
NK088(su)001:12842: skabs ma 'dres pa las dang mtshan nyid ma rmongs
NK088(su)001:12843: pa nyid la sel bar nus pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12844: ril du gsal bar mkhyen pa'i lhag mthong gi ngo bo nyid do //
NK088(su)001:12845: lang ka'i bdag po thabs kyi rtsa ba ni /
NK088(su)001:12846: zhes pa byang chub kyi spyod pa rgya mtsho bdag
NK088(su)001:12847: gzhan don du spyod la mi dmigs pas 'ching bar
NK088(su)001:12848: ma gyur pa gang yin pa de nyid zung du
NK088(su)001:12849: 'brel ba'o // lang ka'i bdag po de dag ni zhes pa sgra bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:12850: sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa 'dus pa'i mdo chen po las /
NK088(su)001:12851: bkod pa rnam par 'grel pa'i le'u zhes pa le'u'i mtshan te /
NK088(su)001:12852: rgyu'i bstan pa'i lde'u mig gsum gyis 'grel pa'i don bstan pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:12853: bzhi bcu lnga pa 'grel pa'o ////gsang sngags kyi lde'u mig bshad pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:12854: de nas yang lang ka'i mnga' bdag byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po des /
NK088(su)001:12855: zhes pa la sogs pa sdud pa pos thub pa rigs kyi 'jug sgo dang /
NK088(su)001:12856: grub pa lung gi gsang sgo gnyis lde'u mig cha mthun par dris pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12858: lang ka'i bdag po sgo gnyis ni /
NK088(su)001:12859: zhes pa thabs kyi sbyor sgo dang /
NK088(su)001:12862: phyi nang thun mong gi yan lag drug /mdo bzhi /
NK088(su)001:12864: gang 'di ltar yan lag drug ni 'di lta ste /
NK088(su)001:12865: zhes pa de nyid nye bar bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:12872: khrus dang gtsang sbra la sogs pa spyod pa gtsor
NK088(su)001:12873: gyur pas bya ba las kyi rgyud yin pa'i phyir
NK088(su)001:12874: dang / gong 'og gnyis ka'i thabs la brten nas
NK088(su)001:12875: grub pa mthar phyin thabs kyi rgyud yin pa'i phyir
NK088(su)001:12876: dang / dang / ting nge 'dzin gtsor spyod pas zhi gnas sbyor ba'i rgyud yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK088(su)001:12877: blang dor med pa'i spyod pas ji ltar 'dul bar
NK088(su)001:12878: mdzad pas mthun 'jug spyod pa'i rgyud yin pa'i phyir
NK088(su)001:12879: dang / mnyam pa'i don ji lta ba nyid la
NK088(su)001:12880: 'ching ba bral bas spyod pa ched du byar med
NK088(su)001:12881: pas rnam grol rig pa'i rgyud yin pa'i phyir dang
NK088(su)001:12882: dang / / ril 'bras bu'i ngo bo la 'phral
NK088(su)001:12883: du btsal du med par lhun gyis grub pas bya
NK088(su)001:12884: bral rdzogs pa'i rgyud yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:12885: de ltar phyi nang gnyis ka gcig tu brtsis pas
NK088(su)001:12886: drug tu langs pas thun mong gi yan lag drug
NK088(su)001:12887: tu 'gyur ba'o // lang ka'i bdag po yan lag
NK088(su)001:12888: drug po 'di dag /ces pa de shes par byed
NK088(su)001:12889: tu 'gyur ba'o // pa ni / re re'ang skol mdo bcu gnyis dang /
NK088(su)001:12890: 'chad pa'i thabs drug gis gsal bar ston pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12893: zhes pa grangs nye bar bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:12896: nges pa rnyed pa'i thabs thos pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12897: bsam pa'i shes rab don dpyod pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12898: don la bsgom pa'i shes rab ting nge 'dzin gyi yul dang /
NK088(su)001:12900: phrin las kyis bdag gzhan don la sbyor ba dang /
NK088(su)001:12903: rig 'dzin gyi sa rten pa'i gzhi dang /
NK088(su)001:12904: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi sa dang /
NK088(su)001:12906: 'o na rdzogs pa'i yan lag skol mdo bcu gnyis
NK088(su)001:12907: kyis 'grel par mi rigs pas 'gal lo zhe na
NK088(su)001:12908: / bya ba dang bral ba'i skol mdo ni /
NK088(su)001:12910: bsrung mtshams dang bral ba'i dam tshig la sogs pa
NK088(su)001:12911: tshang bas gang yang spang bya min pa'i phyir mi
NK088(su)001:12912: 'gal te / 'on kyang sgra mthun pa las don
NK088(su)001:12913: ni skol mdo bcu gnyis kyi grangs phrag drug tu
NK088(su)001:12914: 'gal te / 'gyur te / khyad par can du 'grel to //
NK088(su)001:12915: yang bshad lugs kyi yan lag ston pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:12921: gleng gsum bslang ba drug dang /
NK088(su)001:12923: bshad thabs kyi don bcu drug cu dang /
NK088(su)001:12924: don nges pa'i bye brag gdul bya rnam bzhi la sogs nyi shu phrag drug pa bcu gnyis dang /
NK088(su)001:12925: yang dag pa'i don la sbyor ba bdag gzhan don drug cu rtsa gcig rgyud drug ka brtsi go //
NK088(su)001:12926: lang ka'i bdag po 'di dag ni /
NK088(su)001:12927: zhes pa phyi nang gi rgyud drug re re'ang yan
NK088(su)001:12928: lag 'di drug dang ldan pas sgra thun mong du
NK088(su)001:12929: 'jal bar bya'o // sdud pa po la bos nas bshad pa dag ni /
NK088(su)001:12930: rtogs par byed pa'i thabs su gyur pas yan lag ste /
NK088(su)001:12931: bshad pa'i sgo gnyis po yan lag de rnams kyis gsal bar byed cing 'grel pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12932: de dag rgyas par le'u re res 'chad par 'gyur ro //
NK088(su)001:12933: lang ka'i bdag po de la mdo gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:12934: zhes pa don bsdu na bzhi ste /
NK088(su)001:12935: yo ga phyi nang gi rang gzhung ngos nas drug
NK088(su)001:12936: tsho dngos po rnams mtshan ma gnyis med pa'i chos
NK088(su)001:12937: nyid rgyu rkyen dang bral bas dngos gzhi med par
NK088(su)001:12938: bstan pa dang / de la blang dor bzang ngan bral ba dang /
NK088(su)001:12939: ye ma bslad ma bcos pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12940: phral du byar med par 'chad pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12942: de dag ni gzhan gyi skye ba med /
NK088(su)001:12943: ces pa yo ga phyi nang gi mdo bzhi po ni /
NK088(su)001:12944: rgyu'i theg pa don dam pa 'ba' zhig la dngos gzhi med pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12947: bsgrub tu med par smra ba dang /
NK088(su)001:12948: che ba'i khyad par ma 'dres pa ste /
NK088(su)001:12949: gzhi bden pa phyogs gcig pa dang dbyer med pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:12950: de bas na don gyi gzhi nas khyad par che'o //
NK088(su)001:12951: dbu ma'i slob dpon +aar+ya de ba nyid kyi man ngag las /
NK088(su)001:12952: gcig dang du ma rten 'brel gyis //
NK088(su)001:12953: bral ba'i ma skyes stong lta ba //
NK088(su)001:12954: bems po'i nang na de la ngas //
NK088(su)001:12955: bems po'i mchog tu smra ba min //
NK088(su)001:12956: rgyu yi bgrod pa'i kun tu 'od //
NK088(su)001:12957: thabs chen lam gyi cho sku ste //
NK088(su)001:12958: yang dag rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas la //
NK088(su)001:12959: rgya mtsho'i rlabs bzhin shugs kyis 'char //
NK088(su)001:12961: smon lam stobs la rag ma lus //
NK088(su)001:12963: che ba'i khyad par gsal bar yid ches so //
NK088(su)001:12966: zhes pa rang bzhin lam dang grub pa ni /
NK088(su)001:12967: gzhir gyur pa'i grangs te sangs rgyas dang sems can gyis rtogs rung ma rtogs rung /
NK088(su)001:12968: gsang sngags ji bzhin pa'i don nyid bstan pa dang /
NK088(su)001:12969: de'i don ji lta bas thag chod pa'i gdeng mi 'gyur ba dang /
NK088(su)001:12970: mngon du gyur pas bya ba mthar phyin pa gsum mo //
NK088(su)001:12971: sdud pa po la bos nas bshad pa ni /
NK088(su)001:12972: chos ril gyi rtsa ba ste des rtogs par byed pa'o //
NK088(su)001:12973: bsdu ba rnam par 'grel pa'i le'u zhes pa /
NK088(su)001:12974: gsang sngags kyi don bstan pa ril gyi don bsdus
NK088(su)001:12975: pa lde'u mig gsum gyis 'byed pa ston pa le'u
NK088(su)001:12976: ni mtshan no // bzhi bcu drug pa 'grel pa'o ////de nas yang gsang ba'i bdag pos /
NK088(su)001:12977: lang ka'i bdag po la bos te smras pa /
NK088(su)001:12979: ston pas sdud pa po la bos nas de dag
NK088(su)001:12980: las bshad pa rnams las 'dir thabs kyi sbyor sgo
NK088(su)001:12981: las khyad par du nges pa'i gsang sgo gsang sngags
NK088(su)001:12982: nang pa'i lde'u mig 'byed tshul nye bar bstan pa
NK088(su)001:12984: zhes pa rgyal ba kun gyi thugs kyi brnag pa'i don 'byung ba'i sgo la /
NK088(su)001:12985: lde'u mig yan lag drug dang mdo bzhi dang rtsa ba gsum ste /
NK088(su)001:12986: gsum gyis 'byed pa'i thabs kyi rtogs pa gsum mo //
NK088(su)001:12987: 'byed pa rgyu dang rtsa ba dang //
NK088(su)001:12988: zhes pa gsang don phye 'byed pa bas ngo shes par byed pa la yang yan lag drug ste /
NK088(su)001:12989: rgyu 'byung ba'i rgyu gleng gzhi dang /
NK088(su)001:12990: brjod pa'i gzhi rkyen gleng bslang ba dang /
NK088(su)001:12991: rtsod pa bzlog pa'i dgos 'brel bzhi dang /
NK088(su)001:12992: don byed pas 'dren par nges pa bzhi dang /
NK088(su)001:12993: bdag gzhan gyi don drug cu rtsa gcig gis yang
NK088(su)001:12994: dag pa la sbyor bas drug tshang rdzogs pa ba'o
NK088(su)001:12995: // de ni 'di gcig pur ma yin te /
NK088(su)001:12996: bstan pa'i gsang sngags brjod 'byung kun la 'jug go //
NK088(su)001:12997: rgyu gzhi gang 'byung ched phyir ni //
NK088(su)001:12999: rgyu gleng gzhi phun sum tshogs pa la phye ba gsum ste /
NK088(su)001:13000: ru dra'i dngos po 'jig rten du byung ba 'dul ba'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:13001: gdul bya sngon gyi gleng gzhi dang /
NK088(su)001:13002: gang bstan pa gsang sngags kyi dngos po 'byung ba'i dgos ched yod pas smos pa'i ngo bo ni /
NK088(su)001:13003: byin rlabs 'byung ba'i gleng gzhi'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:13004: gtan tshigs byung khung gi gleng gzhi dang /
NK088(su)001:13005: byin brlabs brgyud pa'i phyir lung bstan brgyud pa'i gleng gazhi'o //
NK088(su)001:13006: rtsa ba yan lag gang dag gis //
NK088(su)001:13007: zhes pa gleng bslang ba brjod pa'i rtsa ba la yan lag gis dbye ba gsum ste /
NK088(su)001:13008: ston pa mdun bsu ba ni 'khor don la spro ba bskyed pa'i phyir nas gleng bslang ba dang /
NK088(su)001:13009: 'khor gyis gus pas ston pas gsungs pa don ma
NK088(su)001:13010: rig pa'i the tshom dri ba dris nas gleng bslang
NK088(su)001:13011: ba dang / ston pas gsung ba'i gnas skabs las skabs glo glor gleng langs pa'o //
NK088(su)001:13012: 'brel ba'i yan lag rnam pa bzhi //
NK088(su)001:13013: zhes pa la dgos 'brel bzhi ni /
NK088(su)001:13014: yang na ston pa'o rjod byed bstan pa tshig dang yi ge'o dang /
NK088(su)001:13018: de la 'brel ba dang dgos pa la gnyis gnyis te /
NK088(su)001:13020: thabs dang thabs las byung ba ste /
NK088(su)001:13021: dgos pa dgos pa'i dgos par phye bas grangs bzhir 'dren pa'o //
NK088(su)001:13022: de la brjod bya ni rgyud kyi don te /
NK088(su)001:13024: sbas pa'i don mtshon 'byung ba'i rigs //
NK088(su)001:13025: ma mthong rnams la bstan par bshad //
NK088(su)001:13027: rjod byed phyag na rdo rjes 'chad pa'i skyes bu nyid do //
NK088(su)001:13029: thabs dang thabs las byung ba dang rgyu dang 'bras bu'i tshul te /
NK088(su)001:13030: ston pa kun tu bzang pos gsang ba pa la dbang bskur nas /
NK088(su)001:13031: phyag na rdo rjes lag tu rgya gram babs pa'i
NK088(su)001:13032: 'khor lo bskor te 'khor 'dus pa phal mo che
NK088(su)001:13034: gsang ba'i bdag po ni rdo rje sems dpa'i thugs
NK088(su)001:13035: de bzhin nyid las skyes pas bcom ldan 'das kyi
NK088(su)001:13037: dgos pa ni lam rnams dang de'i cha rkyen rnams te dang du blang ba'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:13038: dgos pa'i dgos pa ni gsang sngags ji bzhin pa
NK088(su)001:13039: sems kyi dkyil 'khor 'od gsal ba nyid mngon du
NK088(su)001:13040: gyur pa ste / dgos pas don gnyer ba'i sgo don yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:13042: zhes pa la sogs pa 'bru gnyer gyi don gang phyir smra brjod tshig gi /
NK088(su)001:13043: yan du 'dren pas de'i don la 'dren pa'o //
NK088(su)001:13044: gang zhes pa brjod bya ji snyed pa'o //
NK088(su)001:13045: bsdus pa'i skabs 'dir rnam pa bcu'o //
NK088(su)001:13046: bshad pa'i yan lag bcu ni /
NK088(su)001:13048: don gyi tshoms sa gcod kyis dbye ba dang /
NK088(su)001:13049: spyi don sdud pa'i tshig gis khog dbub pa dang /
NK088(su)001:13050: gong 'og gi le'u mtshams 'byor bas bya ba dang /
NK088(su)001:13051: rang rkyen gnyer gyis 'bru gzhom pa dang /
NK088(su)001:13052: ldem dgongs man ngag gi tshig gis mi 'tshams pa 'tshams par bshad pa dang /
NK088(su)001:13053: gtar ka gegs sel gyi tshig gis the tshom bcad pa dang /
NK088(su)001:13054: tshad ma bka' gzhung gi tshig ma bslad pas yid ches shing gdeng rnyed par bya ba dang /
NK088(su)001:13056: mtha' mthun pa dang mi mthun pa nye bar sbyar
NK088(su)001:13057: bas yid ches shing go sla bar bya ba dang
NK088(su)001:13058: / bsnol mtshams 'phen sdud kyi tshig gis gong 'og gi 'brel brtsi zhing 'khrugs bsdeb pa'o //
NK088(su)001:13059: des mtshon pa'i dpe ni gsal bar byed pa ste /
NK088(su)001:13060: khyung nam mkha' la lding ba lta bu dang /
NK088(su)001:13061: stag gi mchongs pa lta bu dang /
NK088(su)001:13062: seng ge'i mchongs pa lta bu dang /
NK088(su)001:13064: ru sbal gyi 'gros lta bu dang /
NK088(su)001:13065: gna' phrug brag la 'dzegs pa lta bu dang /
NK088(su)001:13066: glag gzan la 'jums pa lta bu dang /
NK088(su)001:13067: dus kyi 'brug dang char lta bu dang /
NK088(su)001:13069: thags dang seng phrug rtsal sbyang ba lta bu'o //
NK088(su)001:13070: des mtshon la rtogs par bya ba ni dpe sgron ma ni tshig go //
NK088(su)001:13071: mun pa ni don mi mthong ba'o //
NK088(su)001:13072: rdzas 'tshol ba ni gser dang 'dra ba'i brjod pa sbyar ba ni don nges par mthong ba'o //
NK088(su)001:13074: bshad pa dang 'chad pa'i 'grel lugs rnams kyang 'dis khong mjal du bya'o //
NK088(su)001:13075: nges pa bzhi bzhi bzhir sbyar bas //
NK088(su)001:13076: bcu gnyis yan lag bzhir kun snang //
NK088(su)001:13077: zhes pa la nges pa'i don rnyed pa'i bye brag gi yan lag la nges pa zhes bya'o ni /
NK088(su)001:13080: chos don bzhi gang du dgongs gar nges pa ngo bo dmigs bzung ba dang /
NK088(su)001:13081: bzhi gsum la drug bcu gnyis gnyis so //
NK088(su)001:13083: de'i don bzhi ste yan lag bzhi tsho ma 'dres par cha rer 'chad pa'ang snang ngo //
NK088(su)001:13084: sbyor ba bzhi pa lnga gnyis bzhi /
NK088(su)001:13085: yan lag lngar snang de ltar sbyor //
NK088(su)001:13086: zhes pa nges pa'i thabs chen pos lam dam pa la nges par sbyor ba'i yan lag ni /
NK088(su)001:13088: rgyu shes pa sogs mtshan nyid kyi yan lag bzhi dang /
NK088(su)001:13089: de 'brel de dgos sogs dgos 'brel bzhi dang /
NK088(su)001:13090: thos chung goms sogs dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa'i yan lag bzhi tsho gnyis dang /
NK088(su)001:13091: sems 'jug pa'i rim pa bzhi dang /
NK088(su)001:13092: bsnyen bsgrub bsnyen pa nye bsnyen bzhi dang /
NK088(su)001:13093: de'i don shes bya de bzhin mnyam gyur sogs bzhi ni bdag don no //
NK088(su)001:13094: de ltar brtsis pa'i grangs ni bzhi tsho brgyad do //
NK088(su)001:13095: gzhan don mdzad pa cho 'phrul bzhi dang /
NK088(su)001:13097: sngags kyi rang bzhin lnga ste phrag gnyis dang /
NK088(su)001:13098: phrin las zhi ba sogs rnam bzhi dang /
NK088(su)001:13099: thabs kyi yan lag lnga dang /
NK088(su)001:13100: des don la sbyor thabs lnga'o //
NK088(su)001:13101: rtog 'jug drug cu gcig thabs nas //
NK088(su)001:13102: yan lag drug tu rdzogs pa'o //
NK088(su)001:13103: zhes pa nges par don gnyis la 'jug pas sbyor ba la bzhi tsho bcu dang /
NK088(su)001:13104: lnga phrag bzhi rtsa ba nyid dang /
NK088(su)001:13105: grangs drug cu rtsa gcig tu bstan pa'i thabs gnyis yan chad nas /
NK088(su)001:13106: gleng gzhi man chad 'chad pa'i yan lag drug po rnams bshad pa 'dir tshangs par 'dus pa ste /
NK088(su)001:13107: rdzogs pa'o zhes de ltar drug pa spyir brgya dgu
NK088(su)001:13108: bcu rtsa gcig tu nyams su 'gyur sbyor ba'i re
NK088(su)001:13109: gcig ro // gleng gzhi gnyis gsum /
NK088(su)001:13113: nges pa bcu phrag gnyis kyis rdzogs pa'o //
NK088(su)001:13114: lang ka'i bdag po gang 'dir yang yan lag drug ni 'di lta ste /
NK088(su)001:13115: zhes pa sdud pa po la bos nas /
NK088(su)001:13116: yan lag drug brnan nas ston pa ni re re nas rgyas par bstan pa'i phyir smos te /
NK088(su)001:13117: rnam grangs bstan pa sgra bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:13118: lang ka'i bdag po de la rgyu'i yan lag ni /
NK088(su)001:13119: gang 'byung ba'i rgyur gyur pa ste /
NK088(su)001:13120: zhes pa gleng gzhi bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:13121: bstan pa'i dngos po snang ba'i rgyu yin pa'i phyir ming nges par 'grub bo //
NK088(su)001:13122: de'i ngo bo bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:13129: 'di ni yang gsum du phye ba las /
NK088(su)001:13130: gtan tshigs 'byung khungs rgyu'i gleng gzhir gyur pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:13131: lang ka'i bdag po de yang 'di ltar /
NK088(su)001:13132: 'di skad bdag gis thos pa de kho na nyid nges par snang ba'i dus gcig na /
NK088(su)001:13133: zhes pa sdud pa po la bos nas /
NK088(su)001:13134: gsang ba'i bdag po 'chad pa'i skyes bu nyid /
NK088(su)001:13135: 'di skabs kyi sdud pa por gyur pas 'di skad
NK088(su)001:13136: nye bar bstan pa'i don chos kyi sku la bdag
NK088(su)001:13137: gis thos pa sdud pa ni /
NK088(su)001:13138: chos ji de kho na nyid bzhin pa nyid du
NK088(su)001:13139: rig pa'i nges par gsung gis rig pa la mi
NK088(su)001:13140: 'gyur bar snang ba'i dus gcig na shar ba'i tshe
NK088(su)001:13141: / zhes pa rgyu'i sdud pa dang dus phun sum tshogs pa'o //
NK088(su)001:13143: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs /
NK088(su)001:13144: zhes pa la sogs pa mthar thug pa'i ye shes chen po gnyis med pa ni /
NK088(su)001:13145: bya ba thams cad mdzad bcom pa'i ye shes yon
NK088(su)001:13146: tan thams cad ldan par bzhugs kyang ngo bo yongs
NK088(su)001:13148: ye ji bzhin pa de bzhin nyid du phyin pa
NK088(su)001:13149: gshegs pa med par son pa'i thams cad ngo bo
NK088(su)001:13150: thugs mi g.yo ba chen por bzhugs pa dang /
NK088(su)001:13151: spang bya'i 'tshe ba ril ma spangs bral ba dgra bcom chen por bzhugs pa dang /
NK088(su)001:13152: yon tan ji snyed pa btsal ba med par yang
NK088(su)001:13153: dag par mngon du byas pas gang la'ang rag lus
NK088(su)001:13154: pa med pa rdzogs pa dang /
NK088(su)001:13155: sa'i zhen pa mtha'i ril bral sangs pa'i ye shes kun tu rgyas bdal ba dang /
NK088(su)001:13156: de'i ngo bor ye zhugs pa la tha dad dang ltos pa'i zla ba dang bral bas /
NK088(su)001:13157: de nyid kyi btag pa med pa tha snyad bral ba dang /
NK088(su)001:13158: ngo bo bstan du med par glo bur gyi ming
NK088(su)001:13159: bla dwags thams cad las 'das pa rnams ma spangs
NK088(su)001:13160: bral ba dang / nam mkha' la sogs phyin pa
NK088(su)001:13161: med par kun tu bdal ba 'di ye shes ril
NK088(su)001:13162: gyi dngos gzhi bdag nyid yin par bstan pa dang
NK088(su)001:13163: bral ba dang / / dbyibs mngon sum sogs dang
NK088(su)001:13164: kha dog gi sku rnams ma bkol mi ldan pas
NK088(su)001:13165: dpe bskrun du med pa dang /
NK088(su)001:13166: dngos po gnyis pa yongs su rdzogs pa ril gyi
NK088(su)001:13167: bdag nyid du zhugs pa'i chos bcu dang ldan pa
NK088(su)001:13168: ni / ston pa phun sum tshogs pa chos kyi sku'o //
NK088(su)001:13170: sa yongs su khyab pa'i gnas rdzogs pa spyir chibs zhes bya ba /
NK088(su)001:13171: zhes pa la sogs pa thams cad kyang ma bkol
NK088(su)001:13172: bar sa yongs su khyab bdal ba'i gzhi rgyu 'bras
NK088(su)001:13173: kun lhun gyis rdzogs pas sa'i rim pa'i spyir chibs
NK088(su)001:13175: mnyam pa nam mkha'i chen po mu mtha' med pa
NK088(su)001:13176: la gdung ba ngang gis bral ba'i bde ba chen
NK088(su)001:13177: po klong / dngos po thams cad gnyis pa ril
NK088(su)001:13178: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas par sar gsal
NK088(su)001:13179: bar mkhyen rdzogs pas thams cad kyi 'byung gnas bkod
NK088(su)001:13180: pa chos nyid kyi ngang rgyal ba ril gyi bzhugs
NK088(su)001:13181: gnas kun gzhi chen pos khyab ye 'byams pas /
NK088(su)001:13182: rgya phyogs bcur ris yongs su med par mnyam pas
NK088(su)001:13183: gsal zhing chos nyid kyi nam mkha' zad mtha' med
NK088(su)001:13184: pa la / tshig gis brjod du med bstan par dka' ba /
NK088(su)001:13185: rgyan rang byung gis ye shes kyi nyi ma 'char
NK088(su)001:13186: nub med par gsal ba tshad dpag tu med pa
NK088(su)001:13187: rang shar ba gsal ba la /
NK088(su)001:13188: yod med rtag chad mtha' dang dbus med la sogs
NK088(su)001:13189: pa 'das pas dbu ma'i tha snyad med pa rgya
NK088(su)001:13190: mnyam nyid / srog chags ldem bu yan chod du
NK088(su)001:13191: snums tshabs che chung med par gyur pa'i bdal khyab
NK088(su)001:13192: mnyam nyid / mtshan ni / gnas bdal khyab chen po'i zhing khams so //
NK088(su)001:13193: ston pa'i mtshan nyid ji lta bu zhe na /
NK088(su)001:13194: gang du'ang mi gnas gnas pa chen po /
NK088(su)001:13197: gang du'ang mi gnas mtha' gang gis kyang ma reg pas 'di 'drar med la /
NK088(su)001:13198: thams cad kyi dngos por yang shar gnas pa chen po ba /
NK088(su)001:13199: mtshan nyid gang dang yang lhan mi gcig gang la'ang ma chags la /
NK088(su)001:13200: rim dang mi phyed pa chen chags pa'i bdag nyid po /
NK088(su)001:13201: ched du bya ba ci yang mi mdzad med par
NK088(su)001:13202: phrin las thams cad par bzhugs mdzad pa lhun grub
NK088(su)001:13203: pas 'gro don rgyun chad med par mdzad pa'o //
NK088(su)001:13204: rgyu rkyen mi skye bral bas mi 'gag 'pho 'gyur med pa /
NK088(su)001:13205: phyin ci log dang yang dag pa'i 'ching ba thams cad bcad rnam grol pa /
NK088(su)001:13206: mtha' spros pa dri ma dang bral rnam dag ba /
NK088(su)001:13207: dngos po ma yin ther zug med par cir yang 'byung zhing nam mkha'i rang bzhin gsal ba /
NK088(su)001:13208: ye ma bcos legs pa chen po byed pa po
NK088(su)001:13209: bral bas ma byas ma btsal ma bcos pa'i ye
NK088(su)001:13211: smad 'khor ba mi spong skyon du mi 'dor ba
NK088(su)001:13212: de nyid chos kyi sku nyid du ye bdal khyab
NK088(su)001:13214: chags sdang dug gsum ma rig pa'i nad ma spang
NK088(su)001:13215: bar mi spong sku gsum gyi bdud rtsir mdzad pas
NK088(su)001:13216: sman pa chen po 'tsho mdzad chen po /
NK088(su)001:13217: spyod yul ka nas dag pa cir yang mi dmigs
NK088(su)001:13218: la rnam pa'i 'dzin pa ye nas bral bzhin du
NK088(su)001:13219: de dag tu snang ba'i 'byung gnas su gyur pa
NK088(su)001:13220: / dmigs pa kun 'byung ngo bo brjod du med
NK088(su)001:13221: par tshig gi lam chad smra brjod pa kun 'byung
NK088(su)001:13222: lhun gyis grub pas rang 'char ba /
NK088(su)001:13223: mtha' gang gis kyang gang dang ma 'dres ma bsgos
NK088(su)001:13224: par tha snyad kyi dngos gzhir ril gcig tu yongs
NK088(su)001:13225: su 'dus pa / dus kun nas kun tu dang
NK088(su)001:13226: skabs snga phyir mtha'i dri ma'i rdul bral ba'i ngang
NK088(su)001:13227: bzang po mchog tu gyur pa /
NK088(su)001:13228: dus gsum du mi nus mi rlag pa'i tog rgyal mtshan chen por bzhugs pa ste /
NK088(su)001:13229: 'dir tsho gnyis dang mtshan nyid lnga'am gsum dang ldan par bzhugs so //
NK088(su)001:13231: ye shes brjod kyis mi lang ba'i yang brjod kyis mi lang ba'i /
NK088(su)001:13232: zhes pa la sogs pa ye shes chen po nyid
NK088(su)001:13233: kyang brjod du med pa'i rang snang ba'i dag pa'i
NK088(su)001:13234: bye brag grangs las 'das pa'ang brjod du med pa
NK088(su)001:13235: dang / thog ma dang tha ma 'du 'bral med
NK088(su)001:13236: par lhun gyis rdzogs la ma 'dres pas gcig dang
NK088(su)001:13237: du ma las grol ba'i dngos po med pa'i ngo
NK088(su)001:13238: bo bzhugs thabs su gyur pa'o //
NK088(su)001:13239: gnas kyi don gyis sa bcu pa spyir chibs thob pas /
NK088(su)001:13240: chos sku las nyan pa'i 'khor du gyur par rigs so //
NK088(su)001:13241: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku'i gleng gzhi bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:13242: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid kyi tshig 'di skad du /
NK088(su)001:13243: mthun 'jug skabs su thos pa'i dus gcig na /
NK088(su)001:13244: zhes pa bstan pa'i gsang sngags bstan pa'i don brjod pa dang 'dra ba'i phyir sgra 'di skad du /
NK088(su)001:13245: thabs mang pos ji ltar mthun pa 'dul ba'i don
NK088(su)001:13246: sdud pa pos gsang bas longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku
NK088(su)001:13247: la dgongs pa'am / sku'i bstan par thos pa'i dus de'i tshe /
NK088(su)001:13248: ston pa nyid ni gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:13249: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bcom ldan 'das gsang ba mchog gi bdag po /
NK088(su)001:13250: zhes pa la sogs pa gzugs sku'i rgyal ba gdul
NK088(su)001:13251: bya la snang ba rigs lnga la sogs ma lus
NK088(su)001:13252: pa'i kun gyi gtso mchog drug pa ston pa po
NK088(su)001:13253: gsang sngags bla na med pa'i mchog gi theg pa'i
NK088(su)001:13254: mnga' bdag / 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das
NK088(su)001:13255: pa la spong len med blang dor mi mnga' par
NK088(su)001:13256: nyid kyi thugs ye shes su ma 'dres la yongs
NK088(su)001:13257: su rdzogs pas byin gyis brlabs kyi yul med par
NK088(su)001:13258: dbang phyug longs spyod pa'i bstan pa dang dngos grub
NK088(su)001:13259: kyi 'dod pa kun 'byung gnas kyang 'phel 'grib mi
NK088(su)001:13260: mnga' bar mi zad mdzod kyi bkod pa ldan pa'o
NK088(su)001:13261: mnga' bdag / // ston pa'i mtshan nyid ni /
NK088(su)001:13262: mtshan dang dpe byad rdzogs pa'i sku mchog che ba
NK088(su)001:13263: kun spyom longs spyod mchog mnga' ba'i che ba mdzad
NK088(su)001:13264: pa / 'khor thams cad kyang ngom par rol ngo mtshar skye ba'i sku'i gzi brjid byin dang /
NK088(su)001:13265: phrin las kyi mdzad thabs skabs su gcod pa'i mtha'
NK088(su)001:13266: yas pas bya ba med par don spyod pas thugs
NK088(su)001:13267: rjes chen pos 'phro ba med par gdul ba'i don
NK088(su)001:13268: la spyod pa'i ston pa de lta bu'i ngo bo'o
NK088(su)001:13270: rmad du byung ba'i don 'di nyid gleng ba'i gnas /
NK088(su)001:13271: tshogs chen po rdzogs pa'i gzhi /
NK088(su)001:13272: rtsal chen po rdzogs pa'i sa /
NK088(su)001:13274: rmad du byung ba'i don 'di nyid gsang sngags kyi
NK088(su)001:13275: theg pa khyad par can dbyings kyi sku dang dgongs
NK088(su)001:13276: pas gleng ba'i ston pa'i bzhugs gnas ni gang zhe
NK088(su)001:13277: na / tshogs rnam gnyis rdzogs pa'i gzhi phyir /
NK088(su)001:13278: bsgrub bya'i mthar lam pa rtsal rdzogs pa'i sa bde ba rnam gnyis la mnga' mdzad pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:13279: de dang can ldan pa'i zhing khams so //
NK088(su)001:13280: gnas gzhi ni 'dul bya'i ngo bo la zhing khams de na gzhal yas khang yod par snang ba'o //
NK088(su)001:13281: 'og min ni chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang rin
NK088(su)001:13282: po che sna tshogs kyi gzhal yas khang mtha' dang
NK088(su)001:13283: dbus med cing / zhes pa la sogs pa rang bzhin dang /
NK088(su)001:13285: gnas kyi 'og min ni chos nyid dang /
NK088(su)001:13286: gzung 'dzin bral ba'i ye shes dang /
NK088(su)001:13287: gzhal yas khang dbang phyug gi gnas so //
NK088(su)001:13288: 'dir gdul bya'i ngo la snang bas gnas kyi 'og
NK088(su)001:13289: min don chos mnyam pa nyid kyi gnas pho brang
NK088(su)001:13290: rgyu ye shes rin po che sna tshogs las byas
NK088(su)001:13291: pa gzhal yas rgya dang mtha' dang dbus med yan
NK088(su)001:13293: ril nang nyid du gyur pa la dbus mtha' bral ba'i ngo bo /
NK088(su)001:13294: gzhal yas khang gi rtse mo spros pa med pa'i
NK088(su)001:13295: rang rtags grwa zur med par kun tu rgya mnyam
NK088(su)001:13296: pa zlum po thams cad du khyab pa'o //
NK088(su)001:13297: 'o na sgo dang dbyibs smos pa la nges par gzung ba med do zhe na /
NK088(su)001:13298: de dag gi don smos pa ste gdul bya'i ngo
NK088(su)001:13299: la dbyibs dang sgo snang zhing tshad med pa ste
NK088(su)001:13300: / dper mi rnams rang rang gi gnas na 'dug
NK088(su)001:13301: pas lung pa'i dbyibs dang phu mda' dang lam sgo
NK088(su)001:13302: / shes kyang / lung pa ril gyis rgya dang dpang tshad 'di tsam zhes ma dmigs pa ltar /
NK088(su)001:13303: 'khor gyi byang chub sems dpas gzhal yas khang mthong
NK088(su)001:13304: nas de na bdag cag chos ston cing 'dug kyang
NK088(su)001:13305: / rgya dang dpang dmigs par mi nus te /
NK088(su)001:13306: gal te dmigs na tshad mi rnyed pa ni byang
NK088(su)001:13307: chub sems dpa' dpal stobs kyis bcom ldan 'das kyi
NK088(su)001:13308: dbu'i gtsug tor bltas pas ma mthong ba bzhin no
NK088(su)001:13309: // rgyan gyi mtshan nyid ji lta bu snyam pa la /
NK088(su)001:13310: rin po che'i rgyal pos rnam par brgyan pa mu tig gi lcang lo dang /
NK088(su)001:13311: zhes pa la sogs pa rin po che 'bar bas kun nas brgyan pa /
NK088(su)001:13312: mu tig gi phreng ba mang por 'khrigs pas phyi nang nas brgyan pa ste /
NK088(su)001:13313: ji snyed pa'i yon tan gyi bdag nyid dang /
NK088(su)001:13314: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i ye shes mnga' ba'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:13315: gzhan yang bden pa gnyis med pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:13316: rin po che'i chun 'phyang pany+tsa re kha'i phyi nang nas brgyan pa dang /
NK088(su)001:13317: dar gyi lda ldi 'phan dang ba dan bla bre
NK088(su)001:13318: la sogs pas phyogs dang mtshams dang steng nas mdzes
NK088(su)001:13319: pas brgyan pa / logs la nyi zla tshes bcu drug pa lta bu dang /
NK088(su)001:13320: tshes brgyad pa lta bu'i 'od kyis gsal btab cing spel mar bkod pa /
NK088(su)001:13321: skar ma che ba dang chung bas rin po che'i rtsig pa'i gzer mgo rnams brgyan pa /
NK088(su)001:13322: dbus kyi phyogs mtshams na ka ba mchog brgyan kyis gdung mgo bteg pa /
NK088(su)001:13323: ka lo'i ka rgyan nyi zlas byas pa /
NK088(su)001:13324: ka ba la rin che sna tshogs kyis brgyan pa las kyang rin po che brgyus pa'i gtsar dang /
NK088(su)001:13326: rin po che'i gdung brgyad snol mar byung bas bar re'u mig tu gsal ba /
NK088(su)001:13327: chos ma skyes pas kun tu khyab pa'i bla bre las rdo rje ma 'dres par byung ba /
NK088(su)001:13328: ye shes chen po cir yang snang la ma nges
NK088(su)001:13329: pas cho 'phrul phyogs ji snyed kun gtams pa dang
NK088(su)001:13330: / gdul bya'i sems bskyed pa'i chos dang sprul pa'i char 'bab pa /
NK088(su)001:13331: gdul bya'i nyon mongs pa'i dgon gdung bsangs nas med cing dag par byed pa /
NK088(su)001:13332: gdul bya'i rgyud la ye shes ji snyed pa'i sgo sngar ma skyes par skyed pa /
NK088(su)001:13333: theg pa chen po gsang sngags kyi chos sgra phyogs kun nas 'byung ba /
NK088(su)001:13334: theg pa chen po ji bzhin pa zla med par 'di don bstan par gleng bslang ba /
NK088(su)001:13335: don tshig tu bstan pa bral zhing /
NK088(su)001:13336: dpe bzhin dang me long ltar /
NK088(su)001:13337: gzhal yas khang gi dbyibs kha dog mthong bas don snang bar gyur pa /
NK088(su)001:13338: gnas mi phyed mi 'gyur ba'i ngo bo shin tu nyams dga' ba /
NK088(su)001:13339: rin po che las byas pa'i rdo rjes phyogs bzhi nas brgyan pa /
NK088(su)001:13340: rgyu rin po che mang po las mngon par grub pa /
NK088(su)001:13341: 'og gser gyi sa gzhi bdal ba /
NK088(su)001:13342: rtsig pa rgyan dang 'og dang ngos kun kyang me long ngam chu shel lam chu dang ba'am /
NK088(su)001:13343: gser shin tu sbyangs pa ltar mnyam zhing snyoms la
NK088(su)001:13344: gsal zhing 'tsher ba las gzhan gyis gzugs brnyan nang
NK088(su)001:13345: du snang ba'o // mnan na nem pa /
NK088(su)001:13349: mtshan nyid rdul med par dang ba /
NK088(su)001:13350: gzhal yas khang rtse mo ldem pa /
NK088(su)001:13351: gdos pa med par mnyen pa /
NK088(su)001:13353: 'di 'dra'i rnam par rtog pa med pa /
NK088(su)001:13355: zhes pa la sogs pa de snyed kyi 'od ma 'dres par byung nas phyogs kun tu khyab pa /
NK088(su)001:13356: gzhal yas khang gi phyi nang mun pa 'od kyis sel ba /
NK088(su)001:13358: steng bum pa'i nang 'khor lo rtsib bzhi las 'od 'bar ba /
NK088(su)001:13359: rdo rje'i mu khyud kyi phreng bas rim pa gnyis su brgyan pa'o //
NK088(su)001:13360: sgo gsum kun tu gsal ba la /
NK088(su)001:13361: pa ti 'od kyi mu tig yongs su ma chad pa /
NK088(su)001:13362: zhes pa la sogs pa phyogs gcig na'ang sgo sum
NK088(su)001:13363: brtsegs la rin po che smug po'i 'od kyis bskor
NK088(su)001:13365: nyi ma dang zla ba kha sbyar sum rgyud sbrel
NK088(su)001:13366: ba zung rer gshibs nas 'od 'bar ba dang ldan
NK088(su)001:13367: pa / sgo'i phyi nang them skas brgyad dang /
NK088(su)001:13368: ya phubs kyi steng na yar rta rkang sgrom dang /
NK088(su)001:13375: khyu mgo la sogs pa'i rta babs dang ldan te /
NK088(su)001:13376: theg pa brgyad kyi rgyu 'bras kyi phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:13377: bden pa bzhi'i phyir gru chad bzhi dang /
NK088(su)001:13378: 'dir bden pa gnyis dbyer med pas bar khyams gsum dang /
NK088(su)001:13379: legs pa'i mdzes pa rgyan gyi sgras bdag nyid kyis brgyad do //
NK088(su)001:13380: ha ra dang ha ra chen pos /
NK088(su)001:13381: zhes pa ye shes rtsig pa'i steng nas mu tig ha ra phyed pa dang rangs pas brgyan pa'o //
NK088(su)001:13382: de la yang chu srin t+wa ra nas bzung ba ste ya phubs su yang rigs so //
NK088(su)001:13383: rin po che'i phreng bas brgyan pa /
NK088(su)001:13384: rtsig pa dang bya 'dab gnyis kyi bar mgul 'khor bar d+r+wa ba gnyis kyis brgyan pa /
NK088(su)001:13385: logs la zar tshags kyis brgyan pa /
NK088(su)001:13386: sgo'i rtse mo g.yas g.yon nas rdo rje rin po ches shin tu mdangs gsal bar byas pa /
NK088(su)001:13387: dril bu g.yer kha 'phyang bas theg pa chen po'i
NK088(su)001:13388: chos ston pa'i sgra grags pa gnyis su med pa'i
NK088(su)001:13389: chos sku chen po'i don mtshon pa snang ba'i gzhi
NK088(su)001:13390: khyad par du legs pa'i rgyan /
NK088(su)001:13391: rdo rje mu khyud ma chad par /
NK088(su)001:13392: zhes pa la sogs pa bshad pa bzhin mu khyud ni lte ba la'o //
NK088(su)001:13393: rdo rje bgreng bu ni lte ba'i rdo rje'i tshul dang /
NK088(su)001:13395: phyi rol du yang d+r+wa bas brgyan pa /
NK088(su)001:13396: ye shes shing sgo'i g.yas g.yon nas skyes pa la tsong tsong gi sbrel ba'i tsong tsong las /
NK088(su)001:13397: rin po che sna tshogs kyi phra min gis brgyan pa las g.yer ka 'phyang ba'o //
NK088(su)001:13398: ye shes kyi chu rgyun g.yas g.yon nas 'bab pa /
NK088(su)001:13399: ril gzung 'dzin bral ba'i ye shes kho na bas
NK088(su)001:13400: phyi rol med de nang du gyur pa ste rgyal
NK088(su)001:13401: ba'i snang ba'o // ston pa'i mtshan nyid ni /
NK088(su)001:13402: gang yang ma 'gag snang ba chen po /
NK088(su)001:13403: zhes pa ston pa kun tu zhal du bzhugs pa /
NK088(su)001:13404: cir yang ma gsung ma brjod par sku dang dgongs
NK088(su)001:13405: pa'i byin rlabs kyis gdul bya'i rig pa la gsang
NK088(su)001:13406: sngags dam par rdzogs par rgya cher bshad pa mjal
NK088(su)001:13407: bar mdzad pa / gang la'ang mi dgongs pa bsam
NK088(su)001:13408: dpyod bral ba la mi g.yo bar ting nge 'dzin
NK088(su)001:13410: mnga' thang yongs su longs spyod gnyis la ril lhun
NK088(su)001:13411: gyis rdzogs pa'i bdag nyid du bzhugs pa'i rgyal po
NK088(su)001:13412: chen po de / 'khor ji lta bu dang ldan zhe na /
NK088(su)001:13413: rdzogs longs spyod pa'i 'khor brjod kyis mi lang ba'i yang brjod kyis mi lang ba 'di lta ste /
NK088(su)001:13414: zhes pa la sogs pa 'khor grangs las 'das pa nye bar bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:13415: phung po lnga nyid rang rig pa gcig dang du
NK088(su)001:13416: ma'i mtha' las grol ba de nyid rtogs pas de
NK088(su)001:13417: nyid du son pas ye shes lnga gsal ba nyid
NK088(su)001:13418: gdul bya la rigs lnga'i skur byung ba ni /
NK088(su)001:13419: rtog pa phung po lnga dag pa'i tshul nas mtshan nges par 'grub pa'o //
NK088(su)001:13420: rnam shes me long ye shes chen po la 'byung 'jug med pa mi bskyod pa dang /
NK088(su)001:13421: tshor ba mnyam pa'i ye shes kyi phyir btang snyoms dang /
NK088(su)001:13422: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes gsal la mi 'dzin
NK088(su)001:13423: pa la 'du shes gsum gyi mtshan ma med pa
NK088(su)001:13424: bral ba dang / bya ba grub pa'i ye shes
NK088(su)001:13425: bdag gzhan gyi dgos pa las mi g.yo ba sems
NK088(su)001:13426: dpa' chen po nyid du 'du byed sems dpa' dag
NK088(su)001:13427: bral ba dang / dang / stong pa nyid kyi
NK088(su)001:13428: ye shes 'byed pa med pa rnam par rig byed
NK088(su)001:13429: ma yin pa'i gzugs dag pa las btag pa'i phyir
NK088(su)001:13430: rtog pa'i mtshan nyid la cha re'ang smos pa'o //
NK088(su)001:13431: de lta bu phung po lnga nyid de'i tshe rnam par mthong ba'i phung po dang /
NK088(su)001:13432: ting nge 'dzin gyi phung po dang /
NK088(su)001:13433: shes rab kyi phung po dang /
NK088(su)001:13434: rnam par grol ba'i phung po dang /
NK088(su)001:13435: tshul khrims kyi phung po lnga'i bdag nyid zag pa med par gsal ba'i rigs lnga'o //
NK088(su)001:13436: shes rab nam mkha' lta bur 'brel ba /
NK088(su)001:13437: zhes pa so so rigs kyi yum dang gnyis su med par bzhugs pa'o //
NK088(su)001:13438: gtso bo dang 'khor gyi tshul du /
NK088(su)001:13439: zhes pa rigs lnga rang rang gi sems dpa'i 'khor ji snyed pa dang /
NK088(su)001:13440: longs spyod chen po'i ston pa dang /
NK088(su)001:13441: rigs lnga kho na ltar longs spyod rdzogs pa'i gtso 'khor du bzhugs pa ste /
NK088(su)001:13442: gnas kyi dgos pas rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor gyis /
NK088(su)001:13443: rdzogs sku la nyan pa'i 'khor de dag go //
NK088(su)001:13444: rgya cher brjod pa ldem dgongs sbyor ba'i tshig 'di skad /
NK088(su)001:13446: rgya cher brjod pa sprul pa'i sku'i bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:13447: ldem dgongs sbyor ba'i can du gsungs pa ji snyed pa'o //
NK088(su)001:13448: bstan pa de yang sdud pa po phyag na rdo
NK088(su)001:13449: rje nyid kyis 'gro ba dkri drang gi thabs su
NK088(su)001:13450: tshig dngos su thos pa'i dus de'i tshe'o //
NK088(su)001:13451: ston pa ni ston pa'i rang bzhin thub pa'i dbang po la sogs pa /
NK088(su)001:13452: cho 'phrul chen po mdzad pa'i phrin las gdul dbang
NK088(su)001:13453: gis ma nges par snang ba'i ci yang snang ba
NK088(su)001:13454: ston pa ji snyed pa'i sku rnams so //
NK088(su)001:13456: bya ba rdzogs pa'i gnas bsod nams gter zhes bya ba /
NK088(su)001:13457: zhes pa la sogs pa phrin las bya ba rdzogs kyi mdzad pa rol pa nyi shu dang /
NK088(su)001:13458: bcu gnyis tshang bar mdzad pa'i gnas sa gnyis pa bsod nams gter gyi sa ste /
NK088(su)001:13459: gdul bya sems nges par skyes pas tshogs lam spyod
NK088(su)001:13460: pa'i 'jig rten zhing khams 'jig rten gyi khams bshad
NK088(su)001:13461: pa ltar bsam las 'das pa dpag tu med pa
NK088(su)001:13462: ni / gnas ji bzhin pa 'jig rten 'di kho na nyid las ma bcos pa /
NK088(su)001:13463: 'khor gdul bya mos pa can zhes bya ba dang ldan pa sha stag gnas pa'i zhing khams so //
NK088(su)001:13466: zhes rigs drug 'khor ba 'dren thar par 'don cing ma rig snang srid pa'i ling tog sel ba /
NK088(su)001:13467: gdung ba nyon mongs pa dang sdug bsngal bral bar mdzad pa /
NK088(su)001:13468: ji ltar 'dul bzhin 'gro don mdzad pa'i gtso mchog
NK088(su)001:13469: shin tu bsgyur dka' ba'ang thabs mkhas ldem dgongs brgyad
NK088(su)001:13470: dang / lung bzhi la sogs pas sgrol ba'i thugs rje chen po can /
NK088(su)001:13471: sprul sku snga phyi 'byung ba rgyun rgyud du mi 'chad par sgron ma snang ba /
NK088(su)001:13472: thugs rje chen po rgyun gyi rtag pa'i mnga' bdag chen po'i skur byung ba'o //
NK088(su)001:13476: tshogs dang sbyor lam pa gnyis grangs las 'das pa'i 'khor rnams dang /
NK088(su)001:13477: dngos su tshig gis ston pa dang rna bas nyan
NK088(su)001:13478: pa ste 'dra tshul du brjod pa ni gdul bya'i
NK088(su)001:13479: snang ba ste / gsung dbyangs yan lag rnam pa
NK088(su)001:13480: bshad pa bsam gyis mi khyab ste bka' stsal pa'i
NK088(su)001:13481: snang ba ste / tshul ril yang / kun rdzob
NK088(su)001:13482: dang don dam pa'i bden pa thams cad bden pa
NK088(su)001:13483: gnyis 'ba' zhig tu chos ston tshul ston pa'o //
NK088(su)001:13484: gnas kyi dgos pas bsod nams gter gyi sa pa ni 'khor du nges pa'o //
NK088(su)001:13485: 'dod pa rang rkyen gyi tshig 'di skad ces pa /
NK088(su)001:13486: gsang ba'i sku'i bstan pa dang /
NK088(su)001:13487: 'dod chags can gyi rkyen du 'dod pa spyod pa'i bstan pa'o //
NK088(su)001:13488: de yang spang du med de don de nyid chos nyid yin pa dang /
NK088(su)001:13489: don 'byin par byed pa la dgongs te /
NK088(su)001:13490: sdud pa po gsang bdag gis seng ge lta bu'i
NK088(su)001:13491: gsung thabs kyi sgo nas brjod pa dang 'dra bar
NK088(su)001:13492: dgongs pa la snang ba ni /
NK088(su)001:13493: thos pa'i dus de'i tshe ste /
NK088(su)001:13494: zla spangs pa ni thams cad nas thams cad du
NK088(su)001:13495: ma yin pa ste bshad pa la yang sbyar ro
NK088(su)001:13498: zhes pa rten thig le 'dus pa'i ye shes chen po ro dang ldan par bzhugs pa nyid do //
NK088(su)001:13500: cho 'phrul yongs su rdzogs pa'i gnas gtsug tor 'khor lo //
NK088(su)001:13501: zhes pa nas pad+mo can gyi bar la sogs pa ji snyed pa'i sprul pa'i 'byung gnas /
NK088(su)001:13502: gsang ba'i rdo rje gtsug tor dang gsang ba'i sna
NK088(su)001:13503: rtse 'phrad pas rten gyi ngo bo 'khor lo bsgyur
NK088(su)001:13504: dbu na yar bzlogs pa'i thabs mchog khyad par zab
NK088(su)001:13505: mo dpag par dka' bas nyams su myong bar yang
NK088(su)001:13506: dka' ba ro rnam gnyis kyi dga' ba dgyes pa
NK088(su)001:13507: chen po'i bye brag brgyad gnyis dang ldan pa'i yum
NK088(su)001:13508: gyi lhums b+ha ga 'dab brgyad kyi pad+ma'i snying po
NK088(su)001:13509: rtse mo'i ze'u 'bru rgyal ba ji snyed pa'i pho
NK088(su)001:13511: shin tu chags pa can 'dul ba'i don mdzad pa 'byung ba'i lam la gshegs pa'i shul dam pa /
NK088(su)001:13512: thabs dang bral na srid pa gsum gyi khams gsum
NK088(su)001:13513: gyi 'gro ba'i rgyu gzhi shin tu chags pa'i zhen
NK088(su)001:13514: pa'i rten du gyur pa sems can gyi 'byung gnas
NK088(su)001:13515: / rnal 'byor pa dang 'gro ba rnams thabs kyis
NK088(su)001:13516: zin ma zin gyis 'gro bar byed pa'i lam du
NK088(su)001:13517: gyur pa de dag gdul ba'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:13518: spyod pa cha mthun du mtshungs par bstan pa chags
NK088(su)001:13519: pa med par byed pa'i pad+ma can 'dab brgyad dang
NK088(su)001:13520: ldan pa'i phyir / mtshan nges pa'i grags pa'i gzhi tha dad pa de na bzhugs so //
NK088(su)001:13523: zhes pa yo ga phyi pa man chad thun mong kyi yul ma yin pa'i gsang sku de'o //
NK088(su)001:13525: gsang ba'i 'khor brjod kyis mi lang ba'i yang brjod kyis mi lang ba 'di lta ste /
NK088(su)001:13526: gsang ba'i sems dpa' chen po rdo rje myur ba dang /
NK088(su)001:13527: zhes pa la sogs pa gsang ba'i sku'i 'khor grangs
NK088(su)001:13528: las 'das pa'i mdor nye bar bstan pa ni gang
NK088(su)001:13529: zhe na / 'khor de dag kyang phyi pa man chad kyi yul ma yin gsang ba pa /
NK088(su)001:13530: gnyis med kyi ye shes gsang ba'i ma btsal ba'i
NK088(su)001:13531: thabs kyi cha res nyon mongs pa dang sgrib pa'i
NK088(su)001:13532: phung po 'joms shing gsang sngags kyi don la sems
NK088(su)001:13533: mi g.yo bar dmigs shing mtha' sel ba'i dpal phyir
NK088(su)001:13534: / kun kyang gsang ba'i sems dpa' rdo rje yin par nges pa'o //
NK088(su)001:13536: 'di dag rgyud so so ma yin pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:13537: thabs khyad par can gyis zin pa'i sgo nas ye
NK088(su)001:13538: shes chen po gsang sngags kyi don de ma thag
NK088(su)001:13539: par myur ba byung ba dang /
NK088(su)001:13540: yang dag pa'i sa la skad cig gis phyin par byed pa mgyogs pa dang /
NK088(su)001:13541: log pa'i d+r+wa ba gcod pa rnon po dang /
NK088(su)001:13542: yon tan gyi bye brag 'char ba 'byung ba dang /
NK088(su)001:13543: rig pa'i sgo gsal bar byed pa 'byed pa dang /
NK088(su)001:13544: thabs gong na med pa che ba dang /
NK088(su)001:13545: dman pa ma spangs bkol ba med pa yangs pa dang /
NK088(su)001:13546: thabs kyi don dpag dka' ba zab pa dang /
NK088(su)001:13547: snang ba chen po shar ba'i ye shes nub pa med pa brtan pa dang /
NK088(su)001:13548: ye shes chen po ji snyed pa'i bye brag 'dus sna tshogs pa'o //
NK088(su)001:13549: dngos po sogs gzhan bsdu ba ni brjod kyis mi lang ba rnams so //
NK088(su)001:13550: de lta bu'i 'khor pad+mo snying po'i gnas su rang rang gi gnas nas 'ong 'byung ba dang /
NK088(su)001:13552: rang rang gi gnas su 'gro ba dang bcas pa'i
NK088(su)001:13553: 'khor gyi dngos po ji snyed pa dag rten phrad
NK088(su)001:13554: pa las the tshom gcod chod bdo ba dang /
NK088(su)001:13555: slar log nas rang rang gi gnas su phyin pas
NK088(su)001:13556: gsang ba dam pa'i gdeng rnyed zin pa chod dang
NK088(su)001:13557: / yang rang rang gi gnas cha yis bskyod nas
NK088(su)001:13558: gsang ba'i don rtse mo'i gnas su zhu bar rtsom
NK088(su)001:13560: gsum na rgyud tha dad pa'i dbang du yang 'gyur ro //
NK088(su)001:13561: rtsa gnas bye ma byes ye shes su skye ba dang /
NK088(su)001:13562: skyes pa dang skye bar ldog pa'i rim pa kho na'o //
NK088(su)001:13563: 'di dag ril yang gsang ba chen po'i sku'i yan
NK088(su)001:13564: lag gi bye brag tu 'dus pa'i phyir 'khor du
NK088(su)001:13565: nges pa'o // de ltar na de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad re re la'ang /
NK088(su)001:13566: zhes pa la sogs pa sku bzhi'i gleng gzhi'i ngo
NK088(su)001:13567: bo drug drug bstan pa'i tshul des de ltar na
NK088(su)001:13568: / gdul dbang gis phyir rgyal ba ji snyed pa
NK088(su)001:13569: re re'ang sku bzhi bye brag so sor snang la
NK088(su)001:13570: ngo bo ris su yang 'byung rgyu yang med pa'i
NK088(su)001:13571: / phyir / gcig tha dad du ma'i mtha' las
NK088(su)001:13572: rgyal ba ril grol bas ma g.yos gsal la bde
NK088(su)001:13574: kun nas phyogs ril dang dus tu gnas ril du snang ngo //
NK088(su)001:13575: de dag ni mtha' las zhen pa bsal ba'i phyir bka' stsal pa'o //
NK088(su)001:13576: de'i tshe de'i dus na mi chen po'i yul /
NK088(su)001:13578: de'i tshe dus gnyis ni sku bzhis bka' stsal pa dang /
NK088(su)001:13579: de'i dus gsang ba pa'i thos pa gnyis kyi phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:13580: dbugs chen 'byin lam gyi gsum rten pas khyad par
NK088(su)001:13581: du 'gro ba pa yan chad kyis spyod yul gsang
NK088(su)001:13582: sngags dam pa'i rgyud 'di ngas sku bshad pa bzhi
NK088(su)001:13583: las thos pa ma nor ba'i gsang don /
NK088(su)001:13584: rgyal ba'i gdung 'dzin pa'i 'dus pa phal mo che la sogs dag la /
NK088(su)001:13585: ston pa sku bzhis gsungs pa ji ltar bar bgro zhing bshad pa nye bar bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:13586: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad chos thams cad /
NK088(su)001:13587: ces pa la sogs pa sangs rgyas kun dang chos so cog ril du snang ba'i rgyu /
NK088(su)001:13588: rgyal ba'i dgongs pa spong len ngang gis bral ba'i
NK088(su)001:13589: gsang sngags ji bzhin pa'i ngang las 'byung 'jug med
NK088(su)001:13590: par shar zhing snang bar thugs su chud nas /
NK088(su)001:13591: sku gsung thugs nyid kyi tha snyad dang yang bral
NK088(su)001:13592: ba'i ngo bo nyid de kho na nyid kyi ngo
NK088(su)001:13593: bor bzhugs te / rten dang rten can ni 'dod pa ma yin no //
NK088(su)001:13594: 'on tang de la'ang ji bzhin pa'i ngang las 'phral du 'jug pa dang /
NK088(su)001:13596: rab tu yang bye brag tu yang ldog pa'i 'gro 'ong ni med do //
NK088(su)001:13598: gnyis ni gang 'byung ba brjod pa nyid do //
NK088(su)001:13599: zhes pa la sogs pa sdud pa po la bos
NK088(su)001:13600: nas 'di'i gleng gzhi gnas dang ston pa gnyis ni
NK088(su)001:13602: bstan pa zab mo'i dngos por snang ba sngar byung ba brjod pa gnyis nyid do //
NK088(su)001:13604: de dag ni rgyu'i yan lag ces bya'o //
NK088(su)001:13605: zhes pa rgyud 'di 'byung ba'i rgyu'i ngo bo tshogs
NK088(su)001:13606: pa'i phyir gtan tshigs byung khungs kyi gleng gzhi ste
NK088(su)001:13607: / gsang sngags dam pa'i yan lag cig go //
NK088(su)001:13608: gleng gzhi 'dir smos pa ni bstan par 'gyur gyi /
NK088(su)001:13609: rgyud 'byung bar mi rigs pas dgos pa med do bar dogs pa la /
NK088(su)001:13610: 'byung khungs kyi gleng gzhi 'di dag mi snang na
NK088(su)001:13611: ni gsang ba'i bdag po nyid kyang gsang bdag tu
NK088(su)001:13612: mi 'gyur bas / 'di smos pas 'khor rnams dang
NK088(su)001:13613: po gsang bdag nyid kyis su la thos pa'i lo
NK088(su)001:13614: rgyus kyi yid ches par 'gyur ba dang /
NK088(su)001:13615: 'dir mi yul du snang ba gtsor byas pa dang /
NK088(su)001:13616: rgyud dkrug pa'i dbang gis gral la the tshom med do //
NK088(su)001:13617: gral ni gleng bslang ba dang yang rjes su mthun no //
NK088(su)001:13618: gleng gzhi'i le'u bzhi bcu bdun pa 'grel pa'o ////thun
NK088(su)001:13619: mong ma yin pa ngo bo'i byung khungs kyi gleng
NK088(su)001:13620: bslang ba rjes su bstan pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:13621: lang ka'i bdag po rtsa ba'i yan lag gang zhe na /
