NK088(su)001:13623: brjod pa 'byung ba gang gis gang la gleng bslang ba /
NK088(su)001:13624: zhes pa sdud pa po la bos nas /
NK088(su)001:13625: yan lag gnyis pa nye bar bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:13626: rgyud kyi tshig dang yi ge snang ba'i rtsa bar gyur pas ming 'grub bo //
NK088(su)001:13628: ston pa'i dngos pos 'khor gyi dngos po la mdun
NK088(su)001:13629: bsu ba dang gus pas dri ba'i tshul du gleng
NK088(su)001:13630: bslang ba'i dngos po nges pa nyid la gzhag go
NK088(su)001:13631: // thun mong ma yin pa'i dbang du yab yum gyis gleng bslang ba'i ngo bo nyid do //
NK088(su)001:13632: de yang mdun bsu ba lta bu dang /
NK088(su)001:13633: yum gyis gleng bslang ba bstan pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:13634: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa de dag dbyings kyi ngang las mi g.yo bar mnal bzhin du /
NK088(su)001:13635: zhes pa la sogs pa bshad pa'i yang na gang
NK088(su)001:13636: gi sku bzhi sku gsung thugs mi dmigs pa'i ngang
NK088(su)001:13637: dbyings las bzhugs pa las ma g.yos mnal bzhin du
NK088(su)001:13638: yum kun tu bzang po rgyal ba thams cad skyed
NK088(su)001:13639: par mdzad ma ma skyes pa'i chos nyid kyi ngang
NK088(su)001:13640: las skur rang snang bas yab dbyings nas bzhengs pa'i
NK088(su)001:13642: yod med stong pa shin tu rnal 'byor mthus //
NK088(su)001:13643: zhes pa la sogs pa gang ji bzhin pa nyid ni ci'ang med pas cir yang snang ba'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:13644: stong pa mtha' gsum grol ba'i ngang las ma g.yos pa ni rnal 'byor mchog ste /
NK088(su)001:13645: de nyid ril du mi 'gag par mthus 'char ba'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK088(su)001:13646: dpe nam mkha' lta bu'i bzhin ngang las sngon gyi
NK088(su)001:13647: thugs dam gyis mi 'da' bas 'gro don la nye
NK088(su)001:13648: bar bskul ba'o // yang dag pa'i ye shes chen
NK088(su)001:13649: po 'phel 'grib med pa dang ro gcig pas shin
NK088(su)001:13650: tu zab pa rgya mtsho des ril gsal la mi
NK088(su)001:13651: dmigs rnam par grol ba klong la log sel dang
NK088(su)001:13652: bar bskul ba'o // bral bas / mtshan nyid gcig
NK088(su)001:13653: tu mi zin mi gnas pa la spyod yul med
NK088(su)001:13654: pa mi dmigs nam mkha' lta bu'i ngang dbyings las
NK088(su)001:13655: sku 'gro don mngon du bzhengs ston cig par bskul
NK088(su)001:13656: bar bskul ba'o // bral bas / lo // bcom
NK088(su)001:13657: ldan 'das de dag gis chos thams cad byang chub
NK088(su)001:13658: bar bskul ba'o // bral bas / lo // snying
NK088(su)001:13659: po / zhes pa de dag snyeg sdud kyi sgra
NK088(su)001:13660: bar bskul ba'o // bral bas / lo // snying
NK088(su)001:13661: po / ni / sku bzhi'i khyad par snang ba'i
NK088(su)001:13663: de ril gyis chos rnams gsang sngags byang chub ji
NK088(su)001:13664: bzhin pa las snang bar shar bar bskul ba'i sgo
NK088(su)001:13665: nas thugs su chud mkhyen nas /
NK088(su)001:13666: byang chub snying po mtha' med pa'i stong pa nyid
NK088(su)001:13667: kyi ngang las 'gro ba'i mun pa sel ba'i nyi
NK088(su)001:13668: ma sku rdo rje mi 'gyur bar byung snang bar
NK088(su)001:13669: mdzad de / dper na nam mkha' la nyi ma shar ba lta bu'o //
NK088(su)001:13670: de nas nyi ma'i snying po de las 'od zer bye ba /
NK088(su)001:13672: de nas bzhengs ma thag par sku shan tu gsal
NK088(su)001:13673: ba nyi ma'i snying po las gdul bya'i ngo la
NK088(su)001:13674: sku'i 'od zer mang po bkye nas snang ba nyi
NK088(su)001:13675: ma'i snying po las 'od 'byung ba bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:13676: 'od zer de dag las thugs rje byang chub sems kyi sprin mngon par /
NK088(su)001:13677: zhes pa la sogs pa brda'i don te byang chub sems rnam gnyis kyi sprin mngon du bstan to //
NK088(su)001:13678: de'i rkyen rol thabs nyi shu ni /
NK088(su)001:13679: thabs dang shes rab dgyes par longs spyod pa'i char mngon du 'bab pa dang /
NK088(su)001:13681: khu ba 'pho ba glog 'byung ba dang /
NK088(su)001:13682: phyi'i 'dod yon mchod pa lngas bde ba bskyed pa dang /
NK088(su)001:13683: snyan pa'i glus bde ba bskyed pa dang /
NK088(su)001:13684: lag gi spyod pa gar dang /
NK088(su)001:13687: sen mos 'tshe ba ker ko dang /
NK088(su)001:13688: tsam+b+ha ni byed pa gling bu dang /
NK088(su)001:13689: yab yum gyi rgyan rnams dang /
NK088(su)001:13690: lus kyi mdangs 'byin cing mnyes pa dga' ba dang /
NK088(su)001:13691: dgos pas spyod pa skyod thabs mang po'i don ji lta ba rnams shes par byed pa dang /
NK088(su)001:13692: de dag gi thabs rig pa ye shes dang /
NK088(su)001:13693: skabs su nyams brtag pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK088(su)001:13694: dgyes pas bde ba dang dga' ba myong ba dang /
NK088(su)001:13695: lhan cig pa'i ye shes chen po'i ro tshor ba dang /
NK088(su)001:13696: bde ba skyes pa yum mtshan dga' ba rnams dang
NK088(su)001:13697: ldan pa de dag gis btsun mo yum gyi mkha'
NK088(su)001:13698: ma skyes pa chos nyid kyi ngo bo la 'jug
NK088(su)001:13699: par mdzad do // de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi yum /
NK088(su)001:13701: de nas yab kyis rol pa'i char bab ma thag par /
NK088(su)001:13702: yum gyis thabs shes rab kyi spyod pa'i stong pa
NK088(su)001:13703: nyid kyi ngang las sku cir yang bstan pa bskul
NK088(su)001:13704: ba'i sgra 'di tshig tu gsungs pa /
NK088(su)001:13705: sku gsum lhun gyis grub pas tshogs chen gnyis rdzogs
NK088(su)001:13706: mi gnas pa'i ye shes mchog gi bdag nyid thugs
NK088(su)001:13707: dam ni / mnyam pa'i dbyings dang dbyer med pas rgyud dag pa'i lha khyod /
NK088(su)001:13708: dgyes pa'i longs spyod mnga' thang lhun gyis rdzogs grub
NK088(su)001:13709: pa mdzad pas thabs mchog rol pa'i sku chen po'i
NK088(su)001:13710: zhes bya'o // skye 'jig mi mnga' ba'i rdo rje ngang las sems ma g.yos par /
NK088(su)001:13711: log phung 'jams pa'i stan dpa' pa /
NK088(su)001:13712: yon tan tshad las 'das pa'i mnga' thang skal bzang
NK088(su)001:13713: mchog gi bdag nyid bdag gzhan gyi don lhun gyis
NK088(su)001:13715: yum bdag la 'dod chags thabs kyi spyod pa rol
NK088(su)001:13716: pa mdzad pas 'khor snod du rung bar dbang bskur
NK088(su)001:13717: ba'i phyir / bde ba chen po dgyes pa'i dbyings nas sku bzhengs shig par bskul to //
NK088(su)001:13718: bde ba chen po'i ngang de las cho 'phrul chen po rnam par bzhengs te /
NK088(su)001:13719: zhes pa la sogs pa rol pa nyi shus bde
NK088(su)001:13720: ba chen po'i ngang la bzhugs pa la bskul bas
NK088(su)001:13721: dgyes pa'i ro mchog bdar ba'i ngo bo de las
NK088(su)001:13722: sku'i cho 'phrul cir yang snang bar mdzad pa ni
NK088(su)001:13723: bcu ste / sku las sprul pa rnam par 'phrul cir yang ma 'dres snang ba dang /
NK088(su)001:13724: sku mchog yongs su rdzogs pa rnam par 'khyil nyid du snang ba dang /
NK088(su)001:13725: rnam par 'gyings seng ge'i tshul dang /
NK088(su)001:13727: phyag gi gar thabs rgya dang /
NK088(su)001:13729: thugs rje sprul pa'i 'byung 'jug snang ba dang /
NK088(su)001:13730: 'bras bu yon tan gyi bye brag dang /
NK088(su)001:13733: brda'i dbang du na 'khor dbang bsgyur ba'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:13734: rol pa'i byang chub sems las byin rlabs cir yang snang ba dang /
NK088(su)001:13735: byang chub sems slar bskyil ba dang /
NK088(su)001:13736: rdo rje'i gnas rnams gang ba dang /
NK088(su)001:13737: bde ba'i brjid ro mi 'gyur ba'i byin dang /
NK088(su)001:13738: 'khor la dbang bskur ba'i phyag gi gar brda cir yang snang ba dang /
NK088(su)001:13739: dbang bskur bar bzhad dgyes pa dang /
NK088(su)001:13740: dbang gi don 'phro 'du mdzad pa'i sbyor ba bral ba dang /
NK088(su)001:13741: dbang gi byin brlabs yon tan ma 'dres pa dang /
NK088(su)001:13742: 'khor gyi rig pa la 'od zer byin brlabs snang zhing gsal bar byas pa dang /
NK088(su)001:13743: gzhan bsdu ba ni byin rlabs ji snyed pa'o //
NK088(su)001:13744: sprul pa'i glog gi phreng bas nam mkha' /
NK088(su)001:13745: zhes pa la sogs pa byang chub sems kyi byin
NK088(su)001:13746: rlabs cir yang snang bar gsal ba rgyun ma chod
NK088(su)001:13747: par nam mkha'i khams kyi 'khor ji snyed pa la
NK088(su)001:13749: thams cad nas thams cad dus snga phyi 'khor gyi
NK088(su)001:13750: rig pa la mtshan 'dzin dang rnam rtog dang mtha'
NK088(su)001:13751: gnyis su med pa la lta ba yod pa la
NK088(su)001:13752: / gsang dbang gi byin rlabs kyis khyab pas de
NK088(su)001:13753: nyid ched du ma gsal bar ji bzhin par shes
NK088(su)001:13755: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi yum stong pa chen po /
NK088(su)001:13756: zhes pa la sogs pa 'khor la gsang dbang gi
NK088(su)001:13757: byin rlabs kyis khyab par mdzad ma thag par yang
NK088(su)001:13758: yum gyis rgyud bshad pa bskul ba tha ma dang
NK088(su)001:13759: sprul pa'i mdzad pa snang bar bya dgos so //
NK088(su)001:13761: ye shes sgyu mas rnam par rol //
NK088(su)001:13762: zhes pa dag ye shes chen po rang snang ba'i
NK088(su)001:13763: sgyu ma'i sku mchog gi 'gro don rnam par mdzad
NK088(su)001:13764: pa'i ston pas / thabs shes rab gnyis med rol
NK088(su)001:13765: pa'i che la longs spyod mnga' brnyes pa kyi mnga'
NK088(su)001:13766: bdag rgyal ba 'phags rje ril gyi rje bo sprul
NK088(su)001:13767: pa mang po kun gyi gzhi /
NK088(su)001:13768: nyid bde gshegs bde ba chen po brnyes nas gzhan
NK088(su)001:13769: yang bde bar gshegs pa la dgod par mdzad pa
NK088(su)001:13770: khyod / 'gro don du sprul pa dang rgyud 'chad pa'i ston par bzhengs su gsol zhes bskul to //
NK088(su)001:13771: bcom ldan 'das gsang ba mchog gi bdag po /
NK088(su)001:13772: zhes pa la sogs pa ston pa gsang sngags kyi mnga' bdag rigs thams cad pa'i bdag po nyid /
NK088(su)001:13773: rdo rje gsum rol pa thabs shes rab kyi spyod
NK088(su)001:13774: pa mdzad pas de kho na nyid mnyam pa ma
NK088(su)001:13775: nor ba'i dgongs pa las mi g.yo bar bzhugs te
NK088(su)001:13776: / zhu ba bsgugs pa'i ched du cang mi gsung ngo //
NK088(su)001:13777: de dag gi 'khor gyis ci'ang ma zhus par ston
NK088(su)001:13778: pa yab yum gyis gleng nas dbang bskur ba'i phyir
NK088(su)001:13779: mdun bsu ba'i don du sbyar ro //
NK088(su)001:13780: gus pas dri ba gleng pa lta bu gang snyam pa la /
NK088(su)001:13781: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi yum /
NK088(su)001:13782: zhes pa la sogs pa rtsa ba'i rgyud las ni
NK088(su)001:13783: rigs kyi bdag po kun tu bzang po'i yum kun
NK088(su)001:13784: tu bzang mor gsal bar byung ba'i yum des yab
NK088(su)001:13785: la bskul ba'i tshig gsungs pa la /
NK088(su)001:13786: 'khor 'dus pa phal mo che rnams shin tu ya
NK088(su)001:13787: mtshan zhing don la ngam pa chen por gyur pas
NK088(su)001:13788: ngag mtshungs par / ston pa rdo rje rol pa
NK088(su)001:13789: de kho na nyid kyi ngang du bzhugs pa la
NK088(su)001:13790: glu'i dgyes pa bskyed pas gnang ba'i rgyur gyur pa'i
NK088(su)001:13793: yid bzhin sku mchog nam mkha' lta bu la //
NK088(su)001:13794: zhes pa la sogs pa ston pa'i sku'i yon tan gyi mdzad pa la ngam nas smras pa ni /
NK088(su)001:13795: yid bzhin yon tan lhun gyis grub pas sku mchog
NK088(su)001:13796: cir yang snang ba nam mkha' lta bur bzhugs pa
NK088(su)001:13797: las thams cad du bdal khyab pa'i chos sku'i yon
NK088(su)001:13798: tan ma grub la snang ba'i byin rlabs ngo bo
NK088(su)001:13799: rdo rje gsum gyi gar mdzad pa gang du'ang ma
NK088(su)001:13801: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku gzi brjid mtshan dang dpe
NK088(su)001:13802: byad la sogs pa'i gzi byin sprin dpung phun sum
NK088(su)001:13803: tshogs pas longs spyod chen po la rol pas mnga'
NK088(su)001:13804: mdzad pa'i dbang phyug chen po'i bsgyings sku 'gro ba'i
NK088(su)001:13805: don la skad cig la thogs med sku gsung thugs
NK088(su)001:13806: rdo rje dbyer med pa'i sprul pas rol pa'i don
NK088(su)001:13807: mdzad pas sprul pa'i sku yang cho 'phrul mnyes pas
NK088(su)001:13808: don mdzod ces sku gsum gyi sgo nas gsol to
NK088(su)001:13810: yid bzhin gsung mchog /ces pa la sogs pa gsung
NK088(su)001:13811: gi yon tan la ngo mtshar skyes nas gsol pa
NK088(su)001:13812: / gsung lnga lhun gyis grub pas gdul bya ji
NK088(su)001:13813: ltar 'dod pa ltar 'byung ba sgra brnyan lta bu
NK088(su)001:13814: / las / gdul bya'i rna bar dga' ba bskyed
NK088(su)001:13815: pa'i gsung lnga'i byin rlabs rdo rje theg pa'i chos
NK088(su)001:13816: ston par mdzad pa'i gsung bshad pa ltar gcig la'ang
NK088(su)001:13817: yan lag bcu bcur 'gyur pas mu mtha' med par
NK088(su)001:13818: / las / rdzogs pa'i gsung / dpe seng ge
NK088(su)001:13819: sgra lta bu log lta gnon pas theg pa chen
NK088(su)001:13820: po ston cig par gsol ba btab bo //
NK088(su)001:13822: ye shes snying po nam mkha' lta bu las /
NK088(su)001:13823: zhes pa la sogs pa thugs kyi yon tan rgya mtsho la ngo mtshar ba ni /
NK088(su)001:13824: mi gnas pa'i ye shes ni ye shes ril gyi
NK088(su)001:13825: rtsa ba ste thams cad du rang gsal ba las
NK088(su)001:13826: / ye shes kyi 'od ji snyed du gsal ba'i
NK088(su)001:13827: byin rlabs skye 'jig med pas gdul bya bde ba
NK088(su)001:13829: gi 'phro ba med pas 'dzin pa'i rnam pa dang
NK088(su)001:13830: bral ba'i thugs kyi ngang las /
NK088(su)001:13831: mi shes pa'i mdud pa ngang gis bral ba'i thugs kyi mdzad pa bstan du gsol zhes pa'o //
NK088(su)001:13832: mi shes blun rmongs 'dam bying 'gro ba rnams //
NK088(su)001:13833: zhes pa la sogs pa de 'gro ba ma rig
NK088(su)001:13834: pas mdongs pas 'khor ba'i rgya mtshor nub cing thar
NK088(su)001:13835: dka' ba kun gdung zhing nyam thag pa thar zhing
NK088(su)001:13836: thon pa'i thabs dang bral ba'i mdud pa thabs kyi
NK088(su)001:13837: thugs rjes bshigs par mdzod cig pa dang /
NK088(su)001:13838: 'gro ba'i ma rig pa'i ling tog gis shes rab
NK088(su)001:13839: kyi spyan gtibs pa dbye ru gsol zhes pa dang
NK088(su)001:13840: / 'khor ba'i chu 'jing las thabs kyi mdzad pa'i gru yis sgrol cig pa dang /
NK088(su)001:13841: rgyal ba ril gyi thugs ye shes mchog ni lhun gyis grub pa'i ye shes te /
NK088(su)001:13842: de lta bu mnga' ba lags pas /
NK088(su)001:13843: rnal 'byor gsum gyi don mthar phyin pa'i rdo rje
NK088(su)001:13844: theg pa chen po bstan pa thams cad kyi gzhi
NK088(su)001:13845: rtsar gyur pa sgro skur dang bral ba 'di /
NK088(su)001:13846: bdag cag mang po 'dus pa'i 'khor tshogs la lhag pa med par bka' stsal du gsol /
NK088(su)001:13847: zhes dgyes pa bskyed pa'i sgra brjod de sgo gsum 'dud pa byas te gsol ba gdab bo //
NK088(su)001:13848: de nas bcom ldan 'das gsang ba mchog gi bdag po des /
NK088(su)001:13849: zhes pa la sogs pa gsol ba btab ma thag
NK088(su)001:13850: par rigs kyi bdag po gsang sngags kyi rgyal ba
NK088(su)001:13851: ston pa de / gsol ba'i rkyen gyis gnang bas
NK088(su)001:13852: 'khor la spyan gzigs te zhal 'dzum pa ni 'khor
NK088(su)001:13853: ston pa de / gyi snang ba'o // de nas
NK088(su)001:13854: yab yum nyid kyi thugs mtha' dang bral ba'i dbyings
NK088(su)001:13855: nas thig le gzi mdangs bkra mdangs kyi ngo bo
NK088(su)001:13856: zla ba dang nyi ma byang sems rnam gnyis 'od
NK088(su)001:13857: zer grangs las 'das pa dang ldan pa'i ye shes
NK088(su)001:13858: chen po la ye shes thams cad 'dus pa'i 'od
NK088(su)001:13859: mu mtha' med pa'i gnas ril du khyab par mdzad
NK088(su)001:13860: ston pa de / gyi snang ba'o // do //
NK088(su)001:13861: ye shes chen po'i 'od zer de dag re re
NK088(su)001:13862: las kyang khro bo gnod sbyin dang srin po lta
NK088(su)001:13863: bu mang po tha dad par snang bar mdzad de
NK088(su)001:13864: ston pa de / gyi snang ba'o // do // / 'khor gyi sgrib pa gzhom pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:13865: khro bo re re las sangs rgyas mang po la
NK088(su)001:13866: rang rang gi 'khor dang bcas pa zhing tha dad
NK088(su)001:13867: na chos ston pa snang bar mdzad de /
NK088(su)001:13868: theg pa gzhan gyi gleng gzhi 'di'i byin rlabs las snang ba'o //
NK088(su)001:13869: de dag las rig pa'i nyi ma'i 'od /
NK088(su)001:13870: ces pa theg pa so so'i gleng gzhi'i de dag
NK088(su)001:13871: las dgongs pa'i rig pa'i don ston pa'i nyi ma'i
NK088(su)001:13872: 'od zer bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i sgo /
NK088(su)001:13873: gdul bya'i gnas nam mkha'i khams mtha' thug pa med par byung bas /
NK088(su)001:13874: gdul bya mun pa ma rig pa'i smag rum du
NK088(su)001:13875: chud pa thams cad kyi sgrib pa dag par mdzad
NK088(su)001:13876: do // de gang gis zhe na /
NK088(su)001:13877: rig pa'i chos kyi 'brug sgra dang /
NK088(su)001:13879: don ji lta ba rig pa'i mthong bar byed pa'i gsung gi sgra chen po dang /
NK088(su)001:13880: chos kyi char mang po phab pa dang /
NK088(su)001:13881: chos kyi glu dbyangs sum brgya drug cu la sogs pa mdzad pa'i gar thabs mang po dang /
NK088(su)001:13882: phyi nang gi mchod pa mang po byung ste /
NK088(su)001:13883: rgya khyon tshad med pa nam mkha' khyab pa'i 'jig
NK088(su)001:13884: rten du chos kyi sgra tha dad pa phyogs mtshams
NK088(su)001:13886: phyogs bzhi la sogs kyi gdul bya'i gnas tha dad
NK088(su)001:13887: par ma khyab pa med par sku bstan pa gsang
NK088(su)001:13888: sngags ji lta bar snang ba ma nges ling long
NK088(su)001:13889: byed pa ni dus rtag par don mdzad do //
NK088(su)001:13891: zhes pa 'gro ba'i ched du sku mchog gi sprul
NK088(su)001:13892: pa mang po ji ltar yang snang bas sku re
NK088(su)001:13893: re la 'od zer bye ba 'bum phrag gsal ba
NK088(su)001:13895: bsnol mar 'byung zhing thams cad du khyab par rtag par don mdzad do //
NK088(su)001:13896: thugs mchog mi rtog pa'i thugs dang /
NK088(su)001:13897: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyang shin tu gsal bar bzhugs so //
NK088(su)001:13898: theg pa chen po'i byin rlabs bstan pa mang po yang dgyes pa'i a ho sgras chos ston to //
NK088(su)001:13899: rgyal ba sangs rgyas dpag med ji snyed pa yang
NK088(su)001:13900: gsung mtshungs par a ho ngam pas theg pa chen
NK088(su)001:13901: po'i mdzad pa snang ba'i chos 'gro don du snang
NK088(su)001:13903: rigs kyi bdag po nyid kyis 'khor khri phrag bcu dang /
NK088(su)001:13904: gdul bya bsam pa tha dad sna tshogs byin rlabs
NK088(su)001:13905: kyis spro ba'i mngon du dga' ba dang ya mtshan
NK088(su)001:13906: skyed de / rig pa'i shes rab kyi rtsal skyed
NK088(su)001:13907: du sbyangs byas don rtogs pas che ba phyung ston
NK088(su)001:13908: pa'i byin rlabs ngom zhing shin tu e ma'o ngo
NK088(su)001:13910: 'khor gdul bya thams cad nye bar ril ston pa
NK088(su)001:13911: la bdun pas gsang ba'i don la nye bar gnas
NK088(su)001:13912: so // rgyud kyi rtog pa zhi bar gyur to //
NK088(su)001:13913: chos kyi don mthong ba'i dga' ba can du gyur to //
NK088(su)001:13914: sku gsung thugs kyi gsol ba btab pa'i lan du ci rigs par sbyar ro //
NK088(su)001:13915: 'khor snod du rung bar byin gyis rlabs pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:13916: de nas gsang ba mchog gi bdag po des /
NK088(su)001:13917: 'khor rnam par sbyong ba rdo rje rgyan /
NK088(su)001:13918: zhes pa la sogs pa ston pa rigs kyi bdag
NK088(su)001:13919: po nyid kyis 'khor gyi sgrib pa dag par sbyangs
NK088(su)001:13920: mdzad pa'i skal pa med pa rnams rdo rje rgyan
NK088(su)001:13922: skal pa can rnams spyan sngar 'du bar byed pa
NK088(su)001:13923: nyid kyis dgongs pa'i mtshan nges par de lta bu
NK088(su)001:13924: la zhugs nas lta ngan dang sgrib pa 'joms pa'i
NK088(su)001:13925: nus pa can gyi sngags tshig shangs kyi dbugs kyi
NK088(su)001:13926: h'u ste / de las 'chad pa bdag gis rdo
NK088(su)001:13927: rje mngon pa'i mthu can 'di dag /sgra bton to
NK088(su)001:13930: zhes pa la sogs pa rdo rje gsum gyi phyir grangs nges pa'o //
NK088(su)001:13931: de yang rdo rje theg pa 'du bar chen po
NK088(su)001:13932: rtogs par 'dod pas spyan sngar 'dus pa'i tshogs pa'i
NK088(su)001:13933: dam tshig chen po sems dpa' rdo rje la sogs
NK088(su)001:13934: pa gsang sngags kyi rigs can dag gral steng 'og
NK088(su)001:13936: theg pa chen po gsang sngags kyi rigs ma yin
NK088(su)001:13937: pa ru dra can la sogs pa gsang ba'i rgyud
NK088(su)001:13938: 'dzin pa ma yin pas song shig pa'o //
NK088(su)001:13940: las dang skal pa mchog gi spyod rigs can rnams
NK088(su)001:13941: kyi yul gsang sngags 'di ni skal med kyis rtogs
NK088(su)001:13943: don 'di las nyams na de dag ngan song du rgyud brlag par 'gyur bas bskrad pa'o //
NK088(su)001:13944: h'u kro d+ha dz+wa la sa ma ya /
NK088(su)001:13945: zhes pa la sogs pa 'og gi 'od kyi phreng ba bzhi 'don pa'i sngags so //
NK088(su)001:13946: zhal ljags kyi dbang po 'od me dpung chen po las /
NK088(su)001:13947: zhes pa la sogs pa ston pa'i ljags kyi me dpung las 'od bzhi byung ba ni /
NK088(su)001:13948: rim pa bzhin rigs kyi he ru ka phra men
NK088(su)001:13949: dang bcas pa'i 'od bar ma chad par byung ba
NK088(su)001:13950: dang / rdo rje srin po khro bo bcu la sogs pa 'od dang bcas par 'phro ba dang /
NK088(su)001:13951: rdo rje gnod sbyin 'od dang bcas par bsnol mar 'khrugs pa dang /
NK088(su)001:13952: za byed chen po ru ti he ru ka la
NK088(su)001:13953: sogs pa'i 'od phung rgyun ma chad par phyung ba'o
NK088(su)001:13954: // skal med dngos gang snyam pa la /
NK088(su)001:13955: ru dra can dang bdud dang srin po dang /
NK088(su)001:13956: zhes pa la sogs pa sgra ji bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:13957: skabs su lu lde dang me khyer ni /
NK088(su)001:13958: dmyal ba'i khyi dang srin bu'o //
NK088(su)001:13959: 'khor ba ni sems can las ngan phal pa'o //
NK088(su)001:13960: chu dang sa ni de dag la gnas pa'i 'gro ba'o //
NK088(su)001:13961: bsam ngan ni log sred can no //
NK088(su)001:13962: dngos po gzhan bsdu ba ni mu stegs la sogs pa'o //
NK088(su)001:13963: de dag ni rgyud tha dad pa'i dbang du 'gyur ro //
NK088(su)001:13964: rgyud gcig pa'i dbang du rtogs pa'i brdar 'gyur te /
NK088(su)001:13965: dregs pa'i nga rgyal dang gti mug dang /
NK088(su)001:13971: las kyibaga chags brtas pa dang /
NK088(su)001:13985: mtshan 'dzin tha dad pa ril ngo bo dag pas
NK088(su)001:13986: chos nyid mnyam pa'i ngang du zug rngu dang bral
NK088(su)001:13987: bar mdzad do // de nas 'od zer de dag nam mkha' la 'khyil ba dang /
NK088(su)001:13988: zhes pa la sogs pa 'od nam mkha' la gcig tu 'khyil gyur pas 'khor rnams sngangs te /
NK088(su)001:13989: dbang gi snod du rung bar gsol ba btab bo //
NK088(su)001:13990: 'od kyi skal ngan e ma bskrad pa dang /
NK088(su)001:13991: sbyang ba e ma la ngom ste /
NK088(su)001:13992: ston pas bcom ldan 'das bdag cag la zab mo'i
NK088(su)001:13993: dbang bskur la gsang sngags kyi snod du rung ba
NK088(su)001:13994: dang / rigs su mi 'gyur bar mdzad du gsol
NK088(su)001:13995: byin gyis brlabs zhes zhus pas gnang nas zab mo'i
NK088(su)001:13997: bcom ldan 'das kyis zhal gyi mdangs phyungs pas /
NK088(su)001:13998: zhes pa dag phyi ltar zhal las 'od dngos phyungs pas /
NK088(su)001:13999: 'od nyid mtshan rtog zhi zhing 'khyil ba'i ye shes
NK088(su)001:14000: kyi 'od mdzes legs pas 'khor bde ba la 'god
NK088(su)001:14001: pa'i yon tan can des 'khor thams cad gyis bsam
NK088(su)001:14002: pa dag pas rangs par rgyud dag par snod sbyangs
NK088(su)001:14003: mdzad de / slar ston pa'i 'od kyi gnas ljags nyid la thim pa'o //
NK088(su)001:14005: thabs shes rab rol pa'i thig le gzi bcom mdangs
NK088(su)001:14006: can bde ldan ba'i ro dang mtshungs 'das pa de
NK088(su)001:14007: rdo rje'i zhal nas phyungs te /
NK088(su)001:14008: thig le de dag 'dus pa'i 'od mang por rdo
NK088(su)001:14009: rje rtog pa dang bral ba zhi zhing gnyis med
NK088(su)001:14011: bde ba'i ros thams cad 'khor rang rang gi rig
NK088(su)001:14012: pa rangs par byas dga' bde'i ro can du gyur
NK088(su)001:14013: te / bde ba'i nyams rnyed pas 'khor rnams dgyes
NK088(su)001:14014: pa'i ros tshim rangs par byas nas rgyud la yod
NK088(su)001:14015: pa'i rtog pa rnams snod rnam par sbyangs dag par
NK088(su)001:14016: te / byas te / thig le drangs te slar
NK088(su)001:14017: 'od kyi bzlog pas rang rang gi gnas tha dad
NK088(su)001:14018: te / byas te / par thim ste / bum
NK088(su)001:14019: pa chus gang ba ltar bde ba'i ro dang bcas
NK088(su)001:14020: pas lus gang bar gyur to //
NK088(su)001:14021: de ltar ye shes rang gnas bden pa'i tshig gis dbang bskur te zab mo'i snod du gyur to //
NK088(su)001:14022: de nas rigs kyi bdag po phyag na rdo rje
NK088(su)001:14023: la sogs pa'i 'khor dbang thob pa la rgyud bshad
NK088(su)001:14024: pa ni / lang ka'i bdag po /
NK088(su)001:14025: de nas bcom ldan 'das gsang ba mchog gi bdag
NK088(su)001:14026: po de mi gnas pa'i ye shes chen po'i klong
NK088(su)001:14027: nas / zhes pa la sogs pa gsang ba pas
NK088(su)001:14028: sdud pa la bos te lo rgyus su brjod pa
NK088(su)001:14029: nas / ni / ston pa chen po de'i thugs
NK088(su)001:14030: mi gnas mtshan nyid thams cad dang bral ba'i dbyings
NK088(su)001:14031: nas / ni / klong nas / sku mngon du
NK088(su)001:14032: snang bar bzhengs mdzad nas seng ge thams cad zil
NK088(su)001:14033: gyis gnon pa'i gsung gis bka' stsal pa'i don gang
NK088(su)001:14034: nas / ni / klong nas / zhe na / don gyi bkod pa rtags kyi rol pa /
NK088(su)001:14035: zhes pa sems kyi dkyil 'khor 'od gsal ba ji
NK088(su)001:14036: bzhin pa'i ye shes chen po la bsgrub bya dang
NK088(su)001:14037: shes bya'i don ji snyed ma btsal lhun gyis rdzogs
NK088(su)001:14038: pas bkod pa 'dogs su gnang ba'i sgo nas bstan
NK088(su)001:14039: pa'i tshig dang yi ge'i gzugs brnyan 'di yang de
NK088(su)001:14040: bzhin no // mdzad pa ril lhun gyis grub pa'i
NK088(su)001:14041: byang chub sems de nyid gdul bya la rtags kyi
NK088(su)001:14043: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor de zhi bar snang nas ji ltar 'dul ba'i don ril mdzad pa'o //
NK088(su)001:14044: gsang ba'i nges pa zhes pa /
NK088(su)001:14045: dam pa'i gsang ba'i mdzod gsum gyi nang nas yang nges don dam pa yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:14047: rgyud lung man ngag bka'i gzhan la 'bebs pa'i 'grel pa phyir /
NK088(su)001:14048: chos kyi me long zhes pa /
NK088(su)001:14049: chos rnams kyi ji lta ba nyid gsal bar chos
NK088(su)001:14050: kyi ston pa'i don du ji bzhin du ma 'dres
NK088(su)001:14051: la yongs su rdzogs pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:14052: gtan tshigs kyi 'byung gnas zhes pa /
NK088(su)001:14053: chos rtags gtan tshigs bzhi sgo gsum gyi lde'u mig
NK088(su)001:14054: gsum po thams cad gsal bar 'byung ba'i gnas phyir
NK088(su)001:14055: ro // dgongs pa kun 'dus zhes pa /
NK088(su)001:14056: rgyal ba ril gyi dgongs don gyi mdo 'dus pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:14057: rdo rje rnam par bsgyings pa'i gzhung chen po las sgra 'dis bshad do //
NK088(su)001:14058: zhes pa ji bzhin pa'i gsang ba nyid mi phyed
NK088(su)001:14059: cing rdo rje 'dus ma byas pa la yon tan
NK088(su)001:14060: dang 'bras bu ril ma btsal bar rdzogs pas rnam
NK088(su)001:14061: par bsgyings pa'i brjid pa'i rgyud dang /
NK088(su)001:14062: theg pa'i lugs gzhung ma 'khyar ba'i don chen po'i
NK088(su)001:14063: theg pa chen po rtsa ba nas bshad pa sgra
NK088(su)001:14064: byung ngo ni / +amo h'u m+aum zhes pa /
NK088(su)001:14065: bshad pa'i mtshan dang che ba ji ltar bstan kyang
NK088(su)001:14066: yi ge gsum bshad pa gzhan dkyil 'khor rnam gsum
NK088(su)001:14067: gyi don gyi ngo bo brdas bstan pa der 'dus
NK088(su)001:14068: pas yi ge'i don gsum gyi mtshan brgyad du yon
NK088(su)001:14069: tan gyi khyad par gyis bgrangs pa'o //
NK088(su)001:14070: 'on kyang mdo de dag tsam brjod pas gsang ba
NK088(su)001:14071: dag la sogs pa'i sgrib pa mtha' spangs kyi rtsal
NK088(su)001:14072: chen pa 'khor gyis rgyas par go'o //
NK088(su)001:14073: gzhan du na +amo yab m+aum yum h'u gnyis su med pa'i sgo nas /
NK088(su)001:14074: ye shes chen po'i gsang ba rgyud kyi don 'byung ba'i brda ste /
NK088(su)001:14075: dngos su brjod pa ni ma yin no //
NK088(su)001:14076: de nas ston pas tshig cang mi gsung shin tu mi gsung ste /
NK088(su)001:14077: gsung ba'i rtsol rtog mi mnga' ba'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:14079: bden pa re mos bral bas mi g.yo ba chen
NK088(su)001:14080: po la bstan pa gdul bya la bka' stsal pa'i
NK088(su)001:14082: 'gog pa ma yin par 'dul bzhin bka' rtsal par snang ngo //
NK088(su)001:14083: ched du 'ang gsungs pa nyid na mi mnga' ba'i
NK088(su)001:14084: dus nges pa na'ang bsam gyis mi khyab par bshad
NK088(su)001:14085: pa rgya cher bshad pa nyid kyi ngo bor gnas
NK088(su)001:14086: so // sdud pa po la bos nas lang ka'i bdag po ngo bo bstan pa'o //
NK088(su)001:14087: bzhi bcu brgyad pa'i 'grel pa'o ////lang ka'i bdag po /
NK088(su)001:14088: de la 'brel ba'i yan lag gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:14089: zhes pa yan lag gsum pa rgyas par bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:14090: rgyu gang dang thabs kyi dngos gzhi dang 'bras bu
NK088(su)001:14091: thabs las byung ba'i dngos po rnams 'brel ba ni
NK088(su)001:14092: ngo bo'o // de'i don ni 'di ltar nye bar
NK088(su)001:14093: 'byung ba ltar khyod kyis go bar bya ba'i dgos
NK088(su)001:14094: ched du ngas ched du brjod par rgyas par bstan
NK088(su)001:14095: par bya'o zhes zhal gyis bzhes pa'o //
NK088(su)001:14096: dgos 'brel bzhi las rjod byed 'chad pa'i skyes bu nyid don bstan pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:14098: de nas bdag de'i tshe de'i dus na /
NK088(su)001:14099: zhes pa sdud pa po la bos nas /
NK088(su)001:14100: gleng bslang ba de nas bdun bsu ba lta bur
NK088(su)001:14101: phyag na rdo rje nyid stan pas dbang bskur nas
NK088(su)001:14102: rgyud bshad pa'i dus gnyis 'dzom pa'i skabs na /
NK088(su)001:14103: bdag gi mtshan dam tshig chen po rdo rje sems dpa' zhes bya bar gyur pa ni /
NK088(su)001:14104: bcom ldan 'das ston pa rigs kyi bdag po gsang
NK088(su)001:14105: ba mchog gi gsang sngags kyi theg pa chen po
NK088(su)001:14106: gsang ba'i don 'khor gzhan la phyag na rdo rje
NK088(su)001:14107: bdag nyid kyis ngas 'chad cing brjod cig par ston
NK088(su)001:14108: du gzhug par dgongs pa'i ched du ston pa'i zhal
NK088(su)001:14109: zhal 'dud pas bdag kho na la gzigs te 'dzum
NK088(su)001:14110: pas bdag la bshad pa'i bskul bar mdzad do //
NK088(su)001:14111: de nas bdag dam tshig chen po rdo rje sems dpa' zhes bya bar snang ba des /
NK088(su)001:14112: zhes pa la sogs pa dus der bdag mtshan 'di
NK088(su)001:14113: skad du grags pa des yang dag par 'chad par
NK088(su)001:14114: bskul bar rig shes nas ston pa la 'chad pa'i
NK088(su)001:14115: dbang nod par zhus pa ni /
NK088(su)001:14116: bdag phyag na rdo rje rang gi stan las langs te /
NK088(su)001:14117: bdag nyid kyi thugs mtshan ma mtshon pa'i rtags rdo
NK088(su)001:14118: rje rgya gram gyis bdag nyid kyi spyi bo la
NK088(su)001:14119: sogs pa lngar reg par byas nas /
NK088(su)001:14120: theg pa chen po gsang sngags kyi don de kho
NK088(su)001:14121: na nyid ma nor ba rgya cher bshad pa'i phyir
NK088(su)001:14122: / 'chad pa'i rtags khyad par du yang bdag gi
NK088(su)001:14123: lce chu skyes su gsal ba'i steng du rgya gram
NK088(su)001:14124: bzhag nas shin tu sgo gsum gus pa'i lus kyi
NK088(su)001:14125: lto sa la phab pa'i brkyang phyag rnal 'byor nang
NK088(su)001:14127: bag tsha ba dang 'jigs pa med pa'i seng ge
NK088(su)001:14128: lta stangs kyis ston pa'i zhal du bltas te 'di
NK088(su)001:14129: skad ces gsol ba btab bo //
NK088(su)001:14130: rdo rje rgyal po tshogs bdag dgongs su gsol //
NK088(su)001:14131: zhes pa la sogs pa rdo rje gsum mi phyed
NK088(su)001:14132: pa'i mnga' bdag 'dus pa'i 'khor rnams kyi tshogs bdag
NK088(su)001:14133: chos kyi rgyal po bdag la thugs brtse bar mdzad
NK088(su)001:14134: du gsol / ston pa chos kyi mnga' bdag rgyal po chen po ni /
NK088(su)001:14135: dgongs pa mi g.yo mi bskyod pa'i brjid pa chos
NK088(su)001:14136: kyi rgyal po'i chos tshul lugs su mdzad pa'i ston
NK088(su)001:14138: longs spyod bde chen la rab bzhugs chen po la rol cing bzhugs pas /
NK088(su)001:14139: bdag chos smra ba'i 'chad pa'i khyad par mchog can
NK088(su)001:14140: byed pa'i lce rdo rje rgya gram du 'od 'bar
NK088(su)001:14141: ba 'di / chos kyi gsung sgra'i dbyangs mnga' bdag
NK088(su)001:14142: ston pa rnams dang rigs kyi bdag pos rgyal po
NK088(su)001:14143: bdag 'chad pa'i mthu dang ldan par byin gyis rlobs
NK088(su)001:14144: zhes gsol ba btab pa dang /
NK088(su)001:14146: gsang sngags rgyal po chos kyi me long 'di //
NK088(su)001:14147: zhes pa dag rgyud mchog thun mong ma yin pa
NK088(su)001:14148: 'di nyid sangs rgyas rgyal mchog thams cad kyi yang
NK088(su)001:14149: rab mchog dbang phyug chos kyi rgyal po chen po
NK088(su)001:14150: khyod nyid kyi sku gsung thugs kyi byin rlabs kyis
NK088(su)001:14151: bdag cag 'dus pa'i tshogs 'khor rnams la rgyas cher
NK088(su)001:14152: brjod par 'os par bshad par rigs so zhes gsol
NK088(su)001:14153: to // de ltar dgyes pa bskyed pa'i sgra a ho dang bcas par zhus pas /
NK088(su)001:14154: gsang ba mchog gi bdag po des //
NK088(su)001:14155: zhes pa la sogs pa ston pa des bdag gsang
NK088(su)001:14156: bdag nyid rdo rje theg pa 'chad pa'i las byed
NK088(su)001:14157: pa'i skyes bur las bka' par bsgo ba gnyer btad
NK088(su)001:14158: pa de / gsang sngags rdo rje rgya cher smra
NK088(su)001:14159: ba'i brjod pa chen po stobs chen por bya ba'i
NK088(su)001:14160: byin gyis brlab pa'i ched du /
NK088(su)001:14161: ston pa nyid rdo rje gsum dbyer med pa'i ngang
NK088(su)001:14162: las gsang sngags kyi bstan pa rnam par 'phro ba
NK088(su)001:14163: zhes bya ba'i 'byung ba'i dgongs pa la zhugs nas
NK088(su)001:14164: / ljags kyi 'od las sngags badz+ra karma sat+wa tsakra ha ha ham zhes gsungs nas /
NK088(su)001:14165: sngags kyi don kyang rdo rje rgya gram gyi 'khor lo 'od 'bar ba zhig phyung zhes dbyung nas /
NK088(su)001:14166: bdag sems dpa' rdo rje'i lag tu nges par bzhag ste /
NK088(su)001:14167: 'chad pa'i las byed pa'i rdo rje dbang bskur thob ste /
NK088(su)001:14168: bdag gis kyang dbang thob pa'i rtags dang yon tan ni /
NK088(su)001:14169: so so'i bye brag ma 'dres par rnam par smra ba chen po chos ston pa /
NK088(su)001:14170: rgyud 'di'i don thogs pa med par 'chad pa'i shin
NK088(su)001:14171: tu bla bkyal ba'i spobs pa can du mdzad pas
NK088(su)001:14172: gsang sngags kyi bdag por gyur nas /
NK088(su)001:14173: dus thams cad nas thams cad du bdag gi sgo
NK088(su)001:14174: gsum ched du bsdams pa med pas mi gzob pa
NK088(su)001:14176: ngo bo log par gyur pa med pa'i bag chen por gyur to //
NK088(su)001:14177: de ltar dbang dag thob pa ni /
NK088(su)001:14178: dgos 'brel bzhi las thabs dang thabs las byung ba'i tshul du 'brel ba'o //
NK088(su)001:14179: de nas sems dpa' rdo rje des las kyi mtshan ma de lag tu blangs te /
NK088(su)001:14180: zhes pa la sogs pa bdag gis der rdo rje rgya gram de lag tu blangs nas /
NK088(su)001:14181: chos bshad pa'i phyir rdo rje theg pa dam pa'i
NK088(su)001:14182: chos brda tshig sna tshogs dang bshad thabs mang pos
NK088(su)001:14183: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga'i mdzad pa'i
NK088(su)001:14184: phyir / chos kyi 'khor lo grangs lnga lngar bskyar zhing bskor ro //
NK088(su)001:14185: bcu gnyis ni nyi shu ste nyi shu rtsa lngar bskor ba ni lan grangs te /
NK088(su)001:14186: don gyi gzhi sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las
NK088(su)001:14187: nyi shu rtsa lnga'i phyir grangs thun mong du bstan
NK088(su)001:14189: rgyud gzhung 'di nyid du ni rnal 'byor rnam pa lnga'i chos bstan pa yang /
NK088(su)001:14190: yan lag sa bcu dang rnal 'byor bcu ste nyi shur bsgyur nas bstan te /
NK088(su)001:14191: bsdoms pas nyi shu rtsa lngar gyur pas zhing khams
NK088(su)001:14192: thams cad na gzhi lnga las snang ba'i 'khor mang
NK088(su)001:14193: po dag rang rang thabs dang 'tshams pa'i chos kyis
NK088(su)001:14194: / rig pa la gsang sngags rnal 'byor g.yos te rtsa ba lnga'i don ldang ba dang /
NK088(su)001:14195: g.yo ba tshabs che chung du gyur pa dang /
NK088(su)001:14196: rig pa don gyi phyogs su bskyod pa 'gul dang /
NK088(su)001:14197: ldeg logs su gyur pas rang gi sa la mi rten pas sa gong mar 'gro ba dang /
NK088(su)001:14198: 'khrug sa gong ma'i yang gong ma'i don rig pa dang mi phyed par gyur pa dang /
NK088(su)001:14199: 'ur rnam par rtog pa skabs kyi sgrib pa rnams 'phyag pa dang /
NK088(su)001:14201: mtha' mtho na zhes pa dag bshad zin to //
NK088(su)001:14202: 'di dag 'dul bya'i snang ba la phyi rol gyi cho 'phrul snang bar yang 'gyur ro //
NK088(su)001:14203: zhing khams thams cad bdag sems dpa' rdo rje /
NK088(su)001:14204: zhes pa 'dul zhing gi 'khor rnams gsang sngags thos shing gsang sngags rtogs pas /
NK088(su)001:14205: bdag gsang ba po nyid dang 'dra ba 'ba' zhig tu gyur nas /
NK088(su)001:14206: de dag kyang gsang sngags kyi don ma nor ba'i
NK088(su)001:14207: lugs rgya cher ston pa'i sgra rnam par smra bar
NK088(su)001:14208: gyur to // bdag 'chad pa'i skyes bu sems dpa'
NK088(su)001:14209: rdo rje nyid rnam par chos 'chad par 'khor la
NK088(su)001:14211: rigs kyi bdag po nyid kyi mdun phyogs su seng
NK088(su)001:14212: ge'i khri rdo rjes brgyan pa'i chos 'chad pa'i khri
NK088(su)001:14213: la lus 'gying bag gis 'dug go zhes pa'i don
NK088(su)001:14214: to // de bas na phyag na rdo rjes rigs kyi bdag po gcig la'ang thos la /
NK088(su)001:14215: 'dir 'chad pa po yin pa yang lo rgyus 'di the tshom med par gsal lo //
NK088(su)001:14216: rgyu dang 'bras bu'i tshul du 'brel ba gang snyam pa la /
NK088(su)001:14217: de nas 'dus pa'i tshogs 'khor phal mo che rnams
NK088(su)001:14218: kyis bcom ldan 'das la 'di skad ces gsol to
NK088(su)001:14219: // zhes pa 'chad pa'i skyes bus chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ma thag par /
NK088(su)001:14220: lang ka la sogs pa'i 'khor 'dus pa mang pos
NK088(su)001:14221: 'chad pa'i skyes bu la ngo mtshar skyes nas gsol
NK088(su)001:14222: pa / ngam pas ston pa la bos nas 'chad
NK088(su)001:14223: pa'i skyes bu rdo rje sems dpa' zhes bya ba
NK088(su)001:14224: 'di rgyud kyi don gting phyin par rtogs pa dang
NK088(su)001:14225: pa / / 'gro don gyi thabs khyad par can mnga' bas /
NK088(su)001:14226: thabs dang shes rab kyis 'di ltar gdul dka' drag po kun btul ba'i mthu dang /
NK088(su)001:14227: zhing khams ril byin gyis brlabs pas sa g.yos pa sogs gyur pa dang /
NK088(su)001:14228: dgongs don gyi mdzod du gyur pas rgya che ba
NK088(su)001:14229: don gyi bye brag mdzad pa ma 'dres par mkhas
NK088(su)001:14230: pa mkhyen pa / dgongs pa'i lta ba dang ting
NK088(su)001:14231: nge 'dzin zab cing gsal ba'i yon tan dang ldan
NK088(su)001:14233: rgyu bcom ldan 'das khyod kyi thugs ye shes dang rgyu dang 'bras bur 'brel cing /
NK088(su)001:14234: thugs kyi byin rlabs las snang ba gsang sngags ji
NK088(su)001:14235: bzhin pa ston pa'i rang bzhin de kho na nyid
NK088(su)001:14236: dang yang tshul snga ma ltar 'brel cing de'i byin
NK088(su)001:14237: rlabs de kho na nyid las snang ba lags so
NK088(su)001:14238: zhes kho bo gsang bdag nyid la ston pa'i spyan
NK088(su)001:14239: sngar 'khor rnams kyis bstod do zhes pa'i don to
NK088(su)001:14241: bcom ldan 'das des de dag la bka' stsal pa /
NK088(su)001:14242: zhes pa la sogs pa ston pa chen pos 'khor
NK088(su)001:14243: dwang ba bskyed pa'i phyir 'chad pa'i skyes bu'i yon
NK088(su)001:14245: sems dpa' rdo rje 'di ni byang chub sems kyi ngo bo zhes pa bcu gnyis grangs so //
NK088(su)001:14246: de dag phyogs phyi mas 'grel te /
NK088(su)001:14248: thog ma dang tha ma med par mnyam pa'i dus /
NK088(su)001:14249: zhes pa de dag gtan tshigs gang gis mngon na 'di lta ste /
NK088(su)001:14250: 'khor ba thog ma tha ma med pa'i dus nyid
NK088(su)001:14251: nas rang rig pa rtsol mthas ma bsgos byang shing
NK088(su)001:14252: ril gyi dngos gzhi sems g.yo ba dang bral ba
NK088(su)001:14253: la gnyis pa'i chos ril ma dmigs pa'i ngo bo
NK088(su)001:14254: / dus gsum ma 'gag bral ba mtshan nyid thams cad pa'i ngo bo phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:14255: pha mtha' las kyang pha mtha' zhes pa /
NK088(su)001:14256: dus thog ma'i pha mtha'i yang thog ma pha mtha'
NK088(su)001:14257: med pa nas thugs rje chen po ril thams cad
NK088(su)001:14258: kyi 'byung ba'i dbang phyug bdag po chen po'i phyir
NK088(su)001:14259: dang po dang gnyis pa'i gtan tshigs so //
NK088(su)001:14260: thabs dpag tu med mang ba cing ngo bo bsam du med pa /
NK088(su)001:14261: zhes pa thabs kyi bye brag thams cad shin tu
NK088(su)001:14262: zab pa mang ba che ba yangs pa mnga' ba'i
NK088(su)001:14263: phyir gong na med pas mchog gsum pa'i 'grel to
NK088(su)001:14265: zhes pa mu mtha' med pa'i dus na mnyam pa
NK088(su)001:14266: chen po lhun gyis grub pa'i sangs rgyas thams cad
NK088(su)001:14267: kyi rje btsan bdag nyid du bzhugs pa'i phyir ro
NK088(su)001:14268: // bya ba byas shing byed pa byas pa /
NK088(su)001:14269: zhes pa bdag gi bya ba lhun gyis rdzogs pas /
NK088(su)001:14270: sa la gnas pa'i sems dpa' rnams kyi yab rnams
NK088(su)001:14271: kyi byed pa byas don ji ltar 'dul ba bzhin
NK088(su)001:14272: mdzad pas sa la 'don pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:14273: mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa yin te /
NK088(su)001:14274: zhes pa gsang sngags de bzhin nyid chen po'i rig
NK088(su)001:14275: pa mngon du byas pas skyed du bya ba med
NK088(su)001:14276: pa rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa de la /
NK088(su)001:14277: mtha' dang zhen mtha' med par rnal 'byor kun gyi
NK088(su)001:14278: mi g.yo bdal ba rnal 'byor chen po'i dgongs bzhugs
NK088(su)001:14279: pa'o // de ni chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin du sbyor zhing /
NK088(su)001:14280: zhes pa sems dpa' rdo rje ni 'khor ba dang
NK088(su)001:14281: mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos thams cad kyi rang
NK088(su)001:14282: bzhin sbyong zhing ji bzhin pa'i mya ngan las 'das
NK088(su)001:14283: pa'i ngang la kun kyang dgod par mdzad pa'i phyir
NK088(su)001:14284: ro // chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin du 'brel bas /
NK088(su)001:14285: zhes pas dngos po chos thams cad rnams kyi de
NK088(su)001:14286: kho na rang bzhin nyid ji lta bu nyid son
NK088(su)001:14287: 'brel pas / ye shes chen pos bdud bzhi thams
NK088(su)001:14288: cad kyi dpung thams cad bcom pa'i bdud chen po
NK088(su)001:14289: 'brel pas / phyir ro // rgyal ba thams cad kyi thugs las skyes shing /
NK088(su)001:14290: zhes pa sangs rgyas kun gyi thugs ye shes kyis byin gyis brlabs shing /
NK088(su)001:14291: rgyal ba ril gyi mthu'i byin rlabs bdag tu snang
NK088(su)001:14292: bas mthu thams cad kyi yang bdag por gyur pas
NK088(su)001:14293: / gnod sbyin la sogs pa shin tu nyon mongs
NK088(su)001:14294: che zhing sangs rgyas kyis gdul dka' kha lo bsgyur
NK088(su)001:14295: bar dka' ba dag gi 'dul ba gnyen por gyur
NK088(su)001:14296: / pa'o // thugs dang 'brel ba zhes pa /
NK088(su)001:14297: sangs rgyas rnams kyi thugs ye shes dang rgyu dang
NK088(su)001:14298: 'bras bur 'brel bas dgongs pa'i gsang ba don thams
NK088(su)001:14299: cad bdag po gi thob pas bstan pa ril chos
NK088(su)001:14300: thams cad kyis dang gsang sngags kyi 'byung gnas su
NK088(su)001:14301: mdzod gyur pa'o // des lan gnyis su 'grel to //
NK088(su)001:14302: thams cad kyi yab tu gyur pa yin te /
NK088(su)001:14303: zhes pa rang byung kyi ye shes yab gsang ba thams cad kyi dam pa'i ngo bo nyid pas /
NK088(su)001:14304: ye shes ji snyed pa thams cad kyi 'char zhing
NK088(su)001:14305: snang ba'i gzhir 'byung gnas chen por gyur pa'i phyir
NK088(su)001:14306: te / yon tan de 'dra'o lta bu'o zhes kho
NK088(su)001:14307: bo bdag la yon tan ci yod pa basngagasa pa
NK088(su)001:14308: brjod pas rnams mchog tu bka' stsal pa ni /
NK088(su)001:14309: 'khor ba rnams gsang bdag la gsang don zhu ba la gzud pa'i ched do //
NK088(su)001:14310: 'dus pa'i 'khor thams cad ngo mtshar du gyur te zhes pa la sogs pa /
NK088(su)001:14311: ston pas phyag na rdo rje la basngagasa pa'i yon
NK088(su)001:14312: tan brjod pa la 'dus pa'i ngam pa skyed nas
NK088(su)001:14313: ngo bo ngo mtshar gnyis tshig brnan nas smras te
NK088(su)001:14314: / rgyud kyi don zhu ba'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:14315: sems dpa' rdo rje dam pa de la logs su btud nas /
NK088(su)001:14316: zhes pa la sogs pa 'khor rnams kyis gsang bdag
NK088(su)001:14317: phyag na rdo rje la ston pa chen po'i spyan
NK088(su)001:14318: sngar ma yin par gud du logs su sgo gsum
NK088(su)001:14320: mnyes pas gnang ba'i rgyur gyur pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:14321: ye shes chen po rmad du byung ba'i rang snang ba'i me tog khyad par can dang /
NK088(su)001:14322: phyi nang gsang ba'i ting nge'i mchod pa mang po bsam pas sprul te mchod nas zhus pa /
NK088(su)001:14323: 'di ltar rmad byung ngo mtshar khyod //
NK088(su)001:14324: ces pa la pa 'dir ston pas gsungs pa ltar
NK088(su)001:14325: yon tan mchog rmad byung ngo mtshar ba mnga' ba'i
NK088(su)001:14326: skyes bu phyag na rdo rje khyod /
NK088(su)001:14327: rgyal ba sangs rgyas rdo rje 'dzin pa chen po'i
NK088(su)001:14328: thugs las rgyal tshab tu 'khrungs pa skyes tshul ji
NK088(su)001:14329: ltar da ltar gyi zhing khams 'dir skur snang nas
NK088(su)001:14330: ston par gyur zhig gu pa khyod ni /
NK088(su)001:14331: rnal 'byor pa'i yab rgyal ba'i sras chos thams cad
NK088(su)001:14332: rang bzhin dang gnyis med pa sangs rgyas kun gyi
NK088(su)001:14333: thugs gcig dang brel ba lags pas /
NK088(su)001:14334: khyod kyi gsang sngags kyi bka'i chos kyi 'khor lo rab bskor bas /
NK088(su)001:14335: log lam dang bral ba'i rnam dag nye lam lam mchog gsang sngags mchog gi don dam pa rnams /
NK088(su)001:14336: thun mong ma yin pa'i tshig gis gsal bar mtshon
NK088(su)001:14337: te bshad du gsol gsal bar mdzod zhes zhus pa'i
NK088(su)001:14338: a ho dgyes sgra dang bcas par gsol ba'o //
NK088(su)001:14339: gnang nas bshad par ltar chos bshad pa bstan pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:14341: de nas dam pa rdo rje bdag gis rdo rje bskor te bsgyur nas /
NK088(su)001:14342: brjid bag tu rdo rje tshig tu smras pa zhes pa /
NK088(su)001:14343: sdud pa po la bos nas de nas gsol ba
NK088(su)001:14344: btab ma thag par bdag dam pa rdo rje gsang
NK088(su)001:14346: ston pas dbang rtags lag tu rdo rje rgya gram bzhag pa de bskor te /
NK088(su)001:14347: bla bkyal ba'i spobs pa yod pas brjid bag dang ldan pas /
NK088(su)001:14348: rdo rje theg pa mtshon pa'i tshig tu sgra ston
NK088(su)001:14349: pas kho bo ji skad bstan pa ltar smras pa
NK088(su)001:14350: bshad pa zhes pa'i don to //
NK088(su)001:14352: +amo h'u m+aum a ho zhes pa /
NK088(su)001:14353: yi ge gsum ni bshad zin te rgyud don ji lta ba bzhin bshad pa'o //
NK088(su)001:14354: de dag kyang 'dus pa'i 'khor la rgyas par bshad
NK088(su)001:14355: par dgyes pa'i yi ge a ho gnyis brjod pa'o
NK088(su)001:14356: // rgyal ba'i sras ni cang mi gsung //
NK088(su)001:14357: mi gsung ba ni rgya cher bshad //
NK088(su)001:14358: ces pa la sogs pa rdo rje 'dzin pa chen
NK088(su)001:14359: po rgyal ba ril gyi gdung rgyud sras po du
NK088(su)001:14360: byung ba de ni ci'ang gsung mi brjod de brjod
NK088(su)001:14361: du'ang med do // ma gsung ba nyid brjod pa
NK088(su)001:14362: thams cad pa'i phyir gsung ngo bar mi rtog par
NK088(su)001:14363: bstan pa rgya chen thams cad du gsal bar bka'
NK088(su)001:14364: du'ang med do // bshad stsal to // de'i tshul ni /
NK088(su)001:14365: gsang sngags theg pa chen po'i ngo bo'i bshad du
NK088(su)001:14366: med pa'i chos nyid brjod pa dang bral ba'i rgyud
NK088(su)001:14368: 'das pa'i rgyal ba sangs rgyas rnams kyis kyang ma bshad gsungs te gsung zhing brjod du med do //
NK088(su)001:14369: tshul de bzhin du rigs kyi bdag po ston pa rgyal mchog kyang rdo rje 'dzin pa yang /
NK088(su)001:14370: tshig tu sprul pa ltar rnam par bshad par mi bzhed de bka' mi stsol te /
NK088(su)001:14371: rig pa'i gsung mnga' bas byin rlabs kyis rgya cher
NK088(su)001:14372: gdul bya 'khor gyi rig pa la bshad pa mjal
NK088(su)001:14373: bar byed pas dgongs pas chos ston to //
NK088(su)001:14375: skye ba med pa'i chos nyid 'di //
NK088(su)001:14376: zhes pa dag gang rgyu rkyen dang bral bas dngos
NK088(su)001:14377: gzhi skye ba med pa'i don chos nyid nges pa
NK088(su)001:14378: ni / de ltar ngo bo byung skyes ma myong
NK088(su)001:14379: bas rgyu 'bras kyi rtsa bcud du snying po bshad
NK088(su)001:14380: gsal ba'i snying po'i don gyi dngos po ma nor
NK088(su)001:14381: ba'i rgyud gang yin pa 'di brjod du med pa
NK088(su)001:14382: la brjod pas mi phebs tshig tu smra bar yod
NK088(su)001:14383: ma yin bshad cing brjod par rig pa ma yin
NK088(su)001:14384: ni / no // spros pa nyid na gol ba zhes //
NK088(su)001:14385: zhes pa dag tshig rgyas par spros pa bshad pa
NK088(su)001:14386: ni don la mi phebs pas 'khrul pa gol ba
NK088(su)001:14387: zhes yin par sangs rgyas kun gyis kyang yang dag
NK088(su)001:14388: bshad gsungs so // de bas gtan tshigs la snyegs
NK088(su)001:14389: par rigs kyi bdag pos rdo rje rgyal po nyid
NK088(su)001:14390: tshig tu bka' ma stsal bar ma phyung bar /
NK088(su)001:14391: kho bo la sogs pa la ting nge 'dzin dgongs pa'o bshad de /
NK088(su)001:14392: mnyam pa nyid gsang sngags rgya mtsho las mi g.yo bar bzhugs so //
NK088(su)001:14393: dgongs pa ji ltar brgyud zhe na /
NK088(su)001:14394: dgongs pa'i don rnams gang 'byin pa //
NK088(su)001:14395: zhes pa dag gsang sngags theg pa chen po'i rgyud
NK088(su)001:14396: mchog 'di gsal bar dgongs pas gang 'byin pa ston
NK088(su)001:14397: pa'i tshul yang / dper ji ltar me long ji
NK088(su)001:14398: ltar g.ya' dwang bar gzugs brnyan rang dbang med par
NK088(su)001:14399: pa'i tshul yang / 'byung ba ltar / gsang ba'i
NK088(su)001:14400: dgongs don mchog sdud po dang 'khor gyi rig pa
NK088(su)001:14401: dwang ba la byin rlabs kyis rang snang gyur pa
NK088(su)001:14402: pa'i tshul yang / 'byung ba ltar / shar ba'o
NK088(su)001:14403: // 'o na de yang tshig gis mtshon du med
NK088(su)001:14404: pa'i tshul yang / 'byung ba ltar / shar ba'o
NK088(su)001:14405: // dam zhe na / dgongs pa'i don gis mtshon
NK088(su)001:14406: pa'i tshul yang / 'byung ba ltar / shar ba'o
NK088(su)001:14407: // dam zhe na / pa'i phyir / ma skyes
NK088(su)001:14409: zhes pa la sogs pa rgyud kyi ma skyes ngo
NK088(su)001:14410: bo brjod pa dang bral ba'i rtsa bar snying po'i
NK088(su)001:14411: gyur pa'i don gyis tshig tu bshad du med spro
NK088(su)001:14413: mi mthun pa ston pa ni dkri phyir ston cing mtshon pa'o //
NK088(su)001:14414: de la gang dag dkri zhe na /
NK088(su)001:14415: mtshan ma tshig gi rnal 'byor pa //
NK088(su)001:14416: zhes pa dag zhe na rtog mtshan ma ma bral
NK088(su)001:14417: bas sgra yid la byed pa tshig gi rnal 'byor
NK088(su)001:14418: rnams / tshig snga ma'i rjes su phyi ma longs
NK088(su)001:14419: btags nas tshig la zhib mthar chags su brjod pa
NK088(su)001:14420: rnams / skad zer yang / don gyi ngo bo'i
NK088(su)001:14421: mtha' yang ma mthong bas don la rtsing don yal
NK088(su)001:14423: sgra'i tshig phyir rjes su shes pa blo 'brangs pas
NK088(su)001:14424: gsang sngags kyi gting mthong ba'i rtsal zhan nus pa
NK088(su)001:14426: gsang sngags la dkri ba drangs shing gsang don gyis
NK088(su)001:14427: yid tshim bsam pa drangs zhing rtogs par bya ba'i
NK088(su)001:14428: ched du / don mi dmigs mtshon du med pa
NK088(su)001:14429: las de dmigs pa'i mtshon pa'i byin rlabs kyi tshig
NK088(su)001:14430: dang sgra rgyud 'di lta bu cho 'phrul bstan nas
NK088(su)001:14431: gsang ba de kho na nyid tshig gis de mtshon
NK088(su)001:14432: rtogs shing goms par bya ba ni dgos ched do
NK088(su)001:14433: ched du / // dgos pa'i yang dgos pa gang snyam pa la /
NK088(su)001:14434: bde gshegs rgyal ba kun gyi thugs //
NK088(su)001:14435: zhes pa dag bde ba chen po'i ngang du son
NK088(su)001:14436: pa'i gdul dbang gi mtshan tha dad du grags pa
NK088(su)001:14437: kun gyi thugs ye shes gsang ba'i brtag dka' la
NK088(su)001:14438: 'bras bu lhun snying po don gyis grub pa'i ngo
NK088(su)001:14439: bo bsgrub bya'i don blang dor dang bral ba mnyam
NK088(su)001:14440: nyid ni / chos kyi sku chen po byang chub zhes kyang bya /
NK088(su)001:14441: ril bkod pas theg pa chen po zhes kyang bya /
NK088(su)001:14442: de lta bu'i mtshan nyid gsal bar ma bsgribs kun la bsnums pa'i khyab snang ba don te /
NK088(su)001:14443: lam la gnas pa rnams kun kyis rang rig pa'i de nyid mngon sum du mthong bar bya ba /
NK088(su)001:14445: thob dgos par bya ba yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK088(su)001:14447: nga ni dus gsum bzhugs pa yi //
NK088(su)001:14448: rgyal ba kun gyi snying po ste //
NK088(su)001:14449: zhes pa dag gsang ba'i bdag po kho bo nyid ni /
NK088(su)001:14450: 'das pa dang da ltar dang ma 'ongs pa'i dus
NK088(su)001:14451: gsum du bzhugs pa'i bde bar gshegs pa'i rgyal ba
NK088(su)001:14452: kun thugs nyid snying po ste yin pas /
NK088(su)001:14453: mtha' gang du'ang rnam pa can du snang ma myong
NK088(su)001:14454: ba'i stong par sbas ngo bo don nyid sus kyang
NK088(su)001:14455: mthong dka' ba'i rgyud kyi rgyal po 'di'i don mi
NK088(su)001:14456: 'dra bas don la brda sbyor ba dang /
NK088(su)001:14457: mthun pa dpe dang mi mthun pas don la sbyor ba dang /
NK088(su)001:14458: lde'u mig gsum la sogs pa dag gis mtshon nas /
NK088(su)001:14459: mnyam nyid ji bzhin pa rigs pa la bstan snang
NK088(su)001:14460: bar sgo dbye 'os byas nas gsha' bas de ston
NK088(su)001:14461: pa po rjod byed la 'chad pa'i skyes bu'o //
NK088(su)001:14463: sbas pa'i don mtshon 'byung ba'i rigs //
NK088(su)001:14464: zhes pa dag thugs la gab cing sbas par ma
NK088(su)001:14465: byung ba'i don ni rgyud 'di'i don te brjod byar
NK088(su)001:14466: gyur pa de tshig gis mtshon 'byung ba'i gsal bar
NK088(su)001:14467: bya bar rigs shing ma shes pa ma mthong rnams
NK088(su)001:14469: de mthong mtshan bya'i don rtogs na don ni ye
NK088(su)001:14470: ma bcos pa'i de kho na nyid du 'dod cing
NK088(su)001:14472: de nas ngas bshad do zhes zhal gyis bzhes pa'i don to //
NK088(su)001:14473: zhes pa gsang ba'i bdag po des /
NK088(su)001:14474: zhes pa dag /de skad ces gsang sngags theg pa'i
NK088(su)001:14475: bdag po sems dpa' rdo rjes chos ril 'dir dgos
NK088(su)001:14476: 'brel bzhir 'dus par rgol ba pos mi tshugs par
NK088(su)001:14478: de nas lang ka'i bdag po zhes pa sgra bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:14479: 'brel ba dgos ched kyi yan lag ces pa pa
NK088(su)001:14480: le'u yi mtshan te rnam pa bzhir phye nas bstan
NK088(su)001:14481: to // le'u bzhi bcu rtsa dgu pa 'grel pa'o ////de nas yang gsang ba'i bdag pos /
NK088(su)001:14482: lang ka'i bdag po la bos te smras pa /
NK088(su)001:14483: zhes pa dgos 'grel bstan ma thag par yan lag
NK088(su)001:14484: bzhi pa bstan pa'i phyir bos nas bka' stsal pa
NK088(su)001:14485: ni / lang ka'i bdag po 'dren pa'i yan lag gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:14486: zhes pa la sogs pa de nyid nye bar bstan
NK088(su)001:14487: pa dngos ni rgyud kyi tshig gi dngos po las
NK088(su)001:14488: bshad pa'i dngos po nang ris mi mthun par 'dren
NK088(su)001:14489: pa ste de khyed la bshad par bgro bar bya'o
NK088(su)001:14490: zhes gnang ba'o // lang ka'i bdag po 'di lta ste /
NK088(su)001:14491: zhes pa de rgyas par bshad pa ni rnam grangs
NK088(su)001:14492: phye nas bstan par bshad pa'i yan lag drug gi
NK088(su)001:14495: gang la lta dang sgo 'byed dang //
NK088(su)001:14496: zhes pa dag rnam grangs brjod pa'o //
NK088(su)001:14497: me long bcu zhes pa 'chad pa'i dpe bcu yi las kyis brtags pa'o //
NK088(su)001:14498: tshig don zhes pa bshad thabs 'dis rgyud kyi tshig don la bkab ste bshad par bya ba'o //
NK088(su)001:14499: de bas na rgyud bshad lugs 'grel lugs kyang don gyis bcur shes par byos shig pa'o //
NK088(su)001:14500: re re nas bstan pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:14501: lang ka'i bdag po 'di lta ste //
NK088(su)001:14502: gang la lta dang lta ba ni //
NK088(su)001:14503: zhes pa dag sdud pa po la bos nas grangs bstan pa 'di lta ste yang /
NK088(su)001:14504: thog mar lta ba nye bar bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:14505: rgyud kyi dngos po gang la lta ba'i yul dang
NK088(su)001:14506: lta ba'i shes pa gnyis med par gsal ba'i don
NK088(su)001:14507: ni / dper na bya khyung gi dngos po nam
NK088(su)001:14508: mkhar 'phur 'gro ba'i nus pas ri brag gyen thur
NK088(su)001:14509: ril gshog pa'i khob 'og tu chud pas lding ba
NK088(su)001:14510: yang 'phang mtho la nyam nga ba dang rjes med
NK088(su)001:14511: ni / pa ltar / rnal 'byor pa lam chen
NK088(su)001:14512: por nges pas de nyid rgyud kyi don 'di la
NK088(su)001:14513: blo rtogs 'gro ba par byed pa yang lung man
NK088(su)001:14514: ngag dang thabs kyis lta bas chos so cog ma
NK088(su)001:14515: 'dres la yongs su rdzogs par rtogs pa la spyod
NK088(su)001:14516: yul med par ye shes chen por rang gsal ba
NK088(su)001:14517: ni / pa ltar / las / shes pa drug
NK088(su)001:14518: mun pa log spyod byis pa phyogs su rig pa
NK088(su)001:14519: mtha' dbus 'byed pa dam pa chen po gis bdar
NK088(su)001:14521: blang dor med par spyi rgya rlabs kyis bcad par 'gyur ro //
NK088(su)001:14522: bgrod par bya ba'i sa tshig dag /ces pa la
NK088(su)001:14523: sogs pa sa bcad par bya ba'i phyir dpe stag
NK088(su)001:14524: gi mchongs rtsal gyis mchongs tshad kyi sa gcod pa
NK088(su)001:14525: ltar / 'dir don gyi tshoms gang ston pa'i tshig
NK088(su)001:14526: gi bar mtshams rnams sa gcod lde'u mig gis dbye
NK088(su)001:14528: tshig dkyus kyi mtshams tshoms ma 'dres par bya'o //
NK088(su)001:14530: ji ltar gang gi khob 'og tu //
NK088(su)001:14531: zhes pa dper na seng ge'i rtsal gyis mchongs pa'i
NK088(su)001:14532: khob 'og tu ri brag yul khams mang po 'dus
NK088(su)001:14533: pa ltar / tshig mang po dbu zhabs rnams rgyud
NK088(su)001:14534: don gyi ngo bo ma nor ba gzhi lam 'bras
NK088(su)001:14535: bu lta bu gcig tu bsdus te /
NK088(su)001:14536: de las so sor yan lag tu 'byung bar shes par bya'o //
NK088(su)001:14537: de bas na 'dir yang don lhun gyis grub pa
NK088(su)001:14538: gcig las rnal 'byor gsum du phye nas 'grel pa'ang
NK088(su)001:14539: ngo bo nyid gcig tu dbyer med par ston pa'o
NK088(su)001:14540: // tshig gi mtshams sbrel pa ni /
NK088(su)001:14541: gang dag gang ltar gang 'gro ba //
NK088(su)001:14542: zhes pa dper na ngang pa rnams phyogs gang dang
NK088(su)001:14543: gang du gang ltar 'gro ba dag pa'i gom 'gros
NK088(su)001:14544: drangs por 'brel la snga rjes phyi rjes kyis non
NK088(su)001:14545: pas 'brel ba snang mthar chags su gyur pa ltar
NK088(su)001:14546: / sngar brjod pa'i tshig dang phyi don brjod bya'i
NK088(su)001:14547: ngo bos gcad pa'i tshig snga phyi mtshams dag mi
NK088(su)001:14548: 'khrugs par gong 'og tshig 'brel ba dang bcas par
NK088(su)001:14550: rang rkyen gnyer gyi tshig ni /
NK088(su)001:14551: gang 'gro gnas su bgrod pa ni //
NK088(su)001:14552: zhes pa dper rus sbal gang 'gro gyi dngos po
NK088(su)001:14553: gnas gang du 'gro ba'i 'gros kyang gzhan gyis g.yo
NK088(su)001:14554: 'gul 'gro bar mi mngon mthong yang rang gi nur
NK088(su)001:14555: shugs kyis 'gro bas phyin pa ltar /
NK088(su)001:14556: tshig tu yi ge bshad pa'i don gnas skabs kyi
NK088(su)001:14557: gtan tshigs lung man ngag gi tshig rang gnyer gyis
NK088(su)001:14558: don gyi ngo bo gzhi gang dngos yin pa la
NK088(su)001:14559: / sel de bzhin med par bshad tshul mtha' bcu
NK088(su)001:14560: dang gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum dang drug sbyar zhing
NK088(su)001:14562: ldem dgongs man ngag gi tshig gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:14563: gang zhig gang ltar gang 'gro ba //
NK088(su)001:14564: zhes pa dag dper gna' phrug chung ngu gang zhig
NK088(su)001:14565: brag gi g.yang sar gang ltar 'gro ba gang 'gro
NK088(su)001:14566: ba ni chung bas ri dwags gzhan par mi 'tshams
NK088(su)001:14567: ma rigs na'ang kho nyid la bde blag tu 'tshams
NK088(su)001:14568: snang pa ltar phyi pa lta bu'i ngag barlangasa po
NK088(su)001:14569: dang lnga tsho bzhi spyad pa lta bu zher 'debs
NK088(su)001:14570: pa'i skyon tshig 'phrul du snang ba'i brjod sgra dag
NK088(su)001:14571: tshig bstan pa yang 'dir bshad pa ltar don gzhan
NK088(su)001:14572: du ldem po la dgongs nas gsungs pas /
NK088(su)001:14573: don 'grub par rang thad du gang mi 'tshams yang /
NK088(su)001:14574: de nyid kyis 'du shes bsgyur nas 'dul bar byed
NK088(su)001:14575: pas bder 'tshams snang 'tshams pa ste de ltar ston
NK088(su)001:14576: sbyor pa'o // gtar ka gegs sel gyi tshig ci lta bu snyam pa la /
NK088(su)001:14577: gang dag yid la btags pa'i zas //
NK088(su)001:14578: dri ba'ang yin zhes pa dper na glag khra mo
NK088(su)001:14579: zhig rang gi bsam par 'dod pa'i kha zas la
NK088(su)001:14580: 'jums pa'i tshe / sha g.yag la sogs pa gang
NK088(su)001:14581: gi yang tha mal gyi sha bor nas snying 'byin
NK088(su)001:14582: 'jums pa'i tshe / pa bzhin / shes bya'i dngos
NK088(su)001:14583: po gang du ston pa'i skabs su'ang gtar ka dang
NK088(su)001:14584: the tshom gyi don gyi mdud pa dmigs su bzung
NK088(su)001:14585: nas don gang mi gsal ba mthong dka' ba de
NK088(su)001:14586: lung man ngag gis brda mjal bar mngon du the
NK088(su)001:14587: tshom med par bar ston byed lan thebs pa'ang yin
NK088(su)001:14588: 'jums pa'i tshe / pa bzhin / pa'o // tshad
NK088(su)001:14589: ma bka' gzhung gi tshig ji lta bu snyam pa
NK088(su)001:14590: 'jums pa'i tshe / pa bzhin / pa'o // la / ji ltar sgra rlan rgyun byung na //
NK088(su)001:14591: zhes pa dper na sgra snyan dus kyi 'brug grags pas char gyi rgyun bab byung na /
NK088(su)001:14592: mi rnams kyis gang skyes rtsi thog gi dngos po
NK088(su)001:14593: dbyar dus su skye bar shes pa la yid ches
NK088(su)001:14595: de bzhin tshad ma'i sgro skur bral bas rdzun nor
NK088(su)001:14596: spangs pa'i lung zab mo'i yul byung na tshig gsungs
NK088(su)001:14597: pas / lung man ngag gsum chos rtags bzhi dang /
NK088(su)001:14598: lung man gag gis lam pa dag don ma nor
NK088(su)001:14599: ma bcos pa de nyid yin pa'i gtan tshigs yin
NK088(su)001:14600: par nges yid ches par byed pa'o //
NK088(su)001:14601: mtshon pa de'i tshig gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:14602: gang 'dir dag pa'i me long gis //
NK088(su)001:14603: zhes pa dper na me long g.ya' med pas byad bzhin dang gzugs brnyan gsal bar ston pa ltar /
NK088(su)001:14604: don gyi skabs gang rung du'ang don de nye bar
NK088(su)001:14605: rtogs par mtshon par byed pa'i dpe me long pha
NK088(su)001:14606: rol la grags pa'i chos dag gis don gyi dngos
NK088(su)001:14607: po gang mi mthong ba brtag dka' ba de gsal
NK088(su)001:14608: bar byed pa ni don dper sbyor ba dang /
NK088(su)001:14609: tha snyad mthun mi mthun dper sbyor ba ste /
NK088(su)001:14610: chos nyid ma skyes pa 'dus ma byas pa yin te /
NK088(su)001:14611: log rtog lta bu'o zhes pa dang /
NK088(su)001:14612: de ltar yin te nam mkha' lta bu'o zhes pa la sogs pa'o //
NK088(su)001:14613: bsnol mtshams 'phen sdud kyi tshig gis gong 'og gi 'khrugs pa bsdebs pa gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:14615: zhes pa dper na thags kyi bkad gong 'og tu
NK088(su)001:14616: dgos pa 'og dang steng nas 'chol bar len pa
NK088(su)001:14617: ltar / rgyud kyi tshig tshoms gong 'og 'khrugs pa'i
NK088(su)001:14618: bar 'phen sdud kyi tshig gis go rims 'khrugs pa
NK088(su)001:14619: bsdebs pa la nyams su blang zhing go bde bar
NK088(su)001:14620: ltar / byed pa dang / yang seng ge'i mchongs
NK088(su)001:14621: pa slob ba'i stobs ma 'dres par gcig nas gcig
NK088(su)001:14623: rgyud kyi tshig tshom 'khrug ma la bar dag bzhag
NK088(su)001:14624: cing de nyid go rims dang 'dug sa bsgyur te
NK088(su)001:14625: gong 'og mthun par shes pas gcig tu bsdebs pa'o
NK088(su)001:14626: // lang ka'i bdag po de dag ni /
NK088(su)001:14627: zhes pa la sogs pa sdud pa po la bos
NK088(su)001:14628: nas bshad pa de dag rnam pa bcu ni bshad
NK088(su)001:14629: pa'i thabs kyi yan lag dbu zhabs su sbyar bar
NK088(su)001:14630: shes par gyis shig ces gdams pa'o //
NK088(su)001:14631: zhes gsang ba'i bdag pos zhes pa sgra bzhin te bstan pa'i yon tan no //
NK088(su)001:14632: yongs su 'dren pa'i yan lag rnam pa bgros pa zhes pa le'u'i mtshan no //
NK088(su)001:14633: le'u lnga bcu pa 'grel pa'o ////rjes su mthun par
NK088(su)001:14634: bshad pa yan lag lnga pa nges don bye brag
NK088(su)001:14635: gi gtan tshigs gang snyam pa la /
NK088(su)001:14636: de gnas gsang ba'i bdag pos /
NK088(su)001:14637: sems dpa' chen po lang ka'i bdag po de la nges par bos te rnam par smras pa /
NK088(su)001:14638: zhes pa 'dren pa tshig gi yan lag bshad ma
NK088(su)001:14639: thag par phyag na rdo rjes lang ka la nges
NK088(su)001:14640: par bos te / gtan tshigs ma 'dres par bya ba'i phyir bshad pa'o //
NK088(su)001:14641: lang ka'i bdag po 'di lta ste /
NK088(su)001:14642: gang du nges pa'i yan lag ni //
NK088(su)001:14643: zhes pa dag sdud pa po la bos nas nye bar bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:14644: skabs thams cad du nges don ma 'dres par bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:14645: gang la gang gis gang brjod pa //
NK088(su)001:14646: 'brel gzhi bshad sbyor brjod pa'i sgo //
NK088(su)001:14648: sdud pa po dang 'khor gyi dngos po gang la
NK088(su)001:14649: ston pas gang gis rgyud 'di gang brjod bshad pa
NK088(su)001:14650: la / gleng gzhi dang rtsa ba gleng bslang ba ni rgyud kyi rgyu rkyen no //
NK088(su)001:14652: 'dren pa'i yan lag rgyud kyi bshad thabs bcu dang /
NK088(su)001:14653: nges par sbyor ba'i yan lag dang /
NK088(su)001:14654: gleng bslang ba brjod pa 'byung ba'i rtsa ba dang /
NK088(su)001:14655: yan lag lngas bstan par brjod pa'i bya ba rgyud
NK088(su)001:14656: kyi don dri ma med pa gsal ba snang bar
NK088(su)001:14657: sgo byed pa'i don yang yan lag 'di nyid de
NK088(su)001:14658: / de 'byung ba'i rgyu ni gdul bya'i gang la
NK088(su)001:14659: dngos po la thugs rje'i bya ras spyan ras gzigs
NK088(su)001:14660: dbang gis mi gtong bar gsal ba'i dbang gis /
NK088(su)001:14661: 'dir gdul bya mang po mtha' thug med pa'i 'gro
NK088(su)001:14662: gang dag yang nges pa'i yan lag 'di ni nyid
NK088(su)001:14663: kyis don gyi snod bzhi ru kho nar gzigs mkhyen
NK088(su)001:14664: te / zhen chags can dang log sred can //
NK088(su)001:14665: rigs rgyud can dang blo gros can //
NK088(su)001:14666: zhes pa 'dod pa la zhen pa'i gdul bya dang /
NK088(su)001:14667: log pa'i lta spyod la dga' ba dang ldan pa'i gdul bya dang /
NK088(su)001:14668: byang chub sems nges par skyes pas spyod pa brtul
NK088(su)001:14669: phod pas theg pa chen po gsang sngags pa'i rigs
NK088(su)001:14670: dang ldan pa'i gdul bya dang /
NK088(su)001:14671: shes rab dang ting nge 'dzin dang ldan pa'i gdul bya dang /
NK088(su)001:14672: gdul bya thams cad ril de ltar bzhir cha bzhir snang ba ste gsal ba bzhi tsho thog ma'o //
NK088(su)001:14673: ched du bstan pa sngags bstan thabs ni /
NK088(su)001:14674: 'dod khrid sbyor dang nges par snang //
NK088(su)001:14676: 'dod pa can la de nyid kyis 'dul ba dang /
NK088(su)001:14677: log sred can la khrid ldem dgongs kyi tshig gis drang ba dang /
NK088(su)001:14678: sems skyes pa'i rigs can rnams gsang ba'i don bstan la sbyor gzhug pa dang /
NK088(su)001:14679: blo gros can la nges pa'i don nyid kyis 'dul lo //
NK088(su)001:14680: de dag bzhi phrag gnyis pa'o //
NK088(su)001:14681: de dag res 'ga' cha bzhi ste //
NK088(su)001:14682: zhes pa dag gdul thabs de dag bzhi po dag
NK088(su)001:14683: kyang res 'ga' lan grangs ston pa'i sgras 'dul ba'i
NK088(su)001:14684: chos cha yis dbye ba'ang bzhi phrag mi mthun pa
NK088(su)001:14686: gdul bya 'dul ba'i skabs la bab pa'i dus su
NK088(su)001:14687: 'dod pa'i chos lta bu zhig la'ang mthar phyin pa'i
NK088(su)001:14688: dgos ched de gdul bya gang 'dul ba'i skabs su
NK088(su)001:14689: dgos ched dang / de la de skad bya ba gang rung gis nges pa'i tshig dang /
NK088(su)001:14690: bstan pa'i don rang gi ngo bo ci zhig yin pa dang /
NK088(su)001:14691: don gyi dmigs btsal ba'i gal po'i dmigs gar 'gyur ba'o //
NK088(su)001:14692: sbrags bcas pa las ma'i sgras 'dul thabs gcig la'ang bzhi bzhi ldan par ston pa'o //
NK088(su)001:14693: de dag bzhi phrag gsum pa'o //
NK088(su)001:14694: de gtan tshigs gang gis yid ches par byed ce na /
NK088(su)001:14695: bka' don gtan tshigs rig pa bzhi //
NK088(su)001:14697: rgyal ba'i lung bka' las snang ba dang /
NK088(su)001:14698: don shes rtogs gyi ngo bo dang /
NK088(su)001:14699: rang rang la bden par grub pa'i gtan tshigs dang /
NK088(su)001:14700: mngon sum dang 'thad pa sogs kyi rig pas yid ches par byed pas bzhi phrag bzhi'o //
NK088(su)001:14702: zhes pa gtan tshigs chos rtags bzhi'i tshul ji ltar
NK088(su)001:14703: sbyor ba ni bshad pa'i bstan pa'i gzhi chos gang
NK088(su)001:14704: ston yang / lung las gsal bar snang ba 'byung ba dang /
NK088(su)001:14705: don gyi ngo bo dang mi 'gal ba dang /
NK088(su)001:14706: gtan tshigs kyis rgyas pa dang /
NK088(su)001:14707: rigs pas 'thad na nor du rung ba ste bzhi
NK088(su)001:14708: phrag lnga ste khas blang ba'i rnam grangs nyi shu'o
NK088(su)001:14709: // des don gyi nges pa'i gtan tshigs don ni gang snyam pa la /
NK088(su)001:14710: thams cad med rgyu btags chags pa //
NK088(su)001:14712: thams cad rkyen las byung bas ther zug med pa
NK088(su)001:14713: dang dngos po thams cad rnams kyi de kho na
NK088(su)001:14714: med nyid mtha' ril ka nas dag pa nyid thams
NK088(su)001:14715: cad ma bkol snang ba yang gzhi rgyu yin pas
NK088(su)001:14716: ming gis bla dwags rang blos ji ltar btags pa
NK088(su)001:14718: bsgrub 'grub ji ltar bltas par snang //
NK088(su)001:14719: zhes pa 'bras bu'i dngos gzhir gyur pas /
NK088(su)001:14720: lam pas ji ltar don du gnyer ba bsgrub ltar
NK088(su)001:14721: 'bras bu tha dad 'grub 'grub cing lta bas ji
NK088(su)001:14722: ltar bltas pa'i don tha dad par theg pa so
NK088(su)001:14723: so'i ngo bzhin yang snang ngo //
NK088(su)001:14724: gang dag gang la brda 'phrad pas //
NK088(su)001:14725: zhes pa gtan tshigs kyi sgo nas don gyi dngos
NK088(su)001:14726: po gang dag rnal 'byor pa gang la su zhig
NK088(su)001:14727: gi blo la go zhing brda 'jal bar brda 'phra
NK088(su)001:14729: gang gi don len nyid du nges //
NK088(su)001:14731: gang gi shes bya zab mo'i dngos po nyid dang
NK088(su)001:14732: 'phrad nas don nyams su len pa la nyid du
NK088(su)001:14734: de bas na bstan pa bzhi'i don ma nor ba
NK088(su)001:14735: gong gis bzhi cha phyi ma gnyis gtan la 'bebs
NK088(su)001:14736: pa'i gtan tshigs bka' don bzhi smos te shes pa'i
NK088(su)001:14737: mtshan nyid do // de skad ces nges pa dam pa nyid du bgros pas /
NK088(su)001:14738: zhes pa bshad pa bzhin nges don gyi bye brag mchog bshad pa'o //
NK088(su)001:14739: dman pa'i 'khor rnams kyis kyang gtan tshigs rgyas par
NK088(su)001:14740: khong du chud pa'i rgyus don tshig brda smos pa
NK088(su)001:14741: tsam gyis gsang sngags kyi don nyid nyams rnyed par
NK088(su)001:14742: gyur to // le'u lnga bcu rtsa gcig pa 'grel
NK088(su)001:14743: pa'o ////de nas gang gsang ba'i bdag pos des zhes
NK088(su)001:14745: yan lag lnga pa bshad ma thag par /
NK088(su)001:14746: drug pa rjes mthud du bstan pa'i phyir sdud pa po la bos nas bka' stsal pa /
NK088(su)001:14747: yan lag drug gi tha ma 'dis rdzogs pas rtogs
NK088(su)001:14748: pa lta ba ting nge 'dzin gyi nyams su blang
NK088(su)001:14749: ba 'jug thabs lung gzhan don bstan pa ni /
NK088(su)001:14750: gnas skabs don dang 'bras bu mthar nges pa la sbyor bas ming 'grub ste /
NK088(su)001:14751: dbye bas drug cu rtsa gcig tu bshad pa'o //
NK088(su)001:14752: de la dang po rtogs pa rnam bzhi gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:14753: rang bzhin 'byung sgo dbang sbyor dang //
NK088(su)001:14754: nges pa'i khong du chud pa yis //
NK088(su)001:14755: zhes pa chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin pa rtags
NK088(su)001:14756: na rang bzhin ma skyes pa zhig med pa bsam
NK088(su)001:14757: na thams cad du ma 'gags pa zhig snang ba
NK088(su)001:14758: nyid bden pa dbyer med par gcig pa'i ngo bo
NK088(su)001:14759: bshad pa ltar med rgyu btags chags bsgrub 'grub tu
NK088(su)001:14760: snang ba'i brtag bya'am tshul bya'i gzhir gyur pas rgyu
NK088(su)001:14763: chos thams cad sku gsung thugs 'bras bur 'byung ba'i sgo ste /
NK088(su)001:14764: gsung sku thugs a o +amo gyis mtshon pa'i las
NK088(su)001:14765: as mtshon pa'i rang bzhin chos so cog rang gi
NK088(su)001:14766: sems rgyu rkyen dang bral bas mtshan nyid gang du
NK088(su)001:14767: ma skyes par gsal ba'i gsung dang /
NK088(su)001:14768: de nyid nyi tshe ba'i stong pa ma yin te /
NK088(su)001:14769: ye shes su gsal bas dbyings ye shes gnyis med
NK088(su)001:14770: pa'i chos kyi sku yi ge cha gnyis pa'i tshul
NK088(su)001:14771: dang / de dag kyang rang byung gi ye shes
NK088(su)001:14772: chen po ye shes lnga ma btsal bar rdzogs pa'i
NK088(su)001:14773: thugs yi ge rdzogs pa'i tshul du sangs rgyas par
NK088(su)001:14775: byin gyi rlabs kyis rtogs pa ni /
NK088(su)001:14776: rtogs pa'i mthus rang dbang med par don la sbyor ba ste /
NK088(su)001:14777: dper na rgyu ras snam dkar po las kha dog
NK088(su)001:14778: dmar por sgyur ba'i mthu btsod la yod pa dang
NK088(su)001:14779: / sngon por bsgyur na rams pa yod bya ba ltar /
NK088(su)001:14780: khams gsum rang rig pa rnam par dag pa'i snam bu ye yin pa nyid /
NK088(su)001:14781: bshad pa'i rtogs pa gnyis kyi mtshon gyis rang rig
NK088(su)001:14782: pa la sku dang ye shes 'bras bu'i kha dog
NK088(su)001:14783: tu snang bar byed pa'i snums pa ni rlob pa'o
NK088(su)001:14784: // rig pa rang la shar ba ni brlabs pa'o //
NK088(su)001:14785: 'on kyang min pa las yin par bsgyur ba ni med do //
NK088(su)001:14786: mngon sum par rtogs pa ni /
NK088(su)001:14787: de ltar gsum gyi yang 'bras bu ste /
NK088(su)001:14788: chos rnams gsang sngags de kho na nyid lhun gyi
NK088(su)001:14789: grub pa'i don rang gi rig pa'i mngon sum rtogs
NK088(su)001:14790: pa yang sgra la rten pa dang don zhe la
NK088(su)001:14791: 'dzin pa tsam ma yin mi 'gyur nges pa'i khong
NK088(su)001:14792: du chud pa'i gdeng rnyed pa'o //
NK088(su)001:14793: de ltar bzhis de kho na nyid yang dag don la blo nges par lta ba bzhag par bya'o //
NK088(su)001:14794: 'di dag lta ba kho na ste bzhi phrag dang po'o //
NK088(su)001:14795: mtshan nyid rnam pa bzhi spyi dang bye brag tu bstan pa'i phyir /
NK088(su)001:14797: lhun gyis grub pa'i mtshan nyid yin //
NK088(su)001:14798: zhes pa mngon sum par rtogs pa'i ngo bo rang gsal shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba dang /
NK088(su)001:14799: de ltar mthong ba'i don la ting nge 'dzin gyis 'jug pa dang /
NK088(su)001:14800: spyod bsgom rjes su 'jug pa ting 'dzin dang spyod pa gnyis dang /
NK088(su)001:14801: de ltar 'bad pas zung du 'brel ba'i drod rtags
NK088(su)001:14802: 'bras bu'i mthar lam man chod rig 'dzin du gyur
NK088(su)001:14803: pa dang / mjug ma btsal bar lhun gyis grub
NK088(su)001:14804: pas bskyed du bya ba med pa'i 'bras bu chen
NK088(su)001:14806: rnal 'byor lnga'am bcu'i rgyu mthong rkyen gnyis bsgom mthar 'bras lhun grub lam 'bras bu'am /
NK088(su)001:14807: de dag ni rnal 'byor gsum shes pa gzhi 'jug
NK088(su)001:14808: pa lam 'bras bu chen po gyi don du'ang 'gyur
NK088(su)001:14810: dgos 'brel de dgos de mtshon dgos //
NK088(su)001:14811: de yi rjes su byed dgos yin //
NK088(su)001:14812: zhes pa snyegs pa'i don gyis 'dir rnal 'byor gsum dang lam gyi dgos 'brel du gyur te /
NK088(su)001:14813: rgyu shes rkyen 'jug 'bras bu grub pa'i 'bras bu'i
NK088(su)001:14814: mtshan nyid bzhi yang snga ma ni rgyu la phyi
NK088(su)001:14815: ma ni 'bras bu'i tshul du'ang 'brel te /
NK088(su)001:14816: snga ma ni thabs su 'gyur la phyi ma ni thabs las byung bar 'brel yang 'gyur ro //
NK088(su)001:14817: de bas na rnal 'byor lnga dang bcu yang rjes su mthun par 'gyur ro //
NK088(su)001:14818: de dag gi dgos pa ni so so cha rkyen yan lag gis dang du blang dgos pa'o //
NK088(su)001:14819: de la mtshon pa ni brjod pa ste de la brjod bya rjod byed do //
NK088(su)001:14820: brjod bya ni rgyud kyi don lam rim dang rnal 'byor gsum gyi skabs skabs kyis shes par bya'o //
NK088(su)001:14821: rjod byed ni rkyen tshig dang yi ge rnams kyis mtshon cing thob par byed pa'o //
NK088(su)001:14822: 'dir dgos pa brjod pa ni khyad par gyi dgos pa ste brjod bya mtshon dgos pa'o //
NK088(su)001:14823: de dag gi rjes su bsgrub pas de las su
NK088(su)001:14824: rung nas mthar phyin pa ni dgos pa'i yang dgos
NK088(su)001:14825: pa ste de bsgrub par bya ba yin no //
NK088(su)001:14826: de ltar bzhi phrag gsum mo //
NK088(su)001:14828: thos chung goms dang nges par 'gyur //
NK088(su)001:14829: zhes pa spyir bslab pa'i mtha' bcu yang /
NK088(su)001:14830: rim pa bsdus na thabs kyi theg pa'i gzhung ma
NK088(su)001:14831: nor bar thos par bya ba'i mtha' bcu shes pa
NK088(su)001:14832: thos pa la rag las pas thog mar gces pa
NK088(su)001:14833: dang / don gyi gdeng thos pa'i sgo nas chud de rtogs pa dang /
NK088(su)001:14834: rtogs pa la rnal 'byor du byas nas goms pa dang /
NK088(su)001:14835: goms pas las su rung bas 'bras bu mi 'gyur ba nges par thob pa'o //
NK088(su)001:14837: de'i dpe dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa'i yan lag bzhi ni /
NK088(su)001:14838: phye mthong zhugs dang thob pa yin //
NK088(su)001:14839: zhes pa thos pa'i shes rab kyi mig dwangs pa ni dper mig phye ba lta bu'o //
NK088(su)001:14840: thos bsam gyis don gyi gdeng rnyed pa ni /
NK088(su)001:14841: gsang sngags kyi dkyil 'khor rnam gsum mthong ba'o //
NK088(su)001:14842: dper phyi'i yul mthong ba dang 'dra'o //
NK088(su)001:14843: rtogs pa'i don la rnal 'byor du byed pa ni /
NK088(su)001:14844: dkyil 'khor gsum du zhugs pa ste /
NK088(su)001:14845: dper dkyil 'khor du bcug pa dang 'dra'o //
NK088(su)001:14846: de ltar zhugs te 'bad pas sa 'og ma non gong ma thob pa 'bras bu grub pa ni /
NK088(su)001:14847: dper dkyil 'khor du dbang thob pa dang 'dra ste /
NK088(su)001:14848: de ltar bzhi phrag lnga pa'o //
NK088(su)001:14849: thos chung dang lam phye mthong gnyis de dag ni lam zag pa dang po lnga /
NK088(su)001:14850: gnyis pa mthong gsum bsgom bzhi po mthar lam du sbyar ro //
NK088(su)001:14852: sems 'jug cing skye ba'i yan lag bzhi gang zhe na /
NK088(su)001:14853: de tshol de rnyed 'jug mngon gyur //
NK088(su)001:14854: zhes pa dang po kho nar snyegs pa'i sgras gsang
NK088(su)001:14855: sngags mig phye ba'i thams kyis don tshol ba dang
NK088(su)001:14856: / btsal bas gsang sngags kyi gdeng rnyed de bden pa mthong ba dang /
NK088(su)001:14857: de'i don 'dris par bya ba'i phyir 'jug pa dang /
NK088(su)001:14858: goms par byas pas mngon du gyur pa'o //
NK088(su)001:14859: de ltar bzhi phrag drug go //
NK088(su)001:14861: bsnyen pa nye bsnyen bsgrub dang 'grub //
NK088(su)001:14862: ces pa dang por lam tshol ba'i bsnyen pa'o //
NK088(su)001:14863: rtogs pa ni nye ba'i bsnyen pa'o //
NK088(su)001:14865: mthar phyin pa ni bsgrub pa 'grub chen po'o //
NK088(su)001:14866: 'og gi ma h+aa yo ga dbang du ni mnyam pa'i don shes pa ni bsnyen pa'o //
NK088(su)001:14867: bsgom pa ni nye bsnyen no //
NK088(su)001:14868: lta bsgom gnyis su med par grub pa bsgrub pa'o //
NK088(su)001:14869: de dag las su rung ba mngon du gyur pa bsgrub pa chen po ste bzhi phrag bdun no //
NK088(su)001:14870: mtshan nyid dang sbyar ba'i yang grub pa bzhi ni /
NK088(su)001:14872: lhun grub las su rung ba'o //
NK088(su)001:14873: zhes pa bshad pa de bzhin ltar 'jug pa'ang thos bsam gyis mnyam pa rtogs par 'gyur ba dang /
NK088(su)001:14874: rtogs pas rnal 'byor du 'dris par byed pas 'grub pa dang /
NK088(su)001:14875: bsgoms pas lta ba dang ting nge 'dzin zung du lhun gyis grub pa dang /
NK088(su)001:14876: de ltar gyur pas mthar phyin te 'bras bur grub pa las su rung ba'o dang /
NK088(su)001:14877: bzhi brgyad ni nges par lam du 'jug pa'i rim pa ste bdag gi don to //
NK088(su)001:14878: spyir gsang sngags 'byung 'jug gi yan lag ni lam
NK088(su)001:14879: la rim par zhugs nas gong du rim par skyed
NK088(su)001:14880: du 'byung ba'o // 'di dag las don gyi rnal 'byor lnga dang bcur dgyes pa'ang yin la /
NK088(su)001:14881: rnal 'byor gyi cha rkyen so so'i yan lag tu'ang 'gyur ro //
NK088(su)001:14882: gzhan gyi don du 'byung rims bzhi //
NK088(su)001:14883: g.yo dang cho 'phrul snang mdzad pa'o //
NK088(su)001:14884: zhes pa 'byung 'jug gi yan lag nges par gzung ba ni bdag don 'jug pa mthar phyin nas /
NK088(su)001:14885: gzhan don du thugs rje 'byung bas gzhan nges par sbyor ba kho na nyid do //
NK088(su)001:14887: thugs rje chen po kun tu g.yo ldang zhing skye ba dang /
NK088(su)001:14888: mtshan nyid ma nges pa'i sprul pa sna tshogs 'byung ba dang /
NK088(su)001:14889: sku gsung thugs kyi mdzad pa'i dngos po gdul bya la snang ba dang /
NK088(su)001:14890: des ji ltar 'tshams par mdzad pa dang mdzad spyod bzhi'o //
NK088(su)001:14892: ji ltar rim bzhin sbyar ba yin //
NK088(su)001:14894: bdag don tshul gyi ji lta bar lam pa de
NK088(su)001:14895: dag gi blo'i rim par 'gro don la sbyor ba'o
NK088(su)001:14896: // shes pa lnga gang snyam pa la /
NK088(su)001:14897: de shes de ma skyes par shes //
NK088(su)001:14898: de dus dngos med shes pa dang //
NK088(su)001:14899: ye nas shes pa rim bzhin no //
NK088(su)001:14900: zhes pa don bya ba'i gdul bya'i mtshan nyid ji lta ba ma 'dres par mkhyen pa dang /
NK088(su)001:14901: de lta bu'i gdul bya'i rang bzhin ma skyes par yang shes pa dang /
NK088(su)001:14902: de ltar mkhyen cing don byed pa'i dus shes pa dang /
NK088(su)001:14903: bdag dang gzhan dang thabs kun snang stong gi dngos po gnyis ka'ang med par mkhyen pa dang /
NK088(su)001:14904: de yang 'phral du btsal ba las byung ba ma yin te /
NK088(su)001:14905: ye phyi mo nyid nas thams cad gsal bar mkhyen
NK088(su)001:14906: pas 'gro don skal pa'i rim pa bzhin mdzad pa'o
NK088(su)001:14907: // skabs kha cig tu grangs kyi spyi dbang gis
